#: ../../content/developer.rst:6
msgid "Developer"
msgstr "Dasturchi"

#: ../../content/developer.rst:13
msgid ""
"Welcome to the developer documentation of Odoo! Whether you're a seasoned"
" developer or just getting started, you'll find here all the technical "
"guidance and resources you need for developing Odoo applications. Explore"
" our extensive collection of tutorials, how-to guides, and reference "
"materials to achieve your development goals."
msgstr ""
"Odoo dasturchi hujjatlariga xush kelibsiz! Tajribali dasturchi bo'lasizmi"
" yoki endigina boshlaayotgan bo'lasizmi, bu yerda Odoo ilovalarini ishlab"
" chiqish uchun zarur bo'lgan barcha texnik ko'rsatmalar va resurslarni"
" topasiz. Rivojlanish maqsadlaringizga erishish uchun o'quv qo'llanmalar,"
" amaliy qo'llanmalar va ma'lumotnomalarning keng to'plamini o'rganing."

#: ../../content/developer.rst:18
msgid ""
"The Odoo development ecosystem is built on a modular and extensible "
"architecture that allows you to extend existing applications or create "
"new ones to meet the specific needs of modern businesses. You can make "
"use of the tools and frameworks provided by Odoo to focus on getting your"
" web application up and running quickly, without needing to reinvent the "
"wheel and worry about the underlying infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ishlab chiqish ekotizimi modulli va kengaytiriluvchi arxitektura"
" asosida qurilgan bo'lib, u mavjud ilovalarni kengaytirish yoki zamonaviy"
" bizneslarning maxsus ehtiyojlarini qondirish uchun yangilarini yaratish"
" imkonini beradi. Odoo tomonidan taqdim etilgan vositalar va freymvorklardan"
" foydalanib, tekerlikni qayta ixtiro qilmasdan va asosiy infratuzilma"
" haqida qayg'urmasdan, veb-ilovangizni tezda ishga tushirishga e'tibor"
" qaratishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer.rst:24
msgid ""
"If you are new to Odoo or web application development, start with the "
":doc:`developer/tutorials/server_framework_101` tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Agar siz Odoo yoki veb-ilova ishlab chiqishga yangi kelgan bo'lsangiz,"
" :doc:`developer/tutorials/server_framework_101` o'quv qo'llanmasidan boshlang."

