#: ../../content/developer/glossary.rst:12
msgid ""
"string identifier stored in ``ir.model.data``, can be used to refer to a "
"record regardless of its database identifier during data imports or "
"export/import roundtrips."
msgstr ""
"``ir.model.data``da saqlangan satr identifikator, ma'lumotlarni import qilish"
