#: ../../content/developer/glossary.rst:16
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"External identifiers are in the form :samp:`{module}.{id}` (e.g. "
"``account.invoice_graph``). From within a module, the :samp:`{module}.` "
"prefix can be left out."
msgstr ""
"Tashqi identifikatorlar :samp:`{module}.{id}` shaklida bo'ladi (masalan,"
" ``account.invoice_graph``). Modul ichidan :samp:`{module}.` prefiksi"
" qoldirib ketilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/glossary.rst:20
msgid ""
"Sometimes referred to as \"xml id\" or ``xml_id`` as XML-based "
":ref:`reference/data` make extensive use of them."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zan \"xml id\" yoki ``xml_id`` deb ataladi, chunki XML-asosidagi"
" :ref:`reference/data` ulardan keng foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/glossary.rst:22
msgid "format string"
msgstr "format satri"

#: ../../content/developer/glossary.rst:24
msgid ""
"inspired by `jinja variables`_, format strings allow more easily mixing "
"literal content and computed content (expressions): content between "
"``{{`` and ``}}`` is interpreted as an expression and evaluated, other "
"content is interpreted as literal strings and displayed as-is"
msgstr ""
"`jinja variables`_ dan ilhomlangan format satrlari so'zma-so'z kontent va"
" hisoblangan kontent (ifodalar)ni osonroq aralashtirishga imkon beradi:"
" ``{{`` va ``}}`` orasidagi kontent ifoda sifatida talqin qilinadi va"
" baholanadi, boshqa kontent so'zma-so'z satr sifatida talqin qilinadi"
" va o'z holatida ko'rsatiladi"

