#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:91
msgid ""
"Tags are a way to sort accounts. For example, imagine you want to create "
"a financial report having multiple lines but you have no way to find a "
"rule to dispatch the accounts according to their ``code``. The solution "
"is the usage of tags, one for each report line, to filter accounts like "
"you want."
msgstr ""
"Teglar hisoblarni saralashning bir usuli. Masalan, bir nechta qatorga"
" ega moliyaviy hisobot yaratmoqchi bo'lsangiz, ammo hisoblarni ularning"
" ``code`` si bo'yicha tarqatish uchun qoida topa olmasangiz. Yechim —"
" har bir hisobot qatori uchun bittadan teg ishlatish, hisoblarni"
" xohlaganingizcha filtrlash uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:95
