#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:124
msgid ""
"Avoid the usage of `asset_cash` ``account_type``! Indeed, the bank & cash"
" accounts are created directly at the installation of the localization "
"module and then, are linked to an ``account.journal``."
msgstr ""
"`asset_cash` ``account_type`` ni ishlatishdan saqlaning! Aslida, bank va"
" naqd pul hisoblar lokalizatsiya moduli o'rnatilganda to'g'ridan-to'g'ri"
" yaratiladi va keyin ``account.journal`` ga bog'lanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:126
msgid ""
"Only one account of type payable/receivable is enough for the generic "
"case.  We need to define a PoS receivable account as well however. "
"(linked in the CoA)"
msgstr ""
"Umumiy holat uchun bitta to'lanadigan/olinadigan turdagi hisob yetarli."
" Biroq, PoS olinadigan hisobni ham aniqlashimiz kerak. (Hisoblar rejasida bog'langan)"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:127
msgid ""
"Don't create too many accounts: 200-300 is enough. But mostly, we try to "
"find a good balance where the CoA needs minimal adapting for most "
"companies afterwards."
msgstr ""
"Juda ko'p hisob yaratmang: 200-300 ta yetarli. Ammo asosan, keyinchalik"
" ko'p kompaniyalar uchun Hisoblar rejasi minimal moslashtirishni talab"
" qiladigan yaxshi muvozanatni topishga harakat qilamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:131
msgid "Account groups"
msgstr "Hisob guruhlari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:134
msgid ":ref:`Account Group References <reference/account_group>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Hisob guruhi ma'lumotnomalari <reference/account_group>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:136
msgid ""
"Account groups allow describing the hierarchical structure of the chart "
"of accounts. The filter needs to be activated in the report and then when"
" you decollapse into journal entries it will show the parents of the "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Hisob guruhlari hisoblar rejasining ierarxik tuzilishini tasvirlashga"
" imkon beradi. Filtr hisobotda faollashtirilishi kerak va jurnaldagi"
" yozuvlarga kengaytirilganda hisobning ota-elementlarini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/accounting_localization.rst:138
msgid ""
"It works with the prefix *start*/*end*, so every account where the code "
"starts with something between *start* and *end* will have this "
"``account.group`` as the parent group.  Furthermore, the account groups "
"can have a parent account group as well to form the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"U *start*/*end* prefiksi bilan ishlaydi, shuning uchun kodi *start* va"
" *end* orasidagi biror narsadan boshlanadigan har bir hisob ushbu"
" ``account.group`` ni ota guruh sifatida oladi. Bundan tashqari, hisob"
" guruhlari ham ierarxiyani shakllantirish uchun ota hisob guruhiga ega"
