"0% as you need to often distinguish between exempt, 0%, not subject, ... "
"taxes. This model only has two required fields: `name` and `country`. "
"Create the file :file:`data/template/account.tax.group-xx.csv` and list "
"the groups."
msgstr ""
"Soliqlarni qo'shish uchun avval fiskal pozitsiyalar va soliq guruhlarini"
