#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:6
msgid "Multi-company Guidelines"
msgstr "Ko'p kompaniyali ko'rsatmalar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:10
msgid ""
"This tutorial requires good knowledge of Odoo. Please refer to the "
":doc:`../tutorials/server_framework_101` tutorial first if needed."
msgstr ""
"Bu o'quv qo'llanma Odoo haqida yaxshi bilimlarga ega bo'lishni talab"
" qiladi. Zarur bo'lsa, avval :doc:`../tutorials/server_framework_101`"
" o'quv qo'llanmasiga murojaat qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:13
msgid ""
"As of version 13.0, a user can be logged in to multiple companies at "
"once. This allows the user to access information from multiple companies,"
" but also to create/edit records in a multi-company environment."
msgstr ""
"13.0 versiyasidan boshlab, foydalanuvchi bir vaqtning o'zida bir nechta"
" kompaniyalarga tizimga kira oladi. Bu foydalanuvchiga bir nechta"
" kompaniyalardan ma'lumotlarga kirish imkonini beradi, shuningdek"
" ko'p kompaniyali muhitda yozuvlarni yaratish/tahrirlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:17
msgid ""
"If not managed correctly, it may be the source of a lot of inconsistent "
"multi-company behaviors. For instance, a user logged in to both companies"
" A and B could create a sales order in company A and add products "
"belonging to company B to it. It is only when the user logs out from "
"company B that access errors will occur for the sales order."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ri boshqarilmasa, bu ko'plab nomuvofiq ko'p kompaniyali xatti-"
"harakatlarning manbai bo'lishi mumkin. Masalan, A va B kompaniyalarga"
" kirgan foydalanuvchi A kompaniyasida sotuv buyurtmasi yaratishi va"
" unga B kompaniyasiga tegishli mahsulotlarni qo'shishi mumkin. Faqat"
" foydalanuvchi B kompaniyasidan chiqqandagina sotuv buyurtmasi uchun"
" kirish xatolari yuzaga keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:22
msgid ""
"To correctly manage multi-company behaviors, Odoo's ORM provides multiple"
" features:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'p kompaniyali xatti-harakatlarni to'g'ri boshqarish uchun Odoo ORM"
" bir nechta imkoniyatlarni taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:24
msgid ":ref:`Company-dependent fields <howto/company/company_dependent>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Kompaniyaga bog'liq maydonlar <howto/company/company_dependent>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:25
msgid ":ref:`Multi-company consistency <howto/company/check_company>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Ko'p kompaniyali izchillik <howto/company/check_company>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:26
msgid ":ref:`Default company <howto/company/default_company>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Standart kompaniya <howto/company/default_company>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:27
msgid ":ref:`Views <howto/company/views>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Ko'rinishlar <howto/company/views>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:28
msgid ":ref:`Security rules <howto/company/security>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Xavfsizlik qoidalari <howto/company/security>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:33
msgid "Company-dependent fields"
msgstr "Kompaniyaga bog'liq maydonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:35
msgid ""
"When a record is available from multiple companies, we must expect that "
"different values will be assigned to a given field depending on the "
"company from which the value is set."
msgstr ""
"Yozuv bir nechta kompaniyalardan mavjud bo'lganda, berilgan maydon uchun"
" qiymat o'rnatilgan kompaniyaga qarab turli qiymatlar tayinlanishini"
" kutishimiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:38
msgid ""
"For the field of the same record to support several values, it must be "
"defined with the attribute `company_dependent` set to `True`."
msgstr ""
"Bir xil yozuvning maydoni bir nechta qiymatlarni qo'llab-quvvatlashi"
" uchun, u `company_dependent` atributi `True` ga o'rnatilgan holda"
" aniqlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:57
msgid ""
"The `_compute_display_info` method is decorated with "
"`depends_context('company')` (see :attr:`~odoo.api.depends_context`) to "
"ensure that the computed field is recomputed depending on the current "
"company (`self.env.company`)."
msgstr ""
"`_compute_display_info` metodi `depends_context('company')` bilan"
" bezatilgan (qarang: :attr:`~odoo.api.depends_context`) — bu hisoblangan"
" maydon joriy kompaniyaga (`self.env.company`) qarab qayta hisoblanishini"
" ta'minlash uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:61
msgid ""
"When a company-dependent field is read, the current company is used to "
"retrieve its value. In other words, if a user is logged in to companies A"
" and B with A as the main company and creates a record for company B, the"
" value of company-dependent fields will be that of company A."
msgstr ""
"Kompaniyaga bog'liq maydon o'qilganda, uning qiymatini olish uchun joriy"
" kompaniya ishlatiladi. Boshqacha aytganda, agar foydalanuvchi A asosiy"
" kompaniya sifatida A va B kompaniyalariga kirgan bo'lsa va B kompaniyasi"
" uchun yozuv yaratsa, kompaniyaga bog'liq maydonlarning qiymati A"
" kompaniyaning qiymati bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:65
msgid ""
"To read the values of company-dependent fields set by another company "
"than the current one, we need to ensure the company we are using is the "
"correct one.  This can be done with "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.with_company`, which updates the current "
"company."
msgstr ""
"Joriy kompaniyadan boshqa kompaniya tomonidan o'rnatilgan kompaniyaga"
" bog'liq maydonlarning qiymatlarini o'qish uchun, biz foydalanayotgan"
" kompaniya to'g'ri ekanligini ta'minlashimiz kerak. Bu joriy kompaniyani"
" yangilaydigan :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.with_company` yordamida"
" amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:80
msgid ""
"Whenever you are computing/creating/... things that may behave "
"differently in different companies, you should make sure whatever you are"
" doing is done in the right company. It doesn't cost much to always use "
"`with_company` to avoid problems later."
msgstr ""
"Turli kompaniyalarda boshqacha ishlashi mumkin bo'lgan narsalarni"
" hisoblaganda/yaratganda/... keyin muammolardan qochish uchun har doim"
" `with_company` ishlatish katta xarajat talab qilmaydi. Siz nima"
" qilayotganingiz to'g'ri kompaniyada amalga oshirilayotganligiga ishonch"
" hosil qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:101
msgid "Multi-company consistency"
msgstr "Ko'p kompaniyali izchillik"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:103
msgid ""
"When a record is made shareable between several companies by the means of"
" a `company_id` field, we must take care that it cannot be linked to the "
"record of another company through a relational field. For instance, we do"
" not want to have a sales order and its invoice belonging to different "
"companies."
msgstr ""
"Yozuv `company_id` maydoni orqali bir nechta kompaniyalar o'rtasida"
" bo'lishilganda, biz relatsion maydon orqali boshqa kompaniya yozuviga"
" bog'lanmasligiga e'tibor berishimiz kerak. Masalan, sotuv buyurtmasi"
" va uning hisob-fakturasi turli kompaniyalarga tegishli bo'lishini"
" xohlamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:107
msgid "To ensure this multi-company consistency, you must:"
msgstr "Ushbu ko'p kompaniyali izchillikni ta'minlash uchun siz:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:109
msgid "Set the class attribute `_check_company_auto` to `True`."
msgstr "`_check_company_auto` sinf atributini `True` ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:110
msgid ""
"Define relational fields with the attribute `check_company` set to `True`"
" if their model has a `company_id` field."
msgstr ""
"Modeli `company_id` maydoniga ega bo'lsa, `check_company` atributi"
" `True` ga o'rnatilgan holda relatsion maydonlarni aniqlang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:113
msgid ""
"On each :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` and "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write`, automatic checks will be triggered to "
"ensure the multi-company consistency of the record."
msgstr ""
"Har bir :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` va :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write`"
" da yozuvning ko'p kompaniyali izchilligini ta'minlash uchun avtomatik"
" tekshiruvlar ishga tushiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:127
msgid "The field `company_id` must not be defined with `check_company=True`."
msgstr "`company_id` maydoni `check_company=True` bilan aniqlanmasligi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:132
msgid ""
"The `check_company` feature performs a strict check! It means that if a "
"record has no `company_id` (i.e., the field is not required), it cannot "
"be linked to a record whose `company_id` is set."
msgstr ""
"`check_company` xususiyati qat'iy tekshiruv amalga oshiradi! Bu shuni"
" anglatadiki, agar yozuvda `company_id` yo'q bo'lsa (ya'ni, maydon"
" majburiy emas), u `company_id` o'rnatilgan yozuvga bog'lanishi"
" mumkin emas."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:138
msgid ""
"When no domain is defined on the field and `check_company` is set to "
"`True`, a default domain is added: `['|', '('company_id', '=', False), "
"('company_id', '=', company_id)]`"
msgstr ""
"Maydon uchun domen aniqlanmagan va `check_company` `True` ga o'rnatilgan"
" bo'lsa, standart domen qo'shiladi: `['|', '('company_id', '=', False),"
" ('company_id', '=', company_id)]`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:144
msgid "Default company"
msgstr "Standart kompaniya"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:146
msgid ""
"When the field `company_id` is made required on a model, a good practice "
"is to set a default company. It eases the setup flow for the user or even"
" guarantees its validity when the company is hidden from view. Indeed, "
"the company is usually hidden if the user does not have access to "
"multiple companies (i.e., when the user does not have the group "
"`base.group_multi_company`)."
msgstr ""
"Modelda `company_id` maydoni majburiy qilinganida, standart kompaniyani"
" o'rnatish yaxshi amaliyot hisoblanadi. Bu foydalanuvchi uchun sozlash"
" jarayonini osonlashtiradi yoki hatto kompaniya ko'rinishdan yashirilganda"
" uning to'g'riligini kafolatlaydi. Haqiqatan ham, kompaniya odatda"
" foydalanuvchi bir nechta kompaniyalarga kirish huquqiga ega bo'lmasa"
" yashiriladi (ya'ni, foydalanuvchida `base.group_multi_company` guruhi"
" yo'q bo'lganda)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:168
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:129
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:91
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:776
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:497
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:294
msgid "Views"
msgstr "Ko'rinishlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:170
msgid ""
"As stated in :ref:`above <howto/company/default_company>`, the company is"
" usually hidden from view if the user does not have access to multiple "
"companies. This is assessed with the group `base.group_multi_company`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`yuqorida <howto/company/default_company>` aytilganidek, kompaniya"
" odatda foydalanuvchi bir nechta kompaniyalarga kirish huquqiga ega"
" bo'lmasa ko'rinishdan yashiriladi. Bu `base.group_multi_company` guruhi"
" orqali baholanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:197
msgid "Security rules"
msgstr "Xavfsizlik qoidalari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:199
msgid ""
"When working with records shared across companies or restricted to a "
"single company, we must take care that a user does not have access to "
"records belonging to other companies."
msgstr ""
"Kompaniyalar o'rtasida bo'lishilgan yoki bitta kompaniyaga cheklangan"
" yozuvlar bilan ishlashda, foydalanuvchi boshqa kompaniyalarga tegishli"
" yozuvlarga kirish huquqiga ega emasligiga e'tibor berishimiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/company.rst:202
msgid ""
"This is achieved with security rules based on `company_ids`, which "
"contain the current companies of the user (the companies the user checked"
" in the multi-company widget)."
msgstr ""
"Bu foydalanuvchining joriy kompaniyalarini (foydalanuvchi ko'p kompaniyali"
" vidjetda belgilagan kompaniyalarni) o'z ichiga olgan `company_ids` ga"
" asoslangan xavfsizlik qoidalari yordamida amalga oshiriladi."

