#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:5
msgid ""
"IoT Drivers allow any Odoo module to communicate in real-time with any "
"device connected to the IoT Box. Communication with the IoT Box goes both"
" ways, so the Odoo client can send commands to and receive information "
"from any of the supported devices."
msgstr ""
"IoT Drayverlari har qanday Odoo moduliga IoT Qutiiga ulangan har qanday"
" qurilma bilan real vaqtda muloqot qilish imkonini beradi. IoT Quti bilan"
" muloqot ikki tomonlama bo'lib, Odoo mijozi qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan"
" qurilmalarning istalganiga buyruqlar yuborishi va ulardan ma'lumot"
" olishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:10
msgid "To add support for a device, all we need is:"
msgstr "Qurilmani qo'llab-quvvatlash uchun bizga kerak bo'lgani:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:12
msgid "an `Interface`, to detect connected devices of a specific type"
msgstr "muayyan turdagi ulangan qurilmalarni aniqlash uchun `Interface`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:13
msgid "a `Driver`, to communicate with an individual device"
msgstr "alohida qurilma bilan muloqot qilish uchun `Driver`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:15
msgid ""
"At each boot, the IoT Box will load all of the Interfaces and Drivers "
"that can be located on the connected Odoo instance. Each module can "
"contain an `iot_handlers` directory that will be copied to the IoT Box. "
"The structure of this directory is the following"
msgstr ""
"Har bir yuklashda IoT Quti ulangan Odoo nusxasida topilishi mumkin"
" bo'lgan barcha Interfeyslar va Drayverlarni yuklaydi. Har bir modul"
" IoT Qutiga ko'chiriladigan `iot_handlers` katalogini o'z ichiga olishi"
" mumkin. Bu katalogning tuzilishi quyidagicha"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:34
msgid "Detect Devices"
msgstr "Qurilmalarni aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:36
msgid ""
"Devices connected to the IoT Box are detected through `Interfaces`. There"
" is an Interface for each supported connection type (USB, Bluetooth, "
"Video, Printers, Serial, etc.). The interface maintains a list of "
"detected devices and associates them with the right Driver."
msgstr ""
"IoT Qutiga ulangan qurilmalar `Interfaces` orqali aniqlanadi. Har bir"
" qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan ulanish turi (USB, Bluetooth, Video, Printerlar,"
" Serial va h.k.) uchun Interfeys mavjud. Interfeys aniqlangan qurilmalar"
" ro'yxatini saqlaydi va ularni to'g'ri Drayver bilan bog'laydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:41
msgid ""
"Supported devices will appear both on the IoT Box Homepage that you can "
"access through its IP address and in the IoT module of the connected Odoo"
" instance."
msgstr ""
"Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan qurilmalar ham IP manzili orqali kira oladigan"
" IoT Quti bosh sahifasida, ham ulangan Odoo nusxasining IoT modulida"
" ko'rinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:45
msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Interfeys"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:47
msgid ""
"The role of the Interface is to maintain a list of devices connected "
"through a determined connection type. Creating a new interface requires"
msgstr ""
"Interfeysning roli belgilangan ulanish turi orqali ulangan qurilmalar"
" ro'yxatini saqlashdan iborat. Yangi interfeys yaratish quyidagilarni talab qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:50
msgid "Extending the `Interface` class"
msgstr "`Interface` sinfini kengaytirish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:51
msgid "Setting the `connection_type` class attribute"
msgstr "`connection_type` sinf atributini o'rnatish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:52
msgid ""
"Implementing the `get_devices` method, that should return a dictionary "
"containing data about each detected device. This data will be given as "
"argument to the constructors and `supported` method of the Drivers."
msgstr ""
"Har bir aniqlangan qurilma haqidagi ma'lumotlarni o'z ichiga olgan"
" lug'atni qaytarishi kerak bo'lgan `get_devices` metodini amalga oshirish."
" Bu ma'lumotlar Drayverlarning konstruktorlari va `supported` metodiga"
" argument sifatida beriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:57
msgid ""
"Setting the `_loop_delay` attribute will modify the interval between "
"calls to `get_devices`. By default, this interval is set to 3 seconds."
msgstr ""
"`_loop_delay` atributini o'rnatish `get_devices` ga chaqiruvlar orasidagi"
" intervalni o'zgartiradi. Standart bo'yicha, bu interval 3 soniyaga"
" o'rnatilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:74
msgid "Driver"
msgstr "Drayver"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:76
msgid ""
"Once the interface has retrieved the list of detected devices, it will "
"loop through all of the Drivers that have the same `connection_type` "
"attribute and test their respective `supported` method on all detected "
"devices. If the supported method of a Driver returns `True`, an instance "
"of this Driver will be created for the corresponding device."
msgstr ""
"Interfeys aniqlangan qurilmalar ro'yxatini olgandan so'ng, u bir xil"
" `connection_type` atributiga ega barcha Drayverlar bo'ylab aylana oladi"
" va ularning `supported` metodlarini barcha aniqlangan qurilmalarda"
" sinab ko'radi. Agar Drayverning qo'llab-quvvatlash metodi `True` qaytarsa,"
" bu Drayverning nusxasi mos qurilma uchun yaratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:83
msgid ""
"`supported` methods of drivers are given a priority order. The "
"`supported` method of a child class will always be tested before the one "
"of its parent. This priority can be adjusted by modifying the `priority` "
"attribute of the Driver."
msgstr ""
"Drayverlarning `supported` metodlariga ustuvorlik tartibi berilgan."
" Bolalar sinfining `supported` metodi har doim ota-sinfning metodidan"
" oldin sinovdan o'tkaziladi. Bu ustuvorlik Drayverning `priority`"
" atributini o'zgartirish orqali sozlanishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:88
msgid "Creating a new Driver requires:"
msgstr "Yangi Drayver yaratish quyidagilarni talab qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:90
msgid "Extending `Driver`"
msgstr "`Driver` ni kengaytirish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:91
msgid "Setting the `connection_type` class attribute."
msgstr "`connection_type` sinf atributini o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:92
msgid ""
"Setting the `device_type`, `device_connection` and `device_name` "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
"`device_type`, `device_connection` va `device_name` atributlarini o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:93
msgid "Defining the `supported` method"
msgstr "`supported` metodini aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:113
msgid "Communicate With Devices"
msgstr "Qurilmalar bilan muloqot qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:115
msgid ""
"Once your new device is detected and appears in the IoT module, the next "
"step is to communicate with it. Since the box only has a local IP "
"address, it can only be reached from the same local network. "
"Communication, therefore, needs to happen on the browser-side, in "
"JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Yangi qurilmangiz aniqlangandan va IoT modulida paydo bo'lgandan so'ng,"
" keyingi qadam u bilan muloqot qilishdir. Quti faqat mahalliy IP"
" manziliga ega bo'lganligi sababli, u faqat bir xil mahalliy tarmoqdan"
" erishilishi mumkin. Shuning uchun muloqot brauzer tomonida, JavaScript"
" da amalga oshirilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:120
msgid ""
"The process depends on the direction of the communication: - From the "
"browser to the box, through `Actions`_ - From the box to the browser, "
"through `Longpolling`_"
msgstr ""
"Jarayon muloqot yo'nalishiga bog'liq: - Brauzerdan qutiga, `Actions`_"
" orqali - Qutidan brauzerga, `Longpolling`_ orqali"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:124
msgid ""
"Both channels are accessed from the same JS object, the `DeviceProxy`, "
"which is instantiated using the IP of the IoT Box and the device "
"identifier."
msgstr ""
"Ikkala kanal ham IoT Qutining IP si va qurilma identifikatori yordamida"
" namunalangan `DeviceProxy` deb nomlangan bir xil JS ob'ektidan kirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:137
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:1124
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:1535
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/forms.rst:43
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:3
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:45
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "Amallar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:139
msgid ""
"Actions are used to tell a selected device to execute a specific action, "
"such as taking a picture, printing a receipt, etc."
msgstr ""
"Amallar tanlangan qurilmaga rasm olish, chek chiqarish va h.k. kabi"
" muayyan amalni bajarishni bildirish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:143
msgid ""
"It must be noted that no \"answer\" will be sent by the box on this route, "
"only the request status. The answer to the action, if any, has to be "
"retrieved via the longpolling."
msgstr ""
"Shuni ta'kidlash kerakki, bu marshrut bo'yicha qutidan hech qanday"
" \"javob\" yuborilmaydi, faqat so'rov holati. Amarga javob, agar mavjud"
" bo'lsa, longpolling orqali olinishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:147
msgid "An action can be performed on the DeviceProxy Object."
msgstr "DeviceProxy Ob'ektida amal bajarilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:153
msgid ""
"In your driver, define an `action` method that will be executed when "
"called from an Odoo module. It takes the data given during the call as "
"argument."
msgstr ""
"Drayvеringizda, Odoo modulidan chaqirilganda bajarilishi kerak bo'lgan"
" `action` metodini aniqlang. U chaqiruv paytida berilgan ma'lumotlarni"
" argument sifatida oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:162
msgid "Longpolling"
msgstr "Longpolling"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:164
msgid ""
"When any module in Odoo wants to read data from a specific device, it "
"creates a listener identified by the IP/domain of the box and the device "
"identifier and passes it a callback function to be called every time the "
"device status changes. The callback is called with the new data as "
"argument."
msgstr ""
"Odooda har qanday modul muayyan qurilmadan ma'lumot o'qishni xohlasa,"
" u qutining IP/domeni va qurilma identifikatori bilan aniqlangan"
" tinglovchi yaratadi va har safar qurilma holati o'zgarganda chaqiriladigan"
" qayta chaqiruv funksiyasini uzatadi. Qayta chaqiruv yangi ma'lumotlar"
" bilan argument sifatida chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/connect_device.rst:177
msgid ""
"In the Driver, an event is released by calling the `device_changed` "
"function from the `event_manager`. All callbacks set on the listener will"
" then be called with `self.data` as argument."
msgstr ""
"Drayverda, `event_manager` dan `device_changed` funksiyasini chaqirish"
" orqali voqea chiqariladi. Tinglovchida o'rnatilgan barcha qayta chaqiruvlar"
" keyin `self.data` ni argument sifatida qabul qilib chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:5
msgid ""
"SQL views are a technique for creating customized reports to show data "
"that cannot be shown with existing models' fields and views. In other "
"words, this technique helps avoid unnecessary creation and calculation of"
" additional fields solely for data analysis purposes."
msgstr ""
"SQL ko'rinishlari mavjud modellarning maydonlari va ko'rinishlari bilan"
" ko'rsatib bo'lmaydigan ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatish uchun maxsus hisobotlar"
" yaratishning bir usuli. Boshqacha aytganda, bu usul faqat ma'lumotlarni"
" tahlil qilish maqsadida qo'shimcha maydonlarni keraksiz yaratish va"
" hisoblashdan qochishga yordam beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:11
msgid "Create a model"
msgstr "Model yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:13
msgid "A SQL view is created in a similar manner as a standard model:"
msgstr "SQL ko'rinishi standart model kabi yaratiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:26
msgid "Where the attributes:"
msgstr "Atributlarda:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:28
msgid ""
"`_auto = False` indicates that we do not want to store the model in the "
"database"
msgstr "`_auto = False` modelni ma'lumotlar bazasida saqlamaslikni bildiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:29
msgid ""
"`_rec_name` indicates which of the model's fields represents a record's "
"name (i.e. the name that will be used in the navigation breadcrumb when "
"opening a record's form view)"
msgstr ""
"`_rec_name` modelning qaysi maydoni yozuv nomini ifodalashini bildiradi"
" (ya'ni, yozuv forma ko'rinishini ochishda navigatsiya yo'nalishida"
" ishlatiladigan nom)"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:32
msgid ""
"and its fields are defined in the same way as a standard model, except "
"every field is marked as `readonly=True`."
msgstr ""
"va uning maydonlari standart model kabi aniqlanadi, bundan tashqari"
" har bir maydon `readonly=True` sifatida belgilanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:36
msgid "Don't forget to add your new model to your security file."
msgstr "Yangi modelingizni xavfsizlik faylingizga qo'shishni unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:39
msgid "Populate the model"
msgstr "Modelni to'ldirish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:41
msgid "There are 2 ways to populate a SQL view's table:"
msgstr "SQL ko'rinishi jadvalini to'ldirishning 2 usuli mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:43
msgid "override the `BaseModel.init()` method,"
msgstr "`BaseModel.init()` metodini qayta yozish,"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:44
msgid "set the `_table_query` property."
msgstr "`_table_query` xususiyatini o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:46
msgid ""
"Regardless of which way is used, a SQL query will be executed to populate"
" the model. Therefore, any SQL commands can be used to collect and/or "
"calculate the data needed and you are expected to keep in mind that you "
"are bypassing the ORM (i.e. it is a good idea to read through "
":ref:`reference/security` if you haven't already). The columns returned "
"from the `SELECT` will populate the model's fields, so ensure that your "
"column names match your field names, or use alias names that match."
msgstr ""
"Qaysi usul ishlatilishidan qat'i nazar, modelni to'ldirish uchun SQL"
" so'rovi bajariladi. Shuning uchun, zarur ma'lumotlarni yig'ish va/yoki"
" hisoblash uchun istalgan SQL buyruqlaridan foydalanish mumkin va siz"
" ORM ni chetlab o'tayotganingizni yodda tutishingiz kutiladi (ya'ni,"
" hali o'qimagan bo'lsangiz :ref:`reference/security` ni o'qib chiqish"
" yaxshi fikr). `SELECT` dan qaytarilgan ustunlar modelning maydonlarini"
" to'ldiradi, shuning uchun ustun nomlari maydon nomlari bilan mos"
" kelishini yoki mos keladigan taxallus nomlardan foydalanishni ta'minlang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:55
msgid "Overriding `BaseModel.init()`"
msgstr "`BaseModel.init()` ni qayta yozish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:57
msgid ""
"In most cases, overriding the `BaseModel.init()` method is the standard "
"and better option to use. It requires the import of `tools` and is "
"typically written as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'p hollarda, `BaseModel.init()` metodini qayta yozish standart va"
" yaxshiroq usul hisoblanadi. Bu `tools` ni import qilishni talab qiladi"
" va odatda quyidagicha yoziladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"`tools.drop_view_if_exists` ensures that a conflicting view is not "
"created when the SQL query is executed. It is standard to separate the "
"different parts of the query to allow for easier model extension. Exactly"
" how the query is split up across methods is not standardized, but at "
"minimum, the `_select` and `_from` methods are common, and of course, all"
" these methods will return strings."
msgstr ""
"`tools.drop_view_if_exists` SQL so'rovi bajarilganda ziddiyatli ko'rinish"
" yaratilmasligini ta'minlaydi. Modelni osonroq kengaytirish uchun so'rovning"
" turli qismlarini ajratish standart hisoblanadi. So'rov metodlar bo'yicha"
" qanday bo'linishi standartlashtirilmagan, ammo kamida `_select` va `_from`"
" metodlari keng tarqalgan va albatta barcha bu metodlar satrlarni qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:78
msgid ""
"`Example: a SQL view using an override of BaseModel.init() "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/project/report/project_report.py>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Misol: BaseModel.init() ni qayta yozishdan foydalanadigan SQL ko'rinishi"
" <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/project/report/project_report.py>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:81
msgid "Using `_table_query`"
msgstr "`_table_query` dan foydalanish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:83
msgid ""
"The ``_table_query`` property is used when the view depends on the "
"context. It is typically written as follows:"
msgstr ""
"``_table_query`` xususiyati ko'rinish kontekstga bog'liq bo'lganda"
" ishlatiladi. U odatda quyidagicha yoziladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:92
msgid ""
"and follows the same `_select` and `_from` methods standards as "
"`BaseModel.init()`."
msgstr ""
"va `BaseModel.init()` kabi bir xil `_select` va `_from` metodlari"
" standartlariga amal qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:94
msgid ""
"An example of when the property should be used instead of overriding "
"`BaseModel.init()` is in a multi-company and multi-currency environment "
"where currency related amounts need to be converted using currency "
"exchange rates when the user switches between companies."
msgstr ""
