#: ../../content/developer/howtos/javascript_view.rst:66
msgid ""
"The possibilities for extending views are endless. While we have only "
"extended the controller here, you can also extend the renderer to add new"
" buttons, modify how records are presented, or customize the dropdown, as"
" well as extend other components such as the model and `buttonTemplate`."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishlarni kengaytirish imkoniyatlari cheksiz. Bu yerda faqat kontrolerni"
" kengaytirganimizda bo'lsa-da, yangi tugmalar qo'shish, yozuvlarning ko'rsatilish"
" usulini o'zgartirish yoki ochiladigan ro'yxatni sozlash uchun rendererni,"
" shuningdek model va `buttonTemplate` kabi boshqa komponentlarni ham kengaytirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/javascript_view.rst:71
