" the view."
msgstr ""
"Modelning roli ko'rinishdagi barcha zarur ma'lumotlarni olish va boshqarishdan iborat."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/javascript_view.rst:157
msgid ":file:`beautiful_model.js`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/javascript_view.rst:186
msgid ""
"For advanced cases, instead of creating a model from scratch, it is also "
