#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:86
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:111
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:89
msgid ""
"`Bootstrap Reboot on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/1a6fdfae6b/scss/_reboot.scss>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:95
msgid "HTML tags"
msgstr "HTML teglar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:97
msgid ""
"It may seem obvious, but the simplest and most **consistent** way of "
"making text look like a title is to use a header tag (`<h1>`, `<h2>`, "
"...). Besides reboot rules, mostly all tags carry decorative styles "
"defined by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Ayon ko'rinishi mumkin, ammo matnni sarlavhaga o'xshatishning eng oddiy va **izchil** "
"usuli sarlavha tegini (`<h1>`, `<h2>`, ...) ishlatishdir. Qayta yuklash qoidalaridan "
"tashqari, deyarli barcha teglar Odoo tomonidan belgilangan dekorativ uslublarga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:106
msgid "Don't"
msgstr "Qilmang"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:138
msgid "Do"
msgstr "Qiling"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:163
msgid ""
"Besides reducing the amount of code, a modular-design approach (use "
"classes, tags, mixins...) keeps the visual result consistent and easily "
"**maintainable**."
msgstr ""
"Kod miqdorini kamaytirish bilan bir qatorda, modulli dizayn yondashuvi (klasslar, "
"teglar, mixinlar... ishlatish) vizual natijani izchil va oson **qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan** "
"holda ushlab turadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:166
msgid ""
"Following the last example, if Odoo titles' design changes, these changes"
" will be applied in the `o_module_custom_title` element too since it's "
"using an `<h5>` tag."
msgstr ""
"So'nggi misolga ko'ra, agar Odoo sarlavhalarining dizayni o'zgarsa, bu o'zgarishlar "
"`o_module_custom_title` elementiga ham qo'llaniladi, chunki u `<h5>` tegini ishlatmoqda."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:172
msgid "Utility classes"
msgstr "Yordamchi klasslar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:174
msgid ""
"Our framework defines a multitude of utility classes designed to cover "
"almost all layout/design/interaction needs. The simple fact that a class "
"already exists justifies its use over custom CSS whenever possible."
msgstr ""
"Bizning freymvork deyarli barcha tartib/dizayn/o'zaro ta'sir ehtiyojlarini qoplash uchun "
"mo'ljallangan ko'plab yordamchi klasslarni belgilaydi. Klass allaqachon mavjud bo'lishi "
"imkon qadar maxsus CSS o'rniga undan foydalanishni oqlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:178
msgid "Take the example of `position-relative`."
msgstr "`position-relative` misolini ko'rib chiqing."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:186
msgid ""
"Since a utility-class is defined, any CSS line with the declaration "
"`position: relative` is **potentially** redundant."
msgstr ""
"Yordamchi klass belgilanganligi sababli, `position: relative` deklaratsiyasi bilan "
"har qanday CSS qator **potensial** ravishda ortiqchadir."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:189
msgid ""
"Odoo relies on the default `Bootstrap utility-classes "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/utilities/background/>`_ stack and "
"defines its own using `Bootstrap API "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/utilities/api/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo standart `Bootstrap utility-classes "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/utilities/background/>`_ to'plamiga tayanadi va "
"o'zining klasslarini `Bootstrap API "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/utilities/api/>`_ yordamida belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:194
msgid ""
"`Bootstrap utility classes "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/utilities/api/>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:195
msgid ""
"`Odoo custom utilities on github "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/src/scss/utilities_custom.scss>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:201
msgid "Handling utility-classes verbosity"
msgstr "Yordamchi klasslar verbozligini boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:203
msgid "The downside of utility-classes is the potential lack of readability."
msgstr "Yordamchi klasslarning kamchiligi o'qilishning potensial yetishmasligi hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:214
msgid "To overcome the issue you may combine different approaches:"
msgstr "Muammoni bartaraf etish uchun turli yondashuvlarni birlashtirishingiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:216
msgid "in Qweb attributes, only use classes to be toggled *on-the-fly*;"
msgstr "Qweb atributlarida faqat *tezkor* almashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan klasslardan foydalaning;"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:217
msgid "use new lines for each attribute;"
msgstr "har bir atribut uchun yangi qatordan foydalaning;"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:218
msgid ""
"order classes using the convention `[odoo component] [bootstrap "
"component] [css declaration order]`."
msgstr ""
"klasslarni `[odoo component] [bootstrap component] [css declaration order]` "
"konvensiyasi bo'yicha tartibga soling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:233
msgid ""
":ref:`Odoo CSS properties order "
"<contributing/coding_guidelines/scss/properties_order>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:5
msgid ""
"For any number of reasons, you may want to have a standalone Owl "
"application that isn't a part of the web client. One example in Odoo is "
"the self-ordering application, that lets customers order food from their "
"phone. In this chapter we will go into what's required to achieve "
"something like this."
msgstr ""
"Turli sabablarga ko'ra, veb-mijozning bir qismi bo'lmagan mustaqil Owl ilovasiga ega "
"bo'lishni xohlashingiz mumkin. Odoo'dagi bir misol - mijozlarga telefonlari orqali "
"taom buyurtma berishga imkon beruvchi o'z-o'zidan buyurtma berish ilovalari. "
"Bu bobda bunday narsani amalga oshirish uchun nima kerakligini ko'rib chiqamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:12
msgid "To have a standalone Owl app, a few things are required:"
msgstr "Mustaqil Owl ilovasiga ega bo'lish uchun bir nechta narsa talab etiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:14
msgid "a root component for the application"
msgstr "ilova uchun ildiz komponent"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:15
msgid "an assets bundle that contains the setup code"
msgstr "sozlash kodini o'z ichiga olgan assets to'plami"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:16
msgid "a QWeb view that calls the assets bundle"
msgstr "assets to'plamini chaqiruvchi QWeb ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:17
msgid "a controller that renders the view"
msgstr "ko'rinishni render qiluvchi kontroler"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:20
msgid "1. Root component"
msgstr "1. Ildiz komponenti"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:25
msgid ""
"First, create the template in "
":file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/root.xml`."
msgstr ""
"Avval :file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/root.xml` faylida shablonni yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:36
msgid ""
"Then create the JavaScript file for that component in "
":file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/root.js`."
msgstr ""
"So'ngra :file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/root.js` faylida ushbu komponent "
"uchun JavaScript faylini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:47
msgid ""
"It's generally a good idea to have the application setup code that mounts"
" the component in a separate file. Create the JavaScript file that will "
"mount the app in :file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/app.js`."
msgstr ""
"Komponentni o'rnatuvchi ilova sozlash kodini alohida faylda saqlash odatda yaxshi "
"g'oya hisoblanadi. :file:`/your_module/static/src/standalone_app/app.js` faylida "
"ilovani o'rnatuvchi JavaScript faylini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:58
msgid ""
"The `mountComponent` utility function will take care of creating the Owl "
"application and configuring it correctly: it will create an environment, "
"start the :ref:`services<frontend/services>`, make sure the app is "
"translated and give the app access to the templates from your assets "
"bundle, among other things."
msgstr ""
"`mountComponent` yordamchi funksiyasi Owl ilovasini yaratish va uni to'g'ri "
"sozlash ishlarini bajaradi: u muhit yaratadi, :ref:`services<frontend/services>` "
"xizmatlarini ishga tushiradi, ilova tarjima qilinganligini ta'minlaydi va ilovaga "
"assets to'plamidagi shablonlarga kirish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:68
msgid "2. Creating an assets bundle containing our code"
msgstr "2. Kodimizni o'z ichiga olgan assets to'plamini yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:70
msgid ""
"In the manifest of your module, create a new :ref:`assets "
"bundle<reference/assets_bundle>`. It should include the "
"`web._assets_core` bundle, which contains the Odoo JavaScript framework "
"and the core libraries it needs (e.g. Owl and luxon), after which you can"
" have a glob that adds all the files for your application in the bundle."
msgstr ""
"Modulingizning manifest faylida yangi :ref:`assets bundle<reference/assets_bundle>` "
"yarating. U Odoo JavaScript freymvorkini va zarur asosiy kutubxonalarni (masalan, "
"Owl va luxon) o'z ichiga olgan `web._assets_core` to'plamini qamrab olishi kerak, "
"shundan so'ng to'plamga ilovangizning barcha fayllarini qo'shuvchi glob qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:92
msgid ""
"The other lines are bundles and scss files that are required to make "
"Bootstrap work. They are mandatory, as the components of the web "
"framework use bootstrap classes for their styling and layout."
msgstr ""
"Qolgan qatorlar Bootstrap'ni ishlashi uchun zarur bo'lgan to'plamlar va scss fayllardir. "
"Ular majburiy hisoblanadi, chunki veb-freymvorkning komponentlari stilizatsiya va "
"tartib uchun bootstrap klasslaridan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:97
msgid ""
"Make sure that the files for your standalone app are only added to this "
"bundle, if you already have a definition for `web.assets_backend` or "
"`web.assets_frontend` and they have globs, make sure these globs don't "
"match the files for your standalone app, otherwise the startup code for "
"your app will conflict with the existing startup code in those bundles."
msgstr ""
"Mustaqil ilovangizning fayllari faqat shu to'plamga qo'shilishiga ishonch hosil qiling. "
"Agar `web.assets_backend` yoki `web.assets_frontend` uchun allaqachon ta'rif mavjud bo'lsa "
"va ularda glob'lar bo'lsa, bu glob'lar mustaqil ilovangizning fayllariga mos kelmasligini "
"ta'minlang, aks holda ilovangizning ishga tushirish kodi o'sha to'plamlardagi mavjud "
"ishga tushirish kodi bilan ziddiyatga kiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:106
msgid "3. XML view that calls the assets bundle"
msgstr "3. Assets to'plamini chaqiruvchi XML ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:108
msgid ""
"Now that we have created our assets bundle, we need to create a "
":ref:`QWeb view <reference/view_architectures/qweb>` that uses that "
"assets bundle."
msgstr ""
