msgid ""
"The CSRF token, which is required to interact with HTTP controllers in "
"many cases."
msgstr "Ko'p hollarda HTTP kontrolerlari bilan muloqot qilish uchun zarur bo'lgan CSRF token."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:137
msgid ""
"The debug value, which is used in many places to add additional logging "
"or developer-friendly checks."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shimcha logging yoki dasturchi uchun qulay tekshiruvlar qo'shish uchun ko'p joylarda "
"ishlatiladigan debug qiymati."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:138
msgid ""
"`__session_info__`, that contains information from the server that is "
"always needed and for which we don't want to perform an additional "
"request. More on this in the next section."
msgstr ""
"`__session_info__` - har doim kerak bo'lgan va qo'shimcha so'rov yubormaslik uchun "
"serverdan olinadigan ma'lumotlarni o'z ichiga oladi. Bu haqda keyingi bo'limda batafsil."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:142
msgid "4. Controller that renders the view"
msgstr "4. Ko'rinishni render qiluvchi kontroler"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:144
msgid ""
"Now that we have the view, we need to make it accessible to the user. For"
" that purpose, we will create an :ref:`HTTP "
"controller<reference/controllers>` that renders that view and returns it "
"to the user."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinish tayyor bo'lgach, uni foydalanuvchi uchun ochiq qilishimiz kerak. Shu maqsadda "
"ushbu ko'rinishni render qilib foydalanuvchiga qaytaruvchi :ref:`HTTP "
"kontroler<reference/controllers>` yaratamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:161
msgid ""
"Notice how we're giving the template `session_info`. We get it from the "
"`get_frontend_session_info` method, and it will end up containing "
"information used by the web framework, such as the current user's ID if "
"they are logged in, the server version, the Odoo edition, etc."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, biz shablonga `session_info` berayapmiz. Buni `get_frontend_session_info` "
"metodidan olamiz va u veb-freymvork tomonidan ishlatiladigan ma'lumotlarni o'z ichiga oladi: "
"masalan, tizimga kirgan foydalanuvchining identifikatori, server versiyasi, Odoo nashri va h.k."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/standalone_owl_application.rst:165
msgid ""
