#: ../../content/developer/howtos/translations.rst:133
msgid ""
"To translate, the translation function needs to know the *language* and "
"the *module* name. When using ``Environment._`` the language is known and"
" you may pass the module name as a parameter, otherwise it's extracted "
"from the caller."
msgstr ""
"Tarjima qilish uchun tarjima funksiyasi *til* va *modul* nomini bilishi kerak. "
