"extracted from the context. For this, we inspect the caller's local "
"variables. The drawback of this method is that it is error-prone: we try "
"to find the context variable or ``self.env``, however these may not exist"
" if you use translations outside of model methods; i.e. it does not work "
"inside regular functions or python comprehensions."
msgstr ""
"``odoo.tools.translate._`` holatida til va modul kontekstdan olinadi. Buning uchun "
"chaqiruvchining lokal o'zgaruvchilari tekshiriladi. Bu usulning kamchiligi xatolarga "
"moyilligidir: biz kontekst o'zgaruvchisi yoki ``self.env`` ni topmoqchi bo'lamiz, ammo "
"ular model metodlaridan tashqarida tarjimalardan foydalansangiz mavjud bo'lmasligi mumkin; "
"ya'ni u oddiy funksiyalar yoki Python tushunishlari ichida ishlamaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/translations.rst:145
msgid ""
