#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:5
msgid ""
"Upgrading to a new version of Odoo can be challenging, especially if the "
"database you work on contains custom modules. This page intent is to "
"explain the technical process of upgrading a database with customized "
"modules. Refer to :doc:`Upgrade documentation </administration/upgrade>` "
"for guidance on how to upgrade a database without customized modules."
msgstr ""
"Odoo'ning yangi versiyasiga o'tish qiyin bo'lishi mumkin, ayniqsa ishlayotgan "
"ma'lumotlar bazangiz maxsus modullarni o'z ichiga olsa. Bu sahifaning maqsadi "
"maxsus modullar bilan ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilashning texnik jarayonini "
"tushuntirishdir. Maxsus modullarsiz ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilash bo'yicha "
"ko'rsatma uchun :doc:`Yangilash hujjati </administration/upgrade>` ga murojaat qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:10
msgid ""
"We consider a custom module, any module that extends the standard code of"
" Odoo and that was not built with the Studio app. Before upgrading such a"
" module, or before requesting its upgrade, have a look at the :ref"
":`upgrade-sla` to make sure who's responsible for it."
msgstr ""
"Biz maxsus modul deb Odoo'ning standart kodini kengaytiradigan va Studio ilovasi "
"bilan qurilmagan har qanday modulni hisoblaymiz. Bunday modulni yangilashdan oldin "
"yoki yangilashni so'rashdan oldin, kim mas'ulligini aniqlash uchun :ref:`upgrade-sla` "
"ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:14
msgid ""
"While working on what we refer to as the **custom upgrade** of your "
"database, keep in mind the goals of an upgrade:"
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazangizning **maxsus yangilanishi** deb ataydigan narsaga ishlashda "
"yangilashning maqsadlarini yodda tuting:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:17
msgid "Stay supported"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlashni saqlab qolish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:18
msgid "Get the latest features"
msgstr "So'nggi funksiyalarni olish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:19
msgid "Enjoy the performance improvement"
msgstr "Ishlash unumdorligining yaxshilanishidan bahramand bo'lish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:20
msgid "Reduce the technical debt"
msgstr "Texnik qarzni kamaytirish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:21
msgid "Benefit from security improvements"
msgstr "Xavfsizlik yaxshilanishlaridan foydalanish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:23
msgid ""
"With every new version of Odoo, changes are introduced. These changes can"
" impact modules on which customization have been developed. This is the "
"reason why upgrading a database that contains custom modules requires "
"additional steps in order to upgrade the source code."
msgstr ""
"Odoo'ning har yangi versiyasi bilan o'zgarishlar kiritiladi. Bu o'zgarishlar "
"moslashtirishlar ishlab chiqilgan modullarga ta'sir ko'rsatishi mumkin. Aynan shu sababli "
"maxsus modullarni o'z ichiga olgan ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilash manba kodini yangilash "
"uchun qo'shimcha qadamlarni talab etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:27
msgid "These are the steps to follow to upgrade customized databases:"
msgstr "Moslashtirilgan ma'lumotlar bazalarini yangilash uchun quyidagi qadamlarga amal qiling:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:29
msgid ""
":ref:`Stop the developments and challenge them "
"<upgrade_custom/stop_developments>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:30
msgid ":ref:`Request an upgraded database <upgrade_custom/request_upgrade>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`Make your module installable on an empty database "
"<upgrade_custom/empty_database>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:32
msgid ""
":ref:`Make your module installable on the upgraded database "
"<upgrade_custom/upgraded_database>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:33
msgid ""
":ref:`Test extensively and do a rehearsal "
"<upgrade_custom/testing_rehearsal>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:34
msgid ":ref:`Upgrade the production database <upgrade_custom/production>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:39
msgid "Step 1: Stop the developments"
msgstr "1-qadam: Ishlanmalarni to'xtatish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:41
msgid ""
"Starting an upgrade requires commitment and development resources. If "
"developments keep being made at the same time, those features will need "
"to be re-upgraded and tested every time you change them. This is why we "
"recommend a complete freeze of the codebase when starting the upgrade "
"process. Needless to say, bug fixing is exempt from this recommendation."
msgstr ""
"Yangilashni boshlash mas'uliyat va ishlab chiqish resurslarini talab etadi. Agar "
"ishlanmalar bir vaqtda davom etsa, o'zgartirilganda bu funksiyalar qayta yangilanishi "
"va sinab ko'rilishi kerak bo'ladi. Shu sababli yangilash jarayonini boshlaganda kod "
"bazasini to'liq muzlatishni tavsiya etamiz. Aytmasak ham bo'ladiki, xatolarni tuzatish "
"bu tavsiyadan mustasno."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once you have stopped development, it is a good practice to assess the "
"developments made and compare them with the features introduced between "
"your current version and the version you are targeting. Challenge the "
"developments as much as possible and find functional workarounds. "
"Removing redundancy between your developments and the standard version of"
" Odoo will lead to an eased upgrade process and reduce technical debt."
msgstr ""
"Ishlanmalarni to'xtatgandan so'ng, amalga oshirilgan ishlanmalarni baholab, ularni "
"joriy versiyangiz va maqsad versiya o'rtasida kiritilgan funksiyalar bilan solishtirish "
"yaxshi amaliyot hisoblanadi. Ishlanmalarni iloji boricha sinab ko'ring va funktsional "
"muqobil yechimlarni toping. Ishlanmalaringiz va Odoo'ning standart versiyasi o'rtasidagi "
"ortiqchalikni olib tashlash yangilash jarayonini osonlashtiradi va texnik qarzni kamaytiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:53
msgid ""
"You can find information on the changes between versions in the `Release "
"Notes <https:/odoo.com/page/release-notes>`_."
msgstr ""
"Versiyalar o'rtasidagi o'zgarishlar haqida ma'lumotni `Chiqarish eslatmalari "
"<https:/odoo.com/page/release-notes>`_ da topishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:59
msgid "Step 2: Request an upgraded database"
msgstr "2-qadam: Yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasini so'rash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:61
msgid ""
"Once the developments have stopped for the custom modules and the "
"implemented features have been challenged to remove redundancy and "
"unnecessary code, the next step is to request an upgraded test database. "
"To do so, follow the steps mentioned in :ref:`upgrade-request-test`, "
"depending on the hosting type of your database."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullar uchun ishlanmalar to'xtatilib, joriy etilgan funksiyalar ortiqchalik va "
"keraksiz kodni olib tashlash uchun ko'rib chiqilgandan so'ng, keyingi qadam yangilangan "
"test ma'lumotlar bazasini so'rashdir. Buning uchun ma'lumotlar bazangizning joylashuviga "
"qarab :ref:`upgrade-request-test` da ko'rsatilgan qadamlarga amal qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:66
msgid ""
"The purpose of this stage is not to start working with the custom modules"
" in the upgraded database, but to make sure the standard upgrade process "
"works seamlessly, and the test database is delivered properly. If that's "
"not the case, and the upgrade request fails, request the assistance of "
"Odoo via the `support page <https://odoo.com/help?stage=migration>`_ by "
"selecting the option related to testing the upgrade."
msgstr ""
"Bu bosqichning maqsadi yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasida maxsus modullar bilan ishlashni "
"boshlash emas, balki standart yangilash jarayoni muammosiz ishlashini va test ma'lumotlar "
"bazasi to'g'ri yetkazib berilishini ta'minlashdir. Agar bunday bo'lmasa va yangilash "
"so'rovi muvaffaqiyatsiz tugasa, yangilashni sinab ko'rish bilan bog'liq variantni "
"tanlab `qo'llab-quvvatlash sahifasi <https://odoo.com/help?stage=migration>`_ orqali "
"Odoo yordamini so'rang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:75
msgid "Step 3: Empty database"
msgstr "3-qadam: Bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:77
msgid ""
"Before working on an upgraded test database, we recommend to make the "
"custom developments work on an empty database in the targeted version of "
"your upgrade. This ensures that the customization is compatible with the "
"new version of Odoo, allows to analyze how it behaves and interacts with "
"the new features, and guarantees that they will not cause any issues when"
" upgrading the database."
msgstr ""
"Yangilangan test ma'lumotlar bazasida ishlashdan oldin, maxsus ishlanmalarning "
"yangilash maqsad versiyasining bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasida ishlashini ta'minlashni "
"tavsiya etamiz. Bu moslashtirishning Odoo'ning yangi versiyasi bilan mosligini ta'minlaydi, "
"yangi funksiyalar bilan qanday harakat qilishini va o'zaro ta'sirini tahlil qilish "
"imkonini beradi va ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilashda muammolar keltirib chiqarmasligini kafolatlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:82
msgid ""
"Making the custom modules work in an empty database also helps avoid "
"changes and wrong configurations that might be present in the production "
"database (like studio customization, customized website pages, email "
"templates or translations). They are not intrinsically related to the "
"custom modules and that can raise unwanted issues in this stage of the "
"upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullarning bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasida ishlashini ta'minlash ishlab chiqarish "
"ma'lumotlar bazasida bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan o'zgarishlar va noto'g'ri konfiguratsiyalardan "
"(masalan, studio moslashtirishlari, moslashtirilgan sayt sahifalari, elektron pochta "
"shablonlari yoki tarjimalar) qochishga ham yordam beradi. Ular maxsus modullar bilan "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri bog'liq emas va yangilash jarayonining bu bosqichida istalmagan "
"muammolar keltirib chiqarishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:87
msgid ""
"To make custom modules work on an empty database we advise to follow "
"these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullarni bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasida ishlashiga erishish uchun quyidagi "
"qadamlarga amal qilishni tavsiya etamiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:89
msgid ":ref:`upgrade_custom/empty_database/modules_installable`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:90
msgid ":ref:`upgrade_custom/empty_database/test_fixes`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:91
msgid ":ref:`upgrade_custom/empty_database/clean_code`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:92
msgid ""
":ref:`Make standard tests run successfully "
"<upgrade_custom/empty_database/standard_test>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:97
msgid "Make custom modules installable"
msgstr "Maxsus modullarni o'rnatiluvchi qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:99
msgid ""
"The first step is to make the custom modules installable in the new Odoo "
"version. This means, starting by ensuring there are no tracebacks or "
"warnings during their installation. For this, install the custom modules,"
" one by one, in an empty database of the new Odoo version and fix the "
"tracebacks and warnings that arise from that."
msgstr ""
"Birinchi qadam - maxsus modullarni Odoo'ning yangi versiyasiga o'rnatiluvchi qilishdir. "
"Bu ularni o'rnatish paytida traceback va ogohlantirishlar yo'qligini ta'minlashdan "
"boshlanadi. Buning uchun Odoo'ning yangi versiyasidagi bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasiga "
"maxsus modullarni bittadan o'rnating va paydo bo'lgan traceback va ogohlantirishlarni tuzating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:104
msgid ""
"This process will help detect issues during the installation of the "
"modules. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Bu jarayon modullarni o'rnatish paytidagi muammolarni aniqlashga yordam beradi. Masalan:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:106
msgid "Invalid module dependencies."
msgstr "Noto'g'ri modul bog'liqliklari."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:107
msgid "Syntax change: assets declaration, OWL updates, attrs."
msgstr "Sintaksis o'zgarishi: assets deklaratsiyasi, OWL yangilanishlari, attrs."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:108
msgid ""
"References to standard fields, models, views not existing anymore or "
"renamed."
msgstr "Endi mavjud bo'lmagan yoki qayta nomlangan standart maydonlar, modellar, ko'rinishlarga havolalar."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:109
msgid "Xpath that moved or were removed from views."
msgstr "Ko'rinishlardan ko'chirilgan yoki olib tashlangan Xpath."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:110
msgid "Methods renamed or removed."
msgstr "Qayta nomlangan yoki olib tashlangan metodlar."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:116
msgid "Test and fixes"
msgstr "Sinov va tuzatishlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:118
msgid ""
"Once there are no more tracebacks when installing the modules, the next "
"step is to test them. Even if the custom modules are installable on an "
"empty database, this does not guarantee there are no errors during their "
"execution. Because of this, we encourage to test thoroughly all the "
"customization to make sure everything is working as expected."
msgstr ""
"Modullarni o'rnatishda endi traceback bo'lmagandan so'ng, keyingi qadam ularni sinab "
"ko'rishdir. Maxsus modullar bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasiga o'rnatilsa ham, bu ularni "
"bajarilish paytida xatolar yo'qligini kafolatlamaydi. Shu sababli hamma narsa kutilgandek "
"ishlashini ta'minlash uchun barcha moslashtirishlarni puxta sinab ko'rishni tavsiya etamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:123
msgid ""
"This process will help detect further issues that are not identified "
"during the module installation and can only be detected in runtime. For "
"example, deprecated calls to standard python or OWL functions, non-"
"existing references to standard fields, etc."
msgstr ""
"Bu jarayon modul o'rnatilish paytida aniqlanmagan va faqat ishlash vaqtida aniqlanishi "
"mumkin bo'lgan qo'shimcha muammolarni aniqlashga yordam beradi. Masalan, eskirgan "
"Python yoki OWL funksiyalariga chaqiriqlar, mavjud bo'lmagan standart maydonlarga "
"havolalar va hokazo."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:127
msgid ""
"We recommend to test all the customization, especially the following "
"elements:"
msgstr "Barcha moslashtirishlarni, ayniqsa quyidagi elementlarni sinab ko'rishni tavsiya etamiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:130
msgid "Email templates"
msgstr "Elektron pochta shablonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:131
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Hisobotlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:132
msgid "Server actions and automated actions"
msgstr "Server amallari va avtomatlashtirilgan amallar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:133
msgid "Changes in the standard workflows"
msgstr "Standart ish oqimlaridagi o'zgarishlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:134
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:716
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:465
msgid "Computed fields"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:136
msgid ""
"We also encourage to write automated tests to save time during the "
"testing iterations, increase the test coverage, and ensure that the "
"changes and fixes introduced do not break the existing flows. If there "
"are tests already implemented in the customization, make sure they are "
"upgraded to the new Odoo version and run successfully, fixing issues that"
" might be present."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, sinov takrorlanishlarida vaqtni tejash, test qamrovini oshirish va kiritilgan "
"o'zgarishlar hamda tuzatishlar mavjud jarayonlarni buzmasligini ta'minlash uchun "
"avtomatlashtirilgan testlar yozishni tavsiya etamiz. Agar moslashtirishda allaqachon "
"amalga oshirilgan testlar mavjud bo'lsa, ularning Odoo'ning yangi versiyasiga "
"yangilanganligi va muvaffaqiyatli bajarilayotganligini, mavjud muammolar "
"tuzatilganligini ta'minlang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:144
msgid "Clean the code"
msgstr "Kodni tozalash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:146
msgid ""
"At this stage of the upgrade process, we also suggest to clean the code "
"as much as possible. This includes:"
msgstr ""
"Yangilash jarayonining bu bosqichida, kodni iloji boricha tozalashni ham taklif etamiz. "
"Bunga quyidagilar kiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:149
msgid "Remove redundant and unnecessary code."
msgstr "Ortiqcha va keraksiz kodni olib tashlash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:150
msgid ""
"Remove features that are now part of Odoo standard, as described in "
":ref:`upgrade_custom/stop_developments`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`upgrade_custom/stop_developments` da tasvirlanganidek, endi Odoo standartining "
"bir qismi bo'lgan funksiyalarni olib tashlash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:152
msgid "Clean commented code if it is not needed anymore."
msgstr "Endi kerak bo'lmasa, kommentariyga olingan kodni tozalash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:153
msgid "Refactor the code (functions, fields, views, reports, etc.) if needed."
msgstr "Agar kerak bo'lsa, kodni refaktoring qilish (funksiyalar, maydonlar, ko'rinishlar, hisobotlar va h.k.)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:158
msgid "Standard tests"
msgstr "Standart testlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:160
msgid ""
"Once the previous steps are completed, we advise to make sure all "
"standard tests associated to the dependencies of the custom module pass. "
"Standard tests ensure the validation of the code logic and prevent data "
"corruption. They will help you identify bugs or unwanted behavior before "
"you work on your database."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi qadamlar bajarilgandan so'ng, maxsus modulning bog'liqliklariga tegishli barcha "
"standart testlarning o'tishini ta'minlashni tavsiya etamiz. Standart testlar kod mantiqini "
"tasdiqlashni ta'minlaydi va ma'lumotlarning buzilishini oldini oladi. Ular ma'lumotlar "
"bazangizda ishlashdan oldin xatolar yoki istalmagan xatti-harakatlarni aniqlashga yordam beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:165
msgid ""
"In case there are standard test failing, we suggest to analyze the reason"
" for their failure:"
msgstr "Standart testlar muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lsa, muvaffaqiyatsizlik sababini tahlil qilishni tavsiya etamiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:167
msgid ""
"The customization changes the standard workflow: Adapt the standard test "
"to your workflow."
msgstr "Moslashtirish standart ish oqimini o'zgartiradi: Standart testni o'z ish oqimingizga moslashtiring."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:168
msgid ""
"The customization did not take into account a special flow: Adapt your "
"customization to ensure it works for all the standard workflows."
msgstr ""
"Moslashtirish maxsus oqimni hisobga olmagan: Moslashtirishingizni barcha standart "
"ish oqimlari uchun ishlashini ta'minlash uchun moslang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:175
msgid "Step 4: Upgraded database"
msgstr "4-qadam: Yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:177
msgid ""
"Once the custom modules are installable and working properly in an empty "
"database, it is time to make them work on an :ref:`upgraded database "
"<upgrade-request-test>`."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullar bo'sh ma'lumotlar bazasiga o'rnatiluvchi va to'g'ri ishlayotgan bo'lsa, "
"ularni :ref:`yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasi <upgrade-request-test>` da ishlashiga "
"erishish vaqti keldi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:180
msgid ""
"To make sure the custom code is working flawlessly in the new version, "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr "Maxsus kodning yangi versiyada muammosiz ishlayotganligini ta'minlash uchun quyidagi qadamlarga amal qiling:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:182
msgid ":ref:`upgrade_custom/upgraded_database/migrate_data`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:183
msgid ":ref:`upgrade_custom/upgraded_database/test_custom`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:188
msgid "Migrate the data"
msgstr "Ma'lumotlarni migratsiya qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:190
msgid ""
"During the upgrade of the custom modules, you might have to use "
":doc:`upgrade scripts <../reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts>` to reflect"
" changes from the source code to their corresponding data. Together with "
"the upgrade scripts, you can also make use of the "
":doc:`../reference/upgrades/upgrade_utils` and its helper functions."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullarni yangilash paytida, manba kodidagi o'zgarishlarni tegishli "
"ma'lumotlarga aks ettirish uchun :doc:`yangilash skriptlaridan "
"<../reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts>` foydalanishingiz kerak bo'lishi mumkin. "
"Yangilash skriptlari bilan birga :doc:`../reference/upgrades/upgrade_utils` va uning "
"yordamchi funksiyalaridan ham foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:195
msgid ""
"Any technical data that was renamed during the upgrade of the custom code"
" (models, fields, external identifiers) should be renamed using upgrade "
"scripts to avoid data loss during the module upgrade. See also: "
":meth:`rename_field`, :meth:`rename_model`, :meth:`rename_xmlid`."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus kod yangilash paytida qayta nomlangan har qanday texnik ma'lumot (modellar, "
"maydonlar, tashqi identifikatorlar) modul yangilanishi paytida ma'lumotlar yo'qolishini "
"oldini olish uchun yangilash skriptlari yordamida qayta nomlanishi kerak. "
"Shuningdek qarang: :meth:`rename_field`, :meth:`rename_model`, :meth:`rename_xmlid`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:198
msgid ""
"Data from standard models removed from the source code of the newer Odoo "
"version and from the database during the standard upgrade process might "
"need to be recovered from the old model table if it is still present."
msgstr ""
"Odoo'ning yangi versiyasining manba kodidan va standart yangilash jarayonida "
"ma'lumotlar bazasidan olib tashlangan standart modellardan ma'lumotlar, agar eski "
"model jadvali hali ham mavjud bo'lsa, undan tiklanishi kerak bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:203
msgid ""
"Custom fields for model ``sale.subscription`` are not automatically "
"migrated from Odoo 15 to Odoo 16 (when the model was merged into "
"``sale.order``). In this case, a SQL query can be executed on an upgrade "
"script to move the data from one table to the other. Take into account "
"that all columns/fields must already exist, so consider doing this in a "
"``post-`` script (See :ref:`upgrade-scripts/phases`)."
msgstr ""
"``sale.subscription`` modeli uchun maxsus maydonlar Odoo 15 dan Odoo 16 ga "
"(model ``sale.order`` ga birlashtirilganda) avtomatik ravishda migratsiya qilinmaydi. "
"Bu holda, ma'lumotlarni bir jadvaldan boshqasiga ko'chirish uchun yangilash skriptida "
"SQL so'rovi bajarilishi mumkin. Barcha ustunlar/maydonlar allaqachon mavjud bo'lishi "
"kerakligini hisobga oling, shuning uchun buni ``post-`` skriptida bajarishni "
"ko'rib chiqing (qarang: :ref:`upgrade-scripts/phases`)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:223
msgid ""
"Check the documentation for more information on "
":doc:`../reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`../reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts` haqida qo'shimcha ma'lumot uchun "
"hujjatlarni ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:225
msgid "Upgrade scripts can also be used to:"
msgstr "Yangilash skriptlari quyidagi maqsadlarda ham ishlatilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:227
msgid ""
"Ease the processing time of an upgrade. For example, to store the value "
"of computed stored fields on models with an excessive number of records "
"by using SQL queries."
msgstr ""
"Yangilash ish vaqtini yengillashtirish. Masalan, SQL so'rovlaridan foydalanib "
"haddan ziyod yozuvlarga ega modellardagi hisoblangan saqlangan maydonlarning "
"qiymatini saqlash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:229
msgid ""
"Recompute fields in case the computation of their value has changed. See "
"also :meth:`recompute_fields`."
msgstr ""
"Qiymatlarni hisoblash o'zgargan taqdirda maydonlarni qayta hisoblash. "
"Shuningdek qarang: :meth:`recompute_fields`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:231
msgid "Uninstall unwanted custom modules. See also :meth:`remove_module`."
msgstr "Keraksiz maxsus modullarni o'chirib tashlash. Shuningdek qarang: :meth:`remove_module`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:232
msgid "Correct faulty data or wrong configurations."
msgstr "Noto'g'ri ma'lumotlar yoki noto'g'ri konfiguratsiyalarni to'g'rilash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:235
msgid "Running and testing upgrade scripts"
msgstr "Yangilash skriptlarini ishga tushirish va sinab ko'rish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:239
msgid "Odoo Online"
msgstr "Odoo Online"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:241
msgid ""
"As the instalation of custom modules containing Python files is not "
"allowed on Odoo Online databases, it is not possible to run upgrade "
"scripts on this platform."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Online ma'lumotlar bazalarida Python fayllarini o'z ichiga olgan maxsus modullarni "
"o'rnatishga ruxsat berilmaganligi sababli, bu platformada yangilash skriptlarini "
"ishga tushirish mumkin emas."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:244
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/going_live.rst:45
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:160
msgid "Odoo.sh"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:246
msgid ""
"As explained on the `Odoo.sh` tab of :ref:`upgrade-request-test`, Odoo.sh"
" is integrated with the upgrade platform."
msgstr ""
":ref:`upgrade-request-test` ning `Odoo.sh` yorlig'ida tushuntirilganidek, Odoo.sh "
"yangilash platformasi bilan integratsiya qilingan."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:249
msgid ""
"Once the upgrade of a staging branch is on \"Update on commit\" mode, "
"each time a commit is pushed on the branch, the upgraded backup is "
"restored and all the custom modules are updated. This update includes the"
" execution of the upgrade scripts."
msgstr ""
"Bosqichli tarmoqning yangilanishi \"Commit paytida yangilash\" rejimida bo'lgach, "
"har safar commit tarmoqqa surilganda, yangilangan zaxira tiklandi va barcha maxsus "
"modullar yangilanadi. Bu yangilash yangilash skriptlarini bajarishni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:253
msgid ""
"When upgrading the production database, the execution of the upgrade "
"scripts is also part of the update of the custom modules done by the "
"platform when the upgraded database is restored."
msgstr ""
"Ishlab chiqarish ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilashda, yangilash skriptlarini bajarish "
"ham yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasi tiklantirilganda platforma tomonidan amalga "
"oshiriladigan maxsus modullarni yangilashning bir qismi hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:256
msgid "On-premise"
msgstr "On-premise (o'z serverida)"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:258
msgid ""
"Once you receive the upgraded dump of the database from the `Upgrade "
"platform <https://upgrade.odoo.com>`_, deploy the database and update all"
" the custom modules by invoking the command :doc:`odoo-bin "
"</developer/reference/cli>` in the shell. To update the custom modules, "
"use the option: `-u <modules>, --update <modules>`."
msgstr ""
"`Yangilash platformasi <https://upgrade.odoo.com>`_ dan ma'lumotlar bazasining "
"yangilangan dumpini olgach, ma'lumotlar bazasini joylashtiring va shell'da "
":doc:`odoo-bin </developer/reference/cli>` buyrug'ini chaqirish orqali barcha "
"maxsus modullarni yangilang. Maxsus modullarni yangilash uchun quyidagi "
"variantdan foydalaning: `-u <modules>, --update <modules>`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:265
msgid ""
"As mentioned in the :doc:`CLI documentation </developer/reference/cli>`, "
"the command used to call the CLI depends on how you installed Odoo."
msgstr ""
":doc:`CLI hujjati </developer/reference/cli>` da aytib o'tilganidek, CLI ni chaqirish "
"uchun ishlatiladigan buyruq Odoo'ni qanday o'rnatganingizga bog'liq."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:271
msgid "Test the custom modules"
msgstr "Maxsus modullarni sinab ko'rish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:273
msgid ""
"To make sure the custom modules work properly with your data in the "
"upgraded database, they need to be tested as well. This helps ensure both"
" the standard and the custom data stored in the database are consistent "
"and that nothing was lost during the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullarning yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasidagi ma'lumotlaringiz bilan "
"to'g'ri ishlashini ta'minlash uchun ularni ham sinab ko'rish kerak. Bu ma'lumotlar "
"bazasida saqlangan standart va maxsus ma'lumotlarning izchilligini va yangilash "
"jarayonida hech narsa yo'qolmaganligini ta'minlashga yordam beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:277
msgid "Things to pay attention to:"
msgstr "E'tibor berish kerak bo'lgan narsalar:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:279
msgid ""
"Views not working: During the upgrade, if a view causes issues because of"
" its content, it gets disabled. You can find the information on disabled "
"views on the Upgrade report. This view needs to be activated again (or "
"removed if not useful anymore). To achieve this, we recommend the use of "
"upgrade scripts."
msgstr ""
"Ishlamayotgan ko'rinishlar: Yangilash paytida, agar ko'rinish tarkibi sababli muammo "
"keltirib chiqarsa, u o'chirib qo'yiladi. O'chirib qo'yilgan ko'rinishlar haqidagi "
"ma'lumotni Yangilash hisobotida topishingiz mumkin. Bu ko'rinish qayta faollashtirilishi "
"(yoki endi kerak bo'lmasa olib tashlanishi) kerak. Bunga erishish uchun yangilash "
"skriptlaridan foydalanishni tavsiya etamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:283
msgid ""
":doc:`Module data <../tutorials/define_module_data>` not updated: Custom "
"records that have the ``noupdate`` flag are not updated when upgrading "
"the module in the new database. For the custom data that needs to be "
"updated due to changes in the new version, we recommend to use upgrade "
"scripts to do so. See also: :meth:`update_record_from_xml`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Modul ma'lumotlari <../tutorials/define_module_data>` yangilanmadi: "
"``noupdate`` bayrog'iga ega bo'lgan maxsus yozuvlar yangi ma'lumotlar bazasida "
"modulni yangilashda yangilanmaydi. Yangi versiyasidagi o'zgarishlar sababli "
"yangilanishi kerak bo'lgan maxsus ma'lumotlar uchun yangilash skriptlaridan "
"foydalanishni tavsiya etamiz. Shuningdek qarang: :meth:`update_record_from_xml`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:291
msgid "Step 5: Testing and rehearsal"
msgstr "5-qadam: Sinov va mashq"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:293
msgid ""
"When the custom modules are working properly in the upgraded database, it"
" is crucial to do another round of testing to assess the database "
"usability and detect any issues that might have gone unnoticed in "
"previous tests. For further information about testing the upgraded "
"database, check :ref:`upgrade-testing`."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modullar yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasida to'g'ri ishlayotgan bo'lsa, "
"ma'lumotlar bazasining foydalanish imkoniyatini baholash va oldingi testlarda "
"e'tibordan chetda qolgan muammolarni aniqlash uchun yana bir davra sinov o'tkazish "
"muhim ahamiyatga ega. Yangilangan ma'lumotlar bazasini sinab ko'rish haqida qo'shimcha "
"ma'lumot uchun :ref:`upgrade-testing` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:298
msgid ""
"As mentioned in :ref:`upgrade-production`, both standard upgrade scripts "
"and your database are constantly evolving. Therefore it is highly "
"recommended to frequently request new upgraded test databases and ensure "
"that the upgrade process is still successful."
msgstr ""
":ref:`upgrade-production` da aytib o'tilganidek, standart yangilash skriptlari ham, "
"ma'lumotlar bazangiz ham doimiy ravishda rivojlanmoqda. Shuning uchun tez-tez yangi "
"yangilangan test ma'lumotlar bazalarini so'rash va yangilash jarayoni muvaffaqiyatli "
"ekanligini ta'minlash tavsiya etiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:302
msgid ""
"In addition to that, make a full rehearsal of the upgrade process the day"
" before upgrading the production database to avoid undesired behavior "
"during the upgrade and to detect any issue that might have occurred with "
"the migrated data."
msgstr ""
"Bundan tashqari, yangilash paytidagi istalmagan xatti-harakatlarning oldini olish va "
"migratsiya qilingan ma'lumotlar bilan yuzaga kelishi mumkin bo'lgan muammolarni "
"aniqlash uchun ishlab chiqarish ma'lumotlar bazasini yangilashdan bir kun oldin "
"yangilash jarayonini to'liq mashq qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:309
msgid "Step 6: Production upgrade"
msgstr "6-qadam: Ishlab chiqarishdagi yangilash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/upgrade_custom_db.rst:311
msgid ""
"Once you are confident about upgrading your production database, follow "
"the process described on :ref:`upgrade-production`, depending on the "
"hosting type of your database."
msgstr ""
"Ishlab chiqarish ma'lumotlar bazangizni yangilashga ishonch hosil qilgach, "
"ma'lumotlar bazangizning joylashuv turiga qarab :ref:`upgrade-production` da "
"tasvirlangan jarayonga amal qiling."

msgid "Artistic illustration of \"Web design\""
msgstr "\"Veb-dizayn\" badiiy rasmi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes.rst:13
msgid ""
"The Odoo Website Builder is an excellent tool for creating a website "
"fully integrated with other Odoo apps. Using the theme's options and "
"building blocks is easy and allows you to personalize your web presence "
"the way you want. However, you can take things even further."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Veb-sayt Quruvchisi boshqa Odoo ilovalari bilan to'liq integratsiya qilingan "
"veb-sayt yaratish uchun ajoyib vositadir. Mavzu imkoniyatlari va qurilish bloklaridan "
"foydalanish oson va o'zingiz xohlagancha veb-mavjudligingizni shaxsiylashtirish imkonini "
"beradi. Ammo siz narsalarni yanada oldinga olib borishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes.rst:17
msgid ""
"In this documentation, you will learn to completely customize your "
"website without touching Odoo's core files, and this way, preserve the "
"editing options of the Website Builder."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu hujjatda Odoo'ning asosiy fayllarini o'zgartirmasdan veb-saytingizni to'liq "
"moslashtirishni va shu tarzda Veb-sayt Quruvchisining tahrirlash imkoniyatlarini "
"saqlab qolishni o'rganasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes.rst:20
msgid ""
"The information compiled in this documentation is based on our past "
"experiences - both failures and successes. We invite you to use it as a "
"base to build your own website and adapt it to your needs."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu hujjatda to'plangan ma'lumotlar o'tmishdagi tajribalarimizga - ham "
"muvaffaqiyatsizliklar, ham muvaffaqiyatlarga asoslanadi. O'z veb-saytingizni "
"qurish va uni ehtiyojlaringizga moslashtirish uchun asos sifatida foydalanishga "
"taklif qilamiz."

