#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/animations.rst:27
msgid ""
"You can easily define an animation on a column in your custom theme. You "
"need to add two classes: `o_animate` and `o_anim_fade_in`. The second "
"class changes depending on the type of animation you want to use."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus mavzungizdagi ustunda animatsiyani osongina belgilashingiz mumkin. "
"Ikki klass qo'shish kerak: `o_animate` va `o_anim_fade_in`. Ikkinchi klass "
"foydalanmoqchi bo'lgan animatsiya turiga qarab o'zgaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/animations.rst:31
msgid ""
"Add the `o_animate_both_scroll` class to launch the animation every time "
"the column appears on the screen. The animation is only launched once by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Ustun ekranda har paydo bo'lganda animatsiyani ishga tushirish uchun "
"`o_animate_both_scroll` klassini qo'shing. Animatsiya standart holda faqat "
"bir marta ishga tushiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/animations.rst:34
msgid ""
"You should also define an `animation-duration` and an `animation-delay` "
"directly in the `style` attribute."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek `style` atributida to'g'ridan-to'g'ri `animation-duration` va "
"`animation-delay` ni belgilashingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/animations.rst:37
msgid ""
"Additionally, you can add an animation direction. For instance, to "
"animate the element from the bottom of the screen, add a "
"`o_anim_from_bottom` class and set a `--wanim-intensity` in the `style` "
"attribute to control the animation's direction intensity."
msgstr ""
"Bundan tashqari, animatsiya yo'nalishini qo'shishingiz mumkin. Masalan, elementni "
"ekranning pastidan animatsiya qilish uchun `o_anim_from_bottom` klassini qo'shing "
"va animatsiya yo'nalishi kuchini boshqarish uchun `style` atributida "
"`--wanim-intensity` ni o'rnating."

