msgid ""
"Enable animations on hover by adding the `o_animate_on_hover` class on "
"your image tag. You can also define the type of animation in the `data-"
"hover-effect` attribute."
msgstr ""
"Rasm tegingizga `o_animate_on_hover` klassini qo'shib kursorni olib kelganda "
