"bir nechta kategoriyalarga bo'linadi (:guilabel:`Kirish`, :guilabel:`Ustunlar`, "
":guilabel:`Kontent`, :guilabel:`Rasmlar`, :guilabel:`Odamlar` va h.k.)"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:13
