#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:119
msgid ""
"Avoid adding a `section` tag inside another `section` tag: this will "
"trigger twice the Website Builder's options. You can use inner content "
"snippets instead."
msgstr "Bir `section` tegini boshqa `section` tegi ichiga qo'shishdan saqlaning: bu Veb-sayt Quruvchisi imkoniyatlarini ikki marta ishga tushiradi. Buning o'rniga ichki kontent snippetlaridan foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:123
msgid ""
"To write the content of a static page with standard snippets, there are "
"two possible approaches:"
msgstr "Standart snippetlar yordamida statik sahifa mazmunini yozish uchun ikkita mumkin bo'lgan yondashuv mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:126
msgid ""
"**Pre-build the custom static pages with the Website Builder:** Drag & "
"drop snippets, then"
