#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst
msgid "**OR**"
msgstr "**YOKI**"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:132
msgid ""
"**Code everything directly:** But beware of compatibility with the "
"Website Builder. It"
msgstr "**Hamma narsani to'g'ridan-to'g'ri kodlang:** Lekin Veb-sayt Quruvchisi bilan moslikka e'tibor bering. U"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:131
msgid ""
"requires certain classes, names, id, data, etc. to work properly. A good "
"practice is to seek out the snippets code created in standard code in the"
" Odoo source files. Pay attention that the Website Builder sometimes adds"
" classes to the snippets after dropped in the page."
