#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:352
msgid ""
"Grid Layout is a powerful and flexible layout system in CSS that enables "
"users to design complex building block layouts with ease."
msgstr "Grid Layout - foydalanuvchilarga murakkab qurilish bloki tartiblarini osongina loyihalash imkonini beruvchi CSS dagi kuchli va moslashuvchan tartib tizimi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:358
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/media.rst:60
msgid "Use"
msgstr "Ishlatish"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:360
msgid ""
"Enable the Grid Layout by adding the `o_grid_mode` CSS class on the "
"`row`. The number of rows in your grid is defined by the `data-row-count`"
" attribute. The grid always contains 12 columns. The grid gap, specified "
"in the `style` attribute, determines the gaps (or gutters) between rows "
"and columns."
msgstr "`row` da `o_grid_mode` CSS klassini qo'shish orqali Grid Layoutni yoqing. Griddagi qatorlar soni `data-row-count` atributi bilan aniqlanadi. Grid har doim 12 ustunni o'z ichiga oladi. `style` atributida ko'rsatilgan grid bo'shlig'i qatorlar va ustunlar orasidagi bo'shliqlarni (yoki gutterlarni) belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:374
msgid "Items in a grid"
msgstr "Grid elementlari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:376
msgid ""
"Add items in the grid with the `o_grid_item` class. If the grid item "
"contains an image, use the `o_grid_item_image` class."
msgstr "`o_grid_item` klassi yordamida gridga elementlar qo'shing. Agar grid elementi rasm o'z ichiga olsa, `o_grid_item_image` klassidan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:391
msgid ""
"The dimensions and position of a grid item are defined by the grid-area "
"that can be explicitly set in the `style` attribute along with the "
"z-index."
msgstr "Grid elementining o'lchamlari va joylashuvi z-index bilan birga `style` atributida aniq belgilanishi mumkin bo'lgan grid-area orqali aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:394
