"The `g-height-*` and `g-col-lg-*` classes are generated by the Website "
"Builder for editing purposes."
msgstr "`g-height-*` va `g-col-lg-*` klasslari tahrirlash maqsadida Veb-sayt Quruvchisi tomonidan yaratiladi."

