msgstr "Bu data atributlari tizimga ushbu snippet uchun qaysi fayl versiyasini yuklashni ko'rsatadi (masalan, :file:`001.js`, :file:`002.scss`)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:442
msgid "Custom snippet"
msgstr "Maxsus snippet"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:444
msgid ""
"Some more specific needs will require the creation of custom snippets. "
