msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:475
msgid ""
"`data-name` and `data-snippet` attributes have to be specified when a "
"snippet is declared on a theme page. Otherwise, the snippet won't be "
"recognised by the Website Builder and issues might occur whenever a "
"database upgrade is done. Additionally, remember that the name attribute "
"is shown as the name of your custom snippet in the :guilabel:`Blocks` "
"section of the options panel."
msgstr "`data-name` va `data-snippet` atributlari mavzu sahifasida snippet e'lon qilinganda ko'rsatilishi shart. Aks holda, snippet Veb-sayt Quruvchisi tomonidan tanilmaydi va ma'lumotlar bazasi yangilanishida muammolar yuzaga kelishi mumkin. Bundan tashqari, esda tuting, name atributi imkoniyatlar panelining :guilabel:`Blocks` bo'limida maxsus snippetingizning nomi sifatida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:481
msgid "Use Bootstrap native classes as much as possible."
msgstr "Iloji boricha Bootstrap mahalliy klasslaridan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:482
msgid "Prefix all your custom classes."
msgstr "Barcha maxsus klasslarga prefiks qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:483
msgid ""
"Use underscore lowercase notation to name classes, e.g., `.x_nav`, "
"`.x_nav_item`."
msgstr "Klasslarni nomlash uchun pastki chiziqli kichik harf yozuvidan foydalaning, masalan, `.x_nav`, `.x_nav_item`."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:484
msgid ""
"Avoid using ID attribute within your `section` as several instances of a "
"snippet may appear throughout the page (An ID attribute has to be unique "
"on a page)."
msgstr "`section` ichida ID atributidan foydalanmang, chunki snippetning bir nechta nusxasi sahifada paydo bo'lishi mumkin (ID atributi sahifada noyob bo'lishi shart)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:487
msgid ""
"Add the custom snippet to the list of standard snippets, so the user can "
"drag and drop it on the page, directly from the edit panel."
msgstr "Maxsus snippetni standart snippetlar ro'yxatiga qo'shing, shunda foydalanuvchi uni tahrirlash panelidan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri sahifaga sudrab tashlashi mumkin bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:491
