#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:615
msgid ""
"Options allow users to edit a snippet's appearance and behavior using the"
" Website Builder. Options are OWL components defined in JavaScript and "
"rendered with XML templates. Each option is registered through a builder "
"plugin and loaded in the editor assets."
msgstr "Imkoniyatlar foydalanuvchilarga Veb-sayt Quruvchisi yordamida snippet ko'rinishi va xatti-harakatini tahrirlash imkonini beradi. Imkoniyatlar JavaScript da belgilangan va XML shablonlar yordamida ko'rsatiladigan OWL komponentlaridir. Har bir imkoniyat builder plagin orqali ro'yxatga olinadi va muharrir assetlarida yuklanadi."

