#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/building_blocks.rst:698
msgid ""
"Builder plugins register option components, actions, and editor hooks "
"through the `resources` object. They are added to the `website-plugins` "
"registry category to be accessible by the editor. Plugin instances are "
"created when the editor starts and destroyed when the editor closes, they"
" live for the whole editor session."
msgstr "Builder plaginlari `resources` obyekti orqali imkoniyat komponentlari, harakatlar va muharrir ishlovchilarini ro'yxatga oladi. Ular muharrir tomonidan kirish imkoniyatiga ega bo'lish uchun `website-plugins` ro'yxat kategoriyasiga qo'shiladi. Plagin nusxalari muharrir ishga tushganda yaratiladi va muharrir yopilganda yo'q qilinadi, ular butun muharrir sessiyasi davomida yashaydi."

