#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/translations.rst:7
msgid "In this chapter, you will learn how to:"
msgstr "Ushbu bobda siz quyidagilarni o'rganasiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:7
msgid "Create a custom header."
msgstr "Maxsus sarlavha yaratish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:8
msgid "Create a custom footer."
msgstr "Maxsus pastki qism yaratish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:9
msgid "Modify a standard template."
msgstr "Standart shablonni o'zgartirish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:10
msgid "Add a copyright section."
msgstr "Mualliflik huquqi bo'limini qo'shish."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:11
msgid "Improve your website's responsiveness."
msgstr "Veb-saytingizning moslashuvchanligi yaxshilash."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:16
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/navigation.rst:16
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:171
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Standart"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:18
msgid ""
"An Odoo page combines cross-page and unique elements. Cross-page elements"
" are the same on every page, while unique elements are only related to a "
"specific page. By default, a page has two cross-page elements, the header"
" and the footer, and a unique main element that contains the specific "
"content of that page."
msgstr "Odoo sahifasi sahifalararo va noyob elementlarni birlashtiradi. Sahifalararo elementlar har bir sahifada bir xil, noyob elementlar esa faqat muayyan sahifaga tegishli. Standart bo'yicha, sahifada ikkita sahifalararo element — sarlavha va pastki qism, hamda shu sahifaning muayyan kontentini o'z ichiga olgan noyob asosiy element mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:35
msgid ""
"Any Odoo XML file starts with encoding specifications. After that, you "
"must write your code inside an `<odoo>` tag."
msgstr "Har qanday Odoo XML fayli kodlash spetsifikatsiyalari bilan boshlanadi. Shundan so'ng kodingizni `<odoo>` tegi ichiga yozishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:46
msgid ""
"Using precise template names is important to find information through all"
" modules quickly. Template names should only contain lowercase "
"alphanumerics and underscores."
msgstr "Aniq shablon nomlaridan foydalanish barcha modullar orqali tezda ma'lumot topish uchun muhim. Shablon nomlari faqat kichik harfli alfasanli belgilar va pastki chiziqlardan iborat bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:49
msgid ""
"Always add an empty line at the end of your file. This can be done "
"automatically by configuring your IDE."
msgstr "Har doim faylingiz oxiriga bo'sh qator qo'shing. Bu IDE ni sozlash orqali avtomatik ravishda amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:55
msgid "XPath"
msgstr "XPath"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:57
msgid ""
"XPath (XML Path Language) is an expression language that enables you to "
"navigate through elements and attributes in an XML document easily. XPath"
" is used to extend standard Odoo templates."
msgstr "XPath (XML Path Language) — XML hujjatidagi elementlar va atributlar orqali oson navigatsiya qilish imkonini beruvchi ifoda tili. XPath standart Odoo shablonlarini kengaytirish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:60
msgid "A view is coded the following way."
msgstr "Ko'rinish quyidagi tarzda kodlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:76
msgid "ID of the modified view"
msgstr "O'zgartirilgan ko'rinishning IDsi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:77
msgid "inherited_id"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:78
msgid "ID of the standard view (using the following pattern: `module.template`)"
msgstr "Standart ko'rinishning IDsi (quyidagi namuna bo'yicha: `module.template`)"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:80
msgid "Human-readable name of the modified view"
msgstr "O'zgartirilgan ko'rinishning odam o'qiy oladigan nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:82
msgid ""
"For each XPath, you modify two attributes: **expression** and "
"**position**."
msgstr "Har bir XPath uchun ikkita atributni o'zgartirasiz: **ifoda** va **pozitsiya**."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:85
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:533
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:760
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:780
#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/navigation.rst:244
msgid "``/website_airproof/views/website_templates.xml``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:94
msgid "This XPath adds a welcome message right before the page content."
msgstr "Bu XPath sahifa kontentidan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri oldin xush kelibsiz xabarini qo'shadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:97
msgid ""
"Be careful when replacing default elements' attributes. As your theme "
"extends the default one, your changes will take priority over any future "
"Odoo update."
msgstr "Standart elementlar atributlarini almashtirishda ehtiyot bo'ling. Mavzungiz standartni kengaytirganligidan, o'zgartirishlaringiz kelajakdagi har qanday Odoo yangilanishlaridan ustun bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:101
msgid ""
"You should update your module every time you create a new template or "
"record."
msgstr "Har safar yangi shablon yoki yozuv yaratsangiz, modulingizni yangilashingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:102
msgid ""
"*XML IDs* of inheriting views should use the same *ID* as the original "
"record. It helps to find all inheritance at a glance. As final *XML IDs* "
"are prefixed by the module that creates them, there is no overlap."
msgstr "Meros oluvchi ko'rinishlarning *XML IDlari* asl yozuv bilan bir xil *IDdan* foydalanishi kerak. Bu barcha merosni bir ko'rishda topishga yordam beradi. Yakuniy *XML IDlar* ularni yaratgan modul bilan prefikslanganligidan, mos kelish bo'lmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:109
msgid "Expressions"
msgstr "Ifodalar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:111
msgid ""
"XPath uses path expressions to select nodes in an XML document. Selectors"
" are used inside the expression to target the right element. The most "
"useful ones are listed below."
msgstr "XPath XML hujjatidagi tugunlarni tanlash uchun yo'l ifodalaridan foydalanadi. Selektorlar to'g'ri elementni nishonga olish uchun ifoda ichida ishlatiladi. Eng foydaliları quyida keltirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:119
msgid "Descendent selectors"
msgstr "Avlod selektorlari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:121
msgid "/"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:122
msgid "Selects from the root node."
msgstr "Ildiz tugundan tanlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:123
msgid "//"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:124
msgid ""
"Selects nodes in the document from the current node that matches the "
"selection no matter where they are."
msgstr "Hujjatda joriy tugundan boshlab, qayerda bo'lishidan qat'i nazar, tanlovga mos keladigan tugunlarni tanlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:132
msgid "Attribute selectors"
msgstr "Atribut selektorlari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/layout.rst:134
msgid "\\*"
msgstr ""

