#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:235
msgid "**Use case**"
msgstr "**Foydalanish holati**"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:237
msgid ""
"There are several static pages created in the module. This one has been "
"installed on the database and the end-user has updated some of those "
"pages. Some bug fixes must be applied on the static pages while avoiding "
"any loss of changes made by the end-user."
msgstr ""
"Modulda bir nechta statik sahifalar yaratilgan. Bu modul ma'lumotlar "
"bazasiga o'rnatilgan va foydalanuvchi ushbu sahifalarning ba'zilarini "
"yangilagan. Foydalanuvchi kiritgan o'zgarishlarni yo'qotmasdan statik "
"sahifalarga ba'zi xato tuzatmalar qo'llanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:241
msgid "**Problem**"
msgstr "**Muammo**"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:243
msgid ""
"In case of a module update on the database, every record declared into "
"the module will overwrite those existing in the database even if the end-"
"user has changed some of these records."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasida modul yangilanganda, modulda e'lon qilingan har bir "
"yozuv ma'lumotlar bazasidagi mavjud yozuvlarning ustiga yoziladi, "
"foydalanuvchi ushbu yozuvlardan ba'zilarini o'zgartirgan bo'lsa ham."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:246
msgid "**Solution**"
msgstr "**Yechim**"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:248
msgid ""
"By wrapping the record (or all records declared in the file) into a "
"`<data noupdate=\"1\"></data>` tag, the record declared is created at the"
" first module installation but not updated after a module update."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvni (yoki fayl ichida e'lon qilingan barcha yozuvlarni) `<data "
"noupdate=\"1\"></data>` tegiga o'rab, e'lon qilingan yozuv modulning "
"birinchi o'rnatilishida yaratiladi, lekin modul yangilanganidan keyin "
"yangilanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:254
msgid "The system detects that this record doesn't exist and will re-create it."
msgstr "Tizim ushbu yozuv mavjud emasligini aniqlaydi va uni qayta yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/pages.rst:258
msgid "Of course not. It's technically usable for every type of records."
