#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:74
msgid ""
"Relational fields call a field from another model. They allow you to link"
" models together and make them interact easily. In other words, when you "
"use a relational field, you link a record with another one (located on "
"another model), enabling you to retrieve the content of the fields "
"located on this linked record."
msgstr ""
"Relatsion maydonlar boshqa modeldan maydonni chaqiradi. Ular modellarni "
"bir-biriga bog'lash va osongina o'zaro ta'sir qilish imkonini beradi. "
"Boshqacha qilib aytganda, relatsion maydondan foydalanganda, siz yozuvni "
"boshqa yozuv (boshqa modelda joylashgan) bilan bog'laysiz, bu esa "
"bog'langan yozuvdagi maydonlar tarkibini olish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:79
msgid ""
"**Many2one** fields are filled in by choosing one record from a list of "
"records on another model (from *many* records, you select *one*). For "
"example, the *customer* field on a quotation makes you choose one "
"customer from a list of several customers on the *contact* model."
msgstr ""
"**Many2one** maydonlari boshqa modeldagi yozuvlar ro'yxatidan bitta yozuvni "
"tanlash orqali to'ldiriladi (*ko'p* yozuvdan *birini* tanlaysiz). Masalan, "
"tijorat taklifidagi *mijoz* maydoni *kontakt* modelidagi bir nechta "
"mijozlar ro'yxatidan bitta mijozni tanlashga majbur qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:82
msgid ""
"**One2many** fields are reverse searches of existing many2one relations. "
"For example, you could list on a contact all their existing quotations "
"(from *one* record, you display *many*)."
msgstr ""
"**One2many** maydonlari mavjud many2one munosabatlarining teskari "
"qidiruvlaridir. Masalan, kontaktda uning barcha mavjud tijorat takliflari "
"ro'yxatini ko'rsatishingiz mumkin (*bir* yozuvdan *ko'pini* ko'rsatasiz)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:84
msgid ""
"**Many2many** fields are filled in by choosing one or several records "
"from a list of records on another model. For example, you can put several"
" tags on one product, and several products can use the same tags (from "
"*many* records, you can select *many*)."
msgstr ""
"**Many2many** maydonlari boshqa modeldagi yozuvlar ro'yxatidan bir yoki "
"bir nechta yozuvni tanlash orqali to'ldiriladi. Masalan, bitta mahsulotga "
"bir nechta teglar qo'yishingiz mumkin va bir nechta mahsulotlar bir xil "
"teglarni ishlatishi mumkin (*ko'p* yozuvdan *ko'pini* tanlashingiz mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:93
msgid ""
"Views define how records should be displayed to end-users. They are "
"specified in XML, meaning they can be edited independently from the "
"models they represent. They are flexible and allow deep customization of "
"the screens they control."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishlar yozuvlar foydalanuvchilarga qanday ko'rsatilishi kerakligini "
"belgilaydi. Ular XML da ko'rsatiladi, ya'ni ular ifodalayotgan "
"modellardan mustaqil ravishda tahrirlanishi mumkin. Ular moslashuvchan va "
"boshqarayotgan ekranlarni chuqur sozlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:100
msgid "Backend vs. Frontend"
msgstr "Backend va Frontend"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:102
msgid "**Backend views**: Kanban, List, Form, etc."
msgstr "**Backend ko'rinishlari**: Kanban, Ro'yxat, Forma va boshqalar."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:103
msgid "**Frontend view**: QWeb"
msgstr "**Frontend ko'rinishi**: QWeb"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:108
msgid "Static vs. Dynamic"
msgstr "Statik va Dinamik"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:110
msgid ""
"**Static pages** have stable content, such as the homepage. You can "
"define their URL and set some properties like published, indexed, etc."
msgstr ""
"**Statik sahifalar** bosh sahifa kabi barqaror kontentga ega. Ularning "
"URL manzilini belgilashingiz va nashr qilingan, indekslangan va boshqa "
"xususiyatlarni o'rnatishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:112
msgid ""
"**Dynamic pages** are dynamically generated, such as the product page. "
"Their URL is dynamic and is accessible to all by default (this can be "
"changed by configuring access rights)."
msgstr ""
"**Dinamik sahifalar** mahsulot sahifasi kabi dinamik ravishda yaratiladi. "
"Ularning URL manzili dinamik bo'lib, standart ravishda hamma uchun "
"ochiqdir (kirish huquqlarini sozlash orqali o'zgartirilishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:118
msgid "Base vs. Inherited vs. Duplicated"
msgstr "Asosiy va Meros olgan va Nusxalangan"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:120
msgid ""
"**Base view:** View natively implemented by Odoo. It is directly derived "
"from their model. A base view should never be altered as it allows "
"updating an Odoo database without overwriting a client's modification."
msgstr ""
"**Asosiy ko'rinish:** Odoo tomonidan mahalliy ravishda amalga oshirilgan "
"ko'rinish. U to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'z modelidan kelib chiqadi. Asosiy "
"ko'rinish hech qachon o'zgartirilmasligi kerak, chunki u mijozning "
"o'zgartirishlarini ustiga yozmasdan Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasini "
"yangilash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:124
msgid ""
"Modifications always take place in either a duplicated or inherited view "
"with some differences:"
msgstr ""
"O'zgartirishlar har doim ba'zi farqlar bilan nusxalangan yoki meros "
"olgan ko'rinishda amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:126
msgid ""
"**Inherited view** always has an `inherit_id` and applies modifications "
"based on the source code of the base view it inherits from."
msgstr ""
"**Meros olgan ko'rinish** har doim `inherit_id` ga ega va meros olayotgan "
"asosiy ko'rinishning manba kodiga asoslanib o'zgartirishlar qo'llaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/setup.rst:128
msgid ""
"**Duplicated view** is a duplication from another one. Most of the time "
"this kind of view is created by Odoo when the end-user applies "
"modifications through the Website Builder. This mechanism prevents data "
"loss when the module is updated because only the source view will be "
"updated, not the duplicated one. If a duplicated view exists, both the "
"original view and the duplicated one are visible in the list but only the"
" duplicated one has an `external_id` (an `external_id` set means that the"
" view has been created by the source code of a module)."
msgstr ""
"**Nusxalangan ko'rinish** boshqa ko'rinishning nusxasidir. Ko'pincha bunday "
"ko'rinish foydalanuvchi Website Builder orqali o'zgartirish kiritganda "
"Odoo tomonidan yaratiladi. Bu mexanizm modul yangilanganda ma'lumotlar "
"yo'qolishini oldini oladi, chunki faqat manba ko'rinish yangilanadi, "
"nusxalangan emas. Nusxalangan ko'rinish mavjud bo'lsa, ro'yxatda ham "
"asl ko'rinish ham nusxalangan ko'rinish ko'rinadi, lekin faqat "
"nusxalanganning `external_id` si bor (`external_id` o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, "
"ko'rinish modul manba kodi tomonidan yaratilganligini bildiradi)."

