"sezilsa, ularni ham qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:161
msgid ""
"Odoo version and major number are mandatory. However, patch number is "
"optional. If you want to specify the required version of Odoo to run your"
" module, you should use a five arguments structure, using the first two "
"arguments to indicate your current Odoo version (`* = 19.0`)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo versiyasi va asosiy raqam majburiy. Biroq, yamoq raqami ixtiyoriy. "
"Agar modulingizni ishga tushirish uchun Odoo ning talab qilinadigan "
"versiyasini ko'rsatmoqchi bo'lsangiz, joriy Odoo versiyangizni ko'rsatish "
"uchun dastlabki ikkita argumentdan foydalangan holda beshta argument "
"strukturasidan foydalanishingiz kerak (`* = 19.0`)."

msgid "Module versioning"
msgstr "Modul versiyalash"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:169
msgid ""
"Example: `19.0.1.0.0` "
"`odoo_major.odoo_minor.module_major.module_minor.module_patch`"
msgstr ""
"Misol: `19.0.1.0.0` "
"`odoo_major.odoo_minor.module_major.module_minor.module_patch`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:174
msgid ""
"Automated file inclusion using wildcard notations `(ex.: "
"/myfolder/*.scss)` doesn't work in Odoo SaaS databases. In this case, "
"include each file manually in the manifest."
msgstr ""
"Wildcard yozuvlaridan foydalangan holda avtomatlashtirilgan fayl qo'shish "
"`(ex.: /myfolder/*.scss)` Odoo SaaS ma'lumotlar bazalarida ishlamaydi. "
"Bunday holda, har bir faylni manifestda qo'lda qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:180
msgid "Default options"
msgstr "Standart variantlar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:182
msgid ""
"First, try to construct your theme by using Odoo's default options. This "
"ensures two things:"
msgstr ""
"Avvalo, Odoo ning standart variantlaridan foydalanib mavzungizni qurishga "
"harakat qiling. Bu ikki narsani ta'minlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:184
msgid ""
"You do not re-invent something which already exists. For example, as Odoo"
" provides an option to add a border on the footer, you shouldn't recode "
"it yourself. Instead, enable the default option first, then extend it if "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Allaqachon mavjud narsani qayta ixtiro qilmaysiz. Masalan, Odoo footerga "
"chegara qo'shish variantini taqdim etganligi sababli, siz uni o'zingiz "
"qayta kodlamasligingiz kerak. Buning o'rniga, avval standart variantni "
"yoqing, keyin kerak bo'lsa kengaytiring."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:187
msgid ""
"The user can still use all of Odoo's features with your theme. For "
"example, if you recode the border on the footer, you may break the "
"default option or make it useless, giving the user a bad experience. "
"Also, your recode might not work as well as the default option, as other "
"Odoo features may rely on it."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi mavzungiz bilan Odoo ning barcha xususiyatlaridan "
"foydalanishi mumkin. Masalan, footer chegara kodini qayta yozsangiz, "
"standart variantni buzishingiz yoki uni foydasiz qilishingiz mumkin, bu "
"foydalanuvchiga yomon tajriba beradi. Shuningdek, qayta kodlangan versiya "
"standart variant kabi yaxshi ishlamasligi mumkin, chunki boshqa Odoo "
"xususiyatlari unga tayanganligi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:193
msgid "Use four spaces per indentation level."
msgstr "Har bir chekinish darajasi uchun to'rt bo'sh joy ishlating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:194
msgid "Do not use tabs."
msgstr "Tab ishlatmang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:195
msgid "Never mix spaces and tabs."
msgstr "Hech qachon bo'sh joylar va tablarni aralashtirib yubormang."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:198
msgid ""
":doc:`Odoo coding guidelines "
"<../../../contributing/development/coding_guidelines>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Odoo kodlash ko'rsatmalari "
"<../../../contributing/development/coding_guidelines>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:203
msgid "Odoo variables"
msgstr "Odoo o'zgaruvchilari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:205
msgid ""
"Odoo declares many CSS rules, most entirely customizable by overriding "
"the related SCSS variables. To do so, create a "
":file:`primary_variables.scss` file and add it to the "
"`_assets_primary_variables` bundle."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ko'plab CSS qoidalarini e'lon qiladi, ularning aksariyati tegishli "
"SCSS o'zgaruvchilarini bekor qilish orqali to'liq moslashtirilishi mumkin. "
"Buning uchun :file:`primary_variables.scss` fayl yarating va uni "
"`_assets_primary_variables` to'plamiga qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:220
msgid ""
"By reading the source code, variables related to options are easily "
"noticeable."
msgstr ""
"Manba kodini o'qish orqali variantlarga bog'liq o'zgaruvchilarni osongina "
"sezish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:241
msgid ""
"These variables can be overridden through the `$o-website-value-palettes`"
" map, for example."
msgstr ""
"Bu o'zgaruvchilar, masalan, `$o-website-value-palettes` xaritalash orqali "
"bekor qilinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:246
msgid "Global"
msgstr "Global"

