#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:564
msgid ""
"That file must only contain definitions and overrides of SCSS variables "
"and mixins."
msgstr ""
"Bu fayl faqat SCSS o'zgaruvchilari va mikslarining ta'riflari va bekor "
"qilishlarini o'z ichiga olishi kerak."

