#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:444
msgid "**Color combinations**"
msgstr "**Rang kombinatsiyalari**"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:446
msgid ""
"Based on the previously defined five color palettes, the Website Builder "
"automatically generates five color combinations, each defining a color "
"for the background, text, headings, links, primary buttons, and secondary"
" buttons. These colors can be customized later by the user."
msgstr ""
"Avval belgilangan besh rang palitrasiga asoslanib, Website Builder avtomatik "
"ravishda fon, matn, sarlavhalar, havolalar, asosiy tugmalar va ikkilamchi "
"tugmalar uchun rang belgilaydigan besh rang kombinatsiyasini yaratadi. "
"Bu ranglarni keyinchalik foydalanuvchi moslashtirishishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:454
msgid ""
"The colors used in a color combination are accessible and can be "
"overridden through `$o-color-palettes` using a specific prefix (`o-cc` "
"for `color combination`)."
msgstr ""
"Rang kombinatsiyasida ishlatiladigan ranglar mavjud va maxsus prefiks "
"(`color combination` uchun `o-cc`) yordamida `$o-color-palettes` orqali "
"bekor qilinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:483
msgid ""
"For each `o-cc*`, replace the `*` with the digit (1 - 5) corresponding to"
" the desired color combination."
msgstr ""
"Har bir `o-cc*` uchun `*` ni kerakli rang kombinatsiyasiga mos keladigan "
"raqam (1 - 5) bilan almashtiring."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:486
msgid ""
"The default text color is `o-color-5`. If the background is too dark, it "
"will automatically change to the `o-color-4` color."
msgstr ""
"Standart matn rangi `o-color-5` dir. Agar fon juda qorong'i bo'lsa, u "
"avtomatik ravishda `o-color-4` rangiga o'tadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:490
msgid ""
"`Color combinations SCSS "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/944d7c8d5d6bf97cba71644b615e081e4fff6595/addons/html_editor/static/src/scss/html_editor.common.scss#L16>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Rang kombinatsiyalari SCSS "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/944d7c8d5d6bf97cba71644b615e081e4fff6595/addons/html_editor/static/src/scss/html_editor.common.scss#L16>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:495
msgid ""
"The Website Builder automatically generates a page to view the color "
"combinations of the theme color palette: "
"http://localhost:8069/website/demo/color-combinations"
msgstr ""
"Website Builder mavzu rang palitrasining rang kombinatsiyalarini ko'rish "
"uchun avtomatik sahifa yaratadi: "
"http://localhost:8069/website/demo/color-combinations"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:503
msgid ""
"You can also define gradients for the menu, header, footer and copyright "
"bar, directly in your `primary_variables.scss` file."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri `primary_variables.scss` faylingizda "
"menyu, sarlavha, footer va mualliflik huquqi paneli uchun gradientlarni "
"belgilashingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:523
msgid "Bootstrap variables"
msgstr "Bootstrap o'zgaruvchilari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:525
msgid ""
"Odoo includes Bootstrap by default. You can use all variables and mixins "
"of the framework."
msgstr ""
"Odoo standart holda Bootstrap ni o'z ichiga oladi. Framework ning barcha "
"o'zgaruvchilari va mikslaridan foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:527
msgid ""
"If Odoo does not provide the variable you are looking for, there could be"
" a Bootstrap variable that allows it. Indeed all Odoo layouts respect "
"Bootstrap structures and use Bootstrap components or their extensions. If"
" you customize a Bootstrap variable, you add a generic style for the "
"whole user website."
msgstr ""
"Agar Odoo siz qidirayotgan o'zgaruvchini taqdim etmasa, buni amalga "
"oshiruvchi Bootstrap o'zgaruvchisi bo'lishi mumkin. Darhaqiqat, barcha "
"Odoo tartiblari Bootstrap tuzilmalarini hurmat qiladi va Bootstrap "
"komponentlari yoki ularning kengaytmalaridan foydalanadi. Bootstrap "
"o'zgaruvchisini moslashtirsangiz, butun foydalanuvchi veb-sayti uchun "
"umumiy uslub qo'shasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:532
msgid ""
"Use a dedicated file added to the :file:`_assets_frontend_helpers` bundle"
" to override Bootstrap values and *not* the "
":file:`primary_variables.scss` file."
msgstr ""
"Bootstrap qiymatlarini bekor qilish uchun :file:`_assets_frontend_helpers` "
"to'plamiga qo'shilgan maxsus fayldan foydalaning, :file:`primary_variables.scss` "
"faylidan *emas*."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:548
msgid "``/website_airproof/static/src/scss/bootstrap_overridden.scss``"
msgstr "``/website_airproof/static/src/scss/bootstrap_overridden.scss``"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:567
msgid ""
"Don't override Bootstrap variables that depend on Odoo variables. "
"Otherwise, you might break the possibility for the user to customize them"
" using the Website Builder."
msgstr ""
"Odoo o'zgaruvchilariga bog'liq Bootstrap o'zgaruvchilarini bekor "
"qilmang. Aks holda, foydalanuvchining Website Builder yordamida ularni "
"moslashtirishini buzishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:570
msgid ""
"When an option is defined by a variable in `primary_variables.scss` and "
"by a Boostrap variable, you should always go for an override through the "
"primary variables. Do it via `bootstrap_overridden.scss` only if nothing "
"exists in the primary variables."
msgstr ""
"Variant `primary_variables.scss` dagi o'zgaruvchi va Bootstrap o'zgaruvchisi "
"bilan belgilangan bo'lsa, har doim asosiy o'zgaruvchilar orqali bekor qilish "
"yo'lini tanlashingiz kerak. Faqat asosiy o'zgaruvchilarda hech narsa "
"mavjud bo'lmasa, buni `bootstrap_overridden.scss` orqali bajaring."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:575
msgid ""
"`Bootstrap overridden SCSS "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/lib/bootstrap/scss/_variables.scss>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Bootstrap bekor qilish SCSS "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/lib/bootstrap/scss/_variables.scss>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:580
msgid "http://localhost:8069/website/demo/bootstrap"
msgstr "http://localhost:8069/website/demo/bootstrap"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:587
msgid ""
"Odoo has CSS font size classes to separate style (font sizes) and "
"semantic (tag and styles in general). Both logic can be combined to be "
"more flexible."
msgstr ""
"Odoo uslub (shrift o'lchamlari) va semantikani (umumiy teg va uslublar) "
"ajratish uchun CSS shrift o'lcham klasslariga ega. Ikki mantiq ham "
"moslashuvchanroq bo'lishi uchun birlashtirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:591
msgid ""
"`Bootstrap documentation about display headings "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/content/typography/#display-"
"headings>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Ko'rsatish sarlavhalari haqida Bootstrap hujjatlari "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/content/typography/#display-"
