#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:597
msgid "Text style"
msgstr "Matn uslubi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:599
msgid ""
"Odoo's Website Builder allows to select a style for your text. Some are "
"just tag related like the `Header` with no extra CSS class. Other combine"
" tag and style directly applied on them like the `Header 1 Display`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ning Website Builder matniz uchun uslub tanlash imkonini beradi. "
"Ba'zilari qo'shimcha CSS klasisiz faqat teg bilan bog'liq, masalan "
"`Sarlavha`. Boshqalari `1-sarlavha Ko'rsatish` kabi ularga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"qo'llaniladigan teg va uslubni birlashtiradi."

