msgstr "O'lcham klasslari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:626
msgid ""
"The sizing classes are added on a freshly created `span` tag inside the "
"targeted element (See examples below)."
msgstr ""
"O'lcham klasslari maqsadli element ichidagi yangi yaratilgan `span` tegiga "
"qo'shiladi (quyidagi misollarga qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:636
msgid "Heading and body text"
msgstr "Sarlavha va asosiy matn"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:638
msgid ""
"Assuming these classes can be applied on any text element, take `h2` as "
"an example below:"
msgstr ""
"Bu klasslar istalgan matn elementiga qo'llanilishi mumkinligini hisobga "
"olib, quyida `h2` ni misol sifatida ko'rib chiqing:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:661
msgid "Display headings"
msgstr "Ko'rsatish sarlavhalari"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:663
msgid ""
"If larger titles are needed, Odoo uses Bootstrap's Display Headings "
"classes, from `display-1` to `6`."
msgstr ""
"Kattaroq sarlavhalar kerak bo'lsa, Odoo Bootstrap ning `display-1` dan `6` "
"gacha bo'lgan Ko'rsatish Sarlavhalari klasslaridan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:673
msgid ""
"The Website Builder allows the user to configure only sizes from `Display"
