#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:887
msgid "Styles"
msgstr "Uslublar"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:889
msgid ""
"The Website Builder together with Bootstrap are great for defining the "
"basic styles of your website. But to design something unique, you should "
"go a step further. For this, you can easily add any SCSS file to your "
"theme."
msgstr ""
"Website Builder va Bootstrap veb-saytingizning asosiy uslublarini belgilash "
"uchun ajoyib. Ammo noyob narsa yaratish uchun bir qadam olg'a borish kerak. "
"Buning uchun mavzungizga osongina istalgan SCSS faylini qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:904
msgid ""
"Feel free to reuse the variables from your Bootstrap file and the ones "
"used by Odoo in your :file:`theme.scss` file."
msgstr ""
":file:`theme.scss` faylingizda Bootstrap faylingiz va Odoo tomonidan "
