msgstr "``/website_airproof/static/src/scss/theme.scss``"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:920
msgid "Interactivity"
msgstr "Interaktivlik"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:922
msgid "Odoo supports three different kinds of JavaScript files:"
msgstr "Odoo uch xil JavaScript fayllarini qo'llaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:924
msgid ""
":ref:`plain JavaScript files <frontend/modules/plain_js>` (no module "
"system),"
msgstr ""
":ref:`oddiy JavaScript fayllari <frontend/modules/plain_js>` (modul tizimisiz),"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:925
msgid ":ref:`native JavaScript module <frontend/modules/native_js>`, and"
msgstr ":ref:`mahalliy JavaScript moduli <frontend/modules/native_js>`, va"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:926
msgid ""
":ref:`Odoo modules <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` (using a custom module"
" system)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odoo modullari <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` (maxsus modul tizimidan foydalanib)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:928
msgid ""
"Most new Odoo JavaScript codes should use the native JavaScript module "
"system. It's simpler and brings the benefit of a better developer "
"experience with better integration with the IDE."
msgstr ""
"Yangi Odoo JavaScript kodlarining aksariyati mahalliy JavaScript modul "
"tizimidan foydalanishi kerak. U sodda va IDE bilan yaxshiroq integratsiya "
"orqali yaxshiroq dasturchi tajribasini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:943
msgid ""
"If you want to include files from an external library, you can add them "
"to the :file:`/lib` folder of your module."
msgstr ""
"Agar tashqi kutubxonadan fayllarni qo'shmoqchi bo'lsangiz, ularni "
"modulingizning :file:`/lib` papkasiga qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:947
msgid ""
"Use a linter (`ESLint "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/tooling/_eslintrc.json>`_,"
" ...)."
msgstr ""
"Linter ishlating (`ESLint "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/tooling/_eslintrc.json>`_,"
" ...)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:948
msgid "Always add minified JavaScript libraries"
msgstr "Har doim minifikatsiya qilingan JavaScript kutubxonalarini qo'shing"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:949
msgid "Use `js_` prefixed CSS classes on elements you target with JavaScript."
msgstr "JavaScript bilan maqsadlaydigan elementlarda `js_` prefiksi bilan boshlanadigan CSS klasslarini ishlating."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:950
msgid ""
"Variables and functions should be *camelCased* (`myVariable`) instead of "
"*snake_cased* (`my_variable`)."
msgstr ""
"O'zgaruvchilar va funksiyalar *snake_cased* (`my_variable`) o'rniga "
"*camelCased* (`myVariable`) bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:952
msgid "JavaScript classes use *PascalCase* (`MyClass`)."
msgstr "JavaScript klasslari *PascalCase* (`MyClass`) dan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:953
msgid ""
"Do not name a variable `event`; use `ev` instead. This is to avoid bugs "
"on non-Chrome browsers, as Chrome is magically assigning a global `event`"
" variable (so if you use the `event` variable without declaring it, it "
"will work fine on Chrome but crash on every other browser)."
msgstr ""
"O'zgaruvchini `event` deb atamang; buning o'rniga `ev` dan foydalaning. "
"Bu Chrome bo'lmagan brauzerlarda xatolardan qochish uchun, chunki Chrome "
"sehrli ravishda global `event` o'zgaruvchisini belgilaydi (shuning uchun "
"`event` o'zgaruvchisini e'lon qilmasdan ishlatsangiz, Chrome da yaxshi "
"ishlaydi, lekin boshqa har qanday brauzerda ishdan chiqadi)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:957
msgid "Use strict comparisons (`===` instead of `==`)."
msgstr "Qattiq taqqoslashlardan foydalaning (`==` o'rniga `===`)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:958
msgid ""
"Use double quotes for all strings (such as `\"Hello\"`, "
"`\".x_nav_item\"`)."
msgstr ""
"Barcha satrlar uchun qo'sh tirnoqdan foydalaning (masalan, `\"Hello\"`, "
"`\".x_nav_item\"`)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:959
msgid ""
"If you're using native standard JS functions (`start()`, `willStart()`, "
"`cleanForSave()`, etc), make sure you call the parent implementation (for"
" example, `super.start(...arguments)`; check if it's necessary in the "
"standard code)."
msgstr ""
"Agar mahalliy standart JS funksiyalaridan (`start()`, `willStart()`, "
"`cleanForSave()` va boshqalar) foydalanayotgan bo'lsangiz, ota amalga "
"oshirilishini chaqirishingizga ishonch hosil qiling (masalan, "
"`super.start(...arguments)`; standart kodda bu zarurligini tekshiring)."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:964
msgid ""
"`Odoo JavaScript coding guidelines <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/wiki"
"/Javascript-coding-guidelines>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo JavaScript kodlash ko'rsatmalari <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/wiki"
"/Javascript-coding-guidelines>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:965
msgid ""
":doc:`Overview of the Odoo JavaScript framework "
"<../../reference/frontend/javascript_reference>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Odoo JavaScript frameworkiga umumiy ko'rinish "
"<../../reference/frontend/javascript_reference>`"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/theming.rst:967
msgid ""
"`Odoo Experience Talk: Best practices to use the Website Builder like a "
"professional designer "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPy5GqmUbc&ab_channel=Odoo>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo Experience Talk: Website Builderdan professional dizayner sifatida "
"foydalanishning eng yaxshi amaliyotlari "
"<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YPy5GqmUbc&ab_channel=Odoo>`_"

