msgstr "Frontend"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/translations.rst:18
msgid ""
"To translate your pages with the Website Builder, go to your website and "
"click on the language selector to switch to it. If your website was never"
" translated to the target language, click :guilabel:`Add a language...`, "
"select it in the pop-up window, and click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Website Builder yordamida sahifalaringizni tarjima qilish uchun "
"veb-saytingizga o'ting va til tanlagichni bosib unga o'ting. Agar "
"veb-saytingiz hech qachon maqsadli tilga tarjima qilinmagan bo'lsa, "
":guilabel:`Til qo'shish...` ni bosing, ochilish oynasida uni tanlang va "
":guilabel:`Qo'shish` ni bosing."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/translations.rst:22
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Translate` to start translating. Depending on the "
"language, some text is automatically translated and highlighted in green,"
" while everything that should be translated manually is highlighted in "
"yellow."
msgstr ""
"Tarjima qilishni boshlash uchun :guilabel:`Tarjima` ni bosing. Tilga qarab, "
"ba'zi matnlar avtomatik tarjima qilinadi va yashil rangda ajratib ko'rsatiladi, "
"qo'lda tarjima qilinishi kerak bo'lgan hamma narsa esa sariq rangda "
"ajratib ko'rsatiladi."

msgid "Translate button"
msgstr "Tarjima tugmasi"

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/translations.rst:29
msgid ""
"However, you have to understand what's happening under the hood when you "
"translate something through the Website Builder."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, Website Builder orqali biror narsani tarjima qilayotganingizda "
"nima sodir bo'layotganini tushunishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/howtos/website_themes/translations.rst:37
msgid ""
"Odoo creates a base view once the Website is installed. If you edit the "
"page with the Builder, a duplicated view will be created and all your "
"modifications will be saved into this one (and your translations also). "
"The only exception concerns the homepage (by default, Odoo creates a base"
