msgstr "Bir vaqtda bir nechta harakatlarni bajarayotganda harakatning ustunligi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:448
msgid "Writing cron functions"
msgstr "Cron funksiyalarini yozish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:450
msgid ""
"When running a scheduled action, it's recommended that you try to batch "
"the progress in order to avoid blocking a worker for a long period of "
"time and possibly run into timeout exceptions. Therefore, you should "
"split the processing so that each call makes progress on some of the work"
" to be done."
msgstr ""
"Rejalashtirilgan harakatni bajarayotganda, ishchini uzoq vaqt bloklash va "
"muddati o'tish istisnolariga duch kelmaslik uchun rivojlanishni to'plamlarga "
"ajratishga harakat qilish tavsiya etiladi. Shuning uchun, har bir chaqiruv "
"bajarilishi kerak bo'lgan ba'zi ishlarni oldinga siljitadigan tarzda "
"qayta ishlashni bo'lishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:455
msgid ""
"When writing such a function, you should focus on processing a single "
"batch. A batch should process one or many records and should generally "
"take no more than *a few seconds*."
msgstr ""
"Bunday funksiyani yozayotganda, bitta to'plamni qayta ishlashga e'tibor "
"qaratishingiz kerak. To'plam bir yoki bir nechta yozuvlarni qayta ishlashi "
"va odatda *bir necha sekunddan* ko'p bo'lmasligi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:459
msgid ""
"Work is committed by the framework after each batch. The framework will "
"call the function as many times as necessary to process the remaining "
"work. Do not reschedule yourself the job."
msgstr ""
"Ish framework tomonidan har bir to'plamdan keyin bajariladi. Framework qolgan "
"ishni qayta ishlash uchun zarur bo'lgan marta funksiyani chaqiradi. "
"Ishni o'zingiz qayta rejalashtirmang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:475
msgid ""
"In some cases, you may want to share resources between multiple batches "
"or manage the loop yourself to handle exceptions. In this case, you "
"should inform the scheduler of the progress of your work by calling "
":func:`IrCron._commit_progress` and checking the result. The progress "
"function returns the number of seconds remaining for the call; if it is "
"0, you must return as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi hollarda, bir nechta to'plamlar o'rtasida resurslarni almashish yoki "
"istisnolarni hal qilish uchun siklni o'zingiz boshqarishni xohlashingiz mumkin. "
"Bu holda, :func:`IrCron._commit_progress` ni chaqirish va natijani tekshirish "
"orqali rejalashtiruvchini ishingizning rivojlanishi haqida xabardor qilishingiz kerak. "
"Rivojlanish funksiyasi chaqiruv uchun qolgan soniyalar sonini qaytaradi; "
"agar u 0 bo'lsa, imkon qadar tezroq qaytishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:482
msgid ""
"The following is an example of how to commit after each record that is "
"processed, while keeping the connection open."
msgstr ""
"Quyida ulanishni ochiq saqlagan holda qayta ishlangan har bir yozuvdan keyin "
"tasdiqlash misoli keltirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:515
msgid "Running cron functions"
msgstr "Cron funksiyalarini ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:517
msgid ""
"You should not call cron functions directly. There are two ways to run "
"functions:"
msgstr ""
"Cron funksiyalarini to'g'ridan-to'g'ri chaqirmasligingiz kerak. Funksiyalarni "
"ishga tushirishning ikki yo'li mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:523
msgid ""
"Testing of a cron function should be done by calling "
":func:`IrCron.method_direct_trigger` in the registry test mode."
msgstr ""
"Cron funksiyasini sinovdan o'tkazish ro'yxatga olish sinov rejimida "
":func:`IrCron.method_direct_trigger` ni chaqirish orqali amalga oshirilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:527
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1063
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:276
msgid "Security"
msgstr "Xavfsizlik"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:529
msgid ""
"To avoid a fair usage of resources among scheduled actions, some security"
" measures ensure the correct functioning of your scheduled actions."
msgstr ""
"Rejalashtirilgan harakatlar o'rtasida resurslardan adolatli foydalanishni "
"ta'minlash uchun ba'zi xavfsizlik choralari rejalashtirilgan harakatlaringizning "
"to'g'ri ishlashini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:532
msgid ""
"If a scheduled action encounters an error or a timeout three consecutive "
"times, it will skip its current execution and be considered as failed."
msgstr ""
"Agar rejalashtirilgan harakat ketma-ket uch marta xatoga yoki muddati o'tishga "
"duch kelsa, u joriy bajarilishini o'tkazib yuboradi va muvaffaqiyatsiz deb hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:534
msgid ""
"If a scheduled action fails its execution five consecutive times over a "
"period of at least seven days, it will be deactivated and will notify the"
" DB admin."
msgstr ""
"Agar rejalashtirilgan harakat kamida yetti kun davomida ketma-ket besh marta "
"bajarilishida muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lsa, u o'chiriladi va DB administratorini xabardor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/actions.rst:536
msgid ""
"A hard-limit exists for the cron execution at the database level after "
"which the process executing cron jobs is killed."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasi darajasida cron bajarilishi uchun qattiq chegara mavjud bo'lib, "
"undan so'ng cron ishlarini bajarayotgan jarayon o'ldiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:6
msgid "Data Files"
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar fayllari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo is greatly data-driven, and a big part of modules definition is thus"
" the definition of the various records it manages: UI (menus and views), "
"security (access rights and record rules), reports and plain data are all"
" defined via records."
msgstr ""
"Odoo asosan ma'lumotlarga asoslangan va shuning uchun modullar ta'rifining katta "
"qismi u boshqaradigan turli yozuvlarning ta'rifi hisoblanadi: UI (menyular va "
"ko'rinishlar), xavfsizlik (kirish huquqlari va yozuv qoidalari), hisobotlar va "
"oddiy ma'lumotlar hammasini yozuvlar orqali aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:16
msgid ""
"The main way to define data in Odoo is via XML data files: The broad "
"structure of an XML data file is the following:"
msgstr ""
"Odooda ma'lumotlarni aniqlashning asosiy usuli XML ma'lumotlar fayllari orqali: "
"XML ma'lumotlar faylining umumiy tuzilishi quyidagicha:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:19
msgid "Any number of operation elements within the root element ``odoo``"
msgstr "``odoo`` ildiz elementida ixtiyoriy miqdordagi operatsiya elementlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:30
msgid ""
"Data files are executed sequentially, operations can only refer to the "
"result of operations defined previously"
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar fayllari ketma-ket bajariladi, operatsiyalar faqat avval "
"aniqlangan operatsiyalar natijasiga murojaat qilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:35
msgid ""
"If the content of the data file is expected to be applied only once, you "
"can specify the odoo flag ``noupdate`` set to 1.  If part of the data in "
"the file is expected to be applied once, you can place this part of the "
"file in a <data noupdate=\"1\"> domain."
msgstr ""
"Agar ma'lumotlar faylining mazmuni faqat bir marta qo'llanilishi kutilsa, "
"odoo ``noupdate`` bayrog'ini 1 ga o'rnatib ko'rsatishingiz mumkin. Agar fayldagi "
"ma'lumotlarning bir qismi bir marta qo'llanilishi kutilsa, faylning ushbu qismini "
"<data noupdate=\"1\"> domeniga joylashtirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:53
msgid "Core operations"
msgstr "Asosiy operatsiyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:58
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3580
msgid "``record``"
msgstr "``record``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:60
msgid ""
"``record`` appropriately defines or updates a database record, it has the"
" following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"``record`` ma'lumotlar bazasi yozuvini tegishli tarzda aniqlaydi yoki yangilaydi, "
"u quyidagi atributlarga ega:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:63
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:153
msgid "``model`` (required)"
msgstr "``model`` (majburiy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:64
msgid "name of the model to create (or update)"
msgstr "yaratish (yoki yangilash) kerak bo'lgan modelning nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:66
msgid ""
"the :term:`external identifier` for this record. It is strongly "
"recommended to provide one"
msgstr ""
"ushbu yozuv uchun :term:`external identifier`. Uni ko'rsatish qat'iyan tavsiya etiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:69
msgid ""
"for record creation, allows subsequent definitions to either modify or "
"refer to this record"
msgstr ""
"yozuv yaratish uchun, keyingi ta'riflarga ushbu yozuvni o'zgartirish yoki "
"unga murojaat qilish imkonini beradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:71
msgid "for record modification, the record to modify"
msgstr "yozuvni o'zgartirish uchun, o'zgartiriladigan yozuv"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:72
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:853
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3012
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:936
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1704
msgid "``context``"
msgstr "``context``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:73
msgid "context to use when creating the record"
msgstr "yozuv yaratishda foydalaniladigan kontekst"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:77
msgid "``forcecreate``"
msgstr "``forcecreate``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:75
msgid "in update mode whether the record should be created if it doesn't exist"
msgstr "yangilash rejimida yozuv mavjud bo'lmasa yaratilishi kerakmi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:77
msgid "Requires an :term:`external id`, defaults to ``True``."
msgstr ":term:`external id` talab qiladi, sukut bo'yicha ``True``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:80
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3560
msgid "``field``"
msgstr "``field``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:82
msgid ""
"Each record can be composed of ``field`` tags, defining values to set "
"when creating the record. A ``record`` with no ``field`` will use all "
"default values (creation) or do nothing (update)."
msgstr ""
"Har bir yozuv ``field`` teglaridan tashkil topishi mumkin, yozuv yaratishda "
"o'rnatiladigan qiymatlarni aniqlaydi. ``field`` bo'lmagan ``record`` barcha "
"standart qiymatlardan foydalanadi (yaratish) yoki hech narsa qilmaydi (yangilash)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:86
msgid ""
"A ``field`` has a mandatory ``name`` attribute, the name of the field to "
"set, and various methods to define the value itself:"
msgstr ""
"``field`` majburiy ``name`` atributiga ega, o'rnatiladigan maydon nomi va "
"qiymatning o'zini aniqlashning turli usullari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:91
msgid "Nothing"
msgstr "Hech narsa"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:90
msgid ""
"if no value is provided for the field, an implicit ``False`` will be set "
"on the field. Can be used to clear a field, or avoid using a default "
"value for the field."
msgstr ""
"agar maydon uchun qiymat ko'rsatilmagan bo'lsa, maydonga yashirin ``False`` "
"o'rnatiladi. Maydonni tozalash yoki maydon uchun standart qiymatdan foydalanishdan "
"qochish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:98
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:159
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:265
msgid "``search``"
msgstr "``search``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:94
msgid ""
"for :ref:`relational fields <reference/fields/relational>`, should be a "
":ref:`domain <reference/orm/domains>` on the field's model."
msgstr ""
":ref:`relational fields <reference/fields/relational>` uchun, maydon modelidagi "
":ref:`domain <reference/orm/domains>` bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:97
msgid ""
"Will evaluate the domain, search the field's model using it and set the "
"search's result as the field's value. Will only use the first result if "
"the field is a :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one`"
msgstr ""
"Domenni baholaydi, undan foydalanib maydon modelini qidiradi va qidiruv natijasini "
"maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatadi. Maydon :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` bo'lsa "
"faqat birinchi natijadan foydalanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:104
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:216
msgid "``ref``"
msgstr "``ref``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:101
msgid ""
"if a ``ref`` attribute is provided, its value must be a valid "
":term:`external id`, which will be looked up and set as the field's "
"value."
msgstr ""
"agar ``ref`` atributi ko'rsatilgan bo'lsa, uning qiymati to'g'ri "
":term:`external id` bo'lishi kerak, bu qidiriladi va maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:104
msgid ""
"Mostly for :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` and "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Reference` fields"
msgstr ""
"Ko'pincha :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` va "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Reference` maydonlari uchun"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:107
msgid ""
"if a ``type`` attribute is provided, it is used to interpret and convert "
"the field's content. The field's content can be provided through an "
"external file using the ``file`` attribute, or through the node's body."
msgstr ""
"agar ``type`` atributi ko'rsatilgan bo'lsa, u maydon mazmunini talqin qilish va "
"konvertatsiya qilish uchun ishlatiladi. Maydon mazmuni ``file`` atributi yordamida "
"tashqi fayl orqali yoki tugun tanasi orqali ko'rsatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:111
msgid "Available types are:"
msgstr "Mavjud turlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:115
msgid "``xml``, ``html``"
msgstr "``xml``, ``html``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:114
#, python-format
msgid ""
"extracts the ``field``'s children as a single document, evaluates any "
":term:`external id` specified with the form ``%(external_id)s``. ``%%`` "
"can be used to output actual *%* signs."
msgstr ""
"``field`` ning bolalarini bitta hujjat sifatida chiqaradi, ``%(external_id)s`` "
"shakli bilan ko'rsatilgan har qanday :term:`external id` ni baholaydi. ``%%`` "
"haqiqiy *%* belgilarini chiqarish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:118
msgid "``file``"
msgstr "``file``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:118
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"ensures that the field content is a valid file path in the current model,"
" saves the pair :samp:`{module},{path}` as the field value"
msgstr ""
"maydon mazmunining joriy modelda to'g'ri fayl yo'li ekanligini ta'minlaydi, "
":samp:`{module},{path}` juftligini maydon qiymati sifatida saqlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:121
msgid "``char``"
msgstr "``char``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:121
msgid "sets the field content directly as the field's value without alterations"
msgstr "maydon mazmunini o'zgartirishsiz to'g'ridan-to'g'ri maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:124
msgid "``base64``"
msgstr "``base64``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:124
msgid ""
"base64_-encodes the field's content, useful combined with the ``file`` "
"*attribute* to load e.g. image data into attachments"
msgstr ""
"maydon mazmunini base64_ bilan kodlaydi, masalan, rasm ma'lumotlarini "
"ilovalar ichiga yuklash uchun ``file`` *atributi* bilan birgalikda foydali"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:127
msgid "``int``"
msgstr "``int``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:127
msgid ""
"converts the field's content to an integer and sets it as the field's "
"value"
msgstr "maydon mazmunini butun songa aylantiradi va uni maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:130
msgid "``float``"
msgstr "``float``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:130
msgid "converts the field's content to a float and sets it as the field's value"
msgstr "maydon mazmunini float ga aylantiradi va uni maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:135
msgid "``list``, ``tuple``"
msgstr "``list``, ``tuple``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:133
msgid ""
"should contain any number of ``value`` elements with the same properties "
"as ``field``, each element resolves to an item of a generated tuple or "
"list, and the generated collection is set as the field's value"
msgstr ""
"``field`` bilan bir xil xususiyatlarga ega ixtiyoriy miqdordagi ``value`` "
"elementlarini o'z ichiga olishi kerak, har bir element yaratilgan tuple yoki "
"ro'yxat elementiga aylanadi va yaratilgan to'plam maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:145
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:246
msgid "``eval``"
msgstr "``eval``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:138
msgid ""
"for cases where the previous methods are unsuitable, the ``eval`` "
"attributes simply evaluates whatever Python expression it is provided and"
" sets the result as the field's value."
msgstr ""
"oldingi usullar mos kelmaydigan holatlarda, ``eval`` atributi berilgan "
"Python ifodasini baholaydi va natijani maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:142
msgid ""
"The evaluation context contains various modules (``time``, ``datetime``, "
"``timedelta``, ``relativedelta``), a function to resolve :term:`external "
"identifiers` (``ref``) and the model object for the current field if "
"applicable (``obj``)"
msgstr ""
"Baholash konteksti turli modullarni (``time``, ``datetime``, ``timedelta``, "
"``relativedelta``), :term:`external identifiers` (``ref``) ni hal qilish "
"funksiyasini va tegishli bo'lsa joriy maydon uchun model ob'ektini (``obj``) o'z ichiga oladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:148
msgid "``delete``"
msgstr "``delete``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:150
msgid ""
"The ``delete`` tag can remove any number of records previously defined. "
"It has the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"``delete`` tegi oldin aniqlangan ixtiyoriy miqdordagi yozuvlarni o'chirishi mumkin. "
"U quyidagi atributlarga ega:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:154
msgid "the model in which a specified record should be deleted"
msgstr "ko'rsatilgan yozuv o'chirilishi kerak bo'lgan model"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:156
msgid "the :term:`external id` of a record to remove"
msgstr "o'chiriladigan yozuvning :term:`external id` si"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:158
msgid ""
"a :ref:`domain <reference/orm/domains>` to find records of the model to "
"remove"
msgstr ""
"o'chiriladigan model yozuvlarini topish uchun :ref:`domain <reference/orm/domains>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:161
msgid "``id`` and ``search`` are exclusive"
msgstr "``id`` va ``search`` o'zaro eksklyuziv"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:164
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:284
msgid "``function``"
msgstr "``function``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:166
msgid ""
"The ``function`` tag calls a method on a model, with provided parameters."
" It has two mandatory parameters ``model`` and ``name`` specifying "
"respectively the model and the name of the method to call."
msgstr ""
"``function`` tegi ko'rsatilgan parametrlar bilan modelda metodini chaqiradi. "
"U ikkita majburiy parametrga ega: ``model`` va ``name`` mos ravishda modelni va "
"chaqiriladigan metod nomini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:170
msgid ""
"Parameters can be provided using ``eval`` (should evaluate to a sequence "
"of parameters to call the method with) or ``value`` elements (see "
"``list`` values)."
msgstr ""
"Parametrlar ``eval`` (metod chaqirilishi kerak bo'lgan parametrlar ketma-ketligiga "
"baholanishi kerak) yoki ``value`` elementlari (``list`` qiymatlariga qarang) "
"yordamida ko'rsatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:200
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Qisqartmalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:202
msgid ""
"Because some important structural models of Odoo are complex and "
"involved, data files provide shorter alternatives to defining them using "
":ref:`record tags <reference/data/record>`:"
msgstr ""
"Odooning ba'zi muhim tuzilmaviy modellari murakkab va ko'p qirrali bo'lganligi "
"sababli, ma'lumotlar fayllari ularni :ref:`record tags <reference/data/record>` "
"yordamida aniqlashning qisqaroq muqobillarini taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:207
msgid "``menuitem``"
msgstr "``menuitem``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:209
msgid "Defines an ``ir.ui.menu`` record with a number of defaults and fallbacks:"
msgstr "Bir qator standartlar va zaxira variantlar bilan ``ir.ui.menu`` yozuvini aniqlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:220
msgid "``parent``"
msgstr "``parent``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:214
msgid ""
"If a ``parent`` attribute is set, it should be the :term:`external id` of"
" an other menu item, used as the new item's parent"
msgstr ""
"Agar ``parent`` atributi o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, u yangi elementning ota-onasi sifatida "
"ishlatiladigan boshqa menyu elementining :term:`external id` si bo'lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:216
msgid ""
"If no ``parent`` is provided, tries to interpret the ``name`` attribute "
"as a ``/``-separated sequence of menu names and find a place in the menu "
"hierarchy. In that interpretation, intermediate menus are automatically "
"created"
msgstr ""
"Agar ``parent`` ko'rsatilmagan bo'lsa, ``name`` atributini ``/`` bilan ajratilgan "
"menyu nomlari ketma-ketligi sifatida talqin qilishga va menyu ierarxiyasida joy "
"topishga harakat qiladi. Ushbu talqinda oraliq menyular avtomatik ravishda yaratiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:220
msgid ""
"Otherwise the menu is defined as a \"top-level\" menu item (*not* a menu "
"with no parent)"
msgstr ""
"Aks holda menyu \"yuqori daraja\" menyu elementi sifatida aniqlanadi "
"(ota-onasi bo'lmagan menyu *emas*)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:223
msgid ""
"If no ``name`` attribute is specified, tries to get the menu name from a "
"linked action if any. Otherwise uses the record's ``id``"
msgstr ""
"Agar ``name`` atributi ko'rsatilmagan bo'lsa, mavjud bo'lsa, bog'langan harakatdan "
"menyu nomini olishga harakat qiladi. Aks holda yozuvning ``id`` sidan foydalanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:228
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:254
#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1291
msgid "``groups``"
msgstr "``groups``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:226
msgid ""
"A ``groups`` attribute is interpreted as a comma-separated sequence of "
":term:`external identifiers` for ``res.groups`` models. If an "
":term:`external identifier` is prefixed with a minus (``-``), the group "
"is *removed* from the menu's groups"
msgstr ""
"``groups`` atributi ``res.groups`` modellari uchun vergul bilan ajratilgan "
":term:`external identifiers` ketma-ketligi sifatida talqin qilinadi. Agar "
":term:`external identifier` minus (``-``) bilan boshlangan bo'lsa, guruh "
"menyu guruhlaridan *o'chiriladi*"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:231
msgid "``action``"
msgstr "``action``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:231
msgid ""
"if specified, the ``action`` attribute should be the :term:`external id` "
"of an action to execute when the menu is open"
msgstr ""
"agar ko’rsatilgan bo’lsa, ``action`` atributi menyu ochilganda bajarish uchun "
"harakatning :term:`external id` si bo’lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:234
msgid "the menu item’s :term:`external id`"
msgstr "menyu elementining :term:`external id` si"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:239
msgid "``template``"
msgstr "``template``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:241
msgid ""
"Creates a :ref:`QWeb view <reference/view_architectures/qweb>` requiring "
"only the ``arch`` section of the view, and allowing a few *optional* "
"attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Faqat ko’rinishning ``arch`` bo’limini talab qiladigan va bir nechta "
"*ixtiyoriy* atributlarga ruxsat beradigan :ref:`QWeb ko’rinishini "
"<reference/view_architectures/qweb>` yaratadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:247
msgid "the view’s :term:`external identifier`"
msgstr "ko’rinishning :term:`external identifier` si"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:249
msgid "``name``, ``inherit_id``, ``priority``"
msgstr "``name``, ``inherit_id``, ``priority``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:249
msgid ""
"same as the corresponding field on ``ir.ui.view`` (nb: ``inherit_id`` "
"should be an :term:`external identifier`)"
msgstr ""
"``ir.ui.view`` dagi tegishli maydon bilan bir xil (eslatma: ``inherit_id`` "
":term:`external identifier` bo’lishi kerak)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:252
msgid "``primary``"
msgstr "``primary``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:252
msgid ""
"if set to ``True`` and combined with a ``inherit_id``, defines the view "
"as a primary"
msgstr ""
"agar ``True`` ga o’rnatilsa va ``inherit_id`` bilan birlashtirsa, "
"ko’rinishni asosiy sifatida aniqlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:255
msgid "comma-separated list of group :term:`external identifiers`"
msgstr "guruh :term:`external identifiers` larining vergul bilan ajratilgan ro’yxati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:265
msgid "``active``"
msgstr "``active``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:257
msgid ""
"indicates whether the view is active. If inactive, its XPath rules won’t "
"be applied, which is thus mainly relevant for views with ``inherit_id``"
msgstr ""
"ko’rinish faolligini bildiradi. Agar faol bo’lmasa, uning XPath qoidalari "
"qo’llanilmaydi, bu asosan ``inherit_id`` ga ega ko’rinishlar uchun tegishli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:262
msgid ""
"Defining the ``active`` value on the ``<template>`` node itself comes "
"with a subtlety: it is only considered when creating the record. On "
"subsequent updates, the view will be updated but not its ``active`` "
"status."
msgstr ""
"``<template>`` tugunining o’zida ``active`` qiymatini aniqlash noziklik bilan "
"keladi: u faqat yozuv yaratishda hisobga olinadi. Keyingi yangilanishlarda "
"ko’rinish yangilanadi, lekin uning ``active`` holati emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:270
msgid "``asset``"
msgstr "``asset``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:272
msgid "Creates an :ref:`asset <frontend/assets/ir_asset>`."
msgstr ":ref:`asset <frontend/assets/ir_asset>` yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:282
msgid "**Attributes**"
msgstr "**Atributlar**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:287
msgid "the asset’s :term:`external identifier`"
msgstr "resursning :term:`external identifier` si"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:289
msgid "same as the corresponding field on ``ir.asset``"
msgstr "``ir.asset`` dagi tegishli maydon bilan bir xil"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:298
msgid "``active`` (optional)"
msgstr "``active`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:291
msgid "indicates whether the asset is active"
msgstr "resurs faolligini bildiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:295
msgid ""
"Same as ``<template>``, defining the ``active`` value on the ``<asset>`` "
"node itself comes with a subtlety: it is only considered when creating "
"the record. On subsequent updates, the asset will be updated but not its "
"``active`` status."
msgstr ""
"``<template>`` singari, ``<asset>`` tugunining o’zida ``active`` qiymatini "
"aniqlash noziklik bilan keladi: u faqat yozuv yaratishda hisobga olinadi. "
"Keyingi yangilanishlarda resurs yangilanadi, lekin uning ``active`` holati emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:300
msgid "**Child elements**"
msgstr "**Bola elementlar**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:307
