msgid ""
"required to define the corresponding fields on ``ir.asset`` (the "
"``directive`` field can be controlled using the ``directive`` attribute "
"on the ``<bundle>`` child)"
msgstr ""
"``ir.asset`` da tegishli maydonlarni aniqlash uchun zarur (``directive`` maydonni "
"``<bundle>`` bolasida ``directive`` atributi yordamida boshqarish mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/data.rst:310
