#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:23
msgid "Basic messaging system"
msgstr "Asosiy xabar almashish tizimi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:25
msgid ""
"Integrating messaging features to your model is extremely easy. Simply "
"inheriting the ``mail.thread`` mixin and adding the chatter "
"``<chatter/>`` element to your form view will get you up and running in "
"no time. The chatter element supports some options to control form "
"behavior:"
msgstr ""
"Xabar almashish xususiyatlarini modelingizga integratsiya qilish juda oson. "
"Shunchaki ``mail.thread`` mixinidan meros olib, forma ko'rinishingizga chatter "
"``<chatter/>`` elementini qo'shsangiz, tezda ishga tushirasiz. Chatter elementi "
"forma xatti-harakatini boshqarish uchun ba'zi variantlarni qo'llab-quvvatlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:30
msgid "``open_attachments``: Shows attachment section expanded by default"
msgstr "``open_attachments``: Sukut bo'yicha ilova bo'limini kengaytirilgan holda ko'rsatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:31
msgid ""
"``reload_on_attachment``: Reloads form view when attachments are "
"added/removed"
msgstr "``reload_on_attachment``: Ilovalar qo'shilganda/o'chirilganda forma ko'rinishini qayta yuklaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:32
msgid "``reload_on_follower``: Reloads form view when followers are updated"
msgstr "``reload_on_follower``: Kuzatuvchilar yangilanganda forma ko'rinishini qayta yuklaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:33
msgid "``reload_on_post``: Reloads form view when new messages are posted"
msgstr "``reload_on_post``: Yangi xabarlar joylashtirilganda forma ko'rinishini qayta yuklaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:37
msgid ""
"Let's create a simplistic model representing a business trip. Since "
"organizing this kind of trip usually involves a lot of people and a lot "
"of discussion, let's add support for message exchange on the model."
msgstr ""
"Keling, ishbilarmon sayohatni ifodalovchi oddiy model yarataylik. Bunday sayohatni "
"tashkil etish odatda ko'p odamlarni va ko'p muhokamalarni o'z ichiga olganligi "
"sababli, modelga xabar almashish imkoniyatini qo'shaylik."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:52
msgid "In the form view:"
msgstr "Forma ko'rinishida:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once you've added chatter support on your model, users can easily add "
"messages or internal notes on any record of your model; every one of "
"those will send a notification (to all followers for messages, to "
"employee (*base.group_user*) users for internal notes). If your mail "
"gateway and catchall address are correctly configured, these "
"notifications will be sent by e-mail and can be replied-to directly from "
"your mail client; the automatic routing system will route the answer to "
"the correct thread."
msgstr ""
"Modelingizga chatter qo'llab-quvvatlashini qo'shganingizdan so'ng, foydalanuvchilar "
"modelingizning istalgan yozuviga osongina xabarlar yoki ichki eslatmalar qo'sha oladi; "
"ularning har biri bildirishnoma yuboradi (xabarlar uchun barcha kuzatuvchilarga, "
"ichki eslatmalar uchun xodim (*base.group_user*) foydalanuvchilariga). Agar pochta "
"shlyuzi va catchall manzili to'g'ri sozlangan bo'lsa, ushbu bildirishnomalar "
"elektron pochta orqali yuboriladi va to'g'ridan-to'g'ri pochta mijozingizdan "
"javob berish mumkin; avtomatik marshrutlash tizimi javobni to'g'ri ipga yo'naltiradi."

