"behavior may be implemented by overriding this method."
msgstr ""
"Standart xatti-harakat tegishli modelning yangi yozuvini yaratishdir (xabardan "
"olingan juda asosiy ma'lumotlarga asoslangan). Ushbu metodini bekor qilish "
"orqali qo'shimcha xatti-harakat amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:136
