#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:202
msgid ""
"The ``mail`` module adds a powerful tracking system on fields, allowing "
"you to log changes to specific fields in the record's chatter. To add "
"tracking to a field, simple set the tracking attribute to True."
msgstr ""
"``mail`` moduli maydonlarda kuchli kuzatish tizimini qo'shadi, bu sizga "
"yozuvning chatteri da muayyan maydonlardagi o'zgarishlarni jurnalga yozishga "
"imkon beradi. Maydonga kuzatishni qo'shish uchun, shunchaki tracking atributini True ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:208
