#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:222
msgid ""
"From now on, every change to a trip's name or responsible will log a note"
" on the record. The ``name`` field will be displayed in the notification "
"as well to give more context about the notification (even if the name did"
" not change)."
msgstr ""
"Bundan buyon, sayohat nomiga yoki mas'uli ga har qanday o'zgarish yozuvga eslatma "
"jurnalga yoziladi. ``name`` maydoni ham bildirishnomaga ko'proq kontekst berish "
"uchun ko'rsatiladi (hatto nom o'zgarmagan bo'lsa ham)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:228
msgid "Subtypes"
msgstr "Pastturlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:230
msgid ""
"Subtypes give you more granular control over messages. Subtypes act as a "
"classification system for notifications, allowing subscribers to a "
"document to customize the subtype of notifications they wish to receive."
msgstr ""
"Pastturlar xabarlarga ko'proq granülyar nazorat beradi. Pastturlar "
"bildirishnomalar uchun tasniflash tizimi sifatida ishlaydi, hujjat "
"obunachilarga qabul qilmoqchi bo'lgan bildirishnomalar pastturini "
"sozlashga imkon beradi."

