" void, the name will be added instead"
msgstr ""
"ushbu pasttur uchun joylashtirilgan xabarga qo'shilishi mumkin bo'lgan tavsif. "
"Agar bo'sh bo'lsa, uning o'rniga nom qo'shiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:243
msgid "``internal`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Boolean`"
msgstr "``internal`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Boolean`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:243
msgid ""
"messages with internal subtypes will be visible only by employees, aka "
"members of the ``base.group_user`` group"
msgstr ""
"ichki pastturlarga ega xabarlar faqat xodimlar, ya'ni ``base.group_user`` "
"guruh a'zolari tomonidan ko'rinadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:248
