"u ota pasttur orqali topilgan pastturlar bilan ushbu loyihaning barcha vazifalariga "
"obuna bo'ladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:251
msgid "``relation_field`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Char`"
msgstr "``relation_field`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Char`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:251
