#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:324
msgid "Customizing notifications"
msgstr "Bildirishnomalarni moslashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:326
msgid ""
"When sending notifications to followers, it can be quite useful to add "
"buttons in the template to allow quick actions directly from the e-mail. "
"Even a simple button to link directly to the record's form view can be "
"useful; however in most cases you don't want to display these buttons to "
"portal users."
msgstr ""
"Kuzatuvchilarga bildirishnomalar yuborayotganda, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri elektron "
"pochta orqali tezkor harakatlarni amalga oshirish uchun shablonga tugmalar qo'shish "
"juda foydali bo'lishi mumkin. Hatto yozuvning forma ko'rinishiga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"bog'laydigan oddiy tugma ham foydali bo'lishi mumkin; biroq ko'p hollarda bu "
"tugmalarni portal foydalanuvchilariga ko'rsatishni xohlamaysiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:331
msgid ""
"The notification system allows customizing notification templates in the "
"following ways:"
msgstr ""
"Bildirishnoma tizimi bildirishnoma shablonlarini quyidagi usullarda "
"moslashtirish imkonini beradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:334
msgid ""
"Display *Access Buttons*: these buttons are visible at the top of the "
"notification e-mail and allow the recipient to directly access the form "
"view of the record"
msgstr ""
"*Kirish tugmalarini* ko'rsatish: bu tugmalar bildirishnoma elektron pochta "
"xabarining yuqori qismida ko'rinadi va qabul qiluvchiga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"yozuvning forma ko'rinishiga kirish imkonini beradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:336
msgid ""
"Display *Follow Buttons*: these buttons allow the recipient to directly "
"quickly subscribe from the record"
msgstr ""
"*Kuzatish tugmalarini* ko'rsatish: bu tugmalar qabul qiluvchiga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"yozuvga tezda obuna bo'lish imkonini beradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:338
msgid ""
"Display *Unfollow Buttons*: these buttons allow the recipient to directly"
" quickly unsubscribe from the record"
msgstr ""
"*Kuzatishni bekor qilish tugmalarini* ko'rsatish: bu tugmalar qabul qiluvchiga "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri yozuvdan tezda obunasini bekor qilish imkonini beradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:340
msgid ""
"Display *Custom Action Buttons*: these buttons are calls to specific "
"routes and allow you to make some useful actions directly available from "
"the e-mail (i.e. converting a lead to an opportunity, validating an "
"expense sheet for an Expense Manager, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"*Maxsus harakat tugmalarini* ko'rsatish: bu tugmalar ma'lum marshrutlarga "
"chaqiruvlar bo'lib, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri elektron pochta orqali ba'zi foydali "
"harakatlarni mavjud qilishga imkon beradi (ya'ni, leadni imkoniyatga o'zgartirish, "
"Xarajatlar menejeri uchun xarajatlar varag'ini tasdiqlash va h.k.)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:345
msgid ""
