#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:500
msgid "Context keys:"
msgstr "Kontekst kalitlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:483
msgid ""
"These context keys can be used to somewhat control ``mail.thread`` "
"features like auto-subscription or field tracking during calls to "
"``create()`` or ``write()`` (or any other method where it may be useful)."
msgstr ""
"Bu kontekst kalitlari ``create()`` yoki ``write()`` chaqiruvlari davomida "
"(yoki foydali bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan boshqa metodda) avtomatik obuna yoki "
"maydon kuzatish kabi ``mail.thread`` xususiyatlarini qisman boshqarish uchun "
"ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:487
msgid ""
"``mail_create_nosubscribe``: at create or message_post, do not subscribe "
"the current user to the record thread"
msgstr ""
"``mail_create_nosubscribe``: yaratish yoki message_post da, joriy foydalanuvchini "
"yozuv ipiga obuna qilmang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:489
msgid ""
"``mail_create_nolog``: at create, do not log the automatic '<Document> "
"created' message"
msgstr ""
"``mail_create_nolog``: yaratishda, avtomatik '<Document> created' xabarini jurnalga yozmang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:491
msgid ""
"``mail_notrack``: at create and write, do not perform the value tracking "
"creating messages"
msgstr ""
"``mail_notrack``: yaratish va yozishda, xabarlar yaratuvchi qiymat kuzatishni amalga oshirmang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:493
msgid ""
"``tracking_disable``: at create and write, perform no MailThread features"
" (auto subscription, tracking, post, ...)"
msgstr ""
"``tracking_disable``: yaratish va yozishda, hech qanday MailThread xususiyatlarini "
"bajarmang (avtomatik obuna, kuzatish, joylashtirish, ...)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:495
msgid "``mail_auto_delete``: auto delete mail notifications; True by default"
msgstr "``mail_auto_delete``: pochta bildirishnomalarini avtomatik o'chirish; sukut bo'yicha True"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:496
msgid ""
"``mail_notify_force_send``: if less than 50 email notifications to send, "
"send them directly instead of using the queue; True by default"
msgstr ""
"``mail_notify_force_send``: agar yuborish uchun 50 dan kam elektron pochta "
"bildirishnomalari bo'lsa, navbatdan foydalanish o'rniga ularni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"yuboring; sukut bo'yicha True"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:498
msgid ""
"``mail_notify_user_signature``: add the current user signature in email "
"notifications; True by default"
msgstr ""
"``mail_notify_user_signature``: elektron pochta bildirishnomalariga joriy foydalanuvchi "
"imzosini qo'shish; sukut bo'yicha True"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:505
msgid "Mail alias"
msgstr "Pochta taxallusi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:507
msgid ""
"Aliases are configurable email addresses that are linked to a specific "
"record (which usually inherits the ``mail.alias.mixin`` model) that will "
"create new records when contacted via e-mail. They are an easy way to "
"make your system accessible from the outside, allowing users or customers"
" to quickly create records in your database without needing to connect to"
" Odoo directly."
msgstr ""
"Taxalluslar ma'lum bir yozuvga bog'liq (odatda ``mail.alias.mixin`` modelidan "
"meros olgan) sozlanishi mumkin bo'lgan elektron pochta manzillaridir va elektron "
"pochta orqali murojaat qilganda yangi yozuvlar yaratiladi. Ular tizimingizni "
"tashqaridan foydalanish uchun qulay yo'l bo'lib, foydalanuvchilar yoki "
"mijozlarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri Odooga ulanmasdan ma'lumotlar bazangizda "
"tezda yozuvlar yaratishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:514
msgid "Aliases vs. Incoming Mail Gateway"
msgstr "Taxalluslar va Kiruvchi Pochta Shlyuzi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:516
msgid ""
"Some people use the Incoming Mail Gateway for this same purpose. You "
"still need a correctly configured mail gateway to use aliases, however a "
"single catchall domain will be sufficient since all routing will be done "
"inside Odoo. Aliases have several advantages over Mail Gateways:"
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi odamlar shu maqsad uchun Kiruvchi Pochta Shlyuzidan foydalanadi. "
"Taxalluslardan foydalanish uchun to'g'ri sozlangan pochta shlyuzi kerak, "
"ammo barcha marshrutlash Odoo ichida amalga oshirilganligi sababli bitta "
"catchall domenning o'zi etarli. Taxalluslar Pochta Shlyuzlariga nisbatan "
"bir qancha afzalliklarga ega:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:524
msgid "Easier to configure"
msgstr "Sozlash osonroq"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:522
msgid ""
"A single incoming gateway can be used by many aliases; this avoids having"
" to configure multiple emails on your domain name (all configuration is "
"done inside Odoo)"
msgstr ""
"Bitta kiruvchi shlyuz ko'p taxalluslar tomonidan ishlatilishi mumkin; "
"bu domen nomingizda bir nechta elektron pochtani sozlash zaruriyatini oldini oladi "
"(barcha sozlash Odoo ichida amalga oshiriladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:525
msgid "No need for System access rights to configure aliases"
msgstr "Taxalluslarni sozlash uchun Tizim kirish huquqlari shart emas"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:526
msgid "More coherent"
msgstr "Ko'proq izchil"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:527
msgid "Configurable on the related record, not in a Settings submenu"
msgstr "Sozlamalar kichik menyusida emas, tegishli yozuvda sozlanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:532
msgid "Easier to override server-side"
msgstr "Server tomonida bekor qilish osonroq"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:529
msgid ""
"Mixin model is built to be extended from the start, allowing you to "
"extract useful data from incoming e-mails more easily than with a mail "
"gateway."
msgstr ""
"Mixin modeli boshidan kengaytirish uchun yaratilgan, bu sizga pochta "
"shlyuziga qaraganda kiruvchi elektron pochtalardan foydali ma'lumotlarni "
"osonroq chiqarishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:535
msgid "Alias support integration"
msgstr "Taxallus qo'llab-quvvatlash integratsiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:537
msgid ""
"Aliases are usually configured on a parent model which will then create "
"specific record when contacted by e-mail. For example, Project have "
"aliases to create tasks or issues, Sales Team have aliases to generate "
"Leads."
msgstr ""
"Taxalluslar odatda elektron pochta orqali murojaat qilinganda muayyan yozuv "
"yaratadigan ota-ona modelida sozlanadi. Masalan, Loyihada vazifalar yoki "
"muammolar yaratish uchun taxalluslar mavjud, Savdo Jamoasida Leadlar yaratish "
"uchun taxalluslar mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:541
msgid ""
"The model that will be created by the alias **must** inherit the "
"``mail_thread`` model."
msgstr ""
"Taxallus tomonidan yaratilishi kerak bo'lgan model **albatta** "
"``mail_thread`` modelidan meros olishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:544
msgid ""
"Alias support is added by inheriting ``mail.alias.mixin``; this mixin "
"will generate a new ``mail.alias`` record for each record of the parent "
"class that gets created (for example, every ``project.project`` record "
"having its ``mail.alias`` record initialized on creation)."
msgstr ""
"Taxallus qo'llab-quvvatlash ``mail.alias.mixin`` dan meros olish orqali "
"qo'shiladi; bu mixin yaratilgan ota-ona sinfining har bir yozuvi uchun "
"yangi ``mail.alias`` yozuvini yaratadi (masalan, har bir ``project.project`` "
"yozuvi yaratilishda o'zining ``mail.alias`` yozuvini ishga tushiradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:549
msgid ""
"Aliases can also be created manually and supported by a simple "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` field. This guide assumes you wish a more "
"complete integration with automatic creation of the alias, record-"
"specific default values, etc."
msgstr ""
"Taxalluslar qo'lda ham yaratilishi va oddiy :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` "
"maydoni tomonidan qo'llab-quvvatlanishi mumkin. Ushbu qo'llanma taxallusning "
"avtomatik yaratilishi, yozuvga xos standart qiymatlar va h.k. bilan to'liqroq "
"integratsiyani xohlashingizni taxmin qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:554
msgid ""
"Unlike ``mail.thread`` inheritance, the ``mail.alias.mixin`` **requires**"
" some specific overrides to work correctly. These overrides will specify "
"the values of the created alias, like the kind of record it must create "
"and possibly some default values these records may have depending on the "
"parent object:"
msgstr ""
"``mail.thread`` merosidan farqli o'laroq, ``mail.alias.mixin`` to'g'ri ishlashi "
"uchun ba'zi maxsus bekor qilishlarni **talab qiladi**. Bu bekor qilishlar yaratilgan "
"taxallus qiymatlarini ko'rsatadi, masalan, u yaratishi kerak bo'lgan yozuv turi va "
"ota-ona ob'ektiga qarab ushbu yozuvlarda bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan standart qiymatlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:561
msgid ""
"Return the model name for the alias. Incoming emails that are not replies"
" to existing records will cause the creation of a new record of this "
"alias model. The value may depend on ``vals``, the dict of values passed "
"to ``create`` when a record of this model is created."
msgstr ""
"Taxallus uchun model nomini qaytaradi. Mavjud yozuvlarga javob bo'lmagan "
"kiruvchi elektron pochta xabarlari ushbu taxallus modelining yangi yozuvini "
"yaratishga olib keladi. Qiymat ``vals`` ga bog'liq bo'lishi mumkin, bu ushbu "
"modelning yozuvi yaratilganda ``create`` ga uzatiladigan qiymatlar lug'ati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:566
msgid "values of the newly created record that will holding the alias"
msgstr "taxallusni ushlab turadigan yangi yaratilgan yozuv qiymatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:568
msgid "model name"
msgstr "model nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:573
msgid ""
"Return values to create an alias, or to write on the alias after its "
"creation. While not completely mandatory, it is usually required to make "
"sure that newly created records will be linked to the alias' parent (i.e."
" tasks getting created in the right project) by setting a dictionary of "
"default values in the alias' ``alias_defaults`` field."
msgstr ""
"Taxallus yaratish yoki taxallus yaratilgandan keyin unga yozish uchun "
"qiymatlarni qaytaradi. To'liq majburiy bo'lmasa ham, odatda yangi yaratilgan "
"yozuvlarning taxallusning ota-onasiga bog'lanishini ta'minlash uchun taxallus "
"``alias_defaults`` maydonida standart qiymatlar lug'atini o'rnatish talab qilinadi "
"(ya'ni, to'g'ri loyihada yaratilayotgan vazifalar)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:579
msgid "dictionary of values that will be written to the new alias"
msgstr "yangi taxallusga yoziladigan qiymatlar lug'ati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:582
msgid ""
"The ``_get_alias_values()`` override is particularly interesting as it "
"allows you to modify the behaviour of your aliases easily. Among the "
"fields that can be set on the alias, the following are of particular "
"interest:"
msgstr ""
"``_get_alias_values()`` bekor qilish taxalluslaringizning xatti-harakatini "
"osonlikcha o'zgartirishga imkon berganligi uchun ayniqsa qiziqarli. Taxallusda "
"o'rnatilishi mumkin bo'lgan maydonlar orasida quyidagilar alohida qiziqish uyg'otadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:587
msgid "``alias_name`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Char`"
msgstr "``alias_name`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Char`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:587
msgid ""
"name of the email alias, e.g. 'jobs' if you want to catch emails for "
"<jobs@example.odoo.com>"
msgstr ""
"elektron pochta taxallusining nomi, masalan, <jobs@example.odoo.com> uchun "
"elektron pochtalarni ushlash istasangiz 'jobs'"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:592
msgid "``alias_user_id`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` (``res.users``)"
msgstr "``alias_user_id`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` (``res.users``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:590
msgid ""
"owner of records created upon receiving emails on this alias; if this "
"field is not set the system will attempt to find the right owner based on"
" the sender (From) address, or will use the Administrator account if no "
"system user is found for that address"
msgstr ""
"ushbu taxallusda elektron pochta olish bilan yaratilgan yozuvlar egasi; agar "
"bu maydon o'rnatilmagan bo'lsa, tizim jo'natuvchi (From) manzili asosida to'g'ri "
"egasini topishga harakat qiladi yoki ushbu manzil uchun tizim foydalanuvchisi "
"topilmasa Administrator hisobidan foydalanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:595
msgid "``alias_defaults`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Text`"
msgstr "``alias_defaults`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Text`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:595
msgid ""
"Python dictionary that will be evaluated to provide default values when "
"creating new records for this alias"
msgstr ""
"ushbu taxallus uchun yangi yozuvlar yaratishda standart qiymatlar ko'rsatish "
"uchun baholanadigan Python lug'ati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:599
msgid "``alias_force_thread_id`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Integer`"
msgstr "``alias_force_thread_id`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Integer`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:598
msgid ""
"optional ID of a thread (record) to which all incoming messages will be "
"attached, even if they did not reply to it; if set, this will disable the"
" creation of new records completely"
msgstr ""
"barcha kiruvchi xabarlar unga javob bermagan bo'lsa ham biriktirilishi kerak "
"bo'lgan ip (yozuv) ning ixtiyoriy ID si; o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, bu yangi "
"yozuvlar yaratilishini to'liq o'chirib qo'yadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:606
msgid "``alias_contact`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Selection`"
msgstr "``alias_contact`` - :class:`~odoo.fields.Selection`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:602
msgid "Policy to post a message on the document using the mailgateway"
msgstr "Pochta shlyuzi yordamida hujjatga xabar joylashtirish siyosati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:604
msgid "*everyone*: everyone can post"
msgstr "*everyone*: hamma joylashtirishishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:605
msgid "*partners*: only authenticated partners"
msgstr "*partners*: faqat tasdiqlangan hamkorlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:606
msgid ""
"*followers*: only followers of the related document or members of "
"following channels"
msgstr ""
"*followers*: faqat tegishli hujjat kuzatuvchilari yoki kuzatuvchi kanallar a'zolari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:608
msgid ""
"Note that aliases make use of :ref:`delegation inheritance "
"<reference/orm/inheritance>`, which means that while the alias is stored "
"in another table, you have access to all these fields directly from your "
"parent object. This allows you to make your alias easily configurable "
"from the record's form view."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, taxalluslar :ref:`delegation inheritance "
"<reference/orm/inheritance>` dan foydalanadi, ya'ni taxallus boshqa jadvalda "
"saqlanayotgan bo'lsa ham, barcha bu maydonlarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ota-ona "
"ob'ektingizdan kirish imkoningiz bor. Bu taxallusni yozuvning forma ko'rinishidan "
"osonlikcha sozlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:615
msgid ""
"Let's add aliases on our business trip class to create expenses on the "
"fly via e-mail."
msgstr ""
"Keling, elektron pochta orqali tezda xarajatlar yaratish uchun ishbilarmon "
"sayohat sinfimizga taxalluslar qo'shaylik."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:663
msgid ""
"We would like our alias to be easily configurable from the form view of "
"our business trips, so let's add the following to our form view:"
msgstr ""
"Taxallusimiz ishbilarmon sayohatlarimizning forma ko'rinishidan osonlikcha "
"sozlanishini xohlaymiz, shuning uchun forma ko'rinishimizga quyidagini qo'shaylik:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:688
msgid ""
"Now we can change the alias address directly from the form view and "
"change who can send e-mails to the alias."
msgstr ""
"Endi biz taxallus manzilini to'g'ridan-to'g'ri forma ko'rinishidan o'zgartirish "
"va taxallusga kim elektron pochta yuborishi mumkinligini o'zgartirish imkoniyatiga egamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:691
msgid ""
"We can then override ``message_new()`` on our expense model to fetch the "
"values from our email when the expense will be created:"
msgstr ""
"Keyin xarajat yaratilganda elektron pochtamizdan qiymatlarni olish uchun "
"xarajat modelimizda ``message_new()`` ni bekor qilishimiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:728
msgid "Activities tracking"
msgstr "Faoliyatlarni kuzatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:730
msgid ""
"Activities are actions users have to take on a document like making a "
"phone call or organizing a meeting. Activities come with the mail module "
"as they are integrated in the Chatter but are *not bundled with "
"mail.thread*. Activities are records of the ``mail.activity`` class, "
"which have a type (``mail.activity.type``), name, description, scheduled "
"time (among others). Pending activities are visible above the message "
"history in the chatter widget."
msgstr ""
"Faoliyatlar - foydalanuvchilar hujjat bo'yicha bajarishi kerak bo'lgan harakatlar, "
"masalan, telefon qo'ng'irog'i qilish yoki uchrashuv tashkil etish. Faoliyatlar "
"Chatter ga integratsiyalanganligi uchun pochta moduli bilan birga keladi, ammo "
"*mail.thread bilan birga yuklanmagan*. Faoliyatlar - bu tur (``mail.activity.type``), "
"nom, tavsif, rejalashtirilgan vaqtga ega ``mail.activity`` sinfi yozuvlari. "
"Kutilayotgan faoliyatlar chatter vidjet da xabar tarixi ustida ko'rinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:737
msgid ""
"You can integrate activities using the ``mail.activity.mixin`` class on "
"your object and the specific widgets to display them (via the field "
"``activity_ids``) in the form view and kanban view of your records "
"(``mail_activity`` and ``kanban_activity`` widgets, respectively)."
msgstr ""
"Ob'ektingizda ``mail.activity.mixin`` sinfidan va ularni ko'rsatish uchun "
"maxsus vidjetlardan foydalanib (``activity_ids`` maydoni orqali) yozuvlaringizning "
"forma ko'rinishi va kanban ko'rinishida faoliyatlarni integratsiya qilishingiz mumkin "
"(mos ravishda ``mail_activity`` va ``kanban_activity`` vidjetlari)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:744
msgid ""
"Organizing a business trip is a tedious process and tracking needed "
"activities like ordering plane tickets or a cab for the airport could be "
"useful. To do so, we will add the activities mixin on our model and "
"display the next planned activities in the message history of our trip."
msgstr ""
"Ishbilarmon sayohatni tashkil etish zerikarli jarayon bo'lib, samolyot chiptalarini "
"buyurtma qilish yoki aeroportga taksi chaqirish kabi kerakli faoliyatlarni kuzatish "
"foydali bo'lishi mumkin. Buning uchun modelimizga faoliyatlar mixin ni qo'shamiz va "
"sayohatimizning xabar tarixida keyingi rejalashtirilgan faoliyatlarni ko'rsatamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:759
msgid "We modify the form view of our trips to display their next activities:"
msgstr "Sayohatlarimizning keyingi faoliyatlarini ko'rsatish uchun forma ko'rinishini o'zgartiramiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:778
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:854
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:1073
msgid "You can find concrete examples of integration in the following models:"
msgstr "Quyidagi modellarda integratsiyaning aniq misollarini topishingiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:780
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:856
msgid "``crm.lead`` in the CRM (*crm*) Application"
msgstr "CRM (*crm*) Ilovasidagi ``crm.lead``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:781
msgid "``sale.order`` in the Sales (*sale*) Application"
msgstr "Savdo (*sale*) Ilovasidagi ``sale.order``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:782
msgid "``project.task`` in the Project (*project*) Application"
msgstr "Loyiha (*project*) Ilovasidagi ``project.task``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:788
msgid "Website features"
msgstr "Veb-sayt xususiyatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:793
msgid "Visitor tracking"
msgstr "Tashrif buyuruvchilarni kuzatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:795
msgid ""
"The ``utm.mixin`` class can be used to track online "
"marketing/communication campaigns through arguments in links to specified"
" resources. The mixin adds 3 fields to your model:"
msgstr ""
"``utm.mixin`` sinfi ko'rsatilgan resurslarga havolalardagi argumentlar orqali "
"onlayn marketing/kommunikatsiya kampaniyalarini kuzatish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. "
"Mixin modelingizga 3 ta maydon qo'shadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:799
msgid ""
"``campaign_id``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` field to a "
"``utm.campaign`` object (i.e. Christmas_Special, Fall_Collection, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"``campaign_id``: ``utm.campaign`` ob'ektiga :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydoni "
"(ya'ni, Christmas_Special, Fall_Collection va h.k.)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:801
msgid ""
"``source_id``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` field to a ``utm.source`` "
"object (i.e. Search Engine, mailing list, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"``source_id``: ``utm.source`` ob'ektiga :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydoni "
"(ya'ni, Qidiruv tizimi, pochta ro'yxati va h.k.)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:803
msgid ""
"``medium_id``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` field to a ``utm.medium`` "
"object (i.e. Snail Mail, e-Mail, social network update, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"``medium_id``: ``utm.medium`` ob'ektiga :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydoni "
"(ya'ni, Oddiy Pochta, Elektron Pochta, ijtimoiy tarmoq yangilanishi va h.k.)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:806
msgid ""
"These models have a single field ``name`` (i.e. they are simply there to "
"distinguish campaigns but don't have any specific behaviour)."
msgstr ""
"Bu modellarda bitta ``name`` maydoni mavjud (ya'ni, ular shunchaki kampaniyalarni "
"farqlash uchun mavjud, lekin maxsus xatti-harakati yo'q)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:809
msgid ""
"Once a customer visits your website with these parameters set in the url "
"(i.e. "
"https://www.odoo.com/?campaign_id=mixin_talk&source_id=www.odoo.com&medium_id=website),"
" three cookies are set in the visitor's website for these parameters. "
"Once a object that inherits the utm.mixin is created from the website "
"(i.e. lead form, job application, etc.), the utm.mixin code kicks in and "
"fetches the values from the cookies to set them in the new record. Once "
"this is done, you can then use the campaign/source/medium fields as any "
"other field when defining reports and views (group by, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Mijoz URL da ushbu parametrlar o'rnatilgan holda veb-saytingizga tashrif buyurganida, "
"tashrif buyuruvchining veb-saytida ushbu parametrlar uchun uchta cookie o'rnatiladi. "
"utm.mixin dan meros olgan ob'ekt veb-saytdan yaratilganda (ya'ni, lead formasi, "
"ish uchun ariza va h.k.), utm.mixin kodi ishga kiradi va hisobotlar va ko'rinishlarni "
"aniqlashda boshqa maydon kabi foydalanish uchun ularni yangi yozuvga o'rnatish "
"uchun cookie lardan qiymatlarni oladi (guruh bo'yicha va h.k.)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:818
msgid ""
"To extend this behaviour, simply add a relational field to a simple model"
" (the model should support the *quick create* (i.e. call to ``create()`` "
"with a single ``name`` value) and extend the function "
"``tracking_fields()``:"
msgstr ""
"Bu xatti-harakatni kengaytirish uchun, shunchaki oddiy modelga aloqaviy maydon "
"qo'shing (model *quick create* ni qo'llab-quvvatlashi kerak (ya'ni, bitta ``name`` "
"qiymati bilan ``create()`` ga chaqiruv) va ``tracking_fields()`` funksiyasini "
"kengaytiring:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:847
msgid ""
"This will tell the system to create a cookie named *odoo_utm_my_field* "
"with the value found in the url parameter ``my_field``; once a new record"
" of this model is created by a call from a website form, the generic "
"override of the ``create()`` method of ``utm.mixin`` will fetch the "
"default values for this field from the cookie (and the "
"``my_module.my_track`` record will be creatwed on the fly if it does not "
"exist yet)."
msgstr ""
"Bu tizimga url parametri ``my_field`` da topilgan qiymat bilan *odoo_utm_my_field* "
"nomli cookie yaratishni buyuradi; veb-sayt formasidan chaqiruv orqali bu modelning "
"yangi yozuvi yaratilganda, ``utm.mixin`` ning ``create()`` metodining umumiy "
"bekor qilishi bu maydon uchun cookie dan standart qiymatlarni oladi (va "
"``my_module.my_track`` yozuvi hali mavjud bo'lmasa tezda yaratiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:857
msgid "``hr.applicant`` in the Recruitment Process (*hr_recruitment*) Application"
msgstr "Ishga qabul jarayoni (*hr_recruitment*) Ilovasidagi ``hr.applicant``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:858
#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:1076
msgid ""
"``helpdesk.ticket`` in the Helpdesk (*helpdesk* - Odoo Enterprise only) "
"Application"
msgstr ""
"Yordam Xizmati (*helpdesk* - faqat Odoo Enterprise) Ilovasidagi ``helpdesk.ticket``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:863
msgid "Website visibility"
msgstr "Veb-sayt ko'rinarliligi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:865
msgid ""
"You can quite easily add a website visibility toggle on any of your "
"record. While this mixin is quite easy to implement manually, it is the "
"most often-used after the ``mail.thread`` inheritance; a testament to its"
" usefulness. The typical use case for this mixin is any object that has a"
" frontend-page; being able to control the visibility of the page allows "
"you to take your time while editing the page and only publish it when "
"you're satisfied."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlaringizdan har biriga veb-sayt ko'rinarliligi almashtiruvchisini juda "
"osonlikcha qo'shishingiz mumkin. Bu mixin qo'lda amalga oshirish juda oson "
"bo'lsa-da, ``mail.thread`` merosidan keyin eng ko'p ishlatiladigan mixin; "
"uning foydaliligi dalili. Ushbu mixin uchun odatiy foydalanish holati frontend-"
"sahifaga ega har qanday ob'ektdir; sahifaning ko'rinarlililigini boshqarishga "
"qodir bo'lish sahifani tahrirlashda vaqt olishga va faqat qoniqganingizda "
"nashr etishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:872
msgid ""
"To include the functionality, you only need to inherit "
"``website.published.mixin``:"
msgstr ""
"Funksionallikni qo'shish uchun shunchaki ``website.published.mixin`` dan meros oling:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:881
msgid "This mixin adds 2 fields on your model:"
msgstr "Bu mixin modelingizga 2 ta maydon qo'shadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:883
msgid ""
"``website_published``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Boolean` field which "
"represents the status of the publication"
msgstr ""
"``website_published``: nashriyot holatini ifodalovchi :class:`~odoo.fields.Boolean` maydoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:885
msgid ""
"``website_url``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` field which represents the "
"URL through which the object is accessed"
msgstr ""
"``website_url``: ob'ektga kirish mumkin bo'lgan URLni ifodalovchi :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` maydoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:888
msgid ""
"Note that this last field is a computed field and must be implemented for"
" your class:"
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, bu oxirgi maydon hisoblangan maydon bo'lib, sinfingiz uchun amalga oshirilishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:896
msgid ""
"Once the mechanism is in place, you just have to adapt your frontend and "
"backend views to make it accessible. In the backend, adding a button in "
"the button box is usually the way to go:"
msgstr ""
"Mexanizm o'rnatilgach, shunchaki frontend va backend ko'rinishlaringizni "
"uni foydalanish uchun moslashtirish kerak. Backendda, odatda, tugma qutichasiga "
"tugma qo'shish to'g'ri yo'l:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:907
msgid ""
"In the frontend, some security checks are needed to avoid showing "
"'Editing' buttons to website visitors:"
msgstr ""
"Frontendda, veb-sayt tashrif buyuruvchilariga 'Tahrirlash' tugmalarini ko'rsatishdan "
"qochish uchun ba'zi xavfsizlik tekshiruvlari zarur:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:921
msgid ""
"Note that you must pass your object as the variable ``object`` to the "
"template; in this example, the ``blog.post`` record was passed as the "
"``blog_post`` variable to the ``qweb`` rendering engine, it is necessary "
"to specify this to the publish management template. The ``publish_edit`` "
"variable allow the frontend button to link to the backend (allowing you "
"to switch from frontend to backend and vice-versa easily); if set, you "
"must specify the full external id of the action you want to call in the "
"backend in the ``action`` variable (note that a Form View must exist for "
"the model)."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, ob'ektingizni shablonga ``object`` o'zgaruvchisi sifatida uzatishingiz "
"kerak; ushbu misolda ``blog.post`` yozuvi ``qweb`` ko'rsatish dvigateliga "
"``blog_post`` o'zgaruvchisi sifatida uzatildi, buni nashr boshqaruv shabloniga "
"ko'rsatish zarur. ``publish_edit`` o'zgaruvchisi frontend tugmasiga backendga "
"bog'lanish imkonini beradi (siz frontend va backend o'rtasida osonlikcha almashish "
"imkonini beradi); o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, backend da chaqirmoqchi bo'lgan harakatning "
"to'liq tashqi id sini ``action`` o'zgaruvchisida ko'rsatishingiz kerak "
"(model uchun Forma Ko'rinishi mavjud bo'lishi kerakligini unutmang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:930
msgid ""
"The action ``website_publish_button`` is defined in the mixin and adapts "
"its behaviour to your object: if the class has a valid ``website_url`` "
"compute function, the user is redirected to the frontend when he clicks "
"on the button; the user can then publish the page directly from the "
"frontend. This ensures that no online publication can happen by accident."
" If there is not compute function, the boolean ``website_published`` is "
"simply triggered."
msgstr ""
"``website_publish_button`` harakati mixin da aniqlangan va ob'ektingizga xatti-"
"harakatini moslaydi: agar sinfda to'g'ri ``website_url`` hisoblash funksiyasi "
"bo'lsa, foydalanuvchi tugmani bosganda frontendga yo'naltiriladi; foydalanuvchi "
"keyin sahifani to'g'ridan-to'g'ri frontenddan nashr etishi mumkin. Bu hech qanday "
"onlayn nashr tasodifan sodir bo'lmasligini ta'minlaydi. Agar hisoblash funksiyasi "
"bo'lmasa, ``website_published`` booleani shunchaki ishga tushiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:940
msgid "Website metadata"
msgstr "Veb-sayt metama'lumotlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:942
msgid ""
"This simple mixin simply allows you to easily inject metadata in your "
"frontend pages."
msgstr ""
"Bu oddiy mixin frontend sahifalaringizga metama'lumotlarni osonlikcha kiritish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:952
msgid "This mixin adds 3 fields on your model:"
msgstr "Bu mixin modelingizga 3 ta maydon qo'shadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:954
msgid ""
"``website_meta_title``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` field that allow you "
"to set an additional title to your page"
msgstr ""
"``website_meta_title``: sahifangizga qo'shimcha sarlavha o'rnatish imkonini "
"beruvchi :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` maydoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:956
msgid ""
"``website_meta_description``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` field that "
"contains a short description of the page (sometimes used in search "
"engines results)"
msgstr ""
"``website_meta_description``: sahifaning qisqa tavsifini o'z ichiga oluvchi "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Char` maydoni (ba'zan qidiruv tizimlari natijalarida ishlatiladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:958
msgid ""
"``website_meta_keywords``: :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` field that contains"
" some keywords to help your page to be classified more precisely by "
"search engines; the \"Promote\" tool will help you select lexically-"
"related keywords easily"
msgstr ""
"``website_meta_keywords``: sahifangizning qidiruv tizimlari tomonidan aniqroq "
"tasniflanishiga yordam beruvchi ba'zi kalit so'zlarni o'z ichiga oluvchi "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Char` maydoni; \"Targ'ib qilish\" vositasi leksik jihatdan "
"bog'liq kalit so'zlarni osonlikcha tanlashga yordam beradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:962
msgid ""
"These fields are editable in the frontend using the \"Promote\" tool from"
" the Editor toolbar. Setting these fields can help search engines to "
"better index your pages. Note that search engines do not base their "
"results only on these metadata; the best SEO practice should still be to "
"get referenced by reliable sources."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydonlar frontendda Muharrir asboblar panelidan \"Targ'ib qilish\" vositasi "
"yordamida tahrirlash mumkin. Bu maydonlarni o'rnatish qidiruv tizimlariga "
"sahifalaringizni yaxshiroq indekslashga yordam berishi mumkin. E'tibor bering, "
"qidiruv tizimlari natijalarini faqat ushbu metama'lumotlarga asoslamaydi; "
"eng yaxshi SEO amaliyoti hali ham ishonchli manbalar tomonidan ko'rsatilish bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:970
msgid "Others"
msgstr "Boshqalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:975
msgid "Customer Rating"
msgstr "Mijoz reytingi"

