"agar ``user_id`` dan boshqa maydon ishlatsangiz, bu xatti-harakat "
"``rating_get_rated_partner_id()`` funksiyasi bilan bekor qilinishi mumkin "
"(funksiya ``res.partner`` qaytarishi kerakligini unutmang, ``user_id`` uchun "
"tizim foydalanuvchining hamkorini avtomatik oladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/mixins.rst:1010
msgid ""
"The chatter history will display the rating event (if your model inherits"
