"The manifest file serves to declare a python package as an Odoo module "
"and to specify module metadata."
msgstr ""
"Manifest fayli Python paketini Odoo moduli sifatida e'lon qilish va modul "
"metama'lumotlarini ko'rsatish uchun xizmat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/module.rst:16
msgid ""
"It is a file called ``__manifest__.py`` and contains a single Python "
"dictionary, where each key specifies module metadatum."
msgstr ""
"Bu ``__manifest__.py`` deb nomlangan fayl bo'lib, bitta Python lug'atini o'z ichiga "
"oladi, bu yerda har bir kalit modul metama'lumotini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/module.rst:40
msgid "Available manifest fields are:"
msgstr "Mavjud manifest maydonlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/module.rst:42
