"yoki davr boshi/oxirini olish :class:`~odoo.fields.Date` va "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Datetime` orqali ham mavjud. Bu yordamchilar "
"`odoo.tools.date_utils` ni import qilish orqali ham foydalanish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:198
msgid "Timezones"
msgstr "Vaqt mintaqalari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:200
msgid ""
"Datetime fields are stored as `timestamp without timezone` columns in the"
" database and are stored in the UTC timezone. This is by design, as it "
"makes the Odoo database independent from the timezone of the hosting "
"server system. Timezone conversion is managed entirely by the client "
"side."
msgstr ""
" ma'lumotlar bazasida `timestamp without timezone` ustunlari sifatida "
"saqlanadi va UTC vaqt mintaqasida saqlanadi. Bu ataylab qilingan, chunki "
"bu Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasini server tizimining vaqt mintaqasidan mustaqil "
"qiladi. Vaqt mintaqasini konvertatsiya qilish to'liq mijoz tomoni "
"tomonidan boshqariladi."

