#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:310
msgid ""
"During the computation of the inverse, **all** fields that use said "
"inverse are protected, meaning that they can't be computed, even if their"
" value is not in the cache."
msgstr ""
"Teskari hisoblash vaqtida, shu inversdan foydalanadigan **barcha** "
"maydonlar himoyalangan, ya'ni ular qiymatlar keshlarda bo'lmasa ham "
"hisoblanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:314
msgid ""
