"yozuvlar to'plami. Oldindan yuklab olishsiz, tsikl ma'lumotlar bazasiga "
"2000 ta so'rov yuboradi. Oldindan yuklab olish bilan faqat bitta "
"so'rov yuboriladi::"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:622
msgid ""
"The prefetching also works on *secondary records*: when relational fields"
" are read, their values (which are records) are  subscribed for future "
"prefetching. Accessing one of those secondary records prefetches all "
"secondary records from the same model. This makes the following example "
"generate only two queries, one for partners and one for countries::"
msgstr ""
"Oldindan yuklab olish *ikkilamchi yozuvlarda* ham ishlaydi: munosabat "
"maydonlari o'qilganda, ularning qiymatlari (yozuvlar bo'lgan) kelajakdagi "
"oldindan yuklab olish uchun obuna bo'linadi. Shu ikkilamchi yozuvlardan "
"biriga kirish bir xil modeldan barcha ikkilamchi yozuvlarni oldindan "
"yuklab oladi. Bu quyidagi misolni faqat ikki so'rov yaratishga olib "
"keladi: biri sheriklari uchun, ikkinchisi mamlakatlar uchun::"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:634
msgid ""
"The methods :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_fetch` and "
