#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1012
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Domain` can be used to serialize the domain as a "
"``list`` of simple conditions represented by 3-item ``tuple`` (or a "
"``list``). Such a serialized form may be sometimes faster to read or "
"write. Domain conditions can be combined using logical operators in a "
"*prefix* notation. You can combine 2 domains using ``'&'`` (AND), ``'|'``"
" (OR) and you can negate 1 using ``'!'`` (NOT)."
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Domain` domenni 3 elementli ``tuple`` (yoki "
"``list``) bilan ifodalangan oddiy shartlarning ``list`` sifatida "
"serializatsiya qilish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Bunday serializatsiya "
"qilingan shakl ba'zan o'qish yoki yozish uchun tezroq bo'lishi mumkin. "
"Domen shartlarini *prefiks* yozuvida mantiqiy operatorlar yordamida "
"birlashtirish mumkin. 2 domenni ``'&'`` (VA), ``'|'`` (YOKI) yordamida "
"birlashtirish va 1 ni ``'!'`` (EMAS) yordamida inkor qilish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1040
msgid "Dynamic time values"
msgstr "Dinamik vaqt qiymatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1042
msgid ""
"In the context of search domains, for :ref:`date and datetime fields "
"<reference/fields/date>`, the value can be a moment relative to *now* in "
"the timezone of the user. A simple language is provided to specify these "
"dates. It is a space-separated string of terms. The first term is "
"optional and is \"today\" (at midnight) or \"now\". Then, each term "
"starts with \"+\" (add), \"-\" (subtract) or \"=\" (set), followed by an "
"integer and date unit or a lower-case weekday."
msgstr ""
"Qidiruv domenlari kontekstida, :ref:`sana va sana-vaqt maydonlari "
"<reference/fields/date>` uchun qiymat foydalanuvchining vaqt "
"mintaqasida *hozir* ga nisbatan moment bo'lishi mumkin. Bu sanalarni "
"belgilash uchun oddiy til taqdim etilgan. Bu bo'sh joy bilan ajratilgan "
"atamalar qatoridir. Birinchi atama ixtiyoriy va \"today\" (yarim tunda) "
"yoki \"now\". Keyin har bir atama \"+\" (qo'shish), \"-\" (ayirish) "
"yoki \"=\" (o'rnatish) bilan boshlanadi, keyin butun son va sana birligi "
"yoki kichik harfli hafta kuni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1050
msgid ""
"The date units are: \"d\" (days), \"w\" (weeks), \"m\" (months), \"y\" "
"(years), \"H\" (hours), \"M\" (minutes), \"S\" (seconds). For weekdays, "
"\"+\" and \"-\" mean next and previous weekday (unless we are already in "
"that weekday) and \"=\" means in current week starting on Monday. When "
"setting a date, the lower-units (hours, minutes and seconds) are set to "
"0."
msgstr ""
"Sana birliklari: \"d\" (kunlar), \"w\" (haftalar), \"m\" (oylar), \"y\" "
"(yillar), \"H\" (soatlar), \"M\" (daqiqalar), \"S\" (soniyalar). "
"Hafta kunlari uchun \"+\" va \"-\" keyingi va oldingi hafta kunini "
"bildiradi (agar biz allaqachon o'sha hafta kunida bo'lmasak) va \"=\" "
"dushanba kunidan boshlanadigan joriy haftani bildiradi. Sana "
"o'rnatilganda past birliklar (soatlar, daqiqalar va soniyalar) 0 ga "
"o'rnatiladi."

