msgstr "Operatsiyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1099
msgid ""
"Recordsets are immutable, but sets of the same model can be combined "
"using various set operations, returning new recordsets."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar to'plamlari o'zgarmas, lekin bir xil model to'plamlari turli "
"to'plam operatsiyalari yordamida birlashtirilishi va yangi yozuvlar "
"to'plamlari qaytarilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1104
msgid ""
"``record in set`` returns whether ``record`` (which must be a 1-element "
"recordset) is present in ``set``. ``record not in set`` is the inverse "
"operation"
msgstr ""
"``record in set`` ``record`` (1 elementli yozuvlar to'plami bo'lishi "
"kerak) ``set`` da borligini qaytaradi. ``record not in set`` teskari "
"operatsiya"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1107
msgid ""
"``set1 <= set2`` and ``set1 < set2`` return whether ``set1`` is a subset "
"of ``set2`` (resp. strict)"
msgstr ""
"``set1 <= set2`` va ``set1 < set2`` ``set1`` ning ``set2`` ning kichik "
"to'plami ekanligini qaytaradi (mos ravishda qat'iy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1109
msgid ""
"``set1 >= set2`` and ``set1 > set2`` return whether ``set1`` is a "
"superset of ``set2`` (resp. strict)"
msgstr ""
"``set1 >= set2`` va ``set1 > set2`` ``set1`` ning ``set2`` ning katta "
"to'plami ekanligini qaytaradi (mos ravishda qat'iy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1111
msgid ""
"``set1 | set2`` returns the union of the two recordsets, a new recordset "
"containing all records present in either source"
msgstr ""
"``set1 | set2`` ikki yozuvlar to'plamining birlashmасини qaytaradi, "
"har ikkala manbada mavjud barcha yozuvlarni o'z ichiga olgan yangi "
"yozuvlar to'plami"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1113
msgid ""
"``set1 & set2`` returns the intersection of two recordsets, a new "
"recordset containing only records present in both sources"
msgstr ""
"``set1 & set2`` ikki yozuvlar to'plamining kesishmasini qaytaradi, "
"faqat ikkala manbada ham mavjud yozuvlarni o'z ichiga olgan yangi "
"yozuvlar to'plami"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1115
msgid ""
"``set1 - set2`` returns a new recordset containing only records of "
"``set1`` which are *not* in ``set2``"
msgstr ""
"``set1 - set2`` faqat ``set2`` da *yo'q* ``set1`` yozuvlarini "
"o'z ichiga olgan yangi yozuvlar to'plamini qaytaradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1118
msgid ""
"Recordsets are iterable so the usual Python tools are available for "
"transformation (:func:`python:map`, :func:`python:sorted`, "
":func:`~python:itertools.ifilter`, ...) however these return either a "
":class:`python:list` or an :term:`python:iterator`, removing the ability "
"to call methods on their result, or to use set operations."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar to'plamlari iteratsiya qilinishi mumkin, shuning uchun "
"o'zgartirish uchun odatdagi Python vositalari mavjud "
"(:func:`python:map`, :func:`python:sorted`, "
":func:`~python:itertools.ifilter`, ...) lekin bular "
":class:`python:list` yoki :term:`python:iterator` qaytaradi, bu "
"natijada metodlarni chaqirish yoki to'plam operatsiyalaridan "
"foydalanish imkoniyatini yo'q qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1124
msgid ""
"Recordsets therefore provide the following operations returning "
"recordsets themselves (when possible):"
msgstr ""
"Shuning uchun yozuvlar to'plamlari quyidagi operatsiyalarni taqdim etadi "
"(imkon bo'lganda) yozuvlar to'plamlarining o'zlarini qaytaradi:"

