"topshiruv merosdan foydalanganda, metodlar meros *olinmaydi*, "
"faqat maydonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1331
msgid "`_inherits` is more or less implemented, avoid it if you can;"
msgstr "`_inherits` ko'proq yoki kamroq amalga oshirilgan, iloji bo'lsa undan qoching;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1332
msgid ""
"chained `_inherits` is essentially not implemented, we cannot guarantee "
"anything on the final behavior."
msgstr ""
"Zanjirli `_inherits` asosan amalga oshirilmagan, yakuniy xatti-harakat "
"haqida hech narsa kafolatlay olmaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1336
msgid "Fields Incremental Definition"
msgstr "Maydonlarni bosqichma-bosqich aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1338
msgid ""
"A field is defined as class attribute on a model class. If the model is "
"extended, one can also extend the field definition by redefining a field "
"with the same name and same type on the subclass. In that case, the "
"attributes of the field are taken from the parent class and overridden by"
" the ones given in subclasses."
msgstr ""
"Maydon model sinfida sinf atributi sifatida aniqlanadi. Agar model "
"kengaytirilsa, pastki sinfda bir xil nom va bir xil turda maydonni "
"qayta aniqlash orqali maydon ta'rifini ham kengaytirish mumkin. Bu "
"holda maydon atributlari ota-sinfdan olinadi va pastki sinfda "
"berilganlar bilan qayta belgilanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1344
msgid ""
"For instance, the second class below only adds a tooltip on the field "
"``state``"
msgstr ""
"Masalan, quyidagi ikkinchi sinf faqat ``state`` maydoniga maslahat "
"xabari qo'shadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm.rst:1364
msgid "Error management"
msgstr "Xatolarni boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:5
msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "O'zgarishlar jurnali"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:8
msgid "Odoo version 19.0"
msgstr "Odoo 19.0 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:10
msgid ""
"Add support for ``GROUPING SETS`` for pivot views. See `#194413 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/194413>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishlar uchun ``GROUPING SETS`` qo'llab-quvvatlash qo'shildi. "
"`#194413 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/194413>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:12
msgid ""
"Adding support for dynamic dates in domains. See `#216665 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/216665>`_."
msgstr ""
"Domenlarda dinamik sanalar uchun qo'llab-quvvatlash qo'shildi. "
"`#216665 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/216665>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:14
msgid ""
"Deprecated `odoo.osv` in `#217708 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/217708>`_."
msgstr ""
"`odoo.osv` `#217708 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/217708>`_ da "
"eskirgan deb belgilandi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:15
msgid ""
"Deprecated `record._cr`, `record._context`, `record._uid` in `#193636 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/193636>`_."
msgstr ""
"`record._cr`, `record._context`, `record._uid` `#193636 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/193636>`_ da eskirgan deb belgilandi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:19
msgid "Odoo Online version 18.4"
msgstr "Odoo Online 18.4 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:21
msgid ""
"The `reinit` option is added to the CLI to reinitialize modules. See "
"`#206408 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/206408>`_."
msgstr ""
"Modullarni qayta ishga tushirish uchun CLI ga `reinit` opsiyasi qo'shildi. "
"`#206408 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/206408>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:23
msgid ""
"Possibility to write and combine custom domains for injecting arbitrary "
"SQL. See `#205208 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/205208>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy SQL kiritish uchun maxsus domenlarni yozish va birlashtirish "
"imkoniyati. `#205208 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/205208>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:27
msgid "Odoo Online version 18.3"
msgstr "Odoo Online 18.3 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:29
msgid ""
"Domain optimization is applied before executing `Fields.search` methods. "
"All equalities are handled consistently: `=` is equivalent to `in`. See "
"`#191549 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/191549>`_."
msgstr ""
"`Fields.search` metodlari bajarilishidan oldin domen optimizatsiyasi "
"qo'llaniladi. Barcha tengliklar izchil ravishda ko'rib chiqiladi: "
"`=` `in` ga teng. `#191549 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/191549>`_ "
"ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:32
msgid ""
"New cron API for notifying progress with batch commits. See `#197781 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/197781>`_."
msgstr ""
"Paketli saqlashlar bilan jarayonni xabarlash uchun yangi cron API. "
"`#197781 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/197781>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:34
msgid ""
"Demo data no longer loaded by default. See `#194585 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/194585>`_."
msgstr ""
"Demo ma'lumotlar endi odatda yuklanmaydi. "
"`#194585 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/194585>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:38
msgid "Odoo Online version 18.2"
msgstr "Odoo Online 18.2 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:40
msgid ""
"`read_group` has been deprecated in favor of `_read_group` for backend "
"usage and of `formatted_read_group` as formatted public API. See `#163300"
" <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/163300>`_."
msgstr ""
"`read_group` backend foydalanish uchun `_read_group` va formatlangan "
"ommaviy API sifatida `formatted_read_group` foydasiga eskirgan deb "
"belgilandi. `#163300 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/163300>`_ "
"ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:42
msgid ""
"`@api.private` is added to distinguish public Python methods from methods"
" exposed for RPC calls. See `#195402 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/195402>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ommaviy Python metodlarini RPC chaqiruvlari uchun ochiq metodlardan "
"ajratish uchun `@api.private` qo'shildi. "
"`#195402 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/195402>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:44
msgid ""
"Native namespaces for ``odoo`` module `PEP-420 "
"<https://peps.python.org/pep-0420/>`_. See `#195664 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/195664>`_."
msgstr ""
"``odoo`` moduli uchun mahalliy nom makonlari `PEP-420 "
"<https://peps.python.org/pep-0420/>`_. "
"`#195664 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/195664>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:48
msgid "Odoo Online version 18.1"
msgstr "Odoo Online 18.1 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:50
msgid ""
"New `odoo.domain` and `odoo.Domain` API for domain manipulation. See "
"`#170009 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/170009>`_."
msgstr ""
"Domenlarni boshqarish uchun yangi `odoo.domain` va `odoo.Domain` API. "
"`#170009 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/170009>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:52
msgid ""
"Declare constraints and indexes as model attributes with `#175783 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/175783>`_."
msgstr ""
"Cheklovlar va indekslarni model atributlari sifatida e'lon qilish "
"`#175783 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/175783>`_ bilan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:53
msgid ""
"The `json` controllers have been renamed to `jsonrpc`. They are called "
"the same, only the `type` in the python files changed. See `#183636 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/183636>`_."
msgstr ""
"`json` kontrollerlar `jsonrpc` ga o'zgartirildi. Ular bir xil nomlanadi, "
"faqat python fayllaridagi `type` o'zgardi. "
"`#183636 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/183636>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:57
msgid "Odoo version 18.0"
msgstr "Odoo 18.0 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:59
msgid ""
"Searching by name is now implemented as `_search_display_name` like all "
"other fields. See `#174967 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/174967>`_."
msgstr ""
"Nomi bo'yicha qidirish endi barcha boshqa maydonlar kabi "
"`_search_display_name` sifatida amalga oshirildi. "
"`#174967 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/174967>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:61
msgid ""
"New methods to check access rights and rules now combine both access "
"rights and rules: `check_access`, `has_access` and `_filtered_access`. "
"See `#179148 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/179148>`_."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqlari va qoidalarini tekshirish uchun yangi metodlar endi "
"ikkalasini birlashtiradi: `check_access`, `has_access` va "
"`_filtered_access`. "
"`#179148 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/179148>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:64
msgid ""
"Translations are made available from the `Environment` with `#174844 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/174844>`_."
msgstr ""
"Tarjimalar `Environment` dan `#174844 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/174844>`_ bilan mavjud qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:67
msgid "Odoo Online version 17.4"
msgstr "Odoo Online 17.4 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:69
msgid ""
"The internal operator `inselect` is removed. The alternative is to use "
"`in` with a Query or SQL object. `#171371 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/171371>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ichki operator `inselect` olib tashlandi. Muqobil Query yoki SQL "
"ob'ekti bilan `in` dan foydalanish. "
"`#171371 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/171371>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:74
msgid "Odoo Online version 17.3"
msgstr "Odoo Online 17.3 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:76
msgid ""
"We can now group by date parts numbers in `read_group`, `_read_group` and"
" domains with `#159528 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/159528>`_."
msgstr ""
"Endi `read_group`, `_read_group` va domenlarda sana qismlari raqamlari "
"bo'yicha guruhlash mumkin `#159528 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/159528>`_ bilan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:80
msgid "Odoo Online version 17.2"
msgstr "Odoo Online 17.2 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:82
msgid ""
"The :attr:`group_operator` attribute of :class:`~odoo.fields.Field` is "
"renamed into :attr:`aggregator` with `#127353 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/127353>`_."
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Field` ning :attr:`group_operator` atributi "
"`#127353 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/127353>`_ bilan "
":attr:`aggregator` ga o'zgartirildi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:84
msgid ""
"We can now group/aggregate/order by related no-store field with `#127353 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/127353>`_."
msgstr ""
"Endi `#127353 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/127353>`_ bilan "
"bog'liq saqlanmagan maydon bo'yicha guruhlash/yig'ish/tartiblash mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:88
msgid "Odoo Online version 17.1"
msgstr "Odoo Online 17.1 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:90
msgid ""
"Method :meth:`~odoo.models.Model._flush_search` has been deprecated with "
"`#144747 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/144747>`_. The flushing of "
"fields is now done by :meth:`~odoo.api.Environment.execute_query`, and is"
" based on metadata put in the :class:`~odoo.tools.SQL` object by "
":meth:`~odoo.models.BaseModel._search` and other low-level ORM methods "
"that build such objects.  Those methods are also responsible for checking"
" the access rights on the fields that are used in the SQL object."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._flush_search` metodi "
"`#144747 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/144747>`_ bilan eskirgan "
"deb belgilandi. Maydonlarni yuvish endi "
":meth:`~odoo.api.Environment.execute_query` tomonidan amalga oshiriladi "
"va :meth:`~odoo.models.BaseModel._search` va bunday ob'ektlarni quradigan "
"boshqa past darajali ORM metodlari tomonidan :class:`~odoo.tools.SQL` "
"ob'ektiga qo'yilgan meta-ma'lumotlarga asoslangan. Bu metodlar shuningdek "
"SQL ob'ektida ishlatiladigan maydonlardagi kirish huquqlarini tekshirishga "
"ham javobgardir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:99
msgid "Odoo version 17.0"
msgstr "Odoo 17.0 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:101
msgid ""
"Introduce an :class:`~odoo.tools.SQL` wrapper object to make SQL "
"composition easier and safer with respect to SQL injections. Methods of "
"the ORM now use it internally. Introduced by `#134677 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/134677>`_."
msgstr ""
"SQL in'ektsiyalariga nisbatan SQL kompozitsiyasini osonlashtirish va "
"xavfsizroq qilish uchun :class:`~odoo.tools.SQL` wrapper ob'ektini "
"kiritish. ORM metodlari endi uni ichdan ishlatadi. "
"`#134677 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/134677>`_ tomonidan kiritildi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:106
msgid "Odoo Online version 16.4"
msgstr "Odoo Online 16.4 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:108
msgid ""
"Method :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.name_get` has been deprecated with "
"`#122085 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/122085>`_. Read field "
"`display_name` instead."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.name_get` metodi "
"`#122085 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/122085>`_ bilan eskirgan "
"deb belgilandi. Buning o'rniga `display_name` maydonini o'qing."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:113
msgid "Odoo Online version 16.3"
msgstr "Odoo Online 16.3 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:115
msgid ""
"Method :meth:`~odoo.models.Model._read_group` has a new signature with "
"`#110737 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/110737>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._read_group` metodi "
"`#110737 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/110737>`_ bilan yangi "
"imzoga ega"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:119
msgid "Odoo Online version 16.2"
msgstr "Odoo Online 16.2 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:121
msgid ""
"Refactor the implementation of searching and reading methods to be able "
"to combine both in a minimal number of SQL queries. We introduce two new "
"methods :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_fetch` and "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fetch` that take advantage of the combination. "
"More details can be found on the pull request `#112126 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/112126>`_."
msgstr ""
"Qidirish va o'qish metodlarini ikkalasini minimal SQL so'rovlar "
"sonida birlashtira olish uchun refaktoring. Biz ularning "
"kombinatsiyasidan foydalanadigan ikki yangi metodni "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_fetch` va "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fetch` ni kiritamiz. Ko'proq tafsilotlarni "
"pull so'rovda topish mumkin "
"`#112126 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/112126>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:128
msgid "Odoo version 16.0"
msgstr "Odoo 16.0 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:130
msgid ""
"Translations for translated fields are stored as JSONB values with "
"`#97692 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/97692>`_ and `#101115 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/101115>`_. Code translations are no "
"longer stored into the database. They become static and are extracted "
"from the PO files when needed."
msgstr ""
"Tarjima qilingan maydonlar uchun tarjimalar JSONB qiymatlari sifatida "
"`#97692 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/97692>`_ va `#101115 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/101115>`_ bilan saqlanadi. Kod "
"tarjimalari endi ma'lumotlar bazasida saqlanmaydi. Ular statik bo'lib "
"qoladi va zarur bo'lganda PO fayllaridan olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:135
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` takes the :attr:`limit` argument "
"into account with `#95589 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/95589>`_. It"
" limits the number of records to count, improving performance when a "
"partial result is acceptable."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` `#95589 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/95589>`_ bilan :attr:`limit` "
"argumentini hisobga oladi. U hisoblanadigan yozuvlar sonini cheklaydi, "
"qisman natija qabul qilinsa ishlash samaradorligini yaxshilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:139
msgid "Odoo Online version 15.4"
msgstr "Odoo Online 15.4 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:141
msgid ""
"New API for flushing to the database and invalidating the cache with "
"`#87527 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/87527>`_. New methods have "
"been added to `odoo.models.Model` and `odoo.api.Environment`, and are "
"less confusing about what is actually done in each case. See the section "
":ref:`SQL Execution <reference/orm/sql>`."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasiga yuvish va keshni bekor qilish uchun yangi API "
"`#87527 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/87527>`_ bilan. Yangi metodlar "
"`odoo.models.Model` va `odoo.api.Environment` ga qo'shildi va har bir "
"holda aslida nima qilinishi haqida kamroq chalkashlik mavjud. "
":ref:`SQL Execution <reference/orm/sql>` bo'limiga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:148
msgid "Odoo Online version 15.3"
msgstr "Odoo Online 15.3 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:150
msgid ""
"The argument `args` is renamed to `domain` for "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search`, "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` and "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._search`. `#83687 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search`, "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` va "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._search` uchun `args` argumenti `domain` ga "
"o'zgartirildi. `#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:152
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.filtered_domain` conserves the order of the "
"current recordset. `#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.filtered_domain` joriy yozuvlar to'plamining "
"tartibini saqlaydi. `#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:153
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.browse` does not accept :class:`str` as `ids`. "
"`#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.browse` `ids` sifatida :class:`str` qabul "
"qilmaydi. `#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:154
msgid ""
"The methods :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get_keys` and "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.get_xml_id` on :class:`~odoo.models.Model` are "
"deprecated. `#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.models.Model` dagi "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get_keys` va "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.get_xml_id` metodlari eskirgan deb belgilandi. "
"`#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:155
msgid ""
"The method :meth:`~odoo.models.Model._mapped_cache` is removed. `#83687 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._mapped_cache` metodi olib tashlandi. "
"`#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:156
msgid ""
"Remove the :attr:`limit` attribute of :class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` and "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many`. `#83687 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` va :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` ning "
":attr:`limit` atributi olib tashlandi. "
"`#83687 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83687>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:159
msgid "Odoo Online version 15.2"
msgstr "Odoo Online 15.2 versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:161
msgid ""
"Specific index types on fields:  With `#83274 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83274>`_ and `#83015 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83015>`_, developers can now define "
"what type of indexes can be used on fields by PostgreSQL. See the "
":ref:`index property <reference/fields>` of `odoo.fields.Field`."
msgstr ""
"Maydonlarda aniq indeks turlari: `#83274 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83274>`_ va `#83015 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/83015>`_ bilan, ishlab chiquvchilar "
"PostgreSQL tomonidan maydonlarda qanday turdagi indekslar ishlatilishini "
"aniqlash imkoniga ega bo'ldi. `odoo.fields.Field` ning "
":ref:`index xossasi <reference/fields>` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:165
msgid ""
"The :attr:`_sequence` attribute of :class:`~odoo.models.Model` is "
"removed. Odoo lets PostgreSQL use the default sequence of the primary "
"key. `#82727 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.models.Model` ning :attr:`_sequence` atributi olib "
"tashlandi. Odoo PostgreSQL ga asosiy kalit standart ketma-ketligidan "
"foydalanishga ruxsat beradi. "
"`#82727 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:166
msgid ""
"The method :meth:`~odoo.models.Model._write` does not raise an error for "
"non-existing records. `#82727 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model._write` metodi mavjud bo'lmagan yozuvlar "
"uchun xato chiqarmaydi. "
"`#82727 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/orm/changelog.rst:167
msgid ""
"The :attr:`column_format` and :attr:`deprecated` attributes of "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Field` are removed. `#82727 "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Field` ning :attr:`column_format` va "
":attr:`deprecated` atributlari olib tashlandi. "
"`#82727 <https://github.com/odoo/odoo/pull/82727>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:5
msgid "Performance"
msgstr "Ishlash samaradorligi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:10
msgid "Profiling"
msgstr "Profillashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:14
msgid ""
"Profiling is about analysing the execution of a program and measure "
"aggregated data. These data can be the elapsed time for each function, "
"the executed SQL queries..."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtirish dastur bajarilishini tahlil qilish va yig'ilgan "
"ma'lumotlarni o'lchash haqida. Bu ma'lumotlar har bir funksiya uchun "
"sarflangan vaqt, bajarilgan SQL so'rovlar bo'lishi mumkin..."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:17
msgid ""
"While profiling does not improve the performance of a program by itself, "
"it can prove very helpful in finding performance issues and identifying "
"which part of the program is responsible for them."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtirish o'z-o'zidan dastur samaradorligini yaxshilamasa-da, "
"ishlash muammolarini topish va dasturning qaysi qismi ular uchun "
"javobgar ekanligini aniqlashda juda foydali bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:20
msgid ""
"Odoo provides an integrated profiling tool that allows recording all "
"executed queries and stack traces during execution. It can be used to "
"profile either a set of requests of a user session, or a specific portion"
" of code. Profiling results can be either inspected with the integrated "
"`speedscope <https://github.com/jlfwong/speedscope>`_ :dfn:`open source "
"app allowing to visualize a flamegraph` view or analyzed with custom "
"tools by first saving them in a JSON file or in the database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ijro vaqtida bajarilgan barcha so'rovlar va stek izlarini "
"yozib olish imkonini beruvchi o'rnatilgan profillashtirish vositasini "
"taqdim etadi. U foydalanuvchi sessiyasining so'rovlar to'plamini yoki "
"kodning muayyan qismini profillashtirish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. "
"Profillashtirish natijalari o'rnatilgan "
"`speedscope <https://github.com/jlfwong/speedscope>`_ "
":dfn:`flamegraph vizualizatsiyasiga imkon beruvchi ochiq manbali ilova` "
"ko'rinishi bilan ko'zdan kechirilishi yoki JSON fayliga yoki "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga saqlash orqali maxsus vositalar bilan tahlil "
"qilinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:29
msgid "Enable the profiler"
msgstr "Profillashtiruvchini yoqish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:31
msgid ""
"The profiler can either be enabled from the user interface, which is the "
"easiest way to do so but allows profiling only web requests, or from "
"Python code, which allows profiling any piece of code including tests."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchini foydalanuvchi interfeysidan yoqish mumkin, bu eng "
"oson usul, lekin faqat veb so'rovlarni profillashtirish imkonini beradi, "
"yoki Python kodidan, bu testlar ham kiradigan har qanday kod qismini "
"profillashtirish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:37
msgid "Enable from the user interface"
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi interfeysidan yoqish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:39
msgid ":ref:`Enable the developer mode <developer-mode>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Ishlab chiquvchi rejimini yoqing <developer-mode>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:40
msgid ""
"Before starting a profiling session, the profiler must be enabled "
"globally on the database. This can be done in two ways:"
msgstr ""
"Profillashtirish sessiyasini boshlashdan oldin, profillashtiruvchini "
"ma'lumotlar bazasida global ravishda yoqish kerak. Bu ikki usulda "
"amalga oshirilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:43
msgid ""
"Open the :ref:`developer mode tools <developer-mode/tools>`, then toggle "
"the :guilabel:`Enable profiling` button. A wizard suggests a set of "
"expiry times for the profiling. Click on :guilabel:`ENABLE PROFILING` to "
"enable the profiler globally."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Ishlab chiquvchi rejimi vositalarini <developer-mode/tools>` oching, "
"so'ng :guilabel:`Enable profiling` tugmasini bosing. Sehrgar "
"profillashtirish uchun amal qilish muddatlarini taklif qiladi. "
"Profillashtiruvchini global ravishda yoqish uchun "
":guilabel:`ENABLE PROFILING` tugmasini bosing."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:49
msgid ""
"Go to :guilabel:`Settings --> General Settings --> Performance` and set "
"the desired time to the field :guilabel:`Enable profiling until`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sozlamalar --> Umumiy sozlamalar --> Ishlash samaradorligi` "
"ga o'ting va :guilabel:`Enable profiling until` maydoniga kerakli "
"vaqtni o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:52
msgid ""
"After the profiler is enabled on the database, users can enable it on "
"their session. To do so, toggle the :guilabel:`Enable profiling` button "
"in the :ref:`developer mode tools <developer-mode/tools>` again. By "
"default, the recommended options :guilabel:`Record sql` and "
":guilabel:`Record traces` are enabled. To learn more about the different "
"options, head over to :ref:`performance/profiling/collectors`."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasida profillashtiruvchi yoqilgandan so'ng, "
"foydalanuvchilar uni o'z sessiyalarida yoqishlari mumkin. Buning uchun "
":ref:`ishlab chiquvchi rejimi vositalarida <developer-mode/tools>` "
":guilabel:`Enable profiling` tugmasini yana bosing. Odatda, "
"tavsiya etilgan :guilabel:`Record sql` va :guilabel:`Record traces` "
"opsiyalari yoqilgan. Turli opsiyalar haqida ko'proq bilish uchun "
":ref:`performance/profiling/collectors` ga o'ting."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:60
msgid ""
"When the profiler is enabled, all the requests made to the server are "
"profiled and saved into an `ir.profile` record. Such records are grouped "
"into the current profiling session which spans from when the profiler was"
" enabled until it is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchi yoqilganda, serverga yuborilgan barcha so'rovlar "
"profillanadi va `ir.profile` yozuviga saqlanadi. Bunday yozuvlar "
"profillashtiruvchi yoqilgandan o'chirilgunicha davom etadigan joriy "
"profillashtirish sessiyasiga guruhlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:65
msgid "Odoo Online databases cannot be profiled."
msgstr "Odoo Online ma'lumotlar bazalarini profillashtirish mumkin emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:67
msgid "Enable from Python code"
msgstr "Python kodidan yoqish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:69
msgid ""
"Starting the profiler manually can be convenient to profile a specific "
"method or a part of the code. This code can be a test, a compute method, "
"the entire loading, etc."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchini qo'lda boshlash muayyan metod yoki kod qismini "
"profillashtirish uchun qulay bo'lishi mumkin. Bu kod test, hisoblash "
"metodi, to'liq yuklanish va boshqalar bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:72
msgid ""
"To start the profiler from Python code, call it as a context manager. You"
" may specify *what* you want to record through the parameters. A shortcut"
" is available for profiling test classes: :code:`self.profile()`. See "
":ref:`performance/profiling/collectors` for more information on the "
"`collectors` parameter."
msgstr ""
"Python kodidan profillashtiruvchini boshlash uchun uni kontekst menejeri "
"sifatida chaqiring. Siz parametrlar orqali *nima* yozishingizni "
"ko'rsatishingiz mumkin. Test sinflari uchun profillashtirish uchun "
"qisqartma mavjud: :code:`self.profile()`. `collectors` parametri haqida "
"ko'proq ma'lumot uchun "
":ref:`performance/profiling/collectors` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:100
msgid ""
"The profiler is called outside of the `assertQueryCount` in order to "
"catch queries made when exiting the context manager (e.g., flush)."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchi kontekst menejerdan chiqishda (masalan, flush) "
"qilingan so'rovlarni ushlab olish uchun `assertQueryCount` dan tashqarida "
"chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:106
msgid ""
"When the profiler is enabled, all executions of a test method are "
"profiled and saved into an `ir.profile` record. Such records are grouped "
"into a single profiling session. This is especially useful when using the"
" :code:`@warmup` and :code:`@users` decorators."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchi yoqilganda, test metodining barcha ijrolari "
"profillanadi va `ir.profile` yozuviga saqlanadi. Bunday yozuvlar "
"bitta profillashtirish sessiyasiga guruhlanadi. Bu ayniqsa "
":code:`@warmup` va :code:`@users` dekoratorlari ishlatilganda foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:111
msgid ""
"It can be complicated to analyze profiling results of a method that is "
"called several times because all the calls are grouped together in the "
"stack trace. Add an **execution context** as a context manager to break "
"down the results into multiple frames."
msgstr ""
"Bir necha marta chaqiriladigan metodning profillashtirish natijalarini "
"tahlil qilish murakkab bo'lishi mumkin, chunki barcha chaqiruvlar stek "
"izida birgalikda guruhlanadi. Natijalarni bir nechta kadrlarga ajratish "
"uchun **ijro kontekstini** kontekst menejeri sifatida qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:126
msgid "Analyse the results"
msgstr "Natijalarni tahlil qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:128
msgid ""
"To browse the profiling results, make sure that the :ref:`profiler is "
"enabled globally on the database <performance/profiling/enable>`, then "
"open the :ref:`developer mode tools <developer-mode/tools>` and click on "
"the button in the top-right corner of the profiling section. A list view "
"of the `ir.profile` records grouped by profiling session opens."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtirish natijalarini ko'rish uchun, "
":ref:`profillashtiruvchi ma'lumotlar bazasida global ravishda yoqilganligiga "
"<performance/profiling/enable>` ishonch hosil qiling, so'ng "
":ref:`ishlab chiquvchi rejimi vositalarini <developer-mode/tools>` oching "
"va profillashtirish bo'limining yuqori o'ng burchagidagi tugmani bosing. "
"Profillashtirish sessiyasi bo'yicha guruhlanган `ir.profile` yozuvlarining "
"ro'yxat ko'rinishi ochiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:136
msgid ""
"Each record has a clickable link that opens the speedscope results in a "
"new tab."
msgstr ""
"Har bir yozuvda yangi yorliqda speedscope natijalarini ochadigan "
"bosiladigan havola mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:141
msgid ""
"Speedscope falls out of the scope of this documentation but there are a "
"lot of tools to try: search, highlight of similar frames, zoom on frame, "
"timeline, left heavy, sandwich view..."
msgstr ""
"Speedscope ushbu hujjatlar doirasidan tashqarida, lekin sinab ko'rish "
"uchun ko'plab vositalar mavjud: qidirish, o'xshash kadrlarni ajratib "
"ko'rsatish, kadrni kattalashtirish, vaqt jadvali, left heavy, "
"sandwich ko'rinishi..."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:144
msgid ""
"Depending on the profiling options that were activated, Odoo generates "
"different view modes that you can access from the top menu."
msgstr ""
"Faollashtirilgan profillashtirish opsiyalariga qarab, Odoo yuqori "
"menyudan kirish mumkin bo'lgan turli ko'rinish rejimlarini yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:150
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Combined` view shows all the SQL queries and traces merged"
" togethers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Combined` ko'rinishi barcha SQL so'rovlar va izlarni "
"birlashtirib ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:151
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Combined no context` view shows the same result but "
"ignores the saved execution context <performance/profiling/enable>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Combined no context` ko'rinishi bir xil natijani ko'rsatadi, "
"lekin saqlangan ijro kontekstini e'tiborsiz qoldiradi "
"<performance/profiling/enable>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:153
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`sql (no gap)` view shows all the SQL queries as if they "
"were executed one after another, without any Python logic. This is useful"
" for optimizing SQL only."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`sql (no gap)` ko'rinishi barcha SQL so'rovlarni birbiri "
"ketidan bajarilgandek, hech qanday Python mantig'isiz ko'rsatadi. "
"Bu faqat SQL ni optimallashtirish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:155
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`sql (density)` view shows only all the SQL queries, "
"leaving gap between them. This can be useful to spot if eiter SQL or "
"Python code is the problem, and to identify zones in where many small "
"queries could be batched."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`sql (density)` ko'rinishi faqat barcha SQL so'rovlarni "
"ularning orasidagi bo'shliqlar bilan ko'rsatadi. Bu SQL yoki Python "
"kod muammo ekanligini aniqlash va ko'plab kichik so'rovlar partiyalanishi "
"mumkin bo'lgan zonalarni aniqlash uchun foydali bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:158
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`frames` view shows the results of only the :ref:`periodic "
"collector <performance/profiling/collectors/periodic>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`frames` ko'rinishi faqat "
":ref:`davriy kollektor <performance/profiling/collectors/periodic>` "
"natijalarini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:162
msgid ""
"Even though the profiler has been designed to be as light as possible, it"
" can still impact performance, especially when using the :ref:`Sync "
"collector <performance/profiling/collectors/sync>`. Keep that in mind "
"when analyzing speedscope results."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchi iloji boricha yengil bo'lishi uchun mo'ljallangan "
"bo'lsa-da, u ishlash samaradorligiga ta'sir qilishi mumkin, ayniqsa "
":ref:`Sync kollektori <performance/profiling/collectors/sync>` "
"ishlatilganda. Speedscope natijalarini tahlil qilishda buni yodda "
"tuting."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:169
msgid "Collectors"
msgstr "Kollektorlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:171
msgid ""
"Whereas the profiler is about the *when* of profiling, the collectors "
"take care of the *what*."
msgstr ""
"Profillashtiruvchi profillashtirish *qachon* sodir bo'lishi haqida "
"bo'lsa, kollektorlar *nima* yig'ilishi haqida g'amxo'rlik qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:173
msgid ""
"Each collector specializes in collecting profiling data in its own format"
" and manner. They can be individually enabled from the user interface "
"through their dedicated toggle button in the :ref:`developer mode tools "
"<developer-mode/tools>`, or from Python code through their key or class."
msgstr ""
"Har bir kollektor profillashtirish ma'lumotlarini o'z formatida va "
"tarzida yig'ishda ixtisoslashadi. Ularni alohida-alohida foydalanuvchi "
"interfeysidan :ref:`ishlab chiquvchi rejimi vositalaridagi "
"<developer-mode/tools>` maxsus almashtirish tugmasi orqali yoki Python "
"kodidan ularning kaliti yoki sinfi orqali yoqish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/performance.rst:178
