#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/reports.rst:82
msgid "Translatable Templates"
msgstr "Tarjima qilinadigan shablonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/reports.rst:84
msgid ""
"If you wish to translate reports (to the language of a partner, for "
"example), you need to define two templates:"
msgstr ""
"Hisobotlarni tarjima qilishni xohlasangiz (masalan, sherik tiliga), "
