"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_tour/static/src/tour_service/tour_utils.js#L426>`_ "
"foydalanishingiz yoki o'zingizning shaxsiylashtirilgan qadamingizni yozishingiz mumkin."

