msgid "Here are some example of steps:"
msgstr "Mana bir nechta qadam misollari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:408
msgid "Here are some possible arguments for your personalized steps:"
msgstr "Mana shaxsiylashtirilgan qadamlaringiz uchun ba'zi mumkin bo'lgan argumentlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:410
msgid ""
"**trigger**: Required, Selector/element to ``run`` an action on. The tour"
" will wait until the element exists and is visible before ``run``-ing the"
" action *on it*."
msgstr ""
"**trigger**: Majburiy, ``run`` amali bajariladigan selektor/element. Tur "
"element mavjud va ko'rinib turguncha uni *ustida* amalni ``run`` qilishdan "
"oldin kutadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:413
msgid ""
"**run**: Optional, Action to perform on the *trigger* element. If no "
"``run``, no action."
msgstr ""
"**run**: Ixtiyoriy, *trigger* elementda bajariladigan amal. ``run`` bo'lmasa, "
"hech qanday amal bajarilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:416
msgid "The action can be:"
msgstr "Amal quyidagicha bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:418
msgid ""
"A function, asynchronous, executed with the trigger's ``Tip`` as context "
"(``this``) and the action helpers as parameter."
msgstr ""
"Triggerning ``Tip`` ni kontekst (``this``) sifatida va amal yordamchilarini "
"parametr sifatida ishlatib bajariladigan asinxron funksiya."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:420
msgid ""
"The name of one of the action helpers, which will be run on the trigger "
"element:"
msgstr ""
"Trigger elementda ishga tushiriladigan amal yordamchilaridan birining nomi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:426
msgid "``check``"
msgstr "``check``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:426
msgid ""
"Ensures that the **trigger** element is checked. This helper is intended "
"for `<input[type=checkbox]>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementning belgilanganligini ta'minlaydi. Bu yordamchi faqat "
"`<input[type=checkbox]>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:429
msgid "``clear``"
msgstr "``clear``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:429
msgid ""
"Clears the value of the **trigger** element. This helper is intended for "
"`<input>` or `<textarea>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementning qiymatini tozalaydi. Bu yordamchi faqat `<input>` "
"yoki `<textarea>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:432
msgid "``click``"
msgstr "``click``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:432
msgid ""
"Clicks the **trigger** element, performing all the relevant intermediate "
"events."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementini bosadi, barcha tegishli oraliq hodisalarni bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:434
msgid "``dblclick``,"
msgstr "``dblclick``,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:435
msgid "Same as ``click`` with two repetitions."
msgstr "Ikki takrorlash bilan ``click`` ga o'xshash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:436
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`drag_and_drop {target}`"
msgstr ":samp:`drag_and_drop {target}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:437
msgid "Simulates the dragging of the **trigger** element over to the ``target``."
msgstr "**trigger** elementni ``target`` ga sudrab o'tishni simulatsiya qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:438
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`edit {content}`"
msgstr ":samp:`edit {content}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:439
msgid "``clear`` the element and then ``fill`` the ``content``."
msgstr "Elementni ``clear`` qiling va keyin ``content`` bilan ``fill`` qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:440
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`editor {content}`"
msgstr ":samp:`editor {content}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:441
msgid ""
"Focus the **trigger** element (wysiwyg) and then ``press`` the "
"``content``."
msgstr "**trigger** elementini (wysiwyg) fokusga oling va keyin ``content`` ni ``press`` qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:443
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`fill {content}`"
msgstr ":samp:`fill {content}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:443
msgid ""
"Focus the **trigger** element and then ``press`` the ``content``. This "
"helper is intended for `<input>` or `<textarea>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementini fokusga oling va keyin ``content`` ni ``press`` qiling. "
"Bu yordamchi faqat `<input>` yoki `<textarea>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:445
msgid "``hover``"
msgstr "``hover``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:446
msgid "Performs a hover sequence on the **trigger** element."
msgstr "**trigger** elementida hover ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:447
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`press {content}`"
msgstr ":samp:`press {content}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:448
msgid "Performs a keyboard event sequence."
msgstr "Klaviatura hodisalari ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:450
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`range {content}`"
msgstr ":samp:`range {content}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:450
msgid ""
"Focus the **trigger** element and set ``content`` as value. This helper "
"is intended for `<input[type=range]>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementini fokusga oling va ``content`` ni qiymat sifatida o'rnating. "
"Bu yordamchi faqat `<input[type=range]>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:453
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`select {value}`"
msgstr ":samp:`select {value}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:453
msgid ""
"Performs a selection event sequence on **trigger** element. Select the "
"option by its ``value``. This helper is intended for `<select>` elements "
"only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementida tanlov hodisalari ketma-ketligini bajaradi. Opsiyani "
"``value`` bo'yicha tanlaydi. Bu yordamchi faqat `<select>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:456
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`selectByIndex {index}`"
msgstr ":samp:`selectByIndex {index}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:456
msgid ""
"Same as ``select`` but select the option by its ``index``. Note that "
"first option has index 0."
msgstr ""
"``select`` ga o'xshash, ammo opsiyani ``index`` bo'yicha tanlaydi. "
"Birinchi opsiya 0 indeksiga ega ekanligini unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:458
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":samp:`selectByLabel {label}`"
msgstr ":samp:`selectByLabel {label}`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:459
msgid "Same as ``select`` but select the option by its ``label``."
msgstr "``select`` ga o'xshash, ammo opsiyani ``label`` bo'yicha tanlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:463
msgid "``uncheck``"
msgstr "``uncheck``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:461
msgid ""
"Ensures that the **trigger** element is unchecked. This helper is "
"intended for `<input[type=checkbox]>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"**trigger** elementning belgilanmaganligini ta'minlaydi. Bu yordamchi faqat "
"`<input[type=checkbox]>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:465
msgid ""
"**isActive**: Optional, Activates the step only if all conditions of "
"isActive array are met. - Browser is in either **desktop** or **mobile** "
"mode. - The tour concerns either **community** or **enterprise** edition."
" - The tour is run in either **auto** (runbot) or **manual** (onboarding)"
" mode."
msgstr ""
"**isActive**: Ixtiyoriy, isActive massivining barcha shartlari bajarilgan "
"bo'lsagina qadamni faollashtiradi. - Brauzer **desktop** yoki **mobile** "
"rejimida. - Tur **community** yoki **enterprise** nashrini bog'laydi. "
"- Tur **auto** (runbot) yoki **manual** (onboarding) rejimida ishlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:470
msgid ""
"**tooltipPosition**: Optional, ``\"top\"``, ``\"right\"``, "
"``\"bottom\"``, or ``\"left\"``. Where to position the tooltip relative "
"to the **target** when running interactive tours."
msgstr ""
"**tooltipPosition**: Ixtiyoriy, ``\"top\"``, ``\"right\"``, "
"``\"bottom\"``, yoki ``\"left\"``. Interaktiv turlarni ishga tushirishda "
"**target** ga nisbatan tooltip ni qayerda joylashtirish kerakligi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:473
msgid ""
"**content**: Optional but recommended, the content of the tooltip in "
"interactive tours, also logged to the console so very useful to trace and"
" debug automated tours."
msgstr ""
"**content**: Ixtiyoriy, ammo tavsiya etiladi, interaktiv turlardagi tooltip "
"mazmuni, shuningdek konsolga qayd etiladi, shuning uchun avtomatlashtirilgan "
"turlarni kuzatish va nosozliklarni tuzatish uchun juda foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:476
msgid ""
"**timeout**: How long to wait until the step can ``run``, in "
"milliseconds, 10000 (10 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"**timeout**: Qadam ``run`` qilishi uchun qancha vaqt kutish kerakligi, "
"millisekundlarda, 10000 (10 soniya)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:481
msgid ""
"The last step(s) of a tour should always return the client to a "
"\"stable\" state (e.g. no ongoing editions) and ensure all side-effects "
"(network requests) have finished running to avoid race conditions or "
"errors during teardown."
msgstr ""
"Turning so'nggi qadami(lari) har doim mijozni \"barqaror\" holatga (masalan, "
"davom etayotgan tahrirlashlar yo'q) qaytarishi va o'chirish vaqtida poygali "
"holat yoki xatoliklarning oldini olish uchun barcha yon ta'sirlar (tarmoq "
"so'rovlari) bajarishni tugatganligini ta'minlashi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/backend/testing.rst:487
msgid "`jQuery documentation about find <https://api.jquery.com/find/>`_"
msgstr "`find haqida jQuery hujjatlari <https://api.jquery.com/find/>`_"

