msgid ""
"This command is the default one: you can omit it, and it will be chosen "
"anyway."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq sukut bo'yicha: siz uni o'tkazib yuborishingiz mumkin va u baribir tanlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:85
msgid ""
"database(s) used when installing or updating modules. Providing a comma-"
"separated list restrict access to databases provided in list."
msgstr ""
"modullarni o'rnatish yoki yangilashda ishlatiladigan ma'lumotlar bazasi(lari). "
"Vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxat taqdim etish ro'yxatda ko'rsatilgan "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga kirishni cheklaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:89
msgid ""
"For advanced database options, take a look :ref:`below "
"<reference/cmdline/server/database>`."
msgstr ""
"Kengaytirilgan ma'lumotlar bazasi imkoniyatlari uchun :ref:`quyiga "
"<reference/cmdline/server/database>` qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:93
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of modules to install before running the server "
"(requires :option:`-d`)."
msgstr ""
"serverni ishga tushirishdan oldin o'rnatish uchun vergul bilan ajratilgan "
"modullar ro'yxati (:option:`-d` talab qiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:97
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of modules to update before running the server. Use "
"``all`` for all modules. (requires :option:`-d`)."
msgstr ""
"serverni ishga tushirishdan oldin yangilash uchun vergul bilan ajratilgan "
"modullar ro'yxati. Barcha modullar uchun ``all`` dan foydalaning. "
"(:option:`-d` talab qiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:102
msgid ""
"A comma-separated list of modules to reinitialize before starting the "
"server. (requires :option:`-d`)."
msgstr ""
"Serverni ishga tushirishdan oldin qayta ishga tushirish uchun vergul bilan "
"ajratilgan modullar ro'yxati. (:option:`-d` talab qiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:105
msgid ""
"The reinitialization is similar to a simple upgrade without executing any"
" upgrade script. It loads data in ``init`` mode instead of ``update`` "
"mode, primarily affecting records marked as ``'noupdate'``. All modules "
"that depend directly or indirectly on the specified ones will also be "
"reinitialized."
msgstr ""
"Qayta ishga tushirish hech qanday yangilash skriptini bajarmasdan oddiy "
"yangilashga o'xshaydi. U ma'lumotlarni ``update`` rejimi o'rniga ``init`` "
"rejimida yuklaydi, asosan ``'noupdate'`` sifatida belgilangan yozuvlarga "
"ta'sir qiladi. Ko'rsatilganlarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri yoki bilvosita bog'liq "
"barcha modullar ham qayta ishga tushiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:109
msgid ""
"This option is intended for debugging or development purposes only. **Do "
"not use it with a production database.**"
msgstr ""
"Bu imkoniyat faqat nosozliklarni tuzatish yoki ishlab chiqish maqsadlari "
"uchun mo'ljallangan. **Uni ishlab chiqarish ma'lumotlar bazasi bilan "
"ishlatmang.**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:114
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of directories in which modules are stored. These "
"directories are scanned for modules."
msgstr ""
"modullar saqlanadigan vergul bilan ajratilgan kataloglar ro'yxati. Bu "
"kataloglar modullar uchun skanlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:121
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of directories from which additional upgrade scripts"
" are loaded."
msgstr ""
"qo'shimcha yangilash skriptlari yuklanadigan vergul bilan ajratilgan "
"kataloglar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:126
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of paths to upgrade scripts. The scripts are run "
"before loading base module when an upgrade of any module is requested. "
"This is useful to perform some actions during custom modules upgrade "
"after a major upgrade."
msgstr ""
"yangilash skriptlariga yo'llar bo'yicha vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxat. "
"Skriptlar har qanday modulni yangilash so'ralganda asosiy modulni yuklamasdan "
"oldin ishga tushiriladi. Bu katta yangilashdan keyin maxsus modullarni "
"yangilash davomida ba'zi harakatlarni bajarish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:133
msgid ""
"list of server-wide modules to load. Those modules are supposed to "
"provide features not necessarily tied to a particular database. This is "
"in contrast to modules that are always bound to a specific database when "
"they are installed (i.e. the majority of Odoo addons). Default is "
"``base,web``."
msgstr ""
"yuklash uchun server miqyosidagi modullar ro'yxati. Bu modullar muayyan "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga bog'liq bo'lmagan funksionalliklarni taqdim etishi "
"kerak. Bu o'rnatilganda har doim muayyan ma'lumotlar bazasiga bog'liq "
"bo'lgan modullarga (ya'ni Odoo qo'shimchalarining aksariyati) ziddir. "
"Sukut bo'yicha ``base,web``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:140
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"path to an alternate :ref:`configuration file "
"<reference/cmdline/config>`. If not defined, Odoo checks ``ODOO_RC`` "
"environmental variable and default location :file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc`. See "
"configuration file section :ref:`below <reference/cmdline/config>`."
msgstr ""
"muqobil :ref:`konfiguratsiya fayliga <reference/cmdline/config>` yo'l. "
"Aniqllanmagan bo'lsa, Odoo ``ODOO_RC`` muhit o'zgaruvchisini va standart "
"joyni :file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc` tekshiradi. Konfiguratsiya fayli bo'limi "
":ref:`quyiga <reference/cmdline/config>` qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:147
msgid ""
"directory path where to store Odoo data (eg. filestore, sessions). If not"
" specified, Odoo will fallback to a predefined path. On Unix systems its "
"one defined in ``$XDG_DATA_HOME`` environmental variable or "
":file:`~/.local/share/Odoo` or :file:`/var/lib/Odoo`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ma'lumotlarini (masalan, fayl do'koni, seanslar) saqlash uchun "
"katalog yo'li. Ko'rsatilmagan bo'lsa, Odoo oldindan belgilangan yo'lga "
"qaytadi. Unix tizimlarida u ``$XDG_DATA_HOME`` muhit o'zgaruvchisida yoki "
":file:`~/.local/share/Odoo` yoki :file:`/var/lib/Odoo` da aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:155
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"saves the server configuration to the current configuration file "
"(:file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc` by default, and can be overridden using "
":option:`-c`)."
msgstr ""
"server konfiguratsiyasini joriy konfiguratsiya fayliga saqlaydi "
"(sukut bo'yicha :file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc`, va :option:`-c` yordamida "
"bekor qilinishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:161
msgid "install demo data in new databases."
msgstr "yangi ma'lumotlar bazalariga demo ma'lumotlarini o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:165
msgid ""
"don't install demo data nor in new databases nor when installing new "
"modules in a database that uses demo data, this is the default."
msgstr ""
"na yangi ma'lumotlar bazalariga na demo ma'lumotlardan foydalanadigan "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga yangi modullarni o'rnatishda demo ma'lumotlarni "
"o'rnatmang, bu sukut bo'yicha."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:170
msgid ""
"skips auto-installing modules when a new module installation is "
"requested. This option is useful for development. It serves to check if "
"the installed modules do not indirectly depend on auto-installed modules."
msgstr ""
"yangi modul o'rnatish so'ralganda modullarni avtomatik o'rnatishni o'tkazib "
"yuboradi. Bu imkoniyat ishlab chiqish uchun foydali. U o'rnatilgan modullar "
"avtomatik o'rnatilgan modullarga bilvosita bog'liq emasligini tekshirishga xizmat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:176
msgid "path to a file where the server pid will be stored"
msgstr "server pid saqlanadigan faylga yo'l"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:180
msgid "stops the server after its initialization."
msgstr "initsializatsiyadan so'ng serverni to'xtatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:184
msgid "Absolute path to the GeoIP City database file."
msgstr "GeoIP Shahar ma'lumotlar bazasi fayliga mutlaq yo'l."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:188
msgid "Absolute path to the GeoIP Country database file."
msgstr "GeoIP Mamlakat ma'lumotlar bazasi fayliga mutlaq yo'l."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:194
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "Sinov"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:198
msgid "runs tests after module installation"
msgstr "modul o'rnatilgandan keyin sinovlarni ishga tushiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:202
msgid "runs a python test file"
msgstr "python sinov faylini ishga tushiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:206
msgid ""
"Comma-separated list of specs to filter which tests to execute. Enable "
"unit tests if set."
msgstr ""
"Qaysi sinovlarni bajarish kerakligini filtrlash uchun spesifikatsiyalar "
"vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa birlik sinovlarini yoqadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:208
msgid "Example: `--test-tags :TestClass.test_func,/test_module,external`"
msgstr "Misol: `--test-tags :TestClass.test_func,/test_module,external`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:210
msgid ""
"The `-` specifies if we want to include or exclude tests matching this "
"spec."
msgstr "``-`` bu spesifikatsiyaga mos sinovlarni kiritishni yoki chiqarib tashlashni xohlayotganimizni belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:211
msgid ""
"The tag will match tags added on a class with a "
":func:`~odoo.tests.common.tagged` decorator (all :ref:`test classes "
"<reference/testing>` have `standard` and `at_install` tags until "
"explicitly removed, see the decorator documentation)."
msgstr ""
"Teg :func:`~odoo.tests.common.tagged` dekoratori bilan sinfga qo'shilgan "
"teglar bilan mos keladi (barcha :ref:`sinov sinflari <reference/testing>` "
"aniq olib tashlanguncha `standard` va `at_install` teglarga ega, dekorator "
"hujjatlarini qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:214
msgid "`*` will match all tags."
msgstr "`*` barcha teglar bilan mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:215
msgid "If tag is omitted on include mode, its value is `standard`."
msgstr "Agar kiritish rejimida teg o'tkazib yuborilsa, uning qiymati `standard`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:216
msgid "If tag is omitted on exclude mode, its value is `*`."
msgstr "Agar chiqarib tashlash rejimida teg o'tkazib yuborilsa, uning qiymati `*`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:217
msgid ""
"The module, class, and method will respectively match the module name, "
"test class name and test method name."
msgstr ""
"Modul, sinf va metod mos ravishda modul nomi, sinov sinfi nomi va sinov "
"metodi nomiga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:219
msgid ""
"Filtering and executing the tests happens twice: right after each module "
"installation/update and at the end of the modules loading. At each stage "
"tests are filtered by `--test-tags` specs and additionally by dynamic "
"specs `at_install` and `post_install` correspondingly."
msgstr ""
"Sinovlarni filtrlash va bajarish ikki marta sodir bo'ladi: har bir modul "
"o'rnatish/yangilashdan keyin darhol va modullarni yuklash oxirida. Har bir "
"bosqichda sinovlar `--test-tags` spesifikatsiyalari va qo'shimcha ravishda "
"mos ravishda dinamik spesifikatsiyalar `at_install` va `post_install` "
"orqali filtrlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:227
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Specify directory where to write screenshots when an HttpCase.browser_js "
"test fails. It defaults to :file:`/tmp/odoo_tests/{db_name}/screenshots`"
msgstr ""
"HttpCase.browser_js sinovi muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lganda skrinshot yozish uchun "
"katalogni ko'rsating. Sukut bo'yicha :file:`/tmp/odoo_tests/{db_name}/screenshots`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:232
msgid ""
"Enable screencasts and specify directory where to write screencasts "
"files. The ``ffmpeg`` utility needs to be installed to encode frames into"
" a video file. Otherwise frames will be kept instead of the video file."
msgstr ""
"Screencastlarni yoqing va screencast fayllarini yozish uchun katalogni "
"ko'rsating. Kadrlarni video fayliga kodlash uchun ``ffmpeg`` yordam dasturi "
"o'rnatilgan bo'lishi kerak. Aks holda video fayl o'rniga kadrlar saqlanib qoladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:239
#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:197
msgid "Database"
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar bazasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:243
msgid "database username, used to connect to PostgreSQL."
msgstr "ma'lumotlar bazasi foydalanuvchi nomi, PostgreSQL ga ulanish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:247
msgid "database password, if using `password authentication`_."
msgstr "`parol autentifikatsiyasi`_ dan foydalanilganda ma'lumotlar bazasi paroli."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:251
msgid "host for the database server"
msgstr "ma'lumotlar bazasi serveri uchun host"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:253
msgid "``localhost`` on Windows"
msgstr "Windows da ``localhost``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:254
msgid "UNIX socket otherwise"
msgstr "Aks holda UNIX soketi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:258
msgid "port the database listens on, defaults to 5432"
msgstr "ma'lumotlar bazasi tinglayotgan port, sukut bo'yicha 5432"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:262
msgid "host for the replica database server, disabled when not set / empty"
msgstr "replika ma'lumotlar bazasi serveri uchun host, o'rnatilmagan / bo'sh bo'lganda o'chirilgan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:266
msgid "the port the replica database listens on, defaults to :option:`--db_port`"
msgstr "replika ma'lumotlar bazasi tinglayotgan port, sukut bo'yicha :option:`--db_port`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:270
msgid ""
"hides databases that do not match ``<filter>`` for the Web UI. The filter"
" is a `regular expression`_, with the additions that:"
msgstr ""
"Veb UI uchun ``<filter>`` ga mos kelmaydigan ma'lumotlar bazalarini yashiradi. "
"Filtr `muntazam ifoda`_, quyidagi qo'shimchalar bilan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:273
msgid "``%h`` is replaced by the whole hostname the request is made on."
msgstr "``%h`` so'rov amalga oshiriladigan to'liq hostname bilan almashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:274
#, python-format
msgid ""
"``%d`` is replaced by the subdomain the request is made on, with the "
"exception of ``www`` (so domain ``odoo.com`` and ``www.odoo.com`` both "
"match the database ``odoo``)."
msgstr ""
"``%d`` ``www`` istisnosidan tashqari so'rov amalga oshiriladigan subdomen bilan "
"almashtiriladi (shuning uchun ``odoo.com`` va ``www.odoo.com`` domenlarining "
"ikkalasi ham ``odoo`` ma'lumotlar bazasiga mos keladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:278
#, python-format
msgid ""
"These operations are case sensitive. Add option ``(?i)`` to match all "
"databases (so domain ``odoo.com`` using ``(?i)%d`` matches the database "
"``Odoo``)."
msgstr ""
"Bu operatsiyalar katta-kichik harfga sezgir. Barcha ma'lumotlar bazalariga "
"mos kelish uchun ``(?i)`` opsiyasini qo'shing (shunday qilib ``(?i)%d`` "
"bilan ``odoo.com`` domeni ``Odoo`` ma'lumotlar bazasiga mos keladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:282
msgid ""
"Since version 11, it's also possible to restrict access to a given "
"database listen by using the --database parameter and specifying a comma-"
"separated list of databases"
msgstr ""
"11-versiyadan boshlab, --database parametridan foydalanib va ma'lumotlar "
"bazalarining vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxatini ko'rsatib, muayyan ma'lumotlar "
"bazasiga kirishni cheklash ham mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:286
msgid ""
"When combining the two parameters, db-filter supersedes the comma-"
"separated database list for restricting database list, while the comma-"
"separated list is used for performing requested operations like upgrade "
"of modules."
msgstr ""
"Ikki parametrni birlashtirish vaqtida, db-filter ma'lumotlar bazasi ro'yxatini "
"cheklash uchun vergul bilan ajratilgan ma'lumotlar bazasi ro'yxatidan ustunlik "
"qiladi, vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxat esa modullarni yangilash kabi so'ralgan "
"operatsiyalarni bajarish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:294
msgid "Restrict access to databases whose name starts with 11"
msgstr "Nomi 11 bilan boshlanadigan ma'lumotlar bazalariga kirishni cheklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:300
msgid ""
"Restrict access to only two databases, 11firstdatabase and "
"11seconddatabase"
msgstr "Faqat ikkita ma'lumotlar bazasiga - 11firstdatabase va 11seconddatabase - kirishni cheklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:306
msgid ""
"Restrict access to only two databases, 11firstdatabase and "
"11seconddatabase, and update base module on one database: "
"11firstdatabase. If database 11seconddatabase doesn't exist, the database"
" is created and base modules is installed"
msgstr ""
"Faqat ikkita ma'lumotlar bazasiga - 11firstdatabase va 11seconddatabase - "
"kirishni cheklash va bitta ma'lumotlar bazasida asosiy modulni yangilash: "
"11firstdatabase. Agar 11seconddatabase ma'lumotlar bazasi mavjud bo'lmasa, "
"ma'lumotlar bazasi yaratiladi va asosiy modullar o'rnatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:315
msgid ""
"Restrict access to databases whose name starts with 11, and update base "
"module on one database: 11firstdatabase. If database 11seconddatabase "
"doesn't exist, the database is created and base modules is installed"
msgstr ""
"Nomi 11 bilan boshlanadigan ma'lumotlar bazalariga kirishni cheklash va bitta "
"ma'lumotlar bazasida asosiy modulni yangilash: 11firstdatabase. Agar "
"11seconddatabase ma'lumotlar bazasi mavjud bo'lmasa, ma'lumotlar bazasi "
"yaratiladi va asosiy modullar o'rnatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:320
msgid ""
"This option does not affect cron workers, if no --database is given, cron"
" workers will run on every available database"
msgstr ""
"Bu parametr cron ishchilarga ta'sir qilmaydi, agar --database berilmasa, "
"cron ishchilar har bir mavjud ma'lumotlar bazasida ishlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:324
msgid ""
"when creating new databases from the database-management screens, use the"
" specified `template database`_. Defaults to ``template0``."
msgstr ""
"ma'lumotlar bazasini boshqarish ekranlaridan yangi ma'lumotlar bazalarini "
"yaratishda ko'rsatilgan `shablon ma'lumotlar bazasi`_ dan foydalaning. "
"Sukut bo'yicha ``template0``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:329
msgid ""
"Path to the PostgreSQL binaries that are used by the database manager to "
"dump and restore databases. You have to specify this option only if these"
" binaries are located in a non-standard directory."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasi menejerida ma'lumotlar bazalarini dump qilish va tiklash "
"uchun ishlatiladigan PostgreSQL ikkilik fayllariga yo'l. Bu ikkilik fayllar "
"standart bo'lmagan katalogda joylashganda faqat bu parametrni ko'rsatishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:335
msgid "Suppresses the ability to list databases available on the system"
msgstr "Tizimda mavjud bo'lgan ma'lumotlar bazalarini ro'yxatga olish imkoniyatini bostiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:339
msgid ""
"Control the SSL security of the connection between Odoo and PostgreSQL. "
"Value should be one of 'disable', 'allow', 'prefer', 'require', 'verify-"
"ca' or 'verify-full' Default value is 'prefer'"
msgstr ""
"Odoo va PostgreSQL o'rtasidagi ulanishning SSL xavfsizligini boshqaring. "
"Qiymat 'disable', 'allow', 'prefer', 'require', 'verify-ca' yoki 'verify-full' "
"dan biri bo'lishi kerak. Sukut bo'yicha qiymat 'prefer'"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:346
msgid "Try to enable the unaccent extension when creating new databases"
msgstr "Yangi ma'lumotlar bazalarini yaratishda unaccent kengaytmasini yoqishga urining"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:351
msgid "Emails"
msgstr "Elektron pochta"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:355
msgid "Email address used as <FROM> when Odoo needs to send mails"
msgstr "Odoo xat yuborishi kerak bo'lganda <FROM> sifatida ishlatiladigan elektron pochta manzili"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:359
msgid ""
"Define which email address the SMTP configuration will apply to. The "
"field can be a domain name or an entire email address, or it can remain "
"empty. If the sender's email address does not match this set filter, then"
" the email will be encapsulated using a combination of the two system "
"parameters: ``mail.default.from`` and ``mail.catchall.domain``. For "
"example, \"Admin\" <admin\\@example.com> => \"Admin\" "
"<notifications\\@mycompany.com>."
msgstr ""
"SMTP konfiguratsiyasi qo'llaniladigan elektron pochta manzilini aniqlang. "
"Maydon domen nomi yoki to'liq elektron pochta manzili bo'lishi yoki bo'sh "
"qolishi mumkin. Agar jo'natuvchining elektron pochta manzili bu o'rnatilgan "
"filtrga mos kelmasa, elektron pochta ikkita tizim parametrining kombinatsiyasi "
"yordamida qamrab olinadi: ``mail.default.from`` va ``mail.catchall.domain``. "
"Masalan, \"Admin\" <admin\\@example.com> => \"Admin\" "
"<notifications\\@mycompany.com>."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:367
msgid "Address of the SMTP server to connect to in order to send mails"
msgstr "Xat yuborish uchun ulanadigan SMTP server manzili"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:373
msgid "If set, odoo should use SSL/STARTSSL SMTP connections"
msgstr "O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, odoo SSL/STARTSSL SMTP ulanishlaridan foydalanishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:377
msgid "Username to connect to the SMTP server"
msgstr "SMTP serveriga ulanish uchun foydalanuvchi nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:381
msgid "Password to connect to the SMTP server"
msgstr "SMTP serveriga ulanish uchun parol"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:385
msgid ""
"An SSL certificate is to be used for authentication. If set, then `smtp-"
"ssl-private-key` is required."
msgstr ""
"Autentifikatsiya uchun SSL sertifikatidan foydalaniladi. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, "
"`smtp-ssl-private-key` talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:390
msgid ""
"An SSL private key is used for authentication. If set, then `smtp-ssl-"
"certificate` is required."
msgstr ""
"Autentifikatsiya uchun SSL shaxsiy kalitidan foydalaniladi. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, "
"`smtp-ssl-certificate` talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:395
msgid "Internationalisation"
msgstr "Xalqarolashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:399
msgid ""
"specifies the languages (separated by commas) for the translations you "
"want to be loaded"
msgstr ""
"yuklanishini xohlaydigan tarjimalar uchun tillarni (vergul bilan ajratilgan) ko'rsatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:404
msgid ""
"overwrites existing translation terms on updating a module or importing a"
" CSV or a PO file."
msgstr ""
"modulni yangilash yoki CSV yoki PO faylini import qilishda mavjud tarjima "
"atamalarini qayta yozadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:410
msgid "Advanced Options"
msgstr "Kengaytirilgan imkoniyatlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:415
msgid "Developer features"
msgstr "Ishlab chiquvchi xususiyatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:419
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of features. For development purposes only. Do not "
"use it in production. Possible features are:"
msgstr ""
"vergul bilan ajratilgan xususiyatlar ro'yxati. Faqat ishlab chiqish maqsadlari "
"uchun. Ishlab chiqarishda foydalanmang. Mumkin bo'lgan xususiyatlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:422
msgid "``all``: alias for xml,reload,qweb,access"
msgstr "``all``: xml,reload,qweb,access uchun taxallus"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:424
msgid ""
"``xml``: read QWeb template from xml file directly instead of database. "
"Once a template has been modified in database, it will be not be read "
"from the xml file until the next update/init. Particularly, templates are"
" not translated on using this option."
msgstr ""
"``xml``: QWeb shablonini ma'lumotlar bazasi o'rniga xml fayldan bevosita o'qish. "
"Shablon ma'lumotlar bazasida o'zgartirilgandan so'ng, u keyingi update/init "
"gacha xml fayldan o'qilmaydi. Xususan, bu opsiyadan foydalanishda shablonlar "
"tarjima qilinmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:429
msgid ""
"``reload``: restart server when python file are updated (may not be "
"detected depending on the text editor used)"
msgstr ""
"``reload``: python fayl yangilanganda serverni qayta ishga tushirish "
"(ishlatiladigan matn muharririga qarab aniqlanmasligi mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:432
msgid ""
"``qweb``: break in the evaluation of QWeb template when a node contains "
"``t-debug='debugger'``"
msgstr ""
"``qweb``: tugun ``t-debug='debugger'`` ni o'z ichiga olganda QWeb shablonini "
"baholashda to'xtatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:434
msgid ""
"``werkzeug``: display the full traceback on the frontend page in case of "
"exception"
msgstr ""
"``werkzeug``: istisno hollatida frontend sahifasida to'liq izni ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:436
msgid ""
"``replica``: simulate :option:`--db_replica_host` but connect to the same"
" datbase server as :option:`--db_host`, this makes it possible to test "
"read-only features without the need to set up a replicated database."
msgstr ""
"``replica``: :option:`--db_replica_host` ni simulatsiya qilish, ammo "
":option:`--db_host` bilan bir xil ma'lumotlar bazasi serveriga ulanish, bu "
"repliklangan ma'lumotlar bazasini sozlash zaruratisiz faqat o'qish "
"xususiyatlarini sinab ko'rish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:440
msgid ""
"``access``: log the traceback next to the AccessError when it results in "
"a 403 - Forbidden HTTP response."
msgstr ""
"``access``: 403 - Forbidden HTTP javobiga olib kelganda AccessError yonida "
"izni qayd etish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:447
#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:102
msgid "HTTP"
msgstr "HTTP"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:451
msgid ""
"do not start the HTTP or long-polling workers (may still start :ref:`cron"
" <reference/actions/cron>` workers)"
msgstr ""
"HTTP yoki uzoq so'rovlar ishchilarini ishga tushirmang (:ref:`cron "
"<reference/actions/cron>` ishchilarini baribir ishga tushirishi mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:454
msgid ""
"has no effect if :option:`--test-enable` is set, as tests require an "
"accessible HTTP server"
msgstr ""
"agar :option:`--test-enable` o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, ta'siri yo'q, chunki "
"sinovlar kirish mumkin bo'lgan HTTP serverni talab qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:459
msgid ""
"TCP/IP address on which the HTTP server listens, defaults to ``0.0.0.0`` "
"(all addresses)"
msgstr ""
"HTTP server tinglayotgan TCP/IP manzili, sukut bo'yicha ``0.0.0.0`` (barcha manzillar)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:465
msgid "Port on which the HTTP server listens, defaults to 8069."
msgstr "HTTP server tinglayotgan port, sukut bo'yicha 8069."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:469
msgid ""
"TCP port for websocket connections in multiprocessing or gevent mode, "
"defaults to 8072. Not used in default (threaded) mode."
msgstr ""
"Ko'p jarayonli yoki gevent rejimida websocket ulanishlari uchun TCP port, "
"sukut bo'yicha 8072. Sukut bo'yicha (ipli) rejimda ishlatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:474
msgid ""
"enables the use of ``X-Forwarded-*`` headers through `Werkzeug's proxy "
"support`_."
msgstr ""
"`Werkzeug proksi qo'llab-quvvatlash`_ orqali ``X-Forwarded-*`` sarlavhalaridan "
"foydalanishni yoqadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:477
msgid ""
"It ignores all ``X-Forwarded-*`` headers in case ``X-Forwarded-Host`` is "
"missing from the request."
msgstr ""
"``X-Forwarded-Host`` so'rovda yo'q bo'lsa, barcha ``X-Forwarded-*`` "
"sarlavhalarini e'tiborsiz qoldiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:480
msgid ""
"It always gets the real IP from the last entry of the ``X-Forwarded-For``"
" chain. Configure your web server accordingly using directives such as "
"nginx's `set_real_ip_from "
"<https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_realip_module.html>`_ in case "
"there are other trusted proxies along the chain that must be ignored."
msgstr ""
"U har doim ``X-Forwarded-For`` zanjirining so'nggi yozuvidan haqiqiy IP ni "
"oladi. E'tiborga olinmasligi kerak bo'lgan zanjir bo'ylab boshqa ishonchli "
"proksilar mavjud bo'lsa, nginx ning `set_real_ip_from "
"<https://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_realip_module.html>`_ kabi "
"direktivalar yordamida veb-serveringizni mos ravishda sozlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:485
msgid ""
"``X-Forwarded-Proto`` and ``X-Forwarded-Host`` are used to update the "
"request root URL, which in turn is used to update the ``web.base.url`` "
"system parameter upon a successful admin authentication. This system "
"parameter is used to generate all links for the current database; see "
":ref:`domain-name/web-base-url`."
msgstr ""
"``X-Forwarded-Proto`` va ``X-Forwarded-Host`` so'rov ildiz URL manzilini "
"yangilash uchun ishlatiladi, bu o'z navbatida muvaffaqiyatli admin "
"autentifikatsiyasida ``web.base.url`` tizim parametrini yangilash uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Bu tizim parametri joriy ma'lumotlar bazasi uchun barcha "
"havolalarni yaratish uchun ishlatiladi; :ref:`domain-name/web-base-url` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:492
msgid "proxy mode *must not* be enabled outside of a reverse proxy scenario"
msgstr "proksi rejimi teskari proksi stsenariyidan tashqarida yoqilmasligi *kerak*"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:497
msgid ""
"delegates serving attachments files to the static web server and sets "
"both ``X-Sendfile`` (apache) and ``X-Accel-*`` (nginx) http headers on "
"stream responses. See :ref:`deploy/streaming` for web server "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"biriktirma fayllarini xizmat ko'rsatishni statik veb-serverga topshiradi va "
"oqim javoblarida ``X-Sendfile`` (apache) va ``X-Accel-*`` (nginx) http "
"sarlavhalarini o'rnatadi. Veb-server konfiguratsiyasi uchun "
":ref:`deploy/streaming` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:504
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "Jurnallash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:506
msgid ""
"By default, Odoo displays all logging of level_ ``INFO``, ``WARNING`` and"
" ``ERROR``. All logs independently of the level are output on ``stderr``."
" Various options are available to redirect logging to other destinations "
"and to customize the verbosity."
msgstr ""
"Sukut bo'yicha, Odoo darajadagi ``INFO``, ``WARNING`` va ``ERROR`` barcha "
"jurnallarni ko'rsatadi. Darajasidan qat'i nazar barcha jurnallar ``stderr`` "
"da chiqariladi. Jurnallarni boshqa manzillarga yo'naltirish va batafsilligi "
"sozlash uchun turli imkoniyatlar mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:512
msgid ""
"sends logging output to the specified file instead of ``stderr``. On "
"Unix, the file `can be managed by external log rotation programs "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#watchedfilehandler>`_"
" and will automatically be reopened when replaced"
msgstr ""
"``stderr`` o'rniga belgilangan faylga jurnallash chiqishini yuboradi. Unix da, "
"fayl `tashqi jurnal aylantirish dasturlari tomonidan boshqarilishi mumkin "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#watchedfilehandler>`_ "
"va almashtirilganda avtomatik ravishda qayta ochiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:519
msgid ""
"logs to the system's event logger: `syslog on unices "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#sysloghandler>`_"
" and `the Event Log on Windows "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#nteventloghandler>`_."
msgstr ""
"tizimning hodisa jurnaliga jurnallaydi: `unixlarda syslog "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#sysloghandler>`_ "
"va `Windows da Hodisalar jurnali "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/logging.handlers.html#nteventloghandler>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:522
msgid "Neither is configurable"
msgstr "Ikkalasi ham sozlanmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:526
msgid ""
"logs to the ``ir.logging`` model (``ir_logging`` table) of the specified "
"database. The database can be the name of a database in the \"current\" "
"PostgreSQL, or `a PostgreSQL URI`_ for e.g. log aggregation."
msgstr ""
"ko'rsatilgan ma'lumotlar bazasining ``ir.logging`` modeliga (``ir_logging`` "
"jadval) jurnallaydi. Ma'lumotlar bazasi \"joriy\" PostgreSQL dagi ma'lumotlar "
"bazasi nomi yoki masalan jurnal yig'ish uchun `PostgreSQL URI`_ bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:532
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":samp:`{LOGGER}:{LEVEL}`, enables ``LOGGER`` at the provided ``LEVEL`` "
"e.g. ``odoo.models:DEBUG`` will enable all logging messages at or above "
"``DEBUG`` level in the models."
msgstr ""
":samp:`{LOGGER}:{LEVEL}`, ``LOGGER`` ni ko'rsatilgan ``LEVEL`` da yoqadi, "
"masalan ``odoo.models:DEBUG`` modellarda ``DEBUG`` darajasida yoki undan "
"yuqorida barcha jurnallash xabarlarini yoqadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:536
msgid "The colon ``:`` is mandatory"
msgstr "Ikki nuqta ``:`` majburiy"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:537
msgid "The logger can be omitted to configure the root (default) handler"
msgstr "Jurnalovchi ildiz (sukut bo'yicha) ishlovchini sozlash uchun o'tkazib yuborilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:538
msgid "If the level is omitted, the logger is set to ``INFO``"
msgstr "Agar daraja o'tkazib yuborilsa, jurnalovchi ``INFO`` ga o'rnatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:540
msgid "The option can be repeated to configure multiple loggers e.g."
msgstr "Bir nechta jurnalovchilarni sozlash uchun opsiya takrorlanishi mumkin, masalan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:548
msgid ""
"enables DEBUG logging of HTTP requests and responses, equivalent to "
"``--log-handler=odoo.http:DEBUG``"
msgstr ""
"HTTP so'rovlari va javoblarining DEBUG jurnalashini yoqadi, "
"``--log-handler=odoo.http:DEBUG`` ga teng"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:553
msgid ""
"enables DEBUG logging of SQL querying, equivalent to ``--log-"
"handler=odoo.sql_db:DEBUG``"
msgstr ""
"SQL so'rovlarining DEBUG jurnalashini yoqadi, "
"``--log-handler=odoo.sql_db:DEBUG`` ga teng"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:558
msgid ""
"Shortcut to more easily set predefined levels on specific loggers. "
"\"real\" levels (``critical``, ``error``, ``warn``, ``debug``) are set on"
" the ``odoo`` and ``werkzeug`` loggers (except for ``debug`` which is "
"only set on ``odoo``)."
msgstr ""
"Muayyan jurnalovchilarda oldindan belgilangan darajalarni osonroq o'rnatish "
"uchun yorliq. \"haqiqiy\" darajalar (``critical``, ``error``, ``warn``, "
"``debug``) ``odoo`` va ``werkzeug`` jurnalovchilarida o'rnatiladi "
"(faqat ``odoo`` da o'rnatiladigan ``debug`` dan tashqari)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:563
msgid ""
"Odoo also provides debugging pseudo-levels which apply to different sets "
"of loggers:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo shuningdek turli jurnalovchilar to'plamlariga qo'llaniladigan nosozliklarni "
"tuzatish pseudo-darajalarini ham taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:568
msgid "``debug_sql``"
msgstr "``debug_sql``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:567
msgid "sets the SQL logger to ``debug``"
msgstr "SQL jurnalovchisini ``debug`` ga o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:569
msgid "equivalent to ``--log-sql``"
msgstr "``--log-sql`` ga teng"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:572
msgid "``debug_rpc``"
msgstr "``debug_rpc``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:571
msgid "sets the ``odoo`` and HTTP request loggers to ``debug``"
msgstr "``odoo`` va HTTP so'rovlari jurnalovchilarini ``debug`` ga o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:573
msgid "equivalent to ``--log-level debug --log-request``"
msgstr "``--log-level debug --log-request`` ga teng"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:578
msgid "``debug_rpc_answer``"
msgstr "``debug_rpc_answer``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:575
msgid "sets the ``odoo`` and HTTP request and response loggers to ``debug``"
msgstr "``odoo`` va HTTP so'rovlari va javoblari jurnalovchilarini ``debug`` ga o'rnatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:578
msgid "equivalent to ``--log-level debug --log-request --log-response``"
msgstr "``--log-level debug --log-request --log-response`` ga teng"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:582
msgid ""
"In case of conflict between :option:`--log-level` and :option:`--log-"
"handler`, the latter is used"
msgstr ""
":option:`--log-level` va :option:`--log-handler` o'rtasida ziddiyat yuzaga "
"kelganda, ikkinchisi ishlatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:588
msgid "Multiprocessing"
msgstr "Ko'p jarayonlilik"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:592
msgid ""
"if ``count`` is not 0 (the default), enables multiprocessing and sets up "
"the specified number of HTTP workers (sub-processes processing HTTP and "
"RPC requests)."
msgstr ""
"agar ``count`` 0 bo'lmasa (sukut bo'yicha), ko'p jarayonlilikni yoqadi va "
"ko'rsatilgan sondagi HTTP ishchilarini (HTTP va RPC so'rovlarini qayta "
"ishlayotgan quyi jarayonlarni) sozlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:596
msgid "multiprocessing mode is only available on Unix-based systems"
msgstr "ko'p jarayonlilik rejimi faqat Unix asosidagi tizimlarda mavjud"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:598
msgid "A number of options allow limiting and recycling workers:"
msgstr "Bir qator imkoniyatlar ishchilarni cheklash va qayta ishlashga imkon beradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:602
msgid ""
"Number of requests a worker will process before being recycled and "
"restarted."
msgstr "Ishchi qayta ishlanib qayta ishga tushirilishidan oldin qayta ishlaydigan so'rovlar soni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:605
msgid "Defaults to *8196*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *8196*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:609
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed virtual memory per worker in bytes. If the limit is "
"exceeded, the worker is killed and recycled at the end of the current "
"request."
msgstr ""
"Har bir ishchi uchun baytlarda ruxsat etilgan maksimal virtual xotira. "
"Chegara oshib ketsa, ishchi o'ldiriladi va joriy so'rov oxirida qayta ishlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:612
msgid "Defaults to *2048MiB (2048\\*1024\\*1024B)*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *2048MiB (2048\\*1024\\*1024B)*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:616
msgid ""
"Hard limit on virtual memory in bytes, any worker exceeding the limit "
"will be immediately killed without waiting for the end of the current "
"request processing."
msgstr ""
"Baytlarda virtual xotiraga qattiq chegara, chegarani oshirib yuborgan "
"har qanday ishchi joriy so'rov qayta ishlashining oxirini kutmasdan "
"darhol o'ldiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:620
msgid "Defaults to *2560MiB (2560\\*1024\\*1024B)*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *2560MiB (2560\\*1024\\*1024B)*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:624
msgid ""
"Prevents the worker from using more than <limit> CPU seconds for each "
"request. If the limit is exceeded, the worker is killed."
msgstr ""
"Ishchining har bir so'rov uchun <limit> dan ortiq CPU sekundidan "
"foydalanishini oldini oladi. Chegara oshib ketsa, ishchi o'ldiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:627
msgid "Defaults to *60*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *60*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:631
msgid ""
"Prevents the worker from taking longer than <limit> seconds to process a "
"request. If the limit is exceeded, the worker is killed."
msgstr ""
"Ishchining so'rovni qayta ishlash uchun <limit> sekunddan ko'proq vaqt "
"sarflashini oldini oladi. Chegara oshib ketsa, ishchi o'ldiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:634
msgid ""
"Differs from :option:`--limit-time-cpu` in that this is a \"wall time\" "
"limit including e.g. SQL queries."
msgstr ""
":option:`--limit-time-cpu` dan farqli ravishda, bu masalan SQL so'rovlarini "
"o'z ichiga olgan \"devor vaqti\" chegarasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:637
msgid "Defaults to *120*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *120*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:641
msgid ""
"number of workers dedicated to :ref:`cron <reference/actions/cron>` jobs."
" Defaults to *2*. The workers are threads in multi-threading mode and "
"processes in multi-processing mode."
msgstr ""
":ref:`cron <reference/actions/cron>` ishlari uchun ajratilgan ishchilar soni. "
"Sukut bo'yicha *2*. Ishchilar ko'p ipli rejimda iplar va ko'p jarayonli "
"rejimda jarayonlardir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:644
msgid ""
"For multi-processing mode, this is in addition to the HTTP worker "
"processes."
msgstr "Ko'p jarayonli rejim uchun bu HTTP ishchi jarayonlariga qo'shimcha."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:648
msgid ""
"Soft limit on how long a :ref:`cron <reference/actions/cron>` "
"thread/worker is allowed to live before is is restarted, in seconds."
msgstr ""
":ref:`cron <reference/actions/cron>` ip/ishchiga qayta ishga tushirilishidan "
"oldin qancha vaqt yashash ruxsat etilishiga yumshoq chegara, soniyalarda."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:651
msgid "Set to 0 to disable."
msgstr "O'chirish uchun 0 ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:653
msgid "Defaults to *0*."
msgstr "Sukut bo'yicha *0*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:658
msgid "Configuration file"
msgstr "Konfiguratsiya fayli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:662
msgid ""
"Most of the command-line options can also be specified via a "
"configuration file. Most of the time, they use similar names with the "
"prefix ``-`` removed and other ``-`` are replaced by ``_`` e.g. :option"
":`--db-template` becomes ``db_template``."
msgstr ""
"Buyruq satri imkoniyatlarining aksariyati konfiguratsiya fayli orqali ham "
"ko'rsatilishi mumkin. Ko'pincha, ular ``-`` prefiksi olib tashlangan va "
"boshqa ``-`` lar ``_`` bilan almashtirilgan o'xshash nomlardan foydalanadi, "
"masalan :option:`--db-template` ``db_template`` ga aylanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:667
msgid "Some conversions don't match the pattern:"
msgstr "Ba'zi konvertatsiyalar naqshga mos kelmaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:669
msgid ":option:`--db-filter` becomes ``dbfilter``"
msgstr ":option:`--db-filter` ``dbfilter`` ga aylanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:670
msgid ":option:`--no-http` corresponds to the ``http_enable`` boolean"
msgstr ":option:`--no-http` ``http_enable`` mantiqiy qiymatiga mos keladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:671
msgid ""
"logging presets (all options starting with ``--log-`` except for :option"
":`--log-handler` and :option:`--log-db`) just add content to "
"``log_handler``, use that directly in the configuration file"
msgstr ""
"jurnallash oldindan belgilanganlari (:option:`--log-handler` va "
":option:`--log-db` dan tashqari ``--log-`` bilan boshlanadigan barcha "
"imkoniyatlar) ``log_handler`` ga kontent qo'shadi, konfiguratsiya faylida "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri foydalaning"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:674
msgid ":option:`--smtp` is stored as ``smtp_server``"
msgstr ":option:`--smtp` ``smtp_server`` sifatida saqlanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:675
msgid ":option:`--database` is stored as ``db_name``"
msgstr ":option:`--database` ``db_name`` sifatida saqlanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:679
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The default configuration file is :file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc` which can be "
"overridden using :option:`--config <odoo-bin -c>`. Specifying "
":option:`--save <odoo-bin -s>` will save the current configuration state "
"back to that file. The configuration items relative to the command-line "
"are to be specified in the section ``[options]``."
msgstr ""
"Sukut bo'yicha konfiguratsiya fayli :file:`{$HOME}/.odoorc` bo'lib, "
":option:`--config <odoo-bin -c>` yordamida bekor qilinishi mumkin. "
":option:`--save <odoo-bin -s>` ko'rsatish joriy konfiguratsiya holatini "
"o'sha faylga saqlaydi. Buyruq satriga tegishli konfiguratsiya elementlari "
"``[options]`` bo'limida ko'rsatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:685
msgid "Here is a sample file:"
msgstr "Mana namuna fayli:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:711
msgid "`shell` - Open a Shell"
msgstr "`shell` - Shell ochish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:713
msgid ""
"The Odoo command line also allows launching Odoo as a Python console "
"environment, enabling direct interaction with the :ref:`orm "
"<reference/orm>` and its functionalities. Since running a shell involves "
"starting the server, the configuration file options do apply."
msgstr ""
"Odoo buyruq satri shuningdek Odooni Python konsol muhiti sifatida ishga "
"tushirishga imkon beradi, bu :ref:`orm <reference/orm>` va uning "
"funksionalliklari bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri munosabatda bo'lishga imkon beradi. "
"Shell ishga tushirish serverni ishga tushirishni o'z ichiga olganligi sababli, "
"konfiguratsiya fayli imkoniyatlari qo'llaniladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:723
msgid "Adding an exclamation mark to all contacts' names:"
msgstr "Barcha kontaktlar nomiga undov belgisi qo'shish:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:739
msgid ""
"By default, the shell is running in transaction mode. This means that any"
" change made to the database is rolled back when exiting the shell. To "
"commit changes, use `env.cr.commit()`."
msgstr ""
"Sukut bo'yicha, shell tranzaksiya rejimida ishlaydi. Bu shuni anglatadiki, "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga kiritilgan har qanday o'zgarish shelldan chiqishda "
"qaytariladi. O'zgarishlarni saqlash uchun `env.cr.commit()` dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:745
msgid ""
"Specify a Python script to be run after the start of the shell. Overrides"
" the environment variable `PYTHONSTARTUP`."
msgstr ""
"Shell boshlanganidan so'ng ishga tushiriladigan Python skriptini ko'rsating. "
"`PYTHONSTARTUP` muhit o'zgaruvchisini bekor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:750
msgid ""
"Specify a preferred `REPL` to use in shell mode. This shell is started "
"with the `env` variable already initialized to be able to access the "
"`ORM` and other Odoo modules."
msgstr ""
"Shell rejimida foydalanish uchun afzal ko'rilgan `REPL` ni ko'rsating. "
"Bu shell `ORM` va boshqa Odoo modullariga kirish imkoniyatiga ega bo'lish "
"uchun allaqachon ishga tushirilgan `env` o'zgaruvchisi bilan boshlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:755
msgid ":ref:`reference/orm/environment`"
msgstr ":ref:`reference/orm/environment`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:761
msgid "`db` - Manage a Database"
msgstr "`db` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:765
msgid ""
"This command lets you manage databases through a command-line interface. "
"The operations are specified using subcommands."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq buyruq satri interfeysi orqali ma'lumotlar bazalarini boshqarishga "
"imkon beradi. Operatsiyalar quyi buyruqlar yordamida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:768
#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:969
msgid ""
"For all subcommands, these options to configure your environment are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Barcha quyi buyruqlar uchun muhitingizni sozlash uchun bu imkoniyatlar mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:771
#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:972
#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1093
msgid ":option:`--config <odoo-bin -c>`"
msgstr ":option:`--config <odoo-bin -c>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:772
msgid ":option:`--data-dir <odoo-bin -d>`"
msgstr ":option:`--data-dir <odoo-bin -d>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:773
msgid ":option:`--db_user <odoo-bin --db_user>`"
msgstr ":option:`--db_user <odoo-bin --db_user>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:774
msgid ":option:`--db_password <odoo-bin --db_password>`"
msgstr ":option:`--db_password <odoo-bin --db_password>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:775
msgid ":option:`--db_host <odoo-bin --db_host>`"
msgstr ":option:`--db_host <odoo-bin --db_host>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:776
msgid ":option:`--db_port <odoo-bin --db_port>`"
msgstr ":option:`--db_port <odoo-bin --db_port>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:777
msgid ":option:`--db_sslmode <odoo-bin --db_sslmode>`"
msgstr ":option:`--db_sslmode <odoo-bin --db_sslmode>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:778
msgid ":option:`--pg_path <odoo-bin --pg_path>`"
msgstr ":option:`--pg_path <odoo-bin --pg_path>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:784
msgid "`db init` - Initialize a Database"
msgstr "`db init` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:788
msgid ""
"This command creates a new database and installs the `base` module. You "
"can specify the language and country of the main company."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq yangi ma'lumotlar bazasini yaratadi va `base` modulini o'rnatadi. "
"Asosiy kompaniyaning tili va mamlakatini ko'rsatishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:797
msgid "Name of the database to be initialized."
msgstr "Ishga tushiriladigan ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:801
msgid "Install demo data in the initialized database."
msgstr "Ishga tushirilgan ma'lumotlar bazasiga demo ma'lumotlarini o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:805
msgid "Delete the database if it already exists, before initializing the new one."
msgstr "Yangi bazani ishga tushirishdan oldin, agar u allaqachon mavjud bo'lsa, ma'lumotlar bazasini o'chirib tashlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:809
msgid "Code of the country to be set on the main company"
msgstr "Asosiy kompaniyada o'rnatiladigan mamlakat kodi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:813
msgid "Default language for the instance, default `en_US`"
msgstr "Nusxa uchun sukut bo'yicha til, sukut bo'yicha `en_US`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:817
msgid "Username for the new database, default `admin`"
msgstr "Yangi ma'lumotlar bazasi uchun foydalanuvchi nomi, sukut bo'yicha `admin`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:821
msgid "Password for the new database, default `admin`"
msgstr "Yangi ma'lumotlar bazasi uchun parol, sukut bo'yicha `admin`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:827
msgid "`db dump` - Save a Database Dump"
msgstr "`db dump` - Ma'lumotlar bazasi dumpini saqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:831
msgid "Creates a dump file."
msgstr "Dump fayli yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:839
msgid "Name of the database to dump."
msgstr "Dump qilinadigan ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:843
msgid ""
"(Optional) Database is dumped to specified path. By default it is dumped "
"to `stdout`."
msgstr ""
"(Ixtiyoriy) Ma'lumotlar bazasi ko'rsatilgan yo'lga dump qilinadi. "
"Sukut bo'yicha u `stdout` ga dump qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:848
msgid ""
"If provided, database is dumped used the specified format. Supported "
"formats are `zip` (default), `dump` (pg_dump format)."
msgstr ""
"Taqdim etilgan bo'lsa, ma'lumotlar bazasi ko'rsatilgan format yordamida "
"dump qilinadi. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan formatlar: `zip` (sukut bo'yicha), "
"`dump` (pg_dump formati)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:853
msgid "If provided, zip database is dumped without filestore"
msgstr "Taqdim etilgan bo'lsa, zip ma'lumotlar bazasi fayl do'konisiz dump qilinadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:859
msgid "`db load` - Load a Database Dump"
msgstr "`db load` - Ma'lumotlar bazasi dumpini yuklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:863
msgid "Loads a dump file into an Odoo database, the dump file can be a URL."
msgstr "Dump faylini Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasiga yuklaydi, dump fayli URL bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:871
msgid ""
"(Optional) Name of the database to create from the dump. If not provided,"
" the dump filename without extension is used."
msgstr ""
"(Ixtiyoriy) Dumpdan yaratish uchun ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi. Ko'rsatilmagan "
"bo'lsa, kengaytmasiz dump fayli nomi ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:876
msgid "`.zip` or `pg_dump` file to be loaded."
msgstr "Yuklanadigan `.zip` yoki `pg_dump` fayli."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:880
msgid "Delete the database if it already exists, before loading the new one."
msgstr "Yangisini yuklamasdan oldin, agar u allaqachon mavjud bo'lsa, ma'lumotlar bazasini o'chirib tashlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:884
msgid "Neutralize the database after restoring it."
msgstr "Tiklangandan so'ng ma'lumotlar bazasini neytrallash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:890
msgid "`db duplicate` - Duplicate a Database"
msgstr "`db duplicate` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini nusxalash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:894
msgid "Duplicate a database including filestore."
msgstr "Fayl do'konini o'z ichiga olgan ma'lumotlar bazasini nusxalash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:902
msgid "Name of the source database."
msgstr "Manba ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:906
msgid "Name of the target database."
msgstr "Maqsad ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:910
msgid "Neutralize the database, after restoring it."
msgstr "Tiklangandan so'ng ma'lumotlar bazasini neytrallash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:914
msgid ""
"Delete the target database if it already exists, before initializing the "
"new one."
msgstr "Yangi bazani ishga tushirishdan oldin, agar u allaqachon mavjud bo'lsa, maqsad ma'lumotlar bazasini o'chirib tashlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:920
msgid "`db rename` - Rename a Database"
msgstr "`db rename` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini qayta nomlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:924
msgid "Rename a database from an old name to a new one."
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar bazasini eski nomdan yangi nomga qayta nomlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:932
msgid "Current name of the database."
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar bazasining joriy nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:936
msgid "New name for the database."
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar bazasi uchun yangi nom."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:940
msgid ""
"Delete the target database if it already exists, before renaming the "
"source one."
msgstr "Manbani qayta nomlamasdan oldin, agar u allaqachon mavjud bo'lsa, maqsad ma'lumotlar bazasini o'chirib tashlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:946
msgid "`db drop` - Delete a Database"
msgstr "`db drop` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini o'chirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:956
msgid "Name of the database to drop."
msgstr "O'chiriladigan ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:962
msgid "`i18n` - Internationalization"
msgstr "`i18n` - Xalqarolashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:966
msgid ""
"This command has subcommands that enable you to import or export "
"internationalization files and setup languages on the Odoo instance."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq xalqarolashtirish fayllarini import yoki eksport qilish va Odoo "
"nusxasida tillarni sozlash imkonini beruvchi quyi buyruqlarga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:977
msgid "Language codes must follow the XPG (POSIX) locale format."
msgstr "Til kodlari XPG (POSIX) lokal formatiga amal qilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:979
msgid "To list available codes, you can search them querying the database:"
msgstr "Mavjud kodlarni ro'yxatga olish uchun ma'lumotlar bazasini so'rovlash orqali ularni qidirishingiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:987
msgid ""
"`GNU libc Locale Names "
"<https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Locale-Names.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`GNU libc Lokal nomlari "
"<https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Locale-Names.html>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1000
msgid "`i18n import` - Import i18n files"
msgstr "`i18n import` - i18n fayllarini import qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1004
msgid ""
"This command imports provided translation files in the `.po` or `.csv` "
"formats. By default, only new entries will be added, but you can choose "
"to overwrite existing terms. All the files must refer to the specified "
"language."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq taqdim etilgan tarjima fayllarini `.po` yoki `.csv` formatlarida "
"import qiladi. Sukut bo'yicha faqat yangi yozuvlar qo'shiladi, ammo mavjud "
"atamalarni qayta yozishni tanlashingiz mumkin. Barcha fayllar ko'rsatilgan "
"tilga murojaat qilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1014
msgid "List of files to be imported."
msgstr "Import qilinadigan fayllar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1015
msgid "Allowed extensions: `.po`, `.csv`."
msgstr "Ruxsat etilgan kengaytmalar: `.po`, `.csv`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1019
msgid "(Required) Language code of the translations in the files."
msgstr "(Talab qilinadi) Fayllardagi tarjimalarning til kodi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1023
msgid "Overwrite existing translation when importing."
msgstr "Import paytida mavjud tarjimani qayta yozish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1029
msgid "`i18n export` - Export i18n files"
msgstr "`i18n export` - i18n fayllarini eksport qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1033
msgid ""
"This command exports existing translation terms for modules in the Odoo "
"database to a range of formats: `.po`, `.pot`, `.tgz`, `.csv`. In case of"
" `.po` and `.pot` files, they will be created under the `i18n/` folder of"
" the module they belong to. If you specify an output parameter, only one "
"language can be selected, and all the output will refer to that language."
" The `.tgz` output format makes all output be archived in a single file."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasidagi modullar uchun mavjud tarjima "
"atamalarini bir qator formatlarga eksport qiladi: `.po`, `.pot`, `.tgz`, `.csv`. "
"`.po` va `.pot` fayllar holatida, ular tegishli modul `i18n/` papkasi ostida "
"yaratiladi. Chiqish parametrini ko'rsatsangiz, faqat bitta til tanlanishi mumkin "
"va barcha chiqish o'sha tilga murojaat qiladi. `.tgz` chiqish formati barcha "
"chiqishni bitta faylda arxivlashga olib keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1046
msgid "List of modules you want to export the internationalization files from."
msgstr "Xalqarolashtirish fayllarini eksport qilmoqchi bo'lgan modullar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1050
msgid "List of language codes you want to export, `pot` for template (default)."
msgstr "Eksport qilmoqchi bo'lgan til kodlari ro'yxati, shablon uchun `pot` (sukut bo'yicha)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1054
msgid "Path of an only output file with translations from all provided modules."
msgstr "Barcha taqdim etilgan modullardan tarjimalar bilan faqat bitta chiqish fayli yo'li."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1055
msgid "Allowed extensions: `.po`, `.pot`, `.tgz`, `.csv`"
msgstr "Ruxsat etilgan kengaytmalar: `.po`, `.pot`, `.tgz`, `.csv`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1056
msgid "If `-` is provided, the content is written as a `.po` file to stdout."
msgstr "Agar `-` taqdim etilsa, kontent stdout ga `.po` fayli sifatida yoziladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1058
msgid "Only one language is allowed when this option is active."
msgstr "Bu opsiya faol bo'lganda faqat bitta tilga ruxsat beriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1064
msgid "`i18n loadlang` - Load language"
msgstr "`i18n loadlang` - Tilni yuklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1068
msgid ""
"This command loads one of the available languages into the Odoo database "
"and activates it."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq mavjud tillardan birini Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasiga yuklaydi va uni faollashtiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1076
msgid "language codes of the languages to be installed."
msgstr "o'rnatiladigan tillarning til kodlari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1082
msgid "`module` - Manage modules"
msgstr "`module` - Modullarni boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1086
msgid ""
"This command has subcommands that enable you to install, uninstall and "
"upgrade modules on the Odoo instance. There's also a command to force "
"install the demo data into the database."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq Odoo nusxasida modullarni o'rnatish, o'chirish va yangilash "
"imkonini beruvchi quyi buyruqlarga ega. Ma'lumotlar bazasiga demo "
"ma'lumotlarni majburan o'rnatish buyrug'i ham mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1090
msgid "For all subcommands, these options are available:"
msgstr "Barcha quyi buyruqlar uchun bu imkoniyatlar mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1100
msgid "`module install` - Install modules"
msgstr "`module install` - Modullarni o'rnatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1104
msgid "This command installs all selected modules straight away."
msgstr "Bu buyruq barcha tanlangan modullarni darhol o'rnatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1106
msgid ""
"Before installing modules, the Odoo database needs to be created and "
"initialized on your PostgreSQL instance, e.g. using the "
":ref:`reference/cmdline/db/init` command."
msgstr ""
"Modullarni o'rnatishdan oldin, PostgreSQL nusxangizda Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasi "
"yaratilgan va ishga tushirilgan bo'lishi kerak, masalan "
":ref:`reference/cmdline/db/init` buyrug'i yordamida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1115
msgid "List of modules you want to install."
msgstr "O'rnatmoqchi bo'lgan modullar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1121
msgid "`module uninstall` - Uninstall modules"
msgstr "`module uninstall` - Modullarni o'chirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1125
msgid "This command uninstalls all selected modules straight away."
msgstr "Bu buyruq barcha tanlangan modullarni darhol o'chiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1133
msgid "List of modules you want to uninstall."
msgstr "O'chirmoqchi bo'lgan modullar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1139
msgid "`module upgrade` - Upgrade modules"
msgstr "`module upgrade` - Modullarni yangilash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1143
msgid "This command upgrades all selected modules straight away."
msgstr "Bu buyruq barcha tanlangan modullarni darhol yangilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1151
msgid ""
"List of modules you want to upgrade. Use ``base`` or ``all`` for all "
"installed modules."
msgstr ""
"Yangilamoqchi bo'lgan modullar ro'yxati. Barcha o'rnatilgan modullar uchun "
"``base`` yoki ``all`` dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1156
msgid ""
"Only update modules that have a newer version on disk. If ``all`` is used"
" as ``modules`` argument, this applies to all installed modules."
msgstr ""
"Faqat diskda yangi versiyaga ega modullarni yangilang. Agar ``all`` "
"``modules`` argumenti sifatida ishlatilsa, bu barcha o'rnatilgan modullarga qo'llaniladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1163
msgid "`module forcedemo` - Force demo data install"
msgstr "`module forcedemo` - Demo ma'lumotlarni majburan o'rnatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1167
msgid ""
"This command forces the installation of :ref:`Demo Data "
"<tutorials/define_module_data/demo_data>`"
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq :ref:`Demo ma'lumotlarini <tutorials/define_module_data/demo_data>` "
"o'rnatishni majburlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1171
msgid ""
"Once installed, there is no way to undo it, so you might want to save a "
"backup of the database first with the command :ref:`db dump "
"<reference/cmdline/db/dump>`"
msgstr ""
"O'rnatilgandan so'ng, uni bekor qilishning imkoni yo'q, shuning uchun avval "
":ref:`db dump <reference/cmdline/db/dump>` buyrug'i bilan ma'lumotlar "
"bazasining zaxira nusxasini saqlashni xohlashingiz mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1174
msgid "There are no additional options to this command."
msgstr "Bu buyruq uchun qo'shimcha imkoniyatlar yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1180
msgid "`neutralize` - Neutralize a Database"
msgstr "`neutralize` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini neytrallash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1184
msgid ""
"The Odoo command line allows for neutralizing a database as well. The "
"command must be run with a database option."
msgstr ""
"Odoo buyruq satri ma'lumotlar bazasini neytrallashga ham imkon beradi. "
"Buyruq ma'lumotlar bazasi opsiyasi bilan bajarilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1193
msgid "Specify the database name that you would like to neutralize."
msgstr "Neytrallashni xohlaydigan ma'lumotlar bazasi nomini ko'rsating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1198
msgid "Output the neutralization SQL instead of applying it"
msgstr "Uni qo'llash o'rniga neytrallash SQL ni chiqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1201
msgid ":doc:`../../administration/neutralized_database`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../administration/neutralized_database`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1206
msgid "`scaffold` - Scaffold a Module"
msgstr "`scaffold` - Modul yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1210
msgid ""
"Scaffolding is the automated creation of a skeleton structure to simplify"
" bootstrapping (of new modules, in the case of Odoo). While not necessary"
" it avoids the tedium of setting up basic structures and looking up what "
"all starting requirements are."
msgstr ""
"Scaffolding - bu bootstrappingni (Odoo holatida yangi modullar uchun) "
"soddalashtirish uchun skelet strukturasini avtomatlashtirilgan tarzda yaratish. "
"Zarur bo'lmasa ham, u asosiy strukturalarni sozlash va barcha boshlang'ich "
"talablarni qidirishning zerikarliligini oldini oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1215
msgid "Scaffolding is available via the :command:`odoo-bin scaffold` subcommand."
msgstr "Scaffolding :command:`odoo-bin scaffold` quyi buyrug'i orqali mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1223
msgid ""
"the name of the module to create, may munged in various manners to "
"generate programmatic names (e.g. module directory name, model names, …)"
msgstr ""
"yaratish uchun modul nomi, dasturiy nomlar yaratish uchun turli usullarda "
"o'zgartirilishi mumkin (masalan, modul katalogi nomi, model nomlari, …)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1228
msgid ""
"directory in which to create the new module, defaults to the current "
"directory"
msgstr ""
"yangi modul yaratish uchun katalog, sukut bo'yicha joriy katalog"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1233
msgid ""
"a template directory, files are passed through jinja2_ then copied to the"
" ``destination`` directory"
msgstr ""
"shablon katalogi, fayllar jinja2_ orqali o'tkaziladi va keyin "
"``destination`` katalogiga ko'chiriladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1237
msgid "This will create module *my_module* in directory */addons/*."
msgstr "Bu */addons/* katalogida *my_module* modulini yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1242
msgid "`populate` - Populate a Database"
msgstr "`populate` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini to'ldirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1246
msgid ""
"Odoo Populate allows to duplicate existing data in a given database. This"
" can be used for testing and benchmarking when large tables are needed. "
"The duplication process introduces variation for some fields to respect "
"`UNIQUE` constraints, among other things. It also follows x2Many "
"relationships."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Populate berilgan ma'lumotlar bazasidagi mavjud ma'lumotlarni "
"nusxalash imkonini beradi. Bu katta jadvallar kerak bo'lganda sinovlar va "
"benchmarking uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Nusxalash jarayoni boshqa narsalar "
"qatorida `UNIQUE` cheklovlariga rioya qilish uchun ba'zi maydonlarga "
"o'zgaruvchanlik kiritadi. U shuningdek x2Many munosabatlariga ham amal qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1257
msgid "name of the database to populate"
msgstr "to'ldiriladigan ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1261
msgid ""
"list of models to populate. Models appearing twice will only be populated"
" once."
msgstr ""
"to'ldiriladigan modellar ro'yxati. Ikki marta paydo bo'ladigan modellar "
"faqat bir marta to'ldiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1265
msgid ""
"list of populate factors. In case a factor is missing for a model, the "
"last factor in the list will be used."
msgstr ""
"to'ldirish omillari ro'yxati. Agar model uchun omil yo'q bo'lsa, "
"ro'yxatdagi oxirgi omil ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1270
msgid "separator used to generate record names"
msgstr "yozuv nomlari yaratish uchun ishlatiladigan ajratuvchi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1275
msgid "`cloc` - Count Lines of Code"
msgstr "`cloc` - Kod satrlarini hisoblash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1279
msgid ""
"Odoo Cloc is a tool to count the number of relevant lines of code written"
" in Python, Javascript, CSS, SCSS, or XML. This can be used as a rough "
"metric for pricing maintenance of extra modules."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Cloc Python, Javascript, CSS, SCSS yoki XML da yozilgan tegishli "
"kod satrlarining sonini hisoblash uchun vositadir. Bu qo'shimcha modullar "
"texnik xizmat ko'rsatishni narxlash uchun taxminiy metrik sifatida "
"ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1292
msgid ""
"Process the code of all extra modules installed on the provided database,"
" and of all server actions and computed fields manually created in the "
"provided database."
msgstr ""
"Taqdim etilgan ma'lumotlar bazasida o'rnatilgan barcha qo'shimcha modullar "
"kodini va taqdim etilgan ma'lumotlar bazasida qo'lda yaratilgan barcha "
"server harakatlari va hisoblangan maydonlarni qayta ishlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1294
msgid ""
"The :option:`--addons-path` option is required to specify the path(s) to "
"the module folder(s)."
msgstr ""
"Modul papkasi(lari) ga yo'l(lar) ni ko'rsatish uchun :option:`--addons-path` "
"opsiyasi talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1297
msgid ""
"If combined with :option:`--path`, the count will be that of the sum of "
"both options' results (with possible overlaps). At least one of these two"
" options is required to specify which code to process."
msgstr ""
"Agar :option:`--path` bilan birlashtirilsa, hisoblash ikki opsiya "
"natijalarining yig'indisi bo'ladi (mumkin bo'lgan qoplamalari bilan). "
"Qaysi kodni qayta ishlashni ko'rsatish uchun bu ikki opsiyadan kamida "
"biri talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1304
msgid ":ref:`reference/cmdline/cloc/database-option`"
msgstr ":ref:`reference/cmdline/cloc/database-option`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1309
msgid "Process the files in the provided path."
msgstr "Taqdim etilgan yo'ldagi fayllarni qayta ishlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1312
msgid ""
"If combined with :option:`--database`, the count will be that of the sum "
"of both options' results (with possible overlaps). At least one of these "
"two options is required to specify which code to process."
msgstr ""
"Agar :option:`--database` bilan birlashtirilsa, hisoblash ikki opsiya "
"natijalarining yig'indisi bo'ladi (mumkin bo'lgan qoplamalari bilan). "
"Qaysi kodni qayta ishlashni ko'rsatish uchun bu ikki opsiyadan kamida "
"biri talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1319
msgid "Multiple paths can be provided by repeating the option."
msgstr "Opsiyani takrorlash orqali bir nechta yo'llar taqdim etilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1326
msgid ":ref:`reference/cmdline/cloc/path-option`"
msgstr ":ref:`reference/cmdline/cloc/path-option`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1333
msgid "Required if the :option:`--database` option is used."
msgstr ":option:`--database` opsiyasi ishlatilsa talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1338
msgid ""
"Specify a configuration file to use in place of the :option:`--addons-"
"path` option."
msgstr ""
":option:`--addons-path` opsiyasi o'rnida foydalanish uchun konfiguratsiya faylini ko'rsating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1343
msgid "Show the details of lines counted for each file."
msgstr "Har bir fayl uchun hisoblangan satrlar tafsilotlarini ko'rsatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1347
msgid "Processed files"
msgstr "Qayta ishlangan fayllar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1352
msgid "With the :option:`--database` option"
msgstr ":option:`--database` opsiyasi bilan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1354
msgid ""
"Odoo Cloc counts the lines in each file of extra installed modules in a "
"given database. In addition, it counts the Python lines of server actions"
" and custom computed fields that have been directly created in the "
"database or imported. Finally, it counts the lines of code of Javascript,"
" CSS, and SCSS files, and of QWeb views from imported modules."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Cloc berilgan ma'lumotlar bazasidagi qo'shimcha o'rnatilgan "
"modullarning har bir faylida satrlarni hisoblaydi. Bundan tashqari, u "
"bevosita ma'lumotlar bazasida yaratilgan yoki import qilingan server "
"harakatlari va maxsus hisoblangan maydonlarning Python satrlarini hisoblaydi. "
"Nihoyat, u Javascript, CSS va SCSS fayllarning va import qilingan "
"modullardan QWeb ko'rinishlarining kod satrlarini hisoblaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1360
msgid "Some files are excluded from the count by default:"
msgstr "Ba'zi fayllar sukut bo'yicha hisobdan chiqariladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1362
msgid "The manifest (:file:`__manifest__.py` or :file:`__openerp__.py`)"
msgstr "Manifest (:file:`__manifest__.py` yoki :file:`__openerp__.py`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1363
msgid "The contents of the folder :file:`static/lib`"
msgstr ":file:`static/lib` papkasining mazmuni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1364
msgid "The tests defined in the folder :file:`tests` and :file:`static/tests`"
msgstr ":file:`tests` va :file:`static/tests` papkalarida aniqlangan sinovlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1365
msgid ""
"The migrations scripts defined in the folder :file:`migrations` and "
"`upgrades`"
msgstr ":file:`migrations` va `upgrades` papkalarida aniqlangan migratsiya skriptlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1366
msgid ""
"The XML files declared in the ``demo`` or ``demo_xml`` sections of the "
"manifest"
msgstr "Manifestning ``demo`` yoki ``demo_xml`` bo'limlarida e'lon qilingan XML fayllar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1368
msgid ""
"For special cases, a list of files that should be ignored by Odoo Cloc "
"can be defined per module. This is specified by the ``cloc_exclude`` "
"entry of the manifest:"
msgstr ""
"Maxsus holatlar uchun, Odoo Cloc tomonidan e'tiborga olinmasligi kerak "
"bo'lgan fayllar ro'yxati har bir modul uchun aniqlanishi mumkin. Bu "
"manifestning ``cloc_exclude`` yozuvi orqali ko'rsatiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1381
msgid ""
"The pattern ``**/*`` can be used to ignore an entire module. This can be "
"useful to exclude a module from maintenance service costs."
msgstr ""
"``**/*`` naqshi butun modulni e'tiborga olmaslik uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. "
"Bu modulni texnik xizmat ko'rsatish xarajatlaridan chiqarish uchun foydali bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1383
msgid ""
"For more information about the pattern syntax, see `glob "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/pathlib.html#pathlib.Path.glob>`_."
msgstr ""
"Naqsh sintaksisi haqida ko'proq ma'lumot uchun `glob "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/pathlib.html#pathlib.Path.glob>`_ ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1388
msgid "With the :option:`--path` option"
msgstr ":option:`--path` opsiyasi bilan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1390
msgid ""
"This method works the same as with the :ref:`--database option "
"<reference/cmdline/cloc/database-option>` if a manifest file is present "
"in the given folder. Otherwise, it counts all files."
msgstr ""
"Bu metod agar berilgan papkada manifest fayli mavjud bo'lsa, "
":ref:`--database opsiyasi <reference/cmdline/cloc/database-option>` bilan "
"bir xil ishlaydi. Aks holda, barcha fayllarni hisoblaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1396
msgid "Identifying Extra Modules"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha modullarni aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1398
msgid ""
"To distinguish between standard and extra modules, Odoo Cloc uses the "
"following heuristic: modules that are located (real file system path, "
"after following symbolic links) in the same parent directory as the "
"``base``, ``web`` or ``web_enterprise`` standard modules are considered "
"standard. Other modules are treated as extra modules."
msgstr ""
"Standart va qo'shimcha modullarni farqlash uchun Odoo Cloc quyidagi "
"evristikadan foydalanadi: ``base``, ``web`` yoki ``web_enterprise`` standart "
"modullar bilan bir xil ota katalogda joylashgan (simvolik havolalarga "
"amal qilgandan so'ng, haqiqiy fayl tizimi yo'li) modullar standart "
"hisoblanadi. Boshqa modullar qo'shimcha modullar sifatida ko'rib chiqiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1405
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:662
msgid "Error Handling"
msgstr "Xatolarni boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1407
msgid ""
"Some file cannot be counted by Odoo Cloc. Those file are reported at the "
"end of the output."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi fayllar Odoo Cloc tomonidan hisoblanmasligi mumkin. Bu fayllar "
"chiqish oxirida xabar qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1411
msgid "Max file size exceeded"
msgstr "Maksimal fayl hajmi oshib ketdi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1413
msgid ""
"Odoo Cloc rejects any file larger than 25MB. Usually, source files are "
"smaller than 1 MB. If a file is rejected, it may be:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Cloc 25MB dan katta har qanday faylni rad etadi. Odatda, manba "
"fayllar 1 MB dan kichikroq. Fayl rad etilsa, u bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1416
msgid ""
"A generated XML file that contains lots of data. It should be excluded in"
" the manifest."
msgstr ""
"Ko'p ma'lumotlarni o'z ichiga olgan yaratilgan XML fayl. U manifestda chiqarib tashlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1417
msgid ""
"A JavaScript library that should be placed in the :file:`static/lib` "
"folder."
msgstr ":file:`static/lib` papkasiga joylashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan JavaScript kutubxonasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1420
msgid "Syntax Error"
msgstr "Sintaksis xatosi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1422
msgid ""
"Odoo Cloc cannot count the lines of code of a Python file with a syntax "
"problem. If an extra module contains such files, they should be fixed to "
"allow the module to load. If the module works despite the presence of "
"those files, they are probably not loaded and should therefore be removed"
" from the module, or at least excluded in the manifest via "
"``cloc_exclude``."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Cloc sintaksis muammosi bo'lgan Python faylining kod satrlarini "
"hisoblay olmaydi. Agar qo'shimcha modul bunday fayllarni o'z ichiga olsa, "
"modulning yuklanishiga imkon berish uchun ularni tuzatish kerak. Agar "
"modul shu fayllar mavjudligiga qaramay ishlasa, ular ehtimol yuklanmaydi "
"va shuning uchun moduldan olib tashlanishi yoki hech bo'lmaganda ``cloc_exclude`` "
"orqali manifestda chiqarib tashlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1432
msgid "`obfuscate` - Obfuscate database"
msgstr "`obfuscate` - Ma'lumotlar bazasini niqoblash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1436
msgid ""
"This command provides a quick and easy way to obfuscate some of the data "
"in the Odoo instance, mainly used for instructional purposes or to make "
"quick videos for the support team helping technicians avoid leaking "
"sensitive information."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq Odoo nusxasidagi ba'zi ma'lumotlarni niqoblashning tezkor va "
"oson usulini taqdim etadi, asosan o'quv maqsadlari uchun yoki texnikchilarga "
"maxfiy ma'lumotlar oqib chiqishining oldini olishga yordam beradigan qo'llab-"
"quvvatlash guruhi uchun tezkor videolar yaratish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1442
msgid ""
"This command must be used carefully, as it is **not** considered a safe "
"method for full anonymizing data before transfer to a third party. "
"Images, PDF attachments, amounts, many other informations may not be "
"obfuscated and cause sensitive information leaks. A thorough review is "
"required before sharing data to ensure that no sensitive information is "
"exposed."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq ehtiyotkorlik bilan ishlatilishi kerak, chunki u uchinchi "
"tomonga o'tkazishdan oldin ma'lumotlarni to'liq anonimlashtirish uchun "
"xavfsiz usul **emas** hisoblanadi. Rasmlar, PDF biriktirmalari, miqdorlar "
"va boshqa ko'p ma'lumotlar niqoblanmasligi va maxfiy ma'lumotlar oqishiga "
"sabab bo'lishi mumkin. Ma'lumotlarni ulashishdan oldin hech qanday maxfiy "
"ma'lumot ochilmasligini ta'minlash uchun to'liq ko'rib chiqish talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1448
msgid ""
"Obfuscation is symmetric, so content can be unobfuscated using the same "
"password."
msgstr ""
"Niqoblash simmetrikdir, shuning uchun kontent xuddi shu parol yordamida "
"niqoblanmagan holga keltirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1450
msgid ""
"All the configurations available for the :ref:`server "
"<reference/cmdline/server>` command are available here too."
msgstr ""
":ref:`server <reference/cmdline/server>` buyrug'i uchun mavjud barcha "
"konfiguratsiyalar bu yerda ham mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1459
msgid ""
"(Required) the password that will be used to symmetrically obfuscate "
"content."
msgstr "(Talab qilinadi) kontentni simmetrik tarzda niqoblash uchun ishlatiladigan parol."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1463
msgid "if you want to unobfuscate instead of obfuscate."
msgstr "agar niqoblash o'rniga niqobni olib tashlashni xohlasangiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1467
msgid "comma-separated list of `table.column` entries to obfuscate/unobfuscate."
msgstr "niqoblash/niqobni olib tashlash uchun `table.column` yozuvlarining vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1471
msgid ""
"file containing the list of `table.column` entries to "
"obfuscate/unobfuscate."
msgstr "niqoblash/niqobni olib tashlash uchun `table.column` yozuvlari ro'yxatini o'z ichiga olgan fayl."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1475
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of `table.column` entries not to "
"obfuscate/unobfuscate."
msgstr "niqoblamaslik/niqobni olib tashlamaslik uchun `table.column` yozuvlarining vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1479
#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1485
msgid "used only when :option:`--unobfuscate` is selected."
msgstr "faqat :option:`--unobfuscate` tanlanganda ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1481
msgid ""
"Try to unobfuscate all fields. It's slower than specifying the fields "
"manually."
msgstr "Barcha maydonlarning niqobini olib tashlashga urining. Bu maydonlarni qo'lda ko'rsatishdan sekinroq."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1487
msgid ""
"After unobfuscation, completely clear the obfuscated tables and reclaim "
"unused disk space."
msgstr "Niqobni olib tashlagandan so'ng, niqoblangan jadvallarni to'liq tozalang va foydalanilmagan disk maydonini qaytarib oling."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1491
msgid "commit once per table, after obfuscation."
msgstr "niqoblashdan so'ng, har bir jadval uchun bir marta commit qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1493
msgid ""
"It avoids big transactions that might get a timeout or face rollback "
"after an error."
msgstr "Bu timeout olishi yoki xatоdan so'ng rollback bilan duch kelishi mumkin bo'lgan katta tranzaksiyalardan qochadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1497
msgid "don't ask for manual confirmation."
msgstr "qo'lda tasdiqlashni so'ramang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1499
msgid ""
"Only use if you're sure that you're not going to leak sensible "
"information by sharing the database to third party without a review."
msgstr ""
"Faqat ma'lumotlar bazasini ko'rib chiqmasdan uchinchi tomonga ulashish "
"orqali maxfiy ma'lumotlar oqib chiqmasligiga ishonch hosil qilgan "
"bo'lsangiz foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1506
msgid "`deploy` - Deploy module remotely"
msgstr "`deploy` - Modulni masofadan joylashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1510
msgid ""
"This command uploads a module to a remote Odoo server and installs it. "
"It's simpler than manually connecting to the remote server, and it does "
"not require full access to the machine that hosts the Odoo instance, only"
" the Odoo administrative credentials."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq modulni masofaviy Odoo serveriga yuklaydi va o'rnatadi. Bu "
"masofaviy serverga qo'lda ulanishdan oddiyroq va Odoo nusxasini joylashtirgan "
"mashinaga to'liq kirishni talab qilmaydi, faqat Odoo ma'muriy ma'lumotnomasini."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1520
msgid "Prerequisites:"
msgstr "Talablar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1522
msgid "The server must have the module `base_import_module` installed."
msgstr "Serverda `base_import_module` moduli o'rnatilgan bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1523
msgid ""
"The user selected with the `--login` option must have administrative "
"rights."
msgstr ""
"`--login` opsiyasi bilan tanlangan foydalanuvchi administrator huquqlariga "
"ega bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1527
msgid "path of the module to be deployed"
msgstr "joylashtirilayotgan modulning yo'li"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1531
msgid ""
"(Optional) url of the server where the module must be deployed (default "
"`http://localhost:8069`)"
msgstr ""
"(Ixtiyoriy) modul joylashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan serverning URL manzili "
"(standart `http://localhost:8069`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1536
msgid "database name (if the server does not use the `--db-filter` option)"
msgstr "ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi (agar server `--db-filter` opsiyasidan foydalanmasa)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1540
msgid "name of the user with admin rights (default `admin`)"
msgstr "admin huquqlariga ega foydalanuvchi nomi (standart `admin`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1544
msgid "password of the user with admin rights (default `admin`)"
msgstr "admin huquqlariga ega foydalanuvchi paroli (standart `admin`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1548
msgid ""
"verify the server's SSL certificate, to ensure the target instance is "
"legit."
msgstr ""
"maqsadli nusxa qonuniy ekanligini ta'minlash uchun serverning SSL "
"sertifikatini tekshirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1552
msgid ""
"re-initialize the module in case it's already installed. It will update "
"`noupdate=\"1\"` records."
msgstr ""
"modul allaqachon o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, uni qayta ishga tushirish. "
"`noupdate=\"1\"` yozuvlarini yangilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1559
msgid "`upgrade_code` - Rewrite source code"
msgstr "`upgrade_code` - Manba kodini qayta yozish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1563
msgid ""
"This command rewrites the entire source code using the scripts found in "
"the `odoo/upgrade_code` folder. It is used for doing the heavy-lifting "
"when dealing with big code migrations and forward ports."
msgstr ""
"Bu buyruq `odoo/upgrade_code` papkasidagi skriptlardan foydalanib butun "
"manba kodini qayta yozadi. U katta kod migratsiyalari va oldinga portlar "
"bilan ishlashda og'ir ishlarni bajarish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1569
msgid ""
"All the scripts are doing a best-effort at migrating the source code, but"
" they are not silver bullets."
msgstr ""
"Barcha skriptlar manba kodini migratsiya qilishda maksimal harakat qiladi, "
"lekin ular universal yechim emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1572
msgid "It accepts the :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>` option."
msgstr ":option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>` opsiyasini qabul qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1580
msgid "run a single script"
msgstr "bitta skriptni ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1584
msgid "run all script starting from this version included"
msgstr "ushbu versiyadan boshlab barcha skriptlarni ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1588
msgid ""
"to be used with :option:`--from`. Run all scripts up to this version "
"included. Default is `odoo.release.version`."
msgstr ""
":option:`--from` bilan birgalikda ishlatiladi. Ushbu versiyagacha barcha "
"skriptlarni ishga tushirish. Standart `odoo.release.version`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1593
msgid "filter the files to be rewritten, default is every file (`\\*\\*/\\*`)"
msgstr "qayta yoziladigan fayllarni filtrlash, standart har bir fayl (`\\*\\*/\\*`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1597
msgid "list the files that would be re-written, but do not apply changes"
msgstr "qayta yoziladigan fayllar ro'yxatini ko'rsatish, lekin o'zgarishlarni qo'llamaslik"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1600
msgid "Code upgrade scripts"
msgstr "Kod yangilash skriptlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1602
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The scripts must be named `{version}-{name}.py`, and must expose an "
"`upgrade` function that takes a single `file_manager` argument and have "
"no return."
msgstr ""
"Skriptlar `{version}-{name}.py` nomlanishi va bitta `file_manager` "
"argumentini qabul qiladigan hamda qaytarish qiymati bo'lmagan `upgrade` "
"funksiyasini ochib berishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1605
msgid ""
"The `file_manager` argument is a sequence of `files`, which have 3 "
"attributes and some helper methods:"
msgstr ""
"`file_manager` argumenti 3 ta atribut va bir nechta yordamchi metodlarga "
"ega `files` ketma-ketligidir:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1608
msgid "`path`: the `pathlib.Path` where the file is on the file system."
msgstr "`path`: fayl tizimida faylning joylashuvi `pathlib.Path`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1609
msgid "`addon`: the addon the file belongs to."
msgstr "`addon`: fayl tegishli addon."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1610
msgid "`content`: the re-writtable content of the file (lazy)."
msgstr "`content`: faylning qayta yoziladigan mazmuni (lazy)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/cli.rst:1611
msgid "`print_progress(current, total)`: outputs the current progress."
msgstr "`print_progress(current, total)`: joriy jarayonni chiqaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:3
msgid "External JSON-2 API"
msgstr "Tashqi JSON-2 API"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo is usually extended internally via modules, but many of its features"
" and all of its data are also available externally for analysis or "
"integration with various other softwares. Part of the "
":ref:`reference/orm/model` API is easily available over HTTP via the "
"``/json/2`` endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Odoo odatda modullar orqali ichki ravishda kengaytiriladi, lekin uning "
"ko'plab xususiyatlari va barcha ma'lumotlari tahlil yoki turli dasturlar "
"bilan integratsiya uchun tashqi ravishda ham mavjud. :ref:`reference/orm/model` "
"API ning bir qismi ``/json/2`` endpointi orqali HTTP dan osongina foydalanish "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:12
msgid ""
"The actual models, fields and methods available are specific to every "
"database and can be consulted on their ``/doc`` page."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud modellar, maydonlar va metodlar har bir ma'lumotlar bazasiga xos "
"bo'lib, ularning ``/doc`` sahifasida ko'rish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:16
#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:25
msgid ""
"Access to data via the external API is only available on *Custom* Odoo "
"pricing plans. Access to the external API is not available on *One App "
"Free* or *Standard* plans. For more information visit the `Odoo pricing "
"page <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ or reach out to your Customer "
"Success Manager."
msgstr ""
"Tashqi API orqali ma'lumotlarga kirish faqat *Custom* Odoo narx rejalarida "
"mavjud. *One App Free* yoki *Standard* rejalarda tashqi API ga kirish "
"mavjud emas. Qo'shimcha ma'lumot uchun `Odoo narx sahifasini "
"<https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ ko'ring yoki Mijoz muvaffaqiyat "
"menejeringizga murojaat qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:29
msgid "Post a JSON object at the ``/json/2/<model>/<method>`` URL."
msgstr "``/json/2/<model>/<method>`` URL manziliga JSON ob'ekt yuboring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:31
msgid "**HTTP Headers**"
msgstr "**HTTP Sarlavhalari**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "Host"
msgstr "Host"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:33
msgid "Required, the hostname of the server."
msgstr "Majburiy, serverning xost nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "Autorization"
msgstr "Autorization"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:34
msgid ""
"Required, ``bearer`` followed by an :ref:`API key "
"<reference/external_api/api_key>`."
msgstr ""
"Majburiy, ``bearer`` keyin :ref:`API kaliti <reference/external_api/api_key>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "Content-Type"
msgstr "Content-Type"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:35
msgid "Required, ``application/json``, a charset is recommended."
msgstr "Majburiy, ``application/json``, charset tavsiya etiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "X-Odoo-Database"
msgstr "X-Odoo-Database"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:36
msgid "Optional, the name of the database to connect to."
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy, ulanilayotgan ma'lumotlar bazasining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "User-Agent"
msgstr "User-Agent"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:37
msgid "Recommended, the name of your software."
msgstr "Tavsiya etiladi, dasturingizning nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:39
msgid "**URL Path**"
msgstr "**URL yo'li**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "model"
msgstr "model"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:41
msgid "Required, the technical model name."
msgstr "Majburiy, texnik model nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "method"
msgstr "method"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:42
msgid "Required, the method to execute."
msgstr "Majburiy, bajariladigan metod."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:44
msgid "**Body JSON object**"
msgstr "**Body JSON ob'ekti**"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "ids"
msgstr "ids"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:46
msgid ""
"An array of record ids on which to execute the method. Empty or omitted "
"when calling an ``@api.model``-decorated method."
msgstr ""
"Metod bajariladigan yozuv identifikatorlari massivi. ``@api.model`` "
"dekoratori bilan chaqirilganda bo'sh yoki o'tkazib yuboriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "context"
msgstr "context"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:48
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Optional, an object of additional values. e.g. ``{\"lang\": \"en_US\"}``."
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy, qo'shimcha qiymatlar ob'ekti. Masalan ``{\"lang\": \"en_US\"}``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "*param*"
msgstr "*param*"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:49
msgid "As many time as needed, the method's parameters."
msgstr "Kerak bo'lganicha, metodning parametrlari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:77
msgid ""
"In case of **success**, a **200** status with the JSON-serialized return "
"value of the called method in the body."
msgstr ""
"**Muvaffaqiyat** holatida, **200** statusi va tanada chaqirilgan metodning "
"JSON-serializatsiya qilingan qaytarish qiymati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:90
msgid ""
"In case of **error**, a **4xx**/**5xx** status with a JSON-serialized "
"error object in the body."
msgstr ""
"**Xato** holatida, **4xx**/**5xx** statusi va tanada JSON-serializatsiya "
"qilingan xato ob'ekti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:92
msgid "The fully qualified name of the Python exception that occured."
msgstr "Yuz bergan Python istisnoning to'liq nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "message"
msgstr "message"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:93
msgid "The exception message, usually the same as `arguments[0]`."
msgstr "Istisno xabari, odatda `arguments[0]` bilan bir xil."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "arguments"
msgstr "arguments"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:94
msgid "All the exception arguments."
msgstr "Barcha istisno argumentlari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:95
msgid "The context used by the request."
msgstr "So'rov tomonidan ishlatiladigan kontekst."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst
msgid "debug"
msgstr "debug"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:96
msgid "The exception traceback, for debugging purpose."
msgstr "Nosozlikni tuzatish uchun istisno traceback."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:116
msgid "Debug"
msgstr "Debug"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:135
#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:34
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:53
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguratsiya"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:140
msgid "API Key"
msgstr "API kaliti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:142
msgid ""
"An API key must be set in the ``Authorization`` request header, as a "
"bearer token."
msgstr ""
"API kaliti ``Authorization`` so'rov sarlavhasida bearer token sifatida "
"o'rnatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:144
msgid ""
"Create a new API key for a user via :menuselection:`Preferences --> "
"Account Security --> New API Key`."
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Preferences --> Account Security --> New API Key` orqali "
"foydalanuvchi uchun yangi API kaliti yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:159
msgid ""
"Both a description and a duration are needed to create a new API key. The"
" description makes it possible to identify the key, and to determine "
"later whether the key is still in use or should be removed. The duration "
"determines the lifetime of the key, after which the key becomes invalid. "
"It is recommended to set a short duration (typically one day) for "
"interactive usage. For security reasons, it is not possible to create "
"keys that last for more than three months. This means that long lasting "
"keys must be rotated at least once every three months."
msgstr ""
"Yangi API kaliti yaratish uchun tavsif ham, davomiylik ham kerak. Tavsif "
"kalitni aniqlash va keyinchalik kalitning hali ishlatilayotganini yoki "
"o'chirilishi kerakligini aniqlash imkonini beradi. Davomiylik kalitning "
"umr bo'yi miqdorini belgilaydi, undan keyin kalit yaroqsiz bo'ladi. "
"Interaktiv foydalanish uchun qisqa davomiylik (odatda bir kun) o'rnatish "
