"method is decorated with ``@api.model``, no record ID is extracted, and "
"``args`` is left as-is. It is only possible to give a context with "
"``execute_kw``, as it is extracted from the keyword argument named "
"``context``."
msgstr ""
"Yozuv IDlari birinchi ``args`` dan olinadi. Chaqirilgan metod "
"``@api.model`` bilan dekoratsiya qilingan bo'lsa, hech qanday yozuv ID "
"olinmaydi va ``args`` o'z holicha qoladi. Kontekstni faqat ``execute_kw`` "
"bilan berish mumkin, chunki u ``context`` nomlangan kalit so'z argumentdan olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:490
msgid "To run the following:"
msgstr "Quyidagini bajarish uchun:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:501
msgid "Using XML-RPC (JSON-RPC would be similar):"
msgstr "XML-RPC dan foydalanib (JSON-RPC ham o'xshash bo'ladi):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:520
msgid ""
"The JSON-2 API replaces the object service with a few differences. The "
"database must only be provided (via the ``X-Odoo-Database`` HTTP header) "
"on systems where there are multiple databases available for a same "
"domain. The login/password authentication scheme is replaced by an API "
"key (via the ``Authorization: bearer`` HTTP header). The ``model`` and "
"``method`` are placed in the URL. The request body is a JSON object with "
"all the methods arguments, plus ``ids`` and ``context``. All the "
"arguments are named; there is no way in JSON-2 to call a function with "
"positional arguments."
msgstr ""
"JSON-2 API bir nechta farq bilan object xizmatini almashtiradi. Ma'lumotlar "
"bazasi faqat bir xil domen uchun bir nechta ma'lumotlar bazalari mavjud "
"bo'lgan tizimlarda (``X-Odoo-Database`` HTTP sarlavhasi orqali) taqdim "
"etilishi kerak. Login/parol autentifikatsiya sxemasi API kaliti "
"(``Authorization: bearer`` HTTP sarlavhasi orqali) bilan almashtiriladi. "
"``model`` va ``method`` URL da joylashtiriladi. So'rov tanasi barcha metod "
"argumentlari, shuningdek ``ids`` va ``context`` bilan JSON ob'ektidir. "
"Barcha argumentlar nomlanadi; JSON-2 da funksiyani pozitsional argumentlar "
"bilan chaqirish imkoni yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_api.rst:528
msgid "Using JSON-2:"
msgstr "JSON-2 dan foydalanib:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:3
msgid "External RPC API"
msgstr "Tashqi RPC API"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:9
msgid ""
"Both the XML-RPC and JSON-RPC APIs at endpoints ``/xmlrpc``, "
"``/xmlrpc/2`` and ``/jsonrpc`` are scheduled for removal in Odoo 22 (fall"
" 2028) and Online 21.1 (winter 2027). The :doc:`external_api` acts as a "
"replacement."
msgstr ""
"``/xmlrpc``, ``/xmlrpc/2`` va ``/jsonrpc`` endpointlaridagi XML-RPC ham, "
"JSON-RPC ham API Odoo 22 (2028 kuz) va Online 21.1 (2027 qish) da olib "
"tashlanishi rejalashtirilgan. :doc:`external_api` o'rnini bosuvchi sifatida "
"ishlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:16
msgid ""
"Odoo is usually extended internally via modules, but many of its features"
" and all of its data are also available from the outside for external "
"analysis or integration with various tools. Part of the "
":ref:`reference/orm/model` API is easily available over XML-RPC_ and "
"accessible from a variety of languages."
msgstr ""
"Odoo odatda modullar orqali ichki ravishda kengaytiriladi, lekin uning "
"ko'plab xususiyatlari va barcha ma'lumotlari tashqi tahlil yoki turli "
"vositalar bilan integratsiya uchun tashqaridan ham mavjud. "
":ref:`reference/orm/model` API ning bir qismi XML-RPC_ orqali osongina "
"mavjud va turli tillarda kirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:21
msgid ""
"Starting with PHP8, the XML-RPC extension may not be available by "
"default. Check out the `manual "
"<https://www.php.net/manual/en/xmlrpc.installation.php>`_ for the "
"installation steps."
msgstr ""
"PHP8 dan boshlab, XML-RPC kengaytmasi standart bo'yicha mavjud bo'lmasligi "
"mumkin. O'rnatish bosqichlari uchun `qo'llanmaga "
"<https://www.php.net/manual/en/xmlrpc.installation.php>`_ qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:31
msgid "Connection"
msgstr "Ulanish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:36
msgid ""
"If you already have an Odoo server installed, you can just use its "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Agar Odoo serveri allaqachon o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, uning parametrlaridan "
"foydalanish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:40
msgid ""
"For Odoo Online instances (<domain>.odoo.com), users are created without "
"a *local* password (as a person you are logged in via the Odoo Online "
"authentication system, not by the instance itself). To use XML-RPC on "
"Odoo Online instances, you will need to set a password on the user "
