msgstr ""
"Odoo Online nusxalari (<domain>.odoo.com) uchun foydalanuvchilar *mahalliy* "
"parolsiz yaratiladi (siz nusxaning o'zi emas, Odoo Online autentifikatsiya "
"tizimi orqali kirasiz). Odoo Online nusxalarida XML-RPC dan foydalanish "
"uchun foydalanmoqchi bo'lgan foydalanuvchi hisobiga parol o'rnatishingiz kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:46
msgid "Log in your instance with an administrator account."
msgstr "Nusxangizga administrator hisobi bilan kiring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:47
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Users`."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Users` ga o'ting."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:48
msgid "Click on the user you want to use for XML-RPC access."
msgstr "XML-RPC kirish uchun foydalanmoqchi bo'lgan foydalanuvchiga bosing."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:49
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Action` and select :guilabel:`Change Password`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Action` ga bosing va :guilabel:`Change Password` ni tanlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:50
msgid ""
"Set a :guilabel:`New Password` value then click :guilabel:`Change "
"Password`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`New Password` qiymatini o'rnating, keyin :guilabel:`Change "
"Password` ga bosing."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:52
msgid ""
"The *server url* is the instance's domain (e.g. "
"*https://mycompany.odoo.com*), the *database name* is the name of the "
"instance (e.g. *mycompany*). The *username* is the configured user's "
"login as shown by the *Change Password* screen."
msgstr ""
"*server url* nusxaning domeni (masalan *https://mycompany.odoo.com*), "
"*database name* nusxaning nomi (masalan *mycompany*). *username* esa "
"*Change Password* ekranida ko'rsatilgan sozlangan foydalanuvchining logini."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:99
msgid "API Keys"
msgstr "API kalitlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:103
msgid ""
"Odoo has support for **api keys** and (depending on modules or settings) "
"may **require** these keys to perform webservice operations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **api kalitlari** ni qo'llab-quvvatlaydi va (modullarga yoki "
"sozlamalarga qarab) veb-xizmat operatsiyalarini bajarish uchun bu kalitlarni "
"**talab qilishi** mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:106
msgid ""
"The way to use API Keys in your scripts is to simply replace your "
"**password** by the key. The login remains in-use. You should store the "
"API Key as carefully as the password as they essentially provide the same"
" access to your user account (although they can not be used to log-in via"
" the interface)."
msgstr ""
"Skriptlarda API kalitlaridan foydalanish usuli - shunchaki **parolingizni** "
"kalit bilan almashtirish. Login ishlatilishda qoladi. API kalitini parol "
"kabi ehtiyotkorlik bilan saqlashingiz kerak, chunki ular aslida foydalanuvchi "
"hisobingizga bir xil kirish imkonini beradi (garchi interfeys orqali "
"tizimga kirish uchun ishlatib bo'lmasa ham)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:111
msgid ""
"In order to add a key to your account, simply go to your "
":guilabel:`Preferences` (or :guilabel:`My Profile`):"
msgstr ""
"Hisobingizga kalit qo'shish uchun :guilabel:`Preferences` "
"(yoki :guilabel:`My Profile`) ga o'ting:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:117
msgid ""
"then open the :guilabel:`Account Security` tab, and click :guilabel:`New "
"API Key`:"
msgstr ""
"keyin :guilabel:`Account Security` yorlig'ini oching va :guilabel:`New "
"API Key` ga bosing:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:123
msgid ""
"Input a description for the key, **this description should be as clear "
"and complete as possible**: it is the only way you will have to identify "
"your keys later and know whether you should remove them or keep them "
"around."
msgstr ""
"Kalit uchun tavsif kiriting, **bu tavsif iloji boricha aniq va to'liq "
"bo'lishi kerak**: bu keyinchalik kalitlaringizni aniqlash va ularni "
"o'chirish yoki saqlab qolish kerakligini bilishning yagona usuli."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:127
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate Key`, then copy the key provided. **Store this "
"key carefully**: it is equivalent to your password, and just like your "
"password the system will not be able to retrieve or show the key again "
"later on. If you lose this key, you will have to create a new one (and "
"probably delete the one you lost)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Generate Key` ga bosing va taqdim etilgan kalitni nusxalang. "
"**Bu kalitni ehtiyotkorlik bilan saqlang**: u parolingizga teng va parolingiz "
"kabi tizim keyinchalik kalitni tiklash yoki ko'rsata olmaydi. Agar bu "
"kalitni yo'qotsangiz, yangi yaratishingiz kerak (va ehtimol yo'qolganini o'chirish)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:133
msgid ""
"Once you have keys configured on your account, they will appear above the"
" :guilabel:`New API Key` button, and you will be able to delete them:"
msgstr ""
"Hisobingizda kalitlar sozlangach, ular :guilabel:`New API Key` tugmasidan "
"yuqorida paydo bo'ladi va ularni o'chirish mumkin bo'ladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:139
msgid ""
"**A deleted API key can not be undeleted or re-set**. You will have to "
"generate a new key and update all the places where you used the old one."
msgstr ""
"**O'chirilgan API kalitini qayta tiklab yoki qayta o'rnatib bo'lmaydi**. "
"Yangi kalit yaratish va eski kalitni ishlatgan barcha joylarda yangilash "
"kerak bo'ladi."

