#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:226
msgid "Logging in"
msgstr "Tizimga kirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:228
msgid ""
"Odoo requires users of the API to be authenticated before they can query "
"most data."
msgstr ""
"Odoo API foydalanuvchilaridan ko'pchilik ma'lumotlarni so'rashdan oldin "
"autentifikatsiya qilinishini talab qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:231
msgid ""
"The ``xmlrpc/2/common`` endpoint provides meta-calls which don't require "
"authentication, such as the authentication itself or fetching version "
"information. To verify if the connection information is correct before "
"trying to authenticate, the simplest call is to ask for the server's "
"version. The authentication itself is done through the ``authenticate`` "
"function and returns a user identifier (``uid``) used in authenticated "
"calls instead of the login."
msgstr ""
"``xmlrpc/2/common`` endpointi autentifikatsiyani talab qilmaydigan "
"meta-chaqiruvlarni ta'minlaydi, masalan autentifikatsiyaning o'zi yoki "
"versiya ma'lumotlarini olish. Autentifikatsiya qilishga urinishdan oldin "
"ulanish ma'lumotlari to'g'ri ekanligini tekshirish uchun eng oddiy chaqiruv "
"serverning versiyasini so'rishdir. Autentifikatsiyaning o'zi ``authenticate`` "
"funksiyasi orqali amalga oshiriladi va loginning o'rniga autentifikatsiya "
"qilingan chaqiruvlarda ishlatiladigan foydalanuvchi identifikatorini "
"(``uid``) qaytaradi."

