#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:391
msgid "List records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni ro'yxatlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:393
msgid "Records can be listed and filtered via :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search`."
msgstr "Yozuvlar :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` orqali ro'yxatlanishi va filtrlanishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:395
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` takes a mandatory :ref:`domain "
"<reference/orm/domains>` filter (possibly empty), and returns the "
"database identifiers of all records matching the filter."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` majburiy :ref:`domen "
"<reference/orm/domains>` filtrini (bo'sh bo'lishi ham mumkin) qabul qiladi "
"va filtrga mos keladigan barcha yozuvlarning ma'lumotlar bazasi "
"identifikatorlarini qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:401
msgid "To list customer companies, for instance:"
msgstr "Masalan, mijoz kompaniyalarini ro'yxatlash uchun:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:446
msgid "Pagination"
msgstr "Sahifalash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:448
msgid ""
"By default a search will return the ids of all records matching the "
"condition, which may be a huge number. ``offset`` and ``limit`` "
"parameters are available to only retrieve a subset of all matched "
"records."
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha qidiruv shartga mos keladigan barcha yozuvlarning "
"identifikatorlarini qaytaradi, bu juda katta son bo'lishi mumkin. "
"``offset`` va ``limit`` parametrlari faqat barcha mos yozuvlarning "
"to'plamini olish uchun mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:499
msgid "Count records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni hisoblash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:501
msgid ""
"Rather than retrieve a possibly gigantic list of records and count them, "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` can be used to retrieve only the "
"number of records matching the query. It takes the same :ref:`domain "
"<reference/orm/domains>` filter as :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` and "
"no other parameter."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlarning katta ro'yxatini olish va ularni hisoblash o'rniga, "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_count` so'rovga mos keladigan yozuvlar "
"sonini olish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. U :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` "
"bilan bir xil :ref:`domen <reference/orm/domains>` filtrini qabul qiladi "
"va boshqa parametr yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:552
msgid ""
"Calling ``search`` then ``search_count`` (or the other way around) may "
"not yield coherent results if other users are using the server: stored "
"data could have changed between the calls."
msgstr ""
"``search`` keyin ``search_count`` ni chaqirish (yoki aksincha) boshqa "
"foydalanuvchilar serverdan foydalanayotgan bo'lsa izchil natijalar "
"bermaydi: saqlangan ma'lumotlar chaqiruvlar orasida o'zgargan bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:557
msgid "Read records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni o'qish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:559
msgid ""
"Record data are accessible via the :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` "
"method, which takes a list of ids (as returned by "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search`), and optionally a list of fields to "
"fetch. By default, it fetches all the fields the current user can read, "
"which tends to be a huge amount."
msgstr ""
"Yozuv ma'lumotlariga :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` metodi orqali "
"kirish mumkin, u identifikatorlar ro'yxatini (:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` "
"tomonidan qaytarilganidek) va ixtiyoriy ravishda olinadigan maydonlar "
"ro'yxatini qabul qiladi. Standart bo'yicha joriy foydalanuvchi o'qiy "
"oladigan barcha maydonlarni oladi, bu odatda juda ko'p miqdor."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:639
msgid "Conversely, picking only three fields deemed interesting."
msgstr "Aksincha, faqat qiziqarli deb hisoblangan uchta maydonni tanlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:687
msgid "Even if the ``id`` field is not requested, it is always returned."
msgstr "``id`` maydoni so'ralмagan bo'lsa ham, u har doim qaytariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:690
msgid "List record fields"
msgstr "Yozuv maydonlarini ro'yxatlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:692
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get` can be used to inspect a model's "
"fields and check which ones seem to be of interest."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get` modelning maydonlarini tekshirish "
"va qaysilar qiziqarli ekanini aniqlash uchun ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:695
msgid ""
"Because it returns a large amount of meta-information (it is also used by"
" client programs) it should be filtered before printing, the most "
"interesting items for a human user are ``string`` (the field's label), "
"``help`` (a help text if available) and ``type`` (to know which values to"
" expect, or to send when updating a record)."
msgstr ""
"U katta miqdordagi meta-ma'lumotlarni qaytarganligi sababli (u mijoz "
"dasturlari tomonidan ham ishlatiladi) chop etishdan oldin filtrlanishi "
"kerak, odam foydalanuvchisi uchun eng qiziqarli elementlar ``string`` "
"(maydonning yorlig'i), ``help`` (mavjud bo'lsa yordam matni) va ``type`` "
"(qaysi qiymatlarni kutish yoki yozuvni yangilashda yuborish kerakligini bilish uchun)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:784
msgid "Search and read"
msgstr "Qidirish va o'qish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:786
msgid ""
"Because it is a very common task, Odoo provides a "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_read` shortcut which, as its name "
"suggests, is equivalent to a :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` followed "
"by a :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read`, but avoids having to perform two "
"requests and keep ids around."
msgstr ""
"Bu juda keng tarqalgan vazifa bo'lganligi sababli, Odoo "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search_read` yorliqni taqdim etadi, bu nomi "
"ko'rsatganidek :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` dan keyin "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` ga teng, lekin ikki so'rov bajarish va "
"identifikatorlarni saqlash kerakligini oldini oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:792
msgid ""
"Its arguments are similar to :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search`'s, but it "
"can also take a list of ``fields`` (like :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read`,"
" if that list is not provided it will fetch all fields of matched "
"records)."
msgstr ""
"Uning argumentlari :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` ning argumentlariga "
"o'xshash, lekin u ``fields`` ro'yxatini ham qabul qila oladi (masalan "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` kabi, agar bu ro'yxat taqdim etilmasa, "
"mos yozuvlarning barcha maydonlarini oladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:880
msgid "Create records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:882
msgid ""
"Records of a model are created using :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create`. "
"The method creates a single record and returns its database identifier."
msgstr ""
"Model yozuvlari :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` yordamida yaratiladi. "
"Metod bitta yozuv yaratadi va uning ma'lumotlar bazasi identifikatorini qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:885
msgid ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` takes a mapping of fields to values, "
"used to initialize the record. For any field which has a default value "
"and is not set through the mapping argument, the default value will be "
"used."
msgstr ""
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` yozuvni ishga tushirish uchun "
"ishlatiladigan maydonlarning qiymatlarga xaritasini qabul qiladi. "
"Standart qiymatga ega va xarita argumenti orqali o'rnatilmagan har qanday "
"maydon uchun standart qiymat ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:933
msgid ""
"While most value types are what would expect (integer for "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Integer`, string for :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` or "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Text`),"
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik qiymat turlari kutilganidek bo'lsa-da (:class:`~odoo.fields.Integer` "
"uchun butun son, :class:`~odoo.fields.Char` yoki :class:`~odoo.fields.Text` "
"uchun satr),"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:937
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Date`, :class:`~odoo.fields.Datetime` and "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Binary` fields use string values"
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Date`, :class:`~odoo.fields.Datetime` va "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Binary` maydonlari satr qiymatlaridan foydalanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:939
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` and :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` use a "
"special command protocol detailed in :meth:`the documentation to the "
"write method <odoo.models.Model.write>`."
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` va :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` "
":meth:`write metodi hujjatlarida <odoo.models.Model.write>` batafsil "
"ko'rsatilgan maxsus buyruq protokolidan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:944
msgid "Update records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni yangilash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:946
msgid ""
"Records can be updated using :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write`. It takes a"
" list of records to update and a mapping of updated fields to values "
"similar to :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create`."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write` yordamida yangilanishi mumkin. "
"U yangilanayotgan yozuvlar ro'yxatini va :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.create` "
"ga o'xshash yangilangan maydonlarning qiymatlarga xaritasini qabul qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:950
msgid ""
"Multiple records can be updated simultaneously, but they will all get the"
" same values for the fields being set. It is not possible to perform "
"\"computed\" updates (where the value being set depends on an existing "
"value of a record)."
msgstr ""
"Bir vaqtning o'zida bir nechta yozuvlarni yangilash mumkin, lekin "
"o'rnatiladigan maydonlar uchun hammasiga bir xil qiymatlar beriladi. "
"\"Hisoblangan\" yangilanishlarni (o'rnatiladigan qiymat yozuvning mavjud "
"qiymatiga bog'liq bo'lsa) bajarish mumkin emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1027
msgid "Delete records"
msgstr "Yozuvlarni o'chirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1029
msgid ""
"Records can be deleted in bulk by providing their ids to "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.unlink`."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar ularning identifikatorlarini :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.unlink` "
"ga taqdim etish orqali ommaviy ravishda o'chirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1100
msgid "Inspection and introspection"
msgstr "Ko'zdan kechirish va o'z-o'zini tahlil qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1102
msgid ""
"While we previously used :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get` to query a"
" model and have been using an arbitrary model from the start, Odoo stores"
" most model metadata inside a few meta-models which allow both querying "
"the system and altering models and fields (with some limitations) on the "
"fly over XML-RPC."
msgstr ""
"Oldin modelni so'rash uchun :meth:`~odoo.models.Model.fields_get` dan "
"foydalangan bo'lsak va boshidan ixtiyoriy modeldan foydalanib kelgan bo'lsak "
"ham, Odoo ko'pchilik model metadata sini bir nechta meta-modellar ichida "
"saqlaydi, bu ham tizimni so'rash, ham XML-RPC orqali tezda modellar va "
"maydonlarni o'zgartirish imkonini beradi (ba'zi cheklovlar bilan)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1111
msgid "``ir.model``"
msgstr "``ir.model``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1113
msgid "Provides information about Odoo models via its various fields."
msgstr "Odoo modellari haqida turli maydonlari orqali ma'lumot beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1116
msgid "a human-readable description of the model"
msgstr "modelning odam o'qiy oladigan tavsifi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1117
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3008
msgid "``model``"
msgstr "``model``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1118
msgid "the name of each model in the system"
msgstr "tizimda har bir modelning nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1120
msgid ""
"whether the model was generated in Python code (``base``) or by creating "
"an ``ir.model`` record (``manual``)"
msgstr ""
"model Python kodida yaratilgan (``base``) yoki ``ir.model`` yozuvi "
"yaratish orqali (``manual``) yaratilgan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1123
msgid "``field_id``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1123
msgid ""
"list of the model's fields through a :class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` to "
":ref:`reference/webservice/inspection/fields`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`reference/webservice/inspection/fields` ga :class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` "
"orqali modelning maydonlari ro'yxati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1126
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` to the "
":doc:`../reference/user_interface/view_architectures` defined for the "
"model"
msgstr ""
"model uchun belgilangan :doc:`../reference/user_interface/view_architectures` "
"ga :class:`~odoo.fields.One2many`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1130
msgid "``access_ids``"
msgstr "``access_ids``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1129
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` relation to the "
":ref:`reference/security/acl` set on the model"
msgstr ""
"modelda o'rnatilgan :ref:`reference/security/acl` ga "
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` munosabati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1132
msgid "``ir.model`` can be used to"
msgstr "``ir.model`` quyidagi uchun ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1134
msgid ""
"Query the system for installed models (as a precondition to operations on"
" the model or to explore the system's content)."
msgstr ""
"O'rnatilgan modellar uchun tizimni so'rash (model bo'yicha operatsiyalar "
"uchun oldindan shart yoki tizim mazmunini o'rganish uchun)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1136
msgid ""
"Get information about a specific model (generally by listing the fields "
"associated with it)."
msgstr ""
"Muayyan model haqida ma'lumot olish (odatda u bilan bog'liq maydonlarni "
"ro'yxatlab)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1138
msgid "Create new models dynamically over RPC."
msgstr "RPC orqali dinamik yangi modellar yaratish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1141
msgid "Custom model names must start with ``x_``."
msgstr "Maxsus model nomlari ``x_`` bilan boshlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1142
msgid ""
"The ``state`` must be provided and set to ``manual``, otherwise the model"
" will not be loaded."
msgstr ""
"``state`` taqdim etilishi va ``manual`` ga o'rnatilishi kerak, aks holda "
"model yuklanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1144
msgid "It is not possible to add new *methods* to a custom model, only fields."
msgstr "Maxsus modelga yangi *metodlar* qo'shish mumkin emas, faqat maydonlar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1148
msgid ""
"A custom model will initially contain only the \"built-in\" fields "
"available on all models:"
msgstr ""
"Maxsus model dastlab barcha modellarda mavjud bo'lgan faqat \"o'rnatilgan\" "
"maydonlarni o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1271
msgid "``ir.model.fields``"
msgstr "``ir.model.fields``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1273
msgid ""
"Provides information about the fields of Odoo models and allows adding "
"custom fields without using Python code."
msgstr ""
"Odoo modellari maydonlari haqida ma'lumot beradi va Python kodi ishlatmasdan "
"maxsus maydonlar qo'shish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1277
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` to "
":ref:`reference/webservice/inspection/models` to which the field belongs"
msgstr ""
"maydon tegishli :ref:`reference/webservice/inspection/models` ga "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1280
msgid "the field's technical name (used in ``read`` or ``write``)"
msgstr "maydonning texnik nomi (``read`` yoki ``write`` da ishlatiladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1281
msgid "``field_description``"
msgstr "``field_description``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1282
msgid "the field's user-readable label (e.g. ``string`` in ``fields_get``)"
msgstr "maydonning foydalanuvchi o'qiy oladigan yorlig'i (masalan ``fields_get`` dagi ``string``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1283
msgid "``ttype``"
msgstr "``ttype``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1284
msgid "the :ref:`type <reference/orm/fields>` of field to create"
msgstr "yaratilayotgan maydonning :ref:`turi <reference/orm/fields>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1286
msgid ""
"whether the field was created via Python code (``base``) or via "
"``ir.model.fields`` (``manual``)"
msgstr ""
"maydon Python kodi (``base``) orqali yoki ``ir.model.fields`` (``manual``) "
"orqali yaratilgan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1288
msgid "``required``, ``readonly``, ``translate``"
msgstr "``required``, ``readonly``, ``translate``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1289
msgid "enables the corresponding flag on the field"
msgstr "maydon uchun mos bayroqni yoqadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1291
msgid ""
":ref:`field-level access control <reference/security/fields>`, a "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` to ``res.groups``"
msgstr ""
":ref:`maydon darajasida kirish nazorati <reference/security/fields>`, "
"``res.groups`` ga :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1295
msgid ""
"``selection``, ``size``, ``on_delete``, ``relation``, ``relation_field``,"
" ``domain``"
msgstr ""
"``selection``, ``size``, ``on_delete``, ``relation``, ``relation_field``,"
" ``domain``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1294
msgid ""
"type-specific properties and customizations, see :ref:`the fields "
"documentation <reference/orm/fields>` for details"
msgstr ""
"turga xos xususiyatlar va moslashtirishlar, tafsilotlar uchun "
":ref:`maydonlar hujjatlariga <reference/orm/fields>` qarang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1298
msgid ""
"Like custom models, only new fields created with ``state=\"manual\"`` are"
" activated as actual fields on the model."
msgstr ""
"Maxsus modellar kabi, faqat ``state=\"manual\"`` bilan yaratilgan yangi "
"maydonlar modeldagi haqiqiy maydonlar sifatida faollashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/external_rpc_api.rst:1300
msgid ""
"Computed fields can not be added via ``ir.model.fields``, some field "
"meta-information (defaults, onchange) can not be set either."
msgstr ""
"Hisoblangan maydonlarni ``ir.model.fields`` orqali qo'shib bo'lmaydi, "
"ba'zi maydon meta-ma'lumotlari (standartlar, onchange) ham o'rnatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:3
msgid "Extract API"
msgstr "Extract API"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo provides a service to automate the processing of documents of type "
"**invoices**, **bank statements**, **expenses** or **resumes**."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **hisob-fakturalar**, **bank ko'chirmalari**, **xarajatlar** yoki "
"**rezyumeler** turdagi hujjatlar ishlovini avtomatlashtirish uchun xizmat "
"taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:11
msgid ""
"The service scans documents using an |OCR| engine and then uses "
":abbr:`AI(Artificial Intelligence)`-based algorithms to extract fields of"
" interest such as the total, due date, or invoice lines for *invoices*, "
"the initial and final balances, the date for *bank statements*, the "
"total, date for *expenses*, or the name, email, phone number for "
"*resumes*."
msgstr ""
"Xizmat hujjatlarni |OCR| dvigatelidan foydalanib skanerlaydi, keyin "
"*hisob-fakturalar* uchun jami, to'lov muddati yoki hisob-faktura satrlari, "
"*bank ko'chirmalari* uchun boshlang'ich va yakuniy qoldiqlar, sana, "
"*xarajatlar* uchun jami, sana yoki *rezyumeler* uchun ism, elektron pochta, "
"telefon raqami kabi qiziqarli maydonlarni chiqarish uchun "
":abbr:`AI(Artificial Intelligence)` ga asoslangan algoritmlardan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:16
msgid ""
"This service is a paid service. Each document processing will cost you "
"one credit from your document digitization |IAP| account. More "
"information about |IAP| accounts can be found :doc:`here "
"</applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>`."
msgstr ""
"Bu xizmat pullik xizmat. Har bir hujjat ishlovida hujjat raqamlashtirish "
"|IAP| hisobingizdan bir kredit sarflanadi. |IAP| hisoblari haqida qo'shimcha "
"ma'lumot :doc:`bu yerda </applications/essentials/in_app_purchase>` topilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:20
msgid ""
"You can either use this service directly in the Accounting, Expense, or "
"Recruitment App or through the API. The Extract API, which is detailed in"
" the next section, allows you to integrate our service directly into your"
" own projects."
msgstr ""
"Bu xizmatni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri Accounting, Expense yoki Recruitment "
"ilovasida yoki API orqali ishlatish mumkin. Keyingi bo'limda batafsil "
"ko'rsatilgan Extract API xizmatimizni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'z loyihalaringizga "
"integratsiya qilish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:28
msgid ""
"The extract API uses the JSON-RPC2_ protocol; its endpoint routes are "
"located at `https://extract.api.odoo.com`."
msgstr ""
"Extract API JSON-RPC2_ protokolidan foydalanadi; uning endpoint yo'llari "
"`https://extract.api.odoo.com` manzilida joylashgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:36
msgid "The version of the Extract API is specified in the route."
msgstr "Extract API versiyasi yo'lda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:42
msgid "The latest versions are:"
msgstr "Eng so'nggi versiyalar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:39
msgid "invoices: 123"
msgstr "hisob-fakturalar: 123"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:40
msgid "bank statements: 100"
msgstr "bank ko'chirmalari: 100"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:41
msgid "expenses: 132"
msgstr "xarajatlar: 132"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:42
msgid "applicant: 102"
msgstr "ariza beruvchi: 102"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:45
msgid "Flow"
msgstr "Jarayon"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:47
msgid "The flow is the same for each document type."
msgstr "Jarayon har bir hujjat turi uchun bir xil."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst
msgid ""
"Call :ref:`/parse <extract_api/parse>` to submit your documents (one call"
" for each document). On success, you receive a `document_token` in the "
"response."
msgstr ""
"Hujjatlaringizni yuborish uchun :ref:`/parse <extract_api/parse>` ni "
"chaqiring (har bir hujjat uchun bitta chaqiruv). Muvaffaqiyat holatida "
"javobda `document_token` olasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst
msgid ""
"You then have to regularly poll :ref:`/get_result "
"<extract_api/get_result>` to get the document's parsing status."
msgstr ""
"Keyin hujjatning tahlil qilish holatini olish uchun "
":ref:`/get_result <extract_api/get_result>` ni muntazam so'rashingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can provide a `webhook_url` at the time of the call to"
" :ref:`/parse <extract_api/parse>` and you will be notified (via a POST "
"request) when the result is ready."
msgstr ""
"Muqobil ravishda, :ref:`/parse <extract_api/parse>` ga chaqiruv vaqtida "
"`webhook_url` taqdim etishingiz mumkin va natija tayyor bo'lganda "
"(POST so'rovi orqali) xabar olasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:57
msgid ""
"The HTTP POST method should be used for all of them. A python "
"implementation of the full flow for invoices can be found :download:`here"
" <extract_api/implementation.py>` and a token for integration testing is "
"provided in the :ref:`integration testing section "
"<latestextract_api/integration_testing>`."
msgstr ""
"Barchasi uchun HTTP POST metodi ishlatilishi kerak. Hisob-fakturalar uchun "
"to'liq jarayonning Python implementatsiyasi :download:`bu yerda "
"<extract_api/implementation.py>` topilishi mumkin va integratsiya sinovi uchun "
"token :ref:`integratsiya sinovi bo'limida <latestextract_api/integration_testing>` "
"taqdim etilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:64
msgid "Parse"
msgstr "Tahlil qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:66
msgid ""
"Request the digitization of a document. The route will return a "
"`document_token` that you can use to fetch the result of your request."
msgstr ""
"Hujjatni raqamlashtirishni so'rang. Yo'l so'rovingiz natijasini olish "
"uchun ishlatishingiz mumkin bo'lgan `document_token` qaytaradi."

