msgstr "``documents`` (majburiy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:100
msgid ""
"The document must be provided as a Base64 string in the ASCII encoding. "
"The list should contain only one document. This field is a list only for "
"legacy reasons. The supported formats are *pdf*, *png* and *jpg*."
msgstr ""
"Hujjat ASCII kodlashdagi Base64 satri sifatida taqdim etilishi kerak. "
"Ro'yxat faqat bitta hujjat o'z ichiga olishi kerak. Bu maydon faqat "
"meros sabablar uchun ro'yxat. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan formatlar: *pdf*, *png* va *jpg*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:103
msgid "``dbuuid`` (optional)"
msgstr "``dbuuid`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:104
