msgstr "Odoo ma’lumotlar bazasining noyob identifikatori."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:106
msgid "``webhook_url`` (optional)"
msgstr "``webhook_url`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:106
msgid ""
"A webhook URL can be provided. An empty POST request will be sent to "
"``webhook_url/document_token`` when the result is ready."
msgstr ""
"Webhook URL taqdim etilishi mumkin. Natija tayyor bo’lganda "
"``webhook_url/document_token`` ga bo’sh POST so’rovi yuboriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:135
msgid "``user_infos`` (optional)"
msgstr "``user_infos`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:109
msgid ""
"Information concerning the person sending the document to the extract "
"service. It can be the client or the supplier (depending on the "
"``perspective``). This information is not required in order for the "
"service to work but it greatly improves the quality of the result."
msgstr ""
"Hujjatni extract xizmatiga yuborayotgan shaxs haqida ma’lumot. Bu mijoz "
"yoki yetkazib beruvchi bo’lishi mumkin (``perspective`` ga qarab). Bu "
"ma’lumot xizmat ishlashi uchun talab qilinmaydi, lekin natija sifatini "
"sezilarli darajada yaxshilaydi."

