"if not provided."
msgstr ""
"Xarid buyurtmasini aniqlash uchun regex. Taqdim etilmasa Odoo PO "
"formatiga qaytadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:135
msgid "``perspective`` (optional)"
msgstr "``perspective`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:131
msgid ""
"Can be ``client`` or ``supplier``. This field is useful for invoices "
"only. ``client`` means that the user information provided are related to "
"the client of the invoice. ``supplier`` means that it’s related to the "
"supplier. If not provided, client will be used."
msgstr ""
"``client`` yoki ``supplier`` bo’lishi mumkin. Bu maydon faqat "
"hisob-fakturalar uchun foydali. ``client`` taqdim etilgan foydalanuvchi "
"ma’lumotlari hisob-faktura mijoziga tegishli ekanligini anglatadi. "
"``supplier`` esa yetkazib beruvchiga tegishliligini anglatadi. "
"Taqdim etilmasa, client ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/extract_api.rst:162
msgid ""
"The ``user_infos`` parameter is optional but it greatly improves the "
"quality of the result, especially for invoices. The more information you "
"can provide, the better."
msgstr ""
"``user_infos`` parametri ixtiyoriy, lekin natija sifatini sezilarli "
"darajada yaxshilaydi, ayniqsa hisob-fakturalar uchun. Qancha ko’p "
"ma’lumot taqdim etsangiz, shuncha yaxshi."

