"Each field of interest we want to extract from the document such as the "
"total or the due date are also called **features**. An exhaustive list of"
" all the extracted features associated to a type of document can be found"
" in the sections below."
msgstr ""
"Hujjatdan chiqarmoqchi bo’lgan jami yoki to’lov muddati kabi har bir "
"qiziqarli maydon ham **xususiyatlar** deb ataladi. Hujjat turiga bog’liq "
"barcha chiqarilgan xususiyatlarning to’liq ro’yxati quyidagi bo’limlarda topilishi mumkin."

