"For each feature, we return a list of candidates and we spotlight the "
"candidate our model predicts to be the best fit for the feature."
msgstr ""
"Har bir xususiyat uchun nomzodlar ro’yxatini qaytaramiz va modelimiz "
"xususiyatga eng mos deb taxmin qilgan nomzodga e’tibor qaratamiz."

