#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/assets.rst:317
msgid ""
"In most cases the assets declared in the manifest will largely suffice. "
"Yet for more flexibility, the framework also supports dynamic assets "
"declared in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ko'p hollarda manifestda e'lon qilingan aktivlar ko'p jihatdan yetarli. "
"Biroq ko'proq moslashuvchanlik uchun freymvork ma'lumotlar bazasida "
"e'lon qilingan dinamik aktivlarni ham qo'llab-quvvatlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/assets.rst:321
msgid ""
"This is done by creating `ir.asset` records. Those will be processed as "
"if they were found in a module manifest, and they give the same "
"expressive power as their manifest counterparts."
msgstr ""
