"the directives `replace`, `before` and `after`."
msgstr ""
"To'plamdagi pozitsiyani ko'rsatish uchun maqsadli fayl. Faqat `replace`, "
"`before` va `after` direktivalari bilan ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/assets.rst:360
