#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:277
msgid ""
"In practice, the `orm` service automatically adds the user context to "
"each of its requests. This is why it is usually not necessary to import "
"it directly in most cases."
msgstr ""
"Amalda, `orm` xizmati har bir so'roviga foydalanuvchi kontekstini "
"avtomatik qo'shadi. Shu sababli aksariyat holatlarda uni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"import qilish odatda shart emas."

