#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:285
msgid "Action Context"
msgstr "Amal konteksti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:287
msgid ""
"The :ref:`ir.actions.act_window<reference/actions/window>` and "
":ref:`ir.actions.client<reference/actions/client>` support an optional "
"`context` field. This field is a `char` that represents an object. "
"Whenever the corresponding action is loaded in the web client, this "
"context field will be evaluated as an object and given to the component "
"that corresponds to the action."
msgstr ""
":ref:`ir.actions.act_window<reference/actions/window>` va "
":ref:`ir.actions.client<reference/actions/client>` ixtiyoriy `context` "
"maydonini qo'llab-quvvatlaydi. Bu maydon ob'ektni ifodalovchi `char` dir. "
"Tegishli amal veb-mijozda yuklanganida, bu kontekst maydoni ob'ekt sifatida "
"baholanadi va amalga mos komponentga beriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:297
msgid ""
"It can be used in many different ways. For example, the views add the "
"action context to every requests made to the server. Another important "
"use is to activate some search filter by default (see example above)."
msgstr ""
"U ko'plab turli usullarda ishlatilishi mumkin. Masalan, ko'rinishlar "
"serverga har bir so'rovga amal kontekstini qo'shadi. Yana bir muhim "
"ishlatish stanchi chidamli qidiruv filtrini standart tarzda faollashtirish "
"(yuqoridagi misolga qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:301
msgid ""
"Sometimes, when we execute new actions manually (so, programmatically, in"
" javascript), it is useful to be able to extend the action context. This "
"can be done with the `additional_context` argument."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zida yangi amallarni qo'lda (ya'ni, dasturiy tarzda, javascript da) "
"bajarishimizda, amal kontekstini kengaytira olish foydali. Bu "
"`additional_context` argumenti yordamida amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:317
msgid ""
"In this example, the action with xml_id `addon_name.something` will be "
"loaded, and its context will be extended with the `default_period_id` "
"value. This is a very important usecase that lets developers combine "
"actions together by providing some information to the next action."
msgstr ""
"Bu misolda, xml_id `addon_name.something` bilan amal yuklanadi va uning "
"konteksti `default_period_id` qiymati bilan kengaytiriladi. Bu ishlab "
"chiquvchilarga keyingi amalga ma'lumot berish orqali amallarni birlashtirish "
"imkonini beruvchi juda muhim foydalanish holatidir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:325
msgid "Python Interpreter"
msgstr "Python tarjimoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:327
