#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:603
msgid "Debug mode"
msgstr "Debug rejimi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:605
msgid ""
"Odoo can sometimes operate in a special mode called the `debug` mode. It "
"is used for two main purposes:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ba'zida `debug` rejimi deb ataladigan maxsus rejimda ishlashi mumkin. "
"U ikki asosiy maqsad uchun ishlatiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:608
msgid "display additional information/fields for some particular screens,"
msgstr "ba'zi muayyan ekranlar uchun qo'shimcha ma'lumot/maydonlarni ko'rsatish,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:609
msgid "provide some additional tools to help developer debug the Odoo interface."
msgstr ""
"ishlab chiquvchiga Odoo interfeysini debug qilishga yordam beruvchi "
"qo'shimcha vositalar taqdim etish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:611
msgid ""
"The `debug` mode is described by a string. An empty string means that the"
" `debug` mode is not active. Otherwise, it is active.  If the string "
"contains `assets` or `tests`, then the corresponding specific sub modes "
"are activated (see below). Both modes can be active at the same time, for"
" example with the string `assets,tests`."
msgstr ""
"`debug` rejimi satr bilan tavsiflanadi. Bo'sh satr `debug` rejimi faol "
"emasligini anglatadi. Aks holda, u faol. Agar satr `assets` yoki `tests` "
"ni o'z ichiga olsa, tegishli maxsus alt rejimlar faollashtiriladi (quyida "
"qarang). Ikkala rejim ham bir vaqtda faol bo'lishi mumkin, masalan "
"`assets,tests` satri bilan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:616
msgid ""
"The `debug` mode current value can be read in the "
":ref:`environment<frontend/framework/environment>`: `env.debug`."
msgstr ""
"`debug` rejimining joriy qiymatini "
":ref:`muhit<frontend/framework/environment>` da o'qish mumkin: `env.debug`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:621
msgid ""
"To show menus, fields or view elements only in debug mode, you should "
"target the group `base.group_no_one`:"
msgstr ""
"Menyular, maydonlar yoki ko'rinish elementlarini faqat debug rejimida "
"ko'rsatish uchun `base.group_no_one` guruhini nishonlash kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:629
msgid ":ref:`Activate the debug mode <developer-mode>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Debug rejimini faollashtirish <developer-mode>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:635
msgid "Assets mode"
msgstr "Aktivlar rejimi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:637
msgid ""
"The `debug=assets` sub mode is useful to debug javascript code: once "
"activated, the :ref:`assets<reference/assets>` bundles are no longer "
"minified, and source-maps are generated as well. This makes it useful to "
"debug all kind of javascript code."
msgstr ""
"`debug=assets` alt rejimi javascript kodini debug qilish uchun foydali: "
"faollashtirilgandan so'ng, :ref:`aktivlar<reference/assets>` to'plamlari "
"endi minifikatsiya qilinmaydi va manba xaritalar ham yaratiladi. Bu barcha "
"turdagi javascript kodini debug qilish uchun foydali qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:644
msgid "Tests mode"
msgstr "Testlar rejimi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:646
msgid ""
"There is another sub mode named `tests`: if enabled, the server injects "
"the bundle `web.assets_tests` in the page. This bundle contains mostly "
"test tours (tours whose purpose is to test a feature, not to show "
"something interesting to users). The `tests` mode is then useful to be "
"able to run these tours."
msgstr ""
"`tests` deb nomlangan yana bir alt rejim mavjud: yoqilganda, server "
"sahifaga `web.assets_tests` to'plamini kiritadi. Bu to'plam asosan test "
"sayohatlarini o'z ichiga oladi (maqsadi foydalanuvchilarga qiziqarli narsa "
"ko'rsatish emas, balki xususiyatni sinab ko'rish bo'lgan sayohatlar). "
"`tests` rejimi bu sayohatlarni ishga tushirish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/framework_overview.rst:652
