msgstr "`Owl Repository <https://github.com/odoo/owl>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:5
msgid "Hooks"
msgstr "Hooklar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:7
msgid ""
"`Owl hooks "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md>`_ are a "
"way to factorize code, even if it depends on some component lifecycle. "
"Most hooks provided by Owl are related to the lifecycle of a component, "
"but some of them (such as `useComponent "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#usecomponent>`_)"
" provide a way to build specific hooks."
msgstr ""
"`Owl hooklari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md>`_ ba'zi "
"komponent hayot sikliga bog'liq bo'lsa ham kodni faktorizatsiya qilish "
"usulidir. Owl tomonidan taqdim etilgan hooklar ko'pchiligi komponent hayot "
"sikliga bog'liq, lekin ularning ba'zilari (masalan, `useComponent "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#usecomponent>`_) "
"maxsus hooklarni yaratish usulini taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:13
msgid ""
"Using these hooks, it is possible to build many customized hooks that "
"help solve a specific problem, or make some common tasks easier. The rest"
" of this page documents the list of hooks provided by the Odoo web "
"framework."
msgstr ""
"Bu hooklardan foydalanib, muayyan muammoni hal qilishga yordam beruvchi "
"yoki ba'zi umumiy vazifalarni osonlashtiradigan ko'plab moslashtirgan "
"hooklarni yaratish mumkin. Ushbu sahifaning qolgan qismi Odoo veb "
"freymvorki tomonidan taqdim etiladigan hooklar ro'yxatini hujjatlashtiradi."

