"Helps positioning an HTMLElement (the `popper`) relatively to another "
"HTMLElement (the `reference`). This hook ensures the positioning is "
"updated when the window is resized/scrolled."
msgstr ""
"HTMLElement (`popper`) ni boshqa HTMLElement (`reference`) ga nisbatan "
"joylashtirishga yordam beradi. Bu hook oyna o'lchamlari o'zgartirilganda/ "
"aylantirilganda joylashuv yangilanishini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:212
msgid ""
"You should indicate your `popper` element using a `t-ref directive "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_."
msgstr ""
"`popper` elementingizni `t-ref direktivi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_ "
"yordamida ko'rsatishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:219
msgid "the target HTMLElement to be positioned from"
msgstr "joylashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan nishon HTMLElement"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:221
msgid "the positioning options (see table below)"
msgstr "joylashuv opsiyalari (quyidagi jadvalga qarang)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:230
msgid "`popper`"
msgstr "`popper`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:232
msgid ""
"this is a `useRef reference "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_"
" for the element that will get positioned. Default is `\"popper\"`."
msgstr ""
"bu joylashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan element uchun `useRef havolasi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_ dir. "
"Standart `\"popper\"` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:234
msgid "`container`"
msgstr "`container`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:235
msgid "HTMLElement"
msgstr "HTMLElement"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:236
msgid ""
"the container from which the popper is expected not to overflow. If "
"overflowing occurs, other popper positions are tried until a not "
"overflowing one is found. (default: the `<html/>` node)"
msgstr ""
"popperning toshib chiqmasligi kutilgan konteyner. Agar toshib chiqish "
"sodir bo'lsa, toshib chiqmaydigan biri topilgunga qadar boshqa popper "
"pozitsiyalari sinab ko'riladi. (standart: `<html/>` tugun)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:239
msgid "`margin`"
msgstr "`margin`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:240
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:456
msgid "number"
msgstr "raqam"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:241
msgid "added margin between popper and reference elements (default: `0`)"
msgstr "popper va havola elementlari o'rtasiga qo'shilgan margin (standart: `0`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:242
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:487
msgid "`position`"
msgstr "`position`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:243
msgid "Direction[-Variant]"
msgstr "Direction[-Variant]"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:244
msgid ""
"the desired position. It is a string composed of one `Direction` and one "
"`Variant` separated by a dash character. `Direction` could be: `top`, "
"`bottom`, `right`, `left`. `Variant` could be: `start`, `middle`, `end`, "
"`fit`. The variant can be omitted (default variant is `middle`). The "
"`fit` variant means that the popper would have the exact same width or "
"height, depending on the chosen direction. Examples of valid positions: "
"`right-end`, `top-start`, `left-middle`, `left`, `bottom-fit`. (default "
"position: `bottom`)"
msgstr ""
"kerakli pozitsiya. Bu chiziqcha bilan ajratilgan bir `Direction` va bir "
"`Variant` dan iborat satrdir. `Direction` quyidagilar bo'lishi mumkin: "
"`top`, `bottom`, `right`, `left`. `Variant` quyidagilar bo'lishi mumkin: "
"`start`, `middle`, `end`, `fit`. Variantni o'tkazib yuborish mumkin "
"(standart variant `middle`). `fit` varianti popperning tanlangan yo'nalishga "
"qarab aniq bir xil kenglik yoki balandlikka ega bo'lishini anglatadi. "
"To'g'ri pozitsiyalar misollari: `right-end`, `top-start`, `left-middle`, "
"`left`, `bottom-fit`. (standart pozitsiya: `bottom`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:253
msgid "`onPositioned`"
msgstr "`onPositioned`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:254
msgid "(el: HTMLElement, position: PositioningSolution) => void"
msgstr "(el: HTMLElement, position: PositioningSolution) => void"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:255
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"a callback that will be called everytime a positioning occurs (e.g. on "
"component mounted/patched, document scroll, window resize...). Can be "
"used i.e. for dynamic styling regarding the current position. The "
"`PositioningSolution` is an object having the following type: `{ "
"direction: Direction, variant: Variant, top: number, left: number }`."
msgstr ""
"joylashuv sodir bo'lgan har safar chaqiriladigan qayta chaqiruv (masalan, "
"komponent o'rnatilganda/yamaldi, hujjat aylantirilganda, oyna o'lchamlari "
"o'zgartirilganda...). Masalan, joriy pozitsiyaga nisbatan dinamik stil "
"uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. `PositioningSolution` quyidagi turga ega ob'ekt: "
"`{ direction: Direction, variant: Variant, top: number, left: number }`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:297
msgid "useSpellCheck"
msgstr "useSpellCheck"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:307
msgid ""
"Activate the spellcheck state to an input or textarea on focus by a "
"`t-ref=\"spellcheck\"` in the current component. This state is then "
"removed on blur, as well as the red outline, which improves readability "
"of the content."
msgstr ""
"Joriy komponentda `t-ref=\"spellcheck\"` yordamida fokusda kirish yoki "
"textarea uchun imloviy tekshiruv holatini faollashtirish. Bu holat blur "
"da, shuningdek qizil chiziq bilan olib tashlanadi, bu mazmun o'qilishini "
"yaxshilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:311
msgid ""
"The hook can also be used on any HTML element with the `contenteditable` "
"attribute. To disable spellcheck completely on elements that might be "
"enabled by the hook, set explicitly the `spellcheck` attribute as `false`"
" on the element."
msgstr ""
"Hook ham `contenteditable` atributiga ega har qanday HTML elementda "
"ishlatilishi mumkin. Hook tomonidan yoqilishi mumkin bo'lgan elementlarda "
"imloviy tekshiruvni to'liq o'chirish uchun elementda `spellcheck` "
"atributini aniq `false` sifatida belgilang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:317
msgid ""
"In the following example, the spellcheck will be enabled on the first "
"input, the textarea and the div with `contenteditable=\"true\"`."
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi misolda imloviy tekshiruv birinchi kirish, textarea va "
"`contenteditable=\"true\"` bilan divda yoqiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:349
msgid "the spellcheck options (see table below)"
msgstr "imloviy tekshiruv opsiyalari (quyidagi jadvalga qarang)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:358
msgid "`refName`"
msgstr "`refName`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/hooks.rst:360
msgid ""
"this is a `useRef reference "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_"
" for the element that will be spellcheck enabled."
msgstr ""
"bu imloviy tekshiruv yoqiladigan element uchun `useRef havolasi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#useref>`_ dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:5
msgid "Javascript Modules"
msgstr "Javascript modullari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:7
msgid "Odoo supports three different kinds of javascript files:"
msgstr "Odoo uchta turli javascript fayl turlarini qo'llab-quvvatlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`plain javascript files <frontend/modules/plain_js>` (no module "
"system),"
msgstr ""
":ref:`oddiy javascript fayllari <frontend/modules/plain_js>` (modul "
"tizimisiz),"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`native javascript module <frontend/modules/native_js>`."
msgstr ":ref:`mahalliy javascript moduli <frontend/modules/native_js>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Odoo modules <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` (using a custom module"
" system),"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odoo modullari <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` (maxsus modul "
"tizimidan foydalanib),"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:13
msgid ""
"As described in the :ref:`assets management page <reference/assets>`, all"
" javascript files are bundled together and served to the browser. Note "
"that native javascript files are processed by the Odoo server and "
"transformed into Odoo custom modules."
msgstr ""
":ref:`aktivlarni boshqarish sahifasida <reference/assets>` tasvirlanganidek, "
"barcha javascript fayllar birlashtirilib brauzerga taqdim etiladi. E'tibor "
"bering, mahalliy javascript fayllari Odoo serveri tomonidan qayta ishlanadi "
"va Odoo maxsus modullariga aylantiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:17
msgid ""
"Let us briefly explain the purpose behind each kind of javascript file. "
"Plain javascript files should be reserved only for external libraries and"
" some small specific low level purposes. All new javascript files should "
"be created in the native javascript module system. The custom module "
"system is only useful for old, not yet converted files."
msgstr ""
"Har bir turdagi javascript faylning maqsadini qisqacha tushuntiramiz. "
"Oddiy javascript fayllari faqat tashqi kutubxonalar va ba'zi kichik maxsus "
"past darajadagi maqsadlar uchun saqlanib qolinishi kerak. Barcha yangi "
"javascript fayllar mahalliy javascript modul tizimida yaratilishi kerak. "
"Maxsus modul tizimi faqat eski, hali konvertatsiya qilinmagan fayllar "
"uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:26
msgid "Plain Javascript files"
msgstr "Oddiy Javascript fayllari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:28
msgid ""
"Plain javascript files can contain arbitrary content. It is advised to "
"use the *iife* :dfn:`immediately invoked function execution` style when "
"writing such a file:"
msgstr ""
"Oddiy javascript fayllari ixtiyoriy mazmunni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin. "
"Bunday faylni yozishda *iife* :dfn:`darhol chaqiriladigan funksiya bajarish` "
"uslubidan foydalanish tavsiya etiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:39
msgid ""
"The advantages of such files is that we avoid leaking local variables to "
"the global scope."
msgstr ""
"Bunday fayllarning afzalligi shundaki, lokal o'zgaruvchilarning global "
"doiraga oqib chiqishidan qochamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:42
msgid ""
"Clearly, plain javascript files do not offer the benefits of a module "
"system, so one needs to be careful about the order in the bundle (since "
"the browser will execute them precisely in that order)."
msgstr ""
"Aniq, oddiy javascript fayllari modul tizimining afzalliklarini taqdim "
"etmaydi, shuning uchun to'plamdagi tartibga ehtiyot bo'lish kerak (chunki "
"brauzer ularni aynan shu tartibda bajaradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:47
msgid "In Odoo, all external libraries are loaded as plain javascript files."
msgstr "Odoo da barcha tashqi kutubxonalar oddiy javascript fayllari sifatida yuklanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:52
msgid "Native Javascript Modules"
msgstr "Mahalliy Javascript modullari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:54
msgid ""
"Odoo javascript code uses the native javascript module system. This is "
"simpler, and brings the benefits of a better developer experience with a "
"better integration with the IDE."
msgstr ""
"Odoo javascript kodi mahalliy javascript modul tizimidan foydalanadi. "
"Bu soddaroq va IDE bilan yaxshiroq integratsiya bilan yaxshiroq ishlab "
"chiquvchi tajribasining afzalliklarini keltiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:57
msgid ""
