"<frontend/modules/odoo_module>` transpile qiladi. Bu fayl keyin quyidagiga "
"o'xshash Odoo moduliga transpile qilinadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:86
msgid ""
"So, as you can see, the transformation is basically adding `odoo.define` "
"on top and updating the import/export statements. This is an opt-out "
"system, it's possible to tell the transpiler to ignore the file."
msgstr ""
"Ko'ringanidek, o'zgartirish asosan yuqoriga `odoo.define` qo'shish va "
"import/export operatorlarini yangilashdan iborat. Bu opt-out tizim, "
"transpilerga faylni e'tiborsiz qoldirishni aytish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:98
msgid ""
"Note the comment in the first line: it describes that this file should be"
" ignored."
msgstr ""
"Birinchi qatordagi izohga e'tibor bering: u bu fayl e'tiborsiz "
"qoldirilishi kerakligini tavsiflaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:100
msgid ""
"In other folders, files aren't transpiled by default, it is opt-in. Odoo "
"will look at the first line of a JS file and check if it contains a "
"comment with *@odoo-module* and without the tag *ignore*. If so, it will "
"automatically be converted to an Odoo module."
msgstr ""
"Boshqa papkalarda fayllar standart tarzda transpile qilinmaydi, bu opt-in. "
"Odoo JS faylning birinchi qatoriga qarashadi va *@odoo-module* bilan *ignore* "
"tegi bo'lmasdan izoh o'z ichiga oladimi deb tekshiradi. Agar shunday bo'lsa, "
"u avtomatik ravishda Odoo moduliga aylantiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:111
msgid ""
"Another important point is that the transpiled module has an official "
"name: *@web/file_a*. This is the actual name of the module. Every "
"relative imports will be converted as well. Every file located in an Odoo"
" addon :file:`some_addon/static/src/path/to/file.js` will be assigned a "
"name prefixed by the addon name like this: *@some_addon/path/to/file*."
msgstr ""
"Yana bir muhim nuqta shundaki, transpile qilingan modul rasmiy nomga ega: "
"*@web/file_a*. Bu modulning haqiqiy nomi. Barcha nisbiy importlar ham "
"aylantiriladi. Odoo plaginida joylashgan har bir fayl "
":file:`some_addon/static/src/path/to/file.js` plagin nomi bilan old qo'shimcha "
"sifatida quyidagiga o'xshash nom oladi: *@some_addon/path/to/file*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:117
msgid ""
"Relative imports work, but only if the modules are in the same Odoo "
"addon. So, imagine that we have the following file structure:"
msgstr ""
"Nisbiy importlar ishlaydi, lekin faqat modullar bir xil Odoo plaginda "
"bo'lsa. Shunday qilib, quyidagi fayl tuzilmasiga ega ekanligimizni tasavvur "
"qiling:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:133
msgid "The file :file:`file_b` can import :file:`file_a` like this:"
msgstr ":file:`file_b` fayli :file:`file_a` ni quyidagicha import qilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:139
msgid "But :file:`file_c` need to use the full name:"
msgstr "Lekin :file:`file_c` to'liq nomdan foydalanishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:146
msgid "Aliased modules"
msgstr "Taxallus modullari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:148
msgid ""
"Because :ref:`Odoo modules <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` follow a "
"different module naming pattern, a system exists to allow a smooth "
"transition towards the new system. Currently, if a file is converted to a"
" module (and therefore follow the new naming convention), other files not"
" yet converted to ES6-like syntax in the project won't be able to require"
" the module. Aliases are here to map old names with new ones by creating "
"a small proxy function. The module can then be called by its new *and* "
"old name."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odoo modullari <frontend/modules/odoo_module>` boshqa modul nomlash "
"andozasiga amal qilganligi sababli, yangi tizimga silliq o'tishga ruxsat "
"beruvchi tizim mavjud. Hozirda, agar fayl modulga aylantirilsa (va shuning "
"uchun yangi nomlash kelishuviga amal qilsa), loyihadagi hali ES6 ga o'xshash "
"sintaksisga aylantirilmagan boshqa fayllar modulni talab qila olmaydi. "
"Taxalluslar kichik proksi funksiyasini yaratib eski nomlarni yangilariga "
"xaritalash uchun mavjud. Modul keyin yangi *va* eski nomi bilan chaqirilishi "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:154
msgid ""
"To add such alias, the comment tag on top of the file should look like "
"this:"
msgstr ""
"Bunday taxallus qo'shish uchun, fayl tepasidagi izoh tegi quyidagicha "
"ko'rinishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:165
msgid ""
"Then, the translated module will also create an alias with the requested "
"name:"
msgstr ""
"Keyin, tarjima qilingan modul ham so'ralgan nom bilan taxallus yaratadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:173
msgid ""
"The default behaviour of aliases is to re-export the ``default`` value of"
" the module they alias. This is because \"classic\" modules generally "
"export a single value which would be used directly, roughly matching the "
"semantics of default exports. However it is also possible to delegate "
"more directly, and follow the exact behaviour of the aliased module:"
msgstr ""
"Taxalluslarning standart xulq-atvori ular taxallus qiladigan modulning "
"``default`` qiymatini qayta eksport qilishdir. Buning sababi \"klassik\" "
"modullar odatda to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ishlatilishi mumkin bo'lgan yagona "
"qiymatni eksport qiladi, bu standart eksportlarning semantikasiga taxminan "
"mos keladi. Biroq, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri delegatsiya qilish va taxallus "
"qilingan modulning aniq xulq-atvoriga amal qilish ham mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:189
msgid ""
"In that case, this will define an alias with exactly the values exported "
"by the original module:"
msgstr ""
"Bunday holda, bu asl modul tomonidan eksport qilingan aynan qiymatlar "
"bilan taxallus aniqlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:199
msgid ""
"Only one alias can be defined using this method. If you were to need "
"another one to have, for example, three names to call the same module, "
"you would have to add a proxy manually. This is not good practice and "
"should be avoided unless there is no other options."
msgstr ""
"Bu usulda faqat bitta taxallus aniqlanishi mumkin. Agar boshqa bitta kerak "
"bo'lsa, masalan, bir xil modulni chaqirish uchun uchta nom bo'lsa, proksi "
"qo'lda qo'shishingiz kerak bo'ladi. Bu yaxshi amaliyot emas va boshqa "
"variant bo'lmasa bundan qochish kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:204
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3680
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "Cheklovlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:206
msgid ""
"For performance reasons, Odoo does not use a full javascript parser to "
"transform native modules. There are, therefore, a number of limitations "
"including but not limited to:"
msgstr ""
"Unumdorlik sabablari uchun, Odoo mahalliy modullarni o'zgartirish uchun "
"to'liq javascript parseri dan foydalanmaydi. Shuning uchun quyidagilar "
"bilan cheklanmagan bir qancha cheklovlar mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:210
msgid ""
"an `import` or `export` keyword cannot be preceded by a non-space "
"character,"
msgstr ""
"`import` yoki `export` kalit so'zi bo'sh joy bo'lmagan belgidan oldin "
"kelishi mumkin emas,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:211
msgid ""
"a multiline comment or string cannot have a line starting by `import` or "
"`export`"
msgstr ""
"ko'p satrli izoh yoki satr `import` yoki `export` bilan boshlangan "
"satrga ega bo'lishi mumkin emas"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:237
msgid "when you export an object, it can't contain a comment"
msgstr "ob'ekt eksport qilganingizda, u izohni o'z ichiga ola olmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:264
msgid ""
"Odoo needs a way to determine if a module is described by a path (like "
":file:`./views/form_view`) or a name (like `web.FormView`). It has to use"
" a heuristic to do just that: if there is a `/` in the name, it is "
"considered a path.  This means that Odoo does not really support module "
"names with a `/` anymore."
msgstr ""
"Odoo modulning yo'l (masalan :file:`./views/form_view`) yoki nom (masalan "
"`web.FormView`) bilan tasvirlanganligini aniqlash usulini talab qiladi. "
"Buning uchun evristikadan foydalanishi kerak: agar nomda `/` bo'lsa, "
"u yo'l deb hisoblanadi. Bu Odoo endi `/` bilan modul nomlarini haqiqatan "
"ham qo'llab-quvvatlamasligini anglatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:269
msgid ""
"As \"classic\" modules are not deprecated and there is currently no plan "
"to remove them, you can and should keep using them if you encounter "
"issues with, or are constrained by the limitations of, native modules. "
"Both styles can coexist within the same Odoo addon."
msgstr ""
"\"Klassik\" modullar eskirgan emas va hozirda ularni olib tashlash rejasi "
"yo'q, agar mahalliy modullar bilan muammolarga duch kelsangiz yoki ularning "
"cheklovlari tomonidan cheklanagan bo'lsangiz, ulardan foydalanishda davom "
"etishingiz mumkin va etishingiz kerak. Ikkala uslub ham bir xil Odoo plagini "
"ichida yonma-yon mavjud bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:277
msgid "Odoo Module System"
msgstr "Odoo modul tizimi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:279
msgid ""
"Odoo has defined a small module system (located in the file "
":file:`addons/web/static/src/js/boot.js`, which needs to be loaded "
"first). The Odoo module system, inspired by AMD, works by defining the "
"function `define` on the global odoo object. We then define each "
"javascript module by calling that function.  In the Odoo framework, a "
"module is a piece of code that will be executed as soon as possible.  It "
"has a name and potentially some dependencies.  When its dependencies are "
"loaded, a module will then be loaded as well.  The value of the module is"
" then the return value of the function defining the module."
msgstr ""
"Odoo kichik modul tizimini aniqlagan (birinchi yuklanishi kerak bo'lgan "
":file:`addons/web/static/src/js/boot.js` faylida joylashgan). AMD dan "
"ilhomlangan Odoo modul tizimi global odoo ob'ektida `define` funksiyasini "
"aniqlab ishlaydi. Biz keyin har bir javascript modulini o'sha funksiyani "
"chaqirish orqali aniqlaymiz. Odoo freymvorkida modul imkon qadar tezroq "
"bajarilishi kerak bo'lgan kod qismidir. U nomga va ehtimol ba'zi "
"bog'liqliqlarga ega. Uning bog'liqliqlari yuklanganida modul ham yuklanadi. "
"Modulning qiymati modulni aniqlagan funksiyaning qaytarish qiymatidir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:288
msgid "As an example, it may look like this:"
msgstr "Misol sifatida, quyidagicha ko'rinishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:313
msgid ""
"If some dependencies are missing/non ready, then the module will simply "
"not be loaded.  There will be a warning in the console after a few "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"Agar ba'zi bog'liqliklar yo'q bo'lsa/tayyor bo'lmasa, modul shunchaki "
"yuklanmaydi. Bir necha soniyadan so'ng konsolda ogohlantirish bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:316
msgid ""
"Note that circular dependencies are not supported. It makes sense, but it"
" means that one needs to be careful."
msgstr ""
"Aylanma bog'liqliklar qo'llab-quvvatlanmasligini e'tibor bering. Bu "
"mantiqli, lekin ehtiyot bo'lish kerakligini anglatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:320
msgid "Defining a module"
msgstr "Modul aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:322
msgid "The `odoo.define` method is given three arguments:"
msgstr "`odoo.define` metodi uchta argument oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:324
msgid ""
"`moduleName`: the name of the javascript module.  It should be a unique "
"string. The convention is to have the name of the odoo addon followed by "
"a specific description. For example, `web.Widget` describes a module "
"defined in the `web` addon, which exports a `Widget` class (because the "
"first letter is capitalized)"
msgstr ""
"`moduleName`: javascript modulining nomi. Bu noyob satr bo'lishi kerak. "
"Kelishuv Odoo plagini nomidan keyin muayyan tavsifga ega bo'lishdir. "
"Masalan, `web.Widget` `web` plaginida aniqlangan, `Widget` sinfini eksport "
"qiladigan modulni tavsiflaydi (chunki birinchi harf bosh harf bilan yozilgan)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:329
msgid ""
"If the name is not unique, an exception will be thrown and displayed in "
"the console."
msgstr ""
"Agar nom noyob bo'lmasa, istisno tashlanadi va konsolda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:332
msgid ""
"`dependencies`: It should be a list of strings, each corresponding to a "
"javascript module.  This describes the dependencies that are required to "
"be loaded before the module is executed."
msgstr ""
"`dependencies`: Bu har biri javascript moduliga mos keladigan satrlar "
"ro'yxati bo'lishi kerak. Bu modul bajarilishidan oldin yuklanishi kerak "
"bo'lgan bog'liqliklarni tavsiflaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:336
msgid ""
"finally, the last argument is a function which defines the module. Its "
"return value is the value of the module, which may be passed to other "
"modules requiring it."
msgstr ""
"Nihoyat, oxirgi argument modulni aniqlagan funksiya. Uning qaytarish "
"qiymati modulning qiymati bo'lib, uni talab qiluvchi boshqa modullarga "
"berilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:351
msgid "If an error happens, it will be logged (in debug mode) in the console:"
msgstr "Agar xato sodir bo'lsa, u (debug rejimida) konsolda jurnalga yoziladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:353
msgid ""
"`Missing dependencies`: These modules do not appear in the page. It is "
"possible that the JavaScript file is not in the page or that the module "
"name is wrong"
msgstr ""
"`Missing dependencies`: Bu modullar sahifada ko'rinmaydi. JavaScript fayli "
"sahifada bo'lmasligi yoki modul nomi noto'g'ri bo'lishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:356
msgid "`Failed modules`: A javascript error is detected"
msgstr "`Failed modules`: JavaScript xatosi aniqlandi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:358
msgid ""
"`Rejected modules`: The module returns a rejected Promise. It (and its "
"dependent modules) is not loaded."
msgstr ""
"`Rejected modules`: Modul rad etilgan Promise qaytaradi. U (va unga bog'liq "
"modullar) yuklanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:361
msgid "`Rejected linked modules`: Modules who depend on a rejected module"
msgstr "`Rejected linked modules`: Rad etilgan modulga bog'liq modullar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_modules.rst:363
msgid "`Non loaded modules`: Modules who depend on a missing or a failed module"
msgstr "`Non loaded modules`: Yo'q yoki muvaffaqiyatsiz modulga bog'liq modullar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:7
msgid "Javascript Reference"
msgstr "Javascript ma'lumotnomasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:9
msgid ""
"This document presents the Odoo Javascript framework. This framework is "
"not a large application in term of lines of code, but it is quite "
"generic, because it is basically a machine to turn a declarative "
"interface description into a live application, able to interact with "
"every model and records in the database.  It is even possible to use the "
"web client to modify the interface of the web client."
msgstr ""
"Bu hujjat Odoo Javascript freymvorkini taqdim etadi. Bu freymvork kod "
"satrlari nuqtai nazaridan katta ilova emas, lekin u juda umumiy, chunki "
"u asosan deklarativ interfeys tavsifini har bir model va ma'lumotlar bazasidagi "
"yozuvlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir qila oladigan jonli ilovaga aylantiruvchi "
"mashinadir. Veb-mijozdan foydalanib veb-mijoz interfeysini o'zgartirish "
"ham mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:19
msgid "The Javascript framework is designed to work with three main use cases:"
msgstr "Javascript freymvorki uchta asosiy foydalanish holatlarida ishlash uchun mo'ljallangan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:21
msgid ""
"the *web client*: this is the private web application, where one can view"
" and edit business data. This is a single page application (the page is "
"never reloaded, only the new data is fetched from the server whenever it "
"is needed)"
msgstr ""
"*veb-mijoz*: bu biznes ma'lumotlarini ko'rish va tahrirlash mumkin bo'lgan "
"shaxsiy veb ilova. Bu bitta sahifali ilova (sahifa hech qachon qayta "
"yuklanmaydi, faqat kerak bo'lganda yangi ma'lumotlar serverdan olinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:24
msgid ""
"the *website*: this is the public part of Odoo.  It allows an "
"unidentified user to browse some content, to shop or to perform many "
"actions, as a client. This is a classical website: various routes with "
"controllers and some javascript to make it work."
msgstr ""
"*veb-sayt*: bu Odoo ning ommaviy qismi. U aniqlanmagan foydalanuvchiga "
"mijoz sifatida ba'zi kontentni ko'rish, xarid qilish yoki ko'plab amallarni "
"bajarishga imkon beradi. Bu klassik veb-sayt: turli yo'llar boshqaruvchilar "
"va uni ishlatish uchun ba'zi javascript bilan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:28
msgid ""
"the *point of sale*: this is the interface for the point of sale. It is a"
" specialized single page application."
msgstr ""
"*sotish nuqtasi*: bu sotish nuqtasi uchun interfeys. Bu ixtisoslashtirilgan "
"bitta sahifali ilova."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:31
msgid ""
"Some javascript code is common to these three use cases, and is bundled "
"together (see below in the assets section).  This document will focus "
"mostly on the architecture of the web client."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi javascript kodi bu uchta foydalanish holatiga umumiy va birlashtirilib "
"paketlanadi (quyida aktivlar bo'limiga qarang). Ushbu hujjat asosan "
"veb-mijoz arxitekturasiga e'tibor qaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:36
msgid "Web client"
msgstr "Veb-mijoz"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:39
msgid "Single Page Application"
msgstr "Bitta sahifali ilova"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:41
msgid ""
"The web client is a single-page application: instead of requesting a full"
" page from the server each time the user performs an action, it only "
"loads what is needed to update the user interface (UI) as a result of "
"that action. While doing this, it also takes care of updating information"
" in the URL, so that, in most cases, refreshing the page or closing the "
"browser and opening it again shows you the same thing."
msgstr ""
"Veb-mijoz bitta sahifali ilova: foydalanuvchi amal bajarganida serverdan "
"har safar to'liq sahifa so'rash o'rniga, u faqat shu amal natijasida "
"foydalanuvchi interfeysini (UI) yangilash uchun kerakli narsani yuklaydi. "
"Buni qilayotganda, u URL dagi ma'lumotlarni yangilashga ham g'amxo'rlik "
"qiladi, shunda aksariyat holatlarda sahifani yangilash yoki brauzerini "
"yopib qayta ochish bir xil narsani ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:49
msgid "Overview of web client JS code"
msgstr "Veb-mijoz JS kodi umumiy ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:51
msgid ""
"Here, we give a very quick overview of the web client code, in the "
":file:`web` addon. The paths will be described relative to "
":file:`web/static/src`. The following description is deliberately not "
"exhaustive; the goal is only to give the reader a bird's eye view of the "
"architecture."
msgstr ""
"Bu yerda biz :file:`web` plagini dagi veb-mijoz kodining juda tezkor umumiy "
"ko'rinishini beramiz. Yo'llar :file:`web/static/src` ga nisbatan "
"tasvirlanadi. Quyidagi tavsif ataylab to'liq emas; maqsad faqat o'quvchiga "
"arxitekturaning qushning ko'z nuqtai nazarini berish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:56
msgid ""
":file:`module_loader.js`: this is the file that defines the Odoo "
"javascript module system.  It needs to be loaded before any other JS "
"module."
msgstr ""
":file:`module_loader.js`: bu Odoo javascript modul tizimini aniqlagan fayl. "
"U boshqa JS modullardan oldin yuklanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:58
msgid ""
":file:`core/`: this folder contains code that forms the lowest level of "
"the javascript framework and that can be used in the web client as well "
"as the website, portal, and point of sale application."
msgstr ""
":file:`core/`: bu papka javascript freymvorkining eng past darajasini "
"hosil qiluvchi va veb-sayt, portal va sotish nuqtasi ilovasida ham "
"ishlatilishi mumkin bo'lgan kodni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:61
msgid ""
":file:`weblient/`: this folder contains files that are specific to the "
"web client and cannot be used in the website or point of sale, such as "
"the action manager and the action service."
msgstr ""
":file:`webclient/`: bu papka veb-mijozga xos va veb-sayt yoki sotish "
"nuqtasida ishlatila olmaydigan fayllarni o'z ichiga oladi, masalan amal "
"boshqaruvchisi va amal xizmati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:64
msgid ""
":file:`webclient/webclient.js`: this is the webclient component proper. "
"It is mostly a wrapper for the action container and the navbar, and does "
"a few things that are required upon starting the application, such as "
"loading the state of the url."
msgstr ""
":file:`webclient/webclient.js`: bu to'g'ri webclient komponenti. Bu asosan "
"amal konteyneri va navbar uchun o'rash va url holatini yuklash kabi ilova "
"boshlanishida talab qilinadigan bir nechta narsani qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:67
msgid ""
":file:`webclient/actions/`: this folder contains the code responsible for"
" displaying and switching between actions."
msgstr ""
":file:`webclient/actions/`: bu papka amallarni ko'rsatish va ular o'rtasida "
"almashish uchun mas'ul kodni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:69
msgid ""
":file:`views/`: this folder contains the code for the view "
"infrastructure, as well as most of the views (some types of views are "
"added by other addons)."
msgstr ""
":file:`views/`: bu papka ko'rinish infratuzilmasi uchun kodni hamda "
"ko'rinishlarning ko'pchiligini o'z ichiga oladi (ba'zi ko'rinish turlari "
"boshqa plagin tomonidan qo'shiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:71
msgid ""
":file:`views/fields/`: contains the definition of the various field "
"components, as well as some utilities used by multiple fields."
msgstr ""
":file:`views/fields/`: turli maydon komponentlarining ta'rifini hamda "
"bir nechta maydon tomonidan ishlatiladigan ba'zi yordamchi vositalarni "
"o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:73
msgid ""
":file:`search/` all these files define the search view (it is not a view "
"in the point of view of the web client, only from the server point of "
"view)"
msgstr ""
":file:`search/` bu fayllarning barchasi qidiruv ko'rinishini aniqlaydi "
"(bu veb-mijoz nuqtai nazaridan ko'rinish emas, faqat server nuqtai "
"nazaridan)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:78
msgid "What to do if a file is not loaded/updated"
msgstr "Agar fayl yuklanmagan/yangilanmagan bo'lsa nima qilish kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:80
msgid ""
"There are many different reasons why a file may not be properly loaded.  "
"Here are a few things you can try to solve the issue:"
msgstr ""
"Fayl to'g'ri yuklanmasligi uchun ko'plab turli sabablari bo'lishi mumkin. "
"Muammoni hal qilish uchun sinab ko'rish mumkin bo'lgan bir nechta narsa:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:83
msgid ""
"Make sure you saved your file; forgetting to do that happens to the best "
"of us."
msgstr ""
"Faylingizni saqlaganingizga ishonch hosil qiling; buni unutish biz hammamiz "
"uchun sodir bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:84
msgid ""
"Take a look at the console (in the dev tools, usually opened with F12) "
"and check for errors."
msgstr ""
"Konsolga qarang (dev tools da, odatda F12 bilan ochiladi) va xatolarni "
"tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:86
msgid ""
"Try adding a `console.log()` at the beginning of your file so you can see"
" if a file has been loaded or not. If it is not loaded, if may not be in "
"the proper assets bundle, or the asset bundle may not be up to date."
msgstr ""
"Fayl yuklanganligini yoki yuklanmaganligini ko'rish uchun faylingiz boshiga "
"`console.log()` qo'shishga harakat qiling. Agar yuklanmagan bo'lsa, tegishli "
"aktivlar to'plamida bo'lmasligi mumkin yoki aktiv to'plami yangilanmagan "
"bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:89
msgid ""
"Depending on your settings, the server may not regenerate the assets "
"bundles after a file has been modified; there are a few options to solve "
"this:"
msgstr ""
"Sozlamalaringizga qarab, server fayl o'zgartirilgandan so'ng aktivlar "
"to'plamlarini qayta yaratmasligi mumkin; buni hal qilish uchun bir nechta "
"variant mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:92
msgid ""
"restarting the server will force it to check if the asset bundle is up to"
" date the next time it is requested"
msgstr ""
"serverni qayta ishga tushirish uni keyingi safar so'ralganda aktiv to'plami "
"yangilanganligini tekshirishga majbur qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:94
msgid ""
"in debug mode, there is an option in the debug menu (:icon:`fa-bug` "
"button in the navbar) to force the server to regenerate the assets bundle"
" on the fly without restarting."
msgstr ""
"debug rejimida, debug menyusida (:icon:`fa-bug` navbar dagi tugma) serverni "
"qayta ishga tushirmasdan aktivlar to'plamini tezda qayta yaratishga "
"majburlash opsiyasi mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:96
msgid ""
"starting the server with the `--dev=xml` option will force the server to "
"check if an asset bundle is up to date every time it is requested. We "
"advise you to use this option when actively developing, but not in "
"production."
msgstr ""
"`--dev=xml` opsiyasi bilan serverni ishga tushirish serverni har safar "
"so'ralganda aktiv to'plami yangilanganligini tekshirishga majbur qiladi. "
"Faol ishlab chiqishda bu opsiyadan foydalanishni tavsiya qilamiz, lekin "
"ishlab chiqarishda emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:100
msgid ""
"Make sure you refresh your page after changing the code. Odoo currently "
"does not have any hot module reloading mechanism."
msgstr ""
"Kodni o'zgartirgandan so'ng sahifangizni yangilashga ishonch hosil qiling. "
"Odoo da hozirda hech qanday hot module reloading mexanizmi yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:105
msgid "Loading Javascript Code"
msgstr "Javascript kodini yuklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:107
msgid ""
"Large applications are usually broken up into smaller files, that need to"
" be connected together.  Some file may need to use code defined in "
"another file. There are two ways of sharing code between files:"
msgstr ""
"Katta ilovalar odatda birlashtirilishi kerak bo'lgan kichikroq fayllarga "
"bo'linadi. Ba'zi fayl boshqa faylda aniqlangan koddan foydalanishi kerak "
"bo'lishi mumkin. Fayllar o'rtasida kod almashishning ikki usuli mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:111
msgid ""
"using the global scope (the *window* object) to read/write references to "
"some objects or functions,"
msgstr ""
"ba'zi ob'ektlar yoki funksiyalarga havolalarni o'qish/yozish uchun global "
"doiradan (*window* ob'ektidan) foydalanish,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:114
msgid ""
"using a module system that will provide a way for each modules to export "
"or import values, and will make sure that they are loaded in a proper "
"order."
msgstr ""
"har bir modulga qiymatlarni eksport yoki import qilish usulini taqdim "
"etadigan va ularning to'g'ri tartibda yuklanishini ta'minlaydigan modul "
"tizimidan foydalanish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:117
msgid ""
"While it's possible to work in the global scope, this has a number of "
"issues:"
msgstr ""
"Global doirada ishlash mumkin bo'lsa-da, bu bir qator muammolarga ega:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:119
msgid ""
"It is difficult to ensure that implementation details are not exposed: "
"function declarations in the global scope are accessible to all other "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Amalga oshirish tafsilotlari ochilmasligini ta'minlash qiyin: global "
"doiradagi funksiya e'lonlari boshqa barcha kodga kirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:122
msgid ""
"There is a single namespace, creating great potential for naming "
"conflicts."
msgstr ""
"Bitta nom maydoni mavjud bo'lib, nomlash ziddiyatlari uchun katta imkon "
"yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:124
msgid ""
"Dependencies are implicit: if a piece of code depends on another, the "
"order in which they are loaded is important, but difficult to guarantee."
msgstr ""
"Bog'liqliklar yashirindir: agar kod qismi boshqasiga bog'liq bo'lsa, "
"ularning yuklanish tartibi muhim, lekin kafolatlanishi qiyin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:127
msgid ""
"Using a module system helps resolve these issues: because modules specify"
" their dependencies, the module system can load them in the proper order "
"or emit an error if dependencies are missing or circular. Modules also "
"form their own namespace, and can choose what to export, preventing "
"exposure of implementation detail and naming collisions."
msgstr ""
"Modul tizimidan foydalanish bu muammolarni hal qilishga yordam beradi: "
"modullar o'z bog'liqliklarini ko'rsatganligi sababli, modul tizimi ularni "
"to'g'ri tartibda yuklashi yoki bog'liqliklar yo'q yoki aylanma bo'lsa xato "
"chiqarishi mumkin. Modullar ham o'z nom maydonini hosil qiladi va "
"amalga oshirish tafsilotlarini ochishni va nomlash to'qnashuvlarini "
"oldini olish uchun nima eksport qilishni tanlash mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:133
msgid ""
"While we could use ECMAScript (ES) modules directly, there are a number "
"of disadvantages to that approach: each ES module requires a network "
"round trip, which becomes very slow when you have hundreds of files, and "
"many files in Odoo need to be present despite not being imported by "
"anything because they simply add code that the framework will use instead"
" of the other way around."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ridan-to'g'ri ECMAScript (ES) modullaridan foydalanish mumkin bo'lsa-da, "
"bu yondashuvning bir qancha kamchiliklari mavjud: har bir ES moduli tarmoq "
"qayta-qayta borish-kelishini talab qiladi, bu yuzlab faylga ega bo'lsangiz "
"juda sekinlashadi va Odoo dagi ko'plab fayllar hech narsa tomonidan import "
"qilinmasa ham mavjud bo'lishi kerak, chunki ular shunchaki freymvork "
"ishlatadigan kodni qo'shadi, aksincha emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:139
msgid ""
"Because of this, Odoo has a system of asset bundles. In these bundles, "
"JavaScript files are ES modules with a special annotation at the top. "
"These modules will be bundled together and transpiled to be usable by our"
" module loader. While you can write code that doesn't use this module "
"system, it is generally not recommended."
msgstr ""
"Shu sababli, Odoo aktiv to'plamlari tizimiga ega. Bu to'plamlarda JavaScript "
"fayllar tepasida maxsus izoh bilan ES modullardir. Bu modullar birlashtirilib "
"va modul yuklayichimiz tomonidan ishlatilishi uchun transpile qilinadi. "
"Bu modul tizimidan foydalanmagan kodni yozish mumkin bo'lsa-da, odatda "
"tavsiya etilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:144
msgid "(see :ref:`frontend/modules/native_js`)"
msgstr "(qarang :ref:`frontend/modules/native_js`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:148
msgid "Patching classes"
msgstr "Sinflarni yamoqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:150
msgid ""
"While we do our best to provide extension points that don't require it, "
"it is sometimes necessary to modify the behavior of an existing class *in"
" place*. The goal is to have a mechanism to change a class and all "
"future/present instances. This is done by using the `patch` utility "
"function:"
msgstr ""
"Uni talab qilmaydigan kengaytma nuqtalarini taqdim etish uchun qo'limizdan "
"kelganini qilsak-da, ba'zida mavjud sinfni *o'sha joyda* o'zgartirish "
"kerak bo'ladi. Maqsad sinf va barcha kelajak/hozirgi misollarni o'zgartirish "
"mexanizmiga ega bo'lish. Bu `patch` yordamchi funksiyasidan foydalanib "
"amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:167
msgid ""
"When patching methods, you need to patch the class' prototype, but if you"
" would like to patch a static property of the class, you need to patch "
"the class itself."
msgstr ""
"Metodlarni yamoqlashda sinf prototipini yamoqlash kerak, lekin agar sinfning "
"statik xususiyatini yamoqlamoqchi bo'lsangiz, sinfning o'zini yamoqlash "
"kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:170
msgid ""
"Patching is a dangerous operation and should be done with care as it will"
" modify all instances of the class, even if they have already been "
"created. To avoid weird issues, patches should be applied as soon as "
"possible, at the top-level of your module. Patching classes at runtime "
"can result in extremely difficult to debug issues if the class has "
"already been instanciated."
msgstr ""
"Yamoqlash xavfli amal bo'lib, ehtiyot bilan bajarilishi kerak, chunki u "
"allaqachon yaratilgan bo'lsa ham sinfning barcha misollarini o'zgartiradi. "
"G'alati muammolardan qochish uchun, yamalar modulingizning yuqori darajasida "
"imkon qadar tezroq qo'llanilishi kerak. Ish vaqtida sinflarni yamoqlash "
"sinf allaqachon misollangan bo'lsa disk raskadrovka qilish juda qiyin "
"muammolarga olib kelishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:179
msgid ""
"A common need in the Odoo ecosystem is to extend/change the behaviour of "
"the base system from the outside (by installing an application, i.e. a "
"different module).  For example, one may need to add a new field widget "
"in some views. In that case, and many others, the usual process is to "
"create the desired component, then add it to a registry (registering "
"step), to make the rest of the web client aware of its existence."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ekotizimida keng tarqalgan ehtiyoj asosiy tizim xulq-atvorini "
"tashqaridan (ilova, ya'ni boshqa modul o'rnatish orqali) kengaytirish/"
"o'zgartirishdir. Masalan, ba'zi ko'rinishlarda yangi maydon vidjet qo'shish "
"kerak bo'lishi mumkin. Bunday holda va boshqa ko'plab holatlarda, odatdagi "
"jarayon kerakli komponentni yaratish, so'ngra veb-mijozning qolgan qismini "
"uning mavjudligidan xabardor qilish uchun uni registrga qo'shishdir "
"(ro'yxatdan o'tkazish bosqichi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:186
msgid ""
"There are a few registries available in the system. The registries that "
"are used by the framework are categories on the main registry, that can "
"be imported from :js:data:`@web/core/registry`"
msgstr ""
"Tizimda bir nechta registrlar mavjud. Freymvork tomonidan ishlatiladigan "
"registrlar asosiy registr dagi kategoriyalar bo'lib, :js:data:`@web/core/registry` "
"dan import qilinishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:204
msgid "field registry"
msgstr "maydon registri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:191
msgid ""
"The field registry contains all field widgets known to the web client. "
"Whenever a view (typically form or list/kanban) needs a field widget, "
"this is where it will look. A typical use case look like this:"
msgstr ""
"Maydon registri veb-mijozga ma'lum barcha maydon vidjetlarini o'z ichiga "
"oladi. Ko'rinish (odatda forma yoki ro'yxat/kanban) maydon vidjet kerak "
"bo'lganida, u shu yerga qarashadi. Odatdagi foydalanish holati quyidagicha "
"ko'rinadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:207
msgid "view registry"
msgstr "ko'rinish registri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:207
msgid "This registry contains all JS views known to the web client."
msgstr "Bu registr veb-mijozga ma'lum barcha JS ko'rinishlarini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:214
msgid "action registry"
msgstr "amal registri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:210
msgid ""
"We keep track of all client actions in this registry.  This is where the "
"action manager looks up whenever it needs to create a client action. "
"Client actions can be a function - the function will be called when the "
"action is invoked, and the returned value will be executed as a follow up"
" action if needed - or an Owl component that will be displayed when "
"executing that action."
msgstr ""
"Bu registrda barcha mijoz amallarini kuzatamiz. Amal boshqaruvchisi "
"mijoz amali yaratish kerak bo'lganida shu yerga qarashadi. Mijoz amallari "
"funksiya bo'lishi mumkin - funksiya amal chaqirilganda chaqiriladi va "
"qaytarish qiymati kerak bo'lsa keyingi amal sifatida bajariladi - yoki "
"bu amalni bajarishda ko'rsatiladigan Owl komponenti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:219
msgid ""
"Within the webclient, there are some concerns that cannot be handled by a"
" single component, as the concern is transversal, involves many "
"components, or needs to maintain some state for as long as the "
"application is alive."
msgstr ""
"Webclient ichida muammo ko'ndalang bo'lganligi, ko'plab komponentlarni "
"o'z ichiga olganligi yoki ilova ishlayotganda ba'zi holatni saqlab turishi "
"kerakligi sababli bitta komponent tomonidan boshqarilishi mumkin bo'lmagan "
"ba'zi muammolar mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:223
msgid ""
"Services are a solution to these problems: they are created during "
"application startup, are available to components through the hook "
"`useService`, and stay alive for the entire lifetime of the application."
msgstr ""
"Xizmatlar bu muammolarning yechimi: ular ilova ishga tushirishda yaratiladi, "
"`useService` hook orqali komponentlarga mavjud va ilovaning butun umri "
"davomida tirik qoladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:227
msgid ""
"For example, we have the *orm* service whose job is to allow interacting "
"with business objects on the server."
msgstr ""
"Masalan, serverdagi biznes ob'ektlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir qilish imkonini "
"berish vazifasini bajaruvchi *orm* xizmatiga egamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:230
msgid "Here is a simplified example on how the orm service is implemented:"
msgstr "Mana orm xizmati qanday amalga oshirilganining soddalashtirilgan misoli:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:248
msgid "Using services"
msgstr "Xizmatlardan foydalanish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:250
msgid ""
"Services are available in the environment, but should generally be used "
"through the `useService` hook, which prevents calling methods on the "
"service after a component has been destroyed, and prevents further code "
"from executing after a method call if the component was destroyed during "
"the call."
msgstr ""
"Xizmatlar muhitda mavjud, lekin odatda `useService` hook orqali ishlatilishi "
"kerak, bu komponent yo'q qilingandan so'ng xizmatda metodlarni chaqirishni "
"oldini oladi va chaqiruv davomida komponent yo'q qilingan bo'lsa metod "
"chaqiruvidan so'ng kodning keyingi bajarilishiga yo'l qo'ymaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:268
msgid "Talking to the server"
msgstr "Serverga murojaat qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:270
msgid ""
"There are typically two use cases when working on Odoo: one may need to "
"call a method on a (python) model (this goes through the controller "
"`/web/dataset/call_kw`), or one may need to directly call a controller "
"(available on some route)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo da ishlashda odatda ikkita foydalanish holati mavjud: (python) modelda "
"metod chaqirish kerak bo'lishi mumkin (bu `/web/dataset/call_kw` boshqaruvchi "
"orqali o'tadi), yoki to'g'ridan-to'g'ri boshqaruvchini chaqirish kerak "
"bo'lishi mumkin (ba'zi yo'l da mavjud)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:274
msgid "Calling a method on a python model is done through the orm service:"
msgstr "Python modelda metod chaqirish orm xizmati orqali amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:280
msgid "Directly calling a controller is done through the rpc service:"
msgstr "To'g'ridan-to'g'ri boshqaruvchi chaqirish rpc xizmati orqali amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:289
msgid ""
"The rpc service doesn't really perform what is generally understood as a "
"remote procedure call (RPC), but for historical reasons, within Odoo we "
"generally call any network request performed in JavaScript an RPC. As "
"highlighted in the previous paragraph, if you want to call a method on a "
"model, you should use the orm service."
msgstr ""
"rpc xizmati haqiqatan ham masofaviy protsedura chaqiruvi (RPC) sifatida "
"tushunilgan narsani amalga oshirmaydi, lekin tarixiy sabablarga ko'ra, "
"Odoo ichida biz odatda JavaScript da bajarilgan har qanday tarmoq so'rovini "
"RPC deb ataymiz. Oldingi abzasda ta'kidlanganidek, agar modelda metod "
"chaqirmoqchi bo'lsangiz, orm xizmatidan foydalanishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:296
msgid "Notifications"
msgstr "Bildirishnomalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:298
msgid ""
"The Odoo framework has a standard way to communicate various information "
"to the user: notifications, which are displayed on the top right of the "
"user interface. The types of notification follow the bootstrap toasts:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo freymvorki foydalanuvchiga turli ma'lumotlarni yetkazishning standart "
"usulini taqdim etadi: foydalanuvchi interfeysi yuqori o'ng qismida "
"ko'rsatiladigan bildirishnomalar. Bildirishnoma turlari bootstrap toastlar "
"ga amal qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:302
msgid ""
"*info*: useful to display some informational feedback as a consequence of"
" an action that cannot fail."
msgstr ""
"*info*: muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lolmaydigan amalni natijasida ba'zi ma'lumotviy "
"fikr-mulohazani ko'rsatish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:305
msgid ""
"*success*: the user performed an action that can sometimes fail but "
"didn't."
msgstr ""
"*success*: foydalanuvchi ba'zida muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"amalni bajardi, lekin muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lmadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:307
msgid ""
"*warning*: the user performed an action that could only be partially "
"completed. Also useful if something is wrong but wasn't caused by the "
"user directly, or is not particularly actionable."
msgstr ""
"*warning*: foydalanuvchi faqat qisman bajarilishi mumkin bo'lgan amal bajardi. "
"Agar biror narsa noto'g'ri bo'lsa, lekin to'g'ridan-to'g'ri foydalanuvchi "
"tomonidan kelib chiqmagan yoki ayniqsa harakatga yo'naltirilmagan bo'lsa "
"ham foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:311
msgid ""
"*success*: the user tried to performed an action but it couldn't be "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"*success*: foydalanuvchi amalni bajarishga harakat qildi, lekin u "
"yakunlanmadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:314
msgid ""
"Notifications can also be used to ask a question to the user without "
"disturbing their workflow: e.g. a phone call received through VOIP: a "
"sticky notification could be displayed with two buttons to *Accept* or "
"*Decline*."
msgstr ""
"Bildirishnomalar foydalanuvchiga ish jarayonini buzmasdan savol berish "
"uchun ham ishlatilishi mumkin: masalan, VOIP orqali kelgan telefon "
"chaqiruvi: *Qabul qilish* yoki *Rad etish* uchun ikki tugmali yopilmaydigan "
"bildirishnoma ko'rsatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:319
msgid "Displaying notifications"
msgstr "Bildirishnomalarni ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:321
msgid "There are two ways to display notifications in Odoo:"
msgstr "Odoo da bildirishnomalarni ko'rsatishning ikki usuli mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:323
msgid ""
"The *notification* service allows component to display notifications from"
" JS code by calling the add method."
msgstr ""
"*notification* xizmati komponentga add metodi chaqirish orqali JS kodidan "
"bildirishnomalarni ko'rsatishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:326
msgid ""
"The *display_notification* client action allows to trigger the display of"
" a notification from python (e.g. in the method called when the user "
"clicked on a button of type object). This client action uses the "
"notification service."
msgstr ""
"*display_notification* mijoz amali python dan bildirishnoma ko'rsatishni "
"ishga tushirish imkonini beradi (masalan, foydalanuvchi object turidagi "
"tugmani bosganida chaqirilgan metodda). Bu mijoz amali bildirishnoma "
"xizmatidan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:331
msgid "Notifications have a few *options*:"
msgstr "Bildirishnomalarning bir nechta *opsiyalari* mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:333
msgid "*title*: string, optional. This will be displayed on the top as a title."
msgstr "*title*: satr, ixtiyoriy. Bu yuqorida sarlavha sifatida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:335
msgid ""
"*message*: string, optional. The content of the notification. Can be a "
"markup object to display formatted text."
msgstr ""
"*message*: satr, ixtiyoriy. Bildirishnomaning mazmuni. Formatlangan "
"matnni ko'rsatish uchun belgilash ob'ekti bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:338
msgid ""
"*sticky*: boolean, optional (default false). If true, the notification "
"will stay until the user dismisses it.  Otherwise, the notification will "
"be automatically closed after a short delay."
msgstr ""
"*sticky*: mantiqiy, ixtiyoriy (standart false). Agar to'g'ri bo'lsa, "
"foydalanuvchi rad etguncha bildirishnoma qoladi. Aks holda, bildirishnoma "
"qisqa kechikishdan so'ng avtomatik yopiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:342
msgid ""
"*type*: string, optional (default \"warning\"). Determines the style of "
"the notification. Possible values: \"info\", \"success\", \"warning\", "
"\"danger\""
msgstr ""
"*type*: satr, ixtiyoriy (standart \"warning\"). Bildirishnoma uslubini "
"belgilaydi. Mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar: \"info\", \"success\", \"warning\", "
"\"danger\""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:345
msgid ""
"*className*: string, optional.  This is a css class name that will be "
"automatically added to the notification. This could be useful for styling"
" purpose, even though its use is discouraged."
msgstr ""
"*className*: satr, ixtiyoriy. Bu bildirishnomaga avtomatik qo'shiladigan "
"css sinf nomi. Bu uslublash maqsadida foydali bo'lishi mumkin, garchi "
"undan foydalanish tavsiya etilmasa ham."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:349
msgid "Here are some examples on how to display notifications in JS:"
msgstr "Mana JS da bildirishnomalarni qanday ko'rsatish bo'yicha ba'zi misollar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:364
msgid "And in Python:"
msgstr "Va Pythonda:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:381
msgid "Systray"
msgstr "Sistrat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:383
msgid ""
"The Systray is the right part of the navbar in the interface, where the "
"web client displays a few widgets, such as the messaging menu."
msgstr ""
"Sistrat interfeysda navbarning o'ng qismi bo'lib, veb-mijoz xabar almashish "
"menyusi kabi bir nechta vidjetlarni ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:386
msgid ""
"When the systray is created by the navbar, it will look for all "
"registered systray items and display them."
msgstr ""
"Sistrat navbar tomonidan yaratilganda, u ro'yxatdan o'tgan barcha sistrat "
"elementlarini qidiradi va ularni ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:389
msgid ""
"There is currently no specific API for systray items.  They are Owl "
"components, and can communicate with their environment just like other "
"components, e.g. by interacting with services."
msgstr ""
"Hozirda sistrat elementlari uchun maxsus API yo'q. Ular Owl komponentlari "
"va boshqa komponentlar kabi muhiti bilan muloqot qila oladi, masalan "
"xizmatlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir qilish orqali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:394
msgid "Adding a new Systray Item"
msgstr "Yangi Sistrat elementi qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:396
msgid ""
"Items can be added to the systray by adding them to the \"systray\" "
"registry:"
msgstr ""
"Elementlar \"sistrat\" registriga qo'shish orqali sistratga qo'shilishi "
"mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:406
msgid ""
"The items are ordered in the systray according to their sequence in the "
"systray registry."
msgstr ""
"Elementlar sistratdagi ketma-ket tartiblariga ko'ra sistrat registrida "
"tartiblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:410
msgid "Translation management"
msgstr "Tarjimani boshqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:412
msgid ""
"Some translations are made on the server side (basically all text strings"
" rendered or processed by the server), but there are strings in the "
"static files that need to be translated. The way it currently works is "
"the following:"
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi tarjimalar server tomonida amalga oshiriladi (asosan server tomonidan "
"render qilingan yoki qayta ishlangan barcha matn satrlari), lekin statik "
"fayllarda tarjima qilinishi kerak bo'lgan satrlar mavjud. Hozirda qanday "
"ishlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:416
msgid "each translatable string is tagged with the special function *_t*"
msgstr "har bir tarjimalanuvchi satr maxsus *_t* funksiyasi bilan belgilanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:417
msgid "these strings are used by the server to generate the proper PO files"
msgstr "bu satrlar server tomonidan tegishli PO fayllarini yaratish uchun ishlatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:418
msgid ""
"whenever the web client is loaded, it will call the route "
"*/web/webclient/translations*, which returns a list of all translatable "
"terms"
msgstr ""
"veb-mijoz yuklanganida, u barcha tarjimalanuvchi atamalar ro'yxatini "
"qaytaradigan */web/webclient/translations* yo'lini chaqiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:420
msgid ""
"at runtime, whenever the function `_t` is called, it will look up in this"
" list in order to find a translation, and return it or the original "
"string if none is found."
msgstr ""
"ish vaqtida, `_t` funksiyasi chaqirilganida, tarjima topish uchun bu "
"ro'yxatda qidiradi va agar topilmasa uni yoki asl satrni qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:424
msgid ""
"Note that translations are explained in more details, from the server "
"point of view, in the document :doc:`/developer/howtos/translations`."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, tarjimalar server nuqtai nazaridan :doc:`/developer/howtos/translations` "
"hujjatida batafsil tushuntirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:439
msgid ""
"Note that using the translation function requires some care: the string "
"given as an argument cannot be dynamic, as it is extracted statically "
"from the code to generate the PO files and serves as the identifier for "
"the term to translate. If you need to inject some dynamic content in the "
"string, `_t` supports placeholders:"
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, tarjima funksiyasidan foydalanish ba'zi ehtiyotkorlikni "
"talab qiladi: argument sifatida berilgan satr dinamik bo'la olmaydi, "
"chunki u PO fayllarini yaratish uchun koddan statik ravishda olinadi va "
"tarjima qilinadigan atama uchun identifikator bo'lib xizmat qiladi. Agar "
"satrga ba'zi dinamik mazmun kiritish kerak bo'lsa, `_t` joy egallashchilarni "
"qo'llab-quvvatlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:449
msgid ""
"Notice how the string itself is fixed. This allows the translation "
"function to retrieve the translated string *before* using it for "
"interpolation."
msgstr ""
"Satrning o'zi qanday qilib belgilanganligi ga e'tibor bering. Bu tarjima "
"funksiyasiga interpolatsiyada ishlatishdan *oldin* tarjima qilingan satrni "
"olish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:454
msgid "Session"
msgstr "Sessiya"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:456
msgid ""
"The webclient needs some information from the python to function "
"properly. To avoid an extra round-trip with the server by making a "
"network request in JavaScript, this information is serialized directly in"
" the page, and can be accessed in JS through the `@web/session` module."
msgstr ""
"Webclient to'g'ri ishlashi uchun pythondan ba'zi ma'lumotlarga muhtoj. "
"JavaScript da tarmoq so'rovi qilib serverga qo'shimcha borib-kelishdan "
"qochish uchun, bu ma'lumotlar to'g'ridan-to'g'ri sahifada seriallashtirilib, "
"`@web/session` moduli orqali JS da kirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:462
msgid "Adding information to the session"
msgstr "Sessiyaga ma'lumot qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:464
msgid ""
"When the `/web` route is loaded, the server injects this information in a"
" script tag. The information is obtained by calling the method "
"`session_info` of the model `ir.http`. You can override this method to "
"add information to the returned dictionary."
msgstr ""
"``/web` yo'li yuklanganida, server bu ma'lumotni script tegiga kiritadi. "
"Ma'lumotlar `ir.http` modelining `session_info` metodi chaqirish orqali "
"olinadi. Qaytarilgan lug'atga ma'lumot qo'shish uchun bu metoddan qayta "
"foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:482
msgid "Now, the value can be obtained in javascript by reading it in the session:"
msgstr "Endi, qiymat sessiyada o'qish orqali javascript da olinishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:490
msgid ""
"Note that this mechanism is designed to reduce the amount of "
"communication needed by the web client to be ready.  It is only "
"appropriate for data which is cheap to compute (a slow session_info call "
"will delay the loading for the web client for everyone), and for data "
"which is required early in the initialization process."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, bu mexanizm veb-mijozning tayyor bo'lishi uchun kerakli "
"muloqot miqdorini kamaytirish uchun mo'ljallangan. U faqat hisoblash "
"arzon bo'lgan ma'lumotlar uchun mos (sekin session_info chaqiruvi hamma "
"uchun veb-mijoz yuklanishini kechiktiradi) va boshlash jarayonida erta "
"talab qilinadigan ma'lumotlar uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:499
msgid ""
"The word \"view\" has more than one meaning. This section is about the "
"design of the javascript code of the views, not the structure of the "
"*arch* or anything else."
msgstr ""
"\"Ko'rinish\" so'zining bir nechta ma'nosi bor. Bu bo'lim ko'rinishlarning "
"javascript kodi dizayni haqida, *arch* tuzilmasi yoki boshqa hech narsa "
"haqida emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:503
msgid ""
"While views are just owl components, the built-in views generally have "
"the same structure: a component called \"SomethingController\" which is "
"the root of the view. This component creates an instance of some "
"\"model\" (an object responsible for managing the data), and has a "
"subcomponent called a \"renderer\" that handles the display logic."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishlar shunchaki owl komponentlari bo'lsa-da, o'rnatilgan ko'rinishlar "
"odatda bir xil tuzilmaga ega: ko'rinishning ildizi bo'lgan "
"\"SomethingController\" deb nomlangan komponent. Bu komponent ba'zi "
"\"model\" (ma'lumotlarni boshqarish uchun mas'ul ob'ekt) misolini yaratadi "
"va ko'rsatish mantiqini boshqaradigan \"renderer\" deb nomlangan "
"qo'shimcha komponentga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:514
msgid ""
"A good part of the web client experience is about editing and creating "
"data. Most of that work is done with the help of field widgets, which are"
" aware of the field type and of the specific details on how a value "
"should be displayed and edited."
msgstr ""
"Veb-mijoz tajribasining yaxshi qismi ma'lumotlarni tahrirlash va yaratish "
"haqida. Bu ishning ko'p qismi maydon turi va qiymat qanday ko'rsatilishi "
"va tahrirlanishi haqidagi muayyan tafsilotlarni biladigan maydon vidjetlari "
"yordamida amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:521
msgid "Decorations"
msgstr "Dekoratsiyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:523
msgid ""
"Like the list view, field widgets have a simple support for decorations. "
"The goal of decorations is to have a simple way to specify a text color "
"depending on the record current state.  For example:"
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishi kabi, maydon vidjetlari dekoratsiyalar uchun oddiy "
"qo'llab-quvvatlashga ega. Dekoratsiyalarning maqsadi yozuv joriy holatiga "
"qarab matn rangini belgilashning oddiy usulini taqdim etish. Masalan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:531
msgid "The valid decoration names are:"
msgstr "To'g'ri dekoratsiya nomlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:533
msgid "`decoration-bf`"
msgstr "`decoration-bf`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:534
msgid "`decoration-it`"
msgstr "`decoration-it`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:535
msgid "`decoration-danger`"
msgstr "`decoration-danger`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:536
msgid "`decoration-info`"
msgstr "`decoration-info`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:537
msgid "`decoration-muted`"
msgstr "`decoration-muted`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:538
msgid "`decoration-primary`"
msgstr "`decoration-primary`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:539
msgid "`decoration-success`"
msgstr "`decoration-success`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:540
msgid "`decoration-warning`"
msgstr "`decoration-warning`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:542
msgid ""
"Each decoration *decoration-X* will be mapped to a css class *text-X*, "
"which is a standard bootstrap css class (except for *text-it* and *text-"
"bf*, which are handled by odoo and correspond to italic and bold, "
"respectively).  Note that the value of the decoration attribute should be"
" a valid python expression, which will be evaluated with the record as "
"evaluation context."
msgstr ""
"Har bir dekoratsiya *decoration-X* *text-X* css sinfi ga xaritalanadi, bu "
"standart bootstrap css sinfi (Odoo tomonidan boshqariladigan va mos ravishda "
"kursiv va qalin ga mos keladigan *text-it* va *text-bf* bundan mustasno). "
"E'tibor bering, dekoratsiya atributining qiymati yozuv baholash konteksti "
"sifatida baholanadigan to'g'ri python ifodasi bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:549
msgid "Non-relational fields"
msgstr "Munosabatsiz maydonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:551
msgid ""
"We document here all non relational fields available by default, in no "
"particular order."
msgstr ""
"Bu yerda standart tarzda mavjud bo'lgan barcha munosabatsiz maydonlarni "
"hech qanday tartibda hujjatlashtirmaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:585
msgid "Integer (`integer`)"
msgstr "Butun son (`integer`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:555
msgid "This is the default field type for fields of type `integer`."
msgstr "`integer` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:557
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:827
msgid "Supported field types: `integer`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `integer`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:559
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:600
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:693
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:726
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:767
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:799
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:857
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:875
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:905
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:935
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:968
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1004
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1030
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1066
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1151
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1181
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1251
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1266
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1277
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1332
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1361
msgid "Options:"
msgstr "Parametrlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:561
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:602
msgid ""
"`type`: setting the input type (`\"text\"` by default, can be set on "
"`\"number\"`)"
msgstr ""
"`type`: kirish turini sozlash (standart `\"text\"`, `\"number\"` ga "
"o'rnatish mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:563
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:604
msgid ""
"In edit mode, the field is rendered as an input with the HTML attribute "
"type set on `\"number\"` (so user can benefit the native support, "
"especially on mobile). In this case, the default formatting is disabled "
"to avoid incompability."
msgstr ""
"Tahrirlash rejimida, maydon HTML atributi `\"number\"` qilib belgilangan "
"kirish sifatida ko'rsatiladi (foydalanuvchi mahalliy qo'llab-quvvatlashdan "
"foydalanishi mumkin, ayniqsa mobil qurilmalarda). Bu holda, moslik "
"muammolarini oldini olish uchun standart formatlash o'chirib qo'yiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:571
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:612
msgid ""
"`step`: set the step to the value up and down when the user click on "
"buttons (only for input of type number, `1` by default)"
msgstr ""
"`step`: foydalanuvchi tugmalarni bosganida qiymatni oshirish/kamaytirish "
"qadamini belgilaydi (faqat raqam turdagi kirish uchun, standart `1`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:578
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:619
msgid "`format`: should the number be formatted. (`true` by default)"
msgstr "`format`: raqam formatlanishi kerakmi. (standart `true`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:580
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:621
msgid ""
"By default, numbers are formatted according to locale parameters. This "
"option will prevent the field's value from being formatted."
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda raqamlar til parametrlariga muvofiq formatlanadi. Bu "
"parametr maydon qiymatining formatlanishini oldini oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:643
msgid "Float (`float`)"
msgstr "Kasr son (`float`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:588
msgid "This is the default field type for fields of type `float`."
msgstr "`float` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:590
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:650
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:657
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:666
msgid "Supported field types: `float`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `float`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:592
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:925
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1100
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1134
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1174
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1245
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1379
msgid "Attributes:"
msgstr "Atributlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:594
msgid "`digits`: displayed precision"
msgstr "`digits`: ko'rsatiladigan aniqlik"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:628
msgid "`min_display_digits`: The minimum number of decimal digits to display."
msgstr "`min_display_digits`: Ko'rsatiladigan o'nlik raqamlarning minimal soni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:630
msgid ""
"For example, if set to 3 and no decimal precision is provided: `1.2` "
"becomes `\"1.200\"`, `1.123` becomes `\"1.123\"` and `1.1234` becomes "
"`\"1.1234\"`."
msgstr ""
"Masalan, 3 ga o'rnatilgan va o'nlik aniqlik berilmagan bo'lsa: `1.2` "
"`\"1.200\"` ga aylanadi, `1.123` `\"1.123\"` bo'ladi va `1.1234` "
"`\"1.1234\"` bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:638
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:807
msgid ""
"`hide_trailing_zeros`: hide zeros to the right of the last non-zero "
"digit, e.g. `1.20` becomes `1.2` (`false` by default)."
msgstr ""
"`hide_trailing_zeros`: oxirgi nol bo'lmagan raqamdan o'ngdagi nollarni "
"yashirish, masalan `1.20` `1.2` ga aylanadi (standart `false`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:650
msgid "Time (`float_time`)"
msgstr "Vaqt (`float_time`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:646
msgid ""
"The goal of this widget is to display properly a float value that "
"represents a time interval (in hours).  So, for example, `0.5` should be "
"formatted as `0:30`, or `4.75` correspond to `4:45`."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjetning maqsadi vaqt oralig'ini (soatlarda) ifodalovchi kasr "
"qiymatini to'g'ri ko'rsatish. Masalan, `0.5` `0:30` sifatida "
"formatlanishi kerak yoki `4.75` `4:45` ga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:657
msgid "Float Factor (`float_factor`)"
msgstr "Kasr koeffitsient (`float_factor`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:653
msgid ""
"This widget aims to display properly a float value that converted using a"
" factor given in its options. So, for example, the value saved in "
"database is `0.5` and the factor is `3`, the widget value should be "
"formatted as `1.5`."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet parametrlarda berilgan koeffitsient yordamida konvertatsiya "
"qilingan kasr qiymatini to'g'ri ko'rsatishga mo'ljallangan. Masalan, "
"ma'lumotlar bazasida saqlangan qiymat `0.5` va koeffitsient `3` bo'lsa, "
"vidjet qiymati `1.5` sifatida formatlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:670
msgid "Float Toggle (`float_toggle`)"
msgstr "Kasr almashtiruvchi (`float_toggle`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:660
msgid ""
"The goal of this widget is to replace the input field by a button "
"containing a range of possible values (given in the options). Each click "
"allows the user to loop in the range. The purpose here is to restrict the"
" field value to a predefined selection. Also, the widget support the "
"factor conversion as the `float_factor` widget (Range values should be "
"the result of the conversion)."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjetning maqsadi kirish maydonini mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar "
"diapazonini (parametrlarda berilgan) o'z ichiga olgan tugma bilan "
"almashtirish. Har bir bosish foydalanuvchiga diapazonda aylanib o'tish "
"imkonini beradi. Maqsad maydon qiymatini oldindan belgilangan tanlovga "
"cheklash. Shuningdek, vidjet `float_factor` vidjetidagi kabi koeffitsient "
"konvertatsiyasini qo'llab-quvvatlaydi (Diapazon qiymatlari konvertatsiya "
"natijasi bo'lishi kerak)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:675
msgid "Boolean (`boolean`)"
msgstr "Mantiqiy (`boolean`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:673
msgid "This is the default field type for fields of type `boolean`."
msgstr "`boolean` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:675
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1016
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1022
msgid "Supported field types: `boolean`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `boolean`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:680
msgid "Char (`char`)"
msgstr "Matn (`char`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:678
msgid "This is the default field type for fields of type `char`."
msgstr "`char` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:680
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:834
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:842
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:851
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:873
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:894
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1098
msgid "Supported field types: `char`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `char`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:714
msgid "Date (`date`)"
msgstr "Sana (`date`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:685
msgid ""
"This is the default field type for fields of type `date`. It consists of "
"a text box and a date picker. The field will show the date in a readable "
"format like this: `Dec 19, 1997`. The year will be hidden if it's the "
"current one. When editing the field, the numeric format will be shown. "
"This format corresponds to the one set in the current language."
msgstr ""
"`date` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi. U matn qutisi va "
"sana tanlash vositasidan iborat. Maydon sanani o'qilishi qulay formatda "
"ko'rsatadi: `Dec 19, 1997`. Yil joriy yil bo'lsa yashiriladi. Maydonni "
"tahrirlashda raqamli format ko'rsatiladi. Bu format joriy tilda "
"o'rnatilgan formatga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:691
msgid "Supported field types: `date`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `date`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:695
msgid ""
"`min_date` / `max_date`: sets limit dates for accepted values. By "
"default, the earliest accepted date is **1000-01-01** and the latest is "
"**9999-12-31**. Accepted values are SQL-formatted dates (`yyyy-MM-dd "
"HH:mm:ss`) or `\"today\"`."
msgstr ""
"`min_date` / `max_date`: qabul qilinadigan qiymatlar uchun chegara "
"sanalarni belgilaydi. Standart holatda, eng erta qabul qilinadigan sana "
"**1000-01-01** va eng kech **9999-12-31**. Qabul qilinadigan qiymatlar "
"SQL formatidagi sanalar (`yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss`) yoki `\"today\"` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:703
msgid ""
"`warn_future`: displays a warning if the value is in the future (based on"
" today)."
msgstr ""
"`warn_future`: qiymat kelajakda bo'lsa (bugungi kunga nisbatan) ogohlantirish "
"ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:709
msgid ""
"`numeric`: when set to true, it shows the date in the format set on the "
"current language. (default: `false`)."
msgstr ""
"`numeric`: true ga o'rnatilganda, sanani joriy tilda o'rnatilgan formatda "
"ko'rsatadi. (standart: `false`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:760
msgid "Date & Time (`datetime`)"
msgstr "Sana va vaqt (`datetime`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:719
msgid ""
"This is the default field type for fields of type `datetime`. The values "
"are always in the client's timezone. The displayed format has the same "
"behaviour as the date field, see :ref:`Date Field "
"<reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` description. The readable "
"format looks like this: `Dec 19, 1997, 10:45 AM`."
msgstr ""
"`datetime` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi. Qiymatlar "
"doimo mijoz vaqt mintaqasida bo'ladi. Ko'rsatiladigan format sana "
"maydoni bilan bir xil xatti-harakatga ega, :ref:`Sana maydoni "
"<reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` tavsifiga qarang. "
"O'qilishi qulay format quyidagicha ko'rinadi: `Dec 19, 1997, 10:45 AM`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:724
msgid "Supported field types: `datetime`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `datetime`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:728
msgid "see :ref:`Date Field <reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` options"
msgstr ":ref:`Sana maydoni <reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` parametrlariga qarang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:730
msgid ""
"`rounding`: increment used to generate available minutes in the time "
"picker. This does not affect the actual value, just the amount of "
"available options in the select dropdown (default: `5`)."
msgstr ""
"`rounding`: vaqt tanlash vositasida mavjud daqiqalarni yaratish uchun "
"ishlatilgan qadam. Bu haqiqiy qiymatga ta'sir qilmaydi, faqat tanlash "
"ro'yxatidagi mavjud parametrlar soniga ta'sir qiladi (standart: `5`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:738
msgid ""
"`show_seconds`: when set to true, it shows the seconds from the datetime "
"field. The field will still accept datetime values, but the seconds will "
"be shown in the UI (default: `false`)."
msgstr ""
"`show_seconds`: true ga o'rnatilganda, datetime maydonidan soniyalarni "
"ko'rsatadi. Maydon hali ham datetime qiymatlarini qabul qiladi, lekin "
"soniyalar UI da ko'rsatiladi (standart: `false`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:746
msgid ""
"`show_time`: when set to false, it hides the time part from the datetime "
"field. The field will still accept datetime values, but the time part "
"will be hidden in the UI (default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`show_time`: false ga o'rnatilganda, datetime maydonidan vaqt qismini "
"yashiradi. Maydon hali ham datetime qiymatlarini qabul qiladi, lekin "
"vaqt qismi UI da yashiriladi (standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:754
msgid ""
"`show_date`: when set to false, it hides the date part from the datetime "
"field. The field will still accept datetime values, but the date part "
"will be hidden in the UI (default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`show_date`: false ga o'rnatilganda, datetime maydonidan sana qismini "
"yashiradi. Maydon hali ham datetime qiymatlarini qabul qiladi, lekin "
"sana qismi UI da yashiriladi (standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:783
msgid "Date Range (`daterange`)"
msgstr "Sana diapazoni (`daterange`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:763
msgid ""
"This widget allows the user to select start and end date from a single "
"picker."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet foydalanuvchiga bitta tanlash vositasidan boshlanish va tugash "
"sanasini tanlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:765
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:790
msgid "Supported field types: `date`, `datetime`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `date`, `datetime`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:769
msgid ""
"see :ref:`Date Field <reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` or "
":ref:`Date & Time Field <reference/javascript_reference/datetime_field>` "
"options"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Sana maydoni <reference/javascript_reference/date_field>` yoki "
":ref:`Sana va vaqt maydoni <reference/javascript_reference/datetime_field>` "
"parametrlariga qarang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:771
msgid ""
"`start_date_field`: field used to get/set the start value of the date "
"range (cannot be used with `end_date_field`)."
msgstr ""
"`start_date_field`: sana diapazoni boshlanish qiymatini olish/o'rnatish "
"uchun ishlatiladigan maydon (`end_date_field` bilan birga ishlatilmaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:778
msgid ""
"`end_date_field`: field used to get/set the end value of the date range "
"(cannot be used with `start_date_field`)."
msgstr ""
"`end_date_field`: sana diapazoni tugash qiymatini olish/o'rnatish uchun "
"ishlatiladigan maydon (`start_date_field` bilan birga ishlatilmaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:790
msgid "Remaining Days (`remaining_days`)"
msgstr "Qolgan kunlar (`remaining_days`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:786
msgid ""
"This widget can be used on date and datetime fields. In readonly, it "
"displays the delta (in days) between the value of the field and today. "
"The widget turns into a regular date or datetime field in edit mode."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet sana va datetime maydonlarida ishlatilishi mumkin. Faqat o'qish "
"rejimida maydon qiymati va bugun o'rtasidagi farqni (kunlarda) ko'rsatadi. "
"Tahrirlash rejimida vidjet oddiy sana yoki datetime maydoniga aylanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:812
msgid "Monetary (`monetary`)"
msgstr "Pul (`monetary`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:793
msgid ""
"This is the default field type for fields of type `monetary`. It is used "
"to display a currency.  If there is a currency fields given in option, it"
" will use that, otherwise it will fall back to the default currency (in "
"the session)"
msgstr ""
"`monetary` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi. Valyutani "
"ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi. Agar parametrda valyuta maydoni berilgan "
"bo'lsa, u ishlatiladi, aks holda standart valyutaga (seansdagi) qaytadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:797
msgid "Supported field types: `monetary`, `float`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `monetary`, `float`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:801
msgid ""
"`currency_field`: another field name which should be a many2one on "
"currency."
msgstr ""
"`currency_field`: valyutada many2one bo'lishi kerak bo'lgan boshqa maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:818
msgid "Text (`text`)"
msgstr "Matn (`text`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:815
msgid "This is the default field type for fields of type `text`."
msgstr "`text` turdagi maydonlar uchun standart maydon turi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:817
msgid "Supported field types: `text`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `text`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:828
msgid "Handle (`handle`)"
msgstr "Tutqich (`handle`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:821
msgid ""
"This field's job is to be displayed as a `handle`, and allows reordering "
"the various records by drag and dropping them."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydonning vazifasi `handle` sifatida ko'rsatish va yozuvlarni "
"sudrab tashlab qayta tartiblash imkonini berishdir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:824
msgid "It has to be specified on the field by which records are sorted."
msgstr "U yozuvlar tartiblanadigan maydonida ko'rsatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:825
msgid ""
"Having more than one field with a handle widget on the same list is not "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"Bir xil ro'yxatda bir nechta tutqich vidjeti bo'lgan maydonlar qo'llab-"
"quvvatlanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:834
msgid "Email (`email`)"
msgstr "Elektron pochta (`email`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:831
msgid ""
"This field displays email address.  The main reason to use it is that it "
"is rendered as an anchor tag with the proper href, in readonly mode."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydon elektron pochta manzilini ko'rsatadi. Undan foydalanishning "
"asosiy sababi shundaki, u faqat o'qish rejimida to'g'ri href bilan "
"anchor tegi sifatida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:842
msgid "Phone (`phone`)"
msgstr "Telefon (`phone`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:837
msgid ""
"This field displays a phone number.  The main reason to use it is that it"
" is rendered as an anchor tag with the proper href, in readonly mode, but"
" only in some cases: we only want to make it clickable if the device can "
"call this particular number."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydon telefon raqamini ko'rsatadi. Undan foydalanishning asosiy "
"sababi shundaki, u faqat o'qish rejimida to'g'ri href bilan anchor tegi "
"sifatida ko'rsatiladi, lekin faqat ba'zi holatlarda: qurilma ushbu "
"raqamga qo'ng'iroq qila oladigan bo'lsagina bosiladigan qilmoqchimiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:861
msgid "URL (`url`)"
msgstr "URL (`url`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:845
msgid ""
"This field displays an url (in readonly mode). The main reason to use it "
"is that it is rendered as an anchor tag with the proper css classes and "
"href."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydon url ni ko'rsatadi (faqat o'qish rejimida). Undan foydalanishning "
"asosiy sababi shundaki, u to'g'ri css sinflari va href bilan anchor tegi "
"sifatida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:848
msgid ""
"Also, the text of the anchor tag can be customized with the *text* "
"attribute (it won't change the href value)."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, anchor tegining matni *text* atributi bilan sozlanishi mumkin "
"(bu href qiymatini o'zgartirmaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:859
msgid ""
"`website_path`: (default: `false`) by default, the widget forces (if not "
"already the case) the href value to begin with `\"http://\"` except if "
"this option is set to `true`, thus allowing redirections to the "
"database's own website."
msgstr ""
"`website_path`: (standart: `false`) standart holatda, vidjet href "
"qiymatini `\"http://\"` bilan boshlanishga majburlaydi (agar allaqachon "
"shunday bo'lmasa), faqat bu parametr `true` ga o'rnatilgan bo'lsa "
"bundan mustasno, bu esa ma'lumotlar bazasining o'z veb-saytiga "
"yo'naltirishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:887
msgid "Domain (`domain`)"
msgstr "Domen (`domain`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:864
msgid ""
"The `domain` field allows the user to construct a technical-prefix domain"
" thanks to a tree-like interface and see the selected records in real "
"time. In debug mode, an input is also there to be able to enter the "
"prefix char domain directly (or to build advanced domains the tree-like "
"interface does not allow to)."
msgstr ""
"`domain` maydoni foydalanuvchiga daraxtsimon interfeys yordamida texnik "
"prefiks domenini tuzish va tanlangan yozuvlarni real vaqtda ko'rish "
"imkonini beradi. Debug rejimida, prefiks char domenini to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"kiritish (yoki daraxtsimon interfeys qo'llab-quvvatlamaydigan murakkab "
"domenlarni tuzish) uchun kirish maydoni ham mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:870
msgid ""
"Note that this is limited to **static** domains (no dynamic expressions, "
"or access to context variable)."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, bu **statik** domenlar bilan cheklangan (dinamik ifodalar "
"yoki kontekst o'zgaruvchilariga kirish yo'q)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:877
msgid ""
"`model`: the name of the char field encoding the `res_model` on which the"
" domain applies."
msgstr ""
"`model`: domen qo'llaniladigan `res_model` ni kodlaydigan char maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:879
msgid ""
"`foldable` (default: `false`): if true, the domain field is rendered "
"compactly and unfolds itself upon user interaction."
msgstr ""
"`foldable` (standart: `false`): true bo'lsa, domen maydoni ixcham "
"ko'rsatiladi va foydalanuvchi ta'sirida kengayadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:882
msgid ""
"`in_dialog` (default: `false`): if true, the widget opens a dialog when "
"the user wants to edit the domain whereas by default, the domain editor "
"is rendered just below the value."
msgstr ""
"`in_dialog` (standart: `false`): true bo'lsa, foydalanuvchi domenni "
"tahrirlashni xohlayotganda vidjet dialog oynasini ochadi, standart "
"holatda esa domen muharriri qiymatning pastida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:885
msgid ""
"`count_limit` (default: `10000`): the domain widget performs search_count"
" requests to validate the domain, and to indicate the number of records "
"matching it. This requests might be costly on large tables, so by "
"default, the search_count is limited to 10000."
msgstr ""
"`count_limit` (standart: `10000`): domen vidjeti domenni tasdiqlash va "
"unga mos keladigan yozuvlar sonini ko'rsatish uchun search_count "
"so'rovlarini bajaradi. Bu so'rovlar katta jadvallarda qimmatga tushishi "
"mumkin, shuning uchun standart holatda search_count 10000 bilan "
"cheklangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:894
msgid "Link button (`link_button`)"
msgstr "Havola tugmasi (`link_button`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:890
msgid ""
"The `LinkButton` widget actually simply displays a span with an icon and "
"the text value as content. The link is clickable and will open a new "
"browser window with its value as url."
msgstr ""
"`LinkButton` vidjeti aslida icon va matn qiymatini kontent sifatida "
"o'z ichiga olgan span ni ko'rsatadi. Havola bosiladigan bo'lib, uning "
"qiymatini url sifatida yangi brauzer oynasida ochadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:918
msgid "Image File (`image`)"
msgstr "Rasm fayli (`image`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:897
msgid ""
"This widget is used to represent a binary value as an image. In some "
"cases, the server returns a `bin_size` instead of the real image (a "
"`bin_size` is a string representing a file size, such as `\"6.5kb\"`).  "
"In that case, the widget will make an image with a source attribute "
"corresponding to an image on the server."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet ikkilik qiymatni rasm sifatida ifodalash uchun ishlatiladi. "
"Ba'zi hollarda, server haqiqiy rasm o'rniga `bin_size` qaytaradi "
"(`bin_size` fayl hajmini ifodalovchi satr, masalan `\"6.5kb\"`). "
"Bu holda, vidjet serverda joylashgan rasmga mos keladigan source "
"atributi bilan rasm yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:903
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:923
msgid "Supported field types: `binary`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `binary`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:907
msgid ""
"`preview_image`: if the image is only loaded as a `bin_size`, then this "
"option is useful to inform the web client that the default field name is "
"not the name of the current field, but the name of another field."
msgstr ""
"`preview_image`: agar rasm faqat `bin_size` sifatida yuklangan bo'lsa, "
"bu parametr veb-mijozga standart maydon nomi joriy maydon nomi emas, "
"balki boshqa maydonning nomi ekanligini bildirish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:915
msgid ""
"`accepted_file_extensions`: the file extension the user can pick from the"
" file input dialog box (default value is `\"image/\\*\"`)"
msgstr ""
"`accepted_file_extensions`: foydalanuvchi fayl kiritish dialog oynasidan "
"tanlashi mumkin bo'lgan fayl kengaytmasi (standart qiymat `\"image/\\*\"`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:918
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:939
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1270
msgid "(cf: ``accept`` attribute on `<input type=\"file\" />`)"
msgstr "(`<input type=\"file\" />` dagi ``accept`` atributiga qarang)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:939
msgid "Binary File (`binary`)"
msgstr "Ikkilik fayl (`binary`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:921
msgid "Generic widget to allow saving/downloading a binary file."
msgstr "Ikkilik faylni saqlash/yuklab olish imkonini beruvchi umumiy vidjet."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:927
msgid ""
"`filename`: saving a binary file will lose its file name, since it only "
"saves the binary value. The file name can be saved in another field. To "
"do that, a `filename` attribute should be set to a field present in the "
"view."
msgstr ""
"`filename`: ikkilik faylni saqlash uning fayl nomini yo'qotadi, chunki "
"u faqat ikkilik qiymatni saqlaydi. Fayl nomini boshqa maydonda saqlash "
"mumkin. Buning uchun ko'rinishda mavjud bo'lgan maydonga `filename` "
"atributi o'rnatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:937
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1268
msgid ""
"`accepted_file_extensions`: the file extension the user can pick from the"
" file input dialog box"
msgstr ""
"`accepted_file_extensions`: foydalanuvchi fayl kiritish dialog oynasidan "
"tanlashi mumkin bo'lgan fayl kengaytmasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:948
msgid "Priority (`priority`)"
msgstr "Muhimlik darajasi (`priority`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:942
msgid ""
"This widget is rendered as a set of stars, allowing the user to click on "
"it to select a value or not. This is useful for example to mark a task as"
" high priority."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet yulduzlar to'plami sifatida ko'rsatiladi, bu foydalanuvchiga "
"qiymatni tanlash yoki tanlamaslik uchun bosish imkonini beradi. Bu "
"masalan vazifani yuqori muhimlik darajasi bilan belgilash uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:946
msgid "Note that this widget also works in `readonly` mode, which is unusual."
msgstr "E'tibor bering, bu vidjet `readonly` rejimida ham ishlaydi, bu noodatiy holat."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:948
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:966
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:993
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1002
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1132
msgid "Supported field types: `selection`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `selection`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:960
msgid "Image Attachment (`attachment_image`)"
msgstr "Rasm ilovasi (`attachment_image`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:951
msgid ""
"Image widget for `many2one` fields. If the field is set, this widget will"
" be rendered as an image with the proper src url. This widget does not "
"have a different behaviour in edit or readonly mode, it is only useful to"
" view an image."
msgstr ""
"`many2one` maydonlari uchun rasm vidjeti. Agar maydon o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, "
"bu vidjet to'g'ri src url bilan rasm sifatida ko'rsatiladi. Bu vidjet "
"tahrirlash yoki faqat o'qish rejimida farqli xatti-harakatga ega emas, "
"u faqat rasmni ko'rish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:956
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1172
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1217
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1226
msgid "Supported field types: `many2one`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `many2one`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:984
msgid "Label Selection (`label_selection`)"
msgstr "Yorliq tanlash (`label_selection`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:963
msgid ""
"This widget renders a simple non-editable label. This is only useful to "
"display some information, not to edit it."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet oddiy tahrirlanmaydigan yorliqni ko'rsatadi. Bu faqat ma'lumotni "
"ko'rsatish uchun foydali, tahrirlash uchun emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:970
msgid "`classes`: a mapping from a selection value to a CSS class name"
msgstr "`classes`: tanlov qiymatidan CSS sinf nomiga xaritalash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:997
msgid "State Selection (`state_selection`)"
msgstr "Holat tanlash (`state_selection`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:987
msgid ""
"This is a specialized selection widget. It assumes that the record has "
"some hardcoded fields, present in the view: `stage_id`, `legend_normal`, "
"`legend_blocked`, `legend_done`. This is mostly used to display and "
"change the state of a task in a project, with additional information "
"displayed in the dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Bu ixtisoslashgan tanlash vidjeti. U yozuvda ko'rinishda mavjud qattiq "
"kodlangan maydonlar borligini taxmin qiladi: `stage_id`, `legend_normal`, "
"`legend_blocked`, `legend_done`. Bu ko'pincha proyektdagi vazifa holatini "
"ko'rsatish va o'zgartirish uchun ishlatiladi, qo'shimcha ma'lumotlar "
"ochiladigan ro'yxatda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1010
msgid "State Selection - List View (`list.state_selection`)"
msgstr "Holat tanlash - ro'yxat ko'rinishi (`list.state_selection`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1000
msgid ""
"In list views, the `state_selection` field displays by default the label "
"next to the icon."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishlarida `state_selection` maydoni standart holatda "
"belgi yonida yorliq ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1006
msgid "`hide_label`: hide the label next to the icon"
msgstr "`hide_label`: belgi yonidagi yorliqni yashirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1016
msgid "Favorite (`boolean_favorite`)"
msgstr "Sevimli (`boolean_favorite`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1013
msgid ""
"This widget is displayed as an empty (or not) star, depending on a "
"boolean value. Note that it also can be edited in readonly mode."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet mantiqiy qiymatga qarab bo'sh (yoki bo'sh bo'lmagan) yulduz "
"sifatida ko'rsatiladi. E'tibor bering, u faqat o'qish rejimida ham "
"tahrirlanishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1022
msgid "Toggle (`boolean_toggle`)"
msgstr "Almashtiruvchi (`boolean_toggle`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1019
msgid ""
"Displays a toggle switch to represent a boolean. This is a subfield of "
"the `boolean` field, mostly used to have a different look."
msgstr ""
"Mantiqiy qiymatni ifodalash uchun almashtirish kalitini ko'rsatadi. "
"Bu `boolean` maydonning pastki maydoni bo'lib, asosan boshqacha "
"ko'rinishga ega bo'lish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1047
msgid "Stat Info (`statinfo`)"
msgstr "Statistika ma'lumoti (`statinfo`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1025
msgid ""
"This widget is meant to represent statistical information in a `stat "
"button`. It is basically just a label with a number."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet `stat button` da statistik ma'lumotni ifodalashga mo'ljallangan. "
"Asosan bu faqat raqam bilan yorliq."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1028
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1055
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1064
msgid "Supported field types: `integer`, `float`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `integer`, `float`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1032
msgid ""
"`label_field`: if given, the widget will use the value of the "
"`label_field` as text."
msgstr ""
"`label_field`: berilgan bo'lsa, vidjet `label_field` qiymatini matn "
"sifatida ishlatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1059
msgid "Percent Pie (`percentpie`)"
msgstr "Foiz diagrammasi (`percentpie`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1050
msgid ""
"This widget is meant to represent statistical information in a `stat "
"button`. This is similar to a statinfo widget, but the information is "
"represented in a **pie chart** (empty to full).  Note that the value is "
"interpreted as a percentage (a number between `0` and `100`)."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet `stat button` da statistik ma'lumotni ifodalashga mo'ljallangan. "
"Bu statinfo vidjetiga o'xshaydi, lekin ma'lumot **doira diagrammasi** "
"(bo'shdan to'liqgacha) shaklida ifodalanadi. E'tibor bering, qiymat "
"foiz sifatida talqin qilinadi (`0` dan `100` gacha son)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1090
msgid "Progress Bar (`progressbar`)"
msgstr "Progress paneli (`progressbar`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1062
msgid "Represent a value as a progress bar (from `0` to some value)"
msgstr "Qiymatni progress paneli sifatida ifodalash (`0` dan qandaydir qiymatgacha)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1068
msgid "`editable`: boolean determining whether the `value` is editable"
msgstr "`editable`: `value` tahrirlanishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi mantiqiy qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1070
msgid ""
"`current_value`: get the current value from the field that must be "
"present in the view"
msgstr ""
"`current_value`: ko'rinishda mavjud bo'lishi kerak bo'lgan maydondan "
"joriy qiymatni olish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1072
msgid ""
"`max_value`: get the maximum value from the field that must be present in"
" the view"
msgstr ""
"`max_value`: ko'rinishda mavjud bo'lishi kerak bo'lgan maydondan "
"maksimal qiymatni olish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1074
msgid "`edit_max_value`: boolean determining whether the `max_value` is editable"
msgstr "`edit_max_value`: `max_value` tahrirlanishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi mantiqiy qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1076
msgid "`title`: title of the bar, displayed on top of the bar"
msgstr "`title`: panelning sarlavhasi, panelning tepasida ko'rsatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1078
msgid ""
"-> not translated, use `title` attribute (not option) instead if the term"
" must be translated"
msgstr ""
"-> tarjima qilinmaydi, agar atama tarjima qilinishi kerak bo'lsa, "
"o'rniga `title` atributini (parametr emas) ishlating"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1106
msgid "Journal Dashboard Graph (`dashboard_graph`)"
msgstr "Jurnal boshqaruv paneli grafigi (`dashboard_graph`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1093
msgid ""
"This is a more specialized widget, useful to display a graph representing"
" a set of data. For example, it is used in the accounting dashboard "
"kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Bu yanada ixtisoslashgan vidjet bo'lib, ma'lumotlar to'plamini ifodalovchi "
"grafik ko'rsatish uchun foydali. Masalan, u buxgalteriya boshqaruv paneli "
"kanban ko'rinishida ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1096
msgid "It assumes that the field is a JSON serialization of a set of data."
msgstr "U maydon ma'lumotlar to'plamining JSON serializatsiyasi ekanligini taxmin qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1102
msgid "`graph_type`: string, can be either `\"line\"` or `\"bar\"`"
msgstr "`graph_type`: satr, `\"line\"` yoki `\"bar\"` bo'lishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1112
msgid "Ace Editor (`ace`)"
msgstr "Ace muharriri (`ace`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1109
msgid ""
"This widget is intended to be used on Text fields. It provides Ace Editor"
" for editing XML and Python."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet Matn maydonlarida ishlatilishga mo'ljallangan. U XML va Python "
"tahrirlash uchun Ace Editor ni taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1112
msgid "Supported field types: `char`, `text`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `char`, `text`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1125
msgid "Badge (`badge`)"
msgstr "Nishon (`badge`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1115
msgid "Displays the value inside a bootstrap badge pill."
msgstr "Qiymatni bootstrap nishon pill ichida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1117
msgid "Supported field types: `char`, `selection`, `many2one`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `char`, `selection`, `many2one`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1119
msgid ""
"By default, the badge has a light grey background, but it can be "
"customized by using the :ref:`Decoration "
"<reference/javascript_reference/field_decoration>` mechanism. For "
"instance, to display a red badge under a given condition:"
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda nishon ochiq kulrang fonga ega, lekin uni "
":ref:`Dekoratsiya <reference/javascript_reference/field_decoration>` "
"mexanizmi yordamida sozlash mumkin. Masalan, muayyan sharoitda qizil "
"nishon ko'rsatish uchun:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1130
msgid "Selection (`selection`)"
msgstr "Tanlov (`selection`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1136
msgid ""
"`placeholder`: a string which is used to display some info when no value "
"is selected"
msgstr ""
"`placeholder`: hech qanday qiymat tanlanmagan paytda ma'lumot ko'rsatish "
"uchun ishlatiladigan satr"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1157
msgid "Radio (`radio`)"
msgstr "Radio (`radio`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1143
msgid ""
"This is a subfield of `FielSelection`, but specialized to display all the"
" valid choices as radio buttons."
msgstr ""
"Bu `FielSelection` ning pastki maydoni, lekin barcha to'g'ri tanlovlarni "
"radio tugmalar sifatida ko'rsatishga ixtisoslashgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1146
msgid ""
"Note that if used on a many2one records, then more rpcs will be done to "
"fetch the name_gets of the related records."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, agar many2one yozuvlarida ishlatilsa, tegishli yozuvlarning "
"name_get larini olish uchun ko'proq rpc lar bajariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1149
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1163
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1352
msgid "Supported field types: `selection`, `many2one`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `selection`, `many2one`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1153
msgid "`horizontal`: if `true`, radio buttons will be displayed horizontally."
msgstr "`horizontal`: `true` bo'lsa, radio tugmalar gorizontal ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1167
msgid "Badge Selection (`selection_badge`)"
msgstr "Nishon tanlash (`selection_badge`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1160
msgid ""
"This is a subfield of `selection` field, but specialized to display all "
"the valid choices as rectangular badges."
msgstr ""
"Bu `selection` maydonning pastki maydoni, lekin barcha to'g'ri tanlovlarni "
"to'rtburchakli nishonlar sifatida ko'rsatishga ixtisoslashgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1206
msgid "Many2one (`many2one`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-bir (`many2one`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1170
msgid "Default widget for many2one fields."
msgstr "many2one maydonlari uchun standart vidjet."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1176
msgid ""
"`can_create`: allow the creation of related records (takes precedence "
"over `no_create` option)"
msgstr ""
"`can_create`: tegishli yozuvlar yaratishga ruxsat berish (`no_create` "
"parametridan ustun turadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1179
msgid "`can_write`: allow the editing of related records (default: `true`)"
msgstr "`can_write`: tegishli yozuvlarni tahrirlashga ruxsat berish (standart: `true`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1183
msgid ""
"`quick_create`: allow the quick creation of related records (default: "
"`true`)"
msgstr ""
"`quick_create`: tegishli yozuvlarni tez yaratishga ruxsat berish (standart: "
"`true`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1185
msgid ""
"`no_create`: prevent the creation of related records - hide both the "
"**Create \"xxx\"** and **Create and Edit** dropdown menu items (default: "
"`false`)"
msgstr ""
"`no_create`: tegishli yozuvlar yaratishni oldini olish - ham **\"xxx\" "
"yaratish** ham **Yaratish va tahrirlash** ochiladigan menyu elementlarini "
"yashirish (standart: `false`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1188
msgid ""
"`no_quick_create`: prevent the quick creation of related records - hide "
"the **Create \"xxx\"** dropdown menu item (default: `false`)"
msgstr ""
"`no_quick_create`: tegishli yozuvlarni tez yaratishni oldini olish - "
"**\"xxx\" yaratish** ochiladigan menyu elementini yashirish (standart: "
"`false`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1191
msgid ""
"`no_create_edit`: hide the **Create and Edit** dropdown menu item "
"(default: `false`)"
msgstr ""
"`no_create_edit`: **Yaratish va tahrirlash** ochiladigan menyu elementini "
"yashirish (standart: `false`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1193
msgid ""
"`create_name_field`: when creating a related record, if this option is "
"set, the value of the `create_name_field` will be filled with the value "
"of the input (default: `name`)"
msgstr ""
"`create_name_field`: tegishli yozuv yaratishda, agar bu parametr o'rnatilgan "
"bo'lsa, `create_name_field` qiymati kirish qiymati bilan to'ldiriladi "
"(standart: `name`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1197
msgid ""
"`always_reload`: boolean, default to `false`. If `true`, the widget will "
"always do an additional `name_get` to fetch its name value. This is used "
"for the situations where the `name_get` method is overridden (please do "
"not do that)"
msgstr ""
"`always_reload`: mantiqiy, standart `false`. `true` bo'lsa, vidjet "
"doimo nom qiymatini olish uchun qo'shimcha `name_get` bajaradi. Bu "
"`name_get` metodi qayta yozilgan holatlarda ishlatiladi (iltimos, buni "
"qilmang)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1201
msgid ""
"`no_open`: boolean, default to `false`. If set to `true`, the many2one "
"will not redirect on the record when clicking on it (in readonly mode)"
msgstr ""
"`no_open`: mantiqiy, standart `false`. `true` ga o'rnatilsa, many2one "
"unga bosilganda (faqat o'qish rejimida) yozuvga yo'naltirmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1217
msgid "Many2one Barcode (`many2one_barcode`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-bir shtrix-kod (`many2one_barcode`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1209
msgid ""
"Widget for `many2one` fields allows to open the camera from a mobile "
"device (Android/iOS) to scan a barcode."
msgstr ""
"`many2one` maydonlari uchun vidjet mobil qurilmadan (Android/iOS) "
"shtrix-kodni skanerlash uchun kamerani ochish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1211
msgid ""
"Specialization of `many2one` field where the user is allowed to use the "
"native camera to scan a barcode. Then it uses `name_search` to search "
"this value."
msgstr ""
"`many2one` maydonining ixtisoslashuvi bo'lib, foydalanuvchi shtrix-kodni "
"skanerlash uchun mahalliy kameradan foydalanishga ruxsat beriladi. Keyin "
"u ushbu qiymatni qidirish uchun `name_search` dan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1214
msgid ""
"If this widget is set and user is not using the mobile application, it "
"will fallback to regular `many2one` (`Many2OneField`)"
msgstr ""
"Agar bu vidjet o'rnatilgan bo'lsa va foydalanuvchi mobil ilovadan "
"foydalanmayotgan bo'lsa, u oddiy `many2one` (`Many2OneField`) ga qaytadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1226
msgid "Many2one Avatar (`many2one_avatar`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-bir avatar (`many2one_avatar`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1220
msgid ""
"This widget is only supported on `many2one` fields pointing to a model "
"which inherits from `image.mixin`. In readonly, it displays the image of "
"the related record next to its `display_name`. Note that the "
"`display_name` isn't a clickable link in this case. In edit, it behaves "
"exactly like the regular `many2one`."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet faqat `image.mixin` dan meros olgan modelga ishora qiluvchi "
"`many2one` maydonlarida qo'llab-quvvatlanadi. Faqat o'qish rejimida u "
"tegishli yozuv rasmini uning `display_name` yonida ko'rsatadi. E'tibor "
"bering, bu holda `display_name` bosiladigan havola emas. Tahrirlash "
"rejimida u oddiy `many2one` kabi ishlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1233
msgid "Many2one Avatar User (`many2one_avatar_user`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-bir avatar foydalanuvchi (`many2one_avatar_user`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1229
msgid ""
"This widget is a specialization of the `Many2OneAvatar`. When the avatar "
"is clicked, we open a chat window with the corresponding user. This "
"widget can only be set on `many2one` fields pointing to the `res.users` "
"model."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet `Many2OneAvatar` ning ixtisoslashuvidir. Avatar bosilganda, "
"tegishli foydalanuvchi bilan suhbat oynasini ochamiz. Bu vidjet faqat "
"`res.users` modeliga ishora qiluvchi `many2one` maydonlarida o'rnatilishi "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1233
msgid "Supported field types: `many2one` (pointing to `res.users`)"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `many2one` (`res.users` ga ishora qiluvchi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1238
msgid "Many2one Avatar Employee (`many2one_avatar_employee`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-bir avatar xodim (`many2one_avatar_employee`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1236
msgid ""
"Same as `many2one_avatar_user`, but for `many2one` fields pointing to "
"`hr.employee`."
msgstr ""
"`many2one_avatar_user` bilan bir xil, lekin `hr.employee` ga ishora "
"qiluvchi `many2one` maydonlari uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1238
msgid "Supported field types: `many2one` (pointing to `hr.employee`)"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `many2one` (`hr.employee` ga ishora qiluvchi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1257
msgid "Many2many (`many2many`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p (`many2many`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1241
msgid "Default widget for `many2many` fields."
msgstr "`many2many` maydonlari uchun standart vidjet."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1243
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1264
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1275
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1310
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1315
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1324
msgid "Supported field types: `many2many`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `many2many`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1247
msgid "`mode`: string, default view to display"
msgstr "`mode`: satr, ko'rsatiladigan standart ko'rinish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1249
msgid "`domain`: restrict the data to a specific domain"
msgstr "`domain`: ma'lumotlarni muayyan domenga cheklash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1253
msgid ""
"`create_text`: allow the customization of the text displayed when adding "
"a new record"
msgstr ""
"`create_text`: yangi yozuv qo'shishda ko'rsatiladigan matnni "
"sozlash imkonini berish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1255
msgid ""
"`link`: domain determining whether records can be added to the relation "
"(default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`link`: yozuvlar munosabatga qo'shilishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi domen "
"(standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1257
msgid ""
"`unlink`: domain determining whether records can be removed from the "
"relation (default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`unlink`: yozuvlar munosabatdan olib tashlanishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi "
"domen (standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1270
msgid "Many2many Binary File (`many2many_binary`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p ikkilik fayl (`many2many_binary`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1260
msgid ""
"This widget helps the user to upload or delete one or more files at the "
"same time."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet foydalanuvchiga bir vaqtning o'zida bir yoki bir nechta faylni "
"yuklash yoki o'chirish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1262
msgid "Note that this widget is specific to the model `ir.attachment`."
msgstr "E'tibor bering, bu vidjet `ir.attachment` modeliga xos."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1304
msgid "Many2many Tags (`many2many_tags`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p teglar (`many2many_tags`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1273
msgid "Display a `many2many` field as a list of tags."
msgstr "`many2many` maydonini teglar ro'yxati sifatida ko'rsatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1279
msgid ""
"`create`: domain determining whether or not new tags can be created "
"(default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`create`: yangi teglar yaratilishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi domen "
"(standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1285
msgid ""
"`color_field`: the name of a numeric field, which should be present in "
"the view. A color will be chosen depending on its value."
msgstr ""
"`color_field`: ko'rinishda mavjud bo'lishi kerak bo'lgan raqamli maydon "
"nomi. Rang uning qiymatiga qarab tanlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1292
msgid ""
"`no_edit_color`: set to `true` to remove the possibility to change the "
"color of the tags (default: `false`)."
msgstr ""
"`no_edit_color`: teglar rangini o'zgartirish imkoniyatini olib tashlash "
"uchun `true` ga o'rnating (standart: `false`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1299
msgid ""
"`edit_tags`: set to `true` to add the possibility to update tag related "
"record by clicking on the tags. (default: `false`)."
msgstr ""
"`edit_tags`: teglarga bosish orqali teg tegishli yozuvni yangilash "
"imkoniyatini qo'shish uchun `true` ga o'rnating. (standart: `false`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1310
msgid "Many2many Tags - Form View (`form.many2many_tags`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p teglar - forma ko'rinishi (`form.many2many_tags`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1307
msgid ""
"Specialization of `many2many_tags` widget for form views. It has some "
"extra code to allow editing the color of a tag."
msgstr ""
"Forma ko'rinishlari uchun `many2many_tags` vidjetining ixtisoslashuvi. "
"Tegning rangini tahrirlash imkonini beruvchi qo'shimcha kodi mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1315
msgid "Many2many Tags - Kanban View (`kanban.many2many_tags`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p teglar - kanban ko'rinishi (`kanban.many2many_tags`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1313
msgid "Specialization of `many2many_tags` widget for kanban views."
msgstr "Kanban ko'rinishlari uchun `many2many_tags` vidjetining ixtisoslashuvi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1324
msgid "Many2many Checkboxes (`many2many_checkboxes`)"
msgstr "Ko'p-ko'p belgilash katakchalari (`many2many_checkboxes`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1318
msgid ""
"This field displays a list of checkboxes and allows the user to select a "
"subset of the choices. Note that the number of displayed values is "
"limited to `100`. This limit isn't customizable. It simply allows to "
"handle extreme cases where this widget is wrongly set on a field with a "
"huge comodel. In those cases, a list view is more adequate as it allows "
"pagination and filtering."
msgstr ""
"Bu maydon belgilash katakchalari ro'yxatini ko'rsatadi va foydalanuvchiga "
"tanlovlar to'plamini tanlash imkonini beradi. E'tibor bering, ko'rsatiladigan "
"qiymatlar soni `100` bilan cheklangan. Bu chegara sozlanmaydi. Bu shunchaki "
"ushbu vidjet katta komodel bilan maydonga noto'g'ri o'rnatilgan ekstremal "
"holatlarda ishlash imkonini beradi. Bunday hollarda ro'yxat ko'rinishi "
"ko'proq mos keladi, chunki u sahifalash va filtrlarni qo'llab-quvvatlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1346
msgid "One2many (`one2many`)"
msgstr "Bir-ko'p (`one2many`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1327
msgid ""
"Default widget for `one2many` fields. It usually displays data in a sub "
"list view, or a sub kanban view."
msgstr ""
"`one2many` maydonlari uchun standart vidjet. U odatda ma'lumotlarni "
"quyi ro'yxat ko'rinishi yoki quyi kanban ko'rinishida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1330
msgid "Supported field types: `one2many`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `one2many`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1334
msgid ""
"`create`: domain determining whether or not related records can be "
"created (default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`create`: tegishli yozuvlar yaratilishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi domen "
"(standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1336
msgid ""
"`delete`: domain determining whether or not related records can be "
"deleted (default: `true`)."
msgstr ""
"`delete`: tegishli yozuvlar o'chirilishi mumkinligini aniqlovchi domen "
"(standart: `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1342
msgid "`create_text`: a string that is used to customize the 'Add' label/text."
msgstr "`create_text`: 'Qo'shish' yorlig'i/matnini sozlash uchun ishlatiladigan satr."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1352
msgid "Status Bar (`statusbar`)"
msgstr "Holat paneli (`statusbar`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1349
msgid ""
"This is a field specific to the form views. It is the bar on top of many "
"forms which represent a flow, and allow selecting a specific state."
msgstr ""
"Bu forma ko'rinishlariga xos maydon. Bu ko'plab formasida oqimni "
"ifodalovchi va muayyan holatni tanlash imkonini beruvchi yuqoridagi "
"paneldir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1364
msgid "Reference (`reference`)"
msgstr "Havola (`reference`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1355
msgid ""
"The `reference` field is a combination of a select (for the model) and a "
"`many2one` field (for its value).  It allows the selection of a record on"
" an arbitrary model."
msgstr ""
"`reference` maydoni tanlash (model uchun) va `many2one` maydoni "
"(uning qiymati uchun) kombinatsiyasidir. U ixtiyoriy modelda yozuv "
"tanlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1359
msgid "Supported field types: `char`, `reference`"
msgstr "Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: `char`, `reference`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1363
msgid ""
"`model_field`: name of an `ir.model` containing the model of the records "
"that can be selected. When this option is set, the select part of the "
"`reference` field isn't displayed."
msgstr ""
"`model_field`: tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan yozuvlar modelini o'z ichiga "
"oluvchi `ir.model` ning nomi. Bu parametr o'rnatilganda, `reference` "
"maydonning tanlash qismi ko'rsatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1369
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2742
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:93
msgid "Widgets"
msgstr "Vidjetlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1383
msgid "Ribbon (`web_ribbon`)"
msgstr "Lenta (`web_ribbon`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1372
msgid ""
"This widget displays a ribbon at the top right corner of the kanban card "
"or the form view sheet, for instance, to indicate archived records."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet kanban kartasi yoki forma ko'rinishi varag'ining yuqori o'ng "
"burchagida lenta ko'rsatadi, masalan, arxivlangan yozuvlarni bildirish uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1381
msgid "`title`: text displayed in the ribbon."
msgstr "`title`: lentada ko'rsatiladigan matn."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1382
msgid "`tooltip`: text displayed in the ribbon's tooltip."
msgstr "`tooltip`: lentaning maslahat qo'shimchasida ko'rsatiladigan matn."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1383
msgid ""
"`bg-class`: classname to set on the ribbon, typically to define the "
"ribbon's color."
msgstr ""
"`bg-class`: lentaga o'rnatiladigan sinf nomi, odatda lentaning rangini "
"belgilash uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1391
msgid "Week Days (`week_days`)"
msgstr "Hafta kunlari (`week_days`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1386
msgid ""
"This widget displays a list of checkboxes for week days, 1 checkbox for "
"each day and allow the user to select a subset of the choices."
msgstr ""
"Bu vidjet hafta kunlari uchun belgilash katakchalari ro'yxatini ko'rsatadi, "
"har bir kun uchun 1 ta katakcha va foydalanuvchiga tanlovlar to'plamini "
"tanlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1394
msgid "Client actions"
msgstr "Mijoz amallari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1396
msgid ""
"A client action is a component that can be displayed as the main element "
"in the webclient, occupying all the space below the navbar, just like an "
"`act_window_action`. This is useful when you need a component that is not"
" closely linked to an existing view or a specific model.  For example, "
"the Discuss application is a client action."
msgstr ""
"Mijoz amali - bu `act_window_action` kabi navbardan pastdagi barcha "
"joyni egallagan holda veb-mijozda asosiy element sifatida ko'rsatilishi "
"mumkin bo'lgan komponent. Bu mavjud ko'rinish yoki muayyan model bilan "
"yaqin bog'liq bo'lmagan komponent kerak bo'lganda foydali. Masalan, "
"Muhokama ilovasi mijoz amali hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1401
msgid ""
"A client action is a term that has various meanings, depending on the "
"context:"
msgstr ""
"Mijoz amali - bu kontekstga qarab turli ma'nolarga ega bo'lgan atama:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1403
msgid ""
"from the perspective of the server, it is a record of the model "
"*ir_action*, with a field *tag* of type char"
msgstr ""
"server nuqtai nazaridan bu char turidagi *tag* maydoni bilan *ir_action* "
"modelining yozuvi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1405
msgid ""
"from the perspective of the web client, it is an Owl component registered"
" in the action registry under the same key its tag"
msgstr ""
"veb-mijoz nuqtai nazaridan bu amal registrida o'zining tegi bilan bir xil "
"kalit ostida ro'yxatdan o'tgan Owl komponenti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1408
msgid ""
"Whenever a menu item is associated with a client action, opening it will "
"simply fetch the action definition from the server, then lookup its tag "
"in the action registry to get the component definition. This component "
"will then be rendered by the action container."
msgstr ""
"Menyu elementi mijoz amali bilan bog'langan bo'lsa, uni ochish shunchaki "
"serverdan amal ta'rifini oladi, keyin komponent ta'rifini olish uchun "
"amal registrida uning tegini qidiradi. Bu komponent keyinchalik amal "
"konteyner tomonidan ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1414
msgid "Adding a client action"
msgstr "Mijoz amali qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1416
msgid ""
"A client action is a component that will control the part of the screen "
"below the navbar. Defining a client action is as simple as creating an "
"Owl component and adding it to the action registry."
msgstr ""
"Mijoz amali - bu navbardan pastdagi ekran qismini boshqaradigan komponent. "
"Mijoz amalini aniqlash Owl komponenti yaratish va uni amal registriga "
"qo'shish kabi oddiy."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/javascript_reference.rst:1426
msgid ""
"Then, to use the client action in the web client, we need to create a "
"client action record (a record of the model ``ir.actions.client``) with "
"the proper ``tag`` attribute:"
msgstr ""
"Keyin, veb-mijozda mijoz amalidan foydalanish uchun to'g'ri ``tag`` "
"atributi bilan mijoz amali yozuvini (``ir.actions.client`` modelining "
"yozuvi) yaratish kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:5
msgid "Mobile JavaScript"
msgstr "Mobil JavaScript"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:10
msgid ""
"In Odoo 10.0 we released a mobile app which allows you to access all "
"**Odoo apps** (even your customized modules)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 10.0 da biz barcha **Odoo ilovalar** ga (hatto maxsus modullaringizga "
"ham) kirish imkonini beruvchi mobil ilova chiqardik."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:13
msgid ""
"The application is a combination of **Odoo Web** and **Native Mobile "
"components**. In other words it is a Odoo Web instance loaded inside a "
"native, mobile, WebView container."
msgstr ""
"Ilova **Odoo Web** va **Mahalliy mobil komponentlar** kombinatsiyasidir. "
"Boshqacha qilib aytganda, u mahalliy, mobil, WebView konteyner ichiga "
"yuklangan Odoo Web namunasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:16
msgid ""
"This page documents how you can access mobile native components like "
"Camera, Vibration, Notification and Toast through Odoo Web (via "
"JavaScript). For this, you do not need to be a mobile developer, if you "
"know Odoo JavaScript API you can access all available mobile features."
msgstr ""
"Bu sahifa Odoo Web orqali (JavaScript yordamida) Kamera, Tebranish, "
"Bildirishnoma va Toast kabi mobil mahalliy komponentlarga qanday kirishingiz "
"mumkinligini hujjatlashtiradi. Buning uchun mobil ishlab chiqaruvchi "
"bo'lishingiz shart emas, Odoo JavaScript API ni bilsangiz barcha mavjud "
"mobil funksiyalarga kirishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:22
msgid "These features work with **Odoo Enterprise 10.0+** only"
msgstr "Bu funksiyalar faqat **Odoo Enterprise 10.0+** bilan ishlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:25
msgid "How does it work?"
msgstr "U qanday ishlaydi?"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:27
msgid "Internal workings of the mobile application:"
msgstr "Mobil ilovaning ichki ishlash tartibi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:31
msgid ""
"Of course, it is a web page that loads on a Mobile Native Web container. "
"But it is integrated in such a way that you can access native resources "
"from your web JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Albatta, bu Mobil Mahalliy Web konteynerga yuklanadigan veb-sahifa. "
"Lekin u shunday integratsiyalashganki, siz veb JavaScript dan mahalliy "
"resurslarga kirishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:35
msgid ""
"WebPages (Odoo Web) is on the top of each layer, where the second layer "
"is a Bridge between Odoo Web (JS) and the native mobile components."
msgstr ""
"WebPages (Odoo Web) har bir qatlamning tepasida joylashgan, ikkinchi "
"qatlam Odoo Web (JS) va mahalliy mobil komponentlar o'rtasidagi Ko'prik."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:38
msgid ""
"When any call from JavaScript is triggered it passes through Bridge and "
"Bridge passes it to the native invoker to perform that action."
msgstr ""
"JavaScript dan har qanday chaqiruv ishga tushganda u Ko'prikdan o'tadi "
"va Ko'prik uni ushbu amalni bajarish uchun mahalliy chaqiruvchiga uzatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:41
msgid ""
"When the native component has done its work, it is passed to the Bridge "
"again and you get the output in JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Mahalliy komponent ishini tugatganda, u yana Ko'prikka uzatiladi va siz "
"chiqishni JavaScript da olasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:44
msgid ""
"Process time taken by the Native component depends on what you are "
"requesting from the Native resources. For example the Camera or GPS "
"Location."
msgstr ""
"Mahalliy komponent tomonidan sarflanadigan jarayon vaqti mahalliy "
"resurslardan nimani so'rashi ga bog'liq. Masalan, Kamera yoki GPS "
"joylashuvi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:48
msgid "How to use it?"
msgstr "Undan qanday foydalanish kerak?"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:50
msgid ""
"Just like the Odoo Web Framework, the Mobile API can be used anywhere by "
"getting the object from **web_mobile.rpc**"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Web Framework kabi, Mobil API **web_mobile.rpc** dan ob'ektni "
"olib istalgan joyda ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:55
msgid ""
"The mobile RPC object provides a list of methods that are available (this"
" only works with the mobile app)."
msgstr ""
"Mobil RPC ob'ekti mavjud metodlar ro'yxatini taqdim etadi (bu faqat "
"mobil ilova bilan ishlaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:58
msgid "Check if the method is available and then execute it."
msgstr "Metod mavjudligini tekshiring va keyin uni bajaring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:61
msgid "Methods"
msgstr "Metodlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:63
msgid ""
"Each of the methods returns a JQuery Deferred object which returns a data"
" JSON dictionary"
msgstr ""
"Har bir metod ma'lumotlar JSON lug'atini qaytaruvchi JQuery Deferred "
"ob'ektini qaytaradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:67
msgid "Show Toast in device"
msgstr "Qurilmada Toast ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:71
msgid "**message** text to display"
msgstr "**message** ko'rsatiladigan matn"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:73
msgid ""
"A toast provides simple feedback about an operation in a small popup. It "
"only fills the amount of space required for the message and the current "
"activity remains visible and interactive."
msgstr ""
"Toast kichik qalqib chiquvchi oynada operatsiya haqida oddiy qayta "
"aloqa beradi. U faqat xabar uchun kerakli joy hajmini to'ldiradi va "
"joriy faoliyat ko'rinadigan va interaktiv bo'lib qoladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:84
msgid "Vibrating device"
msgstr "Qurilmani tebratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:88
msgid "Vibrates constantly for the specified period of time (in milliseconds)."
msgstr "Belgilangan vaqt davomida (millisekundlarda) doimiy tebranadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:91
msgid "Vibrate mobile device with given duration."
msgstr "Mobil qurilmani berilgan davomiylik bilan tebratish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:98
msgid "Show snackbar with action"
msgstr "Amal bilan snackbar ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:102
msgid ""
"(*required*) **Message** to show in snackbar and action **button label** "
"in Snackbar (optional)"
msgstr ""
"(*majburiy*) snackbarda ko'rsatiladigan **xabar** va Snackbar dagi amal "
"**tugma yorlig'i** (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:103
msgid ""
"``True`` if the user clicks on the Action button, ``False`` if SnackBar "
"auto dismissed after some time."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi Amal tugmasini bossа ``True``, SnackBar bir muddat o'tgach "
"avtomatik yopilsa ``False``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:105
msgid ""
"Snackbars provide lightweight feedback about an operation. They show a "
"brief message at the bottom of the screen on mobile or in the lower left "
"corner on larger devices. Snackbars appear above all the other elements "
"on the screen and only one can be displayed at a time."
msgstr ""
"Snackbarlar operatsiya haqida engil qayta aloqa beradi. Ular mobil "
"qurilmalarda ekranning pastida yoki katta qurilmalarda pastki chap "
"burchakda qisqacha xabar ko'rsatadi. Snackbarlar ekrandagi barcha boshqa "
"elementlardan yuqorida ko'rinadi va bir vaqtda faqat bittasi ko'rsatilishi "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:123
msgid "Showing notification"
msgstr "Bildirishnoma ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:127
msgid ""
"**title** (first row) of the notification, **message** (second row) of "
"the notification, in a standard notification."
msgstr ""
"Standart bildirishnomada bildirishnomaning **sarlavhasi** (birinchi qator), "
"bildirishnomaning **xabari** (ikkinchi qator)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:129
msgid ""
"A notification is a message you can display to the user outside of your "
"application's normal UI. When you tell the system to issue a "
"notification, it first appears as an icon in the notification area. To "
"see the details of the notification, the user opens the notification "
"drawer. Both the notification area and the notification drawer are "
"system-controlled areas that the user can view at any time."
msgstr ""
"Bildirishnoma - bu foydalanuvchiga ilovangizning oddiy UI dan tashqarida "
"ko'rsatishingiz mumkin bo'lgan xabar. Tizimga bildirishnoma chiqarishni "
"aytganda, u avval bildirishnomalar sohasida belgi sifatida paydo bo'ladi. "
"Bildirishnoma tafsilotlarini ko'rish uchun foydalanuvchi bildirishnomalar "
"tortmasini ochadi. Bildirishnomalar sohasi va bildirishnomalar tortmasi "
"ham foydalanuvchi istalgan vaqtda ko'rishi mumkin bo'lgan tizim tomonidan "
"boshqariladigan sohalar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:144
msgid "Create contact in device"
msgstr "Qurilmada kontakt yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:148
msgid ""
"Dictionary with contact details. Possible keys (name, mobile, phone, fax,"
" email, website, street, street2, country_id, state_id, city, zip, "
"parent_id, function and image)"
msgstr ""
"Kontakt tafsilotlari bilan lug'at. Mumkin bo'lgan kalitlar (name, mobile, "
"phone, fax, email, website, street, street2, country_id, state_id, city, "
"zip, parent_id, function va image)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:150
msgid "Create a new device contact with the given contact details."
msgstr "Berilgan kontakt tafsilotlari bilan yangi qurilma kontakti yaratish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:177
msgid "Scanning barcodes"
msgstr "Shtrix-kodlarni skanerlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:181
msgid "Scanned ``code`` from any barcode"
msgstr "Har qanday shtrix-koddan skanerlangan ``code``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:183
msgid ""
"The barcode API detects barcodes in real-time, on the device, in any "
"orientation."
msgstr ""
"Shtrix-kod API qurilmada, har qanday yo'nalishda real vaqtda shtrix-kodlarni "
"aniqlatydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:185
msgid "The barcode API can read the following barcode formats:"
msgstr "Shtrix-kod API quyidagi shtrix-kod formatlarini o'qiy oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:187
msgid ""
"1D barcodes: EAN-13, EAN-8, UPC-A, UPC-E, Code-39, Code-93, Code-128, "
"ITF, Codabar"
msgstr ""
"1D shtrix-kodlar: EAN-13, EAN-8, UPC-A, UPC-E, Code-39, Code-93, Code-128, "
"ITF, Codabar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:188
msgid "2D barcodes: QR Code, Data Matrix, PDF-417, AZTEC"
msgstr "2D shtrix-kodlar: QR Code, Data Matrix, PDF-417, AZTEC"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:199
msgid "Switching account in device"
msgstr "Qurilmada hisobni almashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/mobile.rst:203
msgid "Use switchAccount to switch from one account to another on the device."
msgstr "Qurilmada bir hisobdan boshqasiga o'tish uchun switchAccount dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:3
msgid "Odoo Editor"
msgstr "Odoo muharriri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo Editor is Odoo's own rich text editor. Its sources can be found in "
"the `odoo-editor directory "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/editor"
"/odoo-editor>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo muharriri - bu Odoo ning o'z boy matn muharriri. Uning manba kodlari "
"`odoo-editor katalogida "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/editor"
"/odoo-editor>`_ topilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:10
msgid "Powerbox"
msgstr "Powerbox"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Powerbox is a piece of user interface that contains :ref:`commands "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/command>` organized into "
":ref:`categories <reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/category>`. It "
"appears when typing `/` in the editor. The commands can be filtered when "
"the user inputs text, and navigated with the arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"Powerbox - bu :ref:`toifalar <reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/category>` "
"bo'yicha tashkil etilgan :ref:`buyruqlar "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/command>` ni o'z ichiga olgan "
"foydalanuvchi interfeysi qismi. U muharrirda `/` yozilganda paydo bo'ladi. "
"Buyruqlar foydalanuvchi matn kiritganda filtrlanishi va o'q tugmalari bilan "
"navigatsiya qilinishi mumkin."

msgid "The Powerbox opened after typing \"/\"."
msgstr "\"/\" yozilgandan so'ng ochilgan Powerbox."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:23
msgid "Modifying the Powerbox"
msgstr "Powerbox ni o'zgartirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:25
msgid ""
"Only one Powerbox should be instantiated at the time, and that job is "
"done by the editor itself. Its Powerbox instance can be found in its "
"`powerbox` instance variable. To change the Powerbox's contents and "
"options, change the options passed to the editor before it gets "
"instantiated."
msgstr ""
"Bir vaqtning o'zida faqat bitta Powerbox misol qilinishi kerak va bu ishni "
"muharrir o'zi bajaradi. Uning Powerbox misoli `powerbox` misol o'zgaruvchisida "
"topilishi mumkin. Powerbox mazmuni va parametrlarini o'zgartirish uchun "
"muharrirga uzatilgan parametrlarni u misol qilinishidan oldin o'zgartiring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:32
msgid ""
"Never instantiate the Powerbox yourself. Always use the current editor's "
"own instance instead."
msgstr ""
"Hech qachon Powerboxni o'zingiz misol qilmang. Buning o'rniga har doim "
"joriy muharrirning o'z misolidan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:36
msgid ""
"Say we want to add a new command `Document` to the Powerbox, just for the"
" `mass_mailing` module. We want to add it to a new category called "
"`Documentation` and we want it all the way at the top of the Powerbox."
msgstr ""
"Aytaylik, faqat `mass_mailing` moduli uchun Powerbox ga yangi `Document` "
"buyrug'ini qo'shmoqchimiz. Uni `Documentation` deb nomlangan yangi toifaga "
"qo'shmoqchimiz va uni Powerbox ning eng tepasida joylashtirishni xohlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:40
msgid ""
"`mass_mailing` `extends "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/mass_mailing/static/src/js/wysiwyg.js>`_"
" `web_editor`'s `Wysiwyg class "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/wysiwyg/wysiwyg.js>`_,"
" which instantiates the editor in its `start` method. Before doing so, it"
" calls its own `_getPowerboxOptions` method, which can conveniently be "
"overridden to add our new commands."
msgstr ""
"`mass_mailing` `web_editor` ning `Wysiwyg sinfini "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/wysiwyg/wysiwyg.js>`_"
" `kengaytiradi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/mass_mailing/static/src/js/wysiwyg.js>`_,"
" bu muharrirnini `start` metodida misol qiladi. Bunga qadar u yangi buyruqlar "
"qo'shish uchun qulay qayta yozilishi mumkin bo'lgan o'zining `_getPowerboxOptions` "
"metodini chaqiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:48
msgid ""
"Since `mass_mailing` already overrides `_getPowerboxOptions`, let's just "
"add our new command to it:"
msgstr ""
"`mass_mailing` allaqachon `_getPowerboxOptions` ni qayta yozganligi sababli, "
"shunchaki yangi buyrug'imizni unga qo'shaylik:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:71
msgid ""
"In order to allow the names and descriptions of your commands and "
"categories to be translated, make sure to wrap them in the `_t` function."
msgstr ""
"Buyruqlar va toifalarning nomlari va tavsiflarini tarjima qilish imkonini "
"berish uchun ularni `_t` funksiyasiga o'rashni unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:75
msgid ""
"To avoid out-of-control escalations, don't use random numbers for your "
"priorities: look at which other priorities already exist and choose your "
"value accordingly (like you would do for a `z-index`)."
msgstr ""
"Nazorat qilib bo'lmaydigan kuchaytirishlardan qochish uchun ustuvorliklar "
"uchun tasodifiy sonlardan foydalanmang: qaysi boshqa ustuvorliklar allaqachon "
"mavjudligini ko'ring va qiymatni shunga muvofiq tanlang (`z-index` uchun "
"qilganingiz kabi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:80
msgid "Opening a custom Powerbox"
msgstr "Maxsus Powerbox ochish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:82
msgid ""
"It is possible to open the Powerbox with a custom set of categories and "
"commands, bypassing all pre-existing ones. To do that, call the `open` "
"method of the Powerbox and pass it your custom commands and categories."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud barcha kategoriya va buyruqlarni chetlab o'tib, maxsus toifalar va "
"buyruqlar to'plami bilan Powerboxni ochish mumkin. Buning uchun Powerbox "
"ning `open` metodini chaqiring va unga maxsus buyruqlar va toifalarni uzating."

msgid ""
"The Powerbox opened with custom categories and commands when pasting an\n"
"image URL."
msgstr ""
"Rasm URL sini joylashtirganida maxsus toifalar va buyruqlar bilan "
"ochilgan Powerbox."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:92
msgid ""
"We need the current instance of the Powerbox, which can be found in the "
"current editor. In the `Wysiwyg class "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/wysiwyg/wysiwyg.js>`_,"
" you will find it as `this.odooEditor.powerbox`."
msgstr ""
"Joriy muharriarda topilishi mumkin bo'lgan Powerbox ning joriy misoli "
"kerak. `Wysiwyg sinfida "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web_editor/static/src/js/wysiwyg/wysiwyg.js>`_"
" uni `this.odooEditor.powerbox` sifatida topasiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:97
msgid ""
"Now to open it with our custom \"Document\" command in a custom "
"\"Documentation\" category:"
msgstr ""
"Endi uni maxsus \"Documentation\" toifasidagi maxsus \"Document\" "
"buyrug'i bilan ochish uchun:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:117
msgid "Filtering commands"
msgstr "Buyruqlarni filtrlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:119
msgid "There are three ways to filter commands:"
msgstr "Buyruqlarni filtrlashning uch yo'li mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:121
msgid ""
"Via the `powerboxFilters` :ref:`Powerbox option "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/options>`."
msgstr ""
"`powerboxFilters` :ref:`Powerbox parametri "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/options>` orqali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:123
msgid ""
"Via a given :ref:`command "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/command>`'s `isDisabled` entry."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan :ref:`buyruq "
"<reference/frontend/odoo_editor/powerbox/command>` ning `isDisabled` "
"yozuvi orqali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:126
msgid ""
"The user can filter commands by simply typing text after opening the "
"Powerbox. It will fuzzy-match that text with the names of the categories "
"and commands."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi Powerbox ni ochgandan so'ng shunchaki matn yozib buyruqlarni "
"filtrlashi mumkin. U ushbu matnni toifalar va buyruqlar nomlari bilan "
"noaniq moslashtirib qidiradi."

msgid "The Powerbox with its commands filtered using the word \"head\"."
msgstr "\"head\" so'zi yordamida filtrlangan buyruqlar bilan Powerbox."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:140
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:107
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Toifa"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:151
msgid "the name of the category"
msgstr "toifaning nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:152
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:187
msgid "`priority`"
msgstr "`priority`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:153
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:188
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:377
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:852
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:855
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:858
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1080
msgid "`number`"
msgstr "`number`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:154
msgid ""
"used to order the category: a category with a higher priority is "
"displayed higher into the Powerbox (categories with the same priority are"
" ordered alphabetically)"
msgstr ""
"toifani tartiblashtirish uchun ishlatiladi: yuqori ustuvorlikka ega toifa "
"Powerbox da yuqorida ko'rsatiladi (bir xil ustuvorlikka ega toifalar "
"alifbo tartibida tartiblanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:159
msgid ""
"If several categories exist with the same name, they will be grouped into"
" one. Its priority will be that defined in the version of the category "
"that was declared last."
msgstr ""
"Agar bir xil nomdagi bir nechta toifa mavjud bo'lsa, ular bittaga "
"guruhlanadi. Uning ustuvorligi oxirgi e'lon qilingan toifa versiyasida "
"belgilanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:166
msgid "Command"
msgstr "Buyruq"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:177
msgid "the name of the command"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:178
msgid "`category`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:180
msgid "the name of the category the command belongs to"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:181
msgid "`description`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:183
