#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:184
msgid "`fontawesome`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:186
msgid "the name of a *Font Awesome* that will serve as the command's icon"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:189
msgid ""
"used to order the command: a command with a higher priority is displayed "
"higher into the Powerbox (commands with the same priority are ordered "
"alphabetically)"
msgstr ""
"buyruqni tartiblashtirish uchun ishlatiladi: yuqori ustuvorlikka ega "
"buyruq Powerbox da yuqorida ko'rsatiladi (bir xil ustuvorlikka ega "
"buyruqlar alifbo tartibida tartiblanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:192
msgid "`callback`"
msgstr "`callback`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:193
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:196
msgid "`function` (`() => void`)"
msgstr "`function` (`() => void`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:194
msgid "the function to execute when the command is picked (can be asynchronous)"
msgstr "buyruq tanlanganda bajarish uchun funksiya (asinxron bo'lishi mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:195
msgid "`isDisabled` (optional)"
msgstr "`isDisabled` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:197
msgid ""
"a function used to disable the command under certain conditions (when it "
"returns `true`, the command will be disabled)"
msgstr ""
"muayyan sharoitda buyruqni o'chirib qo'yish uchun ishlatiladigan funksiya "
"(u `true` qaytarsa, buyruq o'chirib qo'yiladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:201
msgid ""
"If the command points to a category that doesn't exist yet, that category"
" will be created and appended at the end of the Powerbox."
msgstr ""
"Agar buyruq hali mavjud bo'lmagan toifaga ishora qilsa, o'sha toifa "
"yaratiladi va Powerbox ning oxiriga qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:209
msgid ""
"The following options can be passed to OdooEditor, that will then be "
"passed to the instance of the Powerbox:"
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi parametrlar OdooEditor ga uzatilishi mumkin, ular keyin Powerbox "
"misoliga uzatiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:219
msgid "`commands`"
msgstr "`commands`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:220
msgid "`array of commands`"
msgstr "`buyruqlar massivi`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:221
msgid "commands to add to the default defined by the editor"
msgstr "muharrir tomonidan belgilangan standartga qo'shiladigan buyruqlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:222
msgid "`categories`"
msgstr "`categories`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:223
msgid "`array of categories`"
msgstr "`toifalar massivi`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:224
msgid "categories to add to the default defined by the editor"
msgstr "muharrir tomonidan belgilangan standartga qo'shiladigan toifalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:225
msgid "`powerboxFilters`"
msgstr "`powerboxFilters`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:226
msgid "`array of functions` (`commands => commands`)"
msgstr "`funksiyalar massivi` (`commands => commands`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:227
msgid "functions used to filter commands displayed in the Powerbox"
msgstr "Powerbox da ko'rsatiladigan buyruqlarni filtrlash uchun ishlatiladigan funksiyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:228
msgid "`getContextFromParentRect`"
msgstr "`getContextFromParentRect`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:229
msgid "`function` (`() => DOMRect`)"
msgstr "`function` (`() => DOMRect`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/odoo_editor.rst:230
msgid ""
"a function that returns the `DOMRect` of an ancestor of the editor (can "
"be useful when the editor is in an iframe)"
msgstr ""
"muharrir ajdodining `DOMRect` ini qaytaruvchi funksiya (muharrir iframe "
"ichida bo'lganda foydali bo'lishi mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:5
msgid "Owl components"
msgstr "Owl komponentlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Odoo Javascript framework uses a custom component framework called "
"Owl. It is a declarative component system, loosely inspired by Vue and "
"React. Components are defined using :doc:`QWeb templates <qweb>`, "
"enriched with some Owl specific directives. The official `Owl "
"documentation <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/readme.md>`_ "
"contains a complete reference and a tutorial."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Javascript freymvorki Owl deb nomlangan maxsus komponent freymvorkidan "
"foydalanadi. Bu Vue va React dan ilhomlanib yaratilgan deklarativ komponent "
"tizimi. Komponentlar bir nechta Owl xususiy direktivalari bilan boyitilgan "
":doc:`QWeb shablonlari <qweb>` yordamida aniqlanadi. Rasmiy `Owl "
"hujjatlari <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/readme.md>`_ "
"to'liq ma'lumotnoma va qo'llanmani o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:16
msgid ""
"Although the code can be found in the `web` module, it is maintained from"
" a separate GitHub repository. Any modification to Owl should therefore "
"be made through a pull request on https://github.com/odoo/owl."
msgstr ""
"Garchi kod `web` modulida topilsa ham, u alohida GitHub omboridan "
"saqlanadi. Owl ga har qanday o'zgartirish shuning uchun https://github.com/odoo/owl "
"da pull request orqali amalga oshirilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:21
msgid ""
"Currently, all Odoo versions (starting in version 14) share the same Owl "
"version."
msgstr ""
"Hozirda barcha Odoo versiyalari (14-versiyadan boshlab) bir xil Owl "
"versiyasini baham ko'radi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:24
msgid "Using Owl components"
msgstr "Owl komponentlaridan foydalanish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:26
msgid ""
"The `Owl documentation`_ already documents in detail the Owl framework, "
"so this page will only provide Odoo specific information. But first, let "
"us see how we can make a simple component in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"`Owl hujjatlari`_ allaqachon Owl freymvorkini batafsil hujjatlashtirgan, "
"shuning uchun bu sahifa faqat Odoo ga xos ma'lumotlarni taqdim etadi. "
"Lekin avval Odoo da oddiy komponent qanday yaratilishini ko'rib chiqaylik."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:50
msgid ""
"This example shows that Owl is available as a library in the global "
"namespace as `owl`: it can simply be used like most libraries in Odoo. "
"Note that we defined here the template as a static property, but without "
"using the `static` keyword, which is not available in some browsers (Odoo"
" javascript code should be Ecmascript 2019 compliant)."
msgstr ""
"Bu misol Owl ning global nom maydonida `owl` kutubxonasi sifatida "
"mavjudligini ko'rsatadi: u Odoo dagi ko'pchilik kutubxonalar kabi "
"shunchaki ishlatilishi mumkin. E'tibor bering, biz bu yerda shablonni "
"statik xususiyat sifatida aniqladik, lekin ba'zi brauzerlarda mavjud "
"bo'lmagan `static` kalit so'zidan foydalanmadik (Odoo javascript kodi "
"Ecmascript 2019 ga mos kelishi kerak)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:56
msgid ""
"We define here the template in the javascript code, with the help of the "
"`xml` helper. However, it is only useful to get started. In practice, "
"templates in Odoo should be defined in an xml file, so they can be "
"translated. In that case, the component should only define the template "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Biz bu yerda `xml` yordamchisi yordamida shablonni javascript kodida "
"aniqlaymiz. Lekin bu faqat boshlash uchun foydali. Amalda, Odoo dagi "
"shablonlar tarjima qilinishi mumkin bo'lishi uchun xml faylda aniqlanishi "
"kerak. Bu holda komponent faqat shablon nomini aniqlashi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:61
msgid ""
"In practice, most components should define 2 or 3 files, located at the "
