#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:176
msgid ""
"This is a component that can perform actions when an element is swiped "
"horizontally. The swiper is wrapping a target element to add actions to "
"it. The action is executed once the user has released the swiper passed a"
" portion of its width."
msgstr ""
"Bu element gorizontal ravishda sıyrıldığında amallarni bajarishi mumkin "
"bo'lgan komponent. Swiper maqsad elementini o'rab olib, unga amallar "
"qo'shadi. Amal foydalanuvchi swiper ni uning kengligining bir qismidan "
"o'tkazib qo'yib yuborgandan so'ng bajariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:187
msgid ""
"The simplest way to use the component is to use it around your target "
"element directly in an xml template as shown above. But sometimes, you "
"may want to extend an existing element and would not want to duplicate "
"the template. It is possible to do just that."
msgstr ""
"Komponentdan foydalanishning eng oddiy yo'li - uni yuqorida ko'rsatilgandek "
"xml shablonida maqsad elementingiz atrofida to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ishlatish. "
"Lekin ba'zan mavjud elementni kengaytirmoqchi bo'lishingiz va shablonni "
"takrorlamoqchi bo'lmasligingiz mumkin. Buni qilish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:191
msgid ""
"If you want to extend the behavior of an existing element, you must place"
" the element inside, by wrapping it directly. Also, you can "
"conditionnally add props to manage when the element might be swipable, "
"its animation and the minimum portion to swipe to perform the action."
msgstr ""
"Agar mavjud elementning xatti-harakatini kengaytirmoqchi bo'lsangiz, "
"elementni to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'rab qo'yib, ichiga joylashtirishingiz kerak. "
"Shuningdek, element syrıla oladigan vaqtni, uning animatsiyasini va amal "
"bajarish uchun kerakli minimal syrma qismini boshqarish uchun shartli "
"ravishda props qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:195
msgid ""
"You can use the component to interact easily with records, messages, "
"items in lists and much more."
msgstr ""
"Komponentdan yozuvlar, xabarlar, ro'yxatlardagi elementlar va boshqa "
"ko'p narsalar bilan oson muloqot qilish uchun foydalanishingiz mumkin."

msgid "Example of ActionSwiper usage"
