#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:415
msgid "Dropdown"
msgstr "Ochiladigan ro'yxat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:420
msgid "`@web/core/dropdown/dropdown` and `@web/core/dropdown/dropdown_item`"
msgstr "`@web/core/dropdown/dropdown` va `@web/core/dropdown/dropdown_item`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:425
msgid ""
"The Dropdown lets you show a menu with a list of items when a toggle is "
"clicked on. They can be combined with DropdownItems to invoke callbacks "
"and close the menu when items are selected."
msgstr ""
"Dropdown almashtiruvchi bosilganda elementlar ro'yxati bilan menyu "
"ko'rsatish imkonini beradi. Ular elementlar tanlanganda callbacklarni "
"chaqirish va menyuni yopish uchun DropdownItems bilan birlashtirilishi "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:429
msgid ""
"Dropdowns are surprisingly complicated components, the list of features "
"they provide is as follow:"
msgstr ""
"Ochiladigan ro'yxatlar ajablanarli darajada murakkab komponentlar bo'lib, "
"ular taqdim etadigan funksiyalar ro'yxati quyidagicha:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:432
msgid "Toggle the item list on click"
msgstr "Bosish orqali elementlar ro'yxatini almashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:433
msgid "Close on outside click"
msgstr "Tashqarida bosilganda yopish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:434
msgid "Call a function when items are selected"
msgstr "Elementlar tanlanganda funksiyani chaqirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:435
msgid "Optionally close the item list when an item is selected"
msgstr "Element tanlanganda ixtiyoriy ravishda elementlar ro'yxatini yopish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:436
msgid "SIY: style it yourself"
msgstr "SIY: uni o'zingiz uslublang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:437
msgid "Support sub dropdowns, up to any level"
msgstr "Har qanday darajadagi quyi ochiladigan ro'yxatlarni qo'llab-quvvatlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:438
msgid "Configurable hotkey to open/close a dropdown or select a dropdown item"
msgstr "Ochiladigan ro'yxatni ochish/yopish yoki elementni tanlash uchun sozlanuvchi tezkor tugma"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:439
msgid "Keyboard navigation (arrows, tab, shift+tab, home, end, enter and escape)"
msgstr "Klaviatura navigatsiyasi (o'qlar, tab, shift+tab, home, end, enter va escape)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:440
msgid "Reposition itself whenever the page scrolls or is resized"
msgstr "Sahifa aylantirilganda yoki o'lcham o'zgartirilganda o'z pozitsiyasini o'zgartirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:441
msgid ""
"Smartly chose the direction it should open (right-to-left direction is "
"automatically handled)."
msgstr ""
"Ochilish yo'nalishini aqlli tanlash (o'ngdan chapga yo'nalishi avtomatik "
"boshqariladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:442
msgid "Direct siblings dropdowns: when one is open, toggle others on hover"
msgstr "Bevosita qo'shni ochiladigan ro'yxatlar: biri ochiq bo'lganda, kursorni olib borganida boshqalarini almashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:444
msgid ""
"To properly use a `<Dropdown/>` component, you need to populate two `OWL "
"slots <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/slots.md>`_ "
":"
msgstr ""
"`<Dropdown/>` komponentidan to'g'ri foydalanish uchun ikkita `OWL "
"slotlarini <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/slots.md>`_ "
"to'ldirish kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:447
msgid ""
"`default` slot: it contains the *toggle* elements of your dropdown. By "
"default, click events will be attached to this element to open and close "
"the dropdown."
msgstr ""
"`default` sloti: u ochiladigan ro'yxatingizning *almashtiruvchi* elementlarini "
"o'z ichiga oladi. Standart holatda, ochiladigan ro'yxatni ochish va yopish "
"uchun bosish hodisalari bu elementga biriktiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:449
msgid ""
"`content` slot: it contains the *elements* of the dropdown menu itself "
"and is rendered inside a popover. Although it is not mandatory, you can "
"put some `DropdownItem` inside this slot, the dropdown will automatically"
" close when these items are selected."
msgstr ""
"`content` sloti: u ochiladigan ro'yxat menyusining *elementlarini* o'z "
"ichiga oladi va popover ichida ko'rsatiladi. Majburiy bo'lmasa ham, bu "
"slotga `DropdownItem` larni qo'yishingiz mumkin, bu elementlar tanlanganda "
"ochiladigan ro'yxat avtomatik ravishda yopiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:469
msgid "Dropdown Props"
msgstr "Dropdown xususiyatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:478
msgid "`menuClass`"
msgstr "`menuClass`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:480
msgid "Optional classname added to the dropdown's menu"
msgstr "Ochiladigan ro'yxat menyusiga qo'shilgan ixtiyoriy sinf nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:483
msgid ""
"Optional, if true, disables the dropdown so the user is not able to open "
"it anymore. (default: `false`)"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy, true bo'lsa, ochiladigan ro'yxatni o'chirib qo'yadi, "
"foydalanuvchi endi uni ochib bo'lmaydi. (standart: `false`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:484
msgid "`items`"
msgstr "`items`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:485
msgid "`Array`"
msgstr "`Array`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:486
msgid ""
"Optional list of items to be displayed as DropdownItems inside the "
"dropdown's menu"
msgstr ""
"Ochiladigan ro'yxat menyusida DropdownItems sifatida ko'rsatiladigan "
"ixtiyoriy elementlar ro'yxati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:489
msgid ""
"Optionally defines the desired menu opening position. RTL direction is "
"automatically applied. Should be a valid :ref:`usePosition "
"<frontend/hooks/useposition>` hook position. (default: `bottom-start`)"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy ravishda kerakli menyu ochilish pozitsiyasini belgilaydi. "
"RTL yo'nalishi avtomatik qo'llaniladi. To'g'ri :ref:`usePosition "
"<frontend/hooks/useposition>` hook pozitsiyasi bo'lishi kerak. "
"(standart: `bottom-start`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:490
msgid "`beforeOpen`"
msgstr "`beforeOpen`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:491
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:494
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:497
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:512
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:529
msgid "`Function`"
msgstr "`Function`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:492
msgid "Optional function called just before opening. May be asynchronous."
msgstr "Ochilishdan oldin chaqiriladigan ixtiyoriy funksiya. Asinxron bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:493
msgid "`onOpened`"
msgstr "`onOpened`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:495
msgid "Optional function called just after opening."
msgstr "Ochilgandan keyin chaqiriladigan ixtiyoriy funksiya."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:496
msgid "`onStateChanged`"
msgstr "`onStateChanged`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:498
msgid ""
"Optional function called after opening or closing (gives a boolean as "
"single argument that represents whether the dropdown is open or not)."
msgstr ""
"Ochilgandan yoki yopilgandan keyin chaqiriladigan ixtiyoriy funksiya "
"(ochiladigan ro'yxat ochiq yoki ochiq emasligini ifodalovchi mantiqiy "
"qiymatni yagona argument sifatida beradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:499
msgid "`state`"
msgstr "`state`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:501
msgid ""
"Optional object with `open()`, `close()` and `isOpen` properties to "
"manually control when the dropdown opens and closes."
msgstr ""
"Ochiladigan ro'yxat qachon ochilish va yopilishini qo'lda boshqarish uchun "
"`open()`, `close()` va `isOpen` xususiyatlariga ega ixtiyoriy ob'ekt."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:502
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:103
msgid "`manual`"
msgstr "`manual`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:504
msgid ""
"Optional, when true, the Dropdown component will not add click event "
"listeners to the toggler. This allows for more control as when to open "
"the dropdown. (This should be used in tandem with the `state` prop)"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy, true bo'lsa, Dropdown komponenti almashtiruvchiga bosish hodisasi "
"tinglovchilarini qo'shmaydi. Bu ochiladigan ro'yxatni qachon ochish "
"haqida ko'proq nazorat imkonini beradi. (Bu `state` xususiyati bilan "
"birgalikda ishlatilishi kerak)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:505
msgid "`navigationOptions`"
msgstr "`navigationOptions`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:507
msgid ""
"Optionally overrides the navigation options of the dropdown, (see "
"`web/core/navigation/navigation`)."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy ravishda ochiladigan ro'yxatning navigatsiya parametrlarini "
"qayta yozadi (`web/core/navigation/navigation` ga qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:508
msgid "`holdOnHover`"
msgstr "`holdOnHover`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:510
msgid ""
"Optional, if true, keeps the Dropdown's menu at the same position while "
"the mouse is hovering it, creating a better UX when the menu's content "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy, true bo'lsa, sichqoncha uning ustiga olib borganida Dropdown "
"menyusini bir xil pozitsiyada saqlaydi, menyu mazmuni o'zgarganda "
"yaxshiroq UX yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:511
msgid "`menuRef`"
msgstr "`menuRef`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:513
msgid ""
"Optional, allows to get a ref of the dropdown's menu, (expects a function"
" returned from `useChildRef`)"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy, ochiladigan ro'yxat menyusiga ref olish imkonini beradi "
"(`useChildRef` dan qaytarilgan funksiyani kutadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:516
msgid "DropdownItem Props"
msgstr "DropdownItem xususiyatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:525
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:903
msgid "`class`"
msgstr "`class`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:526
msgid "`String` or `Object`"
msgstr "`String` yoki `Object`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:527
msgid ""
"Optional value added to the root span classname (supports both strings "
"and `OWL classname object notation "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#dynamic-class-attribute>`_)."
msgstr ""
"Root span sinf nomiga qo'shiladigan ixtiyoriy qiymat (satrlar va "
"`OWL sinf nomi ob'ekt yozuvini "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#dynamic-class-attribute>`_ qo'llab-quvvatlaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:528
msgid "`onSelected`"
msgstr "`onSelected`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:530
msgid "Optional function called when the dropdown item is selected."
msgstr "Ochiladigan ro'yxat elementi tanlanganda chaqiriladigan ixtiyoriy funksiya."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:531
msgid "`closingMode`"
msgstr "`closingMode`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:532
msgid "`\"none\"` | `\"closest\"` | `\"all\"`"
msgstr "`\"none\"` | `\"closest\"` | `\"all\"`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:533
msgid ""
"Optional, controls which parent dropdown should close when the item is "
"selected: `none`: the dropdown will not close, `closest`: the direct "
"parent will close, `all`: every nested parent dropdown will close "
"(default: `all`)"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy, element tanlanganda qaysi ota ochiladigan ro'yxat yopilishi "
"kerakligini boshqaradi: `none`: ochiladigan ro'yxat yopilmaydi, "
"`closest`: bevosita ota yopiladi, `all`: har bir ichki joylashgan ota "
"ochiladigan ro'yxat yopiladi (standart: `all`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:535
msgid "`attrs`"
msgstr "`attrs`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:537
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Optional object representing attributes that are added to the root "
"element. `<DropdownItem attrs=\"{ title: 'A tooltip', 'data-hotkey': "
"'shift+a' }\">`. (If `href` is set, the element will automatically become"
" an `a` element)."
msgstr ""
"Root elementga qo'shiladigan atributlarni ifodalovchi ixtiyoriy ob'ekt. "
"`<DropdownItem attrs=\"{ title: 'A tooltip', 'data-hotkey': "
"'shift+a' }\">`. (Agar `href` o'rnatilsa, element avtomatik ravishda "
"`a` elementiga aylanadi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:540
msgid ""
"When writing custom css for you components, do not forget that the menu "
"elements are not next to the toggle but inside the overlay container, at "
"the bottom of the document. Thus, use the `menuClass` and `class` props "
"to more easily write your selectors. (This DOM magic let us avoid lots of"
" z-index issues.)"
msgstr ""
"Komponentlaringiz uchun maxsus css yozishda, menyu elementlari almashtiruvchi "
"yonida emas, balki hujjatning pastidagi overlay konteyner ichida joylashganligini "
"unutmang. Shuning uchun selectorlaringizni osonroq yozish uchun `menuClass` "
"va `class` xususiyatlaridan foydalaning. (Bu DOM sehri juda ko'p z-index "
"muammolaridan qochish imkonini beradi.)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:546
msgid "Nested Dropdown"
msgstr "Ichma-ich ochiladigan ro'yxat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:548
msgid ""
"Dropdown can be nested, to do this simply put new Dropdown components "
"inside other dropdown's content slot. When the parent dropdown is open, "
"child dropdowns will open automatically on hover."
msgstr ""
"Ochiladigan ro'yxat ichma-ich joylashtirilishi mumkin, buning uchun "
"shunchaki yangi Dropdown komponentlarni boshqa ochiladigan ro'yxatning "
"kontent slotiga qo'ying. Ota ochiladigan ro'yxat ochiq bo'lsa, bola "
"ochiladigan ro'yxatlar kursor ustiga olib borganida avtomatik ochiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:551
msgid "By default, selecting a DropdownItem will close the whole Dropdown tree."
msgstr "Standart holatda, DropdownItem ni tanlash butun Dropdown daraxtini yopadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:555
msgid ""
"This example shows how one could make a nested File dropdown menu, with "
"submenus for the New sub elements."
msgstr ""
"Bu misol Yangi quyi elementlari uchun quyi menyular bilan ichma-ich "
"joylashtirilgan File ochiladigan ro'yxat menyusini qanday yaratish "
"mumkinligini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:575
msgid ""
"In the example bellow, we recursively call a template to display a tree-"
"like structure."
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi misolda daraxtsimon tuzilmani ko'rsatish uchun shablonni "
"rekursiv chaqiramiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:608
msgid "Controlled Dropdown"
msgstr "Boshqariladigan ochiladigan ro'yxat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:610
msgid ""
"If needed, you can also open or close the dropdown using code. To do this"
" you must use the `useDropdownState` hook along with the `state` prop. "
"`useDropdownState` returns an object that has an `open` and a `close` "
"method (as well as an `isOpen` getter). Give the object to the `state` "
"prop of the dropdown you want to control and calling the respective "
"functions should now open and close your dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Kerak bo'lsa, kod yordamida ochiladigan ro'yxatni ham ochish yoki yopish "
"mumkin. Buning uchun `state` xususiyati bilan birgalikda `useDropdownState` "
"hookidan foydalanish kerak. `useDropdownState` `open` va `close` metodlari "
"(hamda `isOpen` getteri) bo'lgan ob'ektni qaytaradi. Ob'ektni boshqarmoqchi "
"bo'lgan ochiladigan ro'yxatning `state` xususiyatiga bering va tegishli "
"funksiyalarni chaqirish endi ochiladigan ro'yxatni ochishi va yopishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:615
msgid ""
"You can also set `manual` to `true` if you don't want the default click "
"handlers to be added on the toggle."
msgstr ""
"Agar standart bosish ishlov beruvchilarini almashtiruvchiga qo'shilishini "
"xohlamasangiz, `manual` ni `true` ga o'rnatishingiz ham mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:619
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The following example shows a dropdown that opens automatically when "
"mounted and only has a 50% chance of closing when clicking on the button "
"inside."
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi misol o'rnatilganda avtomatik ochiluvchi va ichidagi tugmani "
"bosganda faqat 50% ehtimolda yopiladigan ochiladigan ro'yxatni ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:658
msgid "DropdownGroup"
msgstr "DropdownGroup"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:660
msgid "**Location:** `@web/core/dropdown/dropdown_group`"
msgstr "**Joylashuv:** `@web/core/dropdown/dropdown_group`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:662
msgid ""
"You can use the DropdownGroup component to make Dropdowns share a common "
"group, this means that when one of these Dropdown is open, the others "
"will automatically open themselves on mouse hover, without the need for a"
" click."
msgstr ""
"DropdownGroup komponentidan Dropdownlar umumiy guruhni baham ko'rishi "
"uchun foydalanishingiz mumkin, ya'ni ulardan biri ochiq bo'lsa, boshqalari "
"bosishsiz sichqonchani olib borganida avtomatik ochiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:666
msgid ""
"To do this, either surround all the Dropdowns with a single DropdownGroup"
" or surround them with DropdownGroups with the same `group` key."
msgstr ""
"Buning uchun barcha Dropdownlarni bitta DropdownGroup bilan o'rab oling "
"yoki ularni bir xil `group` kalitiga ega DropdownGrouplar bilan o'rang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:670
msgid ""
"In the example bellow, all dropdown in the snippet bellow will share the "
"same group:"
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi misolda, quyidagi koddan barcha ochiladigan ro'yxatlar bir xil "
"guruhni baham ko'radi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:680
msgid ""
"Whereas in the following snippet, only the first, second and fourth "
"dropdown share the same group:"
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi kodda esa faqat birinchi, ikkinchi va to'rtinchi ochiladigan "
"ro'yxatlar bir xil guruhni baham ko'radi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:700
msgid "Notebook"
msgstr "Daftar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:705
msgid "`@web/core/notebook/notebook`"
msgstr "`@web/core/notebook/notebook`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:710
msgid ""
"The Notebook is made to display multiple pages in a tabbed interface. "
"Tabs can be located at the top of the element to display horizontally, or"
" at the left for a vertical layout."
msgstr ""
"Daftar yorliqli interfeysda bir nechta sahifalarni ko'rsatish uchun "
"yaratilgan. Yorliqlar gorizontal ko'rsatish uchun elementning tepasida "
"yoki vertikal joylashuv uchun chapda joylashishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:713
msgid ""
"There are two ways to define your Notebook pages to instanciate, either "
"by using `slot`'s, or by passing a dedicated `props`."
msgstr ""
"Daftar sahifalarini misol qilish uchun belgilashning ikkita yo'li mavjud: "
"`slot` lardan foydalanish yoki maxsus `props` ni uzatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:716
msgid ""
"A page can be disabled with the `isDisabled` attribute, set directly on "
"the slot node, or in the page declaration, if the Notebook is used with "
"the `pages` given as props. Once disabled, the corresponding tab is "
"greyed out and set as inactive as well."
msgstr ""
"Sahifa `isDisabled` atributi bilan o'chirib qo'yilishi mumkin, to'g'ridan-"
"to'g'ri slot tuguniga yoki Daftar xususiyatlar sifatida berilgan `pages` "
"bilan ishlatilsa sahifa e'loniga o'rnatiladi. O'chirib qo'yilgandan so'ng, "
"tegishli yorliq kulrang bo'lib, faolsiz ham qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:730
msgid "`anchors`"
msgstr "`anchors`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:731
msgid "`object`"
msgstr "`object`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:732
msgid ""
"optional. Allow anchors navigation to elements inside tabs that are not "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"ixtiyoriy. Ko'rinmaydigan yorliqlar ichidagi elementlarga anchor navigatsiyasiga "
"ruxsat berish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:733
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:446
msgid "`className`"
msgstr "`className`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:735
msgid "optional. Classname set on the root of the component."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Komponent ildiziga o'rnatilgan sinf nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:736
msgid "`defaultPage`"
msgstr "`defaultPage`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:738
msgid "optional. Page `id` to display by default."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Standart holatda ko'rsatiladigan sahifa `id`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:739
msgid "`icons`"
msgstr "`icons`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:741
msgid "optional. List of icons used in the tabs."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Yorliqlarda ishlatiladigan belgilar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:742
msgid "`orientation`"
msgstr "`orientation`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:744
msgid "optional. Whether tabs direction is `horizontal` or `vertical`."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Yorliqlar yo'nalishi `horizontal` yoki `vertical` ekanligini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:745
msgid "`onPageUpdate`"
msgstr "`onPageUpdate`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:747
msgid "optional. Callback executed once the page has changed."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Sahifa o'zgarganidan so'ng bajariladigan callback."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:748
msgid "`pages`"
msgstr "`pages`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:750
msgid "optional. Contain the list of `page`'s to populate from a template."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Shablondan to'ldiriluvchi `page` lar ro'yxatini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:754
msgid "The first approach is to set the pages in the slots of the component."
msgstr "Birinchi yondashuv - komponent slotlarida sahifalarni o'rnatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:768
msgid ""
"The other way to define your pages is by passing the props. This can be "
"useful if some pages share the same structure. Create first a component "
"for each page template that you may use."
msgstr ""
"Sahifalarni belgilashning yana bir yo'li - xususiyatlarni uzatish. Bu "
"ba'zi sahifalar bir xil tuzilmani baham ko'rsa foydali bo'lishi mumkin. "
"Avval foydalanishingiz mumkin bo'lgan har bir sahifa shabloni uchun "
"komponent yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:811
msgid "Both examples are shown here:"
msgstr "Ikkala misol ham bu yerda ko'rsatilgan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst
msgid "Examples with vertical and horizontal layout"
msgstr "Vertikal va gorizontal joylashuv bilan misollar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:822
msgid "Pager"
msgstr "Sahifalovchi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:827
msgid "`@web/core/pager/pager`"
msgstr "`@web/core/pager/pager`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:832
msgid ""
"The Pager is a small component to handle pagination. A page is defined by"
" an `offset` and a `limit` (the size of the page). It displays the "
"current page and the `total` number of elements, for instance, \"9-12 / "
"20\". In the previous example, `offset` is 8, `limit` is 4 and `total` is"
" 20. It has two buttons (\"Previous\" and \"Next\") to navigate between "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Sahifalovchi - bu sahifalashni boshqarish uchun kichik komponent. Sahifa "
"`offset` va `limit` (sahifa hajmi) bilan belgilanadi. U joriy sahifa va "
"elementlarning umumiy `total` sonini ko'rsatadi, masalan, \"9-12 / 20\". "
"Oldingi misolda `offset` 8, `limit` 4 va `total` 20. U sahifalar o'rtasida "
"navigatsiya qilish uchun ikkita tugmaga ega (\"Oldingi\" va \"Keyingi\")."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:835
msgid ""
"The pager can be used anywhere but its main use is in the control panel. "
"See the :ref:`usePager <frontend/hooks/usepager>` hook in order to "
"manipulate the pager of the control panel."
msgstr ""
"Sahifalovchi har qanday joyda ishlatilishi mumkin, lekin asosiy foydalanish "
"joyi boshqaruv panelida. Boshqaruv panelining sahifalovchisini boshqarish "
"uchun :ref:`usePager <frontend/hooks/usepager>` hookiga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:851
msgid "`offset`"
msgstr "`offset`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:853
msgid ""
"Index of the first element of the page. It starts with 0 but the pager "
"displays `offset + 1`."
msgstr ""
"Sahifaning birinchi elementi indeksi. U 0 dan boshlanadi, lekin sahifalovchi "
"`offset + 1` ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:854
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:856
msgid ""
"Size of the page. The sum of `offset` and `limit` corresponds to the "
"index of the last element of the page."
msgstr ""
"Sahifa hajmi. `offset` va `limit` yig'indisi sahifaning oxirgi elementi "
"indeksiga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:857
msgid "`total`"
msgstr "`total`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:859
msgid "Total number of elements the page can reach."
msgstr "Sahifa erishishi mumkin bo'lgan elementlarning umumiy soni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:860
msgid "`onUpdate`"
msgstr "`onUpdate`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:862
msgid ""
"Function that is called when page is modified by the pager. This function"
" can be async, the pager cannot be edited while this function is "
"executing."
msgstr ""
"Sahifalovchi tomonidan sahifa o'zgartirilganda chaqiriladigan funksiya. "
"Bu funksiya asinxron bo'lishi mumkin, funksiya bajarilayotganda sahifalovchi "
"tahrirlanmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:863
msgid "`isEditable`"
msgstr "`isEditable`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:865
msgid "Allows to click on the current page to edit it (`true` by default)."
msgstr "Joriy sahifani tahrirlash uchun unga bosishga ruxsat beradi (standart `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:866
msgid "`withAccessKey`"
msgstr "`withAccessKey`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:868
msgid ""
"Binds access key `p` on the previous page button and `n` on the next page"
" one (`true` by default)."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi sahifa tugmasiga `p` va keyingi sahifa tugmasiga `n` kirish "
"tugmasini bog'laydi (standart `true`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:873
msgid "SelectMenu"
msgstr "SelectMenu"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:878
msgid "`@web/core/select_menu/select_menu`"
msgstr "`@web/core/select_menu/select_menu`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:883
msgid ""
"This component can be used when you want to do more than using the native"
" `select` element. You can define your own option template, allowing to "
"search between your options, or group them in subsections."
msgstr ""
"Bu komponent mahalliy `select` elementidan ko'proq narsa qilmoqchi "
"bo'lganingizda ishlatilishi mumkin. Siz o'z opsiyalar shablonini "
"belgilashingiz, opsiyalar orasida qidirishga ruxsat berishingiz yoki "
"ularni bo'limlarga guruhlashingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:887
msgid ""
"Prefer the native HTML `select` element, as it provides by default "
"accessibility features, and has a better user interface on mobile "
"devices. This component is designed to be used for more complex use "
"cases, to overcome limitations of the native element."
msgstr ""
"Mahalliy HTML `select` elementini afzal ko'ring, chunki u standart "
"ravishda maxsus imkoniyatlar xususiyatlarini ta'minlaydi va mobil "
"qurilmalarda yaxshiroq foydalanuvchi interfeysiga ega. Bu komponent "
"mahalliy elementning cheklovlarini bartaraf etish uchun murakkabroq "
"foydalanish holatlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:900
msgid "`choices`"
msgstr "`choices`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:902
msgid "optional. List of `choice`'s to display in the dropdown."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Ochiladigan ro'yxatda ko'rsatiladigan `choice` lar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:905
msgid "optional. Classname set on the root of the SelectMenu component."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. SelectMenu komponentining ildiziga o'rnatilgan sinf nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:906
msgid "`groups`"
msgstr "`groups`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:908
msgid ""
"optional. List of `group`'s, containing `choices` to display in the "
"dropdown."
msgstr ""
"ixtiyoriy. Ochiladigan ro'yxatda ko'rsatiladigan `choices` ni o'z ichiga "
"olgan `group` lar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:909
msgid "`multiSelect`"
msgstr "`multiSelect`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:911
msgid ""
"optional. Enable multiple selections. When multiple selection is enabled,"
" selected values are displayed as :ref:`tag <frontend/tags_list>`'s in "
"the SelectMenu input."
msgstr ""
"ixtiyoriy. Bir nechta tanlovni yoqish. Bir nechta tanlov yoqilganda, "
"tanlangan qiymatlar SelectMenu kiritish maydonida "
":ref:`teg <frontend/tags_list>` sifatida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:912
msgid "`togglerClass`"
msgstr "`togglerClass`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:914
msgid "optional. classname set on the toggler button."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Almashtirish tugmasiga o'rnatilgan sinf nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:915
msgid "`required`"
msgstr "`required`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:917
msgid "optional. Whether the selected value can be unselected."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Tanlangan qiymatni bekor qilish mumkin yoki yo'qligini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:918
msgid "`searchable`"
msgstr "`searchable`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:920
msgid "optional. Whether a search box is visible in the dropdown."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Ochiladigan ro'yxatda qidiruv maydoni ko'rinadimi yoki yo'qligini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:921
msgid "`searchPlaceholder`"
msgstr "`searchPlaceholder`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:923
msgid "optional. Text displayed as the search box placeholder."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Qidiruv maydoni to'ldiruvchi matn sifatida ko'rsatiladigan matn."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:925
msgid "`any`"
msgstr "`any`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:926
msgid "optional. Current selected value. It can be from any kind of type."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Joriy tanlangan qiymat. U har qanday turdagi bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:927
msgid "`onSelect`"
msgstr "`onSelect`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:929
msgid "optional. Callback executed when an option is chosen."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Opsiya tanlanganida bajarile qayta chaqiruv."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:931
msgid "The shape of a `choice` is the following:"
msgstr "`choice` ning tuzilishi quyidagicha:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:933
msgid ""
"`value` is actual value of the choice. It is usually a technical string, "
"but can be from `any` type."
msgstr ""
"`value` tanlovning haqiqiy qiymati. Bu odatda texnik satr, lekin `any` "
"turidan bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:934
msgid ""
"`label` is the displayed text associated with the option. This one is "
"usually a more friendly and translated `string`."
msgstr ""
"`label` opsiya bilan bog'liq ko'rsatiladigan matn. Bu odatda yanada "
"qulay va tarjima qilingan `string`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:936
msgid "The shape of a `group` is the following:"
msgstr "`group` ning tuzilishi quyidagicha:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:938
msgid "`choices` is the list of `choice`'s to display for this group."
msgstr "`choices` bu guruh uchun ko'rsatiladigan `choice` lar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:939
msgid ""
"`label` is the displayed text associated with the group. This is a "
"`string` displayed at the top of the group."
msgstr ""
"`label` guruh bilan bog'liq ko'rsatiladigan matn. Bu guruh tepasida "
"ko'rsatiladigan `string`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:943
msgid ""
"In the following example, the SelectMenu will display four choices. One "
"of them is displayed on top of the options, since no groups are "
"associated with it, but the other ones are separated by the label of "
"their group."
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi misolda SelectMenu to'rtta tanlovni ko'rsatadi. Ulardan biri "
"opsiyalar tepasida ko'rsatiladi, chunki u bilan hech qanday guruh "
"bog'liq emas, lekin qolganlar o'z guruhlarining yorlig'i bilan ajratilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:996
msgid ""
"You can also customize the appearance of the toggler and set a custom "
"template for the choices, using the appropriate component `slot`'s."
msgstr ""
"Siz almashtiruvchining ko'rinishini sozlashingiz va mos komponent "
"`slot` laridan foydalanib tanlovlar uchun maxsus shablon o'rnatishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst
msgid "Example of SelectMenu usage and customization"
msgstr "SelectMenu dan foydalanish va sozlash misoli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1016
msgid ""
"When SelectMenu is used with multiple selection, the `value` props must "
"be an `Array` containing the values of the selected choices."
msgstr ""
"SelectMenu bir nechta tanlov bilan ishlatilganda, `value` xususiyati "
"tanlangan tanlovlar qiymatlarini o'z ichiga olgan `Array` bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst
msgid "Example of SelectMenu used with multiple selection"
msgstr "Bir nechta tanlov bilan ishlatiladigan SelectMenu misoli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1023
msgid ""
"For more advanced use cases, you can customize the bottom area of the "
"dropdown, using the `bottomArea` slot. Here, we choose to display a "
"button with the corresponding value set in the search input."
msgstr ""
"Murakkabroq foydalanish holatlari uchun `bottomArea` slotidan foydalanib "
"ochiladigan ro'yxatning pastki qismini sozlashingiz mumkin. Bu yerda "
"biz qidiruv kiritish maydonida o'rnatilgan mos qiymat bilan tugmani "
"ko'rsatishni tanlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst
msgid "Example of SelectMenu's bottom area customization"
msgstr "SelectMenu ning pastki qismini sozlash misoli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1049
msgid "TagsList"
msgstr "TagsList"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1054
msgid "`@web/core/tags_list/tags_list`"
msgstr "`@web/core/tags_list/tags_list`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1059
msgid ""
"This component can display a list of tags in rounded pills. Those tags "
"can either simply list a few values, or can be editable, allowing the "
"removal of items. It can be possible to limit the number of displayed "
"items using the `itemsVisible` props. If the list is longer than this "
"limit, the number of additional items is shown in a circle next to the "
"last tag."
msgstr ""
"Bu komponent teglar ro'yxatini yumaloq doiralar shaklida ko'rsatishi "
"mumkin. Bu teglar bir nechta qiymatlarni oddiy ro'yxatga olishi yoki "
"tahrirlash imkoniyatiga ega bo'lib, elementlarni o'chirishga ruxsat "
"berishi mumkin. `itemsVisible` xususiyatidan foydalanib ko'rsatiladigan "
"elementlar sonini cheklash mumkin. Agar ro'yxat bu chegaradan uzun "
"bo'lsa, qo'shimcha elementlar soni oxirgi tegning yonidagi doirada "
"ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1073
msgid "`displayBadge`"
msgstr "`displayBadge`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1075
msgid "optional. Whether the tag is displayed as a badge."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Teg nishon sifatida ko'rsatiladi yoki yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1076
msgid "`displayText`"
msgstr "`displayText`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1078
msgid "optional. Whether the tag is displayed with a text or not."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Teg matn bilan ko'rsatiladi yoki yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1079
msgid "`itemsVisible`"
msgstr "`itemsVisible`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1081
msgid "optional. Limit of visible tags in the list."
msgstr "ixtiyoriy. Ro'yxatdagi ko'rinadigan teglar chegarasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1082
msgid "`tags`"
msgstr "`tags`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1084
msgid "list of `tag`'s elements given to the component."
msgstr "komponentga berilgan `tag` elementlar ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1086
msgid "The shape of a `tag` is the following:"
msgstr "`tag` ning tuzilishi quyidagicha:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1088
msgid "`colorIndex` is an optional color id."
msgstr "`colorIndex` ixtiyoriy rang identifikatori."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1089
msgid "`icon` is an optional icon displayed just before the displayed text."
msgstr "`icon` ko'rsatiladigan matndan oldin ko'rsatiladigan ixtiyoriy belgi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1090
msgid "`id` is a unique identifier for the tag."
msgstr "`id` teg uchun noyob identifikator."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1091
msgid ""
"`img` is an optional image displayed in a circle, just before the "
"displayed text."
msgstr ""
"`img` ko'rsatiladigan matndan oldin doirada ko'rsatiladigan ixtiyoriy rasm."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1092
msgid ""
"`onClick` is an optional callback that can be given to the element. This "
"allows the parent element to handle any functionality depending on the "
"tag clicked."
msgstr ""
"`onClick` elementga berilishi mumkin bo'lgan ixtiyoriy qayta chaqiruv. "
"Bu ota elementga bosilgan tegga qarab istalgan funksiyani boshqarish "
"imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1093
msgid ""
"`onDelete` is an optional callback that can be given to the element. This"
" makes the removal of the item from the list of tags possible, and must "
"be handled by the parent element."
msgstr ""
"`onDelete` elementga berilishi mumkin bo'lgan ixtiyoriy qayta chaqiruv. "
"Bu elementni teglar ro'yxatidan o'chirishni mumkin qiladi va ota element "
"tomonidan boshqarilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1094
msgid "`text` is the displayed `string` associated with the tag."
msgstr "`text` teg bilan bog'liq ko'rsatiladigan `string`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1098
msgid ""
"In the next example, a TagsList component is used to display multiple "
"tags. It's at the developer to handle from the parent what would happen "
"when the tag is pressed, or when the delete button is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Keyingi misolda TagsList komponenti bir nechta teglarni ko'rsatish uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Tegga bosilganda yoki o'chirish tugmasi bosilganda nima "
"bo'lishini ota elementdan boshqarish dasturchi zimmasida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst:1129
msgid ""
"Depending the attributes given to each tag, their appearance and behavior"
" will differ."
msgstr ""
"Har bir tegga berilgan atributlarga qarab, ularning ko'rinishi va "
"xatti-harakati farq qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/owl_components.rst
msgid "Examples of TagsList using different props and attributes"
msgstr "Turli xususiyatlar va atributlardan foydalanuvchi TagsList misollari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:3
msgid "Patching code"
msgstr "Kodni yamoqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:5
msgid ""
"Sometimes, we need to customize the way the UI works.  Many common needs "
"are covered by some supported API. For example, all registries are good "
"extension points: the field registry allows adding/removing specialized "
"field components, or the main component registry allows adding components"
" that should be displayed all the time."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zan biz UI ning ishlash usulini sozlashimiz kerak. Ko'plab umumiy "
"ehtiyojlar qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan API bilan qoplanadi. Masalan, barcha "
"registrlar yaxshi kengaytirish nuqtalari: maydon registri ixtisoslashgan "
"maydon komponentlarini qo'shish/o'chirishga imkon beradi yoki asosiy "
"komponent registri doim ko'rsatilishi kerak bo'lgan komponentlarni "
"qo'shishga imkon beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:11
msgid ""
"However, there are situations for which it is not sufficient. In those "
"cases, we may need to modify an object or a class in place. To achieve "
"that, Odoo provides the utility function `patch`. It is mostly useful to "
"override/update the behavior of some other component/piece of code that "
"one does not control."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, bu yetarli bo'lmagan holatlar ham mavjud. Bunday hollarda biz "
"ob'ektni yoki sinfni o'z joyida o'zgartirishimiz kerak bo'lishi mumkin. "
"Bunga erishish uchun Odoo `patch` yordamchi funksiyasini taqdim etadi. "
"U asosan boshqa birining boshqaruvidagi komponent/kod qismining "
"xatti-harakatini bekor qilish/yangilash uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:19
msgid "The patch function is located in `@web/core/utils/patch`:"
msgstr "Patch funksiyasi `@web/core/utils/patch` da joylashgan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:23
msgid "the object that should be patched"
msgstr "yamoqlanishi kerak bo'lgan ob'ekt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:24
msgid "an object mapping each key to an extension"
msgstr "har bir kalitni kengaytmaga moslashtiruvchi ob'ekt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:25
msgid "a function to remove the patch"
msgstr "yamoqni o'chirish uchun funksiya"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:27
msgid ""
"The `patch` function modifies in place the `objToPatch` object (or class)"
" and applies all key/value described in the `extension` object.  An "
"unpatch function is returned, so it can be used to remove the patch later"
" if necessary."
msgstr ""
"`patch` funksiyasi `objToPatch` ob'ektini (yoki sinfini) o'z joyida "
"o'zgartiradi va `extension` ob'ektida tasvirlangan barcha kalit/qiymat "
"juftliklarini qo'llaydi. Yamoqni keyinroq zarur bo'lsa o'chirish uchun "
"foydalanish mumkin bo'lgan unpatch funksiyasi qaytariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:31
msgid ""
"Most patch operations provide access to the parent value by using the "
"native `super` keyword (see below in the examples)."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pgina yamoqlash operatsiyalari mahalliy `super` kalit so'zidan "
"foydalanib ota qiymatiga kirish imkonini beradi (quyidagi misollarga "
"qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/patching_code.rst:35
msgid "Patching a simple object"
msgstr "Oddiy ob'ektni yamoqlash"

