#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:339
msgid "Advanced Output"
msgstr "Kengaytirilgan chiqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:341
msgid ""
"By default, ``out`` should HTML-escape content which needs to be escaped,"
" protecting the system against XSS_"
msgstr ""
"Standart ravishda, ``out`` qochilishi kerak bo'lgan kontentni HTML-qochirishi "
"kerak, bu tizimni XSS_ dan himoya qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:344
msgid ""
"Content which does *not* need to be escaped will instead be injected as-"
"is in the document, and may become part of the document's actual markup."
msgstr ""
"Qochilishi *shart bo'lmagan* kontent esa hujjatga o'zgartirilmagan holda "
"kiritiladi va hujjatning haqiqiy belgilanishining bir qismiga aylanishi "
"mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:347
msgid ""
"The only cross-platform \"safe\" content is the output of :ref:`t-call "
"<reference/qweb/call>` or a :ref:`t-set <reference/qweb/set>` used with a"
" \"body\" (as opposed to ``t-value`` or ``t-valuef``)."
msgstr ""
"Yagona platformalar arasi \"xavfsiz\" kontent :ref:`t-call "
"<reference/qweb/call>` yoki \"body\" bilan ishlatiladigan "
":ref:`t-set <reference/qweb/set>` chiqishi (``t-value`` yoki "
"``t-valuef`` ga qarama-qarshi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:354
msgid ""
"Usually you should not have to care too much: APIs for which it makes "
"sense should generate \"safe\" content automatically, and things should "
"work transparently."
msgstr ""
"Odatda siz ko'p tashvishlanishingiz shart emas: bunga mantiqiy bo'lgan "
"API lar avtomatik ravishda \"xavfsiz\" kontent yaratishi va narsalar "
"shaffof tarzda ishlashi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:358
msgid ""
"For the cases where things need to be clearer though the following APIs "
"output safe content which will by default not be (re-)escaped when "
"injected into templates:"
msgstr ""
"Narsalar aniqroq bo'lishi kerak bo'lgan holatlarda esa quyidagi API lar "
"shablonlarga kiritilganda standart ravishda (qayta-)qochilmaydigan "
"xavfsiz kontent chiqaradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:362
msgid ":class:`HTML fields <odoo.fields.Html>`."
msgstr ":class:`HTML maydonlari <odoo.fields.Html>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:363
msgid ""
":func:`~odoo.tools.misc.html_escape` and :func:`markupsafe.escape` (they "
"are aliases, and have no risk of double-escaping)."
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.tools.misc.html_escape` va :func:`markupsafe.escape` (ular "
"taxalluslar bo'lib, ikki marta qochirish xavfi yo'q)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:365
msgid ":func:`~odoo.tools.mail.html_sanitize`."
msgstr ":func:`~odoo.tools.mail.html_sanitize`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:366
msgid ":class:`markupsafe.Markup`."
msgstr ":class:`markupsafe.Markup`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:368
msgid ""
":class:`markupsafe.Markup` is an unsafe API, it's an *assertion* that you"
" want the content to be markup-safe but necessarily can not check that, "
"it should be used with care."
msgstr ""
":class:`markupsafe.Markup` xavfli API bo'lib, u kontent belgilanish-xavfsiz "
"bo'lishini xohlayotganingizning *tasdig'i*, lekin buni tekshira olmaydi, "
"u ehtiyotkorlik bilan ishlatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:371
msgid ""
":func:`~odoo.tools.pycompat.to_text` does not mark the content as safe, "
"but will not strip that information from safe content."
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.tools.pycompat.to_text` kontentni xavfsiz deb belgilamaydi, "
"lekin bu ma'lumotni xavfsiz kontentdan olib tashlamaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:375
msgid "forcing double-escaping"
msgstr "ikki marta qochishni majburlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:377
msgid ""
"If content is marked as safe but for some reason needs to be escaped "
"anyway (e.g. printing the markup of an HTML fields), it can just be "
"converted back to a normal string to \"strip\" the safety flag e.g. "
"`str(content)` in Python and `String(content)` in Javascript."
msgstr ""
"Agar kontent xavfsiz deb belgilangan bo'lsa, lekin biror sabab tufayli "
"baribir qochilishi kerak bo'lsa (masalan, HTML maydonlarining belgilanishini "
"chiqarish), uni xavfsizlik bayrog'ini \"olib tashlash\" uchun odatiy satrga "
"qaytarib o'girish mumkin, masalan Python da `str(content)` va "
"JavaScript da `String(content)`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:384
msgid ""
"Because :class:`~markupsafe.Markup` is a much richer type than "
":js:class:`Markup`, some operations will strip the safety information "
"from a :js:class:`Markup` but not a :class:`~markupsafe.Markup` e.g. "
"string concatenation (``'' + content``) in Python will result in a "
":class:`~markupsafe.Markup` with the other operand having been properly "
"escaped, while in Javascript will yield a :js:class:`String` where the "
"other operand was *not* escaped before the concatenation."
msgstr ""
":class:`~markupsafe.Markup` :js:class:`Markup` dan ancha boy tur "
"bo'lganligi sababli, ba'zi operatsiyalar :js:class:`Markup` dan "
"xavfsizlik ma'lumotini olib tashlaydi, lekin :class:`~markupsafe.Markup` "
"dan emas. Masalan, Python da satrlarni birlashtirish (``'' + content``) "
":class:`~markupsafe.Markup` natija beradi, bu holda boshqa operand "
"to'g'ri qochilgan bo'ladi, JavaScript da esa :js:class:`String` beradi, "
"bu holda boshqa operand birlashtirish oldidan *qochilmagan*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:393
msgid "Deprecated output directives"
msgstr "Eskirgan chiqish direktivlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:399
msgid "``esc``"
msgstr "``esc``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:398
msgid ""
"An alias for ``out``, would originally HTML-escape its input. Not yet "
"formally deprecated as the only difference between ``out`` and ``esc`` is"
" that the latter is a bit unclear / incorrect."
msgstr ""
"``out`` uchun taxallus, dastlab kiritishni HTML-qochiradi. Rasmiy ravishda "
"hali eskirgan emas, chunki ``out`` va ``esc`` orasidagi yagona farq "
"ikkinchisi biroz noaniq/noto'g'ri ekanligi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:411
msgid "``raw``"
msgstr "``raw``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:402
msgid ""
"A version of ``out`` which *never* escapes its content. Content is "
"emitted as-is, whether it's safe or not."
msgstr ""
"``out`` ning kontentni *hech qachon* qochirmaydigan versiyasi. Kontent "
"xavfsiz yoki xavfli bo'lishidan qat'i nazar o'zgartirilmagan holda chiqariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:407
msgid "Use ``out`` with a :class:`markupsafe.Markup` value instead."
msgstr "Buning o'rniga :class:`markupsafe.Markup` qiymati bilan ``out`` dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:409
msgid ""
"``t-raw`` was deprecated because as the code *producting* the content "
"evolves it can be hard to track that it's going to be used for markup, "
"leading to more complicated reviews and more dangerous lapses."
msgstr ""
"``t-raw`` eskirgan deb e'lon qilindi, chunki kontent *yaratuvchi* kod "
"rivojlanar ekan, uning belgilanish uchun ishlatilishini kuzatib borish "
"qiyin bo'lishi mumkin, bu murakkabroq tekshirishlarga va xavfliroq "
"kamchiliklarga olib keladi."

