msgid ""
"``t-inherit-mode`` which is the behaviour of the inheritance: it can "
"either be set to ``primary`` to create a new child template from the "
"parented one or to ``extension`` to alter the parent template in place."
msgstr ""
"``t-inherit-mode`` meros xatti-harakati: u ota shablondan yangi bola "
"shablon yaratish uchun ``primary`` ga yoki ota shablonni o'z joyida "
"o'zgartirish uchun ``extension`` ga o'rnatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:569
msgid ""
"An optional ``t-name`` directive can also be specified. It will be the "
"name of the newly created template if used in primary mode, else it will "
"be added as a comment on the transformed template to help retrace "
"inheritances."
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy ``t-name`` direktivasi ham belgilanishi mumkin. Agar asosiy "
"rejimda ishlatilsa, yangi yaratilgan shablonning nomi bo'ladi, aks holda "
"meros zanjirini kuzatishga yordam berish uchun o'zgartirilgan shablonga "
"izoh sifatida qo'shiladi."

