msgid ""
"For the inheritance itself, the changes are done using xpaths directives."
" See the XPATH_ documentation for the complete set of available "
"instructions."
msgstr ""
"Merosning o'zi uchun o'zgartirishlar xpath direktivlaridan foydalanib "
"amalga oshiriladi. Mavjud ko'rsatmalarning to'liq to'plami uchun "
"XPATH_ hujjatlariga qarang."

