msgid "Primary inheritance (child template)::"
msgstr "Asosiy meros (bola shablon)::"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:584
msgid "Extension inheritance (in-place transformation)::"
msgstr "Kengaytma merosi (joyida o'zgartirish)::"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:593
msgid "Old inheritance mechanism (deprecated)"
msgstr "Eski meros mexanizmi (eskirgan)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:595
msgid ""
"Template inheritance is performed via the ``t-extend`` directive which "
"takes the name of the template to alter as parameter."
msgstr ""
"Shablon merosi o'zgartirilishi kerak bo'lgan shablon nomini parametr "
"sifatida qabul qiluvchi ``t-extend`` direktivasi orqali amalga oshiriladi."

