#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:682
msgid ""
"(core is the ``web.core`` module) An instance of :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine`"
" with all module-defined template files loaded, and references to "
"standard helper objects ``_`` (underscore), ``_t`` (translation function)"
" and JSON_."
msgstr ""
"(core ``web.core`` moduli) Barcha modul belgilangan shablon fayllari "
"yuklangan :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` nusxasi va standart yordamchi "
"ob'ektlarga havolalar ``_`` (underscore), ``_t`` (tarjima funksiyasi) "
"va JSON_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:686
msgid ""
":js:func:`core.qweb.render <QWeb2.Engine.render>` can be used to easily "
"render basic module templates"
msgstr ""
":js:func:`core.qweb.render <QWeb2.Engine.render>` asosiy modul "
"shablonlarini osongina ko'rsatish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:696
msgid ""
"The QWeb \"renderer\", handles most of QWeb's logic (loading, parsing, "
"compiling and rendering templates)."
msgstr ""
"QWeb \"ko'rsatkichi\", QWeb ning aksariyat mantiqini boshqaradi "
"(shablonlarni yuklash, tahlil qilish, kompilyatsiya qilish va ko'rsatish)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:699
msgid ""
"Odoo Web instantiates one for the user in the core module, and exports it"
" to ``core.qweb``. It also loads all the template files of the various "
"modules into that QWeb instance."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Web yadro modulida foydalanuvchi uchun birini yaratadi va uni "
"``core.qweb`` ga eksport qiladi. U shuningdek turli modullarning barcha "
"shablon fayllarini shu QWeb nusxasiga yuklaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:703
msgid "A :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` also serves as a \"template namespace\"."
msgstr ":js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` shuningdek \"shablon nomlar maydoni\" sifatida ham xizmat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:707
msgid ""
"Renders a previously loaded template to a String, using ``context`` (if "
"provided) to find the variables accessed during template rendering (e.g. "
"strings to display)."
msgstr ""
"Ilgari yuklangan shablonni String ga ko'rsatadi, shablon ko'rsatilishi "
"vaqtida kirish imkoniga ega bo'lgan o'zgaruvchilarni topish uchun "
"``context`` dan foydalanadi (masalan, ko'rsatiladigan satrlar)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:711
msgid "the name of the template to render"
msgstr "ko'rsatiladigan shablon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:712
msgid "the basic namespace to use for template rendering"
msgstr "shablon ko'rsatilishi uchun foydalaniladigan asosiy nomlar maydoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:716
msgid ""
"The engine exposes an other method which may be useful in some cases "
"(e.g. if you need a separate template namespace with, in Odoo Web, Kanban"
" views get their own :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` instance so their templates"
" don't collide with more general \"module\" templates):"
msgstr ""
"Mexanizm ba'zi hollarda foydali bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan boshqa metodni "
"ham ochib beradi (masalan, alohida shablon nomlar maydoniga muhtoj bo'lsangiz, "
"Odoo Web da Kanban ko'rinishlari o'zlarining :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` "
"nusxasiga ega bo'lib, ularning shablonlari yanada umumiy \"modul\" "
"shablonlari bilan to'qnashmaydi):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:724
msgid ""
"Loads a template file (a collection of templates) in the QWeb instance. "
"The templates can be specified as:"
msgstr ""
"QWeb nusxasiga shablon faylini (shablonlar to'plami) yuklaydi. "
"Shablonlar quyidagicha belgilanishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:729
msgid "An XML string"
msgstr "XML satr"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:728
msgid "QWeb will attempt to parse it to an XML document then load it."
msgstr "QWeb uni XML hujjatiga tahlil qilishga va keyin yuklashga harakat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:733
msgid "A URL"
msgstr "URL"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:732
msgid ""
"QWeb will attempt to download the URL content, then load the resulting "
"XML string."
msgstr "QWeb URL kontentini yuklab olishga, so'ngra natijadagi XML satrini yuklashga harakat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:738
msgid "A ``Document`` or ``Node``"
msgstr "``Document`` yoki ``Node``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:736
msgid ""
"QWeb will traverse the first level of the document (the child nodes of "
"the provided root) and load any named template or template override."
msgstr ""
"QWeb hujjatning birinchi darajasini (taqdim etilgan ildizning bola "
"tugunlari) ko'rib chiqadi va istalgan nomlangan shablonni yoki "
"shablon bekor qilishini yuklaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:742
msgid ""
"A :js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` also exposes various attributes for behavior "
"customization:"
msgstr ""
":js:class:`QWeb2.Engine` shuningdek xatti-harakatni sozlash uchun turli "
"atributlarni ham ochib beradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:747
msgid ""
"Prefix used to recognize directives during parsing. A string. By default,"
" ``t``."
msgstr ""
"Tahlil qilish vaqtida direktivalarni tanish uchun ishlatiladigan prefiks. "
"Satr. Standart ravishda, ``t``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:752
msgid ""
"Boolean flag putting the engine in \"debug mode\". Normally, QWeb "
"intercepts any error raised during template execution. In debug mode, it "
"leaves all exceptions go through without intercepting them."
msgstr ""
"Mexanizmni \"nosozliklarni tuzatish rejimi\" ga o'rnatuvchi mantiqiy "
"bayroq. Odatda, QWeb shablon bajarilishi vaqtida ko'tarilgan istalgan "
"xatoni ushlaydi. Nosozliklarni tuzatish rejimida u barcha istisnolarni "
"ushlamasdan o'tishiga ruxsat beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:759
msgid ""
"The jQuery instance used during template inheritance processing. Defaults"
" to ``window.jQuery``."
msgstr ""
"Shablon merosi qayta ishlash vaqtida ishlatiladigan jQuery nusxasi. "
"Standart ravishda ``window.jQuery``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:764
msgid ""
"A ``Function``. If present, called before compiling each DOM node to "
"template code. In Odoo Web, this is used to automatically translate text "
"content and some attributes in templates. Defaults to ``null``."
msgstr ""
"``Function``. Mavjud bo'lsa, har bir DOM tugunini shablon kodiga "
"kompilyatsiya qilishdan oldin chaqiriladi. Odoo Web da bu shablonlardagi "
"matn kontenti va ba'zi atributlarni avtomatik tarjima qilish uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Standart ravishda ``null``."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:769
msgid ""
"it is similar in that to Genshi_, although it does not use (and has no "
"support for) `XML namespaces`_"
msgstr ""
"bu jihatdan Genshi_ ga o'xshaydi, garchi `XML nomlar maydonlari`_ ni "
"ishlatmaydi (va qo'llab-quvvatlamaydi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/qweb.rst:772
msgid ""
"although it uses a few others, either for historical reasons or because "
"they remain better fits for the use case. Odoo 9.0 still depends on "
"Jinja_ and Mako_."
msgstr ""
"garchi u bir nechtasini ishlatsa ham, tarixiy sabablarga ko'ra yoki ular "
"foydalanish holati uchun yanada mos kelganligi sababli. Odoo 9.0 hali "
"ham Jinja_ va Mako_ ga bog'liq."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:7
msgid ""
"Registries are (ordered) key/value maps. They are the main web client "
"extension points: many features provided by the Odoo javascript framework"
" simply look up into a registry whenever it needs a definition for some "
"object (such as fields, views, client actions or services). Customizing "
"the web client is then simply done by adding specific values in the "
"correct registry."
msgstr ""
"Registrlar (tartiblangan) kalit/qiymat xaritalar. Ular veb-mijozning "
"asosiy kengaytma nuqtalari: Odoo JavaScript frameworki tomonidan "
"taqdim etiladigan ko'plab xususiyatlar ma'lum bir ob'ekt uchun ta'rif "
"kerak bo'lganda (maydonlar, ko'rinishlar, mijoz amallari yoki xizmatlar "
"kabi) registrdan qidiradi. Veb-mijozni sozlash esa to'g'ri registrga "
"maxsus qiymatlar qo'shish orqali amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:23
msgid ""
"A useful feature of registries is that they maintain a set of sub "
"registries, obtained by the `category` method. If the sub registry does "
"not exist yet, it is created on the fly. All registries used by the web "
"client are obtained in such a way from one root registry, exported in "
"`@web/core/registry`."
msgstr ""
"Registrlarning foydali xususiyati shundaki, ular `category` metodi "
"orqali olingan kichik registrlar to'plamini saqlaydi. Agar kichik "
"registr hali mavjud bo'lmasa, u tezda yaratiladi. Veb-mijoz tomonidan "
"ishlatiladigan barcha registrlar `@web/core/registry` da eksport qilingan "
"bitta ildiz registrdan shunday tarzda olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:37
msgid "Registry API"
msgstr "Registry API"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:41
msgid ""
"Creates a new registry. Note that a registry is an event bus, so one can "
"listen to the `UPDATE` event if necessary. Registries are ordered: the "
":js:meth:`getAll <Registry.getAll>` method returns a list of values "
"ordered according to their sequence number."
msgstr ""
"Yangi registr yaratadi. E'tibor bering, registr voqealar avtobusligi "
"bo'lib, zarurat bo'lsa `UPDATE` voqeasini tinglash mumkin. Registrlar "
"tartiblangan: :js:meth:`getAll <Registry.getAll>` metodi tartib raqamiga "
"qarab tartiblangan qiymatlar ro'yxatini qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:48
msgid "key for the new entry"
msgstr "yangi yozuv uchun kalit"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:49
msgid "value for the new entry"
msgstr "yangi yozuv uchun qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:50
msgid "options"
msgstr "opsiyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:51
msgid "do not throw if key already exists"
msgstr "kalit allaqachon mavjud bo'lsa xato ko'tarmang"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:52
msgid "sequence number (useful to order entries)"
msgstr "tartib raqami (yozuvlarni tartiblashtirish uchun foydali)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:53
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:95
msgid "Registry"
msgstr "Registry"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:55
msgid ""
"Inserts a value at a specific key. If the key is already used, this "
"method throws an error (unless the option `force` is set to true). The "
"option `sequence` is useful to insert the value at a specific position. "
"This method also triggers an `UPDATE` event."
msgstr ""
"Muayyan kalit bo'yicha qiymat kiritadi. Agar kalit allaqachon "
"ishlatilgan bo'lsa, bu metod xato ko'taradi (`force` opsiyasi true ga "
"o'rnatilmagan holda). `sequence` opsiyasi qiymatni muayyan pozitsiyaga "
"kiritish uchun foydali. Bu metod shuningdek `UPDATE` voqeasini ham "
"ishga tushiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:60
msgid "Returns the same registry, so `add` method calls can be chained."
msgstr "Bir xil registrni qaytaradi, shuning uchun `add` metod chaqiruvlari zanjirlashi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:64
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:73
msgid "key for the entry"
msgstr "yozuv uchun kalit"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:65
msgid "return value if no entry for key exists"
msgstr "kalit uchun yozuv mavjud bo'lmasa qaytariladigan qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:67
msgid ""
"Returns the value corresponding to the `key` argument. If the registry "
"does not contain that key, this method returns `defaultValue` if given, "
"or throws an error otherwise."
msgstr ""
"`key` argumentiga mos qiymatni qaytaradi. Agar registr bu kalitni "
"o'z ichiga olmasa, bu metod berilgan bo'lsa `defaultValue` ni qaytaradi, "
"aks holda xato ko'taradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:76
msgid "Returns `true` if `key` is present in the registry"
msgstr "Registrda `key` mavjud bo'lsa `true` qaytaradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:82
msgid ""
"Returns the list of all elements in the registry. It is ordered according"
" to the sequence numbers."
msgstr ""
"Registrdagi barcha elementlar ro'yxatini qaytaradi. U tartib raqamlariga "
"qarab tartiblangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:87
msgid "the key for the entry that should be removed"
msgstr "o'chirilishi kerak bo'lgan yozuv uchun kalit"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:89
msgid ""
"Removes a key/value pair from the registry. This operation triggers an "
"`UPDATE` event."
msgstr ""
"Registrdan kalit/qiymat juftini o'chiradi. Bu operatsiya `UPDATE` "
"voqeasini ishga tushiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:94
msgid "the name for the sub category"
msgstr "kichik toifa uchun nom"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:97
msgid ""
"Returns the sub registry associated with the `subcategory`. If it does "
"not exist yet, the sub registry is created on the fly."
msgstr ""
"`subcategory` bilan bog'liq kichik registrni qaytaradi. Agar u hali "
"mavjud bo'lmasa, kichik registr tezda yaratiladi."

