#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:228
msgid "Systray registry"
msgstr "Systray registri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:230
msgid ""
"The systray is the zone on the right of the navbar that contains various "
"small components, that usually display some sort of information (like the"
" number of unread messages), notifications and/or let the user interact "
"with them."
msgstr ""
"Systray odatda ma'lum ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatuvchi (o'qilmagan xabarlar "
"soni kabi), bildirishnomalar va/yoki foydalanuvchiga ular bilan "
"muloqot qilish imkoniyatini beruvchi turli kichik komponentlarni o'z "
"ichiga oluvchi navigatsiya panelining o'ng tomonidagi zona."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:234
msgid ""
"The `systray` registry contains a description of these systray items, as "
"objects with the following three keys:"
msgstr ""
"`systray` registri ushbu systray elementlarining tavsifini quyidagi "
"uchta kalitga ega ob'ektlar sifatida o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:237
msgid ""
"`Component`: the component class that represents the item. Its root "
"element should be a `<li>` tag, otherwise it might not be styled "
"properly."
msgstr ""
"`Component`: elementni ifodalovchi komponent sinfi. Uning ildiz elementi "
"`<li>` tegi bo'lishi kerak, aks holda u to'g'ri ko'rinishga ega "
"bo'lmasligi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:239
msgid "`props (optional)`: props that should be given to the component"
msgstr "`props (ixtiyoriy)`: komponentga berilishi kerak bo'lgan xususiyatlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:240
msgid ""
"`isDisplayed (optional)`: a function that takes the :ref:`env "
"<frontend/framework/environment>` and returns a boolean. If true, the "
"systray item is displayed. Otherwise it is removed."
msgstr ""
"`isDisplayed (ixtiyoriy)`: :ref:`env <frontend/framework/environment>` "
"ni qabul qiladigan va mantiqiy qiymat qaytaradigan funksiya. Agar true "
"bo'lsa, systray elementi ko'rsatiladi. Aks holda u olib tashlanadi."

