#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:275
msgid "Usermenu registry"
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi menyusi registri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:277
msgid ""
"The user menu registry (category: `user_menuitems`) contains all menu "
"items that are shown when opening the user menu (the navbar element with "
"the user name, on the top right)."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi menyusi registri (toifa: `user_menuitems`) foydalanuvchi "
"menyusi ochilganda (yuqori o'ng tomondagi foydalanuvchi nomi bilan "
"navigatsiya paneli elementi) ko'rsatiladigan barcha menyu elementlarini "
"o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:281
msgid ""
"User menu items are defined by a function taking the :ref:`env "
"<frontend/framework/environment>` and returning a plain object, "
"containing the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi menyu elementlari :ref:`env <frontend/framework/environment>` "
