"ob'ektni qaytaradigan funksiya bilan aniqlanadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:284
msgid "`description` : the menu item text,"
msgstr "`description` : menyu elementi matni,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:285
msgid ""
"`href` : (optional) if given (and truthy), the item text is put in a `a` "
