msgstr "`sequence`: (ixtiyoriy) boshqa ochiladigan ro'yxat elementlari orasida elementning o'rnini belgilaydi (standart: 100)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/registries.rst:290
msgid ""
"The user menu calls all the functions defining items every time it is "
"opened."
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi menyusi har safar ochilganda elementlarni aniqlayotgan barcha funksiyalarni chaqiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:8
msgid ""
"Services are long lived pieces of code that provide a feature. They may "
"be imported by components (with ``useService``) or by other services. "
"Also, they can declare a set of dependencies. In that sense, services are"
" basically a DI :dfn:`dependency injection` system. For example, the "
"``notification`` service provides a way to display a notification, or the"
" ``rpc`` service is the proper way to perform a request to the Odoo "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Xizmatlar xususiyat taqdim etuvchi uzoq yashaydigan kod qismlari. Ular "
"komponentlar tomonidan (``useService`` bilan) yoki boshqa xizmatlar "
"tomonidan import qilinishi mumkin. Bundan tashqari, ular bog'liqliklar "
"to'plamini e'lon qilishi mumkin. Bu ma'noda xizmatlar asosan DI "
":dfn:`bog'liqlik in'yeksiyasi` tizimi. Masalan, ``notification`` xizmati "
"bildirishnoma ko'rsatish usulini taqdim etadi yoki ``rpc`` xizmati Odoo "
"serveriga so'rov yuborishning to'g'ri usuli."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:15
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:86
msgid ""
"The following example registers a simple service that displays a "
"notification every 5 seconds:"
msgstr "Quyidagi misol har 5 soniyada bildirishnoma ko'rsatuvchi oddiy xizmatni ro'yxatga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:34
msgid ""
"At startup, the web client starts all services present in the `services` "
"registry. Note that the name used in the registry is the name of the "
"service."
msgstr ""
"Ishga tushirishda veb-mijoz `services` registrida mavjud barcha xizmatlarni "
"ishga tushiradi. E'tibor bering, registrda ishlatiladigan nom xizmat nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:39
msgid ""
"Most code that is not a component should be *packaged* in a service, in "
"particular if it performs some side effect.  This is very useful for "
"testing purposes: tests can choose which services are active, so there "
"are less chance for unwanted side effects interfering with the code being"
" tested."
msgstr ""
"Komponent bo'lmagan aksariyat kod xizmatga *joylashtirilishi* kerak, "
"ayniqsa u yon ta'sir ko'rsatsa. Bu sinov maqsadlari uchun juda foydali: "
"testlar qaysi xizmatlar faol ekanligini tanlashi mumkin, shuning uchun "
"istalmagan yon ta'sirlarning test qilinayotgan kodga aralashish ehtimoli "
"kamroq."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:45
msgid "Defining a service"
msgstr "Xizmat aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:47
msgid "A service needs to implement the following interface:"
msgstr "Xizmat quyidagi interfeysni amalga oshirishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:51
msgid ""
"Optional list of strings. It is the list of all dependencies (other "
"services) that this service needs"
msgstr ""
"Ixtiyoriy satrlar ro'yxati. Bu xizmat kerak bo'ladigan barcha bog'liqliklar "
"(boshqa xizmatlar) ro'yxati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:56
msgid "the application environment"
msgstr "dastur muhiti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:57
msgid "all requested dependencies"
msgstr "barcha so'ralgan bog'liqliklar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:58
msgid "value of service or Promise<value of service>"
msgstr "xizmat qiymati yoki Promise<xizmat qiymati>"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:60
msgid ""
"This is the main definition for the service. It can return either a value"
" or a promise. In that case, the service loader simply waits for the "
"promise to resolve to a value, which is then the value of the service."
msgstr ""
"Bu xizmat uchun asosiy ta'rif. U qiymat yoki va'da qaytarishi mumkin. "
"Bu holda xizmat yuklagichi va'da qiymatga hal bo'lishini oddiy kutadi, "
"bu esa xizmatning qiymati bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:64
msgid ""
"Some services do not export any value. They may just do their work "
"without a need to be directly called by other code. In that case, their "
"value will be set to ``null`` in ``env.services``."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi xizmatlar hech qanday qiymat eksport qilmaydi. Ular boshqa kod "
"tomonidan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri chaqirilmasdan o'z ishini bajarishi mumkin. "
"Bu holda ``env.services`` da ularning qiymati ``null`` ga o'rnatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:70
msgid "Optional value. If given, it should be `true` or a list of strings."
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy qiymat. Berilgan bo'lsa, `true` yoki satrlar ro'yxati bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:72
msgid ""
"Some services need to provide an asynchronous API. For example, the `rpc`"
" service is an asynchronous function, or the `orm` service provides a set"
" of functions to call the Odoo server."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi xizmatlar asinxron API taqdim etishi kerak. Masalan, `rpc` xizmati "
"asinxron funksiya yoki `orm` xizmati Odoo serverini chaqirish uchun "
"funksiyalar to'plamini taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:76
msgid ""
"In that case, it is possible for components that use a service to be "
"destroyed before the end of an asynchronous function call. Most of the "
"time, the asynchronous function call needs to be ignored. Doing otherwise"
" is potentially very risky, because the underlying component is no longer"
" active. The `async` flag is a way to do just that: it signals to the "
"service creator that all asynchronous calls coming from components should"
" be left pending if the component is destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Bu holda xizmatdan foydalanadigan komponentlar asinxron funksiya chaqiruvi "
"tugaguncha yo'q qilinishi mumkin. Ko'pincha asinxron funksiya chaqiruvi "
"e'tiborga olinmay qo'yilishi kerak. Boshqacha qilish potentsial ravishda "
"juda xavfli, chunki asosiy komponent endi faol emas. `async` bayrog'i "
"aynan shunday qilish usuli: u xizmat yaratuvchisiga komponentlardan "
"keladigan barcha asinxron chaqiruvlar komponent yo'q qilinsa kutilayotgan "
"holda qoldirilishi kerakligini bildiradi."

