#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:520
msgid "Router Service"
msgstr "Yo'llovchi xizmati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:525
msgid "Technical name: `router`"
msgstr "Texnik nom: `router`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:528
msgid "The `router` service provides three features:"
msgstr "`router` xizmati uchta xususiyatni taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:530
msgid "information about the current route"
msgstr "joriy yo'l haqida ma'lumot"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:531
msgid "a way for the application to update the url, depending on its state"
msgstr "dastur uchun o'z holatiga qarab URL ni yangilash usuli"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:532
msgid "listens to every hash change, and notifies the rest of the application"
msgstr "har bir xesh o'zgarishini tinglaydi va dasturning qolgan qismini xabardor qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:540
msgid ""
"The current route can be accessed with the ``current`` key. It is an "
"object with the following information:"
msgstr ""
"Joriy yo'lga ``current`` kaliti bilan kirish mumkin. Bu quyidagi "
"ma'lumotlarga ega ob'ekt:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:543
msgid ""
"`pathname (string)`: the path for the current location (most likely "
"`/web` )"
msgstr "`pathname (string)`: joriy joylashuv uchun yo'l (ko'p holda `/web`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:544
msgid ""
"`search (object)`: a dictionary mapping each search keyword (the "
"querystring) from the url to its value. An empty string is the value if "
"no value was explicitely given"
msgstr ""
"`search (object)`: URL dan har bir qidiruv kalit so'zi (so'rov satri) ni "
"uning qiymatiga moslashtiradigan lug'at. Agar qiymat aniq berilmagan "
"bo'lsa, bo'sh satr qiymat hisoblanadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:547
msgid "`hash (object)`: same as above, but for values described in the hash."
msgstr "`hash (object)`: yuqoridagi bilan bir xil, lekin xeshda tasvirlangan qiymatlar uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:559
msgid "Updating the URL is done with the  `pushState` method:"
msgstr "URL ni yangilash `pushState` metodi orqali amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:563
msgid "object containing a mapping from some keys to some values"
msgstr "ba'zi kalitlardan ba'zi qiymatlarga moslashtirish o'z ichiga olgan ob'ekt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:564
msgid ""
"if true, the url will be replaced, otherwise only key/value pairs from "
"the `hash` will be updated."
msgstr "agar true bo'lsa, url almashtiriladi, aks holda faqat `hash` dan kalit/qiymat juftlari yangilanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:567
msgid ""
"Updates the URL with each key/value pair from the `hash` object. If a "
"value is set to an empty string, the key is added to the url without any "
"corresponding value."
msgstr ""
"`hash` ob'ektidan har bir kalit/qiymat jufti bilan URL ni yangilaydi. "
"Agar qiymat bo'sh satrga o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, kalit URL ga hech qanday "
"mos qiymat qo'shilmagan holda qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:571
msgid ""
"If true, the `replace` argument tells the router that the url hash should"
" be completely replaced (so values not present in the `hash` object will "
"be removed)."
msgstr ""
"Agar true bo'lsa, `replace` argumenti yo'llovchiga URL xeshi to'liq "
"almashtirilishi kerakligini bildiradi (`hash` ob'ektida mavjud bo'lmagan "
"qiymatlar olib tashlanadi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:574
msgid ""
"This method call does not reload the page. It also does not trigger a "
"`hashchange` event, nor a `ROUTE_CHANGE` in the :ref:`main bus "
"<frontend/framework/bus>`. This is because this method is intended to "
"only updates the url. The code calling this method has the responsibility"
" to make sure that the screen is updated as well."
msgstr ""
"Bu metod chaqiruvi sahifani qayta yuklamaydi. U shuningdek `hashchange` "
"voqeasini ham, :ref:`asosiy avtobus <frontend/framework/bus>` da "
"`ROUTE_CHANGE` ni ham ishga tushirmaydi. Bu metod faqat URL ni yangilash "
"uchun mo'ljallangani bois shunday. Bu metodni chaqiruvchi kod ekranning "
"ham yangilanishini ta'minlash mas'uliyatini zimmasiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:591
msgid ""
"Finally, the `redirect` method will redirect the browser to a specified "
"url:"
msgstr "Va nihoyat, `redirect` metodi brauzerni belgilangan URL ga yo'naltiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:595
msgid "a valid url"
msgstr "to'g'ri URL"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:596
msgid "if true, wait for the server to be ready, and redirect after"
msgstr "agar true bo'lsa, server tayyor bo'lishini kuting va keyin yo'naltiring"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:598
msgid ""
"Redirect the browser to `url`. This method reloads the page. The `wait` "
"argument is rarely used: it is useful in some cases where we know that "
"the server will be unavailable for a short duration, typically just after"
" an addon update or install operation."
msgstr ""
"Brauzerni `url` ga yo'naltiradi. Bu metod sahifani qayta yuklaydi. "
"`wait` argumenti kamdan-kam ishlatiladi: u biz server qisqa muddat "
"mavjud bo'lmasligini biladigan ba'zi hollarda foydali, odatda qo'shimcha "
"yangilash yoki o'rnatish operatsiyasidan keyin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:604
msgid ""
"The router service emits a `ROUTE_CHANGE` event on the :ref:`main bus "
"<frontend/framework/bus>` whenever the current route has changed."
msgstr ""
"Yo'llovchi xizmati joriy yo'l o'zgarganda :ref:`asosiy avtobus "
"<frontend/framework/bus>` da `ROUTE_CHANGE` voqeasini chiqaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:610
msgid "RPC service"
msgstr "RPC xizmati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:615
msgid "Technical name: `rpc`"
msgstr "Texnik nom: `rpc`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:618
msgid ""
"The `rpc` service provides a single asynchronous function to send "
"requests to the server. Calling a controller is very simple: the route "
"should be the first argument and optionally, a ``params`` object can be "
"given as a second argument."
msgstr ""
"`rpc` xizmati serverga so'rovlar yuborish uchun bitta asinxron funksiyani "
"taqdim etadi. Kontrollerni chaqirish juda oddiy: yo'l birinchi argument "
"bo'lishi kerak va ixtiyoriy ravishda ``params`` ob'ekti ikkinchi argument "
"sifatida berilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:631
msgid ""
"Note that the ``rpc`` service is considered a low-level service. It "
"should only be used to interact with Odoo controllers. To work with "
"models (which is by far the most important usecase), one should use the "
"``orm`` service instead."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, ``rpc`` xizmati past darajali xizmat deb hisoblanadi. "
"U faqat Odoo kontrollerlari bilan muloqot qilish uchun ishlatilishi "
"kerak. Modellar bilan ishlash uchun (eng muhim foydalanish holati), "
"buning o'rniga ``orm`` xizmatidan foydalanish kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:641
msgid "route targeted by the request"
msgstr "so'rov tomonidan nishonga olingan yo'l"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:642
msgid "(optional) parameters sent to the server"
msgstr "(ixtiyoriy) serverga yuborilgan parametrlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:643
msgid "(optional) request settings (see below)"
msgstr "(ixtiyoriy) so'rov sozlamalari (quyiga qarang)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:645
msgid "The ``settings`` object can contain:"
msgstr "``settings`` ob'ekti quyidagilarni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:647
msgid ""
"``xhr``, which should be a ``XMLHTTPRequest`` object. In that case, the "
"``rpc`` method will simply use it instead of creating a new one. This is "
"useful when one accesses advanced features of the `XMLHTTPRequest` API."
msgstr ""
"``xhr``, bu ``XMLHTTPRequest`` ob'ekti bo'lishi kerak. Bu holda ``rpc`` "
"metodi yangi yaratish o'rniga uni ishlatadi. Bu `XMLHTTPRequest` API "
"ning kengaytirilgan xususiyatlariga kirishda foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:650
msgid ""
"``silent (boolean)`` If set to ``true``, the web client will not provide "
"a feedback that there is a pending rpc."
msgstr "``silent (boolean)`` ``true`` ga o'rnatilsa, veb-mijoz kutilayotgan rpc mavjudligi haqida fikr bildirmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:653
msgid ""
"The ``rpc`` service communicates with the server by using a "
"``XMLHTTPRequest`` object, configured to work with the "
"``application/json`` content type. So clearly the content of the request "
"should be JSON serializable. Each request done by this service uses the "
"``POST`` http method."
msgstr ""
"``rpc`` xizmati ``application/json`` kontent turi bilan ishlash uchun "
"sozlangan ``XMLHTTPRequest`` ob'ekti yordamida server bilan muloqot "
"qiladi. Demak so'rov kontenti JSON serializatsiya qilinishi mumkin "
"bo'lishi kerak. Bu xizmat tomonidan bajariladigan har bir so'rov "
"``POST`` http metodini ishlatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:658
msgid ""
"Server errors actually return the response with an http code 200. But the"
" ``rpc`` service will treat them as error."
msgstr "Server xatoliklari aslida http 200 kodi bilan javob qaytaradi. Lekin ``rpc`` xizmati ularni xato sifatida ko'radi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:664
msgid "An rpc can fail for two main reasons:"
msgstr "RPC ikkita asosiy sabab tufayli muvaffaqiyatsiz tugashi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:666
msgid ""
"either the odoo server returns an error (so, we call this a ``server`` "
"error). In that case the http request will return with an http code 200 "
"BUT with a response object containing an ``error`` key."
msgstr ""
"yoki odoo serveri xato qaytaradi (biz buni ``server`` xatosi deb ataymiz). "
"Bu holda http so'rovi ``error`` kalitini o'z ichiga olgan javob ob'ekti "
"bilan http 200 kodi bilan qaytadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:670
msgid "or there is some other kind of network error"
msgstr "yoki boshqa turdagi tarmoq xatosi bor"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:672
msgid "When a rpc fails, then:"
msgstr "RPC muvaffaqiyatsiz tugaganda:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:674
msgid ""
"the promise representing the rpc is rejected, so the calling code will "
"crash, unless it handles the situation"
msgstr ""
"RPCni ifodalovchi va'da rad etiladi, shuning uchun chaqiruvchi kod "
"holat bilan ishlamasdan ishdan chiqadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:676
msgid ""
"an event ``RPC_ERROR`` is triggered on the main application bus. The "
"event payload contains a description of the cause of the error:"
msgstr ""
"asosiy dastur avtobusida ``RPC_ERROR`` voqeasi ishga tushiriladi. "
"Voqea foydali yuki xato sababining tavsifini o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:679
msgid ""
"If it is a server error (the server code threw an exception). In that "
"case the event payload will be an object with the following keys:"
msgstr ""
"Agar bu server xatosi bo'lsa (server kodi istisno ko'tardi). Bu holda "
"voqea foydali yuki quyidagi kalitlarga ega ob'ekt bo'ladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:683
msgid "``type = 'server'``"
msgstr "``type = 'server'``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:684
msgid "``message(string)``"
msgstr "``message(string)``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:686
msgid "``code(number)``"
msgstr "``code(number)``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:689
msgid ""
"``name(string)`` (optional, used by the error service to look for an "
"appropriate dialog to use when handling the error)"
msgstr ""
"``name(string)`` (ixtiyoriy, xato bilan ishlashda foydalanadigan mos "
"muloqot oynasini topish uchun xato xizmati tomonidan ishlatiladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:692
msgid "``subType(string)`` (optional, often used to determine the dialog title)"
msgstr "``subType(string)`` (ixtiyoriy, ko'pincha muloqot oynasi sarlavhasini aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:693
msgid ""
"``data(object)`` (optional object that can contain various keys among "
"which ``debug`` : the main debug information, with the call stack)"
msgstr ""
"``data(object)`` (turli kalitlarni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"ixtiyoriy ob'ekt, ular orasida ``debug`` : chaqiruv stek bilan asosiy "
"nosozliklarni tuzatish ma'lumotlari)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:696
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If it is a network error, then the error description is simply an object "
"``{type: 'network'}``. When a network error occurs, a :ref:`notification "
"<frontend/services/notification>` is displayed and the server is "
"regularly contacted until it responds. The notification is closed as soon"
" as the server responds."
msgstr ""
"Agar bu tarmoq xatosi bo'lsa, xato tavsifi shunchaki ``{type: 'network'}`` "
"ob'ekti. Tarmoq xatosi yuz berganda :ref:`bildirishnoma "
"<frontend/services/notification>` ko'rsatiladi va server javob bergunga "
"qadar muntazam ravishda server bilan bog'laniladi. Server javob "
"bergandan so'ng bildirishnoma yopiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:705
msgid "Scroller service"
msgstr "Aylandiruvchi xizmati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:710
msgid "Technical name: `scroller`"
msgstr "Texnik nom: `scroller`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:713
msgid ""
"Whenever the user clicks on an anchor in the web client, this service "
"automatically scrolls to the target (if appropriate)."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi veb-mijozda langa bosganida, bu xizmat avtomatik ravishda "
"nishonga (agar maqsadga muvofiq bo'lsa) aylanib o'tadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:716
msgid ""
"The service adds an event listener to get `click`'s on the document. The "
"service checks if the selector contained in its href attribute is valid "
"to distinguish anchors and Odoo actions (e.g. `<a "
"href=\"#target_element\"></a>`). It does nothing if it is not the case."
msgstr ""
"Xizmat hujjatdagi `click` larni olish uchun voqea tinglovchisini qo'shadi. "
"Xizmat langalar va Odoo amallari (masalan, `<a href=\"#target_element\">"
"</a>`) ni ajratish uchun uning href atributida saqlangan selektorning "
"to'g'riligini tekshiradi. Agar bu holat bo'lmasa, hech narsa qilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:720
msgid ""
"An event `SCROLLER:ANCHOR_LINK_CLICKED` is triggered on the main "
"application bus if the click seems to be targeted at an element. The "
"event contains a custom event containing the `element` matching and its "
"`id` as a reference. It may allow other parts to handle a behavior "
"relative to anchors themselves. The original event is also given as it "
"might need to be prevented. If the event is not prevented, then the user "
"interface will scroll to the target element."
msgstr ""
"Agar bosilgan joy elementga nishonlangan ko'rinsa, asosiy dastur "
"avtobusida `SCROLLER:ANCHOR_LINK_CLICKED` voqeasi ishga tushiriladi. "
"Voqea mos `element` va uning `id` sini havola sifatida o'z ichiga olgan "
"maxsus voqeani o'z ichiga oladi. Bu boshqa qismlarga langalar bilan "
"bog'liq xatti-harakatni boshqarishga imkon berishi mumkin. Asl voqea ham "
"beriladi, chunki u oldini olish kerak bo'lishi mumkin. Agar voqeaning "
"oldini olish bo'lmasa, foydalanuvchi interfeysi nishon elementga "
"aylanib o'tadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:729
msgid ""
"The following values are contained in the `anchor-link-clicked` custom "
"event explained above."
msgstr "Quyidagi qiymatlar yuqorida tushuntirilgan `anchor-link-clicked` maxsus voqeasida mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:738
msgid "`element`"
msgstr "`element`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:739
msgid "`HTMLElement | null`"
msgstr "`HTMLElement | null`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:740
msgid "The anchor element targeted by the href"
msgstr "href tomonidan nishonga olingan langa elementi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:741
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:91
msgid "`id`"
msgstr "`id`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:743
msgid "The id contained in the href"
msgstr "href da saqlangan id"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:744
msgid "`originalEv`"
msgstr "`originalEv`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:745
msgid "`Event`"
msgstr "`Event`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:746
msgid "The original click event"
msgstr "Asl bosish voqeasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:749
msgid ""
"The scroller service emits a `SCROLLER:ANCHOR_LINK_CLICKED` event on the "
":ref:`main bus <frontend/framework/bus>`. To avoid the default scroll "
"behavior of the scroller service, you must use `preventDefault()` on the "
"event given to the listener so that you can implement your own behavior "
"correctly from the listener."
msgstr ""
"Aylandiruvchi xizmati :ref:`asosiy avtobus <frontend/framework/bus>` da "
"`SCROLLER:ANCHOR_LINK_CLICKED` voqeasini chiqaradi. Aylandiruvchi "
"xizmatining standart aylanish xatti-harakatidan qochish uchun "
"tinglovchidan o'z xatti-harakatingizni to'g'ri amalga oshira olish uchun "
"tinglovchiga berilgan voqeada `preventDefault()` dan foydalanishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:756
msgid "Title Service"
msgstr "Sarlavha xizmati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:761
msgid "Technical name: `title`"
msgstr "Texnik nom: `title`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:764
msgid ""
"The `title` service offers a simple API that allows to read/modify the "
"document title. For example, if the current document title is \"Odoo\", "
"we can change it to \"Odoo 15 - Apple\" by using the following command:"
msgstr ""
"`title` xizmati hujjat sarlavhasini o'qish/o'zgartirish imkonini beruvchi "
"oddiy API taqdim etadi. Masalan, agar joriy hujjat sarlavhasi \"Odoo\" "
"bo'lsa, quyidagi buyruqdan foydalanib uni \"Odoo 15 - Apple\" ga "
"o'zgartirishimiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:779
msgid "The ``title`` service manipulates the following interface:"
msgstr "``title`` xizmati quyidagi interfeys bilan ishlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:787
msgid ""
"Each key represents the identity of a part of the title, and each value "
"is the string that is displayed, or `null` if it has been removed."
msgstr ""
"Har bir kalit sarlavhaning bir qismi identifikatorini ifodalaydi va har "
"bir qiymat ko'rsatiladigan satr yoki o'chirilgan bo'lsa `null`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:790
msgid "Its API is:"
msgstr "Uning API si:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:795
msgid ""
"This is a string representing the current title. It is structured in the "
"following way: ``value_1 - ... - value_n`` where each `value_i` is a (non"
" null) value found in the `Parts` object (returned by the `getParts` "
"function)"
msgstr ""
"Bu joriy sarlavhani ifodalovchi satr. U quyidagi tarzda tuzilgan: "
"``value_1 - ... - value_n`` bu yerda har bir `value_i` `Parts` ob'ektida "
"topilgan (null bo'lmagan) qiymat (`getParts` funksiyasi tomonidan qaytarilgan)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:801
msgid "Parts the current `Parts` object maintained by the title service"
msgstr "Sarlavha xizmati tomonidan qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan joriy `Parts` ob'ektining qismlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:805
msgid "object representing the required change"
msgstr "talab qilinadigan o'zgarishni ifodalovchi ob'ekt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:807
msgid ""
"The ``setParts`` method allows to add/replace/delete several parts of the"
" title. Delete a part (a value) is done by setting the associated key "
"value to `null`."
msgstr ""
"``setParts`` metodi sarlavhaning bir nechta qismini qo'shish/almashtirish/"
"o'chirishga imkon beradi. Qismni (qiymatni) o'chirish bog'liq kalit "
"qiymatini `null` ga o'rnatish orqali amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:810
msgid ""
"Note that one can only modify a single part without affecting the other "
"parts. For example, if the title is composed of the following parts:"
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, boshqa qismlarga ta'sir qilmasdan faqat bitta qismni "
"o'zgartirish mumkin. Masalan, agar sarlavha quyidagi qismlardan iborat bo'lsa:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:817
msgid "with ``current`` value being ``Odoo - Import`` , then"
msgstr "``current`` qiymati ``Odoo - Import`` bo'lganda, keyin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/services.rst:825
msgid "will change the title to ``Odoo``."
msgstr "sarlavhani ``Odoo`` ga o'zgartiradi."

