msgstr "Joriy \"input[type=range]\" `Target` ga berilgan qiymatni o'rnatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1204
msgid "`input`"
msgstr "`input`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1205
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1386
msgid "`change`"
msgstr "`change`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1212
msgid "Ensures that the given `Target` is unchecked."
msgstr "Berilgan `Target` belgilanmagan ekanligini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1214
msgid ""
"If it is checked, a :js:meth:`click` is triggered on the input. If the "
"input is still checked after the click, an error is thrown."
msgstr ""
"Agar belgilangan bo'lsa, kiritishda :js:meth:`click` ishga tushiriladi. "
"Agar kiritish bosilgandan keyin ham belgilangan bo'lsa, xato chiqariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1224
msgid "Other interaction helpers:"
msgstr "Boshqa o'zaro ta'sir yordamchilari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1226
msgid ""
"Other interaction helpers will not have a `target` parameter. It is not "
"needed, since pressing keys on a keyboard (for example) is done on the "
"current *active element*."
msgstr ""
"Boshqa o'zaro ta'sir yordamchilari `target` parametriga ega bo'lmaydi. "
"Bu talab qilinmaydi, chunki klaviaturada tugmalarni bosish (masalan) joriy "
"*faol elementda* amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1231
msgid "Clears the value of the current *active element*."
msgstr "Joriy *faol elementning* qiymatini tozalaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1233
msgid "This is done using the following sequence:"
msgstr "Bu quyidagi ketma-ketlik yordamida amalga oshiriladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1235
msgid "pressing `\"Control\"` & `\"A\"` to select the whole value;"
msgstr "butun qiymatni tanlash uchun `\"Control\"` va `\"A\"` ni bosish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1236
msgid "pressing `\"Backspace\"` to delete the value;"
msgstr "qiymatni o'chirish uchun `\"Backspace\"` ni bosish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1237
msgid "(optional) triggering a `\"change\"` event by pressing `\"Enter\"`."
msgstr "(ixtiyoriy) `\"Enter\"` ni bosish orqali `\"change\"` hodisasini ishga tushirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1247
msgid "Combination of :js:meth:`clear` and :js:meth:`fill`:"
msgstr ":js:meth:`clear` va :js:meth:`fill` kombinatsiyasi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1249
msgid "first, clears the input value (if any)"
msgstr "avval, kiritish qiymatini tozalaydi (agar mavjud bo'lsa)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1250
msgid "then fills the input with the given value"
msgstr "keyin kiritishni berilgan qiymat bilan to'ldiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1261
msgid ""
"Fills the current *active element* with the given `value`. This helper is"
" intended for `<input>` and `<textarea>` elements, with the exception of "
"`\"checkbox\"` and `\"radio\"` types, which should be selected using the "
"`check` helper."
msgstr ""
"Joriy *faol elementni* berilgan `value` bilan to'ldiradi. Bu yordamchi "
"`check` yordamchisi yordamida tanlanishi kerak bo'lgan `\"checkbox\"` va "
"`\"radio\"` turlaridan tashqari `<input>` va `<textarea>` elementlari "
"uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1265
msgid ""
"If the target is an editable input, its string `value` will be input one "
"character at a time, each generating its corresponding keyboard event "
"sequence. This behavior can be overridden by passing the `instantly` "
"option, which will instead simulate a `control` + `v` keyboard sequence, "
"resulting in the whole text being pasted."
msgstr ""
"Agar maqsad tahrirlanuvchan kiritish bo'lsa, uning qator `value` i bir "
"vaqtda bitta belgi kiritiladi, har biri o'z klaviatura hodisalar "
"ketma-ketligini yaratadi. Bu xatti-harakat `instantly` variantini o'tkazib "
"yuborish orqali bekor qilinishi mumkin, bu o'rniga `control` + `v` "
"klaviatura ketma-ketligini simulyatsiya qiladi va natijada butun matn "
"joylanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1270
msgid "Note that the given value is appended to the current value of the element."
msgstr "Berilgan qiymat elementning joriy qiymatiga qo'shilishini e'tiborda tuting."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1272
msgid ""
"If the active element is a `<input type=\"file\"/>`, the `value` should "
"be a `File`/list of `File` object(s)."
msgstr ""
"Agar faol element `<input type=\"file\"/>` bo'lsa, `value` `File` / "
"`File` ob'ekt(lar) ro'yxati bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1285
msgid "Performs a key down sequence on the current *active element*."
msgstr "Joriy *faol elementda* tugmani pastga bosish ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1289
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1348
msgid "`keydown`"
msgstr "`keydown`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1291
msgid "Additional actions will be performed depending on the key pressed:"
msgstr "Bosilgan tugmaga qarab qo'shimcha harakatlar bajariladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1293
msgid "`Tab`: focus next (or previous with `shift`) focusable element;"
msgstr "`Tab`: keyingi (yoki `shift` bilan oldingi) fokuslanishi mumkin elementga o'tish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1294
msgid "`c`: copy current selection to clipboard;"
msgstr "`c`: joriy tanlovni buferga nusxalash;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1295
msgid "`v`: paste current clipboard content to current element;"
msgstr "`v`: joriy bufer mazmunini joriy elementga joylashtirish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1296
msgid ""
"`Enter`: submit the form if the target is a `<button type=\"button\">` or"
" a `<form>` element, or trigger a `change` event on the target if it is "
"an `<input>` element;"
msgstr ""
"`Enter`: agar maqsad `<button type=\"button\">` yoki `<form>` elementi "
"bo'lsa shaklni yuborish, yoki agar `<input>` elementi bo'lsa maqsadda "
"`change` hodisasini ishga tushirish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1299
msgid ""
"`Space`: trigger a `click` event on the target if it is an `<input "
"type=\"checkbox\">` element."
msgstr ""
"`Space`: agar `<input type=\"checkbox\">` elementi bo'lsa maqsadda "
"`click` hodisasini ishga tushirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1310
msgid "Performs a key up sequence on the current *active element*."
msgstr "Joriy *faol elementda* tugmani yuqoriga ko'tarish ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1314
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1349
msgid "`keyup`"
msgstr "`keyup`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1324
msgid "Performs a leave sequence on the current `Window`."
msgstr "Joriy `Window` da chiqish ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1331
msgid "`pointerout`"
msgstr "`pointerout`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1332
msgid "[desktop] `mouseout`"
msgstr "[desktop] `mouseout`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1333
msgid "`pointerleave`"
msgstr "`pointerleave`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1334
msgid "[desktop] `mouseleave`"
msgstr "[desktop] `mouseleave`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1344
msgid "Performs a keyboard event sequence on the current *active element*."
msgstr "Joriy *faol elementda* klaviatura hodisasi ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1364
msgid "Performs a resize event sequence on the current `Window`."
msgstr "Joriy `Window` da o'lchamni o'zgartirish hodisasi ketma-ketligini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1368
msgid "`resize`"
msgstr "`resize`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1370
msgid ""
"The target will be resized to the given dimensions, enforced by "
"`!important` style attributes."
msgstr ""
"Maqsad `!important` stil atributlari bilan majburlanib, berilgan "
"o'lchamlarga moslashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1381
msgid ""
"Performs a selection event sequence on the current active element. This "
"helper is intended for `<select>` elements only."
msgstr ""
"Joriy faol elementda tanlash hodisasi ketma-ketligini bajaradi. Bu "
"yordamchi faqat `<select>` elementlari uchun mo'ljallangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1397
msgid ""
"Gives the given `File` list to the current file input. This helper only "
"works if a file input has been previously interacted with (by clicking on"
" it)."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan `File` ro'yxatini joriy fayl kiritishiga beradi. Bu yordamchi "
"faqat fayl kiritish avval o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatilgan bo'lsa (uni bosish "
"orqali) ishlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1404
msgid "Triggers a \"beforeunload\" event on the current `Window`."
msgstr "Joriy `Window` da \"beforeunload\" hodisasini ishga tushiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1410
msgid "Mocks"
msgstr "Taqlid (Mock)lar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1412
msgid ""
"By default, a lot of low-level features are mocked by Hoot: `clipboard`, "
"`fetch`, `localStorage`, etc. These mocks are intended to not produce any"
" side-effect that would disturb the test runner or the context of other "
"tests, while still providing the same interface to allow tests to rely on"
" these features seamlessly."
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda, ko'plab past darajali xususiyatlar Hoot tomonidan "
"taqlid qilinadi: `clipboard`, `fetch`, `localStorage` va h.k. Bu "
"taqlidlar test yuklovchi yoki boshqa testlar kontekstini bezovta qiladigan "
"hech qanday yon ta'sir ko'rsatmaslik uchun mo'ljallangan, shu bilan birga "
"testlarga bu xususiyatlarga muammosiz tayanishiga imkon berish uchun "
"bir xil interfeysni taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1417
msgid ""
"There is also a need (most of the time) to force actions on these "
"features or change their behavior for a test, so there exist helpers to "
"interact with these mocked features. The following sections will list the"
" main mocked features and the means to interact with them."
msgstr ""
"Bundan tashqari (ko'pincha) bu xususiyatlarda harakatlarni majburlash yoki "
"test uchun ularning xatti-harakatini o'zgartirish zarurati ham mavjud, "
"shuning uchun bu taqlid qilingan xususiyatlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir "
"o'rnatish uchun yordamchilar mavjud. Quyidagi bo'limlar asosiy taqlid "
"qilingan xususiyatlar va ular bilan o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatish usullarini "
"ro'yxatlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1422
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Vaqt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1424
msgid ""
"Most asynchronous features are mocked: \"timers\" (`setTimeout`, "
"`setInterval` and `requestAnimationFrame`), `Date` and `performance` all "
"behave normally, but can be canceled or sped-up manually to considerably "
"shorten the actual duration of tests. For example: all \"timers\" are "
"canceled at the end of each test to avoid side-effects for the next one."
msgstr ""
"Ko'plab asinxron xususiyatlar taqlid qilinadi: \"taymerlar\" "
"(`setTimeout`, `setInterval` va `requestAnimationFrame`), `Date` va "
"`performance` barchasi odatdagidek ishlaydi, lekin testlarning haqiqiy "
"davomiyligini sezilarli darajada qisqartirish uchun qo'lda bekor qilinishi "
"yoki tezlashtirilishi mumkin. Masalan: barcha \"taymerlar\" keyingi test "
"uchun yon ta'sirlarni oldini olish maqsadida har bir test oxirida bekor "
"qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1430
msgid "There are 2 main timing behaviors that are *NOT* mocked:"
msgstr "Taqlid qilinmaydigan 2 ta asosiy vaqt xatti-harakati mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1432
msgid "`Promise` objects and related API;"
msgstr "`Promise` ob'ektlari va tegishli API;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1433
msgid ""
"OWL's timer functions: to wait for OWL rendering functions, you'll have "
"to resort to the `animationFrame` helper."
msgstr ""
"OWL taymer funksiyalari: OWL ko'rsatish funksiyalarini kutish uchun "
"`animationFrame` yordamchisiga murojaat qilishingiz kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1437
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1550
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1648
msgid "Related helpers"
msgstr "Tegishli yordamchilar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1441
msgid ""
"Calls `advanceTime` with the duration it would take for a given "
"`frameCount` amount of frames to have rendered in the UI (i.e. (1000 / "
"current FPS) x frame count)."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan `frameCount` miqdordagi kadrlarning interfeysda ko'rsatilishi "
"uchun ketadigan davomiylik bilan `advanceTime` ni chaqiradi "
"(ya'ni (1000 / joriy FPS) x kadrlar soni)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1446
msgid ""
"Advances the current time by the given amount of milliseconds. This will "
"affect all timeouts, intervals, animations and date objects."
msgstr ""
"Joriy vaqtni berilgan millisekundlar miqdori bilan oldinga siljitadi. "
"Bu barcha kutish vaqtlari, intervallar, animatsiyalar va sana ob'ektlariga "
"ta'sir qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1449
msgid ""
"It returns a promise resolved after all related callbacks have been "
"executed."
msgstr "U barcha tegishli qayta chaqiruvlar bajarilgandan so'ng hal bo'lgan promise qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1451
msgid "`Promise<number>` time consumed by timers (in ms)"
msgstr "`Promise<number>` taymerlar tomonidan sarflangan vaqt (ms da)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1455
msgid ""
"Returns a promise resolved after the next animation frame, typically "
"allowing Owl components to render."
msgstr ""
"Odatda Owl komponentlariga ko'rsatishga imkon beruvchi, keyingi animatsiya "
"kadridan keyin hal bo'lgan promise qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1458
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1472
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1478
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1513
#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1523
msgid "`Promise<void>`"
msgstr "`Promise<void>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1462
msgid "Cancels all current timeouts, intervals and animations."
msgstr "Barcha joriy kutish vaqtlarini, intervallarni va animatsiyalarni bekor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1466
msgid ""
"Returns a promise resolved after a given amount of milliseconds (default "
"to `0`)."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan millisekundlar miqdoridan keyin hal bo'lgan promise qaytaradi "
"(standart: `0`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1476
msgid "Returns a promise resolved after the next microtask tick."
msgstr "Keyingi mikrotask tikidan keyin hal bo'lgan promise qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1482
msgid "Mocks the current date and time, and also the time zone if any."
msgstr "Joriy sana va vaqtni, shuningdek vaqt mintaqasini (agar mavjud bo'lsa) taqlid qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1484
msgid ""
"Date can either be an object describing the date and time to mock, or a "
"string in SQL or ISO format (time and millisecond values can be omitted)."
" See :js:meth:`mockTimeZone` for the time zone params."
msgstr ""
"Sana taqlid qilinadigan sana va vaqtni tasvirlovchi ob'ekt yoki SQL yoki "
"ISO formatidagi qator bo'lishi mumkin (vaqt va millisekund qiymatlari "
"o'tkazib yuborilishi mumkin). Vaqt mintaqasi parametrlari uchun "
":js:meth:`mockTimeZone` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1496
msgid "Mocks the current time zone."
msgstr "Joriy vaqt mintaqasini taqlid qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1498
msgid "Time zone can either be a locale, a time zone or an offset."
msgstr "Vaqt mintaqasi til joylashuvi, vaqt mintaqasi yoki ofset bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1500
msgid "Returns a function restoring the default zone."
msgstr "Standart mintaqani tikluvchi funksiya qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1510
msgid ""
"Calculates the amount of time needed to run all current timeouts, "
"intervals and animations, and then advances the current time by that "
"amount."
msgstr ""
"Barcha joriy kutish vaqtlari, intervallar va animatsiyalarni bajarish "
"uchun kerakli vaqt miqdorini hisoblab, keyin joriy vaqtni shu miqdor "
"bilan oldinga siljitadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1517
msgid ""
"Sets the current frame rate (in fps) used by animation frames (default to"
" 60fps)."
msgstr ""
"Animatsiya kadrlari tomonidan ishlatiladigan joriy kadr chastotasini "
"(fps da) o'rnatadi (standart: 60fps)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1521
msgid "Returns a promise resolved after the next task tick."
msgstr "Keyingi task tikidan keyin hal bo'lgan promise qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1527
msgid ""
"Returns a promise fulfilled when the given `predicate` returns a truthy "
"value, with the value of the promise being the return value of the "
"`predicate`."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan `predicate` haqiqiy qiymat qaytarganda bajarilgan promise "
"qaytaradi, promise qiymati `predicate` ning qaytarish qiymati bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1530
msgid ""
"The `predicate` is run once initially and then each time the DOM is "
"mutated (see `observe` for more information)."
msgstr ""
"`predicate` dastlab bir marta, keyin esa DOM har safar o'zgartirilganda "
"ishlatiladi (ko'proq ma'lumot uchun `observe` ga qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1533
msgid ""
"The promise automatically rejects after a given `timeout` (defaults to 5 "
"seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Promise berilgan `timeout` dan keyin avtomatik ravishda rad etiladi "
"(standart: 5 soniya)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1535
msgid "`Promise<unknown>` promise with the return value of the predicate"
msgstr "`Promise<unknown>` predikat qaytarish qiymati bilan promise"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1538
msgid "Network"
msgstr "Tarmoq"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1540
msgid ""
"In general, we don't want to perform actual network calls in tests. To "
"ensure this, all calls to `fetch` and `XMLHttpRequest` have been re-"
"routed to a function given to :js:meth:`mockFetch`."
msgstr ""
"Umuman olganda, testlarda haqiqiy tarmoq chaqiruvlarini amalga oshirishni "
"xohlamaymiz. Buning uchun `fetch` va `XMLHttpRequest` ga barcha "
"chaqiruvlar :js:meth:`mockFetch` ga berilgan funksiyaga yo'naltirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1545
msgid ""
"In Odoo, this is generally implicitly handled by a :ref:`MockServer "
"<mock-server/configuration>` which is spawned by the mock environment, "
"i.e. any time a component is rendered using the :ref:`mountWithCleanup "
"<web-test-helpers/components>` helper."
msgstr ""
"Odoo'da bu odatda :ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` "
"yordamchisi yordamida komponent ko'rsatilgan har safar, ya'ni taqlid "
"muhiti tomonidan ishga tushiriladigan :ref:`MockServer "
"<mock-server/configuration>` tomonidan yashirin tarzda hal qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1554
msgid "Mocks the fetch function by replacing it with a given `fetchFn`."
msgstr "Fetch funksiyasini berilgan `fetchFn` bilan almashtirish orqali taqlid qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1556
msgid ""
"The return value of `fetchFn` is used as the response of the mocked "
"fetch, or wrapped in a `MockResponse` object if it does not meet the "
"required format."
msgstr ""
"`fetchFn` ning qaytarish qiymati taqlid qilingan fetchning javobi "
"sifatida ishlatiladi, yoki kerakli formatga javob bermasa `MockResponse` "
"ob'ektiga o'raladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1579
msgid "Activates mock WebSocket classe:"
msgstr "Taqlid WebSocket klassini faollashtiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1581
msgid ""
"websocket connections will be handled by `window.fetch` (see "
":js:meth:`mockFetch`);"
msgstr ""
"websocket ulanishlari `window.fetch` tomonidan boshqariladi "
"(qarang: :js:meth:`mockFetch`);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1583
msgid ""
"the `onWebSocketConnected` callback will be called after a websocket has "
"been created."
msgstr ""
"`onWebSocketConnected` qayta chaqiruvi websocket yaratilgandan keyin "
"chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1587
msgid "Activates mock `Worker` and `SharedWorker` classes:"
msgstr "Taqlid `Worker` va `SharedWorker` klasslarini faollashtiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1589
msgid ""
"actual code fetched by worker URLs will then be handled by `window.fetch`"
" (see :js:meth:`mockFetch`);"
msgstr ""
"worker URLlari tomonidan olingan haqiqiy kod keyin `window.fetch` "
"tomonidan boshqariladi (qarang: :js:meth:`mockFetch`);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1591
msgid ""
"the `onWorkerConnected` callback will be called after a worker has been "
"created."
msgstr ""
"`onWorkerConnected` qayta chaqiruvi worker yaratilgandan keyin chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1594
msgid "Notable global features"
msgstr "E'tiborli global xususiyatlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1596
msgid ""
"The following features may not have any specific mocked feature added, "
"but they do work as expected without changing the actual properties they "
"were meant to:"
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi xususiyatlarga hech qanday maxsus taqlid qilingan xususiyat "
"qo'shilmagan bo'lishi mumkin, lekin ular mo'ljallangan haqiqiy xossalarini "
"o'zgartirmasdan kutilganidek ishlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1599
msgid "`Document <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document>`_"
msgstr "`Document <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1601
msgid ""
"Both `title` and `cookie` can be set and read without changing the actual"
" properties of the current document."
msgstr ""
"Joriy hujjatning haqiqiy xossalarini o'zgartirmasdan `title` va "
"`cookie` ikkalasi ham o'rnatilishi va o'qilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1604
msgid "`History <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History>`_"
msgstr "`History <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1606
msgid ""
"The `history` API is mocked and bound to the `mockLocation` object to "
"return the same values and provide consistency."
msgstr ""
"`history` API taqlid qilingan va bir xil qiymatlarni qaytarish va "
"izchillikni ta'minlash uchun `mockLocation` ob'ektiga bog'langan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1609
msgid "`Location <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location>`_"
msgstr "`Location <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1611
msgid ""
"Hoot returns a `mockLocation` object to use instead of `window.location`,"
" but this relies on the use of an indirection in the actual production "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Hoot `window.location` o'rniga foydalanish uchun `mockLocation` ob'ektini "
"qaytaradi, lekin bu haqiqiy production kodida bilvosita foydalanishga "
"tayanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1615
msgid ""
"This feature will only work if an indirection is set between production "
"code and calls to `window.location`. In Odoo, it works because the "
"`@web/core/browser` module provides such an indirection, and that module "
"is mocked in test environments to redirect to the `mockLocation` object."
msgstr ""
"Bu xususiyat faqat production kodi va `window.location` ga chaqiruvlar "
"o'rtasida bilvosita o'rnatilgan bo'lsa ishlaydi. Odoo'da u ishlaydi, "
"chunki `@web/core/browser` moduli bunday bilvositani taqdim etadi va bu "
"modul test muhitlarida `mockLocation` ob'ektiga yo'naltirish uchun taqlid "
"qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1620
msgid "`Navigator <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator>`_"
msgstr "`Navigator <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1622
msgid ""
"Most used navigator features, such as the `clipboard` API and "
"`userAgent`, have been mocked to hijack their actual behaviors. Its "
"`permissions` object has been bound to a global mock of the permissions "
"API."
msgstr ""
"`clipboard` API va `userAgent` kabi ko'p ishlatiladigan navigator "
"xususiyatlari haqiqiy xatti-harakatlarini boshqarish uchun taqlid "
"qilingan. Uning `permissions` ob'ekti ruxsatlar API ning global "
"taqlidiga bog'langan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1626
msgid ""
"`Notification <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/API/Notification>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Notification <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/API/Notification>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1628
msgid ""
"Notifications have been mocked, with the \"notification\" permissions "
"bound to the global mocked permissions API."
msgstr ""
"Bildirishnomalar taqlid qilingan, \"notification\" ruxsatlari global "
"taqlid qilingan ruxsatlar API ga bog'langan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1631
msgid ""
"`Permissions <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Permissions <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1633
msgid ""
"Permissions can enable or disable other APIs by being given the "
"`\"granted\"` or `\"denied\"` statuses. This can be done through the "
"`mockPermission` helper."
msgstr ""
"Ruxsatlar `\"granted\"` yoki `\"denied\"` statuslarini berib boshqa "
"APIlarni yoqish yoki o'chirishi mumkin. Bu `mockPermission` yordamchisi "
"orqali amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1636
msgid "`Storage <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage>`_"
msgstr "`Storage <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1638
msgid "`localStorage` and `sessionStorage` both point to \"virtual\" storages."
msgstr "`localStorage` va `sessionStorage` ikkalasi ham \"virtual\" saqlash joylariga ishora qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1640
msgid "`Touch <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch_events>`_"
msgstr "`Touch <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch_events>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1642
msgid ""
"Touch features can be force-activated or deactivated globally for a given"
" test/suite using the :js:meth:`mockTouch` helper. It will mock both the "
"presence of touch handlers like `ontouchstart` on window, as well as the "
"`\"pointer\"` media being set to `fine` or `coarse`."
msgstr ""
"Sezgir ekran xususiyatlari :js:meth:`mockTouch` yordamchisi yordamida "
"berilgan test/to'plam uchun global ravishda majburan yoqilishi yoki "
"o'chirilishi mumkin. U oynada `ontouchstart` kabi sezgir ekran "
"ishlovchilarining mavjudligini va `\"pointer\"` medianing `fine` yoki "
"`coarse` ga o'rnatilishini ham taqlid qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1652
msgid ""
"Sets the given value for the given permission. This allows to enable or "
"prevent certain APIs (see the `Permissions API "
"<https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API>`_)."
msgstr ""
"Berilgan ruxsat uchun berilgan qiymatni o'rnatadi. Bu ma'lum APIlarni "
"yoqish yoki oldini olish imkonini beradi (qarang: `Permissions API "
"<https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API>`_)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/hoot.rst:1662
msgid "Toggles touch features on or off in the current `Window`."
msgstr "Joriy `Window` da sezgir ekran xususiyatlarini yoqadi yoki o'chiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:3
msgid "Mock server"
msgstr "Taqlid server"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:6
msgid "Rationale"
msgstr "Asoslama"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:8
msgid ""
"Test cases can range in complexity; from testing the return value of a "
"simple helper function, to rendering an entire webclient to simulate "
"interactions across several components/services."
msgstr ""
"Test holatlari murakkablik bo'yicha farqlanishi mumkin: oddiy yordamchi "
"funksiyaning qaytarish qiymatini sinovdan o'tkazishdan tortib, bir necha "
"komponent/xizmatlar bo'yicha o'zaro ta'sirni simulyatsiya qilish uchun "
"butun veb-mijozni ko'rsatishgacha."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:12
msgid ""
"In the latter cases, many interactions will trigger server requests, "
"without which the components or features will stop functioning properly. "
"However, it is important that these requests *do not* land on the actual "
"server, as they could affect the database, which is definitely not "
"something a test should be doing."
msgstr ""
"Ikkinchi holatlarda ko'plab o'zaro ta'sirlar server so'rovlarini "
"ishga tushiradi, ularsiz komponentlar yoki xususiyatlar to'g'ri "
"ishlashni to'xtatadi. Biroq, bu so'rovlar haqiqiy serverga *tushmasligi* "
"muhim, chunki ular ma'lumotlar bazasiga ta'sir qilishi mumkin, bu esa "
"test qilishi kerak bo'lgan narsa emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:17
msgid ""
"To overcome this, each request should be intercepted and replaced by a "
"function emulating actual server responses with test (i.e. fake) data."
msgstr ""
"Buni bartaraf etish uchun har bir so'rov tutib olinishi va test "
"(ya'ni soxta) ma'lumotlar bilan haqiqiy server javoblarini taqlid qiluvchi "
"funksiya bilan almashtirilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:20
msgid ""
"Since some of these requests are very common (e.g. ORM calls, such as "
"`web_search_read` or `web_save`, or other methods such as `get_views`), a"
" mock server has been implemented by default for every test that spawns "
"an :abbr:`env (Odoo environment)` [#]_."
msgstr ""
"Bu so'rovlarning ba'zilari juda keng tarqalgan bo'lgani uchun (masalan, "
"`web_search_read` yoki `web_save` kabi ORM chaqiruvlari yoki `get_views` "
"kabi boshqa metodlar), :abbr:`env (Odoo muhiti)` [#]_ ni ishga "
"tushiradigan har bir test uchun standart holatda taqlid server "
"joriy etilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:24
msgid ""
"These mock servers act independently for each test, can be configured "
"separately, and provide out of the box helpers for the most used routes "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Bu taqlid serverlar har bir test uchun mustaqil ishlaydi, alohida "
"sozlanishi mumkin va Odoo'da eng ko'p ishlatiladigan marshrutlar uchun "
"tayyor yordamchilarni taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:27
msgid ""
"A mock server is needed as soon as an environment is spawned because some"
" :doc:`services <../services>` do send server requests as soon as they "
"start."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi :doc:`xizmatlar <../services>` ishga tushishi bilan server "
"so'rovlarini yuborishi tufayli muhit ishga tushishi bilan taqlid server "
"kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:33
msgid ""
"A mock server is actually quite simple in itself: it is an object "
"containing a *collection* of all defined mock models, and a *mapping* "
"between routes and callbacks returning the test data."
msgstr ""
"Taqlid server aslida o'zi jihatidan juda oddiy: u barcha belgilangan "
"taqlid modellarining *to'plamini* va marshrutlar hamda test ma'lumotlarini "
"qaytaruvchi qayta chaqiruvlar o'rtasidagi *xaritalashni* o'z ichiga "
"oladigan ob'ektdir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:37
msgid ""
"The mock models themselves hold most of the CRUD logic, as well as the "
"data used to simulate server records."
msgstr ""
"Taqlid modellarning o'zi CRUD mantiqining ko'p qismini, shuningdek server "
"yozuvlarini simulyatsiya qilish uchun ishlatiladigan ma'lumotlarni o'z "
"ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:40
msgid ""
"Once a mock server starts, it hijacks *all* server requests, and for each"
" of them it will check in its *mapping* whether one of its registered "
"routes matches the requested URL. The most notable example of its pre-"
"defined routes is `/web/dataset/call_kw`, which is responsible for "
"calling an ORM method on the appropriate mock model."
msgstr ""
"Taqlid server ishga tushganda, u *barcha* server so'rovlarini egallab "
"oladi va ularning har biri uchun o'z *xaritalashida* ro'yxatdan o'tgan "
"marshrutlaridan biri so'ralgan URLga mos kelishini tekshiradi. Oldindan "
"belgilangan marshrutlarning eng muhim namunasi `/web/dataset/call_kw` "
"bo'lib, u tegishli taqlid modelda ORM metodini chaqirish uchun javobgar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:47
msgid ""
"Like most test helpers not provided by Hoot, mock server-related helpers "
"and classes can be found in the `\"@web/../tests/web_test_helpers\"` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Hoot tomonidan taqdim etilmagan ko'pgina test yordamchilari kabi, taqlid "
"server bilan bog'liq yordamchilar va klasslar "
"`\"@web/../tests/web_test_helpers\"` modulida topilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:55
msgid ""
"By default, a mock server is *\"empty\"*, meaning that it has no defined "
"mock model."
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda, taqlid server *\"bo'sh\"*, ya'ni unda hech qanday "
"belgilangan taqlid model mavjud emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:57
msgid ""
"This does not mean that it is useless though, as it will already handle a"
" few pre-defined routes, such as the ones responsible for fetching "
"`menus` and `translations`, which are spawned by :doc:`services "
"<../services>` as soon as an `env` is spawned."
msgstr ""
"Bu esa u foydali emasligini anglatmaydi, chunki u `env` ishga "
"tushishi bilan :doc:`xizmatlar <../services>` tomonidan ishga "
"tushiriladigan `menus` va `translations` ni olishga javobgar bo'lgan "
"bir necha oldindan belgilangan marshrutlarni allaqachon boshqaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:61
msgid ""
"But this means that ORM methods will fail, as the model that they target "
"has not been defined yet."
msgstr ""
"Lekin bu ORM metodlari muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lishini anglatadi, chunki "
"ular nishonga oladigan model hali belgilanmagan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:64
msgid "To create and define a mock model, you need 2 things:"
msgstr "Taqlid model yaratish va belgilash uchun 2 ta narsa kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:66
msgid "a `class` extending the `models.Model` class;"
msgstr "`models.Model` klassini kengaytiruvchi `class`;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:68
msgid ""
"special keys prefixed with a `_` act as metadata holders, like in Python "
"(e.g. `_name`, `_order`, `_description`, etc.) [#]_ [#]_;"
msgstr ""
"`_` bilan prefiksli maxsus kalitlar Python dagi kabi metadata ushlagichlari "
"vazifasini bajaradi (masalan, `_name`, `_order`, `_description` va h.k.) "
"[#]_ [#]_;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:71
msgid "`_records` holds the list of objects representing fake record data;"
msgstr "`_records` soxta yozuv ma'lumotlarini ifodalovchi ob'ektlar ro'yxatini o'z ichiga oladi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:73
msgid "`_views` can be a mapping of view types and XML arches;"
msgstr "`_views` ko'rinish turlari va XML archlari xaritalashi bo'lishi mumkin;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:75
msgid ""
"other `public class fields <public-class-fields_>`_ will be interpreted "
"as fields (by calling the appropriate method from `fields`);"
msgstr ""
"boshqa `umumiy klass maydonlari <public-class-fields_>`_ maydonlar "
"sifatida talqin qilinadi (`fields` dan tegishli metodni chaqirish orqali);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:78
msgid ""
"model-specific methods (such as `has_group` for `\"res.users\"`) can also"
" be defined here."
msgstr ""
"modelga xos metodlar (masalan, `\"res.users\"` uchun `has_group`) ham "
"bu yerda belgilanishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:81
msgid "calling `defineModels` with the class defined above."
msgstr "yuqorida belgilangan klass bilan `defineModels` ni chaqirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:83
msgid ""
"Only a subset of these special keys will have an actual effect. For "
"example, `_inherit` will not work as intended, prefer standard class "
"extension."
msgstr ""
"Bu maxsus kalitlarning faqat bir qismi haqiqiy ta'sirga ega bo'ladi. "
"Masalan, `_inherit` mo'ljallangandek ishlamaydi, standart klass "
"kengaytirishni afzal ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:86
msgid ""
"These can be altered by each test without thinking about cleaning up: any"
" change performed on a special key will be reverted at the end of a test."
msgstr ""
"Bularni har bir test tozalashni o'ylamasdan o'zgartirishi mumkin: maxsus "
"kalitda bajarilgan har qanday o'zgarish test oxirida qaytariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:89
msgid "Here is a basic example of a simple, fake, `\"res.partner\"` model:"
msgstr "Mana oddiy, soxta `\"res.partner\"` modelining asosiy namunasi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:120
msgid ""
"This code will make these data available for *all* tests in the current "
"test file. Of course, defining a class and calling `defineModels` can "
"also be done from *within* a given test to limit the scope of that model "
"to the current test."
msgstr ""
"Bu kod ushbu ma'lumotlarni joriy test faylidagi *barcha* testlar uchun "
"mavjud qiladi. Albatta, klass belgilash va `defineModels` ni chaqirish "
"modelning doirasini joriy test bilan cheklash uchun berilgan test "
"*ichida* ham amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:124
msgid ""
"Other methods such as `defineMenus`, `defineActions` or `defineParams` "
"can also be used to configure the current mock server. Most of their API "
"is quite straightforward (i.e. they receive JSON-like descriptions of "
"menus, actions, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"`defineMenus`, `defineActions` yoki `defineParams` kabi boshqa metodlar "
"ham joriy taqlid serverni sozlash uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Ularning "
"APIning ko'p qismi juda oddiy (ya'ni ular menyu, amallar va h.k. "
"JSON-ga o'xshash tavsiflarini qabul qiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:129
msgid "Mock models: requests"
msgstr "Taqlid modellar: so'rovlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:131
msgid ""
"Many test cases only require one or a few mock models to work. But "
"sometimes, it is either too bothersome to implement the mocking logic "
"within a model, or a *route* (i.e. server request URL) is simply not "
"associated to a Python model at all."
msgstr ""
"Ko'plab test holatlari faqat bir yoki bir necha taqlid model bilan "
"ishlashi kerak. Lekin ba'zan model ichida taqlid mantiqini joriy etish "
"juda qiyin bo'ladi yoki *marshrut* (ya'ni server so'rov URLi) Python "
"modeli bilan umuman bog'liq emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:135
msgid ""
"In such cases, the `onRpc` method is to be called, to associate a route "
"or an ORM method to a callback."
msgstr ""
"Bunday holatlarda marshrut yoki ORM metodini qayta chaqiruvga "
"bog'lash uchun `onRpc` metodi chaqirilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:139
msgid ""
"Multiple `onRpc` calls can be associated to the same route / ORM method; "
"in which case they will be called sequentially from last to first "
"defined. Returning a *non-null-or-undefined* value will interrupt the "
"current chain, and return that value as final result of the server "
"request."
msgstr ""
"Bir necha `onRpc` chaqiruvlari bir xil marshrut / ORM metodiga "
"bog'lanishi mumkin; bunday holda ular oxiridan birinchisiga ketma-ket "
"chaqiriladi. *null-yoki-undefined-dan-tashqari* qiymat qaytarish joriy "
"zanjirni uzadi va bu qiymatni server so'rovining yakuniy natijasi "
"sifatida qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:144
msgid "It can be used in 4 different ways:"
msgstr "U 4 xil usulda ishlatilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:147
msgid "`onRpc`: with a route (`\"/\"`)"
msgstr "`onRpc`: marshrut bilan (`\"/\"`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:149
msgid ""
"When the first argument is a `string` starting with a `\"/\"`, the "
"callback is expected to be a *route* callback, receiving a `Request_` "
"object:"
msgstr ""
"Birinchi argument `\"/\"` bilan boshlanadigan `string` bo'lganda, "
"qayta chaqiruv `Request_` ob'ektini qabul qiluvchi *marshrut* qayta "
"chaqiruvi bo'lishi kutiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:161
msgid ""
"By default, the return value of these callbacks are wrapped within the "
"`body` of a mock `Response_` object."
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda, bu qayta chaqiruvlarning qaytarish qiymati taqlid "
"`Response_` ob'ektining `body` siga o'raladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:164
msgid ""
"This is fine for most use-cases, but sometimes the callback needs to "
"respond with a `Response_` object with custom `status` or `headers`."
msgstr ""
"Bu ko'plab foydalanish holatlari uchun yaxshi, lekin ba'zan qayta "
"chaqiruv maxsus `status` yoki `headers` bilan `Response_` ob'ekti "
"bilan javob berishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:167
msgid ""
"In such cases, an *optional* dictionary can be passed as a 3rd argument "
"to specify whether the callback is to be considered *\"pure\"*, meaning "
"that its return value should be returned as-is to the server caller:"
msgstr ""
"Bunday holatlarda qayta chaqiruvni *\"sof\"* deb hisoblash kerakligini "
"ko'rsatish uchun 3-argument sifatida *ixtiyoriy* lug'at o'tkazilishi "
"mumkin, ya'ni uning qaytarish qiymati server chaqiruvchisiga o'zgarishsiz "
"qaytarilishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:180
msgid ""
"Using *\"pure\"* request callbacks can also be used to return anything "
"else than a `Response_` object, in which case the returned value will "
"still be wrapped in the body of a mock `Response_` to comply with the "
"`fetch_` / `XMLHttpRequest_` APIs."
msgstr ""
"*\"Sof\"* so'rov qayta chaqiruvlaridan foydalanish `Response_` ob'ektidan "
"boshqa narsalarni qaytarish uchun ham ishlatilishi mumkin, bunday holda "
"qaytarilgan qiymat `fetch_` / `XMLHttpRequest_` APIlariga mos kelish "
"uchun taqlid `Response_` ob'ektining tanasiga o'raladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:186
msgid "`onRpc`: with method name(s)"
msgstr "`onRpc`: metod nomi(lari) bilan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:188
msgid ""
"When the first argument is a `string` *NOT* starting with a `\"/\"` or a "
"list of `strings`, the callback is expected to be an ORM callback, only "
"called when the request's `method` matches the one given as argument."
msgstr ""
"Birinchi argument `\"/\"` bilan boshlanmaydigan `string` yoki "
"`strings` ro'yxati bo'lganda, qayta chaqiruv so'rovning `method` i "
"argument sifatida berilgan metod bilan mos kelganda chaqiriladigan "
"ORM qayta chaqiruvi bo'lishi kutiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:192
msgid "The callback will receive an object containing:"
msgstr "Qayta chaqiruv quyidagilarni o'z ichiga oladigan ob'ektni qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:194
msgid ""
"the *spread* `params` value contained in the request body (typically: "
"`args`, `kwargs`, `model` and `method`);"
msgstr ""
"so'rov tanasidagi *yoyilgan* `params` qiymati (odatda: `args`, "
"`kwargs`, `model` va `method`);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:197
msgid ""
"a `parent()` function, which when invoked will call the defined ORM "
"callback *preceding* this one;"
msgstr ""
"chaqirilganda bu qayta chaqiruvdan *oldin* belgilangan ORM qayta "
"chaqiruvini chaqiradigan `parent()` funksiyasi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:200
msgid ""
"a `route` key, containing the `pathname` of the request (typically: "
"`/web/dataset/call_kw`);"
msgstr ""
"so'rovning `pathname` ini o'z ichiga oladigan `route` kaliti "
"(odatda: `/web/dataset/call_kw`);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:202
msgid "the `request` object."
msgstr "`request` ob'ekti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:214
msgid "`onRpc`: with model name(s) AND method name(s)"
msgstr "`onRpc`: model nomi(lari) VA metod nomi(lari) bilan"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:216
msgid "When:"
msgstr "Qachon:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:218
msgid ""
"the first argument is a `string` *NOT* starting with a `\"/\"` or a list "
"of `strings`;"
msgstr ""
"birinchi argument `\"/\"` bilan boshlanmaydigan `string` yoki "
"`strings` ro'yxati;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:220
msgid "the second argument is also a `string` or a list of `strings`;"
msgstr "ikkinchi argument ham `string` yoki `strings` ro'yxati;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:222
msgid ""
"Then the callback is expected to be an ORM callback, only called when the"
" request's `method` *AND* `model` match the ones given in the arguments."
msgstr ""
"Keyin qayta chaqiruv so'rovning `method` *VA* `model` i argumentlarda "
"berilgan metodlarga mos kelganda chaqiriladigan ORM qayta chaqiruvi "
"bo'lishi kutiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:225
msgid "This works just the same as the above shape, with an added `model` filter:"
msgstr "Bu yuqoridagi shakl bilan bir xil ishlaydi, qo'shimcha `model` filtri bilan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:234
msgid "`onRpc`: for *every* ORM method/model"
msgstr "`onRpc`: *har bir* ORM metod/model uchun"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:236
msgid ""
"When the *only* argument is a callback, it is expected to be an ORM "
"callback to be called for *every* ORM call:"
msgstr ""
"*Yagona* argument qayta chaqiruv bo'lganda, u *har bir* ORM chaqiruvi "
"uchun chaqiriladigan ORM qayta chaqiruvi bo'lishi kutiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:246
msgid "Mock models: fields"
msgstr "Taqlid modellar: maydonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:248
msgid "Model fields can be declared in 2 ways:"
msgstr "Model maydonlari 2 usulda e'lon qilinishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:250
msgid "as `public class fields <public-class-fields_>`_;"
msgstr "`umumiy klass maydonlari <public-class-fields_>`_ sifatida;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:252
msgid "under the `_fields` special key. For example:"
msgstr "`_fields` maxsus kaliti ostida. Masalan:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:261
msgid ""
"Field constructors can take a parameters dictionary to dictate their "
"behaviour. It will be required for some of them, like relational fields, "
"which need a `relation` property to work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Maydon konstruktorlari ularning xatti-harakatini belgilash uchun "
"parametrlar lug'atini qabul qilishi mumkin. To'g'ri ishlash uchun "
"`relation` xossasiga muhtoj bo'lgan munosabat maydonlari kabi ba'zilari "
"uchun bu talab qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:265
msgid ""
"There are limits to what can be done with a mock field compared to an "
"actual Python server field, but expect the most basic properties to be "
"supported: `readonly`, `required`, `string`, etc."
msgstr ""
"Haqiqiy Python server maydoniga nisbatan taqlid maydon bilan nimalar "
"qilinishi mumkinligida cheklovlar mavjud, lekin eng asosiy xossalar "
"qo'llab-quvvatlanishi kutiladi: `readonly`, `required`, `string` va h.k."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:269
msgid ""
"`compute` and `related` do work for the most basic use-cases, but do not "
"expect them to function reliably as they would on the actual server."
msgstr ""
"`compute` va `related` eng asosiy foydalanish holatlari uchun ishlaydi, "
"lekin ularning haqiqiy server da ishlashidek ishonchli ishlashini "
"kutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:273
msgid ""
"There are 4 default fields pre-defined for each created model: `id`, "
"`display_name`, `created_at` and `updated_at`. They match their server-"
"side counterpart in their behaviour (e.g. `id` is incremental and "
"`display_name` has a `compute` function similar to its server "
"counterpart), and can be overridden if needed."
msgstr ""
"Har bir yaratilgan model uchun 4 ta standart maydon oldindan belgilangan: "
"`id`, `display_name`, `created_at` va `updated_at`. Ular xatti-harakat "
"bo'yicha server tomonidagi hamtasdiqlariga mos keladi (masalan, `id` "
"oshib boruvchi va `display_name` server hamtasdiqlasiga o'xshash "
"`compute` funksiyasiga ega) va kerak bo'lsa bekor qilinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:279
msgid "Mock models: records"
msgstr "Taqlid modellar: yozuvlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:281
msgid ""
"Model records are generated based on each object contained in the "
"`_records` special key *when the model is loaded*. They are validated "
"based on the fields available on the current models; if a property does "
"not match a field defined on the model, an error is thrown."
msgstr ""
"Model yozuvlari *model yuklanganida* `_records` maxsus kalitida joylashgan "
"har bir ob'ektga asoslanib yaratiladi. Ular joriy modellarda mavjud "
"maydonlarga asoslanib tekshiriladi; agar xossa modelda belgilangan "
"maydon bilan mos kelmasa, xato chiqariladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:287
msgid ""
"`_records` *cannot* be altered *after* the model has been loaded, i.e. "
"after the mock server has started. This key is only used to generate "
"initial records. If records should be added *after* model creation, do it"
" either form the available components in the UI, or through direct ORM "
"calls on the mock server instance."
msgstr ""
"`_records` model yuklanganidan *keyin*, ya'ni taqlid server ishga "
"tushganidan keyin *o'zgartirilishi mumkin emas*. Bu kalit faqat "
"boshlang'ich yozuvlarni yaratish uchun ishlatiladi. Yozuvlar model "
"yaratilgandan *keyin* qo'shilishi kerak bo'lsa, buni interfeysda mavjud "
"komponentlardan yoki taqlid server nusxasida to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ORM "
"chaqiruvlari orqali amalga oshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:293
msgid "Mock models: views"
msgstr "Taqlid modellar: ko'rinishlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:295
msgid ""
"Since actual views need an `\"ir.ui.view\"` model to be declared, mock "
"models use a simplified *mapping* to provide view arches."
msgstr ""
"Haqiqiy ko'rinishlar e'lon qilinishi uchun `\"ir.ui.view\"` modeli "
"kerak bo'lgani uchun, taqlid modellar ko'rinish archlarini taqdim etish "
"uchun soddalashtirilgan *xaritalashdan* foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:298
msgid ""
"The `_view` special key is a dictionary, with its *keys* being view "
"types, optionally accompanied by a view ID, and its *values* being the "
"XML arch string representation."
msgstr ""
"`_view` maxsus kaliti lug'at bo'lib, uning *kalitlari* ko'rinish turlari "
"(ixtiyoriy ravishda ko'rinish IDsi bilan birga) va uning *qiymatlari* "
"XML arch qator ko'rinishi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:301
msgid ""
"By default, view IDs are `false`, but can be specified explicitly with a "
"comma-separated key combining the view type and its ID:"
msgstr ""
"Standart holatda, ko'rinish IDlari `false`, lekin ko'rinish turi va "
"uning IDsini birlashtiradigan vergul bilan ajratilgan kalit bilan "
"aniq ko'rsatilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:324
msgid "Spawning a mock server"
msgstr "Taqlid server ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:326
msgid "Just like in most cases, only one server can be active for a given test."
msgstr "Ko'plab holatlarda bo'lgani kabi, berilgan test uchun faqat bitta server faol bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:328
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, creating an `env` will automatically deploy a mock "
"server."
msgstr "Yuqorida aytib o'tilganidek, `env` yaratish taqlid serverni avtomatik ravishda joylashtiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:330
msgid ""
"This means that all of these methods will *also* create a mock server, "
"since they do create an `env`:"
msgstr ""
"Bu ushbu metodlarning barchasi `env` yaratganligi sababli taqlid serverni "
"*ham* yaratishini anglatadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:333
msgid ":ref:`makeMockEnv <web-test-helpers/environment>`;"
msgstr ":ref:`makeMockEnv <web-test-helpers/environment>`;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:335
msgid ""
":ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` (calling "
":ref:`makeMockEnv <web-test-helpers/environment>`);"
msgstr ""
":ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` "
"(:ref:`makeMockEnv <web-test-helpers/environment>` ni chaqiradi);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:337
msgid ""
":ref:`mountView <web-test-helpers/views>` (calling :ref:`mountWithCleanup"
" <web-test-helpers/components>`)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mountView <web-test-helpers/views>` "
"(:ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` ni chaqiradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:339
msgid ""
"However, some low-level features may require to spawn a mock server "
"*without* an environment. For that purpose, a `makeMockServer` helper can"
" be called separately to initiate a mock server."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, ba'zi past darajali xususiyatlar muhit *olmagan holda* taqlid "
"server ishga tushirishni talab qilishi mumkin. Buning uchun taqlid "
"server ishga tushirish uchun `makeMockServer` yordamchisi alohida "
"chaqirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:344
msgid ""
"`makeMockServer` should *only* be used by low-level features, such as "
"testing the `rpc` function without the environment. It is not meant to be"
" used as a means to retrieve the current mock server instance. For that "
"purpose, refer to :ref:`MockServer.current <mock-server/interacting>`."
msgstr ""
"`makeMockServer` *faqat* past darajali xususiyatlar tomonidan, masalan, "
"muhitsiz `rpc` funksiyasini testlash uchun ishlatilishi kerak. U joriy "
"taqlid server nusxasini olish vositasi sifatida foydalanilishi mo'ljallanmagan. "
"Buning uchun :ref:`MockServer.current <mock-server/interacting>` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:350
msgid ""
"It is to be noted that subsequent calls to `makeMockServer` after a mock "
"server has been started are simply ignored."
msgstr ""
"Taqlid server ishga tushganidan keyin `makeMockServer` ga keyingi "
"chaqiruvlar shunchaki e'tiborga olinmasligini ta'kidlash kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:356
msgid "Interacting with the server"
msgstr "Server bilan o'zaro ta'sir"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:358
msgid ""
"While most of the server interactions are expected to be done directly or"
" indirectly by production code spawned in the test case, it is sometimes "
"meaningful to bypass the UI and call the mock server directly (e.g. to "
"simulate that another user, somewhere else, somehow, has altered the "
"database)."
msgstr ""
"Server bilan o'zaro ta'sirlarning aksariyati test holatida ishga "
"tushirilgan production kodi tomonidan bevosita yoki bilvosita amalga "
"oshirilishi kutilgan bo'lsa-da, ba'zan interfeysni chetlab o'tish va "
"taqlid serverga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri murojaat qilish ma'qul (masalan, "
"boshqa foydalanuvchi biror joyda ma'lumotlar bazasini o'zgartirganini "
"simulyatsiya qilish uchun)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:363
msgid ""
"This can be done by retrieving the `MockServer.current` static property "
"containing the current mock server instance (only after initialization):"
msgstr ""
"Bu joriy taqlid server nusxasini (faqat ishga tushirishdan keyin) o'z "
"ichiga oladigan `MockServer.current` statik xossasini olish orqali "
"amalga oshirilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/mock_server.rst:377
msgid "`MockServer.env` is just a shortcut to `MockServer.current.env`."
msgstr "`MockServer.env` shunchaki `MockServer.current.env` ga qisqartma."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:3
msgid "Web test helpers"
msgstr "Veb test yordamchilari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:8
msgid ""
"After the :doc:`\"@odoo/hoot\" <./hoot>` module, the second most-"
"solicited module in test files should be "
"`\"@web/../tests/web_test_helpers\"`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`\"@odoo/hoot\" <./hoot>` modulidan keyin, test fayllarida ikkinchi "
"eng ko'p so'raladigan modul `\"@web/../tests/web_test_helpers\"` bo'lishi "
"kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:11
msgid ""
"This module contains all the helpers that combine the low-level helpers "
"provided by Hoot, with all the most common features that are used in "
"tests in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Bu modul Hoot tomonidan taqdim etilgan past darajali yordamchilarni "
"Odoo'dagi testlarda ishlatiladigan eng keng tarqalgan xususiyatlar bilan "
"birlashtiradigan barcha yordamchilarni o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:14
msgid ""
"These helpers are many, and this section of the documentation will only "
"highlight the most common ones, and the way they interact with one "
"another."
msgstr ""
"Bu yordamchilar juda ko'p va hujjatning bu bo'limi faqat eng keng "
"tarqalganlarini va ular bir-biri bilan o'zaro ta'sir qilish usullarini "
"ta'kidlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:17
msgid ""
"For a full list of available helpers, you may refer to the "
"`web_test_helpers file "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/web_test_helpers.js>`_."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud yordamchilarning to'liq ro'yxati uchun `web_test_helpers fayli "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/web_test_helpers.js>`_"
" ga murojaat qilishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:22
msgid "Mock environment"
msgstr "Taqlid muhit"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:24
msgid "The `makeMockEnv` helper is the lowest helper that can spawn an `env`."
msgstr "`makeMockEnv` yordamchisi `env` ni ishga tushira oladigan eng past darajali yordamchidir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:26
msgid "It will take care of"
msgstr "U quyidagilarni bajaradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:28
msgid ""
"creating the `env` object itself, pre-configured with all the required "
"properties for the proper functioning of web components, such as "
"`getTemplate` or `translateFn`;"
msgstr ""
"`getTemplate` yoki `translateFn` kabi veb komponentlarning to'g'ri "
"ishlashi uchun zarur barcha xossalar bilan oldindan sozlangan `env` "
"ob'ektini yaratish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:31
msgid "spawning a `MockServer` (if one did not exist already for that test);"
msgstr "`MockServer` ni ishga tushirish (agar test uchun allaqachon mavjud bo'lmasa);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:33
msgid ""
"starting all registered :doc:`services <../services>`, and awaiting until"
" they are all ready;"
msgstr ""
"barcha ro'yxatdan o'tgan :doc:`xizmatlarni <../services>` ishga tushirish "
"va ularning barchasi tayyor bo'lguncha kutish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:35
msgid ""
"initiating other features that are not tied to a service, such as the web"
" `router`;"
msgstr ""
"veb `router` kabi xizmatga bog'liq bo'lmagan boshqa xususiyatlarni "
"ishga tushirish;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:37
msgid ""
"guaranteeing the teardown of all the features in its setup at the end of "
"the test."
msgstr ""
"test oxirida o'rnatishdagi barcha xususiyatlarni to'g'ri yopilishini "
"kafolatlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:39
msgid ""
"This method is great for testing low-level features, such as "
":doc:`services <../services>` that are not tied to a Component_:"
msgstr ""
"Bu metod Component_ ga bog'liq bo'lmagan :doc:`xizmatlar <../services>` "
"kabi past darajali xususiyatlarni testlash uchun ajoyib:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:50
msgid ""
"Like :ref:`makeMockServer <mock-server/spawning>`, only one `env` can be "
"active for a given test. It is not necessary to call `makeMockEnv` "
"manually to retrieve the current environment instance; the `getMockEnv` "
"helper can be called instead."
msgstr ""
":ref:`makeMockServer <mock-server/spawning>` kabi, berilgan test uchun "
"faqat bitta `env` faol bo'lishi mumkin. Joriy muhit nusxasini olish "
"uchun `makeMockEnv` ni qo'lda chaqirish shart emas; uning o'rniga "
"`getMockEnv` yordamchisi chaqirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:56
msgid ""
"`DateTime input tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/components/datetime/datetime_input.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`DateTime kiritish testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/components/datetime/datetime_input.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:58
msgid ""
"`Name service tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/name_service.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Nom xizmati testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/name_service.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:63
msgid "Mounting components"
msgstr "Komponentlarni joylashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:65
msgid ""
"Instantiating and appending `components <Component_>`_ to the DOM is "
"meant to be easy, through the use of the `mountWithCleanup` helper. It "
"will prepare an `env` internally (if one does not exist yet), which in "
"turn also makes sure that a `MockServer` is running."
msgstr ""
"`mountWithCleanup` yordamchisidan foydalanib `komponentlarni <Component_>`_ "
"yaratish va DOM ga qo'shish oson bo'lishi kerak. U ichki `env` ni "
"tayyorlaydi (agar hali mavjud bo'lmasa), bu o'z navbatida `MockServer` "
"ishlayotganligini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:70
msgid ""
"It takes a `Component` class as its first argument, and an *optional* "
"parameters second argument, used to specify `props` or a custom `target`:"
msgstr ""
"U birinchi argument sifatida `Component` klassini va `props` yoki "
"maxsus `target` ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan *ixtiyoriy* parametrlar "
"ikkinchi argumentini qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:81
msgid "This helper will return the active `Component` instance."
msgstr "Bu yordamchi faol `Component` nusxasini qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:84
msgid ""
"It is generally *ill-advised* to retrieve the `Component` instance to "
"directly interact with it or to perform assertions on its internal "
"variables. The only \"accepted\" use cases are when the `Component` is "
"displaying hard-to-retrieve information in the DOM, such as graphs in a "
"`canvas <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API>`_. "
"For most cases, it is highly preferred to query derived information in "
"the DOM."
msgstr ""
"U bilan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatish yoki uning ichki "
"o'zgaruvchilarida tasdiqlashlar bajarish uchun `Component` nusxasini "
"olish odatda *tavsiya etilmaydi*. Yagona \"qabul qilingan\" foydalanish "
"holatlari `Component` `canvas <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/"
"API/Canvas_API>`_ dagi grafiklar kabi DOM da qiyin olinadigan "
"ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatayotganda. Ko'plab holatlarda DOM dagi kelib "
"chiqadigan ma'lumotlarni so'rash qat'iy afzal."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:92
msgid ""
"`Checkbox tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/checkbox.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Belgilash qutisi testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/checkbox.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:94
msgid ""
"`Popover tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/popover/popover.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Popover testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/popover/popover.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:96
msgid ""
"`DateTimePicker tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/components/datetime/datetime_picker.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`DateTimePicker testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/core/components/datetime/datetime_picker.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:101
msgid "Mounting views"
msgstr "Ko'rinishlarni joylashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:103
msgid ""
"Mounting a view is simply a matter of using :ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-"
"test-helpers/components>` with the View_ component and the correct "
"properties."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishni joylashtirish shunchaki View_ komponenti va to'g'ri "
"xossalar bilan :ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` "
"dan foydalanishdan iborat."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:106
msgid ""
"For that purpose, web test helpers export a `mountView` helper, taking a "
"parameters object determining the view `type`, `resModel`, and other "
"optional properties such as an XML `arch`:"
msgstr ""
"Buning uchun veb test yordamchilari ko'rinish `type` ini, `resModel` ni "
"va XML `arch` kabi boshqa ixtiyoriy xossalarni belgilovchi parametrlar "
"ob'ektini qabul qiladigan `mountView` yordamchisini eksport qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:123
msgid ""
"Like the previous helpers on top of which `mountView` is built, it will "
"ensure that both an `env` and a `MockServer` are running for the current "
"test."
msgstr ""
"`mountView` qurilgan oldingi yordamchilar kabi, u joriy test uchun "
"ham `env` ham `MockServer` ishlayotganligini ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:127
msgid ""
"Like :ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>`, it is *NOT* "
"recommended to retrieve the returned View_ component instance. It can "
"however be done, for cases like the `Graph view "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_view.js>`_."
msgstr ""
":ref:`mountWithCleanup <web-test-helpers/components>` kabi, qaytarilgan "
"View_ komponenti nusxasini olish *TAVSIYA ETILMAYDI*. Biroq, `Grafik "
"ko'rinish "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_view.js>`_"
" kabi holatlarda amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:133
msgid ""
"`Calendar view tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/calendar/calendar_view.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Kalendar ko'rinish testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/calendar/calendar_view.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:135
msgid ""
"`Graph view tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/graph/graph_view.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Grafik ko'rinish testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/graph/graph_view.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:137
msgid ""
"`Kanban view tests "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/kanban/kanban_view.test.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Kanban ko'rinish testlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/tests/views/kanban/kanban_view.test.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:140
msgid "Interacting with components"
msgstr "Komponentlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:142
msgid ""
"Hoot provides helpers to interact with the DOM (e.g. `click`, `press`, "
"etc.). However, these helpers present 2 issues when interacting with more"
" complex components:"
msgstr ""
"Hoot DOM bilan o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatish uchun yordamchilar taqdim etadi "
"(masalan, `click`, `press` va h.k.). Biroq, bu yordamchilar murakkabroq "
"komponentlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatishda 2 muammo keltirib chiqaradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:145
msgid ""
"helpers try to interact instantly, while sometimes the element has yet to"
" be appended to the document (in an unknown amount of time);"
msgstr ""
"yordamchilar darhol o'zaro ta'sir o'rnatishga harakat qiladi, ba'zan esa "
"element hali hujjatga qo'shilmagan (noma'lum vaqt miqdorida);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:148
msgid ""
"helpers only wait a single micro-task tick per dispatched event, while "
"most Owl-based UIs take at least a full animation frame to update."
msgstr ""
"yordamchilar har bir jo'natilgan hodisa uchun faqat bitta mikrotask "
"tikini kutadi, ko'plab Owl asosidagi interfeyslar esa yangilash uchun "
"kamida to'liq animatsiya kadri talab qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:163
msgid ""
"With these constraints in mind, web test helpers provide the `contains` "
"helper:"
msgstr ""
"Bu cheklovlarni hisobga olib, veb test yordamchilari `contains` "
"yordamchisini taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:173
msgid ""
"This approach, while seemingly drifting a bit further away from the "
"concept of \"unit testing\", is still a nice and convenient way to test "
"more complex units such as `views <View_>`_, the `WebClient "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/src/webclient/webclient.js>`_,"
" or interactions between couples of :doc:`services <../services>` and "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Bu yondashuv \"birlik testlash\" tushunchasidan biroz uzoqlashgandek "
"ko'rinsa-da, `ko'rinishlar <View_>`_, `WebClient "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/web/static/src/webclient/webclient.js>`_"
" yoki :doc:`xizmatlar <../services>` va komponentlar juftlari "
"o'rtasidagi o'zaro ta'sirlar kabi murakkabroq birliklarni testlashning "
"yaxshi va qulay usuli hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:178
msgid ""
"It should however not become the default for all interactions, as some of"
" them still need to happen *precisely* within a given time frame, which "
"is a concept completely ignored by `contains`."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, u barcha o'zaro ta'sirlar uchun standartga aylanmasligi kerak, "
"chunki ulardan ba'zilari hali ham berilgan vaqt oralig'ida *aynan* "
"sodir bo'lishi kerak, bu esa `contains` tomonidan butunlay e'tiborga "
"olinmaydigan tushunchadir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/frontend/unit_testing/web_helpers.rst:183
msgid ""
"Most helpers in Hoot are available as methods of a `contains` instance, "
"with (generally) the same shape and API."
msgstr ""
"Hoot'dagi ko'plab yordamchilar `contains` nusxasining metodlari sifatida "
"(odatda) bir xil shakl va API bilan mavjud."

