#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:3
msgid "Upgrade scripts"
msgstr "Yangilanish skriptlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:5
msgid ""
"An upgrade script is a Python file containing a function called "
":meth:`migrate`, which the upgrade process invokes during the update of a"
" module."
msgstr ""
"Yangilanish skripti — bu :meth:`migrate` funksiyasini o'z ichiga olgan "
"Python fayli bo'lib, yangilanish jarayoni uni modul yangilanishi davomida "
"chaqiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:10
msgid "current database cursor"
msgstr "joriy ma'lumotlar bazasi kursorlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:12
msgid "installed version of the module"
msgstr "modulning o'rnatilgan versiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:14
msgid ""
"Typically, this function executes one or multiple SQL queries and can "
"also access Odoo's ORM, as well as the :doc:`./upgrade_utils`."
msgstr ""
"Odatda, bu funksiya bir yoki bir nechta SQL so'rovlarini bajaradi va "
"Odoo ORM hamda :doc:`./upgrade_utils` ga ham kirish imkoniga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:18
msgid "Writing upgrade scripts"
msgstr "Yangilanish skriptlarini yozish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:20
msgid ""
"Upgrade scripts follow a specific tree structure with a naming convention"
" which determines when they are executed."
msgstr ""
"Yangilanish skriptlari qachon bajarilishini belgilovchi nomlash "
"konventsiyasi bilan muayyan daraxt tuzilmasiga amal qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:23
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The structure of an upgrade script path is "
":file:`$module/migrations/$version/{pre,post,end}-*.py`, where `$module` "
"is the module for which the script will run, `$version` is the full "
"version of the module (including Odoo's major version and the module's "
"minor version) and `{pre|post|end}-*.py` is the file that needs to be "
"executed. The file's name will determine the :ref:`phase <upgrade-"
"scripts/phases>` and order in which it is executed for that module and "
"version."
msgstr ""
"Yangilanish skripti yo'lining tuzilmasi "
":file:`$module/migrations/$version/{pre,post,end}-*.py` ko'rinishida bo'lib, "
"bu yerda `$module` — skript ishlaydigan modul, `$version` — modulning to'liq "
"versiyasi (Odoo asosiy versiyasi va modulning kichik versiyasini o'z ichiga "
"olgan) va `{pre|post|end}-*.py` — bajarilishi kerak bo'lgan fayl. Faylning "
"nomi o'sha modul va versiya uchun bajarilish :ref:`bosqichini <upgrade-"
"scripts/phases>` va tartibini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:30
msgid ""
"From Odoo 13 the top-level directory for the upgrade scripts can also be "
"named `upgrades`. This naming is preferred since it has the correct "
"meaning: *migrate* can be confused with *moving out of Odoo*. Thus "
":file:`$module/upgrades/$version/` is also valid."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 13 dan boshlab yangilanish skriptlari uchun yuqori darajadagi katalog "
"`upgrades` deb ham nomlanishi mumkin. Ushbu nomlash afzalroq, chunki u "
"to'g'ri ma'noni anglatadi: *migrate* so'zi *Odoodan chiqib ketish* bilan "
"adashtirishi mumkin. Shuning uchun :file:`$module/upgrades/$version/` ham "
"to'g'ri hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:35
msgid ""
"Upgrade scripts are only executed when the module is being updated. "
"Therefore, the module's minor version set in the `$version` directory "
"needs to be higher than the module's installed version and equal or lower"
" to the updated version of the module."
msgstr ""
"Yangilanish skriptlari faqat modul yangilanayotganda bajariladi. "
"Shuning uchun `$version` katalogida belgilangan modulning kichik versiyasi "
"modulning o'rnatilgan versiyasidan yuqori va yangilangan versiyasiga teng "
"yoki undan past bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/upgrades/upgrade_scripts.rst:41
msgid ""
