"`awesome_partner` upgraded to version `2.0` on Odoo 17."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 17 da `2.0` versiyasiga yangilangan `awesome_partner` nomli maxsus "
"modul uchun yangilanish skriptining katalog tuzilmasi."

