msgstr "`field`: maydon qiymatlarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:136
msgid ""
"The `field` element renders (and allows editing of, possibly) a single "
"field of the current record."
msgstr ""
"`field` elementi joriy yozuvning bitta maydonini ko'rsatadi (va ehtimol "
"tahrirlashga ruxsat beradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:138
msgid ""
"Using the same field multiple times in a form view is supported, and the "
"fields can receive different values for the `invisible` and `readonly` "
"attributes. These fields may have the same values but can be displayed "
"differently. However, the behavior is not guaranteed when several fields "
"exist with different values for the `required` attribute."
msgstr ""
"Forma ko'rinishida bir xil maydondan bir necha marta foydalanish qo'llab-"
"quvvatlanadi va maydonlar `invisible` va `readonly` atributlari uchun "
"turli qiymatlarni qabul qilishi mumkin. Bu maydonlar bir xil qiymatlarga "
"ega bo'lishi mumkin, lekin turlicha ko'rsatilishi mumkin. Biroq, `required` "
"atributi uchun turli qiymatlarga ega bir nechta maydon mavjud bo'lganda, "
"xatti-harakat kafolatlanmaydi."

