"the way the field is rendered and/or the way it can be edited. It refers "
"to a Javascript implementation (an Owl component) registered to the "
"`fields` registry."
msgstr ""
"Maydonni ifodalash uchun ishlatiladigan vidjet. Tanlangan vidjet maydonning "
"ko'rsatilish usulini va/yoki tahrirlash usulini o'zgartirishi mumkin. U "
"`fields` registriga ro'yxatdan o'tgan Javascript realizatsiyasiga (Owl "
"komponentiga) murojaat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:156
msgid ""
"The node id. Useful when there are several occurrences of the same field "
"in the view (see :ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/label`)."
msgstr ""
"Tugun id si. Ko'rinishda bir xil maydonning bir nechta takrorlanishi "
"mavjud bo'lganda foydali (qarang: :ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/label`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:161
msgid "The field name"
msgstr "Maydon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/field_attribute_string.rst:4
