msgstr "Maydonga yoki uning yorlig'iga sichqoncha olib borilaganda ko'rinadigan maslahat."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:177
msgid ""
"The configuration options for the field's widget (including default "
"widgets), as a Python expression that evaluates to a dict."
msgstr ""
"Maydon vidjeti uchun konfiguratsiya parametrlari (standart vidjetlar ham "
"kiritilgan), dict ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:180
msgid ""
"For relation fields, the following options are available: `no_create`, "
"`no_quick_create`, `no_open`, and `no_create_edit`."
msgstr ""
"Relatsion maydonlar uchun quyidagi parametrlar mavjud: `no_create`, "
"`no_quick_create`, `no_open` va `no_create_edit`."

