#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/field_attribute_readonly.rst:4
msgid ""
"Whether the field can be modified by the user (`False`) or is read-only "
"(`True`), as a Python expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Maydon foydalanuvchi tomonidan o'zgartirilishi mumkinmi (`False`) yoki faqat "
"o'qish uchunmi (`True`), bool ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/field_attribute_required.rst:4
msgid ""
"Whether the field can be left empty (`False`) or must be set (`True`), as"
" a Python expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Maydon bo'sh qoldirilishi mumkinmi (`False`) yoki to'ldirilishi shartmi "
"(`True`), bool ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_invisible.rst:4
msgid ""
"Whether the element is visible (`False`) or hidden (`True`), as a Python "
"expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Element ko'rinadimi (`False`) yoki yashirinmi (`True`), bool ga baholanadigan "
"Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_invisible.rst:8
msgid "There are two uses for the `invisible` attribute:"
msgstr "`invisible` atributining ikki xil foydalanish usuli mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_invisible.rst:10
msgid ""
"Usability: to avoid overloading the view and to make it easier for the "
"user to read, depending on the content."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchanlik: kontentga qarab ko'rinishni haddan tashqari to'ldirib "
"yubormaslik va foydalanuvchi uchun o'qishni osonlashtirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_invisible.rst:12
msgid ""
"Technical: a field must be present (invisible is enough) in the view to "
"be used in a Python expression."
msgstr ""
"Texnik: maydon Python ifodada ishlatilishi uchun ko'rinishda mavjud bo'lishi "
"kerak (ko'rinmas bo'lsa ham yetarli)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_groups.rst:4
msgid ""
"The comma-separated list of user groups to whom the element is displayed."
" Users who do not belong to at least one of these groups are unable to "
"see the element. Groups can be prefixed with the negative `!` operator to"
" exclude them."
msgstr ""
"Element ko'rsatiladigan foydalanuvchi guruhlarining vergul bilan ajratilgan "
"ro'yxati. Ushbu guruhlardan kamida biriga tegishli bo'lmagan foydalanuvchilar "
"elementni ko'ra olmaydi. Guruhlarni istisno qilish uchun ularni `!` salbiy "
"operatori bilan prefikslab bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:203
msgid ""
"The filters to apply when displaying existing records for selection, as a"
" Python expression that evaluates to a :ref:`domain "
"<reference/orm/domains>`."
msgstr ""
"Tanlash uchun mavjud yozuvlarni ko'rsatishda qo'llaniladigan filtrlar, "
":ref:`domen <reference/orm/domains>` ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:213
