#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:222
msgid ""
"The context to use when fetching possible values and creating or "
"searching records, as a Python expression that evaluates to a dict."
msgstr ""
"Mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlarni olishda va yozuvlarni yaratish yoki qidirishda "
"ishlatilgan kontekst, dict ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:244
msgid "Whether the field label should be hidden."
msgstr "Maydon yorlig'i yashirilishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:249
msgid "Fields that are a direct child of a `group` element"
msgstr "`group` elementining to'g'ridan-to'g'ri bolasi bo'lgan maydonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:254
msgid ""
"The help message to display on *empty* fields. It can replace field "
"labels in complex forms. However, it *should not* be an example of data, "
"as users may confuse placeholder text with filled fields."
msgstr ""
"*Bo'sh* maydonlarda ko'rsatiladigan yordam xabari. U murakkab formlarda "
"maydon yorliqlarini almashtirishi mumkin. Biroq, bu ma'lumot namunasi "
"*bo'lmasligi kerak*, chunki foydalanuvchilar o'rin egallashchi matnni "
"to'ldirilgan maydonlar bilan adashtirishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:265
msgid ""
"The comma-separated list of display modes (view types) to use for the "
"field's linked records. Allowed modes are: `list`, `form`, `kanban`, and "
"`graph`."
msgstr ""
"Maydonning bog'langan yozuvlari uchun ishlatiladigan ko'rsatish rejimlari "
"(ko'rinish turlari) ning vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati. Ruxsat etilgan "
"rejimlar: `list`, `form`, `kanban` va `graph`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:270
msgid "`list`"
msgstr "`list`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:271
msgid ":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` and :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` fields"
msgstr ":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` va :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` maydonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:4
msgid ""
"The `HTML class <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML_attribute>`_ to set "
"on the generated element."
msgstr ""
"Yaratilgan elementga o'rnatiladigan `HTML klassi "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML_attribute>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:6
msgid ""
"The styling uses the `Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com>`_ framework "
"and :ref:`UI icons <reference/user_interface/ui_icons>`. Common Odoo "
"classes include:"
msgstr ""
"Uslublash `Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com>`_ freymvorki va "
":ref:`UI ikonalari <reference/user_interface/ui_icons>` dan foydalanadi. "
"Odoo ning keng tarqalgan klasslari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:9
msgid ""
"`oe_inline`: prevents the usual line break following fields, and limits "
"their span;"
msgstr ""
"`oe_inline`: maydonlardan keyin odatdagi qator uzilishining oldini oladi "
"va ularning kengligini cheklaydi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:10
msgid ""
"`oe_left`, `oe_right`: `floats <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/CSS/float>`_ the element to the corresponding direction;"
msgstr ""
"`oe_left`, `oe_right`: elementni tegishli tomonga "
"`suztirib qo'yadi <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/float>`_;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:12
msgid ""
"`oe_read_only`, `oe_edit_only`: only displays the element in the "
"corresponding form mode;"
msgstr ""
"`oe_read_only`, `oe_edit_only`: elementni faqat tegishli forma rejimida "
"ko'rsatadi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:13
msgid ""
"`oe_avatar`: for image fields, displays images as an \"avatar\" (max "
"90x90 square);"
msgstr ""
"`oe_avatar`: rasm maydonlari uchun rasmlarni \"avatar\" sifatida ko'rsatadi "
"(maksimal 90x90 kvadrat);"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_class.rst:14
msgid ""
"`oe_stat_button`: defines a particular rendering to dynamically display "
"information while being clickable to target an action."
msgstr ""
"`oe_stat_button`: amalni maqsad qilib bosiladigan bo'lgan holda "
"ma'lumotlarni dinamik ko'rsatish uchun maxsus renderlashni belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:278
msgid "The name of the related field providing the name of the file."
msgstr "Fayl nomini taqdim etadigan bog'liq maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:283
msgid ":class:`~odoo.fields.Binary` fields"
msgstr ":class:`~odoo.fields.Binary` maydonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:288
msgid ""
"Whether the field stores a password and thus its data should not be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Maydon parol saqlaydimi va shuning uchun uning ma'lumotlari "
"ko'rsatilmasligi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:293
msgid ":class:`~odoo.fields.Char` fields"
msgstr ":class:`~odoo.fields.Char` maydonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:298
msgid ""
"The XMLID of the specific Kanban :doc:`view record <view_records>` that "
"should be used when selecting records in a mobile environment."
msgstr ""
"Mobil muhitda yozuvlarni tanlashda ishlatilishi kerak bo'lgan muayyan "
"Kanban :doc:`ko'rinish yozuvi <view_records>` ning XMLID si."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:309
msgid ""
"Whether the field is focused when the view opens. It can be applied to "
"only one field of a view."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinish ochilganda maydon fokuslanadimi. Bu faqat ko'rinishning bitta "
"maydoniga qo'llanilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:316
msgid ""
":ref:`Relational fields <studio/fields/relational-fields>` nodes can "
"contain specific subviews."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Relatsion maydonlar <studio/fields/relational-fields>` tugunlari "
"muayyan quyi ko'rinishlarni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:334
msgid "`label`: display field labels"
msgstr "`label`: maydon yorliqlarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:336
msgid ""
"When a :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` component "
"is not placed directly inside a :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/group>`, or when its `nolabel` "
"attribute is set, the field's label is not automatically displayed "
"alongside its value. The `label` component is the manual alternative of "
"displaying the label of a field."
msgstr ""
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` komponenti to'g'ridan-"
"to'g'ri :ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>` ichiga "
"joylashtirilmaganda yoki uning `nolabel` atributi o'rnatilganda, maydon "
"yorlig'i uning qiymati bilan birga avtomatik ko'rsatilmaydi. `label` "
"komponenti maydon yorlig'ini ko'rsatishning qo'lda tanlangan muqobilidir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:352
msgid "The `label` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`label` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:357
msgid ""
"The reference to the field associated with the label. It can be either "
"the name of the field, or its id (the `id` attribute set on the "
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>`)."
msgstr ""
"Yorliq bilan bog'liq maydonga havola. Bu maydon nomi yoki uning id si "
"(:ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` da o'rnatilgan "
"`id` atributi) bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:360
msgid ""
"When there are several occurrences of the same field in the view, and "
"there are several `label` components associated with these field nodes, "
"these labels must have unique `for` attribute; in this case, referencing "
"the `id` attribute of the corresponding field nodes."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishda bir xil maydonning bir nechta takrorlanishi mavjud bo'lganda va "
"bu maydon tugunlari bilan bog'liq bir nechta `label` komponent bo'lsa, "
"ushbu yorliqlar noyob `for` atributiga ega bo'lishi kerak; bu holda tegishli "
"maydon tugunlarining `id` atributiga havola qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:370
msgid "The label to display."
msgstr "Ko'rsatiladigan yorliq."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:374
msgid "The field's label coming from the field definition on the model"
msgstr "Modeldagi maydon ta'rifidan keladigan maydon yorlig'i"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:383
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1475
msgid "`button`: display action buttons"
msgstr "`button`: amal tugmalarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:392
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1484
msgid "The `button` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`button` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_type.rst:4
msgid ""
"The type of the button indicating how it behaves. It can have two "
"different values:"
msgstr ""
"Tugmaning xatti-harakatini ko'rsatuvchi turi. U ikki xil qiymatga ega "
"bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_type.rst:9
msgid ""
"Call a method on the view's model. The button's `name` is the method that"
" is called with the current record ID and the current `context`."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinish modelida metodni chaqirish. Tugmaning `name` si joriy yozuv ID si "
"va joriy `context` bilan chaqiriladigan metoddir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_type.rst:15
msgid ""
"Load and execute an `ir.actions` action record. The button's `name` is "
"the XMLID of the action to load. The `context` is extended with the "
"view's model (as `active_model`) and with the current record (as "
"`active_id`)."
msgstr ""
"`ir.actions` amal yozuvini yuklash va bajarish. Tugmaning `name` si "
"yuklanadigan amalni XMLID si hisoblanadi. `context` ko'rinish modeli bilan "
"(`active_model` sifatida) va joriy yozuv bilan (`active_id` sifatida) "
"kengaytiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_type.rst:25
msgid "Mandatory if the `special` attribute is not set"
msgstr "`special` atributi o'rnatilmagan bo'lsa majburiy"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_name.rst:4
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The method to call if the `type` is `object`. The :term:`XMLID <external "
"identifier>` of the action to load if the `type` is `action`, either in "
"raw format or in `%(XMLID)d` format."
msgstr ""
"`type` `object` bo'lsa chaqiriladigan metod. `type` `action` bo'lsa "
"yuklanadigan amalning :term:`XMLID <external identifier>` si, xom formatda "
"yoki `%(XMLID)d` formatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_string.rst:4
msgid ""
"The button's text if there is no `icon`, the `alt` text for the icon "
"otherwise."
msgstr ""
"`icon` yo'q bo'lsa tugma matni, aks holda ikona uchun `alt` matni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_icon.rst:4
msgid ""
"The icon to use to display the button. See :ref:`icons "
"<reference/user_interface/ui_icons>` for the reference list."
msgstr ""
"Tugmani ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan ikona. Ma'lumot ro'yxati uchun "
":ref:`ikonalar <reference/user_interface/ui_icons>` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_help.rst:4
msgid "The tooltip message shown when hovering with the mouse cursor."
msgstr "Sichqoncha kursori bilan olib borilaganda ko'rinadigan maslahat xabari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1692
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/button_attribute_context.rst:4
msgid ""
"The context that is merged into the view's context when performing the "
"button's call, as a Python expression that evaluates to a dict."
msgstr ""
"Tugma chaqirilishi bajarilganda ko'rinish kontekstiga qo'shiladigan kontekst, "
"dict ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:415
msgid ""
"The behavior of the button for form views opened in dialog. It can have "
"two different values:"
msgstr ""
"Dialog oynasida ochilgan forma ko'rinishlari uchun tugma xatti-harakati. "
"U ikki xil qiymatga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:420
msgid "Save the record and close the dialog."
msgstr "Yozuvni saqlash va dialog oynasini yopish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:425
msgid "Close the dialog without saving."
msgstr "Saqlamasdan dialog oynasini yopish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:439
msgid ""
"The confirmation message to display (and for the user to accept) before "
"performing the button's action."
msgstr ""
"Tugma amalini bajarishdan oldin ko'rsatiladigan (va foydalanuvchi tomonidan "
"qabul qilinadigan) tasdiqlash xabari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:454
msgid ""
"The hotkey (`keyboard_shortcut`_, similar to an accesskey_) that is bound"
" to the button. It is enabled when the `alt` key is pressed together with"
" the selected character, or together with the `shift` key and the "
"selected character when `shift+` is prepended to the value."
msgstr ""
"Tugmaga bog'langan tezkor tugma (`keyboard_shortcut`_, accesskey_ ga o'xshash). "
"U `alt` tugmasi tanlangan belgi bilan birga bosilganda yoki qiymatga `shift+` "
"oldindan qo'shilganda `shift` tugmasi va tanlangan belgi bilan birga bosilganda "
"faollashadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:471
msgid "Chatter widget"
msgstr "Chatter vidjeti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:473
msgid ""
"The :ref:`chatter widget <reference/mixins/mail/chatter>` is the "
"communication and log tool allowing to email colleagues and customers "
"directly from a record (task, order, invoice, event, note...)."
msgstr ""
":ref:`chatter vidjeti <reference/mixins/mail/chatter>` — bu yozuvdan "
"(vazifa, buyurtma, hisob-faktura, tadbir, eslatma...) to'g'ridan-to'g'ri "
"hamkasblar va mijozlarga elektron pochta jo'natish imkonini beruvchi "
"muloqot va jurnal vositasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:476
msgid ""
"It is added with a `div` element with the class `oe_chatter` when the "
"model inherits the `mail.thread` mixin."
msgstr ""
"Model `mail.thread` miksin dan meros olganda `oe_chatter` klassli `div` "
"elementi bilan qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:496
msgid "Attachments preview widget"
msgstr "Ilovalar oldindan ko'rish vidjeti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:498
msgid ""
"The attachment preview widget is added with an *empty* `div` element with"
" the class `o_attachment_preview`."
msgstr ""
"Ilova oldindan ko'rish vidjeti `o_attachment_preview` klassli *bo'sh* `div` "
"elementi bilan qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:514
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4177
msgid "Structural components"
msgstr "Tuzilmaviy komponentlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:516
msgid ""
"Structural components provide structure or \"visual\" features with "
"little logic. They are used as elements or sets of elements in form "
"views."
msgstr ""
"Tuzilmaviy komponentlar kam mantiq bilan tuzilma yoki \"vizual\" xususiyatlarni "
"ta'minlaydi. Ular forma ko'rinishlarida elementlar yoki elementlar to'plami "
"sifatida ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:519
msgid ""
"Form views accept the following children structural components: "
":ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>`, :ref:`sheet "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/sheet>`, :ref:`notebook "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/notebook>`, :ref:`notebook "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/notebook>`, :ref:`newline "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/newline>`, :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/separator>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/header>`, :ref:`footer "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/footer>`, "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/button_container`, and "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/title_container`."
msgstr ""
"Forma ko'rinishlari quyidagi bolalar tuzilmaviy komponentlarini qabul qiladi: "
":ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>`, :ref:`sheet "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/sheet>`, :ref:`notebook "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/notebook>`, :ref:`notebook "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/notebook>`, :ref:`newline "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/newline>`, :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/separator>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/header>`, :ref:`footer "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/footer>`, "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/button_container` va "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/form/title_container`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:535
msgid "`group`: define columns layouts"
msgstr "`group`: ustun sxemalarini aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:537
msgid ""
"The `group` element is used to define column layouts in forms. By "
"default, groups define 2 columns, and most direct children of groups take"
" a single column."
msgstr ""
"`group` elementi formalarda ustun sxemalarini aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi. "
"Odatda, guruhlar 2 ta ustunni belgilaydi va guruhlarning ko'pchilik to'g'ridan-"
"to'g'ri bolalari bitta ustunni egallaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:540
msgid ""
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` elements that are "
"direct children of groups display a `label` by default, and the label and"
" the field itself have a `colspan` of `1` each."
msgstr ""
"Guruhlarning to'g'ridan-to'g'ri bolalari bo'lgan :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/field>` elementlari odatda `label` "
"ko'rsatadi va yorliq hamda maydonning o'zi har biri `1` `colspan` ga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:543
msgid ""
"Children are laid out horizontally (they try to fill the next column "
"before changing row)."
msgstr ""
"Bolalar gorizontal joylashtiriladi (ular qatorni o'zgartirishdan oldin "
"keyingi ustunni to'ldirishga harakat qiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:553
msgid "The `group` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`group` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:558
msgid "The title displayed for the group."
msgstr "Guruh uchun ko'rsatiladigan sarlavha."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:567
msgid "The number of columns in a `group`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:570
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:579
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1284
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1294
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1987
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2004
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2021
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2038
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2308
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3287
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3357
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3388
msgid "int"
msgstr "int"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:576
msgid "The number of columns taken by a child element."
msgstr "Bola element egallaydigan ustunlar soni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:584
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:668
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:708
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:753
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:871
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1157
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1455
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1506
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1559
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1629
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1725
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1761
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1873
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2125
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2385
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2948
msgid "Possible structure and representation of its rendering"
msgstr "Renderlashning mumkin bo'lgan tuzilmasi va ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:621
msgid "`sheet`: make the layout responsive"
msgstr "`sheet`: sxemani moslashuvchan qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:623
msgid ""
"The `sheet` element can be used as a direct child of the :ref:`form "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` root element for a narrower and more"
" responsive form layout (centered page, margin...). It usually contains "
":ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>` elements."
msgstr ""
"`sheet` elementi torroq va moslashuvchanroq forma sxemasi uchun (markazlashtirilgan "
"sahifa, chegara...) :ref:`form <reference/view_architectures/form>` ildiz "
"elementining to'g'ridan-to'g'ri bolasi sifatida ishlatilishi mumkin. Odatda "
"u :ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>` elementlarini o'z "
"ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:639
msgid "`notebook` & `page`: add tabbed sections"
msgstr "`notebook` va `page`: yorliqli bo'limlar qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:641
msgid ""
"The `notebook` element defines a tabbed section. Each tab is defined "
"through a `page` child element."
msgstr ""
"`notebook` elementi yorliqli bo'limni belgilaydi. Har bir yorliq `page` "
"bola elementi orqali aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:643
msgid "The `notebook` element should not be placed within `group` elements."
msgstr "`notebook` elementi `group` elementlari ichiga joylashtirilmasligi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:655
msgid "The `page` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`page` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:660
msgid "The title of the tab."
msgstr "Yorliqning sarlavhasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:663
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:750
msgid "`str`"
msgstr "`str`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:692
msgid "`newline`: start new group rows"
msgstr "`newline`: yangi guruh qatorlarini boshlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:694
msgid ""
"The `newline` element is used within :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/group>` elements to end the current "
"row early and immediately switch to a new row, without filling any "
"remaining column beforehand."
msgstr ""
"`newline` elementi :ref:`group <reference/view_architectures/form/group>` "
"elementlari ichida joriy qatorni erta tugatish va qolgan ustunlarni "
"avvaldan to'ldirmasdan darhol yangi qatorga o'tish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:730
msgid "`separator`: add horizontal spacing"
msgstr "`separator`: gorizontal bo'shliq qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:732
msgid ""
"The `separator` element adds vertical spacing between elements within a "
"group."
msgstr "`separator` elementi guruh ichidagi elementlar orasiga vertikal bo'shliq qo'shadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:742
msgid "The `<separator>` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`<separator>` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:747
msgid "The title as a section title."
msgstr "Bo'lim sarlavhasi sifatidagi sarlavha."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:781
msgid ""
"The `separator` element can be used to achieve visual separation between "
"elements within the same inner `group` element while keeping them "
"horizontally aligned."
msgstr ""
"`separator` elementi bir xil ichki `group` elementi ichidagi elementlarni "
"gorizontal tekislangan holda saqlashda ular orasida vizual ajratishni "
"amalga oshirish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:787
msgid "`header`: display workflow buttons and a status"
msgstr "`header`: ish jarayoni tugmalarini va statusni ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:789
msgid ""
"The `header` element combined with the :ref:`sheet "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/sheet>` element provides a full-width "
"location above the sheet itself generally used to display workflow "
":ref:`button <reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elements and a "
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` element rendered "
"as status widget."
msgstr ""
"`header` elementi :ref:`sheet <reference/view_architectures/form/sheet>` "
"elementi bilan birgalikda varaqning o'zidan yuqorida to'liq kenglikdagi joylashuvni "
"ta'minlaydi, bu odatda ish jarayoni :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elementlarini va status vidjeti "
"sifatida renderlangan :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/field>` elementini ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:817
msgid "`footer`: display dialog buttons"
msgstr "`footer`: dialog tugmalarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:819
msgid ""
"The `footer` element is used to display :ref:`buttons "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elements at the end of "
"dialogs."
msgstr ""
"`footer` elementi dialoglarning oxirida :ref:`tugmalar "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elementlarini ko'rsatish uchun "
"ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:842
msgid ""
"When no `footer` element is specified, the view's standard buttons (like "
"Save or Discard) will be present by default. It is also possible to avoid"
" replacing the standard buttons in form or x2many dialogs by using the "
"`replace` attribute. This attribute defaults to `True` if not specified "
"but setting it to `False` (or 0) will make it so that the specified "
"`footer` will be added next to the default buttons instead of replacing "
"them."
msgstr ""
"`footer` elementi belgilanmagan bo'lsa, ko'rinishning standart tugmalari "
"(masalan Saqlash yoki Bekor qilish) odatda mavjud bo'ladi. `replace` "
"atributidan foydalanib forma yoki x2many dialoglarida standart tugmalarni "
"almashtirmaslik ham mumkin. Bu atribut belgilanmagan bo'lsa `True` ga "
"standart qo'yiladi, lekin uni `False` ga (yoki 0 ga) qo'yish ko'rsatilgan "
"`footer` ni ularni almashtirish o'rniga standart tugmalar yoniga qo'shilishiga "
"olib keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:858
msgid "Buttons container"
msgstr "Tugmalar konteyneri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:860
msgid ""
"A :ref:`button <reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elements "
"container can be created with a `div` element with the class "
"`button_box`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`button <reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elementlari "
"konteyneri `button_box` klassli `div` elementi bilan yaratilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:893
msgid "Title container"
msgstr "Sarlavha konteyneri"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:895
msgid ""
"A title :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` element "
"container can be created with a `div` element with the class `oe_title`."
msgstr ""
"Sarlavha :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` elementi "
"konteyneri `oe_title` klassli `div` elementi bilan yaratilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:911
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Sozlamalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:913
msgid ""
"Settings views are a customization of the :ref:`form "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` view. They are used to display "
"settings in a centralized place. They differ from generic form views in "
"that they have a search bar and a sidebar."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamalar ko'rinishlari :ref:`form <reference/view_architectures/form>` "
"ko'rinishining moslashtirilishidir. Ular sozlamalarni markazlashtirilgan "
"joyda ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi. Ular umumiy forma ko'rinishlaridan "
"qidiruv paneli va yon panel mavjudligi bilan farqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:946
msgid ""
"Settings views accept the :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/field>`, :ref:`label "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/label>` and :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elements of :ref:`form "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` views, as well as three additional "
"children elements: :ref:`app "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/app>`, :ref:`block "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/block>`, and :ref:`setting "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/setting>`."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamalar ko'rinishlari :ref:`form <reference/view_architectures/form>` "
"ko'rinishlarining :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>`, "
":ref:`label <reference/view_architectures/form/label>` va :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/button>` elementlarini, shuningdek "
"uchta qo'shimcha bola elementlarini qabul qiladi: :ref:`app "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/app>`, :ref:`block "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/block>` va :ref:`setting "
"<reference/view_architectures/settings/setting>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:959
msgid "`app`: declare the application"
msgstr "`app`: ilovani e'lon qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:961
msgid ""
"The `app` element is used to declare the application on the settings "
"view. It creates an entry with the logo of the application on the sidebar"
" of the view. It also acts as delimiter when searching."
msgstr ""
"`app` elementi sozlamalar ko'rinishida ilovani e'lon qilish uchun ishlatiladi. "
"U ko'rinishning yon panelida ilova logotipi bilan yozuv yaratadi. Qidirishda "
"ajratgich sifatida ham ishlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:972
msgid "The `app` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`app` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:977
msgid "The name of the application."
msgstr "Ilovaning nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:985
msgid "The technical name of the application (the name of the module)."
msgstr "Ilovaning texnik nomi (modul nomi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:993
msgid "The `relative path`_ to the logo."
msgstr "Logotipga `nisbiy yo'l`_."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:996
msgid "path_"
msgstr "path_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:997
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"A path computed with the `name` attribute: "
":file:`/{name}/static/description/icon.png`"
msgstr ""
"`name` atributi bilan hisoblangan yo'l: "
":file:`/{name}/static/description/icon.png`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1008
msgid "`block`: declare a group of settings"
msgstr "`block`: sozlamalar guruhini e'lon qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1010
msgid ""
"The `block` element is used to declare a group of settings. This group "
"can have a title and a description."
msgstr ""
"`block` elementi sozlamalar guruhini e'lon qilish uchun ishlatiladi. Bu "
"guruhda sarlavha va tavsif bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1025
msgid "The `block` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`block` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1030
msgid "The title of the block of settings. One can search on its value."
msgstr "Sozlamalar blokining sarlavhasi. Uning qiymati bo'yicha qidirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1039
msgid "The description of the block of settings. One can search on its value."
msgstr "Sozlamalar blokining tavsifi. Uning qiymati bo'yicha qidirish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1052
msgid "`setting`: declare the setting"
msgstr "`setting`: sozlamani e'lon qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1054
msgid "The `setting` element is used to declare the setting itself."
msgstr "`setting` elementi sozlamaning o'zini e'lon qilish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1056
msgid ""
"The first :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` element "
"in the setting is used as the main field. It is placed on the left panel "
"if it is a boolean field, and on the top of the right panel otherwise. "
"The field is also used to create the setting label if a `string` "
"attribute is not defined."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamadagi birinchi :ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` "
"elementi asosiy maydon sifatida ishlatiladi. Agar bu boolean maydon bo'lsa, "
"u chap panelga joylashtiriladi, aks holda o'ng panelning yuqori qismiga. "
"Maydon shuningdek `string` atributi belgilanmagan bo'lsa sozlama yorlig'ini "
"yaratish uchun ham ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1061
msgid ""
"The `setting` element can also contain additional elements (e.g., HTML). "
"All of those elements are rendered in the right panel."
msgstr ""
"`setting` elementi qo'shimcha elementlarni ham o'z ichiga olishi mumkin "
"(masalan, HTML). Ushbu elementlarning barchasi o'ng panelda renderlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1080
msgid "The `<setting>` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`<setting>` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1085
msgid ""
"By default, a setting is visually separated on two panels (left and "
"right), and is used to edit a given :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/form/field>`. By defining "
"`type=\"header\"`, a special kind of setting is rendered instead. This "
"setting is used to modify the scope of the other settings. For example, "
"on the Website application, this setting is used to indicate to which "
"website the other settings apply. The header setting is visually "
"represented as a banner on top of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Odatda, sozlama ikki panelda (chap va o'ng) vizual ajratiladi va berilgan "
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/form/field>` ni tahrirlash uchun "
"ishlatiladi. `type=\"header\"` belgilanishi bilan esa maxsus turdagi sozlama "
"renderlanadi. Bu sozlama boshqa sozlamalar qamrovini o'zgartirish uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Masalan, Veb-sayt ilovasida bu sozlama boshqa sozlamalar qaysi "
"veb-saytga tegishli ekanligini ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi. Header sozlama "
"ekranning yuqori qismida banner sifatida vizual ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1099
msgid "The text used as the label of the setting."
msgstr "Sozlama yorlig'i sifatida ishlatiladigan matn."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1103
msgid "The first field's label"
msgstr "Birinchi maydonning yorlig'i"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1108
msgid "The text used as a tooltip."
msgstr "Maslahat sifatida ishlatiladigan matn."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1117
msgid ""
"The description of the setting. This text is displayed just below the "
"setting label (with the class `text-muted`)."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamaning tavsifi. Bu matn sozlama yorlig'ining darhol pastida "
"(`text-muted` klassi bilan) ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1127
msgid ""
"Whether the setting is company-specific. If set, an icon is displayed "
"next to the setting label."
msgstr ""
"Sozlama kompaniyaga xosmi. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, sozlama yorlig'i yonida "
"ikona ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1129
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1237
msgid "It accepts only the value `'1'`."
msgstr "U faqat `'1'` qiymatini qabul qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1138
msgid ""
"The `path`_ to the documentation on the setting. If set, a clickable icon"
" is displayed next to the setting label. The path can be both an absolute"
" or a `relative path`_. In the latter case, it is relative to "
"`https://www.odoo.com/documentation/<version>`."
msgstr ""
"Sozlama hujjatlariga `yo'l`_. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, sozlama yorlig'i yonida "
"bosiladigan ikona ko'rsatiladi. Yo'l mutlaq yoki `nisbiy yo'l`_ bo'lishi "
"mumkin. Ikkinchi holda, u `https://www.odoo.com/documentation/<version>` ga "
"nisbatan hisoblanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1143
msgid "`path_`"
msgstr "`path_`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1153
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:21
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:315
msgid "List"
msgstr "Ro'yxat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1155
msgid "The root element of list views is `list` (the previous name was `tree`)."
msgstr "Ro'yxat ko'rinishlarining ildiz elementi `list` dir (oldingi nomi `tree` edi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1176
msgid ""
"Optional attributes can be added to the root element `list` to customize "
"the view."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishni sozlashtirish uchun `list` ildiz elementiga ixtiyoriy atributlar "
"qo'shilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1189
msgid "Disable/enable record import from data on the view."
msgstr "Ko'rinishda ma'lumotlardan yozuvni importini o'chirish/yoqish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1198
msgid "Disable/enable record export to data on the view."
msgstr "Ko'rinishda ma'lumotlarga yozuvni eksportini o'chirish/yoqish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1207
msgid ""
"Make the view's records editable in-place, and allow creating new records"
" from a row of the list. It can have two different values:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishning yozuvlarini joyida tahrirlanadigan qilish va ro'yxat qatoridan "
"yangi yozuvlar yaratishga ruxsat berish. U ikki xil qiymatga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1213
msgid "New records are created from the top of the list."
msgstr "Yangi yozuvlar ro'yxat yuqorisidan yaratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1218
msgid "New records are created from the bottom of the list."
msgstr "Yangi yozuvlar ro'yxat pastidan yaratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1220
msgid ""
"The architecture for the inline :ref:`form "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` view is derived from the list view. "
"Most attributes valid on a form view's fields and buttons are thus "
"accepted by list views, although they may not have any meaning if the "
"list view is non-editable."
msgstr ""
"Inline :ref:`form <reference/view_architectures/form>` ko'rinishining "
"arxitekturasi ro'yxat ko'rinishidan olingan. Forma ko'rinishi maydonlari "
"va tugmalari uchun amal qiladigan ko'pchilik atributlar ro'yxat ko'rinishlari "
"tomonidan qabul qilinadi, garchi ular ro'yxat ko'rinishi tahrirlab bo'lmaydigan "
"bo'lsa ma'noga ega bo'lmasligi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1225
msgid "This behavior is disabled if the `edit` attribute is set to `False`."
msgstr "Bu xatti-harakat `edit` atributi `False` ga o'rnatilsa o'chiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1234
msgid ""
"Activate the multi-editing feature that allows updating a field to the "
"same value for multiple records at once."
msgstr ""
"Bir vaqtning o'zida bir nechta yozuvlar uchun maydonni bir xil qiymatga "
"yangilash imkonini beruvchi ko'p tahrirlash xususiyatini faollashtirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1246
msgid "Display a button at the end of each row to open the record in a form view."
msgstr "Yozuvni forma ko'rinishida ochish uchun har bir qator oxirida tugma ko'rsatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1248
msgid "It has no effect if the view is non-editable."
msgstr "Ko'rinish tahrirlab bo'lmaydigan bo'lsa hech qanday ta'siri yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_default_group_by.rst:4
msgid ""
"The name of the field on which the records should be grouped by default "
"if no grouping is specified via the action or the current :ref:`search "
"<reference/view_architectures/search>`."
msgstr ""
"Amal yoki joriy :ref:`qidiruv <reference/view_architectures/search>` "
"orqali guruhlash belgilanmagan bo'lsa yozuvlar odatda guruhlaniladigan "
"maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_default_order.rst:4
msgid ""
"A comma-separated list of fields names that overrides the ordering "
"defined on the model through the :attr:`~odoo.models.BaseModel._order` "
"attribute."
msgstr ""
":attr:`~odoo.models.BaseModel._order` atributi orqali modelda belgilangan "
"tartibni bekor qiladigan vergul bilan ajratilgan maydon nomlari ro'yxati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_default_order.rst:7
msgid ""
"To inverse the sorting order of a field, postfix it with `desc`, "
"separated by a space."
msgstr ""
"Maydon saralash tartibini teskari qilish uchun uni bo'sh joy bilan ajratilgan "
"`desc` bilan postfikslab qo'ying."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1261
msgid ""
"The style that should be applied to matching records' rows, as a Python "
"expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Mos keladigan yozuvlar qatorlariga qo'llanilishi kerak bo'lgan uslub, "
"bool ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1264
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1390
msgid ""
"`<style>` must be replaced by one of `bf` (bold), `it` (italic), `info`, "
"`warning`, `danger`, `muted`, `primary`, and `success`."
msgstr ""
"`<style>` quyidagilardan biri bilan almashtirilishi kerak: `bf` (qalin), "
"`it` (kursiv), `info`, `warning`, `danger`, `muted`, `primary` va `success`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1281
msgid "The default size of a page. It must be strictly positive."
msgstr "Sahifaning standart hajmi. U qat'iy musbat bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1285
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1295
msgid "`80` for list views, `40` for X2many lists in form views"
msgstr "Ro'yxat ko'rinishlari uchun `80`, forma ko'rinishlaridagi X2many ro'yxatlari uchun `40`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1290
msgid ""
"The default number of groups on a page when the list view is grouped. It "
"must be strictly positive."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishi guruhlanganda sahifadagi guruhlarning standart soni. "
"U qat'iy musbat bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1300
msgid ""
"Whether the first level of groups should be opened by default when the "
"list view is grouped."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishi guruhlanganda birinchi daraja guruhlar odatda ochiq "
"bo'lishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1303
msgid "It may be slow, depending on the number of groups."
msgstr "Guruhlar soniga qarab sekin bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_sample.rst:4
msgid ""
"Whether the view should be populated with a set of sample records if none"
" are found for the current model."
msgstr ""
"Joriy model uchun hech qanday yozuv topilmagan bo'lsa ko'rinish namuna "
"yozuvlar to'plami bilan to'ldirilishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_sample.rst:7
msgid ""
"These fake records have heuristics for certain field names/models. For "
"example, a field `display_name` on the model `res.users` will be "
"populated with sample people names, while an `email` field will be in the"
" form `firstname.lastname@sample.demo`."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu soxta yozuvlar muayyan maydon nomlari/modellari uchun evristikalarga ega. "
"Masalan, `res.users` modelidagi `display_name` maydoni namuna odamlar nomlari "
"bilan to'ldiriladi, `email` maydoni esa `firstname.lastname@sample.demo` "
"shaklida bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/root_attribute_sample.rst:11
msgid ""
"The user is unable to interact with these data, and they will be "
"discarded as soon as an action is performed (record created, column "
"added, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi bu ma'lumotlar bilan o'zaro ta'sir qila olmaydi va ular "
"biron bir amal bajarilishi bilan (yozuv yaratildi, ustun qo'shildi va h.k.) "
"darhol o'chiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1316
msgid ""
"List views accept the following children elements: :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/field>`, :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>`, :ref:`groupby "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/groupby>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/header>`, :ref:`control, and create "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/control>`."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishlari quyidagi bola elementlarini qabul qiladi: :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/field>`, :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>`, :ref:`groupby "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/groupby>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/header>`, :ref:`control va create "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/control>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1330
msgid ""
"The `field` element renders (and allows editing of, possibly) a single "
"field of all current records as a column."
msgstr ""
"`field` elementi barcha joriy yozuvlarning bitta maydonini ustun sifatida "
"renderlay di (va ehtimol tahrirlashga ruxsat beradi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1333
msgid "Using the same field multiple times in a list view is not supported"
msgstr "Ro'yxat ko'rinishida bir xil maydondan bir necha marta foydalanish qo'llab-quvvatlanmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1350
msgid ""
"Make the visibility of the field optional. The field's column can be "
"hidden or shown through a button on the view's header."
msgstr ""
"Maydon ko'rinishini ixtiyoriy qilish. Maydon ustuni ko'rinishning sarlavhasidagi "
"tugma orqali yashirilishi yoki ko'rsatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1353
msgid "It can have two different values:"
msgstr "U ikki xil qiymatga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1358
msgid "The field is shown by default."
msgstr "Maydon odatda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1363
msgid "The field is hidden by default."
msgstr "Maydon odatda yashiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_column_invisible.rst:4
msgid ""
"Whether the column is visible (`False`) or hidden (`True`), as a Python "
"expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Ustun ko'rinadimi (`False`) yoki yashirinmi (`True`), bool ga baholanadigan "
"Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures/generic_attribute_column_invisible.rst:7
msgid ""
"Unlike `invisible`, it affects the entire column, and is evaluated "
"without the subtree values."
msgstr ""
"`invisible` dan farqli o'laroq, u butun ustunni qamrab oladi va daraxt quyi "
"qismi qiymatlarsiz baholanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1387
msgid ""
"The style that should be applied to matching records' field, as a Python "
"expression that evaluates to a bool."
msgstr ""
"Mos keladigan yozuvlar maydoniga qo'llanilishi kerak bo'lgan uslub, "
"bool ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1406
msgid ""
"The aggregate to display at the bottom of the column. The aggregation is "
"computed on only records that are currently displayed. The aggregation "
"operation must match the corresponding field's `aggregator`."
msgstr ""
"Ustun pastida ko'rsatiladigan agregat. Agregatsiya faqat joriy ko'rsatilayotgan "
"yozuvlar bo'yicha hisoblanadi. Agregatsiya amali tegishli maydonning "
"`aggregator` si bilan mos kelishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1423
msgid ""
"The list view always tries to optimize the available space among columns."
" For some field types, this is done by enforcing a width, depending on "
"the field type. For instance, we know exactly the number of pixels "
"required to display a date, so we can ensure that a column for a date "
"field doesn't take more space than what is strictly necessary, thus "
"leaving the extra space for the other columns. However, the framework "
"can't guess the adequate width for every field types. For instance, char "
"fields can be used to encode large values, or 3-letter country codes. In "
"the latter case, one can set the width directly in the arch (e.g. "
"`width=\"40px\"`). It represents the width (always in pixels) required to"
" render the values inside the cells. The width of the column will then be"
" the sum of the given value and the cells' left and right paddings."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishi har doim ustunlar orasidagi mavjud joyni optimallashtirishga "
"harakat qiladi. Ba'zi maydon turlari uchun bu maydon turiga qarab kengligi "
"belgilangan holda amalga oshiriladi. Masalan, biz sanani ko'rsatish uchun "
"zarur piksellar sonini aniq bilamiz, shuning uchun sana maydoni ustuni "
"qat'iy zarurdan ko'proq joy egallamamasligi va qo'shimcha joy boshqa "
"ustunlarga qoldirilishini ta'minlashimiz mumkin. Biroq, freymvork har bir "
"maydon turi uchun mos kenglikni taxmin qila olmaydi. Masalan, char maydonlari "
"katta qiymatlarni yoki 3 harfli mamlakat kodlarini kodlash uchun ishlatilishi "
"mumkin. Ikkinchi holda, kenglikni arxda to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'rnatish mumkin "
"(masalan, `width=\"40px\"`). Bu katakchalar ichidagi qiymatlarni renderlash "
"uchun zarur (har doim pikselda) kenglikni ifodalaydi. Ustun kengligi esa "
"berilgan qiymat va katakchalarning chap va o'ng ichki bo'shliqlari yig'indisiga "
"teng bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1440
msgid ""
"Whether the field's column header should remain empty. If set, the column"
" will not be sortable."
msgstr ""
"Maydon ustun sarlavhasi bo'sh qolishi kerakmi. O'rnatilgan bo'lsa, ustun "
"saralash imkoniyatiga ega bo'lmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1442
msgid "It accepts only the value `'1'`"
msgstr "U faqat `'1'` qiymatini qabul qiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1449
msgid ""
"When a list view is grouped, numeric fields are aggregated and displayed "
"for each group. Also, if there are too many records in a group, a pager "
"appears on the right of the group row. For this reason, it is a bad "
"practice to have a numeric field in the last column when the list view is"
" in a situation where it can be grouped. However, it does not pose a "
"problem for X2many fields in a form view, as they cannot be grouped."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ko'rinishi guruhlanganda, raqamli maydonlar har bir guruh uchun "
"agregatlanadi va ko'rsatiladi. Shuningdek, guruhdagi yozuvlar juda ko'p "
"bo'lsa, guruh qatori o'ng tomonida pager paydo bo'ladi. Shu sababli, ro'yxat "
"ko'rinishi guruhlash mumkin bo'lgan holatda so'nggi ustunda raqamli maydon "
"bo'lishi yaxshi amaliyot emas. Biroq, bu X2many maydonlari uchun forma "
"ko'rinishida muammo keltirmaydi, chunki ularni guruhlab bo'lmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1528
msgid "`groupby`: define group headers"
msgstr "`groupby`: guruh sarlavhalarini aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1530
msgid ""
"The `groupby` element is used to define group headers with :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>` elements when grouping "
"records on :attr:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` fields. It also accepts "
":ref:`field <reference/view_architectures/list/field>` elements, which "
"can be used for modifiers. These fields thus belong on the Many2one co-"
"model. These extra fields are fetched in batch."
msgstr ""
"`groupby` elementi :attr:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydonlar bo'yicha "
"yozuvlarni guruhlashda :ref:`button "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>` elementlari bilan guruh "
"sarlavhalarini aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi. U shuningdek modifikatorlar "
"uchun ishlatilishi mumkin bo'lgan :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/field>` elementlarini ham qabul qiladi. "
"Bu maydonlar Many2one hamkor-modeliga tegishli. Bu qo'shimcha maydonlar "
"to'plamda olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1546
msgid "The `groupby` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`groupby` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1551
msgid "The name of the a :attr:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` field to use as header."
msgstr "Sarlavha sifatida ishlatiladigan :attr:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1553
msgid ""
"A special :ref:`button <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` "
"element with `type=\"edit\"` can be defined to open the Many2one field's "
"form view."
msgstr ""
"Many2one maydonning forma ko'rinishini ochish uchun `type=\"edit\"` bilan "
"maxsus :ref:`button <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` elementi "
"aniqlanishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1583
msgid ""
"Fields inside the `groupby` element are used only to fetch and store the "
"value, but they are never displayed."
msgstr ""
"`groupby` elementi ichidagi maydonlar faqat qiymatni olish va saqlash uchun "
"ishlatiladi, lekin ular hech qachon ko'rsatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1589
msgid "`header`: display workflow buttons"
msgstr "`header`: ish jarayoni tugmalarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1600
msgid "The `header` element accepts the following children elements:"
msgstr "`header` elementi quyidagi bola elementlarini qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1605
msgid ""
"The `button` element allows defining buttons in the control panel. It is "
"the same element as the :ref:`button element in list views "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>`, but it accepts one more "
"attribute when placed inside a `header` element:"
msgstr ""
"`button` elementi boshqaruv panelida tugmalarni aniqlash imkonini beradi. "
"Bu :ref:`ro'yxat ko'rinishlaridagi button elementi "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>` bilan bir xil element, lekin "
"`header` elementi ichiga joylashtirilganda bitta qo'shimcha atributni qabul "
"qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1612
msgid "Make the button available at all time, without having to select records."
msgstr "Yozuvlarni tanlash shart bo'lmasdan tugmani har doim foydalanish uchun mavjud qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1614
msgid "It accepts only the value `always`."
msgstr "U faqat `always` qiymatini qabul qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1652
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2968
msgid "`control`: customize create and delete actions"
msgstr "`control`: yaratish va o'chirish amallarini sozlashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1654
msgid ""
"The `control` element allows to customize the create and delete actions. "
"In particular, it allows to add special create buttons with specific "
"contexts, to use regular view buttons as create actions, and to make the "
"create and delete actions available only under certain conditions."
msgstr ""
"`control` elementi yaratish va o'chirish amallarini sozlashtirish imkonini "
"beradi. Xususan, u muayyan kontekstlar bilan maxsus yaratish tugmalarini "
"qo'shish, oddiy ko'rinish tugmalarini yaratish amallari sifatida ishlatish "
"va yaratish va o'chirish amallarini faqat muayyan shartlar ostida mavjud "
"qilish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1659
msgid ""
"The `control` element is only supported in list views inside "
":class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` or :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` fields."
msgstr ""
"`control` elementi faqat :class:`~odoo.fields.One2many` yoki "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` maydonlari ichidagi ro'yxat ko'rinishlarida "
"qo'llab-quvvatlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1673
msgid ""
"The `control` element takes no attributes. It accepts the following "
"children elements:"
msgstr ""
"`control` elementi atributlarni qabul qilmaydi. U quyidagi bola "
"elementlarini qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1678
msgid ""
"The given `create` elements replace the default :guilabel:`Add a line` "
"button. A `create` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Berilgan `create` elementlari standart :guilabel:`Qator qo'shish` tugmasini "
"almashtiradi. `create` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1684
msgid "The button's text."
msgstr "Tugma matni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1702
msgid ""
"Whether the element is visible (`False`) or hidden (`True`), as a Python "
"expression that evaluates to a bool. The parent record and the context "
"can be used in the expresion."
msgstr ""
"Element ko'rinadimi (`False`) yoki yashirinmi (`True`), bool ga baholanadigan "
"Python ifodasi sifatida. Ota yozuv va kontekst ifodada ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1712
msgid ""
"Like :ref:`regular view buttons "
"<reference/view_architectures/list/button>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Oddiy ko'rinish tugmalariga <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` o'xshash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1716
msgid ""
"The `delete` element allows to conditionnaly hide the delete icon, row by"
" row. There can only be one child of this type. It can have only one "
"attribute:"
msgstr ""
"`delete` elementi o'chiruv ikonasini qator bo'yicha shartli ravishda "
"yashirishga imkon beradi. Bu turda faqat bitta bola bo'lishi mumkin. Faqat "
"bitta atributga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1722
msgid ""
"Same as for `create`, except that in this case the record itself can also"
" be used in the expresion."
msgstr ""
"`create` uchungiga o'xshash, bu holda yozuvning o'zi ham ifodada "
"ishlatilishi mumkinligi bundan tashqari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1750
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:138
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:382
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Qidiruv"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1752
msgid ""
"Search views are different from other view types in that they are not "
"used to display content. Although they apply to a specific model, they "
"are used to filter another view's content (usually aggregated views; "
"e.g., :ref:`reference/view_architectures/list` and "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/graph`)."
msgstr ""
"Qidiruv ko'rinishlari kontent ko'rsatish uchun ishlatilmasligi bilan boshqa "
"ko'rinish turlaridan farq qiladi. Garchi ular muayyan modelga tegishli "
"bo'lsa-da, boshqa ko'rinish kontentini filtrlash uchun ishlatiladi "
"(odatda agregatli ko'rinishlar; masalan, :ref:`reference/view_architectures/list` "
"va :ref:`reference/view_architectures/graph`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1757
msgid "The root element of search views is `search`."
msgstr "Qidiruv ko'rinishlarining ildiz elementi `search` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1759
msgid "It takes no attributes."
msgstr "U atributlarni qabul qilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1780
msgid ""
"Search views accept the following children elements: :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/field>`, :ref:`filter "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>`, :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/separator>`, :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>`, and :ref:`searchpanel "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/searchpanel>`."
msgstr ""
"Qidiruv ko'rinishlari quyidagi bola elementlarini qabul qiladi: :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/field>`, :ref:`filter "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>`, :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/separator>`, :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>` va :ref:`searchpanel "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/searchpanel>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1792
msgid "`field`: filter based on field values"
msgstr "`field`: maydon qiymatlari asosida filtrlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1794
msgid ""
"The `field` element defines domains or contexts with user-provided "
"values. When search domains are generated, field domains are joined with "
"each other and with filters using the **AND** operator."
msgstr ""
"`field` elementi foydalanuvchi tomonidan berilgan qiymatlar bilan domenlar "
"yoki kontekstlarni belgilaydi. Qidiruv domenlari yaratilganda, maydon "
"domenlari bir-biri bilan va filtrlar bilan **AND** operatori orqali birlashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1808
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2203
msgid "The name of the field to filter on."
msgstr "Filtrlash uchun maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1818
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"By default, fields generate domains of the form :samp:`[(name, "
"{operator}, value)]`, where `name` is the field's name and `value` is the"
" value provided by the user, possibly filtered or transformed (e.g., a "
"user is expected to provide the *label* of a selection field's value, not"
" the value itself)."
msgstr ""
"Odatda, maydonlar :samp:`[(name, {operator}, value)]` shaklida domenlar "
"yaratadi, bu yerda `name` maydon nomi va `value` foydalanuvchi tomonidan "
"berilgan qiymat bo'lib, u ehtimol filtrlanadi yoki o'zgartiriladi (masalan, "
"foydalanuvchidan tanlash maydon qiymatining *yorlig'ini*, qiymatning o'zini "
"emas, taqdim etishi kutiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1823
msgid ""
"The `operator` attribute allows overriding the default operator, which "
"depends on the field's type (e.g., `=` for float fields, but `ilike` for "
"char fields and `child_of` for many2one)."
msgstr ""
"`operator` atributi standart operaterni bekor qilish imkonini beradi, bu "
"maydon turiga bog'liq (masalan, float maydonlari uchun `=`, lekin char "
"maydonlari uchun `ilike` va many2one uchun `child_of`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1828
msgid "`=`"
msgstr "`=`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1833
msgid ""
"The domain to use as the field's search domain, as a Python expression "
"that evaluates to a :ref:`domain <reference/orm/domains>`."
msgstr ""
"Maydonning qidiruv domeni sifatida ishlatiladigan domen, "
":ref:`domen <reference/orm/domains>` ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1836
msgid ""
"It  can use the `self` variable to inject the provided value in the "
"custom domain. It can be used to generate significantly more flexible "
"domains than with the `operator` attribute alone (e.g., search on "
"multiple fields at once)."
msgstr ""
"U maxsus domenga berilgan qiymatni kiritish uchun `self` o'zgaruvchisidan "
"foydalanishi mumkin. Bu faqat `operator` atributiga qaraganda ancha moslashuvchan "
"domenlarni yaratish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin (masalan, bir vaqtning o'zida "
"bir nechta maydon bo'yicha qidirish)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1840
msgid ""
"If both the `operator` and `filter_domain` attributes are provided, "
"`filter_domain` takes precedence."
msgstr ""
"`operator` va `filter_domain` atributlari ikkalasi ham berilgan bo'lsa, "
"`filter_domain` ustuvorlikka ega bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1850
msgid ""
"The context to merge into the context of the view that the search view is"
" targeting, as a Python expression that evaluates to a dict."
msgstr ""
"Qidiruv ko'rinishi nishon qiladigan ko'rinish kontekstiga qo'shiladigan "
"kontekst, dict ga baholanadigan Python ifodasi sifatida."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1853
msgid ""
"It can contain user-provided values, which are available under the `self`"
" variable."
msgstr ""
"U `self` o'zgaruvchisi ostida mavjud bo'lgan foydalanuvchi tomonidan "
"berilgan qiymatlarni o'z ichiga olishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1862
msgid ""
"The filters to apply to the completion results for fields that allow for "
"auto-completion (e.g., :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one`)."
msgstr ""
"Avtomatik to'ldirishga ruxsat beradigan maydonlar uchun to'ldirish "
"natijalariga qo'llaniladigan filtrlar (masalan, :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one`)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1893
msgid "`filter`: create pre-defined filters"
msgstr "`filter`: oldindan belgilangan filtrlar yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1895
msgid ""
"The `filter` element is used to create pre-defined filters that can be "
"toggled in the search view. It allows adding data to the search context "
":dfn:`the context passed to the data view for searching/filtering`, or "
"appending new sections to the search filter."
msgstr ""
"`filter` elementi qidiruv ko'rinishida almashtiriladigan oldindan belgilangan "
"filtrlar yaratish uchun ishlatiladi. U qidiruv kontekstiga "
":dfn:`qidirish/filtrlash uchun ma'lumotlar ko'rinishiga o'tkazilgan kontekst` "
"ma'lumotlar qo'shish yoki qidiruv filtriga yangi bo'limlar qo'shish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1905
msgid "The `filter` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`filter` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1910
msgid ""
"The technical name of the filter. It can be used to :ref:`enable it by "
"default <reference/view_architectures/search/defaults>` or as an "
":ref:`inheritance hook <reference/view_records/inheritance>`."
msgstr ""
"Filtrning texnik nomi. U :ref:`odatda uni yoqish "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/defaults>` yoki :ref:`meros ilgagi "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance>` sifatida ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1920
msgid "The label of the filter."
msgstr "Filtr yorlig'i."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1928
msgid "The tooltip displayed when hovering the filter."
msgstr "Filtri ustiga sichqoncha olib borilaganda ko'rinadigan maslahat."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1937
msgid "The domain to append to the action's domain as part of the search domain."
msgstr "Qidiruv domenining bir qismi sifatida amal domeniga qo'shilajak domen."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1946
msgid "The name of the `date` or `datetime` field to filter on."
msgstr "Filtrlash uchun `date` yoki `datetime` maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1948
msgid ""
"When used, this attribute creates a set of filters available in a sub-"
"menu of the :guilabel:`Filters` menu. The available filters are time-"
"dependent but not dynamic in the sense that their domains are evaluated "
"at the time of the control panel instantiation."
msgstr ""
"Ishlatilganda, bu atribut :guilabel:`Filtrlar` menyusining quyi menyusida "
"mavjud bo'lgan filtrlar to'plamini yaratadi. Mavjud filtrlar vaqtga bog'liq, "
"lekin dinamik emas, ya'ni ularning domenlari boshqaruv paneli nusxalanish "
"vaqtida baholanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1957
msgid ""
"By default, these filters contain a dropdown with different sub-filters "
"that allow you to filter based on months, quarters and years. "
"Additionally, you can create custom sub-filters that allow filtering "
"using domains. These custom filters must have the following attributes: "
"`name`, `string` and `domain`."
msgstr ""
"Odatda, bu filtrlar oylar, choraklar va yillar asosida filtrlash imkonini "
"beruvchi turli quyi filtrlar bilan ochiladigan menyu o'z ichiga oladi. "
"Bundan tashqari, domenlar yordamida filtrlash imkonini beruvchi maxsus "
"quyi filtrlar yaratish mumkin. Bu maxsus filtrlar quyidagi atributlarga ega "
"bo'lishi kerak: `name`, `string` va `domain`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1968
msgid ""
"Note that all custom filters defined this way are mutually exclusive with"
" each other and with the other sub-filters."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor bering, shu tarzda belgilangan barcha maxsus filtrlar bir-biri "
"bilan va boshqa quyi filtrlar bilan o'zaro eksklyuziv ekanligini unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1977
msgid ""
"The earliest month that will show up in the dropdown of a date filter, as"
" an offset relative to the current month."
msgstr ""
"Joriy oyga nisbatan ofset sifatida sana filtrining ochiladigan menyusida "
"ko'rinadigan eng erta oy."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1984
msgid ""
"If the current month is February, the earliest month selectable in the "
"dropdown will be November."
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy oy fevral bo'lsa, ochiladigan menyuda tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"eng erta oy noyabr bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1988
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2022
