msgstr "`-2`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1989
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2006
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2023
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2040
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2072
msgid "Filters with a non-empty `date` attribute"
msgstr "Bo'sh bo'lmagan `date` atributiga ega filtrlar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:1994
msgid ""
"The latest month that will show up in the dropdown of a date filter, as "
"an offset relative to the current month."
msgstr ""
"Joriy oyga nisbatan ofset sifatida sana filtrining ochiladigan menyusida "
"ko'rinadigan eng so'nggi oy."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2001
msgid ""
"If the current month is February, the latest month selectable in the "
"dropdown will be March."
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy oy fevral bo'lsa, ochiladigan menyuda tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"eng so'nggi oy mart bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2011
msgid ""
"The earliest year that will show up in the dropdown of a date filter, as "
"an offset relative to the current year."
msgstr ""
"Joriy yilga nisbatan ofset sifatida sana filtrining ochiladigan menyusida "
"ko'rinadigan eng erta yil."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2018
msgid ""
"If the current year is 2024, the earliest year selectable in the dropdown"
" will be 2021."
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy yil 2024 bo'lsa, ochiladigan menyuda tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"eng erta yil 2021 bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2028
msgid ""
"The latest year that will show up in the dropdown of a date filter, as an"
" offset relative to the current year."
msgstr ""
"Joriy yilga nisbatan ofset sifatida sana filtrining ochiladigan menyusida "
"ko'rinadigan eng so'nggi yil."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2035
msgid ""
"If the current year is 2024, the latest year selectable in the dropdown "
"will be 2025."
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy yil 2024 bo'lsa, ochiladigan menyuda tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"eng so'nggi yil 2025 bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2045
msgid ""
"The default period of the time-based filter (with a `date` attribute). It"
" must be one of, or a comma-separated list of valid filter ids."
msgstr ""
"Vaqtga asoslangan filtrning (`date` atributli) standart davri. U to'g'ri "
"filtr id laridan biri yoki vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2048
msgid "Valid filter ids include the following:"
msgstr "To'g'ri filtr id lari quyidagilarni o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2050
msgid "`first_quarter`, `second_quarter`, `third_quarter` and `fourth_quarter`."
msgstr "`first_quarter`, `second_quarter`, `third_quarter` va `fourth_quarter`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2051
msgid ""
"One of `month`, `month-x` and `month+x`, where `x` is a non-zero integer "
"value between `start_month` and `end_month`."
msgstr ""
"`month`, `month-x` va `month+x` laridan biri, bu yerda `x` `start_month` "
"va `end_month` orasidagi nolga teng bo'lmagan butun son qiymati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2052
msgid ""
"One of `year`, `year-x` and `year+x`, where `x` is a non-zero integer "
"value between `start_year` and `end_year`."
msgstr ""
"`year`, `year-x` va `year+x` laridan biri, bu yerda `x` `start_year` "
"va `end_year` orasidagi nolga teng bo'lmagan butun son qiymati."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2053
msgid ""
"The `name` of any custom filter defined within the filter, prepended with"
" `custom_`."
msgstr ""
"Filtr ichida belgilangan maxsus filtrning `nomi`, `custom_` bilan prefikslanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2055
msgid ""
"The filter must be in the default set of filters activated at the view "
"initialization."
msgstr ""
"Filtr ko'rinish ishga tushirilganda faollashtiriladigan standart filtrlar "
"to'plamida bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2071
msgid "`month`, or the closest value to the current month if unavailable"
msgstr "`month`, yoki mavjud bo'lmasa joriy oyga eng yaqin qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2081
msgid "The context merged into the action's domain to generate the search domain"
msgstr "Qidiruv domenini yaratish uchun amal domeniga qo'shiladigan kontekst"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2083
msgid ""
"The context key `group_by` set with a field as value can be used to "
"define a group available in the :guilabel:`Group By` menu. When the field"
" is of type `date` or `datetime`, the filter generates a submenu of the "
":guilabel:`Group By` menu with the following interval options available: "
":guilabel:`Year`, :guilabel:`Quarter`, :guilabel:`Month`, "
":guilabel:`Week`, and :guilabel:`Day`."
msgstr ""
"Maydon qiymati sifatida o'rnatilgan `group_by` kontekst kaliti :guilabel:`Guruhlash` "
"menyusida mavjud bo'lgan guruhni aniqlash uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Maydon "
"`date` yoki `datetime` turida bo'lsa, filtr quyidagi interval parametrlari "
"bilan :guilabel:`Guruhlash` menyusining quyi menyusini yaratadi: :guilabel:`Yil`, "
":guilabel:`Chorak`, :guilabel:`Oy`, :guilabel:`Hafta` va :guilabel:`Kun`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2096
msgid ""
"The results of `formatted_read_group` grouped on a field may be "
"influenced by its `group_expand` attribute, allowing to display empty "
"groups when needed. For more information, please refer to "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Field`."
msgstr ""
"Maydon bo'yicha guruhlangan `formatted_read_group` natijalari uning "
"`group_expand` atributi ta'sirida bo'lishi mumkin, kerak bo'lganda bo'sh "
"guruhlarni ko'rsatishga imkon beradi. Ko'proq ma'lumot uchun "
":class:`~odoo.fields.Field` ga murojaat qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2105
msgid ""
"Sequences of filters (without non-filters elements separating them) are "
"treated as inclusively composited: they will be composed with `OR` rather"
" than the usual `AND`."
msgstr ""
"Filtrlar ketma-ketligi (ularni ajratuvchi filtr bo'lmagan elementlarsiz) "
"inklyuziv birlashtirilgan sifatida ko'rib chiqiladi: ular odatdagi `AND` "
"o'rniga `OR` bilan birlashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2114
msgid "Records whose `state` field is `draft` or `done` are shown."
msgstr "`state` maydoni `draft` yoki `done` bo'lgan yozuvlar ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2123
msgid "Records whose `state` field is `draft` **and** `delay` field is below 15."
msgstr "`state` maydoni `draft` **va** `delay` maydoni 15 dan past bo'lgan yozuvlar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2144
msgid "`separator`: separate groups of filters"
msgstr "`separator`: filtrlar guruhlarini ajratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2146
msgid ""
"The `separator` element is used to separates groups of :ref:`filters "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>` in simple search views. For"
" more complex search views, the :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>` element is recommended."
msgstr ""
"`separator` elementi oddiy qidiruv ko'rinishlarida :ref:`filtrlar "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>` guruhlarini ajratish uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Murakkabroq qidiruv ko'rinishlari uchun :ref:`group "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>` elementi tavsiya etiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2158
msgid "The `separator` element takes no attributes."
msgstr "`separator` elementi atributlarni qabul qilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2163
msgid "`group`: separate groups of filters"
msgstr "`group`: filtrlar guruhlarini ajratish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2165
msgid ""
"The `group` element is used to separate groups of :ref:`filters "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>` in cluttered search views. "
"In simpler search views, it can be substituted for the :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>` element."
msgstr ""
"`group` elementi to'liq qidiruv ko'rinishlarida :ref:`filtrlar "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/filter>` guruhlarini ajratish uchun "
"ishlatiladi. Oddiyroq qidiruv ko'rinishlarida u :ref:`separator "
"<reference/view_architectures/search/group>` elementi o'rniga ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2177
msgid "The `group` element takes no attributes."
msgstr "`group` elementi atributlarni qabul qilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2182
msgid "`searchpanel`: display search panels"
msgstr "`searchpanel`: qidiruv panellarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2184
msgid ""
"The `searchpanel` element displays a search panel to the left of multi-"
"records views. It allows for quickly filtering data on the basis of given"
" fields."
msgstr ""
"`searchpanel` elementi ko'p yozuvli ko'rinishlar chapida qidiruv panelini "
"ko'rsatadi. U berilgan maydonlar asosida ma'lumotlarni tezda filtrlash "
"imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2195
msgid "The `searchpanel` element accepts only `field` children elements."
msgstr "`searchpanel` elementi faqat `field` bola elementlarini qabul qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2197
msgid ""
"The `field` element used as a child element of a `searchpanel` element "
"can have the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"`searchpanel` elementi bola elementi sifatida ishlatiladigan `field` "
"elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2213
msgid "The behavior and display of the field. It can have two different values:"
msgstr "Maydonning xatti-harakati va ko'rinishi. U ikki xil qiymatga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2218
msgid ""
"At most one value can be selected. Supported field types are `many2one` "
"and `selection`."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pi bilan bitta qiymat tanlanishi mumkin. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon "
"turlari: `many2one` va `selection`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2223
msgid ""
"Several values can be selected. Supported field types are `many2one`, "
"`many2many` and `selection`."
msgstr ""
"Bir nechta qiymat tanlanishi mumkin. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan maydon turlari: "
"`many2one`, `many2many` va `selection`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2228
msgid "`one`"
msgstr "`one`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2235
msgid "The icon of the field."
msgstr "Maydonning ikonasi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2244
msgid "The color of the field."
msgstr "Maydonning rangi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2250
msgid ""
"When the `field` element has the `select=one` attribute set, it can have "
"the following additional attributes:"
msgstr ""
"`field` elementida `select=one` atributi o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, quyidagi "
"qo'shimcha atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2256
msgid ""
"Whether child categories should appear under their parent category, or at"
" the same hierarchy level."
msgstr ""
"Bola kategoriyalar ota kategoriya ostida yoki bir xil ierarxiya darajasida "
"ko'rinishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2262
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2272
msgid ":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` fields"
msgstr ":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` maydonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2267
msgid ""
"If set to a non zero integer, the hierarchy (if any) will be unfold up to"
" the given level."
msgstr ""
"Nolga teng bo'lmagan butun songacha o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, ierarxiya (agar "
"mavjud bo'lsa) berilgan darajagacha ochilib ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2270
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2274
msgid ""
"When the `field` element has the `select=multi` attribute set, it can "
"have the following additional attributes:"
msgstr ""
"`field` elementida `select=multi` atributi o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, quyidagi "
"qo'shimcha atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2280
msgid "Whether the record counters is computed and displayed if non-zero."
msgstr "Yozuv hisoblagichlari hisoblanib, noldan farq qilsa ko'rsatilishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2283
msgid ""
"This attribute exists to avoid impacting performance. Another way to "
"address performance issues is to override the `search_panel_select_range`"
" and `search_panel_select_multi_range` methods."
msgstr ""
"Bu atribut ishlashga ta'sir qilmaslik uchun mavjud. Ishlash muammolarini "
"hal qilishning yana bir usuli — `search_panel_select_range` va "
"`search_panel_select_multi_range` metodlarini bekor qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2294
msgid "Whether categories and filters with no records should be shown."
msgstr "Yozuvsiz kategoriyalar va filtrlar ko'rsatilishi kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2303
msgid ""
"The maximal number of values to fetch for the field. If the limit is "
"reached, no values are displayed on the search panel, and an error "
"message is shown instead. If set to 0, all values are fetched."
msgstr ""
"Maydon uchun olinadigan maksimal qiymatlar soni. Chegaraga yetilsa, qidiruv "
"panelida hech qanday qiymat ko'rsatilmaydi va o'rniga xato xabari ko'rsatiladi. "
"0 ga o'rnatilsa, barcha qiymatlar olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2309
msgid "`200`"
msgstr "`200`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2314
msgid "The conditions that the records have to satisfy."
msgstr "Yozuvlar bajarishi kerak bo'lgan shartlar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2331
msgid "The name of the field name on which values should be grouped."
msgstr "Qiymatlar guruhlaniladigan maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2336
msgid ":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` and :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` fields"
msgstr ":class:`~odoo.fields.Many2one` va :class:`~odoo.fields.Many2many` maydonlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2341
msgid "Search defaults"
msgstr "Qidiruv standartlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2343
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Search fields and filters can be configured through the action's "
"`context` using :samp:`search_default_{name}` keys. For fields, the value"
" must be the value to set to the field. For filters, it must be a boolean"
" value or a number."
msgstr ""
"Qidiruv maydonlari va filtrlari :samp:`search_default_{name}` kalitlaridan "
"foydalangan holda amalning `context` orqali sozlanishi mumkin. Maydonlar "
"uchun qiymat maydonga o'rnatiladigan qiymat bo'lishi kerak. Filtrlar uchun "
"esa u boolean qiymat yoki son bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2348
msgid ""
"With `foo`, a field, and `bar`, a filter, the following action context "
"will search `foo` on `acro` and enable `bar` by default:"
msgstr ""
"`foo` maydon va `bar` filtr bilan quyidagi amal konteksti odatda `foo` ni "
"`acro` da qidiradi va `bar` ni yoqadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2358
msgid ""
"A numeric value (between 1 and 99) can be used to define the order of "
"default *groupby* filters."
msgstr ""
"Standart *groupby* filtrlar tartibini aniqlash uchun raqamli qiymat "
"(1 dan 99 gacha) ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2361
msgid ""
"With `foo` and `bar`, two *groupby* filters, the following action context"
" will first enable `bar`, then `foo`."
msgstr ""
"`foo` va `bar`, ikki *groupby* filtr bilan quyidagi amal konteksti avval "
"`bar` ni, keyin `foo` ni yoqadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2374
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1043
msgid "Kanban"
msgstr "Kanban"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2376
msgid ""
"Kanban views are used as a `kanban board "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanban_board>`_ visualisation: they "
"display records as \"cards\", halfway between a :ref:`list "
"<reference/view_architectures/list>` and a :ref:`form "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` view."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishlari `kanban taxtasi "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanban_board>`_ vizualizatsiyasi sifatida "
"ishlatiladi: ular yozuvlarni :ref:`ro'yxat "
"<reference/view_architectures/list>` va :ref:`forma "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` ko'rinishlari orasidagi o'rtacha "
"\"kartochkalar\" sifatida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2380
msgid ""
"Records may be grouped in columns for use in workflow visualisation or "
"manipulation (e.g., tasks or work-progress management), or ungrouped "
"(used simply to visualize records)."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar ish jarayonini vizualizatsiya qilish yoki boshqarish uchun "
"(masalan, vazifalar yoki ish jarayonini boshqarish) ustunlarda guruhlanishi "
"yoki guruhlanmagan holda (shunchaki yozuvlarni vizualizatsiya qilish) "
"ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2383
msgid "The root element of Kanban views is `kanban`."
msgstr "Kanban ko'rinishlarining ildiz elementi `kanban` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2400
msgid ""
"Kanban views load and display a maximum of ten columns. Any column after "
"that is closed but can still be opened by the user."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishlari maksimal o'nta ustunni yuklab ko'rsatadi. Undan keyingi "
"har qanday ustun yopiq, lekin foydalanuvchi tomonidan ochilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2408
msgid ""
"Optional attributes can be added to the root element `kanban` to "
"customize the view."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishni sozlashtirish uchun `kanban` ildiz elementiga ixtiyoriy "
"atributlar qo'shilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2425
msgid "Add HTML classes to the root HTML element of the view."
msgstr "Ko'rinishning ildiz HTML elementiga HTML klasslar qo'shish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2434
msgid ""
"The key in the `KanbanExamplesRegistry` of the examples that can be "
"browsed when creating a new column in the grouped kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Guruhlangan kanban ko'rinishida yangi ustun yaratishda ko'rib chiqilishi "
"mumkin bo'lgan misollarning `KanbanExamplesRegistry` dagi kaliti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2438
msgid ""
"`Use of the examples attribute in the utm module "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/utm/static/src/js/utm_campaign_kanban_examples.js>`_"
msgstr ""
"`utm modulida examples atributidan foydalanish "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/19.0/addons/utm/static/src/js/utm_campaign_kanban_examples.js>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2448
msgid "Whether the :guilabel:`Add a new column` bar is visible."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Yangi ustun qo'shish` paneli ko'rinadimi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2457
msgid "Whether columns can be deleted via the cog menu."
msgstr "Ustunlar tishli g'ildirak menyusi orqali o'chirilishi mumkinmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2466
msgid "Whether columns can be edited via the cog menu."
msgstr "Ustunlar tishli g'ildirak menyusi orqali tahrirlash mumkinmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2475
msgid "Whether columns can be reordered."
msgstr "Ustunlar qayta tartiblanishi mumkinmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2484
msgid "Whether records can be dragged when the kanban view is grouped."
msgstr "Kanban ko'rinishi guruhlanganda yozuvlar sudrab olinishi mumkinmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2493
msgid ""
"Whether records belonging to a column can be archived and unarchived when"
" the `active` field is defined on the model."
msgstr ""
"Modelda `active` maydon belgilanganida ustunga tegishli yozuvlar "
"arxivlanishi va arxivdan chiqarilishi mumkinmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2503
msgid ""
"Whether it should be possible to create records without switching to the "
"form view."
msgstr ""
"Forma ko'rinishiga o'tmasdan yozuvlar yaratish imkoniyati mavjud bo'lishi "
"kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2507
msgid ""
"`True` when the kanban view is grouped by many2one, selection, char, or "
"boolean fields, otherwise `False`"
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishi many2one, selection, char yoki boolean maydonlar bo'yicha "
"guruhlanganda `True`, aks holda `False`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2513
msgid ""
"The reference of the :ref:`form <reference/view_architectures/form>` view"
" to open when using the quick creation of records."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlarni tez yaratishda ochiladigan :ref:`forma "
"<reference/view_architectures/form>` ko'rinishiga havola."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2523
msgid "The custom action to call when clicking on :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Yaratish` tugmasini bosganda chaqiriladigan maxsus amal."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2525
msgid ""
"If set to `'quick_create'`, the quick creation of records is used "
"instead. If the quick creation is disabled, the standard create action is"
" called."
msgstr ""
"`'quick_create'` ga o'rnatilsa, o'rniga yozuvlarni tez yaratish ishlatiladi. "
"Agar tez yaratish o'chirilgan bo'lsa, standart yaratish amali chaqiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2535
msgid ""
"By default, clicking on a kanban card opens the corresponding record in a"
" form view. This behavior can be disabled by setting the attribute "
"`can_open` to `False`."
msgstr ""
"Odatda, kanban kartochkasini bosish tegishli yozuvni forma ko'rinishida "
"ochadi. Bu xatti-harakat `can_open` atributini `False` ga o'rnatish orqali "
"o'chirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2545
msgid ""
"Name of the integer field used to color the left border of the kanban "
"cards."
msgstr "Kanban kartochkalarining chap chegarasini ranglash uchun ishlatiladigan butun son maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2557
msgid ""
"Kanban views accept the following children elements: :ref:`templates "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/templates>`, :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/field>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/header>`, :ref:`progressbar "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/progressbar>`."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishlari quyidagi bola elementlarini qabul qiladi: :ref:`templates "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/templates>`, :ref:`field "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/field>`, :ref:`header "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/header>`, :ref:`progressbar "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/progressbar>`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2566
msgid "`templates`: define cards structure"
msgstr "`templates`: kartochkalar tuzilmasini aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2568
msgid ""
"The `templates` element is used to define the :ref:`QWeb templates "
"<reference/qweb>` that structure the kanban cards."
msgstr ""
"`templates` elementi kanban kartochkalarini tuzuvchi :ref:`QWeb shablonlarini "
"<reference/qweb>` aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2571
msgid ""
"The definition of a card's structure can be split into multiple templates"
" for clarity, but at least one root `card` template must be defined."
msgstr ""
"Kartochka tuzilmasining ta'rifi aniqlik uchun bir nechta shablonga bo'linishi "
"mumkin, lekin kamida bitta ildiz `card` shabloni aniqlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2574
msgid ""
"An additional template can be defined: `menu`. If defined, it is rendered"
" inside a dropdown that can be toggled with a vertical ellipsis "
"(:guilabel:`⋮`) on the top right of the card."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shimcha shablon aniqlanishi mumkin: `menu`. Aniqlangan bo'lsa, u "
"kartochkaning yuqori o'ng qismidagi vertikal ellipsis (:guilabel:`⋮`) bilan "
"almashtiriladigan ochiladigan menyu ichida renderlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2577
msgid ""
"The templates are written in :ref:`JavaScript QWeb "
"<reference/qweb/javascript>`."
msgstr ""
"Shablonlar :ref:`JavaScript QWeb <reference/qweb/javascript>` da yoziladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2591
msgid ""
"These are QWeb templates, not `Owl <https://github.com/odoo/owl>`_ "
"templates, meaning that directives like `t-on-click` aren't available."
msgstr ""
"Bular QWeb shablonlari, `Owl <https://github.com/odoo/owl>`_ shablonlari "
"emas, ya'ni `t-on-click` kabi ko'rsatmalar mavjud emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2597
msgid ""
"Inside those templates, the `field` element allows to render a field. It "
"can have the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Bu shablonlar ichida `field` elementi maydonni renderlash imkonini beradi. "
"U quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2602
msgid ""
"By default, field nodes are replaced by a `span` containing their "
"formatted value, unless the `widget` attribute is specified, in which "
"case their rendering and behavior depends on the corresponding widget. "
"The `widget` attribute can have different values including:"
msgstr ""
"Odatda, maydon tugunlari formatlangan qiymatlarini o'z ichiga olgan `span` "
"bilan almashtiriladi, agar `widget` atributi belgilanmagan bo'lsa. `widget` "
"belgilangan bo'lsa, ularning renderlashi va xatti-harakati tegishli vidjetga "
"bog'liq. `widget` atributi quyidagilarni o'z ichiga olgan turli qiymatlarga "
"ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2609
msgid ""
"Allows reordering records with a drag and drop, using the corresponding "
"field as order."
msgstr ""
"Tegishli maydonni tartib sifatida ishlatib, sudrab va tushirish orqali "
"yozuvlarni qayta tartiblaish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2614
msgid ""
"Allows editing a color (integer) field. Combined with the root attribute "
"`highlight_color`, allows editing the color of the cards."
msgstr ""
"Rang (butun son) maydonini tahrirlash imkonini beradi. `highlight_color` "
"ildiz atributi bilan birgalikda kartochkalar rangini tahrirlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2617
msgid ""
"See the :ref:`Field section <reference/js/widgets>` to discover various "
"widgets and their options."
msgstr ""
"Turli vidjetlar va ularning parametrlarini aniqlash uchun :ref:`Maydon "
"bo'limiga <reference/js/widgets>` qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2621
msgid "Rendering Context"
msgstr "Renderlash konteksti"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2623
msgid ""
"Kanban templates being rendered with the :ref:`QWeb engine "
"<reference/qweb/javascript>`, they have a *rendering context*, a set of "
"variables available in the templates, containing useful information and "
"tools. Here're the available variables:"
msgstr ""
":ref:`QWeb mexanizmi <reference/qweb/javascript>` bilan renderlangan kanban "
"shablonlarida foydali ma'lumot va vositalarni o'z ichiga olgan shablonlarda "
"mavjud bo'lgan o'zgaruvchilar to'plami — *renderlash konteksti* mavjud. "
"Mavjud o'zgaruvchilar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2630
msgid ""
"An object with all the fields defined in the view. Each field has two "
"attributes: `value` and `raw_value`. The former is formatted according to"
" current user parameters, while the latter is the raw value (e.g. the "
"`id` for a many2one field). This object is useful for instance, for using"
" field values inside `t-if` conditions. For display purposes, we "
"recommend using the `<field>` tag."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishda belgilangan barcha maydonlari bo'lgan obyekt. Har bir maydonning "
"ikki atributi bor: `value` va `raw_value`. Birinchisi joriy foydalanuvchi "
"parametrlariga ko'ra formatlangan, ikkinchisi esa xom qiymat (masalan, "
"many2one maydon uchun `id`). Bu obyekt, masalan, `t-if` shartlarida maydon "
"qiymatlarini ishlatish uchun foydali. Ko'rsatish maqsadida `<field>` tagidan "
"foydalanishni tavsiya etamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2652
msgid "An object with 2 keys defining the available actions for the user:"
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi uchun mavjud amallarni belgilovchi 2 ta kalitli obyekt:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2654
msgid "`editable`: true if the user can edit records, false otherwise;"
msgstr "`editable`: foydalanuvchi yozuvlarni tahrirlashi mumkin bo'lsa true, aks holda false;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2655
msgid "`deletable`: true if the user can delete records, false otherwise."
msgstr "`deletable`: foydalanuvchi yozuvlarni o'chirishi mumkin bo'lsa true, aks holda false."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2657
msgid ""
"This is useful to conditionally display elements requiring specific "
"access rights."
msgstr "Bu muayyan kirish huquqlarini talab qiluvchi elementlarni shartli ko'rsatish uchun foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2676
msgid ""
"The current context propagated from either the action that opens the "
"kanban view, or the one2many or many2many field that embeds the kanban "
"view in a form view."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishini ochadigan amaldan yoki kanban ko'rinishini forma "
"ko'rinishiga kiritadigan one2many yoki many2many maydondan tarqalgan joriy kontekst."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2682
msgid "Indicates that the view is readonly."
msgstr "Ko'rinish faqat o'qish uchun ekanligini ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2689
msgid ""
"Whether the kanban view is opened when selecting a many2one or many2many "
"field (in mobile environment)."
msgstr ""
"Mobil muhitda many2one yoki many2many maydon tanlanganida kanban "
"ko'rinishi ochilish kerakmi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2697
msgid ""
"The `luxon <https://moment.github.io/luxon/api-docs/index.html>`_ object,"
" allowing to manipulate date and datetime field values."
msgstr ""
"Sana va datetime maydon qiymatlarini manipulyatsiya qilish imkonini beruvchi "
"`luxon <https://moment.github.io/luxon/api-docs/index.html>`_ obyekti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2703
msgid ""
"The Javascript `JSON <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON>`_ namespace object "
"containing a `parse` method allowing to parse json field values into "
"Javascript Objects."
msgstr ""
"JSON maydon qiymatlarini Javascript Obyektlariga tahlil qilishga imkon "
"beruvchi `parse` metodini o'z ichiga olgan Javascript "
"`JSON <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON>`_ "
"nom maydoni obyekti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2708
msgid "Buttons and links"
msgstr "Tugmalar va havolalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2710
msgid ""
"While most of the kanban templates are standard :ref:`QWeb templates "
"<reference/qweb>`, the kanban view processes `button` and `a` elements is"
" a special way. Buttons and links with a `type` attribute perform "
"different operations than their standard HTML function. The `type` "
"attribute can have the values `action` and `object` of :ref:`regular "
"buttons <reference/view_architectures/list/button>`, or the following "
"values:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik kanban shablonlari standart :ref:`QWeb shablonlari "
"<reference/qweb>` bo'lsada, kanban ko'rinishi `button` va `a` elementlarini "
"maxsus usulda qayta ishlaydi. `type` atributiga ega tugmalar va havolalar "
"standart HTML funksiyasidan farqli operatsiyalarni bajaradi. `type` atributi "
":ref:`oddiy tugmalar <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` ning "
"`action` va `object` qiymatlarini yoki quyidagi qiymatlarni qabul qilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2719
msgid "Clicking the element opens the card's record in form view."
msgstr "Elementni bosish kartochka yozuvini forma ko'rinishida ochadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2724
msgid "Clicking the element deletes the card's record and removes the card."
msgstr "Elementni bosish kartochka yozuvini o'chiradi va kartochkani olib tashlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2729
msgid "Clicking the element archives the card's record and removes the card."
msgstr "Elementni bosish kartochka yozuvini arxivlaydi va kartochkani olib tashlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2734
msgid "Clicking the element unarchives the card's record and removes the card."
msgstr "Elementni bosish kartochka yozuvini arxivdan chiqaradi va kartochkani olib tashlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2739
msgid ""
"Clicking the element allows to select an image to set as cover image of "
"the record."
msgstr "Elementni bosish yozuvning muqova rasmi sifatida o'rnatilacak rasmni tanlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2744
msgid ""
"The `widget` element allows to insert dynamically generated (in "
"Javascript) html inside the cards. It has a mandatory `name` attribute, "
"referring to a Javascript implementation (an Owl component) registered to"
" the `view_widgets` registry."
msgstr ""
"`widget` elementi kartochkalar ichiga dinamik ravishda yaratilgan (Javascript "
"da) html kiritish imkonini beradi. U `view_widgets` registriga ro'yxatdan "
"o'tgan Javascript realizatsiyasiga (Owl komponentiga) murojaat qiluvchi "
"majburiy `name` atributiga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2750
msgid ""
"See the :ref:`Widget section "
"<reference/javascript_reference/view_widgets>` to discover various "
"widgets and their options."
msgstr ""
"Turli vidjetlar va ularning parametrlarini aniqlash uchun :ref:`Vidjet "
"bo'limiga <reference/javascript_reference/view_widgets>` qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2754
msgid "Layouts"
msgstr "Sxemalar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2756
msgid ""
"Several card layouts can be easily obtained using standard html elements "
"and `Bootstrap utility classes "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/utilities/api/>`_. By default, the "
"card is a `flexbox container <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_flexible_box_layout/Basic_concepts_of_flexbox>`_ with"
" `column` direction."
msgstr ""
"Standart html elementlari va `Bootstrap utility klasslari "
"<https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/utilities/api/>`_ yordamida bir nechta "
"kartochka sxemalarini osongina olish mumkin. Odatda kartochka `column` "
"yo'nalishli `flexbox konteyneri "
"<https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_flexible_box_layout/Basic_concepts_of_flexbox>`_ dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2774
msgid ""
"The `footer` html element is styled to stick to the bottom of the card, "
"and is as a flexbox container with `row` direction, allowing to easily "
"display several fields on the same line."
msgstr ""
"`footer` html elementi kartochkaning pastiga yopishish uchun uslublangan "
"va `row` yo'nalishli flexbox konteyneri bo'lib, bir qatorda bir nechta "
"maydonlarni osongina ko'rsatish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2794
msgid ""
"To display some content, like an image, on the side of the card, one can "
"use `aside` and `main` html elements, with the `flex-row` classname on "
"the card. The `main` node is a flexbox container like the card is when "
"there's no `aside`."
msgstr ""
"Kartochka tomonida rasm kabi ba'zi kontentni ko'rsatish uchun kartochadagi "
"`flex-row` klasi bilan `aside` va `main` html elementlarini ishlatish mumkin. "
"`main` tugun `aside` bo'lmagan holda kartochkaga o'xshash flexbox konteyner."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2821
msgid ""
"The classname `o_kanban_aside_full` set on the `aside` element removes "
"the padding so that the image spreads to the borders of the card."
msgstr ""
"`aside` elementida o'rnatilgan `o_kanban_aside_full` klasi ichki to'ldirishni "
"olib tashlaydi, shunda rasm kartochkaning chegaralariga yetib boradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2827
msgid "`field`: declare more fields to fetch"
msgstr "`field`: olinadigan qo'shimcha maydonlarni e'lon qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2829
msgid ""
"The `field` element can also be used *outside* the kanban :ref:`templates"
" <reference/view_architectures/kanban/templates>`. In that case, it "
"allows to declare fields that are not displayed in the card, but still "
"need to be fetched, for instance because their value is used in a `t-if` "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"`field` elementi kanban :ref:`shablonlari "
"<reference/view_architectures/kanban/templates>` dan *tashqarida* ham "
"ishlatilishi mumkin. Bu holda u kartochkada ko'rsatilmagan, lekin hali "
"ham olinishi kerak bo'lgan maydonlarni e'lon qilish imkonini beradi, "
"masalan, ularning qiymati `t-if` shartida ishlatilganligi uchun."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2850
msgid "`header`: display buttons in the control panel"
msgstr "`header`: boshqaruv panelida tugmalarni ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2852
msgid ""
"The `header` element is used to insert custom buttons in the control "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"`header` elementi boshqaruv panelida maxsus tugmalar kiritish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2863
msgid ""
"The `header` element accepts only `button` children elements, similar to "
":ref:`list views' button <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"`header` elementi faqat `button` bola elementlarini qabul qiladi, "
":ref:`ro'yxat ko'rinishlarining button <reference/view_architectures/list/button>` "
"elementlariga o'xshash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2866
msgid ""
"The `button` element used as a child element of the `header` element can "
"have the following additional attributes:"
msgstr ""
"`header` elementi bola elementi sifatida ishlatiladigan `button` elementi "
"quyidagi qo'shimcha atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2872
msgid "The display mode of the button. It can have two different values:"
msgstr "Tugmaning ko'rsatish rejimi. U ikki xil qiymatga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2877
msgid ""
"The button is displayed only when some records are selected; their action"
" applies to the selected records."
msgstr ""
"Tugma faqat ba'zi yozuvlar tanlanganda ko'rsatiladi; ularning amali "
"tanlangan yozuvlarga qo'llaniladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2884
msgid "The button is displayed at all times, even if no records are selected."
msgstr "Tugma hech qanday yozuv tanlanmagan bo'lsa ham har doim ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2887
msgid ""
"Only the `always` display mode is available because it is not yet "
"possible to select records in a kanban view."
msgstr ""
"Faqat `always` ko'rsatish rejimi mavjud, chunki kanban ko'rinishida "
"yozuvlarni tanlash hali mumkin emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2900
msgid "`display`"
msgstr "`display`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2905
msgid "`progressbar`: show progress bars on top of columns"
msgstr "`progressbar`: ustunlar tepasida progress barlarini ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2907
msgid ""
"The `progressbar` element is used to define a progress bar to display on "
"top of kanban columns in grouped kanban views."
msgstr ""
"`progressbar` elementi guruhlangan kanban ko'rinishlarida kanban ustunlari "
"tepasida ko'rsatiladigan progress barni aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2917
msgid "The `progressbar` element can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "`progressbar` elementi quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2922
msgid "The name of the field on which the progress bar's sub-groups are based."
msgstr "Progress bar kichik guruhlar asoslanadigan maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2931
msgid ""
"The mapping of the progress bar's field values to the color values "
"`muted`, `success`, `warning`, and `danger`."
msgstr ""
"Progress bar maydon qiymatlarini `muted`, `success`, `warning` va `danger` "
"rang qiymatlariga moslashtirish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2935
msgid ""
"`JSON <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON>`_"
msgstr ""
"`JSON <https://developer.mozilla.org/en-"
"US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/JSON>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2941
msgid ""
"The name of the field to use in a sum displayed next to the progress bar."
" If not set, the total number of records is displayed instead."
msgstr ""
"Progress bar yonida ko'rsatiladigan yig'indida foydalaniladigan maydon nomi. "
"Agar belgilanmagan bo'lsa, yozuvlarning umumiy soni ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2970
msgid "Like for :ref:`list views <reference/view_architectures/list/control>`."
msgstr ":ref:`ro'yxat ko'rinishlari <reference/view_architectures/list/control>` uchun bo'lgani kabi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2973
msgid "kanban-specific CSS"
msgstr "kanban-ga xos CSS"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2974
msgid "kanban structures/widgets (vignette, details, ...)"
msgstr "kanban tuzilmalari/vidjetlar (vignette, details, ...)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2983
msgid ""
"QWeb views are standard :ref:`reference/qweb` templates inside a view's "
"``arch``. They don't have a specific root element. Because QWeb views "
"don't have a specific root element, their type must be specified "
"explicitly (it can not be inferred from the root element of the ``arch`` "
"field)."
msgstr ""
"QWeb ko'rinishlari ko'rinishning ``arch`` ichidagi standart :ref:`reference/qweb` "
"shablonlaridir. Ularda maxsus ildiz elementi yo'q. QWeb ko'rinishlarida maxsus "
"ildiz elementi yo'qligi sababli, ularning turi aniq ko'rsatilishi kerak "
"(``arch`` maydonining ildiz elementidan chiqarib bo'lmaydi)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2988
msgid "QWeb views have two use cases:"
msgstr "QWeb ko'rinishlarining ikkita foydalanish holati mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2990
msgid ""
"they can be used as frontend templates, in which case "
":ref:`reference/data/template` should be used as a shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Ular frontend shablonlari sifatida ishlatilishi mumkin, bunday holda "
":ref:`reference/data/template` yorliq sifatida ishlatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2992
msgid ""
"they can be used as actual qweb views (opened inside an action), in which"
" case they should be defined as regular view with an explicit ``type`` "
"(it can not be inferred) and a model."
msgstr ""
"Ular haqiqiy qweb ko'rinishlari sifatida (amal ichida ochilgan) ishlatilishi mumkin, "
"bunday holda ular aniq ``type`` (chiqarib bo'lmaydi) va model bilan oddiy ko'rinish "
"sifatida aniqlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2996
msgid "The main additions of qweb-as-view to the basic qweb-as-template are:"
msgstr "Asosiy qweb-as-template ga qweb-as-view ning asosiy qo'shimchalari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:2998
msgid ""
"qweb-as-view has a special case for a ``<nav>`` element bearing the CSS "
"class ``o_qweb_cp_buttons``: its contents should be buttons and will be "
"extracted and moved to the control panel's button area, the ``<nav>`` "
"itself will be removed, this is a work-around to control panel views not "
"existing yet"
msgstr ""
"qweb-as-view ``o_qweb_cp_buttons`` CSS klassini ko'taradigan ``<nav>`` elementi "
"uchun maxsus holatga ega: uning mazmuni tugmalar bo'lishi kerak va boshqaruv paneli "
"tugmalar maydoniga olinib ko'chiriladi, ``<nav>`` o'zi o'chiriladi, bu hali mavjud "
"bo'lmagan boshqaruv paneli ko'rinishlari uchun vaqtinchalik yechimdir"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3003
msgid ""
"qweb-as-view rendering adds several items to the standard qweb rendering "
"context:"
msgstr ""
"qweb-as-view ko'rsatish standart qweb ko'rsatish kontekstiga bir nechta elementlar qo'shadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3009
msgid "the model to which the qweb view is bound"
msgstr "qweb ko'rinishi bog'langan model"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3010
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3838
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3887
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3900
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:932
msgid "``domain``"
msgstr "``domain``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3011
msgid "the domain provided by the search view"
msgstr "qidiruv ko'rinishi tomonidan taqdim etilgan domen"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3013
msgid "the context provided by the search view"
msgstr "qidiruv ko'rinishi tomonidan taqdim etilgan kontekst"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3016
msgid "``records``"
msgstr "``records``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3015
msgid ""
"a lazy proxy to ``model.search(domain)``, this can be used if you just "
"want to iterate the records and not perform more complex operations (e.g."
" grouping)"
msgstr ""
"``model.search(domain)`` ga dangasa proksi, bu faqat yozuvlarni aylanib o'tmoqchi "
"bo'lsangiz va murakkabroq amallarni (masalan, guruhlash) bajarmoqchi bo'lmasangiz ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3018
msgid "qweb-as-view also provides additional rendering hooks:"
msgstr "qweb-as-view shuningdek qo'shimcha ko'rsatish qavslarini ham taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3020
msgid ""
"``_qweb_prepare_context(view_id, domain)`` prepares the rendering context"
" specific to qweb-as-view"
msgstr ""
"``_qweb_prepare_context(view_id, domain)`` qweb-as-view ga xos ko'rsatish kontekstini tayyorlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3022
msgid ""
"``qweb_render_view(view_id, domain)`` is the method called by the client "
"and will call the context-preparation methods and ultimately "
"``env['ir.qweb'].render()``."
msgstr ""
"``qweb_render_view(view_id, domain)`` mijoz tomonidan chaqiriladigan usul bo'lib, "
"kontekst-tayyorlash usullarini va oxir-oqibat ``env['ir.qweb'].render()`` ni chaqiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3029
msgid "Graph"
msgstr "Grafik"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3031
msgid ""
"The graph view is used to visualize aggregations over a number of records"
" or record groups. Its root element is ``<graph>`` which can take the "
"following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishi bir qator yozuvlar yoki yozuv guruhlari bo'yicha "
"agregatsiyalarni vizualizatsiya qilish uchun ishlatiladi. Uning ildiz "
"elementi quyidagi atributlarni qabul qilishi mumkin bo'lgan ``<graph>`` dir:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3038
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3074
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3157
msgid "``type`` (optional)"
msgstr "``type`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3038
msgid "one of ``bar`` (default), ``pie`` and ``line``, the type of graph to use"
msgstr "``bar`` (standart), ``pie`` va ``line`` dan biri, foydalaniladigan grafik turi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3042
msgid "``stacked`` (optional)"
msgstr "``stacked`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3041
msgid ""
"only used for ``bar`` charts. Set to ``0`` to prevent the bars within a "
"group to be stacked initially."
msgstr ""
"faqat ``bar`` diagrammalar uchun ishlatiladi. Dastlab guruh ichidagi "
"panellar to'plam bo'lishiga yo'l qo'ymaslik uchun ``0`` ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3045
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3115
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3627
msgid "``disable_linking`` (optional)"
msgstr "``disable_linking`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3045
msgid "set to ``1`` to prevent from redirecting clicks on graph to list view"
msgstr "grafik ustidagi bosimlari ro'yxat ko'rinishiga yo'naltirilishining oldini olish uchun ``1`` ga o'rnating"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3050
msgid "``order`` (optional)"
msgstr "``order`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3048
msgid ""
"if set, x-axis values will be sorted by default according their measure "
"with respect to the given order (``asc`` or ``desc``). Only used for "
"``bar`` and ``pie`` charts."
msgstr ""
"agar belgilansa, x-o'q qiymatlari berilgan tartibga (``asc`` yoki ``desc``) "
"nisbatan ularning o'lchovi bo'yicha standart ravishda tartiblandi. Faqat "
"``bar`` va ``pie`` diagrammalar uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3053
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3085
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3140
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3657
msgid "``string`` (optional)"
msgstr "``string`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3053
msgid "string displayed in the breadcrumbs when redirecting to list view."
msgstr "ro'yxat ko'rinishiga yo'naltirilganda breadcrumbs da ko'rsatiladigan satr."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3057
msgid ""
"The only allowed element within a graph view is ``field`` which can have "
"the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishida ruxsat etilgan yagona element quyidagi atributlarga ega "
"bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan ``field`` dir:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3063
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3135
msgid ""
"the name of a field to use in the view. If used for grouping (rather than"
" aggregating)"
msgstr ""
"ko'rinishda foydalaniladigan maydon nomi. Agar guruhlash uchun (agregatsiya "
"o'rniga) ishlatilsa"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3068
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3162
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3663
msgid "``invisible`` (optional)"
msgstr "``invisible`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3067
msgid ""
"if true, the field will not appear either in the active measures nor in "
"the selectable measures."
msgstr ""
"agar to'g'ri bo'lsa, maydon na faol o'lchovlarda va na tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"o'lchovlarda ko'rinmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3071
msgid ""
"if set to ``measure``, the field will be used as an aggregated value "
"within a group instead of a grouping criteria. It only works for the last"
" field with that attribute but it is useful for other fields with string "
"attribute (see below)."
msgstr ""
"agar ``measure`` ga o'rnatilsa, maydon guruhlash mezoni o'rniga guruh ichida "
"agregatlangan qiymat sifatida ishlatiladi. Bu faqat ushbu atributga ega bo'lgan "
"oxirgi maydon uchun ishlaydi, ammo string atributiga ega boshqa maydonlar "
"uchun foydalidir (quyida qarang)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3080
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3642
msgid "``interval`` (optional)"
msgstr "``interval`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3077
msgid ""
"on date and datetime fields, groups by the specified interval (``day``, "
"``week``, ``month``, ``quarter`` or ``year``) instead of grouping on the "
"specific datetime (fixed second resolution) or date (fixed day "
"resolution). Default is ``month``."
msgstr ""
"sana va sanawaqt maydonlarida, aniq sanawaqt (belgilangan soniya o'lchami) yoki "
"sana (belgilangan kun o'lchami) bo'yicha guruhlash o'rniga, belgilangan interval "
"(``day``, ``week``, ``month``, ``quarter`` yoki ``year``) bo'yicha guruhlaydi. "
"Standart ``month`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3083
msgid ""
"only used for field with ``type=\"measure\"``. The name that will be used"
" to display the field in the graph view, overrides the default python "
"String attribute of the field."
msgstr ""
"faqat ``type=\"measure\"`` li maydon uchun ishlatiladi. Grafik ko'rinishida "
"maydonni ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan nom, maydonning standart python "
"String atributini bekor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3087
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3166
msgid ""
"The measures are automatically generated from the model fields; only the "
"aggregatable fields are used. Those measures are also alphabetically "
"sorted on the string of the field."
msgstr ""
"O'lchovlar model maydonlaridan avtomatik ravishda yaratiladi; faqat agregatlash "
"mumkin bo'lgan maydonlar ishlatiladi. Ushbu o'lchovlar ham maydonning satrida "
"alifbo tartibida tartiblangan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3093
msgid ""
"graph view aggregations are performed on database content, non-stored "
"function fields can not be used in graph views"
msgstr ""
"grafik ko'rinish agregatsiyalari ma'lumotlar bazasi kontentida bajariladi, "
"saqlanmagan funksiya maydonlari grafik ko'rinishlarda ishlatila olmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3097
msgid ""
"In Graph views, a ``field`` can have a ``widget`` attribute to dictate "
"its format. The widget should be a field formatter, of which the most "
"interesting are ``float_time``, and ``monetary``."
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishlarda ``field`` o'z formatini belgilash uchun ``widget`` atributiga "
"ega bo'lishi mumkin. Vidjet maydon formatlash vositasi bo'lishi kerak, ulardan eng "
"qiziqarlilari ``float_time`` va ``monetary`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3108
msgid "Pivot"
msgstr "Pivot"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3110
msgid ""
"The pivot view is used to visualize aggregations as a `pivot table`_. Its"
" root element is ``<pivot>`` which can take the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishi agregatsiyalarni `pivot jadval`_ sifatida vizualizatsiya qilish "
"uchun ishlatiladi. Uning ildiz elementi quyidagi atributlarni qabul qilishi "
"mumkin bo'lgan ``<pivot>`` dir:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3116
msgid "Set to ``1`` to remove table cell's links to list view."
msgstr "Jadval katakchalarining ro'yxat ko'rinishiga havolalarini olib tashlash uchun ``1`` ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3117
msgid "``display_quantity`` (optional)"
msgstr "``display_quantity`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3118
msgid "Set to ``1`` to display the Quantity column by default."
msgstr "Miqdor ustunini standart ravishda ko'rsatish uchun ``1`` ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3127
msgid "``default_order`` (optional)"
msgstr "``default_order`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3120
msgid ""
"The name of the measure and the order (asc or desc) to use as default "
"order in the view."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishda standart tartib sifatida foydalaniladigan o'lchovning nomi va "
"tartib (asc yoki desc)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3129
msgid ""
"The only allowed element within a pivot view is ``field`` which can have "
"the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishida ruxsat etilgan yagona element quyidagi atributlarga ega "
"bo'lishi mumkin bo'lgan ``field`` dir:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3139
msgid ""
"the name that will be used to display the field in the pivot view, "
"overrides the default python String attribute of the field."
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishida maydonni ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan nom, maydonning "
"standart python String atributini bekor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3143
msgid ""
"indicates whether the field should be used as a grouping criteria or as "
"an aggregated value within a group. Possible values are:"
msgstr ""
"maydon guruhlash mezoni sifatida yoki guruh ichida agregatlangan qiymat "
"sifatida ishlatilishi kerakligini bildiradi. Mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3148
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1021
msgid "``row`` (default)"
msgstr "``row`` (standart)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3149
msgid "groups by the specified field, each group gets its own row."
msgstr "belgilangan maydon bo'yicha guruhlanadi, har bir guruh o'z satrini oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3150
msgid "``col``"
msgstr "``col``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3151
msgid "creates column-wise groups"
msgstr "ustun bo'yicha guruhlar yaratadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3152
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1024
msgid "``measure``"
msgstr "``measure``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3153
msgid "field to aggregate within a group"
msgstr "guruh ichida agregate qilinadigan maydon"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3157
msgid "``interval``"
msgstr "``interval``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3155
msgid ""
"on date and datetime fields, groups by the specified interval (``day``, "
"``week``, ``month``, ``quarter`` or ``year``) instead of grouping on the "
"specific datetime (fixed second resolution) or date (fixed day "
"resolution)."
msgstr ""
"sana va sanawaqt maydonlarida, aniq sanawaqt (belgilangan soniya o'lchami) yoki "
"sana (belgilangan kun o'lchami) bo'yicha guruhlash o'rniga, belgilangan interval "
"(``day``, ``week``, ``month``, ``quarter`` yoki ``year``) bo'yicha guruhlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3160
msgid ""
"if true, the field will not appear either in the active measures nor in "
"the selectable measures (useful for fields that do not make sense "
"aggregated, such as fields in different units, e.g. € and $)."
msgstr ""
"agar to'g'ri bo'lsa, maydon na faol o'lchovlarda va na tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"o'lchovlarda ko'rinmaydi (turli birliklardagi maydonlar kabi agregatsiya qilish "
"ma'nosi bo'lmagan maydonlar uchun foydali, masalan € va $)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3172
msgid ""
"like the graph view, the pivot aggregates data on database content which "
"means that non-stored function fields can not be used in pivot views"
msgstr ""
"grafik ko'rinishi kabi, pivot ma'lumotlar bazasi kontentida ma'lumotlarni "
"agregatlaydi, ya'ni saqlanmagan funksiya maydonlari pivot ko'rinishlarda "
"ishlatila olmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3176
msgid ""
"In Pivot view a ``field`` can have a ``widget`` attribute to dictate its "
"format. The widget should be a field formatter, of which the most "
"interesting are ``date``, ``datetime``, ``float_time``, and ``monetary``."
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishida ``field`` o'z formatini belgilash uchun ``widget`` atributiga "
"ega bo'lishi mumkin. Vidjet maydon formatlash vositasi bo'lishi kerak, ulardan "
"eng qiziqarlilari ``date``, ``datetime``, ``float_time`` va ``monetary`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3180
msgid "For instance a timesheet pivot view could be defined as::"
msgstr "Masalan, ish vaqti jadvali pivot ko'rinishi quyidagicha aniqlanishi mumkin::"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3191
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Taqvim"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3193
msgid ""
"Calendar views display records as events in a daily, weekly, monthly or "
"yearly calendar."
msgstr ""
"Taqvim ko'rinishlari yozuvlarni kunlik, haftalik, oylik yoki yillik taqvimda "
"voqealar sifatida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3196
msgid ""
"By default the calendar view will be centered around the current date "
"(today). You can pass a specific initial date to the context of the "
"action in order to set the initial focus of the calendar on the period "
"(see `mode`) around this date (the context key to use being "
"`initial_date`)"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha taqvim ko'rinishi joriy sana (bugun) atrofida markazlashadi. "
"Taqvimning boshlang'ich fokusini ushbu sana atrofidagi davrga (``mode`` ga qarang) "
"o'rnatish uchun amal kontekstiga maxsus boshlang'ich sanani o'tkazishingiz mumkin "
"(foydalaniladigan kontekst kaliti `initial_date` bo'ladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3201
msgid ""
"Their root element is ``<calendar>``. Available attributes on the root "
"node are:"
msgstr ""
"Ularning ildiz elementi ``<calendar>`` dir. Ildiz tugunida mavjud atributlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3208
msgid "Name of the record's field holding the start date for the event."
msgstr "Voqa boshlanish sanasini saqlovchi yozuv maydonining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3216
msgid "Name of the record's field holding the end date for the event."
msgstr "Voqa tugash sanasini saqlovchi yozuv maydonining nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3224
msgid ""
"Alternative to ``date_stop``. Provides the duration of the event instead "
"of its end date (unit: hour)."
msgstr ""
"``date_stop`` ga alternativa. Tugash sanasi o'rniga voqaning davomiyligini "
"ta'minlaydi (birlik: soat)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3233
msgid ""
"Comma-separated list of available scales, among ``day``, ``week``, "
"``month``, ``year``. By default, all scales are available."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud masshtablarning vergul bilan ajratilgan ro'yxati: ``day``, ``week``, "
"``month``, ``year``. Standart bo'yicha barcha masshtablar mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3238
msgid "`\"day,week,month,year\"`"
msgstr "`\"day,week,month,year\"`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3243
msgid "Default scale of the calendar."
msgstr "Taqvimning standart masshtabi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3246
msgid "`\"day\"`, `\"week\"`, `\"month\"` or `\"year\"`"
msgstr "`\"day\"`, `\"week\"`, `\"month\"` yoki `\"year\"`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3247
msgid "`\"week\"`"
msgstr "`\"week\"`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3252
msgid ""
"Name of the record's field to use for *color segmentation*. Records in "
"the same color segment are allocated the same highlight color in the "
"calendar."
msgstr ""
"*Rang segmentatsiyasi* uchun foydalaniladigan yozuv maydonining nomi. Bir xil "
"rang segmentidagi yozuvlarga taqvimda bir xil ajratib ko'rsatish rangi ajratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3261
msgid ""
"Name of the record's boolean field indicating whether the corresponding "
"event is flagged as day-long, in which case duration is irrelevant."
msgstr ""
"Tegishli voqa kun bo'yi sifatida belgilanganligini ko'rsatadigan yozuv boolean "
"maydonining nomi, bunday holda davomiylik ahamiyatsiz."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3270
msgid ""
"Name of the record's field to use to display aggregated values next to "
"filters, in the filter side panel. The aggregator can be explicitly given"
" (e.g. `aggregate=\"expected_revenue:sum\"`). If not given, the "
"aggregator of the field is used. Supported aggregators are `sum`, `avg`, "
"`min`, `max`, `count` and `count_distinct`."
msgstr ""
"Filtr yon panelida filtrlar yonida agregatlangan qiymatlarni ko'rsatish uchun "
"foydalaniladigan yozuv maydonining nomi. Agregator aniq berilishi mumkin "
"(masalan, `aggregate=\"expected_revenue:sum\"`). Berilmasa, maydonning "
"agregatori ishlatiladi. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan agregatorlar: `sum`, `avg`, "
"`min`, `max`, `count` va `count_distinct`."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3282
msgid ""
"Limits the number of events displayed in calendar cells, in `month` "
"scale, and for all-day events in `week` and `day` scales. If there are "
"more events than the limit, a \"more\" button is added to show the rest "
"of the events in a popover."
msgstr ""
"`month` masshtabida taqvim katakchalarida ko'rsatiladigan voqalar sonini va "
"`week` va `day` masshtablarida butun kun voqalarini cheklaydi. Agar voqalar "
"chegaradan ko'p bo'lsa, qolgan voqalarni popoverde ko'rsatish uchun \"more\" "
"tugmasi qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3288
msgid "5"
msgstr "5"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3293
msgid ""
"If set to true weekend days and public holidays have a greyed out "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Agar to'g'ri ga o'rnatilsa, dam olish kunlari va davlat bayramlari kulrang "
"fonga ega bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3302
msgid "Set it to true to hide the date part in the record's popover."
msgstr "Yozuv popoverida sana qismini yashirish uchun true ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3311
msgid "Set it to true to hide the time part in the record's popover."
msgstr "Yozuv popoverida vaqt qismini yashirish uchun true ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3315
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:184
msgid "False"
msgstr "False"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3320
msgid ""
"By default, in month mode, the last days of the previous month and the "
"first days of the next months are displayed, as well as their events. "
"This option allows to disable this such that those sibling days are "
"greyed out and their events aren't displayed."
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha, oy rejimida, oldingi oyning so'nggi kunlari va keyingi "
"oyning birinchi kunlari, shuningdek ularning voqalari ko'rsatiladi. Bu opsiya "
"buni o'chirib qo'yish imkonini beradi, shunda ushbu qo'shni kunlar kulrang "
"bo'lib, ularning voqalari ko'rsatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3332
msgid ""
"By default, a mini calendar (in month mode) is displayed in the side "
"panel, next to the main calendar. This option allows to remove it by "
"setting it to `False`."
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha, asosiy taqvim yonidagi yon panelda mini taqvim (oy rejimida) "
"ko'rsatiladi. Bu opsiya uni `False` ga o'rnatish orqali olib tashlash imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3343
msgid ""
"If true, open events in dialog to edit them, otherwise, open them in a "
"classical form view."
msgstr ""
"Agar to'g'ri bo'lsa, voqalarni tahrirlash uchun dialog oynasida oching, "
"aks holda klassik shakl ko'rinishida oching."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3353
msgid ""
"View to open when the user creates or edits an event. By default, uses "
"the form view of the current action, if any."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi voqa yaratganda yoki tahrirlaganda ochish uchun ko'rinish. "
"Standart bo'yicha, mavjud bo'lsa, joriy amalning shakl ko'rinishini ishlatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3362
msgid ""
"Enables quick event creation on click: only asks the user for a ``name`` "
"and tries to create a new event with just that and the clicked event "
"time. Falls back to a full form view if the quick creation fails."
msgstr ""
"Bosilganda tezkor voqa yaratishni yoqadi: faqat foydalanuvchidan ``name`` "
"so'raydi va faqat shu va bosilgan voqa vaqti bilan yangi voqa yaratishga "
"harakat qiladi. Tezkor yaratish muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'lsa, to'liq shakl "
"ko'rinishiga qaytadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3373
msgid ""
"Name of the record's field holding the display name of the record. This "
"field is used when creating records through the 'quick create' mechanism."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvning ko'rsatma nomini saqlovchi yozuv maydonining nomi. Bu maydon "
"'tezkor yaratish' mexanizmi orqali yozuvlar yaratilganda ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3383
msgid ""
"Id of the form view to open when the attribute ``quick_create`` is set "
"and the user creates an event, instead of the default dialog which only "
"allows to specify a name."
msgstr ""
"``quick_create`` atributi o'rnatilganda va foydalanuvchi voqa yaratganda ochish "
"uchun shakl ko'rinishining Id si, faqat nom belgilashga ruxsat beruvchi standart "
"dialog o'rniga."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3393
msgid ""
"Reference of a form view. When set, in **month** scale, allows to create "
"(and delete) records in batches by clicking on calendar cells or by "
"selecting an area of calendar cells. One record is then created for each "
"selected cell and for each active filter's value, with the values of the "
"multi create form view, which is displayed in the side panel. In delete "
"mode, all records displayed in selected cells are deleted."
msgstr ""
"Shakl ko'rinishiga havola. Belgilanganda, **month** masshtabida, taqvim "
"katakchalariga bosish yoki taqvim katakchalari maydonini tanlash orqali "
"yozuvlarni paketlar bo'yicha yaratish (va o'chirish) imkonini beradi. Keyin "
"har bir tanlangan katak va har bir faol filtr qiymati uchun, yon panelda "
"ko'rsatiladigan ko'p yaratish shakl ko'rinishining qiymatlari bilan bir yozuv "
"yaratiladi. O'chirish rejimida, tanlangan katakchalarda ko'rsatilgan barcha "
"yozuvlar o'chiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3400
msgid ""
"Note: if the side panel contains multiple filter sections, only the first"
" one is used, to avoid a combinatorial explosion."
msgstr ""
"Eslatma: agar yon panel bir nechta filtr bo'limlarini o'z ichiga olsa, "
"kombinatorial portlashning oldini olish uchun faqat birinchisi ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3413
msgid "Disable/enable record deletion on the view."
msgstr "Ko'rinishda yozuvni o'chirishni o'chirish/yoqish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3426
msgid ""
"Calendar views accept a single type of child elements: ``<field>``. Those"
" fields are displayed in a popover, in the given order, which opens when "
"a record (a calendar event) is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Taqvim ko'rinishlari bitta turdagi bola elementlarni qabul qiladi: ``<field>``. "
"Ushbu maydonlar yozuv (taqvim voqasi) bosilganda ochiladigan popoverde, "
"berilgan tartibda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3430
msgid ""
"Fields in the popover are readonly. If the `edit` action is available, an"
" `Edit` button is displayed in the popover, to open a form view where "
"fields can be edited."
msgstr ""
"Popoverdagi maydonlar faqat o'qish uchun. Agar `edit` amali mavjud bo'lsa, "
"maydonlarni tahrirlash mumkin bo'lgan shakl ko'rinishini ochish uchun popoverde "
"`Edit` tugmasi ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3434
msgid "Field nodes can have the following attributes:"
msgstr "Maydon tugunlari quyidagi atributlarga ega bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3441
msgid ""
"Python expression indicating whether the field should be displayed or "
"not. Other fields of the model can be used in the expression, as long as "
"those fields are also declared here."
msgstr ""
"Maydon ko'rsatilishi yoki ko'rsatilmasligi kerakligini bildiruvchi Python "
"ifodasi. Modelning boshqa maydonlari ifodada ishlatilishi mumkin, agar ushbu "
"maydonlar ham bu yerda e'lon qilingan bo'lsa."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3452
msgid ""
"Python expression encoding an object of options for the field. In "
"particular, the option `icon`, allowing to specify, as classnames, which "
"icon to display in front of the field in the popover (for instance, `fa "
"fa-users`). If no icon is given, the option `string` can be set, and its "
"value is then used as label, displayed in front of the field."
msgstr ""
"Maydon uchun opsiyalar ob'ektini kodlovchi Python ifodasi. Xususan, `icon` "
"opsiyasi, popoverde maydoning oldida qaysi belgini ko'rsatishni klass nomlari "
"sifatida belgilash imkonini beradi (masalan, `fa fa-users`). Agar belgi "
"berilmasa, `string` opsiyasi o'rnatilishi mumkin va uning qiymati maydoning "
"oldida ko'rsatiladigan yorliq sifatida ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3462
msgid ""
"Specifying a ``<field>`` in a calendar arch also allows to customize the "
"filter side panel, by setting the `filters` attribute. Extra attributes "
"are then available for that matter:"
msgstr ""
"Taqvim arxitekturasida ``<field>`` ni belgilash `filters` atributini o'rnatish "
"orqali filtr yon panelini sozlash imkonini ham beradi. Unda qo'shimcha "
"atributlar mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3469
msgid ""
"If set to true, the field can be used as filter, from the side panel of "
"the calendar."
msgstr ""
"Agar to'g'ri ga o'rnatilsa, maydon taqvimning yon panelidan filtr sifatida "
"ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3479
msgid ""
"Only for relational fields. Specify the name of the field on the co-model"
" to use to display as avatar in front of field values in the side panel "
"filters."
msgstr ""
"Faqat relatsion maydonlar uchun. Yon panel filtrlarida maydon qiymatlari "
"oldida avatar sifatida ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan hamkor-modeldagi "
"maydon nomini belgilang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3488
msgid ""
"Specify which field to use to colorize the checkbox in the side panel "
"filters. By default, the color attribute of the calendar view is used to "
"match events with values in the filters."
msgstr ""
"Yon panel filtrlarida checkboxni ranglash uchun qaysi maydon ishlatilishini "
"belgilang. Standart bo'yicha, voqalarni filtrlardagi qiymatlar bilan moslashtirish "
"uchun taqvim ko'rinishining color atributi ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3498
msgid ""
"Allows to create new filter values on the fly. The given model is then "
"used as model for those filters.  To combine with `write_field`."
msgstr ""
"Yangi filtr qiymatlarini tezkor yaratish imkonini beradi. Berilgan model keyin "
"ushbu filtrlar uchun model sifatida ishlatiladi. `write_field` bilan birlashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3507
msgid ""
"Combined with `write_model`, specifies the field name, in the given "
"model, to use to encode the filter value."
msgstr ""
"`write_model` bilan birlashtirilganda, filtr qiymatini kodlash uchun foydalaniladigan, "
"berilgan modeldagi maydon nomini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3516
msgid ""
"Combined with `write_model`, specifies the field name, in the given "
"model, to use to encode the status of the filter (whether it is checked "
"or not)."
msgstr ""
"`write_model` bilan birlashtirilganda, filtr holatini (belgilangan yoki "
"yo'qligini) kodlash uchun foydalaniladigan, berilgan modeldagi maydon nomini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3525
msgid "Activity"
msgstr "Faoliyat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3527
msgid ""
"The Activity view is used to display the activities linked to the "
"records. The data are displayed in a chart with the records forming the "
"rows and the activity types the columns. The first cell of each row "
"displays a (customizable, see ``templates``, quite similarly to "
":ref:`reference/view_architectures/kanban`) card representing the "
"corresponding record. When clicking on others cells, a detailed "
"description of all activities of the same type for the record is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Faoliyat ko'rinishi yozuvlarga bog'liq faoliyatlarni ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi. "
"Ma'lumotlar yozuvlar satrlarni, faoliyat turlari esa ustunlarni tashkil etadigan "
"jadvalda ko'rsatiladi. Har bir satrning birinchi katakchasi tegishli yozuvni "
"ifodalovchi (sozlanishi mumkin, ``templates`` ga qarang, :ref:`reference/view_architectures/kanban` "
"ga o'xshash) kartani ko'rsatadi. Boshqa katakchalarga bosilganda, yozuv uchun "
"bir xil turdagi barcha faoliyatlarning batafsil tavsifi ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3536
msgid ""
"The Activity view is only available when the ``mail`` module is "
"installed, and for the models that inherit from the "
"``mail.activity.mixin``."
msgstr ""
"Faoliyat ko'rinishi faqat ``mail`` moduli o'rnatilganda va ``mail.activity.mixin`` "
"dan meros olgan modellar uchun mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3539
msgid ""
"The root element of the Activity view is ``<activity>``, it accepts the "
"following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Faoliyat ko'rinishining ildiz elementi ``<activity>`` bo'lib, u quyidagi "
"atributlarni qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3545
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3616
msgid "``string`` (mandatory)"
msgstr "``string`` (majburiy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3545
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3616
msgid "A title, which should describe the view"
msgstr "Ko'rinishni tavsiflovchi sarlavha"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3547
msgid "Possible children of the view element are:"
msgstr "Ko'rinish elementining mumkin bo'lgan bola elementlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3552
msgid ""
"declares fields to use in activity *logic*. If the field is simply "
"displayed in the activity view, it does not need to be pre-declared."
msgstr ""
"Faoliyat *mantiqida* foydalaniladigan maydonlarni e'lon qiladi. Agar maydon "
"faoliyat ko'rinishida shunchaki ko'rsatilsa, u oldindan e'lon qilinishi shart emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3555
msgid "Possible attributes are:"
msgstr "Mumkin bo'lgan atributlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3560
msgid "``name`` (required)"
msgstr "``name`` (talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3560
msgid "the name of the field to fetch"
msgstr "olish uchun maydon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3580
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4118
msgid "``templates``"
msgstr "``templates``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3563
msgid ""
"defines the :ref:`reference/qweb` templates. Cards definition may be "
"split into multiple templates for clarity, but activity views *must* "
"define at least one root template ``activity-box``, which will be "
"rendered once for each record."
msgstr ""
":ref:`reference/qweb` shablonlarini aniqlaydi. Kartalar ta'rifi aniqlik uchun "
"bir nechta shablonlarga bo'linishi mumkin, ammo faoliyat ko'rinishlari har bir "
"yozuv uchun bir marta ko'rsatiladigan kamida bitta ildiz shabloni ``activity-box`` "
"ni *aniqlashi shart*."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3568
msgid ""
"The activity view uses mostly-standard :ref:`javascript qweb "
"<reference/qweb/javascript>` and provides the following context variables"
" (see :ref:`reference/view_architectures/kanban` for more details):"
msgstr ""
"Faoliyat ko'rinishi asosan standart :ref:`javascript qweb <reference/qweb/javascript>` "
"dan foydalanadi va quyidagi kontekst o'zgaruvchilarini taqdim etadi "
"(batafsil ma'lumot uchun :ref:`reference/view_architectures/kanban` ga qarang):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3576
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4114
msgid "``widget``"
msgstr "``widget``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3575
msgid ""
"the current :js:class:`ActivityRecord`, can be used to fetch some meta-"
"information. These methods are also available directly in the template "
"context and don't need to be accessed via ``widget``"
msgstr ""
"joriy :js:class:`ActivityRecord`, ba'zi meta-ma'lumotlarni olish uchun "
"ishlatilishi mumkin. Ushbu usullar shablon kontekstida ham bevosita mavjud "
"va ``widget`` orqali kira olmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3579
msgid ""
"an object with all the requested fields as its attributes. Each field has"
" two attributes ``value`` and ``raw_value``"
msgstr ""
"barcha so'ralgan maydonlarni atributlari sifatida o'z ichiga olgan ob'ekt. "
"Har bir maydonning ``value`` va ``raw_value`` ikkita atributi mavjud"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3585
msgid "Cohort"
msgstr "Kohort"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3591
msgid ""
"The cohort view is used to display and understand the way some data "
"changes over a period of time.  For example, imagine that for a given "
"business, clients can subscribe to some service.  The cohort view can "
"then display the total number of subscriptions each month, and study the "
"rate at which client leave the service (churn). When clicking on a cell, "
"the cohort view will redirect you to a new action in which you will only "
"see the records contained in the cell's time interval; this action "
"contains a list view and a form view."
msgstr ""
"Kohort ko'rinishi ma'lum ma'lumotlarning vaqt o'tishi bilan qanday o'zgarishini "
"ko'rsatish va tushunish uchun ishlatiladi. Masalan, ma'lum bir biznes uchun "
"mijozlar ba'zi xizmatlarga obuna bo'lishi mumkin. Kohort ko'rinishi har oy "
"obunalar umumiy sonini ko'rsatishi va mijozlar xizmatni tark etish "
"tezligini (churn) o'rganishi mumkin. Katakchaga bosish orqali, kohort ko'rinishi "
"sizi faqat katakchaning vaqt oralig'idagi yozuvlarni ko'radigan yangi amalga "
"yo'naltiradi; bu amal ro'yxat ko'rinishini va shakl ko'rinishini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3599
msgid ""
"By default the cohort view will use the same list and form views as those"
" defined on the action. You can pass a list view and a form view to the "
"context of the action in order to set/override the views that will be "
"used (the context keys to use being `form_view_id` and `list_view_id`)"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha kohort ko'rinishi amalda belgilangan ro'yxat va shakl "
"ko'rinishlarini ishlatadi. Foydalaniladigan ko'rinishlarni o'rnatish/bekor "
"qilish uchun amal kontekstiga ro'yxat ko'rinishi va shakl ko'rinishini o'tkazishingiz "
"mumkin (foydalaniladigan kontekst kalitlari `form_view_id` va `list_view_id` bo'ladi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3604
msgid "For example, here is a very simple cohort view:"
msgstr "Masalan, juda oddiy kohort ko'rinishi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3610
msgid ""
"The root element of the Cohort view is <cohort>, it accepts the following"
" attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Kohort ko'rinishining ildiz elementi <cohort> bo'lib, u quyidagi atributlarni "
"qabul qiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3620
msgid "``date_start`` (mandatory)"
msgstr "``date_start`` (majburiy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3619
msgid ""
"A valid date or datetime field. This field is understood by the view as "
"the beginning date of a record"
msgstr ""
"To'g'ri sana yoki sanawaqt maydoni. Bu maydon ko'rinish tomonidan yozuvning "
"boshlanish sanasi sifatida tushuniladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3624
msgid "``date_stop`` (mandatory)"
msgstr "``date_stop`` (majburiy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3623
msgid ""
"A valid date or datetime field. This field is understood by the view as "
"the end date of a record.  This is the field that will determine the "
"churn."
msgstr ""
"To'g'ri sana yoki sanawaqt maydoni. Bu maydon ko'rinish tomonidan yozuvning "
"tugash sanasi sifatida tushuniladi. Bu churnni aniqlaydigan maydon."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3627
msgid ""
"Set to ``1`` to prevent from redirecting clicks on cohort cells to list "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Kohort katakchalaridagi bosimlari ro'yxat ko'rinishiga yo'naltirilishining "
"oldini olish uchun ``1`` ga o'rnating."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3632
msgid "``mode`` (optional)"
msgstr "``mode`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3630
msgid ""
"A string to describe the mode. It should be either 'churn' or 'retention'"
" (default). Churn mode will start at 0% and accumulate over time whereas "
"retention will start at 100% and decrease over time."
msgstr ""
"Rejimni tavsiflovchi satr. U 'churn' yoki 'retention' (standart) bo'lishi kerak. "
"Churn rejimi 0% dan boshlanadi va vaqt o'tishi bilan to'planadi, retention esa "
"100% dan boshlanadi va vaqt o'tishi bilan kamayadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3638
msgid "``timeline`` (optional)"
msgstr "``timeline`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3635
msgid ""
"A string to describe the timeline. It should be either 'backward' or "
"'forward' (default). Forward timeline will display data from date_start "
"to date_stop, whereas backward timeline will display data from date_stop "
"to date_start (when the date_start is in future / greater than "
"date_stop)."
msgstr ""
"Vaqt chizig'ini tavsiflovchi satr. U 'backward' yoki 'forward' (standart) "
"bo'lishi kerak. Forward vaqt chizig'i date_start dan date_stop gacha ma'lumotlarni "
"ko'rsatadi, backward esa date_stop dan date_start gacha (date_start kelajakda "
"bo'lsa / date_stop dan katta bo'lsa)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3641
msgid ""
"A string to describe a time interval. It should be 'day', 'week', "
"'month'' (default) or 'year'."
msgstr ""
"Vaqt oralig'ini tavsiflovchi satr. U 'day', 'week', 'month' (standart) "
"yoki 'year' bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3646
msgid "``measure`` (optional)"
msgstr "``measure`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3645
msgid ""
"A field that can be aggregated.  This field will be used to compute the "
"values for each cell.  If not set, the cohort view will count the number "
"of occurrences."
msgstr ""
"Agregatlash mumkin bo'lgan maydon. Bu maydon har bir katak uchun qiymatlarni "
"hisoblash uchun ishlatiladi. Agar belgilanmasa, kohort ko'rinishi "
"hodisalar sonini hisoblaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3649
msgid ""
"allows to specify a particular field in order to manage it from the "
"available measures, it's main use is for hiding a field from the "
"selectable measures:"
msgstr ""
"mavjud o'lchovlardan uni boshqarish uchun ma'lum maydonni belgilash imkonini beradi, "
"asosiy maqsadi - maydonni tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan o'lchovlardan yashirish:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3655
msgid "the name of the field to use in the view."
msgstr "ko'rinishda foydalaniladigan maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3657
msgid ""
"the name that would be used to display the field in the cohort view, "
"overrides the default python String attribute of the field."
msgstr ""
"Kohort ko'rinishida maydonni ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladigan nom, maydonning "
"standart python String atributini bekor qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3660
msgid ""
"if true, the field will not appear either in the active measures nor in "
"the selectable measures (useful for fields that do not make sense "
"aggregated, such as fields in different units, e.g. € and $). If the "
"value is a domain, the domain is evaluated in the context of the current "
"row's record, if ``True`` the corresponding attribute is set on the cell."
msgstr ""
"agar to'g'ri bo'lsa, maydon na faol o'lchovlarda va na tanlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"o'lchovlarda ko'rinmaydi (turli birliklardagi maydonlar kabi agregatsiya qilish "
"ma'nosi bo'lmagan maydonlar uchun foydali, masalan € va $). Agar qiymat domen "
"bo'lsa, domen joriy satr yozuvining kontekstida baholanadi, agar ``True`` bo'lsa "
"tegishli atribut katakchada o'rnatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3666
msgid "``widget`` (optional)"
msgstr "``widget`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3666
msgid "alternate representations for a field's display."
msgstr "maydon ko'rinishi uchun muqobil ko'rinishlar."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3682
msgid "This view is a work in progress and may have to be expanded or altered."
msgstr "Bu ko'rinish ishlanma jarayonida va kengaytirilishi yoki o'zgartirilishi kerak bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3684
msgid ""
"only ``date`` column fields have been tested, ``selection`` and "
"``many2one`` are nominally implemented and supported but have not been "
"tested, ``datetime`` is not implemented at all."
msgstr ""
"faqat ``date`` ustun maydonlari sinovdan o'tkazilgan, ``selection`` va "
"``many2one`` nominal ravishda amalga oshirilgan va qo'llab-quvvatlanadi, ammo "
"sinovdan o'tkazilmagan, ``datetime`` umuman amalga oshirilmagan."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3687
msgid "column cells are hardly configurable and must be numerical"
msgstr "ustun katakchalari sozlash qiyin va raqamli bo'lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3688
msgid ""
"cell adjustment is disabled by default and must be configured to be "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"katakcha sozlash standart bo'yicha o'chirilgan va yoqilishi uchun sozlanishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3689
msgid ""
"``create``, ``edit`` and ``delete`` ACL metadata doesn't get "
"automatically set on the view root due to limitations in "
"``fields_view_get`` post-processing (there's a fixed explicit list of the"
" view types getting those attributes)"
msgstr ""
"``create``, ``edit`` va ``delete`` ACL metadata ``fields_view_get`` "
"qayta-ishlash cheklovlari tufayli ko'rinish ildizida avtomatik ravishda "
"o'rnatilmaydi (ushbu atributlarni oladigan ko'rinish turlarining qat'iy "
"aniq ro'yxati mavjud)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3695
msgid "Schema"
msgstr "Sxema"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3697
msgid ""
"The grid view has its own schema and additional validation in this "
"module. The view architecture is:"
msgstr ""
"Grid ko'rinishi ushbu modulda o'z sxemasi va qo'shimcha validatsiyaga ega. "
"Ko'rinish arxitekturasi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3754
msgid "``<grid>`` (1)"
msgstr "``<grid>`` (1)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3701
msgid "architecture root element"
msgstr "arxitektura ildiz elementi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3703
msgid "mandatory ``string`` attribute"
msgstr "majburiy ``string`` atributi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3704
msgid "optional ``create``, ``edit`` and ``delete`` attributes"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``create``, ``edit`` va ``delete`` atributlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3705
msgid "optional ``adjustment`` and ``adjust_name`` attributes"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``adjustment`` va ``adjust_name`` atributlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3707
msgid ""
"``adjustment`` can be either ``object`` or ``action`` to indicate whether"
" a cell's adjustment should be performed through a method call or an "
"action execution. ``adjust_name`` provides respectively the method name "
"and the action id."
msgstr ""
"``adjustment`` katakcha sozlash usul chaqiruvi yoki amal bajarish orqali "
"amalga oshirilishi kerakligini ko'rsatish uchun ``object`` yoki ``action`` "
"bo'lishi mumkin. ``adjust_name`` mos ravishda usul nomini va amal id sini taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3712
msgid ""
"In both cases, the adjustment parameters are provided as a "
"``grid_adjust`` context member, in the ``object`` case, the parameters "
"are also provided as positional function parameters (next to an empty "
"list of ids):"
msgstr ""
"Ikkala holatda ham sozlash parametrlari ``grid_adjust`` kontekst a'zosi "
"sifatida taqdim etiladi, ``object`` holatida parametrlar shuningdek "
"pozitsion funksiya parametrlari sifatida ham taqdim etiladi (bo'sh id "
"ro'yxati yonida):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3717
msgid "``row_domain``"
msgstr "``row_domain``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3718
msgid "the domain matching the entire row of the adjusted cell"
msgstr "sozlangan katakchaning butun satriga mos keladigan domen"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3719
msgid "``column_field``"
msgstr "``column_field``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3720
msgid "the name of the column for the adjusted cell"
msgstr "sozlangan katak uchun ustun nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3721
msgid "``column_value``"
msgstr "``column_value``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3722
msgid "the value of the column for the adjusted cell"
msgstr "sozlangan katak uchun ustun qiymati"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3723
msgid "``cell_field``"
msgstr "``cell_field``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3724
msgid "the measure field of the adjusted cell"
msgstr "sozlangan katakchaning o'lchuv maydoni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3727
msgid "``change``"
msgstr "``change``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3726
msgid ""
"the difference between the old value of the cell and the adjusted one, "
"may be positive or negative"
msgstr ""
"katakchaning eski qiymati va sozlangani o'rtasidagi farq, ijobiy yoki "
"salbiy bo'lishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3729
msgid "optional ``hide_line_total`` and ``hide_column_total`` attributes"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``hide_line_total`` va ``hide_column_total`` atributlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3731
msgid "``hide_line_total``"
msgstr "``hide_line_total``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3732
msgid "set to true to hide total line (default false)"
msgstr "umumiy satrni yashirish uchun true ga o'rnating (standart false)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3734
msgid "``hide_column_total``"
msgstr "``hide_column_total``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3734
msgid "set to true to hide total column (default false)"
msgstr "umumiy ustunni yashirish uchun true ga o'rnating (standart false)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3736
msgid "optional ``barchart_total`` attribute"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``barchart_total`` atributi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3740
msgid "``barchart_total``"
msgstr "``barchart_total``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3739
msgid ""
"set to ``true`` in order to display a bar chart at the bottom of the "
"grid, based on the totals of the columns (default false)."
msgstr ""
"Ustunlar jami asosida gridning pastki qismida panellar diagrammasini "
"ko'rsatish uchun ``true`` ga o'rnating (standart false)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3742
msgid "optional ``create_inline`` and ``display_empty`` attributes"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``create_inline`` va ``display_empty`` atributlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3748
msgid "``create_inline``"
msgstr "``create_inline``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3745
msgid ""
"set to ``true`` in order to display an additional row at bottom of the "
"grid with an ``Add a line`` button (default false). When this option is "
"set to ``true``, the ``Add a line`` button from the control panel is "
"hidden. When no data is available and when ``display_empty`` is not set "
"(so when the help content is displayed), the the ``Add a line`` button "
"from the control panel is shown in order to let the user create a first "
"record."
msgstr ""
"``Add a line`` tugmasi bilan gridning pastki qismida qo'shimcha satr "
"ko'rsatish uchun ``true`` ga o'rnating (standart false). Bu opsiya ``true`` "
"ga o'rnatilganda, boshqaruv panelidan ``Add a line`` tugmasi yashiriladi. "
"Ma'lumotlar mavjud bo'lmaganda va ``display_empty`` o'rnatilmagan bo'lganda "
"(ya'ni yordam kontenti ko'rsatilganda), foydalanuvchiga birinchi yozuv "
"yaratishga ruxsat berish uchun boshqaruv panelidan ``Add a line`` tugmasi ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3754
msgid "``display_empty``"
msgstr "``display_empty``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3751
msgid ""
"set to ``true`` in order to keep displaying the grid when there is no "
"data (default false). This can be useful when you want the user to be "
"able to keep track of the current period (as dates are displayed in the "
"columns headers). As a reminder, when no data are present and when this "
"attribute is no set, the help content is displayed instead of the grid."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar yo'q bo'lganda gridni ko'rsatishda davom etish uchun ``true`` "
"ga o'rnating (standart false). Bu foydalanuvchi joriy davrni kuzatib borishini "
"xohlasangiz foydali bo'lishi mumkin (sanalar ustunlar sarlavhalarida ko'rsatilganligi sababli). "
"Eslatma sifatida, ma'lumotlar mavjud bo'lmaganda va ushbu atribut o'rnatilmagan "
"bo'lganda, grid o'rniga yordam kontenti ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3770
msgid "``<button>`` (0+)"
msgstr "``<button>`` (0+)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3757
msgid "Regular Odoo action buttons, displayed in the view header"
msgstr "Ko'rinish sarlavhasida ko'rsatiladigan oddiy Odoo amal tugmalari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3759
msgid "mandatory ``string`` attribute (the button label)"
msgstr "majburiy ``string`` atributi (tugma yorlig'i)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3760
msgid "mandatory ``type`` attribute, either ``object`` or ``action``"
msgstr "majburiy ``type`` atributi, ``object`` yoki ``action``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3762
msgid "workflow buttons are not supported"
msgstr "ish jarayoni tugmalari qo'llab-quvvatlanmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3764
msgid ""
"mandatory ``name`` attribute, either the name of the method to call, or "
"the ID of the action to execute"
msgstr ""
"majburiy ``name`` atributi, chaqiriladigan usul nomi yoki bajarish uchun "
"amal ID si"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3766
msgid "optional ``context``"
msgstr "ixtiyoriy ``context``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3768
msgid ""
"The server callback is provided with all the record ids displayed in the "
"view, either as the ids passed to the method (``object`` button) or as "
"the context's ``active_ids`` (``action`` buttons)"
msgstr ""
"Server qayta chaqiruvi ko'rinishda ko'rsatilgan barcha yozuv id lari bilan "
"ta'minlanadi, usulga o'tilgan id lar sifatida (``object`` tugmasi) yoki "
"kontekstning ``active_ids`` si sifatida (``action`` tugmalari)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3778
msgid "``<field type=\"row\">`` (1+)"
msgstr "``<field type=\"row\">`` (1+)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3773
msgid ""
"Row grouping fields, will be replaced by the search view's groupby filter"
" if any."
msgstr ""
"Satr guruhlash maydonlari, mavjud bo'lsa qidiruv ko'rinishining groupby "
"filtri bilan almashtiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3776
msgid ""
"The order of ``row`` fields in the view provides their grouping depth: if"
" the first field is ``school`` and the second is ``age`` the records will"
" be grouped by ``school`` first and by ``age`` within each school."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishdagi ``row`` maydonlarining tartibi ularning guruhlash chuqurligini "
"ta'minlaydi: agar birinchi maydon ``school`` va ikkinchisi ``age`` bo'lsa, "
"yozuvlar avval ``school`` bo'yicha va har bir maktab ichida ``age`` bo'yicha "
"guruhlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3799
msgid "``<field type=\"col\">`` (1)"
msgstr "``<field type=\"col\">`` (1)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3781
msgid "Column grouping field."
msgstr "Ustun guruhlash maydoni."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3783
msgid ""
"The col field can contain 0+ ``<range>`` elements which specify "
"customisable column ranges. ``range`` elements have the following "
"mandatory attributes"
msgstr ""
"Col maydoni sozlanishi mumkin bo'lgan ustun diapazonlarini belgilaydigan "
"0+ ``<range>`` elementlarini o'z ichiga olishi mumkin. ``range`` elementlari "
"quyidagi majburiy atributlarga ega"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3788
msgid ""
"can be used to override the default range (the first one by default) "
"through the ``grid_range`` context value"
msgstr ""
"``grid_range`` kontekst qiymati orqali standart diapazonni (standart bo'yicha "
"birinchisi) bekor qilish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3791
msgid "the range button's label (user-visible)"
msgstr "diapazon tugmasining yorlig'i (foydalanuvchiga ko'rinadigan)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3795
msgid "``span``"
msgstr "``span``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3793
msgid ""
"symbolic name of the span of all columns to display at once in the view, "
"may trigger pagination."
msgstr ""
"ko'rinishda bir vaqtda ko'rsatiladigan barcha ustunlarning kengligining "
"ramziy nomi, sahifalashni ishga tushirishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3796
msgid "For ``date`` fields, valid spans are currently ``week`` and ``month``."
msgstr "``date`` maydonlari uchun hozirda to'g'ri kengliklar ``week`` va ``month`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3799
msgid "``step``"
msgstr "``step``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3798
msgid "symbolic name of the step between one column and the previous/next"
msgstr "bir ustun va oldingi/keyingi o'rtasidagi qadam ramziy nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3800
msgid "For ``date`` fields, the only valid span is currently ``day``."
msgstr "``date`` maydonlari uchun hozirda to'g'ri yagona kenglik ``day`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3805
msgid "``<field type=\"measure\">`` (1)"
msgstr "``<field type=\"measure\">`` (1)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3802
msgid "Cell field, automatically accumulated (by ``read_group``)."
msgstr "Katakcha maydoni, avtomatik ravishda to'plangan (``read_group`` tomonidan)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3804
msgid ""
"The measure field can take a ``widget`` attribute to customise its "
"display."
msgstr ""
"O'lchuv maydoni o'z ko'rinishini sozlash uchun ``widget`` atributini olishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3808
msgid "Server interactions"
msgstr "Server o'zaro ta'sirlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3810
msgid "Aside from optional buttons, the grid view currently calls two methods:"
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy tugmalardan tashqari, grid ko'rinishi hozirda ikkita usulni chaqiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3812
msgid ""
"``read_grid`` (provided on all models by the module) returns almost the "
"entirety of the grid's content as a dict:"
msgstr ""
"``read_grid`` (modul tomonidan barcha modellarda taqdim etiladi) grid "
"kontentining deyarli to'liq dict sifatida qaytaradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3815
msgid "the row titles is a list of dictionaries with the following keys:"
msgstr "satr sarlavhalari quyidagi kalitlarga ega lug'atlar ro'yxati:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3818
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3826
msgid "``values`` (required)"
msgstr "``values`` (talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3818
msgid ""
"this maps to a dictionary with a key per ``row`` field, the values are "
"*always* of the form ``[value, label]``."
msgstr ""
"bu har bir ``row`` maydoni uchun kalit bilan lug'atga mos keladi, qiymatlar "
"*har doim* ``[value, label]`` shaklida bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3822
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3828
msgid "``domain`` (required)"
msgstr "``domain`` (talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3821
msgid ""
"the domain of any record at the source of this row, in case it's "
"necessary to copy a record during cell adjustment"
msgstr ""
"ushbu satr manbaida istalgan yozuvning domeni, katakcha sozlash vaqtida "
"yozuvni nusxalash kerak bo'lsa"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3824
msgid "the column titles is a list of dictionaries with at least one key:"
msgstr "ustun sarlavhalari kamida bitta kalit bilan lug'atlar ro'yxati:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3827
msgid "see row title values"
msgstr "satr sarlavha qiymatlarini ko'ring"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3829
msgid "see column domain value"
msgstr "ustun domen qiymatini ko'ring"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3831
msgid "``current`` (optional)"
msgstr "``current`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3831
msgid "boolean, marks/highlights a column"
msgstr "boolean, ustunni belgilaydi/ajratib ko'rsatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3833
msgid ""
"the grid data as a list (of rows) of list (of cells) of cell dicts each "
"with the following keys:"
msgstr ""
"katakcha lug'atlar ro'yxatining (katakchalar) ro'yxati (satrlar) sifatida "
"grid ma'lumotlari, har biri quyidagi kalitlarga ega:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3837
msgid "the numeric value associated with the cell"
msgstr "katakcha bilan bog'liq raqamli qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3839
msgid "the domain matching the cell's records (should be assumed opaque)"
msgstr "katakcha yozuvlariga mos keladigan domen (shaffof emas deb qabul qilinishi kerak)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3840
msgid "``size``"
msgstr "``size``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3841
msgid "the number of records grouped in the cell"
msgstr "katakchada guruhlangan yozuvlar soni"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3843
msgid "``readonly`` (optional)"
msgstr "``readonly`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3843
msgid "a boolean indicating that this specific cell should not be client-editable"
msgstr "ushbu maxsus katakcha mijoz tomonidan tahrirlanmasligi kerakligini ko'rsatadigan boolean"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3850
msgid "``classes`` (optional)"
msgstr "``classes`` (ixtiyoriy)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3846
msgid ""
"a list of classes (as strings) to add on the cell's container (between "
"the cell's TD and the cell's potentially-editable element)."
msgstr ""
"katakchaning konteyneriga qo'shish uchun klasslar ro'yxati (satrlar sifatida) "
"(katakchaning TD si va katakchaning potentsial tahrir qilinadigan elementi o'rtasida)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3849
msgid ""
"In case of conflicts between this list and the base classes (prefixed "
"with ``o_grid_cell_``), the classes in this list are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu ro'yxat va asosiy klasslar (``o_grid_cell_`` prefiksi bilan) o'rtasida "
"ziddiyatlar bo'lsa, ushbu ro'yxatdagi klasslar e'tiborga olinmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3852
msgid ""
"Note that the grid data is *dense*, if querying the database yields no "
"group matching a cell a cell will generate an \"empty\" cell with default"
" values for required keys."
msgstr ""
"Grid ma'lumotlari *zich* ekanligini unutmang, agar ma'lumotlar bazasini "
"so'rash katakchaga mos guruh bermasa, katakcha talab qilinadigan kalitlar "
"uchun standart qiymatlar bilan \"bo'sh\" katak yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3855
msgid ""
"``prev`` and ``next`` which can be either falsy (no pagination) or a "
"context item to merge into the view's own context to ``read_grid`` the "
"previous or next page, it should be assumed to be opaque"
msgstr ""
"``prev`` va ``next`` - noto'g'ri (sahifalash yo'q) yoki oldingi yoki keyingi "
"sahifani ``read_grid`` qilish uchun ko'rinishning o'z kontekstiga qo'shish "
"uchun kontekst elementi bo'lishi mumkin, shaffof emas deb qabul qilinishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3859
msgid ""
"``read_grid_domain(field, range)`` (provided on al models by the module) "
"returns the domain matching the current configured \"span\" of the grid. "
"This is also done internally by ``read_grid``, but can be useful or "
"necessary to call independently to use with separate e.g. "
"``search_count`` or ``read_group``."
msgstr ""
"``read_grid_domain(field, range)`` (modul tomonidan barcha modellarda taqdim "
"etiladi) grid ning joriy sozlangan \"span\" iga mos keladigan domenni qaytaradi. "
"Bu shuningdek ``read_grid`` tomonidan ichki ravishda amalga oshiriladi, ammo "
"alohida ``search_count`` yoki ``read_group`` bilan ishlatish uchun mustaqil "
"chaqirish foydali yoki zarur bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3865
msgid ""
"``adjust_grid``, for which there currently isn't a blanket implementation"
" and whose semantics are likely to evolve with time and use cases"
msgstr ""
"``adjust_grid``, uchun hozirda umumiy amalga oshirish yo'q va uning semantikasi "
"vaqt va foydalanish holatlari bilan rivojlanishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3869
msgid "Server Hooks"
msgstr "Server Qavslar"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3871
msgid ""
"``read_grid`` calls a number of hooks allowing the customisation of its "
"operations from within without having to override the entire method:"
msgstr ""
"``read_grid`` butun usulni bekor qilmasdan ichidan uning operatsiyalarini "
"sozlash imkonini beruvchi bir qancha qavslarni chaqiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3875
msgid "``_grid_format_cell(group, cell_field)``"
msgstr "``_grid_format_cell(group, cell_field)``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3875
msgid ""
"converts the output of a read_group (group-by-group) into cells in the "
"format described above (as part of \"the grid data\")"
msgstr ""
"read_group (guruh-guruh bo'yicha) chiqishini yuqorida tasvirlangan formatdagi "
"katakchalarga aylantiradi (\"grid ma'lumotlari\" ning bir qismi sifatida)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3877
msgid "``_grid_make_empty_cell(row_domain, column_domain, view_domain)``"
msgstr "``_grid_make_empty_cell(row_domain, column_domain, view_domain)``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3878
msgid "generates an empty version of a cell (if there is no corresponding group)"
msgstr "katakchaning bo'sh versiyasini yaratadi (agar mos guruh bo'lmasa)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3908
msgid "``_grid_column_info(name, range)``"
msgstr "``_grid_column_info(name, range)``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3880
msgid ""
"generates a ColumnMetadata object based on the column type, storing "
"values either returned directly (as part of ``read_grid``) or used query "
"and reformat ``read_group`` into ``read_grid``:"
msgstr ""
"Ustun turiga asosan ColumnMetadata ob'ektini yaratadi, bevosita qaytarilgan "
"(``read_grid`` ning bir qismi sifatida) yoki ``read_group`` ni ``read_grid`` "
"ga so'rov va qayta formatlash uchun ishlatiladigan qiymatlarni saqlaydi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3884
msgid "``grouping``"
msgstr "``grouping``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3885
msgid "the actual grouping field/query for the columns"
msgstr "ustunlar uchun haqiqiy guruhlash maydoni/so'rovi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3887
msgid ""
"domain to apply to ``read_group`` in case the column field is paginated, "
"can be an empty list"
msgstr ""
"ustun maydoni sahifalangan bo'lsa ``read_group`` ga qo'llash uchun domen, "
"bo'sh ro'yxat bo'lishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3891
msgid "``prev`` and ``next``"
msgstr "``prev`` va ``next``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3890
msgid ""
"context segments which will be sent to ``read_grid`` for pages before and"
" after the current one. If ``False``, disables pagination in that "
"direction"
msgstr ""
"joriy sahifadan oldin va keyin sahifalar uchun ``read_grid`` ga yuborilishi "
"kerak bo'lgan kontekst segmentlari. Agar ``False`` bo'lsa, o'sha yo'nalishda "
"sahifalashni o'chiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3898
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3908
msgid "``values``"
msgstr "``values``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3894
msgid ""
"column values to display on the \"current page\", each value is a "
"dictionary with the following keys:"
msgstr ""
"\"joriy sahifa\" da ko'rsatiladigan ustun qiymatlari, har bir qiymat "
"quyidagi kalitlarga ega lug'at:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3898
msgid ""
"dictionary mapping field names to values for the entire column, usually "
"just ``name`` -> a value"
msgstr ""
"butun ustun uchun maydon nomlarini qiymatlarga moslashtiradigan lug'at, "
"odatda faqat ``name`` -> bir qiymat"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3901
msgid "domain matching this specific column"
msgstr "ushbu maxsus ustunga mos keladigan domen"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3903
msgid "``is_current``"
msgstr "``is_current``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3903
msgid ""
"``True`` if the current column should be specifically outlined in the "
"grid, ``False`` otherwise"
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy ustun gridda maxsus ajratib ko'rsatilishi kerak bo'lsa ``True``, "
"aks holda ``False``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3906
msgid ""
"how to format the values of that column/type from ``read_group`` "
"formatting to ``read_grid`` formatting (matching ``values`` in "
"ColumnInfo)"
msgstr ""
"ushbu ustun/turning qiymatlarini ``read_group`` formatlashdan ``read_grid`` "
"formatlashga (ColumnInfo da ``values`` ga mos) qanday formatlash"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3911
msgid "ACL"
msgstr "ACL"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3913
msgid "if the view is not editable, individual cells won't be editable"
msgstr "agar ko'rinish tahrirlanmaydigan bo'lsa, alohida katakchalar ham tahrirlanmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3914
msgid ""
"if the view is not creatable, the ``Add a Line`` button will not be "
"displayed (it currently creates a new empty record)"
msgstr ""
"agar ko'rinish yaratib bo'lmaydigan bo'lsa, ``Add a Line`` tugmasi "
"ko'rsatilmaydi (u hozirda yangi bo'sh yozuv yaratadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3918
msgid "Context Keys"
msgstr "Kontekst Kalitlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3921
msgid "``grid_range``"
msgstr "``grid_range``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3921
msgid ""
"selects which range should be used by default if the view has multiple "
"ranges"
msgstr ""
"ko'rinishda bir nechta diapazonlar mavjud bo'lsa standart bo'yicha qaysi "
"diapazon ishlatilishini tanlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3928
msgid "``grid_anchor``"
msgstr "``grid_anchor``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3924
msgid ""
"if applicable, used as the default anchor of column ranges instead of "
"whatever ``read_grid`` defines as its default."
msgstr ""
"agar qo'llanilsa, ``read_grid`` standart sifatida aniqlagan narsaning o'rniga "
"ustun diapazonlarining standart yandovi sifatida ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3927
msgid ""
"For date fields, the reference date around which the initial span will be"
" computed. The default date anchor is \"today\" (in the user's timezone)"
msgstr ""
"Sana maydonlari uchun boshlang'ich kenglik hisoblanadigan islov sana. "
"Standart sana yandovi \"today\" (foydalanuvchi vaqt mintaqasida)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3933
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:971
msgid "Gantt"
msgstr "Gantt"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3939
msgid "Gantt views appropriately display Gantt charts (for scheduling)."
msgstr "Gantt ko'rinishlari Gantt diagrammalarini (rejalashtirishda) to'g'ri ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3941
msgid ""
"The root element of gantt views is ``<gantt/>``, it has no children but "
"can take the following attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Gantt ko'rinishlarining ildiz elementi ``<gantt/>`` bo'lib, uning bola "
"elementlari yo'q, ammo quyidagi atributlarni olishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3945
msgid "string (default: ``''``)"
msgstr "satr (standart: ``''``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3947
msgid ""
"This view title is displayed only if you open an action that has no name "
"and whose target is 'new' (opening a dialog)"
msgstr ""
"Bu ko'rinish sarlavhasi faqat nomi yo'q va maqsadi 'new' bo'lgan "
"(dialog ochiladigan) amalni ochsangiz ko'rsatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:159
msgid "create"
msgstr "create"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3951
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3956
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3961
msgid "bool (default: ``True``)"
msgstr "bool (standart: ``True``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst
msgid "edit"
msgstr "edit"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:159
msgid "delete"
msgstr "delete"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3963
msgid ""
"Disable/enable record deletion on the view through the **Action** "
"dropdown."
msgstr ""
"**Action** ochiladigan ro'yxati orqali ko'rinishda yozuvni o'chirishni "
"o'chirish/yoqish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3968
msgid "``date_start`` (required)"
msgstr "``date_start`` (talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3968
msgid ""
"name of the field providing the start datetime of the event for each "
"record."
msgstr ""
"har bir yozuv uchun voqaning boshlanish sanawaqtini ta'minlaydigan "
"maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3971
msgid "``date_stop`` (required)"
msgstr "``date_stop`` (talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3971
msgid "name of the field providing the end duration of the event for each record."
msgstr "har bir yozuv uchun voqaning tugash davomiyligini ta'minlaydigan maydon nomi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3976
msgid "``dependency_field``"
msgstr "``dependency_field``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3974
msgid ""
"name of the ``many2many`` field that provides the dependency relation "
"between two records. If B depends on A, ``dependency_field`` is the field"
" that allows getting A from B. Both this field and "
"``dependency_inverted_field`` field are used to draw dependency arrows "
"between pills and reschedule them."
msgstr ""
"Ikkita yozuv o'rtasidagi bog'liqlik munosabatini ta'minlaydigan ``many2many`` "
"maydon nomi. Agar B A ga bog'liq bo'lsa, ``dependency_field`` B dan A ni "
"olish imkonini beruvchi maydon. Ushbu maydon ham va ``dependency_inverted_field`` "
"maydoni ham tabletlar o'rtasida bog'liqlik o'qlarini chizish va ularni "
"qayta rejalashtirish uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3980
msgid ""
"``dependency_inverted_field`` (required if ``dependency_field`` is "
"provided)"
msgstr ""
"``dependency_inverted_field`` (``dependency_field`` taqdim etilsa talab qilinadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3979
msgid ""
"name of the ``many2many`` field that provides the invert dependency "
"relation than ``dependency_field``. If B depends on A, "
"``dependency_inverted_field`` is the field that allows getting B from A."
msgstr ""
"``dependency_field`` dan teskari bog'liqlik munosabatini ta'minlaydigan "
"``many2many`` maydon nomi. Agar B A ga bog'liq bo'lsa, "
"``dependency_inverted_field`` A dan B ni olish imkonini beruvchi maydon."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3982
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:901
msgid "``color``"
msgstr "``color``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3983
msgid "name of the field used to color the pills according to its value"
msgstr "qiymatiga qarab tabletkalarni ranglash uchun foydalaniladigan maydon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4011
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:879
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``decoration-{$name}``"
msgstr "``decoration-{$name}``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3985
msgid "`python expression`_ that evaluates to a bool"
msgstr "bool ga baholanadigan `python ifodasi`_"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3987
msgid ""
"allow changing the style of a cell's text based on the corresponding "
"record's attributes."
msgstr ""
"tegishli yozuv atributlariga asoslab katakcha matni stilini o'zgartirish "
"imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3990
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``{$name}`` can be one of the following `bootstrap contextual color`_ "
"(``danger``, ``info``, ``secondary``, ``success`` or ``warning``)."
msgstr ""
"``{$name}`` quyidagi `bootstrap kontekst rang`_ lardan biri bo'lishi mumkin "
"(``danger``, ``info``, ``secondary``, ``success`` yoki ``warning``)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3993
msgid ""
"Define a conditional display of a record in the style of a row's text "
"based on the corresponding record's attributes."
msgstr ""
"Tegishli yozuv atributlariga asoslab satr matni stilida yozuvning shartli "
"ko'rinishini aniqlang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:3996
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:858
msgid ""
"Values are Python expressions. For each record, the expression is "
"evaluated with the record's attributes as context values and if ``true``,"
" the corresponding style is applied to the row. Here are some of the "
"other values available in the context:"
msgstr ""
"Qiymatlar Python ifodalari. Har bir yozuv uchun, ifoda yozuv atributlari "
"kontekst qiymatlari sifatida baholanadi va agar ``true`` bo'lsa, tegishli "
"stil satrga qo'llaniladi. Kontekstda mavjud bo'lgan boshqa qiymatlardan bir nechtasi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4001
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:863
msgid "``uid``: the id of the current user,"
msgstr "``uid``: joriy foydalanuvchining id si,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4002
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:864
msgid "``today``: the current local date as a string of the form ``YYYY-MM-DD``,"
msgstr "``today``: ``YYYY-MM-DD`` shaklida satr sifatidagi joriy mahalliy sana,"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4003
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:865
msgid ""
"``now``: same as ``today`` with the addition of the current time. This "
"value is formatted as ``YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm:ss``."
msgstr ""
"``now``: joriy vaqt qo'shimchasi bilan ``today`` ga o'xshash. Bu qiymat "
"``YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm:ss`` sifatida formatlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4013
msgid "``default_group_by``"
msgstr "``default_group_by``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4014
msgid "name of a field to group tasks by"
msgstr "vazifalarni guruhlash uchun maydon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4015
msgid "``disable_drag_drop``"
msgstr "``disable_drag_drop``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4016
msgid "if set to true, the gantt view will not have any drag&drop support"
msgstr "agar true ga o'rnatilsa, gantt ko'rinishi hech qanday drag&drop qo'llab-quvvatlashga ega bo'lmaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4017
msgid "``consolidation``"
msgstr "``consolidation``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4018
msgid "field name to display consolidation value in record cell"
msgstr "yozuv katakchasida konsolidatsiya qiymatini ko'rsatish uchun maydon nomi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4021
msgid "``consolidation_max``"
msgstr "``consolidation_max``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4020
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"dictionary with the \"group by\" field as key and the maximum "
"consolidation value that can be reached before displaying the cell in red"
" (e.g. ``{\"user_id\": 100}``)"
msgstr ""
"\"group by\" maydoni kalit sifatida va katakchani qizil rangda ko'rsatishdan "
"oldin erishilishi mumkin bo'lgan maksimal konsolidatsiya qiymati bilan lug'at "
"(masalan, ``{\"user_id\": 100}``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4025
msgid "``consolidation_exclude``"
msgstr "``consolidation_exclude``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4024
msgid ""
"name of the field that describes if the task has to be excluded from the "
"consolidation if set to true it displays a striped zone in the "
"consolidation line"
msgstr ""
"agar true ga o'rnatilsa vazifa konsolidatsiyadan chiqarilishi kerakligini "
"tavsiflovchi maydon nomi, konsolidatsiya chizig'ida chiziqli zona ko'rsatadi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4042
msgid "``create``, ``cell_create``, ``edit``, ``delete``, ``plan``"
msgstr "``create``, ``cell_create``, ``edit``, ``delete``, ``plan``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4028
msgid ""
"allows *dis*\\ abling the corresponding action in the view by setting the"
" corresponding attribute to ``false`` (default: ``true``)."
msgstr ""
"tegishli atributni ``false`` ga o'rnatish orqali ko'rinishdagi tegishli "
"amalni *o'chirib qo'yish* imkonini beradi (standart: ``true``)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4031
msgid ""
"``create``: If enabled, an ``Add`` button will be available in the "
"control panel to create records."
msgstr ""
"``create``: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa, yozuvlar yaratish uchun boshqaruv "
"panelida ``Add`` tugmasi mavjud bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4033
msgid ""
"``cell_create``: If enabled and ``create`` enabled, a \"**+**\" button "
"will be displayed while hovering on a time slot cell to create a new "
"record on that slot."
msgstr ""
"``cell_create``: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa va ``create`` yoqilgan bo'lsa, o'sha "
"slotda yangi yozuv yaratish uchun vaqt sloti katakchasida hoverlanganda "
"\"**+**\" tugmasi ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4035
msgid ""
"``edit``: If enabled, the opened records will be in edit mode (thus "
"editable)."
msgstr ""
"``edit``: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa, ochilgan yozuvlar tahrirlash rejimida bo'ladi "
"(ya'ni tahrir qilinishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4036
msgid ""
"``plan``: If enabled and ``edit`` enabled, a \"magnifying glass\" button "
"will be displayed on time slots to plan unassigned records into that time"
" slot."
msgstr ""
"``plan``: Agar yoqilgan bo'lsa va ``edit`` yoqilgan bo'lsa, tayinlanmagan "
"yozuvlarni o'sha vaqt slotiga rejalashtirish uchun vaqt slotlarida "
"\"lupa\" tugmasi ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4041
msgid ""
"When you do not want to create records on the gantt view and the "
"beginning and end dates are required on the model, the planning feature "
"should be disabled because no record will ever be found."
msgstr ""
"Gantt ko'rinishida yozuvlar yaratishni xohlamasangiz va modelda boshlanish "
"va tugash sanalari talab qilinsa, rejalashtirish funksiyasi o'chirilishi kerak, "
"chunki hech qachon yozuv topilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4047
msgid "``offset``"
msgstr "``offset``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4045
msgid ""
"Depending on the scale, the number of units to add to today to compute "
"the default period. Examples: An offset of +1 in default_scale week will "
"open the gantt view for next week, and an offset of -2 in default_scale "
"month will open the gantt view of 2 months ago."
msgstr ""
"Masshtabga qarab, standart davrni hisoblash uchun bugungiga qo'shiladigan "
"birliklar soni. Misol: default_scale haftasida +1 ofset gantt ko'rinishini "
"keyingi hafta uchun ochadi va default_scale oyida -2 ofset 2 oy oldingi "
"gantt ko'rinishini ochadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4050
msgid "``progress``"
msgstr "``progress``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4050
msgid ""
"name of a field providing the completion percentage for the record's "
"event, between 0 and 100"
msgstr ""
"yozuv voqasi uchun tugallanish foizini taqdim etadigan maydon nomi, 0 "
"dan 100 gacha"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4053
msgid "title of the gantt view"
msgstr "gantt ko'rinishining sarlavhasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4078
msgid "``precision``"
msgstr "``precision``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4055
msgid "JSON object specifying snapping precisions for the pills in each scale."
msgstr "Har bir masshtabda tabletlar uchun tirkash aniqliklarini belgilaydigan JSON ob'ekti."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4057
msgid "Possible values for scale ``day`` are (default: ``hour``):"
msgstr "``day`` masshtabi uchun mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar (standart: ``hour``):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4059
msgid "``hour``: records times snap to full hours (ex: 7:12 becomes 8:00)"
msgstr "``hour``: yozuv vaqtlari to'liq soatlarga tirkashadi (masalan: 7:12 8:00 ga aylanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4061
msgid "``hour:half``: records times snap to half hours (ex: 7:12 becomes 7:30)"
msgstr "``hour:half``: yozuv vaqtlari yarim soatlarga tirkashadi (masalan: 7:12 7:30 ga aylanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4063
msgid "``hour:quarter``: records times snap to half hours (ex: 7:12 becomes 7:15)"
msgstr "``hour:quarter``: yozuv vaqtlari chorak soatlarga tirkashadi (masalan: 7:12 7:15 ga aylanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4065
msgid "Possible values for scale ``week`` are (default: ``day:half``):"
msgstr "``week`` masshtabi uchun mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar (standart: ``day:half``):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4067
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4073
msgid ""
"``day``: records times snap to full days (ex: 7:28 AM becomes 11:59:59 PM"
" of the previous day, 10:32 PM becomes 12:00 PM of the current day)"
msgstr ""
"``day``: yozuv vaqtlari to'liq kunlarga tirkashadi (masalan: 7:28 AM "
"oldingi kunning 11:59:59 PM ga, 10:32 PM joriy kunning 12:00 PM ga aylanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4069
#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4075
msgid ""
"``day:half``: records times snap to half hours (ex: 7:28 AM becomes 12:00"
" PM)"
msgstr ""
"``day:half``: yozuv vaqtlari yarim soatlarga tirkashadi (masalan: 7:28 AM "
"12:00 PM ga aylanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4071
msgid "Possible values for scale ``month`` are (default: ``day:half``):"
msgstr "``month`` masshtabi uchun mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar (standart: ``day:half``):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4077
msgid "Scale ``year`` always snap to full day."
msgstr "``year`` masshtabi har doim to'liq kunga tirkashadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4079
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Example of precision attribute: ``{\"day\": \"hour:quarter\", \"week\": "
"\"day:half\", \"month\": \"day\"}``"
msgstr ""
"Aniqlik atributi misoli: ``{\"day\": \"hour:quarter\", \"week\": "
"\"day:half\", \"month\": \"day\"}``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4081
msgid "``total_row``"
msgstr "``total_row``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4081
msgid ""
"boolean to control whether the row containing the total count of records "
"should be displayed. (default: ``false``)"
msgstr ""
"yozuvlarning umumiy sonini o'z ichiga olgan satr ko'rsatilishi kerakligini "
"boshqarish uchun boolean. (standart: ``false``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4084
msgid "``collapse_first_level``"
msgstr "``collapse_first_level``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4084
msgid ""
"boolean to control whether it is possible to collapse each row if grouped"
" by one field. (default: ``false``, the collapse starts when grouping by "
"two fields)"
msgstr ""
"bitta maydon bo'yicha guruhlangan bo'lsa har bir satrni yig'ish mumkinligini "
"boshqarish uchun boolean. (standart: ``false``, yig'ish ikkita maydon bo'yicha "
"guruhlashda boshlanadi)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4088
msgid "``display_unavailability``"
msgstr "``display_unavailability``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4087
msgid ""
"boolean to mark the dates returned by the ``gantt_unavailability`` "
"function of the model as available inside the gantt view. Records can "
"still be scheduled in them, but their unavailability is visually "
"displayed. (default: ``false``)"
msgstr ""
"modelning ``gantt_unavailability`` funksiyasi tomonidan qaytarilgan sanalarni "
"gantt ko'rinishida mavjud deb belgilash uchun boolean. Yozuvlar ular uchun "
"hali ham rejalashtirilishi mumkin, ammo ularning mavjud emasligi vizual "
"ko'rsatiladi. (standart: ``false``)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4096
msgid "``default_scale``"
msgstr "``default_scale``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4091
msgid ""
"default scale when rendering the view. Possible values are (default: "
"``month``):"
msgstr ""
"ko'rinishni ko'rsatishda standart masshtab. Mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlar "
"(standart: ``month``):"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4093
msgid "``day``"
msgstr "``day``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4094
msgid "``week``"
msgstr "``week``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4095
msgid "``month``"
msgstr "``month``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4096
msgid "``year``"
msgstr "``year``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4100
msgid "``scales``"
msgstr "``scales``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4099
msgid ""
"comma-separated list of allowed scales for this view. By default, all "
"scales are allowed. For possible scale values to use in this list, see "
"``default_scale``."
msgstr ""
"ushbu ko'rinish uchun ruxsat etilgan masshtablarning vergul bilan ajratilgan "
"ro'yxati. Standart bo'yicha, barcha masshtablarga ruxsat beriladi. Ushbu "
"ro'yxatda ishlatiladigan mumkin bo'lgan masshtab qiymatlari uchun ``default_scale`` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4103
msgid ""
"defines the :ref:`reference/qweb` template ``gantt-popover`` which is "
"used when the user hovers over one of the records in the gantt view."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi gantt ko'rinishidagi yozuvlardan birida hoverlanganda "
"ishlatiluvchi :ref:`reference/qweb` shabloni ``gantt-popover`` ni aniqlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4106
msgid ""
"The gantt view uses mostly-standard :ref:`javascript qweb "
"<reference/qweb/javascript>` and provides the following context "
"variables:"
msgstr ""
"Gantt ko'rinishi asosan standart :ref:`javascript qweb <reference/qweb/javascript>` "
"dan foydalanadi va quyidagi kontekst o'zgaruvchilarini taqdim etadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4112
msgid ""
"the current :js:class:`GanttRow`, can be used to fetch some meta-"
"information. The ``getColor`` method to convert in a color integer is "
"also available directly in the template context without using ``widget``."
msgstr ""
"joriy :js:class:`GanttRow`, ba'zi meta-ma'lumotlarni olish uchun "
"ishlatilishi mumkin. Rang butun soniga konvertatsiya qilish uchun ``getColor`` "
"usuli ham ``widget`` dan foydalanmasdan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri shablon "
"kontekstida mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4118
msgid "``on_create``"
msgstr "``on_create``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4117
msgid ""
"If specified when clicking the add button on the view, instead of opening"
" a generic dialog, launch a client action. this should hold the xmlid of "
"the action (eg: ``on_create=\"%(my_module.my_wizard)d\"``"
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishdagi qo'shish tugmasini bosish jarayonida belgilansa, umumiy dialog "
"ochish o'rniga mijoz amalini ishga tushiring. Bu amalning xmlid sini saqlashi "
"kerak (masalan: ``on_create=\"%(my_module.my_wizard)d\"``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4123
msgid "``form_view_id``"
msgstr "``form_view_id``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4121
msgid ""
"view to open when the user create or edit a record. Note that if this "
"attribute is not set, the gantt view will fall back to the id of the form"
" view in the current action, if any."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi yozuv yaratganda yoki tahrirlaganda ochish uchun ko'rinish. "
"Agar bu atribut o'rnatilmagan bo'lsa, gantt ko'rinishi joriy amaldagi shakl "
"ko'rinishining id siga qaytadi (agar mavjud bo'lsa)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4127
msgid "``dynamic_range``"
msgstr "``dynamic_range``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4126
msgid ""
"if set to true, the gantt view will start at the first record, instead of"
" starting at the beginning of the year/month/day."
msgstr ""
"agar true ga o'rnatilsa, gantt ko'rinishi yil/oy/kunning boshidan "
"emas, birinchi yozuvdan boshlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4131
msgid "``pill_label``"
msgstr "``pill_label``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4130
msgid ""
"If set to true, the time appears in the pill label when the scale is set "
"on week or month. (e.g. `7:00 AM - 11:00 AM (4h) - DST Task 1`)"
msgstr ""
"Agar true ga o'rnatilsa, masshtab hafta yoki oyga o'rnatilganda tablet "
"yorlig'ida vaqt ko'rinadi. (masalan, `7:00 AM - 11:00 AM (4h) - DST Task 1`)"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4150
msgid "``thumbnails``"
msgstr "``thumbnails``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4134
msgid ""
"This allows to display a thumbnail next to groups name if the group is a "
"relationnal field. This expects a python dict which keys are the name of "
"the field on the active model. Values are the names of the field holding "
"the thumbnail on the related model."
msgstr ""
"Bu guruh relatsion maydon bo'lsa, guruhlar nomi yonida eskiz ko'rsatish "
"imkonini beradi. Bu kalidlar faol modelda maydon nomi bo'lgan python "
"lug'atini kutadi. Qiymatlar tegishli modeldagi eskizni saqlagan maydon nomlari."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4138
msgid ""
"Example: tasks have a field user_id that reference res.users. The "
"res.users model has a field image that holds the avatar, then:"
msgstr ""
"Misol: vazifalar res.users ga havola qiladigan user_id maydoniga ega. "
"res.users modeli avatarani saqlaydigan image maydoniga ega, keyin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4150
msgid ""
"will display the users avatars next to their names when grouped by "
"user_id."
msgstr ""
"user_id bo'yicha guruhlanganda foydalanuvchilar avatarlarini nomlarining "
"yonida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4163
msgid ""
"This view is able to display records on a map and the routes between "
"them. The records are represented by pins. It also allows the "
"visualization of fields from the model in a popup tied to the record's "
"pin."
msgstr ""
"Bu ko'rinish yozuvlarni xaritada va ular orasidagi marshrutlarni ko'rsatish "
"imkoniga ega. Yozuvlar pinlar bilan ko'rsatiladi. Shuningdek, modeldan "
"maydonlarni yozuv pini bilan bog'liq popupda vizualizatsiya qilish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4167
msgid ""
"The model on which the view is applied should contain a `res.partner` "
"many2one since the view relies on the `res.partner`'s address and "
"coordinates fields to localize the records."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinish qo'llaniladigan model `res.partner` many2one ni o'z ichiga olishi kerak, "
"chunki ko'rinish yozuvlarni lokalizatsiya qilish uchun `res.partner` ning "
"manzil va koordinatalar maydonlariga tayanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4172
msgid ""
"The view uses location data platforms' API to fetch the tiles (the map's "
"background), do the geoforwarding (converting addresses to a set of "
"coordinates) and fetch the routes. The view implements two API, "
"OpenStreetMap and MapBox. OpenStreetMap is used by default and is able to"
" fetch `tiles`_ and do `geoforwarding`_. This API does not require a "
"token. As soon as a valid `MapBox`_ token is provided in the general "
"settings the view switches to the MapBox API. This API is faster and "
"allows the computation of routes. A token can be obtained by `signing "
"up`_ to MapBox."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinish plitkalarni (xaritaning fonini) olish, geoforwarding qilish (manzillarni "
"koordinatalar to'plamiga aylantirish) va marshrutlarni olish uchun joylashuv "
"ma'lumot platformalari API sidan foydalanadi. Ko'rinish ikkita API ni amalga "
"oshiradi: OpenStreetMap va MapBox. OpenStreetMap standart bo'yicha ishlatiladi "
"va `plitka`_ larni olish va `geoforwarding`_ qilish qodir. Bu API token talab "
"qilmaydi. Umumiy sozlamalarda to'g'ri `MapBox`_ token taqdim etilishi bilan "
"ko'rinish MapBox API ga o'tadi. Bu API tezroq va marshrutlarni hisoblash "
"imkonini beradi. Token MapBox ga `ro'yxatdan o'tish`_ orqali olinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4179
msgid ""
"The view's root element is ``<map>``. It can have the following "
"attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishning ildiz elementi ``<map>`` dir. U quyidagi atributlarga ega "
"bo'lishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4184
msgid "``res_partner``"
msgstr "``res_partner``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4185
msgid ""
"Contains the `res.partner` many2one. If not provided the view resorts to "
"create an empty map."
msgstr ""
"`res.partner` many2one ni o'z ichiga oladi. Agar berilmasa, ko'rinish "
"bo'sh xarita yaratishga murojaat qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4186
msgid "``default_order``"
msgstr "``default_order``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4187
msgid ""
"If a field is provided the view overrides the model's default order. The "
"field must be part of the model on which the view is applied, not from "
"`res.partner`."
msgstr ""
"Agar maydon berilsa, ko'rinish modelning standart tartibini bekor qiladi. "
"Maydon ko'rinish qo'llaniladigan modelning bir qismi bo'lishi kerak, "
"`res.partner` dan emas."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4188
msgid "``routing``"
msgstr "``routing``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4189
msgid ""
"if ``1`` display the routes between the records. The view needs a valid "
"MapBox token and at least two located records (i.e the records have a "
"`res.partner` many2one and the partner has an address or valid "
"coordinates)."
msgstr ""
"agar ``1`` bo'lsa yozuvlar orasidagi marshrutlarni ko'rsatadi. Ko'rinish "
"to'g'ri MapBox token va kamida ikkita joylashtirilgan yozuvni talab qiladi "
"(ya'ni yozuvlarda `res.partner` many2one va partnyor manzil yoki to'g'ri "
"koordinatalarga ega bo'lishi kerak)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4190
msgid "``hide_name``"
msgstr "``hide_name``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4191
msgid "if ``1`` hide the name from the pin's popup (default: ``0``)."
msgstr "agar ``1`` bo'lsa pin popupidan nomni yashiradi (standart: ``0``)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4192
msgid "``hide_address``"
msgstr "``hide_address``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4193
msgid "if ``1`` hide the address from the pin's popup (default: ``0``)."
msgstr "agar ``1`` bo'lsa pin popupidan manzilni yashiradi (standart: ``0``)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4194
msgid "``hide_title``"
msgstr "``hide_title``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4195
msgid "if ``1`` hide the title from the pin list (default: ``0``)."
msgstr "agar ``1`` bo'lsa pin ro'yxatidan sarlavhani yashiradi (standart: ``0``)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4196
msgid "``panel_title``"
msgstr "``panel_title``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4197
msgid ""
"String to display as title of the pin list. If not provided, the title is"
" the action's name or \"Items\" if the view is not in an action."
msgstr ""
"Pin ro'yxatining sarlavhasi sifatida ko'rsatiladigan satr. Agar berilmasa, "
"sarlavha amalning nomi yoki ko'rinish amalda bo'lmasa \"Items\" bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4199
msgid "``limit``"
msgstr "``limit``"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4199
msgid ""
"Maximum number of records to fetch (default: ``80``). It must be a "
"positive integer."
msgstr ""
"Olish uchun maksimal yozuvlar soni (standart: ``80``). U musbat butun son "
"bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4201
msgid ""
"The ``<map>`` element can contain multiple ``<field>`` elements. Each "
"``<field>`` element is interpreted as a line in the pin's popup. The "
"field's attributes are the following:"
msgstr ""
"``<map>`` elementi bir nechta ``<field>`` elementlarini o'z ichiga olishi "
"mumkin. Har bir ``<field>`` elementi pin popupidagi satr sifatida talqin "
"qilinadi. Maydon atributlari quyidagilar:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4206
msgid "The field to display."
msgstr "Ko'rsatiladigan maydon."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4208
msgid ""
"String to display before the field's content. It can be used as a "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Maydon kontentidan oldin ko'rsatiladigan satr. U tavsif sifatida "
"ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_architectures.rst:4215
msgid "For example here is a map:"
msgstr "Masalan, bu xarita:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:3
msgid "View records"
msgstr "Ko'rinish yozuvlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:5
msgid ""
"Views are what define how records should be displayed to end-users. They "
"are specified in XML and stored as records themselves, meaning they can "
"be edited independently from the models that they represent. They are "
"flexible and allow a high level of customization of the screens that they"
" control. There exist various :ref:`types of views "
"<reference/view_records/types>`. Each represents a visualization mode: "
"*form*, *list*, *kanban*, etc."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rinishlar yozuvlarning oxirgi foydalanuvchilarga qanday ko'rsatilishini "
"aniqlaydi. Ular XML da ko'rsatiladi va o'zlarini yozuvlar sifatida saqlanadi, "
"ya'ni ular ifodalagan modellardan mustaqil ravishda tahrirlanishi mumkin. "
"Ular moslashuvchan va boshqaradigan ekranlarni yuqori darajada sozlash "
"imkonini beradi. Turli xil :ref:`ko'rinish turlari <reference/view_records/types>` "
"mavjud. Har biri vizualizatsiya rejimini ifodalaydi: *form*, *list*, *kanban* va hokazo."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:14
msgid "Generic structure"
msgstr "Umumiy tuzilma"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:16
msgid ""
"Basic views generally share the common minimal structure defined below. "
"Placeholders are denoted in all caps."
msgstr ""
"Asosiy ko'rinishlar odatda quyida belgilangan umumiy minimal tuzilmani "
"o'zaro baham ko'radi. To'ldirgichlar to'liq bosh harf bilan ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:34
msgid "View types"
msgstr "Ko'rinish turlari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:36
msgid ":ref:`Form <reference/view_architectures/form>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Form <reference/view_architectures/form>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:37
msgid "Display and edit the data from a single record."
msgstr "Bitta yozuvdan ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatish va tahrirlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:38
msgid ":ref:`List <reference/view_architectures/list>`"
msgstr ":ref:`List <reference/view_architectures/list>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:39
msgid "View and edit multiple records."
msgstr "Bir nechta yozuvlarni ko'rish va tahrirlash."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:40
msgid ":ref:`Search <reference/view_architectures/search>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Search <reference/view_architectures/search>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:41
msgid ""
"Apply filters and perform searches. The results are displayed in the "
"current list, kanban... view."
msgstr ""
"Filtrlar qo'llash va qidiruvlar bajarish. Natijalar joriy ro'yxat, "
"kanban... ko'rinishida ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:42
msgid ":ref:`Kanban <reference/view_architectures/kanban>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Kanban <reference/view_architectures/kanban>`"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:43
msgid "Display records as \"cards\", configurable as a small template."
msgstr "Yozuvlarni kichik shablon sifatida sozlanishi mumkin bo'lgan \"kartalar\" sifatida ko'rsatish."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:44
