#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:169
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:521
msgid "Inheritance"
msgstr "Meros olish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:171
msgid ""
"Inheritance allows for customizing delivered views. It makes it possible,"
" for example, to add content as modules are installed, or to deliver "
"different displays according to the action."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish taqdim etilgan ko'rinishlarni sozlash imkonini beradi. Bu, "
"masalan, modullar o'rnatilganda kontent qo'shish yoki amalga qarab "
"turli ko'rinishlarni taqdim etish imkonini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:174
msgid ""
"Inherit views generally share the common structure defined below. "
"Placeholders are denoted in all caps. This synthetic view will update a "
"node targeted by an XPath, and another targeted by its name and "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
"Meros oluvchi ko'rinishlar odatda quyida belgilangan umumiy tuzilmani "
"o'zaro baham ko'radi. To'ldirgichlar to'liq bosh harf bilan ko'rsatiladi. "
"Bu sintetik ko'rinish XPath tomonidan nishonlangan tugunni va nomi va "
"atributlari bilan nishonlangan boshqasini yangilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:194
msgid ""
"The `inherit_id` and `mode` fields determine the :ref:`view resolution "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/resolution>`. The `xpath` or `NODE` "
"elements indicate the :ref:`inheritance specs "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/specs>`. The `expr` and `position` "
"attributes specify the :ref:`inheritance position "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/position>`."
msgstr ""
"`inherit_id` va `mode` maydonlari :ref:`ko'rinishni hal qilishni "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/resolution>` aniqlaydi. `xpath` yoki "
"`NODE` elementlari :ref:`meros olish spetsifikatsiyalarini "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/specs>` bildiradi. `expr` va `position` "
"atributlari :ref:`meros olish pozitsiyasini "
"<reference/view_records/inheritance/position>` belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:202
msgid "View resolution"
msgstr "Ko'rinishni hal qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:204
msgid ""
"Resolution generates the final `arch` for a requested/matched `primary` "
"view as follow:"
msgstr ""
"Hal qilish so'ralgan/mos `primary` ko'rinish uchun yakuniy `arch` ni "
"quyidagicha yaratadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:206
msgid ""
"if the view has a parent, the parent is fully resolved, then the current "
"view's inheritance specs are applied;"
msgstr ""
"agar ko'rinishda ota-ona mavjud bo'lsa, ota-ona to'liq hal qilinadi, "
"keyin joriy ko'rinishning meros olish spetsifikatsiyalari qo'llaniladi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:208
msgid "if the view has no parent, its `arch` is used as-is;"
msgstr "agar ko'rinishda ota-ona bo'lmasa, uning `arch` i xuddi shunday ishlatiladi;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:209
msgid ""
"the current view's children with mode `extension` are looked up, and "
"their inheritance specs are applied depth-first (a child view is applied,"
" then its children, then its siblings)."
msgstr ""
"joriy ko'rinishning `extension` rejimidagi bolalari qidiriladi va "
"ularning meros olish spetsifikatsiyalari chuqurlik-birinchi qo'llaniladi "
"(bola ko'rinish qo'llaniladi, keyin uning bolalari, keyin uning tengdoshlari)."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:212
msgid ""
"The inheritance is applied according to the `inherit_id` field. If "
"several view records inherit the same view, the order is determined by "
"the `priority`."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish `inherit_id` maydoniga muvofiq qo'llaniladi. Agar bir nechta "
"ko'rinish yozuvlari bir xil ko'rinishdan meros olsa, tartib `priority` "
"tomonidan aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:215
msgid "The result of applying children views yields the final `arch`."
msgstr "Bola ko'rinishlarni qo'llash natijasi yakuniy `arch` ni beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:217
msgid "NOTE on fields_view_get and link to ORM ?"
msgstr "fields_view_get va ORM ga havola haqida ESLATMA ?"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:222
msgid "Inheritance specs"
msgstr "Meros olish spetsifikatsiyalari"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:224
msgid "Inheritance specs are applied sequentially and are comprised of:"
msgstr "Meros olish spetsifikatsiyalari ketma-ket qo'llaniladi va quyidagilardan iborat:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:226
msgid "an element locator to match the inherited element in the parent view;"
msgstr "ota-ona ko'rinishidagi meros olingan elementga mos keladigan element lokatori;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:227
msgid "children element to modify the inherited element."
msgstr "meros olingan elementni o'zgartirish uchun bola element."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:229
msgid "There are three types of element locators:"
msgstr "Element lokatorlarining uch turi mavjud:"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:231
msgid ""
"An `xpath` element with an `expr` attribute. `expr` is an `XPath "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XPath>`_ expression\\ [#hasclass]_ applied"
" to the current `arch`, matching the first node it finds;"
msgstr ""
"`expr` atributiga ega `xpath` elementi. `expr` joriy `arch` ga qo'llaniladigan, "
"topilgan birinchi tugunga mos keladigan `XPath <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XPath>`_ "
"ifodasi [#hasclass]_;"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:234
msgid ""
"A `field` element with a `name` attribute, matching the first field with "
"the same `name`."
msgstr ""
"`name` atributiga ega `field` elementi, bir xil `name` ga ega birinchi "
"maydonга mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:237
msgid "All other attributes are ignored."
msgstr "Barcha boshqa atributlar e'tiborga olinmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:239
msgid ""
"Any other element, matching the first element with the same `name` and "
"identical attributes."
msgstr ""
"Istalgan boshqa element, bir xil `name` va bir xil atributlarga ega "
"birinchi elementga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:242
msgid "The attributes `position` and `version` are ignored."
msgstr "`position` va `version` atributlari e'tiborga olinmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:244
msgid ""
"An extension function is added for simpler matching in QWeb views: "
"`hasclass(*classes)` matches if the context node has all the specified "
"classes."
msgstr ""
"QWeb ko'rinishlarida oddiyroq moslik uchun kengaytma funksiya qo'shilgan: "
"`hasclass(*classes)` kontekst tugunida barcha belgilangan klasslar bo'lsa mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:261
msgid "Inheritance position"
msgstr "Meros olish pozitsiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:263
msgid ""
"The inheritance specs accept an optional `position` attribute, defaulting"
" to `inside`, that specifies how the matched node should be modified."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish spetsifikatsiyalari standart `inside` bo'lgan ixtiyoriy "
"`position` atributini qabul qiladi, bu mos kelgan tugun qanday o'zgartirilishi "
"kerakligini belgilaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:268
msgid "The content of the inheritance spec is appended to the matched node."
msgstr "Meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontenti mos kelgan tugunga qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:282
msgid ""
"The content of the inheritance spec is appended to the matched node's "
"parent after the matched node."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontenti mos kelgan tugunning ota-onasiga "
"mos kelgan tugundan keyin qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:295
msgid ""
"The content of the inheritance spec is appended to the matched node's "
"parent before the matched node."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontenti mos kelgan tugunning ota-onasiga "
"mos kelgan tugundan oldin qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:308
msgid ""
"The content of the inheritance spec replaces the matched node. Any text "
"node containing only `$0` within the contents of the spec is replaced by "
"a copy of the matched node, effectively wrapping the matched node."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontenti mos kelgan tugunni almashtiradi. "
"Spets kontentida faqat `$0` ni o'z ichiga olgan matn tugun mos kelgan "
"tugunning nusxasi bilan almashtiriladi, samarali ravishda mos kelgan "
"tugunni o'rab oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:324
msgid ""
"The content of the inheritance spec should be made of only `attribute` "
"elements, each with a `name` attribute and an optional body."
msgstr ""
"Meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontenti faqat `attribute` elementlaridan "
"tashkil topishi kerak, har biri `name` atributi va ixtiyoriy korpusga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:327
msgid ""
"If the `attribute` element has a body, a new attributed named after its "
"`name` is added to the matched node with the `attribute` element's text "
"as value."
msgstr ""
"Agar `attribute` elementi korpusga ega bo'lsa, uning `name` idan nomlangan "
"yangi atribut `attribute` elementining matni qiymat sifatida mos kelgan "
"tugunga qo'shiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:329
msgid ""
"If the `attribute` element has no body, the attribute named after its "
"`name` is removed from the matched node."
msgstr ""
"Agar `attribute` elementida korpus bo'lmasa, uning `name` idan nomlangan "
"atribut mos kelgan tugundan olib tashlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:331
msgid ""
"If the `attribute` element has an `add` attribute, a `remove` attribute, "
"or both, the value of the matched node's attribute named after `name` is "
"recomputed to account for the value(s) of `add`, `remove`, and an "
"optional `separator` attribute defaulting to `,`. `add` includes its "
"value(s), separated by `separator`. `remove` removes its value(s), "
"separated by `separator`."
msgstr ""
"Agar `attribute` elementida `add` atributi, `remove` atributi yoki ikkalasi "
"bo'lsa, `name` dan nomlangan mos kelgan tugun atributining qiymati `add`, "
"`remove` va standart `,` bo'lgan ixtiyoriy `separator` atributi qiymatlarini "
"hisobga olish uchun qayta hisoblanadi. `add` o'z qiymat(lar)ini `separator` "
"bilan ajratilgan holda o'z ichiga oladi. `remove` o'z qiymat(lar)ini "
"`separator` bilan ajratilgan holda olib tashlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:346
msgid ""
"The attribute `position=\"move\"` is set on the content of the "
"inheritance spec to specify how nodes are moved relatively to the "
"inheritance spec's element locator, on which the attribute `position` "
"must also be set, with values `inside`, `replace`, `after`, or `before`."
msgstr ""
"``position=\"move\"`` atributi meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining kontentida "
"tugunlarning meros olish spetsifikatsiyasining element lokatoriga nisbatan "
"qanday ko'chirilishini belgilash uchun o'rnatiladi, unda `position` atributi "
"ham `inside`, `replace`, `after` yoki `before` qiymatlari bilan o'rnatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/reference/user_interface/view_records.rst:364
msgid "Model commons"
msgstr "Model umumiyliklari"

