"by killing the corresponding OS process."
msgstr ""
"Server terminaldan ``Ctrl-C`` ni ikki marta bosish orqali yoki tegishli "
"OS jarayonini to'xtatish orqali to'xtatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:38
msgid "Build an Odoo module"
msgstr "Odoo moduli yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:40
msgid ""
"Both server and client extensions are packaged as *modules* which are "
