#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:443
msgid "Relations between models"
msgstr "Modellar o'rtasidagi munosabatlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:445
msgid ""
"A record from a model may be related to a record from another model. For "
"instance, a sale order record is related to a client record that contains"
" the client data; it is also related to its sale order line records."
msgstr ""
"Modeldan yozuv boshqa modeldan yozuv bilan bog'liq bo'lishi mumkin. Masalan, "
"savdo buyurtma yozuvi mijoz ma'lumotlarini o'z ichiga olgan mijoz yozuvi bilan "
"bog'liq; u shuningdek savdo buyurtma qatori yozuvlari bilan ham bog'liq."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:449
msgid "Create a session model"
msgstr "Sessiya modelini yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:451
msgid ""
"For the module Open Academy, we consider a model for *sessions*: a "
"session is an occurrence of a course taught at a given time for a given "
"audience."
msgstr ""
"Open Academy moduli uchun biz *sessiyalar* uchun model ko'rib chiqamiz: "
"sessiya muayyan vaqtda muayyan auditoriya uchun o'tiladigan kursning bir "
"hodisasidir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:454
msgid ""
"Create a model for *sessions*. A session has a name, a start date, a "
"duration and a number of seats. Add an action and a menu item to display "
"them. Make the new model visible via a menu item."
msgstr ""
"*Sessiyalar* uchun model yarating. Sessiyaning nomi, boshlanish sanasi, "
"davomiyligi va o'rindiqlar soni mavjud. Ularni ko'rsatish uchun amal va "
"menyu elementi qo'shing. Yangi modelni menyu elementi orqali ko'rinadigan "
"qiling."

