msgid ""
"Relational fields link records, either of the same model (hierarchies) or"
" between different models."
msgstr ""
"Relatsion maydonlar yozuvlarni bir xil model (ierarxiyalar) ichida yoki "
"turli modellar o'rtasida bog'laydi."

