msgid "Many2one relations"
msgstr "Many2one munosabatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:497
msgid ""
"Using a many2one, modify the *Course* and *Session* models to reflect "
"their relation with other models:"
msgstr ""
"many2one dan foydalanib, *Course* va *Session* modellarini boshqa "
"modellar bilan munosabatlarini aks ettirish uchun o'zgartiring:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:500
msgid ""
"A course has a *responsible* user; the value of that field is a record of"
" the built-in model ``res.users``."
msgstr ""
"Kursda *mas'ul* foydalanuvchi mavjud; bu maydonning qiymati o'rnatilgan "
"``res.users`` modelning yozuvidir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:502
msgid ""
"A session has an *instructor*; the value of that field is a record of the"
" built-in model ``res.partner``."
msgstr ""
"Sessiyada *o'qituvchi* mavjud; bu maydonning qiymati o'rnatilgan "
"``res.partner`` modelning yozuvidir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:504
msgid ""
"A session is related to a *course*; the value of that field is a record "
"of the model ``openacademy.course`` and is required."
msgstr ""
"Sessiya *kurs* bilan bog'liq; bu maydonning qiymati ``openacademy.course`` "
"modelning yozuvi bo'lib, majburiydir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:506
msgid "Adapt the views."
msgstr "Ko'rinishlarni moslang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:508
msgid "Inverse one2many relations"
msgstr "Teskari one2many munosabatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:510
msgid ""
"Using the inverse relational field one2many, modify the models to reflect"
" the relation between courses and sessions."
msgstr ""
"Teskari relatsion maydon one2many dan foydalanib, kurslar va sessiyalar "
"o'rtasidagi munosabatni aks ettirish uchun modellarni o'zgartiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:513
msgid "Multiple many2many relations"
msgstr "Ko'p many2many munosabatlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:515
msgid ""
"Using the relational field many2many, modify the *Session* model to "
"relate every session to a set of *attendees*. Attendees will be "
"represented by partner records, so we will relate to the built-in model "
"``res.partner``. Adapt the views accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Relatsion maydon many2many dan foydalanib, *Session* modelini har bir "
"sessiyani *ishtirokchilar* to'plami bilan bog'lash uchun o'zgartiring. "
"Ishtirokchilar hamkor yozuvlari bilan ifodalanadi, shuning uchun o'rnatilgan "
"``res.partner`` modeliga murojaat qilamiz. Ko'rinishlarni mos ravishda moslang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:524
msgid "Model inheritance"
msgstr "Model meros olish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:526
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:112
msgid ""
"Odoo provides two *inheritance* mechanisms to extend an existing model in"
" a modular way."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mavjud modelni modulli tarzda kengaytirish uchun ikkita *meros olish* "
"mexanizmini taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:529
msgid ""
"The first inheritance mechanism allows a module to modify the behavior of"
" a model defined in another module:"
msgstr ""
"Birinchi meros olish mexanizmi modulga boshqa modulda aniqlangan modelning "
"xatti-harakatini o'zgartirish imkonini beradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:532
msgid "add fields to a model,"
msgstr "modelga maydonlar qo'shish,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:533
msgid "override the definition of fields on a model,"
msgstr "modeldagi maydonlar ta'rifini qayta aniqlash,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:534
msgid "add constraints to a model,"
msgstr "modelga cheklovlar qo'shish,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:535
msgid "add methods to a model,"
msgstr "modelga metodlar qo'shish,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:536
msgid "override existing methods on a model."
msgstr "modeldagi mavjud metodlarni qayta aniqlash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:538
msgid ""
"The second inheritance mechanism (delegation) allows to link every record"
" of a model to a record in a parent model, and provides transparent "
"access to the fields of the parent record."
msgstr ""
"Ikkinchi meros olish mexanizmi (delegatsiya) modelning har bir yozuvini "
"asosiy modelning yozuviga bog'lash imkonini beradi va asosiy yozuvning "
"maydonlariga shaffof kirish ta'minlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:546
msgid ":attr:`~odoo.models.Model._inherit`"
msgstr ":attr:`~odoo.models.Model._inherit`"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:547
msgid ":attr:`~odoo.models.Model._inherits`"
msgstr ":attr:`~odoo.models.Model._inherits`"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:550
msgid "View inheritance"
msgstr "Ko'rinish meros olish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:552
msgid ""
"Instead of modifying existing views in place (by overwriting them), Odoo "
"provides view inheritance where children \"extension\" views are applied "
"on top of root views, and can add or remove content from their parent."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud ko'rinishlarni o'rnida o'zgartirish o'rniga (ularni qayta yozish orqali), "
"Odoo ko'rinish meros olishni taqdim etadi, bunda bolalar \"kengaytma\" ko'rinishlari "
"ildiz ko'rinishlari ustiga qo'llaniladi va ota-onadan kontent qo'shish yoki "
"olib tashlashi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:556
msgid ""
"An extension view references its parent using the ``inherit_id`` field, "
"and instead of a single view its ``arch`` field is composed of any number"
" of ``xpath`` elements selecting and altering the content of their parent"
" view:"
msgstr ""
"Kengaytma ko'rinishi ota-onasiga ``inherit_id`` maydoni yordamida murojaat "
"qiladi va bitta ko'rinish o'rniga uning ``arch`` maydoni ota-ona ko'rinishining "
"kontentini tanlash va o'zgartiradigan ixtiyoriy miqdordagi ``xpath`` elementlaridan "
"iborat:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:577
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:202
msgid "``expr``"
msgstr "``expr``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:577
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:202
msgid ""
"An XPath_ expression selecting a single element in the parent view. "
"Raises an error if it matches no element or more than one"
msgstr ""
"Ota-ona ko'rinishida bitta elementni tanlaydigan XPath_ ifodasi. "
"Agar hech qanday yoki birdan ortiq elementga mos kelsa, xato chiqaradi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:593
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:218
msgid "``position``"
msgstr "``position``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:580
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:205
msgid "Operation to apply to the matched element:"
msgstr "Mos kelgan elementga qo'llaniladigan amal:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:582
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:207
msgid "``inside``"
msgstr "``inside``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:583
msgid "appends ``xpath``'s body at the end of the matched element"
msgstr "``xpath`` tanasini mos kelgan element oxiriga qo'shadi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:585
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:210
msgid ""
"replaces the matched element with the ``xpath``'s body, replacing any "
"``$0`` node occurrence in the new body with the original element"
msgstr ""
"Mos kelgan elementni ``xpath`` tanasi bilan almashtiradi, yangi tanadagi "
"barcha ``$0`` tugun hodisalarini asl element bilan almashtiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:588
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:213
msgid "inserts the ``xpath``'s body as a sibling before the matched element"
msgstr "``xpath`` tanasini mos kelgan elementdan oldin aka-uka sifatida kiritadi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:590
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:215
msgid "inserts the ``xpaths``'s body as a sibling after the matched element"
msgstr "``xpaths`` tanasini mos kelgan elementdan keyin aka-uka sifatida kiritadi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:592
msgid ""
"alters the attributes of the matched element using special ``attribute`` "
"elements in the ``xpath``'s body"
msgstr ""
"``xpath`` tanasidagi maxsus ``attribute`` elementlari yordamida mos kelgan "
"elementning atributlarini o'zgartiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:596
msgid ""
"When matching a single element, the ``position`` attribute can be set "
"directly on the element to be found. Both inheritances below will give "
"the same result."
msgstr ""
"Bitta elementga mos kelganda, ``position`` atributini topilishi kerak bo'lgan "
"element ustida to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'rnatish mumkin. Quyidagi ikkala meros "
"ham bir xil natija beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:610
msgid "Alter existing content"
msgstr "Mavjud kontentni o'zgartirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:612
msgid ""
"Using model inheritance, modify the existing *Partner* model to add an "
"``instructor`` boolean field, and a many2many field that corresponds to "
"the session-partner relation"
msgstr ""
"Model meros olishdan foydalanib, mavjud *Partner* modelini ``instructor`` "
"mantiqiy maydonini va sessiya-hamkor munosabatiga mos keladigan many2many "
"maydonini qo'shish uchun o'zgartiring"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:615
msgid "Using view inheritance, display this fields in the partner form view"
msgstr "Ko'rinish meros olishdan foydalanib, bu maydonlarni hamkor shakl ko'rinishida ko'rsating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:620
msgid ""
"In Odoo, :ref:`reference/orm/domains` are values that encode conditions "
"on records. A domain is a  list of criteria used to select a subset of a "
"model's records. Each criteria is a triple with a field name, an operator"
" and a value."
msgstr ""
"Odoo da, :ref:`reference/orm/domains` yozuvlardagi shartlarni kodlaydigan "
"qiymatlardir. Domen - model yozuvlarining kichik to'plamini tanlash uchun "
"ishlatiladigan mezonlar ro'yxati. Har bir mezon maydon nomi, operator va "
"qiymatdan iborat uchlik."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:624
msgid ""
"For instance, when used on the *Product* model the following domain "
"selects all *services* with a unit price over *1000*::"
msgstr ""
"Masalan, *Product* modelida ishlatilganda quyidagi domen birlik narxi "
"*1000* dan yuqori barcha *xizmatlar*ni tanlaydi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:629
msgid ""
"By default criteria are combined with an implicit AND. The logical "
"operators ``&`` (AND), ``|`` (OR) and ``!`` (NOT) can be used to "
"explicitly combine criteria. They are used in prefix position (the "
"operator is inserted before its arguments rather than between). For "
"instance to select products \"which are services *OR* have a unit price "
"which is *NOT* between 1000 and 2000\"::"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha mezonlar yashirin AND bilan birlashtiriladi. Mantiqiy "
"operatorlar ``&`` (AND), ``|`` (OR) va ``!`` (NOT) mezonlarni aniq "
"birlashtirish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Ular prefiks pozitsiyasida "
"ishlatiladi (operator argumentlar o'rtasida emas, balki ulardan oldin "
"kiritiladi). Masalan, \"xizmat bo'lgan *YOKI* birlik narxi 1000 va 2000 "
"o'rtasida bo'lmagan\" mahsulotlarni tanlash uchun::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:641
msgid ""
"A ``domain`` parameter can be added to relational fields to limit valid "
"records for the relation when trying to select records in the client "
