msgstr "Relatsion maydonlardagi domenlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:646
msgid ""
"When selecting the instructor for a *Session*, only instructors (partners"
" with ``instructor`` set to ``True``) should be visible."
msgstr ""
"*Sessiya* uchun o'qituvchi tanlaganda, faqat o'qituvchilar (``instructor`` "
