msgid "Dependencies"
msgstr "Bog'liqliklar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:697
msgid ""
"The value of a computed field usually depends on the values of other "
"fields on the computed record. The ORM expects the developer to specify "
"those dependencies on the compute method with the decorator "
":func:`~odoo.api.depends`. The given dependencies are used by the ORM to "
"trigger the recomputation of the field whenever some of its dependencies "
"have been modified::"
msgstr ""
"Hisoblangan maydon qiymati odatda hisoblangan yozuvdagi boshqa maydonlar "
"qiymatlariga bog'liq. ORM ishlab chiquvchidan bu bog'liqliklarni "
":func:`~odoo.api.depends` dekoratori bilan hisoblash metodida ko'rsatishni "
"kutadi. Berilgan bog'liqliklar ORM tomonidan bog'liqliklardan biri "
"o'zgartirilganda maydonni qayta hisoblashni ishga tushirish uchun ishlatiladi::"

