msgid "add the given domain to the current search"
msgstr "berilgan domenni joriy qidiruvga qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:935
msgid ""
"add some context to the current search; use the key ``group_by`` to group"
" results on the given field name"
msgstr ""
"joriy qidiruvga biroz kontekst qo'shish; natijallarni berilgan maydon "
"nomiga guruhlash uchun ``group_by`` kalitidan foydalaning"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:955
msgid ""
"To use a non-default search view in an action, it should be linked using "
"the ``search_view_id`` field of the action record."
msgstr ""
"Amaldagi standart bo'lmagan qidiruv ko'rinishidan foydalanish uchun, u "
"amal yozuvining ``search_view_id`` maydoni yordamida bog'lanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:958
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The action can also set default values for search fields through its "
"``context`` field: context keys of the form "
":samp:`search_default_{field_name}` will initialize *field_name* with the"
" provided value. Search filters must have an optional ``@name`` to have a"
" default and behave as booleans (they can only be enabled by default)."
msgstr ""
"Amal shuningdek ``context`` maydoni orqali qidiruv maydonlari uchun standart "
"qiymatlar o'rnatishi mumkin: :samp:`search_default_{field_name}` ko'rinishidagi "
"kontekst kalitlari *field_name* ni berilgan qiymat bilan ishga tushiradi. "
"Qidiruv filtrlari standartga ega bo'lish va mantiqiy sifatida harakat qilish "
"uchun ixtiyoriy ``@name`` ga ega bo'lishi kerak (ular faqat standart bo'yicha "
"yoqilishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:966
msgid ""
"Add a button to filter the courses for which the current user is the "
"responsible in the course search view. Make it selected by default."
msgstr ""
"Kurs qidiruv ko'rinishida joriy foydalanuvchi mas'ul bo'lgan kurslarni "
"filtrlash uchun tugma qo'shing. Uni standart bo'yicha tanlanagan qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:968
msgid "Add a button to group courses by responsible user."
msgstr "Kurslarni mas'ul foydalanuvchi bo'yicha guruhlash uchun tugma qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:974
msgid ""
"The gantt view requires the web_gantt module which is present in the "
":ref:`enterprise edition <install/editions>` version."
msgstr ""
"Gantt ko'rinishi :ref:`enterprise nashr <install/editions>` versiyasida "
"mavjud bo'lgan web_gantt modulini talab qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:977
msgid ""
"Horizontal bar charts typically used to show project planning and "
"advancement, their root element is ``<gantt>``."
msgstr ""
"Loyiha rejalashtirish va rivojlanishini ko'rsatish uchun odatda ishlatiladigan "
"gorizontal chiziqli diagrammalar, ularning ildiz elementi ``<gantt>`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:988
msgid "Gantt charts"
msgstr "Gantt diagrammalari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:990
msgid ""
"Add a Gantt Chart enabling the user to view the sessions scheduling "
"linked to the Open Academy module. The sessions should be grouped by "
"instructor."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchiga Open Academy moduli bilan bog'liq sessiyalar jadvalini "
"ko'rish imkonini beruvchi Gantt diagrammasini qo'shing. Sessiyalar "
"o'qituvchi bo'yicha guruhlangan bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:994
msgid "Graph views"
msgstr "Grafik ko'rinishlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:996
msgid ""
"Graph views allow aggregated overview and analysis of models, their root "
"element is ``<graph>``."
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishlari modellarning agregatlangan ko'rinishini va tahlilini "
"ta'minlaydi, ularning ildiz elementi ``<graph>`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1000
msgid ""
"Pivot views (element ``<pivot>``) a multidimensional table, allows the "
"selection of filers and dimensions to get the right aggregated dataset "
"before moving to a more graphical overview. The pivot view shares the "
"same content definition as graph views."
msgstr ""
"Pivot ko'rinishlari (element ``<pivot>``) ko'p o'lchamli jadval bo'lib, "
"grafik ko'rinishga o'tishdan oldin to'g'ri agregatlangan ma'lumotlar to'plamini "
"olish uchun filtrlar va o'lchamlarni tanlash imkonini beradi. Pivot ko'rinishi "
"grafik ko'rinishlar bilan bir xil kontent ta'rifini baham ko'radi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1004
msgid ""
"Graph views have 4 display modes, the default mode is selected using the "
"``@type`` attribute."
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishlari 4 ta ko'rinish rejimiga ega, standart rejim ``@type`` "
"atributi yordamida tanlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1011
msgid "Bar (default)"
msgstr "Bar (standart)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1008
msgid ""
"a bar chart, the first dimension is used to define groups on the "
"horizontal axis, other dimensions define aggregated bars within each "
"group."
msgstr ""
"chiziqli diagramma, birinchi o'lcham gorizontal o'qda guruhlarni aniqlash "
"uchun ishlatiladi, boshqa o'lchamlar har bir guruh ichidagi agregatlangan "
"barlarni aniqlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1011
msgid ""
"By default bars are side-by-side, they can be stacked by using "
"``@stacked=\"True\"`` on the ``<graph>``"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha barlar yonma-yon, ``<graph>`` da ``@stacked=\"True\"`` "
"yordamida ularni to'plash mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1013
msgid "Line"
msgstr "Chiziq"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1014
msgid "2-dimensional line chart"
msgstr "2 o'lchamli chiziqli diagramma"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1016
msgid "Pie"
msgstr "Pirog"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1016
msgid "2-dimensional pie"
msgstr "2 o'lchamli pirog diagrammasi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1018
msgid ""
"Graph views contain ``<field>`` with a mandatory ``@type`` attribute "
"taking the values:"
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishlari quyidagi qiymatlarni qabul qiladigan majburiy ``@type`` "
"atributiga ega ``<field>`` ni o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1022
msgid "the field should be aggregated by default"
msgstr "maydon standart bo'yicha agregatlangan bo'lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1024
msgid "the field should be aggregated rather than grouped on"
msgstr "maydon guruhlanish o'rniga agregatlangan bo'lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1034
msgid ""
"Graph views perform aggregations on database values, they do not work "
"with non-stored computed fields."
msgstr ""
"Grafik ko'rinishlari ma'lumotlar bazasi qiymatlarida agregatsiya bajaradi, "
"ular saqlanmagan hisoblangan maydonlar bilan ishlamaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1037
msgid "Graph view"
msgstr "Grafik ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1039
msgid ""
"Add a Graph view in the Session object that displays, for each course, "
"the number of attendees under the form of a bar chart."
msgstr ""
"Session ob'ektiga har bir kurs uchun ishtirokchilar sonini chiziqli "
"diagramma shaklida ko'rsatadigan Grafik ko'rinishini qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1045
msgid ""
"Used to organize tasks, production processes, etc… their root element is "
"``<kanban>``."
msgstr ""
"Vazifalar, ishlab chiqarish jarayonlari va h.k.larni tartibga solish uchun "
"ishlatiladi… ularning ildiz elementi ``<kanban>`` dir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1048
msgid ""
"A kanban view shows a set of cards possibly grouped in columns. Each card"
" represents a record, and each column the values of an aggregation field."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishi ehtimol ustunlarda guruhlangan kartalar to'plamini "
"ko'rsatadi. Har bir karta yozuvni, har bir ustun esa agregatsiya maydonining "
"qiymatlarini ifodalaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1051
msgid ""
"For instance, project tasks may be organized by stage (each column is a "
"stage), or by responsible (each column is a user), and so on."
msgstr ""
"Masalan, loyiha vazifalari bosqich bo'yicha (har bir ustun bosqich) yoki "
"mas'ul bo'yicha (har bir ustun foydalanuvchi) va hokazo tartibga solinishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1054
msgid ""
"Kanban views define the structure of each card as a mix of form elements "
"(including basic HTML) and :ref:`reference/qweb`."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishlari har bir kartaning tuzilmasini shakl elementlari "
"(asosiy HTML ni o'z ichiga olgan) va :ref:`reference/qweb` aralashmasi "
"sifatida aniqlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1057
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/14_qwebintro.rst
msgid "Kanban view"
msgstr "Kanban ko'rinishi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1059
msgid ""
"Add a Kanban view that displays sessions grouped by course (columns are "
"thus courses)."
msgstr ""
"Kurs bo'yicha guruhlangan sessiyalarni ko'rsatuvchi Kanban ko'rinishini "
"qo'shing (shuning uchun ustunlar kurslardir)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1065
msgid ""
"Access control mechanisms must be configured to achieve a coherent "
"security policy."
msgstr ""
"Izchil xavfsizlik siyosatiga erishish uchun kirish nazorati mexanizmlari "
"sozlanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1069
msgid "Group-based access control mechanisms"
msgstr "Guruh asosida kirish nazorati mexanizmlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1071
msgid ""
"Groups are created as normal records on the model ``res.groups``, and "
"granted menu access via menu definitions. However even without a menu, "
"objects may still be accessible indirectly, so actual object-level "
"permissions (read, write, create, unlink) must be defined for groups. "
"They are usually inserted via CSV files inside modules. It is also "
"possible to restrict access to specific fields on a view or object using "
"the field's groups attribute."
msgstr ""
"Guruhlar ``res.groups`` modelida oddiy yozuvlar sifatida yaratiladi va "
"menyu ta'riflari orqali menyu kirishiga ruxsat beriladi. Biroq menyu "
"bo'lmasada, ob'ektlarga bilvosita kirish mumkin bo'lishi mumkin, shuning "
"uchun guruhlar uchun haqiqiy ob'ekt darajasidagi ruxsatlar (o'qish, yozish, "
"yaratish, o'chirish) aniqlanishi kerak. Ular odatda modullar ichidagi CSV "
"fayllar orqali kiritiladi. Ko'rinish yoki ob'ektdagi muayyan maydonlarga "
"kirishni maydonning groups atributi yordamida cheklash ham mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1079
msgid "Access rights"
msgstr "Kirish huquqlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1081
msgid ""
"Access rights are defined as records of the model ``ir.model.access``. "
"Each access right is associated to a model, a group (or no group for "
"global access), and a set of permissions: read, write, create, unlink. "
"Such access rights are usually created by a CSV file named after its "
"model: ``ir.model.access.csv``."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqlari ``ir.model.access`` modelining yozuvlari sifatida aniqlanadi. "
"Har bir kirish huquqi model, guruh (yoki global kirish uchun guruhsiz) va "
"ruxsatlar to'plami bilan bog'liq: o'qish, yozish, yaratish, o'chirish. "
"Bunday kirish huquqlari odatda modeli nomidagi CSV fayl orqali yaratiladi: "
"``ir.model.access.csv``."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1093
msgid "Add access control through the Odoo interface"
msgstr "Odoo interfeysi orqali kirish nazoratini qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1095
msgid ""
"Create a new user \"John Smith\". Then create a group \"OpenAcademy / "
"Session Read\" with read access to the *Session* model."
msgstr ""
"Yangi foydalanuvchi \"John Smith\" yarating. Keyin *Session* modeliga "
"o'qish kirishiga ega \"OpenAcademy / Session Read\" guruhini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1098
msgid "Add access control through data files in your module"
msgstr "Modulingizdagi ma'lumot fayllari orqali kirish nazoratini qo'shish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1100
msgid "Using data files,"
msgstr "Ma'lumot fayllaridan foydalanib,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1102
msgid ""
"Create a group *OpenAcademy / Manager* with full access to all "
"OpenAcademy models"
msgstr ""
"Barcha OpenAcademy modellariga to'liq kirish huquqiga ega *OpenAcademy / "
"Manager* guruhini yarating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1104
msgid "Make *Session* and *Course* readable by all users"
msgstr "*Session* va *Course* ni barcha foydalanuvchilar uchun o'qiladigan qiling"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1107
msgid "Record rules"
msgstr "Yozuv qoidalari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1109
msgid ""
"A record rule restricts the access rights to a subset of records of the "
"given model. A rule is a record of the model ``ir.rule``, and is "
"associated to a model, a number of groups (many2many field), permissions "
"to which the restriction applies, and a domain. The domain specifies to "
"which records the access rights are limited."
msgstr ""
"Yozuv qoidasi berilgan modelning yozuvlar kichik to'plamiga kirish huquqlarini "
"cheklaydi. Qoida ``ir.rule`` modelining yozuvi bo'lib, model, bir nechta "
"guruhlar (many2many maydoni), cheklov qo'llaniladigan ruxsatlar va domen "
"bilan bog'liq. Domen kirish huquqlari chegaralanadigan yozuvlarni ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1115
msgid ""
"Here is an example of a rule that prevents the deletion of leads that are"
" not in state ``cancel``. Notice that the value of the field ``groups`` "
"must follow the same convention as the method "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write` of the ORM."
msgstr ""
"Mana ``cancel`` holatida bo'lmagan potentsial mijozlarni o'chirishni "
"oldini oladigan qoida misoli. ``groups`` maydonining qiymati ORM ning "
":meth:`~odoo.models.Model.write` metodi bilan bir xil konventsiyaga "
"rioya qilishi kerakligini e'tibor bering."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1132
msgid "Record rule"
msgstr "Yozuv qoidasi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1134
msgid ""
"Add a record rule for the model Course and the group \"OpenAcademy / "
"Manager\", that restricts ``write`` and ``unlink`` accesses to the "
"responsible of a course. If a course has no responsible, all users of the"
" group must be able to modify it."
msgstr ""
"Course modeli va \"OpenAcademy / Manager\" guruhi uchun kurs mas'uliga "
"``write`` va ``unlink`` kirishlarini cheklaydigan yozuv qoidasi qo'shing. "
"Agar kursda mas'ul bo'lmasa, guruhning barcha foydalanuvchilari uni "
"o'zgartira olishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1142
msgid "Wizards"
msgstr "Sehrgarlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1144
msgid ""
"Wizards describe interactive sessions with the user (or dialog boxes) "
"through dynamic forms. A wizard is simply a model that extends the class "
":class:`~odoo.models.TransientModel` instead of "
":class:`~odoo.models.Model`. The class "
":class:`~odoo.models.TransientModel` extends :class:`~odoo.models.Model` "
"and reuse all its existing mechanisms, with the following "
"particularities:"
msgstr ""
"Sehrgarlar dinamik shakllar orqali foydalanuvchi bilan interaktiv sessiyalarni "
"(yoki dialog qutilari) ta'riflaydi. Sehrgar shunchaki "
":class:`~odoo.models.Model` o'rniga :class:`~odoo.models.TransientModel` "
"klassini kengaytiradigan model. :class:`~odoo.models.TransientModel` klassi "
":class:`~odoo.models.Model` ni kengaytiradi va uning barcha mavjud "
"mexanizmlarini qayta ishlatadi, quyidagi xususiyatlar bilan:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1151
msgid ""
"Wizard records are not meant to be persistent; they are automatically "
"deleted from the database after a certain time. This is why they are "
"called *transient*."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgar yozuvlari doimiy bo'lish uchun mo'ljallanmagan; ular ma'lum vaqtdan "
"keyin ma'lumotlar bazasidan avtomatik ravishda o'chiriladi. Shuning uchun "
"ular *vaqtinchalik* deb ataladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1154
msgid ""
"Wizard records may refer to regular records or wizard records through "
"relational fields(many2one or many2many), but regular records *cannot* "
"refer to wizard records through a many2one field."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgar yozuvlari relatsion maydonlar (many2one yoki many2many) orqali "
"oddiy yozuvlara yoki sehrgar yozuvlariga murojaat qilishi mumkin, lekin "
"oddiy yozuvlar many2one maydoni orqali sehrgar yozuvlariga *murojaat qila olmaydi*."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1158
msgid ""
"We want to create a wizard that allow users to create attendees for a "
"particular session, or for a list of sessions at once."
msgstr ""
"Biz foydalanuvchilarga muayyan sessiya yoki bir vaqtda sessiyalar ro'yxati "
"uchun ishtirokchilar yaratish imkonini beruvchi sehrgar yaratmoqchimiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1161
msgid "Define the wizard"
msgstr "Sehrgarni aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1163
msgid ""
"Create a wizard model with a many2one relationship with the *Session* "
"model and a many2many relationship with the *Partner* model."
msgstr ""
"*Session* modeli bilan many2one munosabatga va *Partner* modeli bilan "
"many2many munosabatga ega sehrgar modeli yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1167
msgid "Launching wizards"
msgstr "Sehrgarlarni ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1169
msgid ""
"Wizards are simply :ref:`window actions <howtos/module/actions>` with a "
"``target`` field set to the value ``new``, which opens the view (usually "
":ref:`a form <howtos/module/views/form>`) in a separate dialog. The "
"action may be triggered via a menu item, but is more generally triggered "
"by a button."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgarlar shunchaki ``target`` maydoni ``new`` qiymatiga o'rnatilgan "
":ref:`oyna amallar <howtos/module/actions>` bo'lib, ko'rinishni (odatda "
":ref:`shakl <howtos/module/views/form>`) alohida dialogda ochadi. Amal "
"menyu elementi orqali ishga tushirilishi mumkin, lekin odatda tugma orqali "
"ishga tushiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1175
msgid ""
"An other way to launch wizards is through the :menuselection:`Action` "
"menu of a list or form view. This is done through the "
"``binding_model_id`` field of the action. Setting this field will make "
"the action appear on the views of the model the action is \"bound\" to."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgarlarni ishga tushirishning boshqa usuli ro'yxat yoki shakl ko'rinishining "
":menuselection:`Amal` menyusi orqali. Bu amalning ``binding_model_id`` "
"maydoni orqali amalga oshiriladi. Bu maydoni o'rnatish amalga \"bog'langan\" "
"modelning ko'rinishlarida amalning paydo bo'lishiga olib keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1191
msgid ""
"While wizards use regular views and buttons, normally clicking any button"
" in a form would first save the form then close the dialog. Because this "
"is often undesirable in wizards, a special attribute "
"``special=\"cancel\"`` is available which immediately closes the wizard "
"without saving the form."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgarlar oddiy ko'rinishlar va tugmalardan foydalansada, odatda shaklda "
"istalgan tugmani bosish avval shaklni saqlaydi, so'ng dialogni yopadi. "
"Bu sehrgarlar uchun ko'pincha istalmagan bo'lgani uchun, shaklni saqlamasdan "
"darhol sehrgarni yopuvchi ``special=\"cancel\"`` maxsus atributi mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1196
msgid "Launch the wizard"
msgstr "Sehrgarni ishga tushirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1198
msgid "Define a form view for the wizard."
msgstr "Sehrgar uchun shakl ko'rinishini aniqlang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1199
msgid "Add the action to launch it in the context of the *Session* model."
msgstr "*Session* modeli kontekstida uni ishga tushirish uchun amal qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1200
msgid ""
"Define a default value for the session field in the wizard; use the "
"context parameter ``self._context`` to retrieve the current session."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgardagi sessiya maydoni uchun standart qiymat aniqlang; joriy sessiyani "
"olish uchun ``self._context`` kontekst parametridan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1203
msgid "Register attendees"
msgstr "Ishtirokchilarni ro'yxatdan o'tkazish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1205
msgid ""
"Add buttons to the wizard, and implement the corresponding method for "
"adding the attendees to the given session."
msgstr ""
"Sehrgarga tugmalar qo'shing va berilgan sessiyaga ishtirokchilarni qo'shish "
"uchun mos metodini implement qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1208
msgid "Register attendees to multiple sessions"
msgstr "Ishtirokchilarni bir nechta sessiyalarga ro'yxatdan o'tkazish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1210
msgid ""
"Modify the wizard model so that attendees can be registered to multiple "
"sessions."
msgstr ""
"Ishtirokchilarni bir nechta sessiyalarga ro'yxatdan o'tkazish mumkin "
"bo'lishi uchun sehrgar modelini o'zgartiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1214
msgid "Internationalization"
msgstr "Xalqarolashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1216
msgid ""
"Each module can provide its own translations within the i18n directory, "
"by having files named LANG.po where LANG is the locale code for the "
"language, or the language and country combination when they differ (e.g. "
"pt.po or pt_BR.po). Translations will be loaded automatically by Odoo for"
" all enabled languages. Developers always use English when creating a "
"module, then export the module terms using Odoo's gettext POT export "
"feature (:menuselection:`Settings --> Translations --> Import/Export --> "
"Export Translation` without specifying a language), to create the module "
"template POT file, and then derive the translated PO files. Many IDE's "
"have plugins or modes for editing and merging PO/POT files."
msgstr ""
"Har bir modul i18n katalogi ichida o'z tarjimalarini taqdim etishi mumkin, "
"LANG.po nomli fayllarga ega bo'lish orqali, bu erda LANG til uchun lokal "
"kod yoki ular farqlanganda til va mamlakat kombinatsiyasi (masalan pt.po "
"yoki pt_BR.po). Tarjimalar barcha yoqilgan tillar uchun Odoo tomonidan "
"avtomatik yuklanadi. Ishlab chiquvchilar modul yaratishda har doim ingliz "
"tilidan foydalanadi, so'ng modul shabloni POT faylini yaratish uchun "
"Odoo ning gettext POT eksport xususiyati (:menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Translations --> Import/Export --> Export Translation` tilni ko'rsatmasdan) "
"yordamida modul atamalarini eksport qiladi, keyin tarjima qilingan PO "
"fayllarini hosil qiladi. Ko'pgina IDE larda PO/POT fayllarini tahrirlash "
"va birlashtirish uchun plaginlar yoki rejimlar mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1228
msgid ""
"The Portable Object files generated by Odoo are published on `Odoo's "
"Translations Platform <https://translate.odoo.com/>`_, making it easy to "
"translate the software."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tomonidan yaratilgan Portable Object fayllari `Odoo ning tarjimalar "
"platformasida <https://translate.odoo.com/>`_ nashr etiladi, bu dasturiy "
"ta'minotni tarjima qilishni osonlashtiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1241
msgid ""
"By default Odoo's POT export only extracts labels inside XML files or "
"inside field definitions in Python code, but any Python string can be "
"translated this way by surrounding it with the function :func:`odoo._` "
"(e.g. ``_(\"Label\")``)"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha Odoo ning POT eksporti faqat XML fayllari ichidagi yoki "
"Python koddagi maydon ta'riflari ichidagi yorliqlarni chiqaradi, lekin "
"har qanday Python qatorini :func:`odoo._` funksiyasi bilan o'rab tarjima "
"qilish mumkin (masalan ``_(\"Label\")``)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1246
