msgstr "Hisobotlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1255
msgid "Printed reports"
msgstr "Chop etiladigan hisobotlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1257
msgid ""
"Odoo uses a report engine based on :ref:`reference/qweb`, `Twitter "
"Bootstrap`_ and Wkhtmltopdf_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo :ref:`reference/qweb`, `Twitter Bootstrap`_ va Wkhtmltopdf_ ga "
"asoslangan hisobot dvigatelidan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1260
msgid "A report is a combination two elements:"
msgstr "Hisobot ikkita elementning kombinatsiyasidir:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1262
msgid ""
"an ``ir.actions.report`` which configures various basic parameters for "
"the report (default type, whether the report should be saved to the "
"database after generation,…)"
msgstr ""
"hisobot uchun turli asosiy parametrlarni sozlaydigan ``ir.actions.report`` "
"(standart tur, hisobot yaratilgandan keyin ma'lumotlar bazasiga saqlanishi "
"kerakmi,…)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1283
msgid ""
"Because it largerly a standard action, as with :ref:`howto/module/wizard`"
" it is generally useful to add the report as a *contextual item* on the "
"list and / or form views of the model being reported on via the "
"``binding_model_id`` field."
msgstr ""
"Bu ko'p jihatdan standart amal bo'lgani uchun, :ref:`howto/module/wizard` "
"da bo'lgani kabi, ``binding_model_id`` maydoni orqali hisobot qilinayotgan "
"modelning ro'yxat va/yoki shakl ko'rinishlarida hisobotni *kontekst elementi* "
"sifatida qo'shish foydali."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1288
msgid ""
"Here we are also using ``binding_type`` in order for the report to be in "
"the *report* contextual menu rather than the *action* one. There is no "
"technical difference but putting elements in the right place helps users."
msgstr ""
"Bu yerda shuningdek hisobot *amal* o'rniga *hisobot* kontekst menyusida "
"bo'lishi uchun ``binding_type`` dan foydalanmoqdamiz. Texnik farq yo'q, "
"lekin elementlarni to'g'ri joyga qo'yish foydalanuvchilarga yordam beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1292
msgid ""
"A standard :ref:`QWeb view <reference/view_architectures/qweb>` for the "
"actual report:"
msgstr ""
