#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1306
msgid ""
"the standard rendering context provides a number of elements, the most "
"important being:"
msgstr ""
"standart ko'rsatish konteksti bir qator elementlarni taqdim etadi, "
"eng muhimlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1310
msgid "the records for which the report is printed"
msgstr "hisobot chop etiladigan yozuvlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1312
msgid "the user printing the report"
msgstr "hisobotni chop etayotgan foydalanuvchi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1314
msgid ""
"Because reports are standard web pages, they are available through a URL "
"and output parameters can be manipulated through this URL, for instance "
"the HTML version of the *Invoice* report is available through "
"http://localhost:8069/report/html/account.report_invoice/1 (if "
"``account`` is installed) and the PDF version through "
"http://localhost:8069/report/pdf/account.report_invoice/1."
msgstr ""
"Hisobotlar standart veb sahifalar bo'lganligi sababli, ular URL orqali "
"mavjud va chiqish parametrlari bu URL orqali boshqarilishi mumkin, masalan "
"*Hisob-faktura* hisobotining HTML versiyasi "
"http://localhost:8069/report/html/account.report_invoice/1 orqali (agar "
"``account`` o'rnatilgan bo'lsa) va PDF versiyasi "
"http://localhost:8069/report/pdf/account.report_invoice/1 orqali mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1325
msgid ""
"If it appears that your PDF report is missing the styles (i.e. the text "
"appears but the style/layout is different from the html version), "
"probably your wkhtmltopdf_ process cannot reach your web server to "
"download them."
msgstr ""
"Agar PDF hisobotingizda uslublar yo'q ko'rinsa (ya'ni matn ko'rinadi, "
"lekin uslub/tartib html versiyasidan farq qiladi), ehtimol wkhtmltopdf_ "
"jarayoningiz ularni yuklab olish uchun veb-serveringizga eta olmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1329
msgid ""
"If you check your server logs and see that the CSS styles are not being "
"downloaded when generating a PDF report, most surely this is the problem."
msgstr ""
"Agar server jurnallaringizni tekshirib, PDF hisobot yaratishda CSS "
"uslublari yuklanmayotganini ko'rsangiz, bu ko'pincha muammo."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1332
msgid ""
"The wkhtmltopdf_ process will use the ``web.base.url`` system parameter "
"as the *root path* to all linked files, but this parameter is "
"automatically updated each time the Administrator is logged in. If your "
"server resides behind some kind of proxy, that could not be reachable. "
"You can fix this by adding one of these system parameters:"
msgstr ""
"wkhtmltopdf_ jarayoni barcha bog'langan fayllar uchun ``web.base.url`` "
"tizim parametrini *ildiz yo'l* sifatida ishlatadi, lekin bu parametr "
"Administrator har kirganda avtomatik yangilanadi. Agar serveringiz qandaydir "
"proksi ortida bo'lsa, unga erishib bo'lmasligi mumkin. Buni quyidagi "
"tizim parametrlaridan birini qo'shish orqali tuzatishingiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1338
msgid ""
"``report.url``, pointing to an URL reachable from your server (probably "
"``http://localhost:8069`` or something similar). It will be used for this"
" particular purpose only."
msgstr ""
"``report.url``, serveringizdan erishish mumkin bo'lgan URL ga ishora "
"qiladi (ehtimol ``http://localhost:8069`` yoki shunga o'xshash). U "
"faqat ushbu maqsad uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1342
msgid ""
"``web.base.url.freeze``, when set to ``True``, will stop the automatic "
"updates to ``web.base.url``."
msgstr ""
"``web.base.url.freeze``, ``True`` ga o'rnatilganda, ``web.base.url`` ga "
"avtomatik yangilanishlarni to'xtatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/backend.rst:1345
