#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:11
msgid "Data Types"
msgstr "Ma'lumot turlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:14
msgid "Master Data"
msgstr "Asosiy ma'lumotlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:16
msgid ""
"Master data is usually part of the technical or business requirements for"
" the module. In other words, such data is often necessary for the module "
"to work properly. This data will always be installed when installing the "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Asosiy ma'lumotlar odatda modul uchun texnik yoki biznes talablarning bir "
"qismidir. Boshqacha qilib aytganda, bunday ma'lumotlar ko'pincha modulning "
"to'g'ri ishlashi uchun zarur. Bu ma'lumotlar modul o'rnatilganda har doim "
"o'rnatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:20
msgid ""
"We already met technical data previously since we have defined "
":doc:`views <../reference/user_interface/view_records>` and :doc:`actions"
" <../reference/backend/actions>`. Those are one kind of master data."
msgstr ""
"Biz avval texnik ma'lumotlar bilan tanishdik, chunki biz "
":doc:`ko'rinishlar <../reference/user_interface/view_records>` va "
":doc:`amallar <../reference/backend/actions>` ni aniqladik. Bular asosiy "
"ma'lumotlarning bir turi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:24
msgid ""
"On top of technical data, business data can be defined, e.g. countries, "
"currencies, units of measure, as well as complete country localization "
"(legal reports, tax definitions, chart of account), and much more..."
msgstr ""
"Texnik ma'lumotlardan tashqari, biznes ma'lumotlari ham aniqlanishi mumkin, "
"masalan mamlakatlar, valyutalar, o'lchov birliklari, shuningdek to'liq "
"mamlakat lokalizatsiyasi (huquqiy hisobotlar, soliq ta'riflari, hisob "
"rejasi) va boshqa ko'plab narsalar..."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:32
msgid "Demo Data"
msgstr "Demo ma'lumotlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:34
msgid ""
"In addition to master data, which is required for a module to work "
"properly, we can also provide data for demonstration purposes:"
msgstr ""
"Modulning to'g'ri ishlashi uchun zarur bo'lgan asosiy ma'lumotlarga qo'shimcha "
"ravishda, namoyish maqsadlari uchun ham ma'lumotlar taqdim etishimiz mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:36
msgid "Help the sales representatives make their demos quickly."
msgstr "Savdo vakillarga ularning namoyishlarini tezda o'tkazishga yordam berish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:37
msgid ""
"Have a set of working data for developers to test new features and see "
"how these new features look with data they might not have added "
"themselves."
msgstr ""
"Ishlab chiquvchilar uchun yangi xususiyatlarni sinash va bu yangi "
"xususiyatlarning o'zlari qo'shmasligi mumkin bo'lgan ma'lumotlar bilan "
"qanday ko'rinishini ko'rish uchun ishchi ma'lumotlar to'plami mavjud bo'lish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:39
msgid "Test that the data is loaded correctly, without raising an error."
msgstr "Ma'lumotlar xato chiqarmasdan to'g'ri yuklanganligini sinash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:40
msgid ""
"Setup most of the features to be used quickly when creating a new "
"database."
msgstr "Yangi ma'lumotlar bazasi yaratishda tezda foydalanish uchun ko'p xususiyatlarni sozlash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:42
msgid ""
"The database manager let you create databases with demo data. The same "
"can be achieved via the command line with :option:`--with-demo <odoo-bin "
"--with-demo>`."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumotlar bazasi menejeri demo ma'lumotlar bilan ma'lumotlar bazasi "
"yaratish imkonini beradi. Xuddi shunday :option:`--with-demo <odoo-bin "
"--with-demo>` buyruq qatori yordamida ham amalga oshirilishi mumkin."

