#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:193
msgid ""
"During the Core Training, we saw in the "
":doc:`server_framework_101/12_inheritance` chapter we could inherit "
"(extend) an existing view. This was a special case of data extension: any"
" data can be extended in a module."
msgstr ""
