"bobida mavjud ko'rinishni meros olish (kengaytirish) mumkinligini ko'rdik. "
"Bu ma'lumot kengaytmasining maxsus holati edi: har qanday ma'lumotlar "
"modulda kengaytirilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:197
msgid ""
"When you are adding new fields to an existing model in a new module, you "
"might want to populate those fields on the records created in the modules"
" you are depending on. This is done by giving the `xml_id` of the record "
"you want to extend. It won't replace it, in this case we will set the "
"``field_c`` to the given value for both records."
msgstr ""
"Yangi modulda mavjud modelga yangi maydonlar qo'shayotganda, siz tayanadigan "
"modullarda yaratilgan yozuvlarda bu maydonlarni to'ldirmoqchi bo'lishingiz "
"mumkin. Bu kengaytirmoqchi bo'lgan yozuvning `xml_id` sini berish orqali "
"amalga oshiriladi. U almashtirilmaydi, bu holda biz ikkala yozuv uchun "
"``field_c`` ni berilgan qiymatga o'rnatamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/define_module_data.rst:218
msgid ""
"Related fields can be set using the ``ref`` key. The value of that key is"
" the ``xml_id`` of the record you want to link. Remember the ``xml_id`` "
"is composed of the name of the module where the data is first declared, "
"followed by a dot, followed by the ``id`` of the record (just the ``id`` "
"works too if you are in the module declaring it)."
msgstr ""
"Bog'liq maydonlar ``ref`` kaliti yordamida o'rnatilishi mumkin. Bu kalit "
"qiymati bog'lamoqchi bo'lgan yozuvning ``xml_id`` si. ``xml_id`` birinchi "
"ma'lumot e'lon qilingan modul nomidan, nuqtadan va yozuvning ``id`` sidan "
"iborat ekanligini unutmang (uni e'lon qilayotgan modulda bo'lsangiz, "
"shunchaki ``id`` ham ishlaydi)."

