"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials>`_ and switch to the branch `19.0`."
msgstr ""
"`Odoo ning rasmiy qo'llanmalar repozitoriyasini <https://github.com/odoo/tutorials>`_ "
"clone qiling va `19.0` branchiga o'ting."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework.rst:40
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework.rst:54
