"Add the cloned repository to your :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin "
"--addons-path>`."
msgstr ""
"Klonlangan repozitoriyani :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin "
"--addons-path>` ga qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework.rst:41
msgid ""
"Start a new Odoo database and install the modules `awesome_owl` (for "
"chapter 1) and `awesome_dashboard` (for chapter 2)."
msgstr ""
"Yangi Odoo ma'lumotlar bazasini boshlang va `awesome_owl` (1-bob uchun) "
"va `awesome_dashboard` (2-bob uchun) modullarini o'rnating."

