"foydalanamiz. Maqsad Odoo veb mijoz kodiga tayanmasdan Owl ning o'zini "
"o'rganish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:29
msgid ""
"The solutions for each exercise of the chapter are hosted on the "
"`official Odoo tutorials repository "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/commits/19.0-discover-js-framework-"
