"yechimga qaramasdan ularni yechishga harakat qilish tavsiya etiladi!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:35
msgid "Example: a `Counter` component"
msgstr "Misol: `Counter` komponenti"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:37
msgid ""
"First, let us have a look at a simple example. The `Counter` component "
"shown below is a component that maintains an internal number value, "
"displays it, and updates it whenever the user clicks on the button."
msgstr ""
"Avval, oddiy misolni ko'rib chiqaylik. Quyida ko'rsatilgan `Counter` "
"komponenti ichki raqam qiymatini saqlaydigan, ko'rsatadigan va foydalanuvchi "
"tugmani bosgan har safar yangilaydigan komponent."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:57
msgid ""
"The `Counter` component specifies the name of a template that represents "
"its html. It is written in XML using the QWeb language:"
msgstr ""
"`Counter` komponenti uning html sini ifodalovchi shablon nomini ko'rsatadi. "
"U QWeb tili yordamida XML da yozilgan:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:71
msgid "1. Displaying a counter"
msgstr "1. Hisoblagichni ko'rsatish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:76
msgid ""
"As a first exercise, let us modify the `Playground` component located in "
":file:`awesome_owl/static/src/` to turn it into a counter. To see the "
"result, you can go to the `/awesome_owl` route with your browser."
msgstr ""
"Birinchi mashq sifatida, :file:`awesome_owl/static/src/` joylashgan "
"`Playground` komponentini hisoblagichga aylantirish uchun o'zgartiraylik. "
"Natijani ko'rish uchun brauzeringiz bilan `/awesome_owl` marshruti ga o'tishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:81
msgid ""
"Modify :file:`playground.js` so that it acts as a counter like in the "
"example above. Keep `Playground` for the class name. You will need to use"
" the `useState hook "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#usestate>`_"
" so that the component is re-rendered whenever any part of the state "
"object that has been read by this component is modified."
msgstr ""
":file:`playground.js` ni yuqoridagi misoldagi kabi hisoblagich sifatida "
"harakat qilishi uchun o'zgartiring. Klass nomi uchun `Playground` ni saqlab "
"qoling. Bu komponent tomonidan o'qilgan holat ob'ektining istalgan qismi "
"o'zgartirilganda komponent qayta ko'rsatilishi uchun `useState hook "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md#usestate>`_"
" dan foydalanishingiz kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:85
msgid "In the same component, create an `increment` method."
msgstr "Xuddi shu komponentda `increment` metodi yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:86
msgid ""
"Modify the template in :file:`playground.xml` so that it displays your "
"counter variable. Use `t-esc "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#outputting-data>`_ to output the data."
msgstr ""
":file:`playground.xml` dagi shablonni hisoblagich o'zgaruvchangizni "
"ko'rsatishi uchun o'zgartiring. Ma'lumotlarni chiqarish uchun `t-esc "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#outputting-data>`_ dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:88
msgid ""
"Add a button in the template and specify a `t-on-click "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/event_handling.md"
"#event-handling>`_ attribute in the button to trigger the `increment` "
"method whenever the button is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Shablonga tugma qo'shing va tugma bosilgan har safar `increment` metodini "
"ishga tushirish uchun tugmadagi `t-on-click "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/event_handling.md"
"#event-handling>`_ atributini ko'rsating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:93
msgid ""
"The Odoo JavaScript files downloaded by the browser are minified. For "
"debugging purpose, it's easier when the files are not minified. Switch to"
" :ref:`debug mode with assets <developer-mode/activation>` so that the "
"files are not minified."
msgstr ""
"Brauzer tomonidan yuklab olingan Odoo JavaScript fayllari miniflanган. "
"Debugging maqsadlari uchun fayllar miniflanmagan bo'lsa osonroq. Fayllar "
"miniflanmasligi uchun :ref:`aktivlar bilan debug rejimiga <developer-mode/activation>` "
"o'ting."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:97
msgid ""
"This exercise showcases an important feature of Owl: the `reactivity "
"system "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md>`_. "
"The `useState` function wraps a value in a proxy so Owl can keep track of"
" which component needs which part of the state, so it can be updated "
"whenever a value has been changed. Try removing the `useState` function "
"and see what happens."
msgstr ""
"Bu mashq Owl ning muhim xususiyatini ko'rsatadi: `reaktivlik tizimi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md>`_. "
"`useState` funksiyasi qiymatni proksi da o'raydi, shuning uchun Owl qaysi "
"komponent holatning qaysi qismiga muhtojligini kuzatib borishi mumkin va "
"qiymat o'zgargan har safar yangilanishi mumkin. `useState` funksiyasini "
"olib tashlab nima bo'lishini ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:103
msgid "2. Extract `Counter` in a sub component"
msgstr "2. `Counter` ni sub-komponentga chiqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:105
msgid ""
"For now we have the logic of a counter in the `Playground` component, but"
" it is not reusable. Let us see how to create a `sub-component "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/component.md#sub-"
"components>`_ from it:"
msgstr ""
"Hozircha hisoblagich mantig'i `Playground` komponentida, lekin u qayta "
"ishlatilmaydi. Undan `sub-komponent "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/component.md#sub-"
"components>`_ ni qanday yaratishni ko'raylik:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:108
msgid ""
"Extract the counter code from the `Playground` component into a new "
"`Counter` component."
msgstr "`Playground` komponentidan hisoblagich kodini yangi `Counter` komponentiga oling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:109
msgid ""
"You can do it in the same file first, but once it's done, update your "
"code to move the `Counter` in its own folder and file. Import it "
"relatively from `./counter/counter`. Make sure the template is in its own"
" file, with the same name."
msgstr ""
"Buni birinchi navbatda bir xil faylda qilishingiz mumkin, lekin bajarilgandan "
"so'ng, `Counter` ni o'zining papkasi va fayliga ko'chirish uchun kodingizni "
"yangilang. Uni `./counter/counter` dan nisbiy import qiling. Shablonning "
"o'z faylida, xuddi shu nom bilan ekanligiga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:112
msgid ""
"Use `<Counter/>` in the template of the `Playground` component to add two"
" counters in your playground."
msgstr ""
"Playground ingizga ikkita hisoblagich qo'shish uchun `Playground` komponentining "
"shablonida `<Counter/>` dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:119
msgid ""
"By convention, most components code, template and css should have the "
"same snake-cased name as the component. For example, if we have a "
"`TodoList` component, its code should be in `todo_list.js`, "
"`todo_list.xml` and if necessary, `todo_list.scss`"
msgstr ""
"Konvensiya bo'yicha, ko'pchilik komponentlar kodi, shabloni va css i "
"komponent bilan bir xil snake-case nomga ega bo'lishi kerak. Masalan, "
"agar `TodoList` komponentimiz bo'lsa, uning kodi `todo_list.js`, "
"`todo_list.xml` va zarur bo'lsa `todo_list.scss` da bo'lishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:126
msgid "3. A simple `Card` component"
msgstr "3. Oddiy `Card` komponenti"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:128
msgid ""
"Components are really the most natural way to divide a complicated user "
"interface into multiple reusable pieces. But to make them truly useful, "
"it is necessary to be able to communicate some information between them. "
"Let us see how a parent component can provide information to a sub "
"component by using attributes (most commonly known as `props "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md>`_)."
msgstr ""
"Komponentlar haqiqatan ham murakkab foydalanuvchi interfeysini bir nechta "
"qayta ishlatiladigan qismlarga ajratishning eng tabiiy usuli. Lekin ularni "
"haqiqatan ham foydali qilish uchun ular o'rtasida ba'zi ma'lumotlarni "
"almashish imkoniyati zarur. Ota-ona komponent atributlar (eng ko'p "
"`props <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md>`_ "
"nomi bilan tanilgan) yordamida sub-komponentga ma'lumot qanday taqdim "
"etishini ko'raylik."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:133
msgid ""
"The goal of this exercise is to create a `Card` component, that takes two"
" props: `title` and `content`. For example, here is how it could be used:"
msgstr ""
"Bu mashqning maqsadi ikkita props qabul qiladigan `Card` komponentini "
"yaratish: `title` va `content`. Masalan, undan qanday foydalanish mumkinligi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:140
msgid ""
"The above example should produce some html using bootstrap that look like"
" this:"
msgstr "Yuqoridagi misol bootstrap yordamida quyidagi ko'rinishdagi ba'zi html yaratishi kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:153
msgid "Create a `Card` component"
msgstr "`Card` komponentini yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:154
msgid "Import it in `Playground` and display a few cards in its template"
msgstr "Uni `Playground` da import qiling va shablonida bir nechta kartani ko'rsating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:160
msgid "4. Using `markup` to display html"
msgstr "4. Html ni ko'rsatish uchun `markup` dan foydalanish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:162
msgid ""
"If you used `t-esc` in the previous exercise, then you may have noticed "
"that Owl automatically escapes its content. For example, if you try to "
"display some html like this: `<Card title=\"'my title'\" "
"content=\"this.html\"/>` with `this.html = \"<div>some "
"content</div>\"\"`, the resulting output will simply display the html as "
"a string."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi mashqda `t-esc` ishlatgan bo'lsangiz, Owl kontentni avtomatik "
"ekranlashini payqagan bo'lishingiz mumkin. Masalan, quyidagi kabi html "
"ko'rsatishga harakat qilsangiz: `<Card title=\"'my title'\" "
"content=\"this.html\"/>` `this.html = \"<div>some content</div>\"\"` bilan, "
"natijadagi chiqish shunchaki html ni qator sifatida ko'rsatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:167
msgid ""
"In this case, since the `Card` component may be used to display any kind "
"of content, it makes sense to allow the user to display some html. This "
"is done with the `t-out directive "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#outputting-data>`_."
msgstr ""
"Bu holda, `Card` komponenti har qanday kontentni ko'rsatish uchun "
"ishlatilishi mumkin bo'lganligi sababli, foydalanuvchiga ba'zi html ni "
"ko'rsatishga ruxsat berish mantiqli. Bu `t-out direktivi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/templates.md"
"#outputting-data>`_ yordamida amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:171
msgid ""
"However, displaying arbitrary content as html is dangerous, it could be "
"used to inject malicious code, so by default, Owl will always escape a "
"string unless it has been explicitely marked as safe with the `markup` "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Biroq, ixtiyoriy kontentni html sifatida ko'rsatish xavfli, u zararli "
"kod kiritish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin, shuning uchun standart bo'yicha, "
"Owl qatorni `markup` funksiyasi bilan aniq xavfsiz deb belgilanmasa "
"har doim ekranlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:175
msgid "Update `Card` to use `t-out`"
msgstr "`Card` ni `t-out` dan foydalanish uchun yangilang"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:176
msgid "Update `Playground` to import `markup`, and use it on some html values"
msgstr "`Playground` ni `markup` ni import qilish uchun yangilang va ba'zi html qiymatlarda ishlatib ko'ring"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:177
msgid ""
"Make sure that you see that normal strings are always escaped, unlike "
"markuped strings."
msgstr ""
"Belgilangan qatorlardan farqli o'laroq, oddiy qatorlar har doim ekranlanishini "
"ko'rishingizga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:181
msgid ""
"The `t-esc` directive can still be used in Owl templates. It is slightly "
"faster than `t-out`."
msgstr ""
"`t-esc` direktivi Owl shablonlarida hali ham ishlatilishi mumkin. U "
"`t-out` dan biroz tezroq."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:187
msgid "5. Props validation"
msgstr "5. Props tekshiruvi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:189
msgid ""
"The `Card` component has an implicit API. It expects to receive two "
"strings in its props: the `title` and the `content`. Let us make that API"
" more explicit. We can add a props definition that will let Owl perform a"
" validation step in `dev mode "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/app.md#dev-"
"mode>`_. You can activate the dev mode in the `App configuration "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/app.md#configuration>`_"
" (but it is activated by default on the `awesome_owl` playground)."
msgstr ""
"`Card` komponenti yashirin API ga ega. U props da ikkita qator qabul "
"qilishni kutadi: `title` va `content`. Keling, bu API ni aniqroq qilaylik. "
"Owl ga `dev rejimida "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/app.md#dev-mode>`_"
" tekshiruv bosqichi bajarishga imkon beruvchi props ta'rifini qo'shishimiz "
"mumkin. Dev rejimini `Ilova konfiguratsiyasida "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/app.md#configuration>`_"
" yoqishingiz mumkin (lekin u `awesome_owl` playground da standart bo'yicha "
"yoqilgan)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:196
msgid "It is a good practice to do props validation for every component."
msgstr "Har bir komponent uchun props tekshiruvi qilish yaxshi amaliyot."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:198
msgid ""
"Add `props validation "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#props-"
"validation>`_ to the `Card` component."
msgstr ""
"`Card` komponentiga `props tekshiruvini "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#props-"
"validation>`_ qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:200
msgid ""
"Rename the `title` props into something else in the playground template, "
"then check in the :guilabel:`Console` tab of your browser's dev tools "
"that you can see an error."
msgstr ""
"Playground shablonida `title` props ni boshqa narsa bilan nomini o'zgartiring, "
"so'ng brauzeringizning dev toolsidagi :guilabel:`Console` tabida xato "
"ko'rishingiz mumkinligini tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:204
msgid "6. The sum of two `Counter`"
msgstr "6. Ikkita `Counter` ning yig'indisi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:206
msgid ""
"We saw in a previous exercise that `props` can be used to provide "
"information from a parent to a child component. Now, let us see how we "
"can communicate information in the opposite direction: in this exercise, "
"we want to display two `Counter` components, and below them, the sum of "
"their values. So, the parent component (`Playground`) need to be informed"
" whenever one of the `Counter` value is changed."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi mashqda `props` ota-ona komponentdan bola komponentga ma'lumot "
"berish uchun ishlatilishini ko'rdik. Endi qarama-qarshi yo'nalishda "
"ma'lumotni qanday uzatishni ko'raylik: bu mashqda ikkita `Counter` "
"komponentini va ularning qiymatlari yig'indisini ko'rsatmoqchimiz. "
"Shuning uchun, ota-ona komponent (`Playground`) `Counter` qiymatlaridan "
"biri o'zgargan har safar xabardor bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:212
msgid ""
"This can be done by using a `callback prop "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#binding-"
"function-props>`_: a prop that is a function meant to be called back. The"
" child component can choose to call that function with any argument. In "
"our case, we will simply add an optional `onChange` prop that will be "
"called whenever the `Counter` component is incremented."
msgstr ""
"Bu `callback prop "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#binding-"
"function-props>`_ yordamida amalga oshirilishi mumkin: qayta chaqirilishi "
"mo'ljallangan funksiya bo'lgan prop. Bola komponent bu funksiyani "
"istalgan argument bilan chaqirishni tanlashi mumkin. Bizning holimizda, "
"`Counter` komponenti ko'paytirilgan har safar chaqiriladigan ixtiyoriy "
"`onChange` prop qo'shamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:217
msgid ""
"Add prop validation to the `Counter` component: it should accept an "
"optional `onChange` function prop."
msgstr ""
"`Counter` komponentiga prop tekshiruvini qo'shing: u ixtiyoriy `onChange` "
"funksiya propni qabul qilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:219
msgid ""
"Update the `Counter` component to call the `onChange` prop (if it exists)"
" whenever it is incremented."
msgstr ""
"`Counter` komponentini ko'paytirilgan har safar `onChange` propni (agar "
"mavjud bo'lsa) chaqirish uchun yangilang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:221
msgid ""
"Modify the `Playground` component to maintain a local state value "
"(`sum`), initially set to 2, and display it in its template"
msgstr ""
"`Playground` komponentini dastlab 2 ga o'rnatilgan mahalliy holat qiymatini "
"(`sum`) saqlash uchun o'zgartiring va uni shablonida ko'rsating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:223
msgid "Implement an `incrementSum` method in `Playground`"
msgstr "`Playground` da `incrementSum` metodini implement qiling"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:224
msgid "Give that method as a prop to two (or more!) sub `Counter` components."
msgstr "Bu metodini ikkita (yoki undan ortiq!) sub `Counter` komponentlariga prop sifatida bering."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:231
msgid ""
"There is a subtlety with callback props: they usually should be defined "
"with the `.bind` suffix. See the `documentation "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#binding-"
