" input html element)."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi mashqdagi `input` ga fokuslanish. Bu `TodoList` komponentidan "
"amalga oshirilishi kerak (input html elementida `focus` metodi borligini "
"e'tibor bering)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:431
msgid ""
"Bonus point: extract the code into a specialized `hook "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md>`_ "
"`useAutofocus` in a new :file:`awesome_owl/utils.js` file."
msgstr ""
"Bonus ball: kodni yangi :file:`awesome_owl/utils.js` faylida ixtisoslashgan "
"`hook <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/hooks.md>`_ "
"`useAutofocus` ga ajrating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:439
msgid ""
"Refs are usually suffixed by `Ref` to make it obvious that they are "
"special objects:"
msgstr ""
"Reflar ko'pincha ular maxsus ob'ektlar ekanligini aniq qilish uchun "
"`Ref` suffiksi bilan nomlanadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:446
msgid "11. Toggling todos"
msgstr "11. Vazifalarni almashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:448
msgid ""
"Now, let's add a new feature: mark a todo as completed. This is actually "
"trickier than one might think. The owner of the state is not the same as "
"the component that displays it. So, the `TodoItem` component needs to "
"communicate to its parent that the todo state needs to be toggled. One "
"classic way to do this is by adding a `callback prop "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#binding-"
"function-props>`_ `toggleState`."
msgstr ""
"Keling, yangi xususiyat qo'shaylik: vazifani bajarilgan deb belgilash. "
"Bu aslida o'ylaganingizdan qiyinroq. Holat egasi uni ko'rsatadigan "
"komponent bilan bir xil emas. Shuning uchun, `TodoItem` komponenti "
"ota-onasiga vazifa holati almashtirilishi kerakligini xabar qilishi kerak. "
"Buning uchun klassik usul `callback prop "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/props.md#binding-"
"function-props>`_ `toggleState` qo'shish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:454
