msgstr ""
"Owl `t-att` direktivi bilan hisoblangan atributlarni agar yolg'on qiymatga "
"baholansa yaratmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:461
msgid "Add a callback props `toggleState` to `TodoItem`."
msgstr "`TodoItem` ga callback props `toggleState` qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:462
msgid ""
"Add a `change` event handler on the input in the `TodoItem` component and"
