#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:498
msgid "13. Generic `Card` with slots"
msgstr "13. Slotlar bilan umumiy `Card`"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:500
msgid ""
"In a :ref:`previous exercise "
"<tutorials/discover_js_framework/simple_card>`, we built a simple `Card` "
