"some arbitrary content inside a card, such as a sub-component? Well, it "
"does not work, since the content of the card is described by a string. It"
" would however be very convenient if we could describe the content as a "
"piece of template."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Oldingi mashqda <tutorials/discover_js_framework/simple_card>` "
"biz oddiy `Card` komponentini yaratdik. Lekin u rostini aytganda ancha "
"cheklangan. Sub-komponent kabi karta ichida ixtiyoriy kontent ko'rsatmoqchi "
"bo'lsak nima bo'ladi? Karta kontenti qator bilan ta'riflanganligi sababli "
"bu ishlamaydi. Biroq, kontentni shablon qismi sifatida ta'riflay olsak "
"juda qulay bo'lardi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:506
msgid ""
"This is exactly what Owl's `slot "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/slots.md>`_ system"
" is designed for: allowing to write generic components."
msgstr ""
"Bu aynan Owl ning `slot "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/slots.md>`_ tizimi "
"mo'ljallangan narsa: umumiy komponentlar yozish imkonini berish."

