"If you open the :guilabel:`Network` tab of your browser's dev tools, you "
"will see that the call to `/awesome_dashboard/statistics` is done every "
"time the client action is displayed. This is because the `onWillStart` "
"hook is called each time the `Dashboard` component is mounted. But in "
"this case, we would prefer to do it only the first time, so we actually "
"need to maintain some state outside of the `Dashboard` component. This is"
" a nice use case for a service!"
msgstr ""
