#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:259
msgid ""
"Everyone likes charts (!), so let us add a pie chart in our dashboard. It"
" will display the proportions of t-shirts sold for each size: "
"S/M/L/XL/XXL."
msgstr ""
"Hamma diagrammalarni yaxshi ko'radi (!), shuning uchun boshqaruv paneliga "
"doiraviy diagramma qo'shamiz. U har bir o'lcham uchun sotilgan futbolkalar "
"ulushini ko'rsatadi: S/M/L/XL/XXL."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:262
msgid ""
"For this exercise, we will use `Chart.js <https://www.chartjs.org/>`_. It"
" is the chart library used by the graph view. However, it is not loaded "
"by default, so we will need to either add it to our assets bundle, or "
"lazy load it. Lazy loading is usually better since our users will not "
"have to load the chartjs code every time if they don't need it."
msgstr ""
"Bu mashq uchun grafik ko'rinishi tomonidan ishlatiladigan diagramma kutubxonasi "
"bo'lgan `Chart.js <https://www.chartjs.org/>`_ dan foydalanamiz. Biroq, u "
"standart holda yuklanmaydi, shuning uchun uni bizning assets bundlemizga qo'shishimiz "
"yoki lazy load qilishimiz kerak. Lazy loading odatda yaxshiroqdir, chunki "
"foydalanuvchilarimiz uni kerak bo'lmasa har safar chartjs kodini yuklashga "
"majbur bo'lmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:267
msgid "Create a `PieChart` component."
msgstr "`PieChart` komponentini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:268
msgid ""
"In its `onWillStart` method, load chartjs, you can use the `loadJs "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/core/assets.js#L23>`_ function to load "
":file:`/web/static/lib/Chart/Chart.js`."
msgstr ""
"Uning `onWillStart` metodida chartjs ni yuklang, "
":file:`/web/static/lib/Chart/Chart.js` faylini yuklash uchun `loadJs "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/core/assets.js#L23>`_ funksiyasidan foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:272
msgid ""
"Use the `PieChart` component in a `DashboardItem` to display a `pie chart"
" <https://www.chartjs.org/docs/2.8.0/charts/doughnut.html>`_ that shows "
"the quantity for each sold t-shirts in each size (that information is "
"available in the `/statistics` route). Note that you can use the `size` "
"property to make it look larger."
msgstr ""
"Har bir o'lchamdagi sotilgan futbolkalar miqdorini ko'rsatadigan `doiraviy "
"diagramma <https://www.chartjs.org/docs/2.8.0/charts/doughnut.html>`_ ni "
"ko'rsatish uchun `DashboardItem` dagi `PieChart` komponentidan foydalaning "
"(bu ma'lumot `/statistics` yo'nalishida mavjud). `size` xossasidan uni "
"kattaroq ko'rsatish uchun foydalanishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:276
msgid ""
"The `PieChart` component will need to render a canvas, and draw on it "
"using `chart.js`."
msgstr ""
"`PieChart` komponenti canvas ni render qilishi va unga `chart.js` yordamida "
"chizishi kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:284
msgid ""
"`Example: lazy loading a js file "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_renderer.js#L57>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Misol: js faylni lazy loading "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_renderer.js#L57>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:287
msgid ""
"`Example: rendering a chart in a component "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_renderer.js#L618>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Misol: komponentda diagrammani render qilish "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/1f4e583ba20a01f4c44b0a4ada42c4d3bb074273/"
" addons/web/static/src/views/graph/graph_renderer.js#L618>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:292
msgid "7. Real life update"
msgstr "7. Haqiqiy hayot yangilanishi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:294
msgid ""
"Since we moved the data loading in a cache, it never updates. But let us "
"say that we are looking at fast moving data, so we want to periodically "
"(for example, every 10min) reload fresh data."
msgstr ""
"Ma'lumot yuklashni keshlashga ko'chirganimizdan beri, u hech qachon "
"yangilanmaydi. Lekin faraz qiling, biz tez o'zgaruvchan ma'lumotlarni "
"ko'rib chiqyapmiz, shuning uchun davriy ravishda (masalan, har 10 daqiqada) "
"yangi ma'lumotlarni qayta yuklashni xohlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:298
msgid ""
"This is quite simple to implement, with a `setTimeout` or `setInterval` "
"in the statistics service. However, here is the tricky part: if the "
"dashboard is currently being displayed, it should be updated immediately."
msgstr ""
"Bu statistika xizmatida `setTimeout` yoki `setInterval` yordamida amalga "
"oshirish juda oddiy. Biroq, qiyin qismi shuki: agar boshqaruv paneli "
"hozirda ko'rsatilayotgan bo'lsa, u darhol yangilanishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:302
msgid ""
"To do that, one can use a `reactive` object: it is just like the proxy "
"returned by `useState`, but not linked to any component. A component can "
"then do a `useState` on it to subscribe to its changes."
msgstr ""
"Buning uchun `reactive` obyektidan foydalanish mumkin: bu `useState` "
"tomonidan qaytarilgan proksi kabi, lekin biron bir komponentga bog'liq emas. "
"Keyin komponent uning o'zgarishlariga obuna bo'lish uchun `useState` ni "
"amalga oshirishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:307
msgid ""
"Update the statistics service to reload data every 10 minutes (to test "
"it, use 10s instead!)"
msgstr ""
"Statistika xizmatini har 10 daqiqada ma'lumotlarni qayta yuklash uchun "
"yangilang (sinab ko'rish uchun 10 soniya ishlating!)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:308
msgid ""
"Modify it to return a `reactive "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md#reactive>`_"
" object. Reloading data should update the reactive object in place."
msgstr ""
"`reactive "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md#reactive>`_"
" obyektini qaytarish uchun uni o'zgartiring. Ma'lumotlarni qayta yuklash "
"reaktiv obyektni o'z joyida yangilashi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:310
msgid "The `Dashboard` component can now use it with a `useState`"
msgstr "`Dashboard` komponenti endi uni `useState` bilan ishlatishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:313
msgid ""
"`Documentation on reactivity "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Reaktivlik haqida hujjat "
"<https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/reference/reactivity.md>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:314
msgid ""
"`Example: Use of reactive in a service "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/bb1b5aed9b6d96ae1b0d044341812b51ed72a05d/"
" addons/mail/static/src/discuss/call/common/rtc_service.js#L124>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Misol: xizmatda reactive dan foydalanish "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/bb1b5aed9b6d96ae1b0d044341812b51ed72a05d/"
" addons/mail/static/src/discuss/call/common/rtc_service.js#L124>`_"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:319
msgid "8. Lazy loading the dashboard"
msgstr "8. Boshqaruv panelini lazy loading"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:321
msgid ""
"Let us imagine that our dashboard is getting quite big, and is only of "
"interest to some of our users. In that case, it could make sense to lazy "
"load our dashboard, and all related assets, so we only pay the cost of "
"loading the code when we actually want to look at it."
msgstr ""
"Tasavvur qiling, bizning boshqaruv panelimiz ancha kattalashib bormoqda va "
"faqat ba'zi foydalanuvchilarimizga qiziq. Bunday holda, boshqaruv panelimizni "
"va barcha tegishli aktivlarni lazy load qilish mantiqiy bo'ladi, shuning uchun "
"biz uni haqiqatan ham ko'rmoqchi bo'lganimizda kod yuklash uchun narx to'laymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:326
msgid ""
"One way to do this is to use `LazyComponent` (from `@web/core/assets`) as"
" an intermediate that will load an asset bundle before displaying our "
"component."
msgstr ""
"Buning bir usuli - komponentimizni ko'rsatishdan oldin asset bundleni "
"yuklaydigan oraliq sifatida `@web/core/assets` dan `LazyComponent` ni ishlatish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:331
msgid ":file:`example_action.js`:"
msgstr ":file:`example_action.js`:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:344
msgid ""
"Move all dashboard assets into a sub folder :file:`/dashboard` to make it"
" easier to add to a bundle."
msgstr ""
"Barcha boshqaruv paneli aktivlarini bundlega qo'shishni osonlashtirish uchun "
":file:`/dashboard` papkasiga ko'chiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:346
msgid ""
"Create a `awesome_dashboard.dashboard` assets bundle containing all "
"content of the :file:`/dashboard` folder."
msgstr ""
":file:`/dashboard` papkasining barcha kontentini o'z ichiga olgan "
"`awesome_dashboard.dashboard` aktivlar bundlini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:348
msgid ""
"Modify :file:`dashboard.js` to register itself to the `lazy_components` "
"registry instead of `actions`."
msgstr ""
":file:`dashboard.js` ni `actions` o'rniga `lazy_components` registryiga "
"ro'yxatdan o'tkazish uchun o'zgartiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:349
msgid ""
"In :file:`src/dashboard_action.js`, create an intermediate component that"
" uses `LazyComponent` and register it to the `actions` registry."
msgstr ""
":file:`src/dashboard_action.js` da `LazyComponent` dan foydalanadigan oraliq "
"komponent yarating va uni `actions` registryiga ro'yxatdan o'tkazing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:353
msgid "9. Making our dashboard generic"
msgstr "9. Boshqaruv panelimizni umumiy qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:355
msgid ""
"So far, we have a nice working dashboard. But it is currently hardcoded "
"in the dashboard template. What if we want to customize our dashboard? "
"Maybe some users have different needs and want to see other data."
msgstr ""
"Hozirgacha bizda ajoyib ishlayotgan boshqaruv paneli bor. Lekin u hozirda "
"boshqaruv paneli shablonida qattiq kodlangan. Agar boshqaruv panelimizni "
"sozlamoqchi bo'lsak nima bo'ladi? Ehtimol, ba'zi foydalanuvchilar boshqa "
"ehtiyojlarga ega va boshqa ma'lumotlarni ko'rishni xohlashadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:359
msgid ""
"So, the next step is to make our dashboard generic: instead of hard-"
"coding its content in the template, it can just iterate over a list of "
"dashboard items. But then, many questions come up: how to represent a "
"dashboard item, how to register it, what data should it receive, and so "
"on. There are many different ways to design such a system, with different"
" trade-offs."
msgstr ""
"Shunday qilib, keyingi qadam boshqaruv panelimizni umumiy qilishdir: tarkibni "
"shablonda qattiq kodlash o'rniga, u shunchaki boshqaruv paneli elementlari "
"ro'yxatida takrorlanishi mumkin. Lekin keyin ko'plab savollar paydo bo'ladi: "
"boshqaruv paneli elementini qanday ifodalash, uni qanday ro'yxatdan o'tkazish, "
"qanday ma'lumotlarni qabul qilishi kerak va hokazo. Bunday tizimni loyihalashning "
"turli savdo-sotiqlar bilan ko'plab usullari mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:365
msgid ""
"For this tutorial, we will say that a dashboard item is an object with "
"the following structure:"
msgstr ""
"Ushbu qo'llanma uchun, boshqaruv paneli elementi quyidagi tuzilmaga ega "
"obyekt deyamiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:381
msgid ""
"The `description` value will be useful in a later exercise to show the "
"name of items that the user can add to their dashboard. The `size` number"
" is optional, and simply describes the size of the dashboard item that "
"will be displayed. Finally, the `props` function is optional. If not "
"given, we will simply give the `statistics` object as data. But if it is "
"defined, it will be used to compute specific props for the component."
msgstr ""
"`description` qiymati keyingi mashqda foydalanuvchi boshqaruv paneliga qo'sha "
"oladigan elementlar nomini ko'rsatishda foydali bo'ladi. `size` raqami "
"ixtiyoriy va ko'rsatiladigan boshqaruv paneli elementining o'lchamini tasvirlaydi. "
"Nihoyat, `props` funksiyasi ixtiyoriy. Agar berilmasa, `statistics` obyektini "
"ma'lumot sifatida beramiz. Lekin agar aniqlangan bo'lsa, komponent uchun "
"muayyan propslarni hisoblash uchun ishlatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:387
msgid ""
"The goal is to replace the content of the dashboard with the following "
"snippet:"
msgstr "Maqsad boshqaruv paneli kontentini quyidagi snippet bilan almashtirish:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:398
msgid ""
"Note that the above example features two advanced features of Owl: "
"dynamic components and dynamic props."
msgstr ""
"Yuqoridagi misol Owl ning ikkita ilg'or xususiyatini o'z ichiga oladi: "
"dinamik komponentlar va dinamik propslar."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:400
msgid ""
"We currently have two kinds of item components: number cards with a title"
" and a number, and pie cards with some label and a pie chart."
msgstr ""
"Hozirda bizda ikki xil element komponentlari bor: sarlavhali va raqamli "
"raqam kartalari va ba'zi belgi va doiraviy diagrammali doira kartalari."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:403
msgid ""
"Create and implement two components: `NumberCard` and `PieChartCard`, "
"with the corresponding props."
msgstr ""
"Tegishli propslar bilan ikkita komponent yarating va amalga oshiring: "
"`NumberCard` va `PieChartCard`."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:404
msgid ""
"Create a file :file:`dashboard_items.js` in which you define and export a"
" list of items, using `NumberCard` and `PieChartCard` to recreate our "
"current dashboard."
msgstr ""
":file:`dashboard_items.js` faylini yarating, unda joriy boshqaruv panelimizni "
"qayta yaratish uchun `NumberCard` va `PieChartCard` dan foydalanib elementlar "
"ro'yxatini aniqlang va eksport qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:406
msgid ""
"Import that list of items in our `Dashboard` component, add it to the "
"component, and update the template to use a `t-foreach` like shown above."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu elementlar ro'yxatini bizning `Dashboard` komponentimizga import qiling, "
"uni komponentga qo'shing va yuqorida ko'rsatilganidek `t-foreach` dan "
"foydalanadigan shablonni yangilang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:415
msgid "And now, our dashboard template is generic!"
msgstr "Va endi bizning boshqaruv paneli shablonimiz umumiy!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:418
msgid "10. Making our dashboard extensible"
msgstr "10. Boshqaruv panelimizni kengaytiriladigan qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:420
msgid ""
"However, the content of our item list is still hardcoded. Let us fix that"
" by using a registry:"
msgstr ""
"Biroq, elementlar ro'yxatimiz kontenti hali ham qattiq kodlangan. Keling, "
"registrydan foydalanib buni tuzataylik:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:422
msgid ""
"Instead of exporting a list, register all dashboard items in a "
"`awesome_dashboard` registry"
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxatni eksport qilish o'rniga, barcha boshqaruv paneli elementlarini "
"`awesome_dashboard` registryiga ro'yxatdan o'tkating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:423
msgid ""
"Import all the items of the `awesome_dashboard` registry in the "
"`Dashboard` component"
msgstr ""
"`Dashboard` komponentida `awesome_dashboard` registryining barcha elementlarini "
"import qiling"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:425
msgid ""
"The dashboard is now easily extensible. Any other Odoo addon that wants "
"to register a new item to the dashboard can just add it to the registry."
msgstr ""
"Boshqaruv paneli endi osongina kengaytiriladi. Boshqaruv paneliga yangi element "
"ro'yxatdan o'tkazmoqchi bo'lgan boshqa har qanday Odoo addon uni shunchaki "
"registryga qo'shishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:429
msgid "11. Add and remove dashboard items"
msgstr "11. Boshqaruv paneli elementlarini qo'shish va o'chirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:431
msgid ""
"Let us see how we can make our dashboard customizable. To make it simple,"
" we will save the user dashboard configuration in the local storage so "
"that it is persistent, but we don't have to deal with the server for now."
msgstr ""
"Keling, boshqaruv panelimizni qanday sozlash mumkinligini ko'raylik. "
"Oddiy qilish uchun, foydalanuvchi boshqaruv paneli konfiguratsiyasini "
"mahalliy xotirada saqlaymiz, shuning uchun u doimiy bo'ladi, lekin hozircha "
"server bilan shug'ullanishimiz shart emas."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:435
msgid "The dashboard configuration will be saved as a list of removed item ids."
msgstr "Boshqaruv paneli konfiguratsiyasi o'chirilgan element identifikatorlari ro'yxati sifatida saqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:437
msgid ""
"Add a button in the control panel with a gear icon to indicate that it is"
" a settings button."
msgstr ""
"Boshqaruv paneliga sozlamalar tugmasi ekanligini bildiruvchi tishli g'ildirak "
"belgisi bilan tugma qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:438
msgid "Clicking on that button should open a dialog."
msgstr "Ushbu tugmani bosish muloqot oynasini ochishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:439
msgid ""
"In that dialog, we want to see a list of all existing dashboard items, "
"each with a checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu muloqot oynasida, har biri belgilash katakchali barcha mavjud boshqaruv "
"paneli elementlari ro'yxatini ko'rmoqchimiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:440
msgid ""
"There should be a `Apply` button in the footer. Clicking on it will build"
" a list of all item ids that are unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Altbilgida `Apply` tugmasi bo'lishi kerak. Uni bosish belgilanmagan barcha "
"element identifikatorlari ro'yxatini tuzadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:442
msgid "We want to store that value in the local storage."
msgstr "Bu qiymatni mahalliy xotirada saqlashni xohlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:443
msgid ""
"And modify the `Dashboard` component to filter the current items by "
"removing the ids of items from the configuration."
msgstr ""
"Va `Dashboard` komponentini konfiguratsiyadan elementlar identifikatorlarini "
"o'chirish orqali joriy elementlarni filtrlash uchun o'zgartiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:451
msgid "12. Going further"
msgstr "12. Chuqurroq"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:453
msgid ""
"Here is a list of some small improvements you could try to do if you have"
" the time:"
msgstr ""
"Agar vaqtingiz bo'lsa, sinab ko'rishingiz mumkin bo'lgan ba'zi kichik "
"yaxshilashlar ro'yxati:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:455
msgid ""
"Make sure your application can be :ref:`translated "
"<reference/translations>` (with `env._t`)."
msgstr ""
"Ilovangizni :ref:`tarjima qilinishi mumkin <reference/translations>` "
"ekanligiga ishonch hosil qiling (`env._t` bilan)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/02_build_a_dashboard.rst:457
msgid ""
"Clicking on a section of the pie chart should open a list view of all "
"orders that have the corresponding size."
msgstr ""
"Doiraviy diagrammaning bir bo'limini bosish mos o'lchamga ega barcha "
"buyurtmalarning ro'yxat ko'rinishini ochishi kerak."

