#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:241
msgid ""
"The ``x_garden_orientation`` field must have 4 possible values: 'North', "
"'South', 'East' and 'West'. The selection list must be created by first "
"creating the `ir.model.fields` record for the field itself, then creating"
" the `ir.model.fields.selection` records. These records take three "
"fields: `field_id`, `name` (the name in the UI) and `value` (the value in"
" the database). A `sequence` field can also be set, which controls the "
"order in which the selections are displayed in the UI (lower sequence "
"values are displayed first)."
msgstr ""
"``x_garden_orientation`` maydoni 4 ta mumkin bo'lgan qiymatga ega bo'lishi "
"kerak: 'North', 'South', 'East' va 'West'. Tanlash ro'yxati avval maydonning "
"o'zi uchun `ir.model.fields` yozuvini yaratib, so'ng `ir.model.fields.selection` "
"yozuvlarini yaratish orqali tuzilishi kerak. Bu yozuvlar uchta maydonni qabul "
"qiladi: `field_id`, `name` (UI dagi nom) va `value` (ma'lumotlar bazasidagi qiymat). "
"Shuningdek, tanlovlar UI da ko'rsatiladigan tartibni nazorat qiladigan `sequence` "
"maydoni ham o'rnatilishi mumkin (pastroq ketma-ketlik qiymatlari birinchi ko'rsatiladi)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:251
msgid ""
"In Python, default values can be set on fields using the ``default`` "
"argument in the field declaration. In data modules, default values are "
"set by creating an ``ir.default`` record for each field. For example, it "
"is possible to set the default value of the ``x_selling_price`` field to "
"``100000`` for all properties by creating the following record:"
msgstr ""
"Pythonda, standart qiymatlar maydon e'lonidagi ``default`` argumenti "
"yordamida maydonga o'rnatilishi mumkin. Ma'lumot modullarida, standart "
"qiymatlar har bir maydon uchun ``ir.default`` yozuvini yaratish orqali "
"o'rnatiladi. Masalan, quyidagi yozuvni yaratish orqali barcha mulklar uchun "
"``x_selling_price`` maydonining standart qiymatini ``100000`` ga o'rnatish mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:266
msgid ""
"For more details, refer to the `ir.default` model in the database "
"available in the :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Actions --> "
"User-defined Defaults` menu or see the `ir.default` model definition in "
"the `base` module."
msgstr ""
"Qo'shimcha ma'lumot uchun :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Actions --> "
"User-defined Defaults` menyusida mavjud bo'lgan ma'lumotlar bazasidagi "
"`ir.default` modeliga yoki `base` modulidagi `ir.default` model ta'rifiga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:271
msgid ""
"These defaults are static but can be set by company and/or user using the"
" ``user_id`` and ``company_id`` fields of the ``ir.default`` record. This"
" means that having a dynamic default value of \"today\" for the "
"``x_date_availability`` field is not possible, for example."
msgstr ""
"Bu standartlar statikdir, lekin ``ir.default`` yozuvining ``user_id`` va "
"``company_id`` maydonlari yordamida kompaniya va/yoki foydalanuvchi tomonidan "
"o'rnatilishi mumkin. Bu, masalan, ``x_date_availability`` maydoni uchun "
"\"bugun\" ning dinamik standart qiymatiga ega bo'lish mumkin emasligini bildiradi."

