#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:391
msgid ""
"Many-to-many fields are defined in the same way as many-to-one fields, "
"but with the `ttype` set to `many2many`. The `relation` attribute is also"
" set to the name of the model to link to. Other attributes can be set to "
"control the relation:"
msgstr ""
"Many-to-many maydonlari many-to-one maydonlari bilan bir xil tarzda "
