#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:467
msgid ""
"Computed fields are a core concept in Odoo and are used to define fields "
"that are computed based on other fields. This is useful for fields that "
"are derived from other fields, like a sum of sub-records (adding up the "
"price of all the items in a sale order)."
msgstr ""
"Hisoblangan maydonlar Odoo ning asosiy kontseptsiyasi bo'lib, boshqa maydonlar "
"asosida hisoblanadigan maydonlarni aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi. Bu boshqa "
"maydonlardan kelib chiqadigan maydonlar uchun foydali, masalan, "
"pastki yozuvlar yig'indisi (savdo buyurtmasidagi barcha elementlar narxini qo'shish)."

