msgid "13. Uploading an image"
msgstr "13. Rasm yuklash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/02_create_gallery_view.rst:356
msgid ""
"Our gallery view does not allow users to upload images. Let us implement "
"that."
msgstr "Bizning galereya ko'rinishimiz foydalanuvchilarga rasm yuklash imkonini bermaydi. Keling, buni amalga oshiramiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/02_create_gallery_view.rst:358
msgid "Add a button on each image by using the `FileUploader` component."
msgstr "`FileUploader` komponentidan foydalanib har bir rasmda tugma qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/02_create_gallery_view.rst:359
msgid ""
"The `FileUploader` component accepts the `onUploaded` props, which is "
"called when the user uploads an image. Make sure to call `webSave` from "
"the orm service to upload the new image."
msgstr ""
"`FileUploader` komponenti foydalanuvchi rasm yuklaganida chaqiriladigan "
"`onUploaded` propsini qabul qiladi. Yangi rasmni yuklash uchun orm "
"xizmatidan `webSave` ni chaqirishingizga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/02_create_gallery_view.rst:361
msgid ""
"You maybe noticed that the image is uploaded but it is not re-rendered by"
" the browser. This is because the image link did not change so the "
"browser do not re-fetch them. Include the `write_date` from the record to"
" the image url."
msgstr ""
"Ehtimol, rasm yuklanganini, lekin brauzer tomonidan qayta ko'rsatilmaganini "
"payqagansiz. Bu rasm havolasi o'zgarmaganligi sababli brauzer ularni "
"qayta olmaydi. Yozuvdagi `write_date` ni rasm urlga qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/02_create_gallery_view.rst:364
msgid ""
"Make sure that clicking on the upload button does not trigger the "
"switchView."
msgstr "Yuklash tugmasini bosish switchViewni ishga tushirmasligiga ishonch hosil qiling."

