msgstr ""
"`Namuna: FileUploader dan foydalanish "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/7710c3331ebd22f8396870bd0731f8c1152d9c41/addons/mail/static/src/web/activity/activity.xml#L48-L52>`_"

