#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:3
msgid "Chapter 3: Customize a kanban view"
msgstr "3-bob: Kanban ko'rinishini sozlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:5
msgid ""
"We have gained an understanding of the numerous capabilities offered by "
"the web framework. As a next step, we will customize a kanban view. This "
"is a more complicated project that will showcase some non trivial aspects"
" of the framework. The goal is to practice composing views, coordinating "
"various aspects of the UI, and doing it in a maintainable way."
msgstr ""
"Biz veb framework taqdim etgan ko'plab imkoniyatlarni tushundik. Keyingi "
"qadam sifatida biz kanban ko'rinishini sozlaymiz. Bu frameworkning ba'zi "
"ahamiyatli jihatlarini namoyish etadigan murakkabroq loyiha. Maqsad "
"ko'rinishlarni tuzishni mashq qilish, UI ning turli jihatlarini "
"muvofiqlashtirishva buni qo'llab-quvvatlash mumkin bo'lgan tarzda qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:10
msgid ""
"Bafien had the greatest idea ever: a mix of a kanban view and a list view"
" would be perfect for your needs! In a nutshell, he wants a list of "
"customers on the left of the CRM kanban view. When you click on a "
"customer on the left sidebar, the kanban view on the right is filtered to"
" only display leads linked to that customer."
msgstr ""
"Bafien eng ajoyib g'oyani topdi: kanban ko'rinishi va ro'yxat ko'rinishining "
"aralashmasi sizning ehtiyojlaringiz uchun ideal bo'ladi! Qisqacha "
"aytganda, u CRM kanban ko'rinishining chap tomonida mijozlar ro'yxatini "
"xohlaydi. Chap yon panelda mijozni bossangiz, o'ng tomondagi kanban "
"ko'rinishi faqat o'sha mijozga bog'liq potentsial mijozlarni ko'rsatish "
"uchun filtrlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:22
msgid ""
"The solutions for each exercise of the chapter are hosted on the "
"`official Odoo tutorials repository "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/commits/19.0-master-odoo-web-"
"framework-solutions/awesome_kanban>`_."
msgstr ""
"Bob mashqlarining har biri uchun yechimlar "
"`rasmiy Odoo qo'llanmalar omborida "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/commits/19.0-master-odoo-web-"
"framework-solutions/awesome_kanban>`_ joylashtirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:27
msgid "1. Create a new kanban view"
msgstr "1. Yangi kanban ko'rinishini yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:29
msgid ""
"Since we are customizing the kanban view, let us start by extending it "
"and using our extension in the kanban view of CRM."
msgstr ""
"Kanban ko'rinishini sozlayotganimiz sababli, keling, uni kengaytirish va "
"kengaytmamizni CRM ning kanban ko'rinishida ishlatishdan boshlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:32
msgid ""
"Create a new empty component that extends the `KanbanController` "
"component from :file:`@web/views/kanban/kanban_controller`."
msgstr ""
":file:`@web/views/kanban/kanban_controller` dan `KanbanController` "
"komponentini kengaytiradigan yangi bo'sh komponent yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:34
msgid ""
"Create a new view object and assign all keys and values from `kanbanView`"
" from :file:`@web/views/kanban/kanban_view`. Override the Controller key "
"by putting your newly created controller."
msgstr ""
"Yangi ko'rinish ob'ektini yarating va :file:`@web/views/kanban/kanban_view` "
"dan `kanbanView` dagi barcha kalit va qiymatlarni belgilang. Yangi "
"yaratilgan controlleringizni qo'yib Controller kalitini bekor qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:37
msgid "Register it in the views registry under `awesome_kanban`."
msgstr "Uni `awesome_kanban` ostida ko'rinishlar registrida ro'yxatdan o'tkazing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/master_odoo_web_framework/03_customize_kanban_view.rst:38
msgid ""
"Update the crm kanban arch in :file:`awesome_kanban/views/views.xml` to "
"use the extended view. This can be done by specifying the `js_class` "
"attribute in the kanban node."
msgstr ""
":file:`awesome_kanban/views/views.xml` dagi crm kanban archini kengaytirilgan "
"ko'rinishdan foydalanish uchun yangilang. Buni kanban tugunida `js_class` "
"atributini belgilash orqali amalga oshirish mumkin."

