#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:3
msgid "Build PDF Reports"
msgstr "PDF hisobotlarini yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:10
msgid ""
"We were previously :doc:`introduced to QWeb "
"<server_framework_101/14_qwebintro>` where it was used to build a kanban "
"view. Now we will expand on one of QWeb's other main uses: creating PDF "
"reports. A common business requirement is the ability to create documents"
" to send to customers and to use internally. These reports can be used to"
" summarize and display information in an organized template to support "
"the business in different ways. Odoo can additionally add our company's "
"header and footer to our reports with minimal extra effort."
msgstr ""
"Biz avval :doc:`QWeb bilan tanishtirilgan <server_framework_101/14_qwebintro>` "
"bo'ldik, u kanban ko'rinishini yaratish uchun ishlatilgan. Endi biz "
"QWebning boshqa asosiy maqsadlaridan birini kengaytiramiz: PDF hisobotlarini "
"yaratish. Umumiy biznes talabi mijozlarga yuborish va ichki foydalanish "
"uchun hujjatlar yaratish qobiliyati. Bu hisobotlar biznesni turli yo'llar "
"bilan qo'llab-quvvatlash uchun tashkil etilgan shablonda ma'lumotlarni "
"umumlashtirish va ko'rsatish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. Odoo qo'shimcha "
"ravishda minimal qo'shimcha harakat bilan kompaniyamizning sarlavhasi va "
"pastki qismini hisobotlarimizga qo'sha oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:17
msgid ""
"The documentation related to this topic can be found in "
":ref:`reference/qweb`, :ref:`reference/reports/report`, and the "
":ref:`reference/actions/report` section of the Actions reference."
msgstr ""
"Bu mavzuga oid hujjatlarni :ref:`reference/qweb`, :ref:`reference/reports/report` "
"va Amallar ma'lumotnomaning :ref:`reference/actions/report` bo'limida topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:22
msgid "File Structure"
msgstr "Fayl tuzilishi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:24
msgid ""
"The bulk of a PDF report is its QWeb template. It also typically needs a "
"corresponding ``ir.actions.report`` to include the report within a "
"module's business logic. There is no strict rule for the file names or "
"where they are located, but these two parts are typically stored in 2 "
"separate files within a ``report`` folder at the top level of your "
"module's directory. If a module has many or multiple long report "
"templates, then they are often organized logically across different files"
" named after the report(s) they contain. All actions for the reports are "
"usually stored in the same file ending with ``_reports.xml``, regardless "
"of the number of reports it contains."
msgstr ""
"PDF hisobotining asosiy qismi uning QWeb shabloni. Shuningdek, u "
"odatda modul biznes mantiqiga hisobotni qo'shish uchun tegishli "
"``ir.actions.report`` ni talab qiladi. Fayl nomlari yoki ular joylashgan "
"joy uchun qat'iy qoidalar yo'q, lekin bu ikki qism odatda modul "
"katalogining yuqori darajasidagi ``report`` papkasida 2 alohida faylda "
"saqlanadi. Agar modulda ko'plab yoki bir nechta uzun hisobot shablonlari "
"bo'lsa, ular ko'pincha o'z ichiga olgan hisobot(lar) nomidagi turli "
"fayllarga mantiqiy tashkil etiladi. Hisobotlarga muvofiq barcha amallar "
"odatda o'z ichiga olgan hisobotlar sonidan qat'iy nazar ``_reports.xml`` "
"bilan tugaydigan bir xil faylda saqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:33
msgid ""
"Therefore, it is expected that your work tree will look something like "
"this:"
msgstr "Shu sababli, ish daraxti quyidagicha ko'rinishi kutiladi:"

