msgid ""
"Copy this `data file <https://github.com/odoo/technical-training-"
"solutions/blob/19.0-J_reports/estate/data/estate_demo.xml>`_ into a new "
"directory (data) in your estate module and copy `these lines "
"<https://github.com/odoo/technical-training-"
"solutions/blob/19.0-J_reports/estate/__manifest__.py#L21-L23>`_ into your"
" __manifest__.py file (you may need to create a new database to load in "
"the demo data)."
msgstr ""
"Bu `ma'lumotlar faylini <https://github.com/odoo/technical-training-"
"solutions/blob/19.0-J_reports/estate/data/estate_demo.xml>`_ mulk modulingizdagi "
"yangi katalogga (data) ko'chiring va `bu qatorlarni "
"<https://github.com/odoo/technical-training-"
"solutions/blob/19.0-J_reports/estate/__manifest__.py#L21-L23>`_ "
"__manifest__.py faylingizga nusxalang (demo ma'lumotlarini yuklash uchun "
"yangi ma'lumotlar bazasini yaratishingiz kerak bo'lishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:92
msgid ""
"Before continuing, click through your data in your database and make sure"
" your data is as expected. Of course you can add the data after you write"
" your report code, but then you will not be able to incrementally test "
"portions of your code as you write it. This can make checking for "
"mistakes and debugging your code more difficult in the long run for "
"complicated reports."
msgstr ""
"Davom etishdan oldin, ma'lumotlar bazangizda ma'lumotlaringizni ko'rib "
"chiqing va ma'lumotlaringiz kutilganidek ekanligiga ishonch hosil qiling. "
"Albatta, hisobot kodingizni yozgandan keyin ma'lumotlarni qo'shishingiz "
"mumkin, lekin keyin uni yozayotganingizda kodingizning qismlarini ketma-ket "
"sinab ko'ra olmaysiz. Bu murakkab hisobotlar uchun uzoq muddatda "
"xatolarni tekshirishni va kodingizni disk raskadrovka qilishni "
"qiyinlashtirishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:98
msgid "Minimal Template"
msgstr "Minimal shablon"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:100
msgid ""
"A minimal viable template is viewable under the \"Minimal viable "
"template\" section of the :ref:`reference/reports/templates` "
"documentation. We can modify this example to build our minimal property "
