msgstr ""
"Minimal ishlaydigan shablon :ref:`reference/reports/templates` hujjatlarining "
"\"Minimal viable template\" bo'limida ko'rib chiqilishi mumkin. Biz minimal "
"mulk takliflari shablon faylimizni yaratish uchun bu namunani o'zgartira olamiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:142
msgid ""
"Most of the Odoo specific (i.e. non-HTML) items in our file are explained"
" in the minimal viable template section. Some additional features in our "
"template are:"
msgstr ""
"Faylimizdagi Odoo-ga xos (ya'ni, HTML bo'lmagan) elementlarning ko'pi "
"minimal ishlaydigan shablon bo'limida tushuntirilgan. Shablon imizdagi "
"ba'zi qo'shimcha xususiyatlar:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:145
msgid ""
"The use of the ``class=\"table\"`` attribute, so our table has some nice "
"formatting. Twitter Bootstrap (we're using its table class in this case),"
" and Font Awesome (useful for adding icons) classes can be used in your "
