"foydalanamiz) va Font Awesome (belgilar qo'shish uchun foydali) sinflari "
"hisobot shablonida ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:148
msgid ""
"The use of ``t-set``, ``t-value``, ``t-foreach``, and ``t-as`` so that we"
" can loop over all the ``offer_ids``."
msgstr ""
"Barcha ``offer_ids`` bo'ylab aylanish mumkin bo'lishi uchun ``t-set``, "
"``t-value``, ``t-foreach`` va ``t-as`` dan foydalanish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:150
msgid ""
"If you are already familiar with website templating engines, then the "
"QWeb directives (i.e. the `t-` commands) probably don't need much "
"explanation and you can just look at its :ref:`documentation "
"<reference/qweb>` and skip ahead to the next subsection."
msgstr ""
"Agar veb-sayt shablon dvigatellari bilan allaqachon tanish bo'lsangiz, "
"QWeb direktivalari (ya'ni `t-` buyruqlari) ko'p tushuntirishga muhtoj "
"emas va faqat uning :ref:`hujjatlarini <reference/qweb>` ko'rib, "
"keyingi bo'limga o'tishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:154
msgid ""
"Otherwise you are encouraged to read more about them ( `Wikipedia "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template_processor>`__ has a good high "
"level description), but the general idea is that QWeb provides the "
"ability to dynamically generate web code based on Odoo data and simple "
"commands. I.e. QWeb can access recordset data (and methods) and process "
"simple programming operations such as setting and accessing temporary "
"variables. For example, in the above example:"
msgstr ""
"Aks holda ular haqida ko'proq o'qishingiz tavsiya etiladi "
"(`Wikipedia <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template_processor>`__ yaxshi "
"yuqori darajadagi tavsifga ega), lekin umumiy fikr shundan iboratki, "
"QWeb Odoo ma'lumotlari va oddiy buyruqlar asosida veb-kodni dinamik "
"ravishda yaratish qobiliyatini taqdim etadi. Ya'ni QWeb yozuvlar to'plami "
"ma'lumotlariga (va metodlariga) kirish va vaqtinchalik o'zgaruvchilarni "
"o'rnatish va ularga kirish kabi oddiy dasturlash operatsiyalarini qayta "
"ishlash imkoniyatiga ega. Masalan, yuqoridagi misolda:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:160
msgid ""
"``t-set`` creates a temporary variable called \"offers\" that has its "
"value set by ``t-value`` to the current ``estate.property`` recordset's "
"``offer_ids``."
msgstr ""
"``t-set`` joriy ``estate.property`` yozuvlar to'plamining ``offer_ids`` "
"ga ``t-value`` tomonidan qiymati o'rnatiladigan \"offers\" deb ataladigan "
"vaqtinchalik o'zgaruvchi yaratadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:162
msgid "The ``t-foreach`` and ``t-as`` usage is the equivalent to the Python:"
msgstr "``t-foreach`` va ``t-as`` dan foydalanish Python bilan ekvivalent:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:169
msgid "Report Action"
msgstr "Hisobot amali"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:171
msgid ""
"Now that we have a template, we need to make it accessible in our app via"
" a ``ir.actions.report``. A practical example of ``ir.actions.report`` is"
" `here "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/event/report/event_event_reports.xml#L20-L30>`__"
" corresponding to `this template "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/event/report/event_event_templates.xml#L5>`__."
" Its contents are all explained in :ref:`the documentation "
"<reference/actions/report>`."
msgstr ""
"Endi shablonimiz bor, uni ilovamizda ``ir.actions.report`` orqali "
"foydalanish mumkin bo'lishi kerak. ``ir.actions.report`` ning amaliy "
"namunasi `bu yerda "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/event/report/event_event_reports.xml#L20-L30>`__ "
"`bu shablonga mos "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/event/report/event_event_templates.xml#L5>`__. "
"Uning tarkibi :ref:`hujjatda <reference/actions/report>` tushuntirilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:178
msgid ""
"An ``ir.actions.report`` is primarily used via the Print menu of a "
"model's view. In the practical example, the ``binding_model_id`` "
"specifies which model's views the report should show, and Odoo will auto-"
"magically add it for you. Another common use case of the report action is"
" to link it to a button as we learned in "
":doc:`server_framework_101/09_actions`. This is handy for reports that "
"only make sense under specific conditions. For example, if we wanted to "
"make a \"Final Sale\" report, then we can link it to a \"Print Sale "
"Info\" button that appears in the form view only when the property is "
"\"Sold\"."
msgstr ""
"``ir.actions.report`` asosan model ko'rinishining Chop etish menyusi orqali "
"ishlatiladi. Amaliy misolda ``binding_model_id`` qaysi modelning ko'rinishlari "
"hisobotni ko'rsatishi kerakligini belgilaydi va Odoo uni avtomatik ravishda "
"qo'shadi. Hisobot amalining yana bir umumiy foydalanish holati - buni "
":doc:`server_framework_101/09_actions` da o'rganganimizdek tugmaga bog'lash. "
"Bu faqat ma'lum sharoitlarda mantiqiy bo'lgan hisobotlar uchun qulay. "
"Masalan, agar biz \"Yakuniy Sotish\" hisobotini yaratmoqchi bo'lsak, "
"uni mulk \"Sotilgan\" bo'lgandagina forma ko'rinishida paydo bo'ladigan "
"\"Sotish ma'lumotlarini chop etish\" tugmasiga bog'lashimiz mumkin."

msgid "Print Menu Button"
msgstr "Chop etish menyusi tugmasi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:190
msgid ""
"You may have noticed or are wondered why our report template loops "
"through a recordset. When our template is passed more than one record, it"
" can produce one PDF report for all the records. Using the Print menu in "
"the list view with multiple records selected will demonstrate this."
msgstr ""
"Siz nima uchun hisobot shablonimiz yozuvlar to'plami bo'ylab aylanishini "
"payqagan yoki hayron bo'lgan bo'lishingiz mumkin. Shablonimizga bir "
"nechta yozuv uzatilganda, u barcha yozuvlar uchun bitta PDF hisobotini "
"ishlab chiqara oladi. Bir nechta yozuv tanlangan holda ro'yxat ko'rinishidagi "
"Chop etish menyusidan foydalanish buni namoyish etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:195
msgid "Make a Report"
msgstr "Hisobot yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:197
msgid ""
"Finally, you now know where to create your files and how the content of "
"the files should look. Happy report making!"
msgstr ""
"Nihoyat, endi fayllaringizni qaerda yaratish va fayl tarkibi qanday "
"ko'rinishi kerakligini bilasiz. Hisobot yaratish baxtiyor bo'lsin!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:199
msgid "Make a report."
msgstr "Hisobot yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:201
msgid ""
"Add the property offers report from the minimal template subsection to "
"the Print menu of the Property views."
msgstr ""
"Minimal shablon bo'limidagi mulk takliflari hisobotini Mulk ko'rinishlarining "
"Chop etish menyusiga qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:203
msgid ""
"Improve the report by adding more data. Refer to the **Goal** of this "
"section to see what additional data you can add and feel free to add even"
" more."
msgstr ""
"Ko'proq ma'lumot qo'shish orqali hisobotni yaxshilang. Qo'shishingiz "
"mumkin bo'lgan qo'shimcha ma'lumotlarni ko'rish uchun ushbu bo'limning "
"**Maqsad** iga murojaat qiling va ko'proq qo'shishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:206
msgid ""
"Bonus: Make an extra flexible report by adding in some logic so that when"
" there are no offers on a property then we don't create a table and "
"instead write something about how there are no offers yet. Hint: you will"
" need to use ``t-if`` and ``t-else``."
msgstr ""
"Bonus: Mulkda takliflar bo'lmaganda jadval yaratmasligimiz va uning "
"o'rniga hali takliflar yo'qligi haqida biror narsa yozishimiz uchun "
"ba'zi mantiq qo'shib yanada moslashuvchan hisobot yarating. Ma'lumotnoma: "
"``t-if`` va ``t-else`` dan foydalanishingiz kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:210
msgid "Remember to check that your PDF reports match your data as expected."
msgstr "PDF hisobotlaringiz ma'lumotlaringizga kutilganidek mos kelishini tekshirishni unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:214
msgid "Sub-templates"
msgstr "Quyi shablonlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:218
msgid ""
"**Goal**: at the end of this section, we will have a sub-template that we"
" use in 2 reports."
msgstr "**Maqsad**: ushbu bo'lim oxirida 2 ta hisobotda ishlatiladigan quyi shablonga ega bo'lamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst
msgid "Report using a subtemplate"
msgstr "Quyi shablondan foydalanadigan hisobot"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:224
msgid ""
"There are two main reasons for using sub-templates. One is to make the "
"code easier to read when working with extra-long or complicated "
"templates. The other is to reuse code where possible. Our simple property"
" offers report is useful, but listing property offers information can be "
"useful for more than just one report template. One example is a report "
"that lists all of a salesman's properties' offers."
msgstr ""
"Quyi shablonlardan foydalanishning ikkita asosiy sababi bor. Biri - "
"juda uzun yoki murakkab shablonlar bilan ishlashda kodni o'qishni "
"osonlashtirish. Ikkinchisi - imkon qadar kodni qayta ishlatish. Oddiy "
"mulk takliflari hisobotimiz foydali, lekin mulk takliflari ma'lumotlarini "
"ro'yxatga olish faqat bitta hisobot shablonidan ko'proq narsa uchun "
"foydali bo'lishi mumkin. Bir misol - savdo agentining barcha mulklari "
"takliflarini ro'yxatlovchi hisobot."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:229
msgid ""
"See if you can understand how to call a sub-template by reading the "
":ref:`documentation <reference/qweb/sub-templates>` on it and/or by "
"looking at an `example "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/portal/static/src/xml/portal_chatter.xml#L147-L160>`__"
" (remember QWeb uses the same control flows regardless if it is for a "
"report or a view in Odoo.)"
msgstr ""
"Quyi shablonni qanday chaqirishni tushunishga harakat qiling, buning uchun "
"u bo'yicha :ref:`hujjatlarni <reference/qweb/sub-templates>` o'qing "
"va/yoki `namunani "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/portal/static/src/xml/portal_chatter.xml#L147-L160>`__ "
"ko'ring (QWeb Odoo da hisobot yoki ko'rinish uchun bo'lishidan qat'iy "
"nazar bir xil boshqaruv oqimlaridan foydalanishini esda tuting.)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:234
msgid "Create and use a sub-template."
msgstr "Quyi shablon yarating va foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:236
msgid ""
"Split the table portion of the offers into its own template. Remember to "
"check that your original report still prints correctly afterwards."
msgstr ""
"Takliflarning jadval qismini o'z shabloniga ajrating. Asl hisobotingiz "
"keyin ham to'g'ri chop etilishini tekshirishni unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:239
msgid ""
"Add a new report for ``res.users`` that allows you to print all of the "
"Real Estate Properties that are visible in their form view (i.e. in the "
"\"Settings\" app). Include the offers for each of those saleman's "
"properties in the same report. Hint: since the ``binding_model_id`` in "
"this case will not be within the estate module, you will need to use "
"``ref=\"base.model_res_users\"``."
msgstr ""
"``res.users`` uchun forma ko'rinishida ko'rinadigan (ya'ni \"Sozlamalar\" "
"ilovasida) barcha Ko'chmas mulk Mulklarini chop etish imkonini beradigan "
"yangi hisobot qo'shing. O'sha savdo agentlarining mulklari uchun "
"takliflarni bir xil hisobotga kiriting. Ma'lumotnoma: bu holda "
"``binding_model_id`` mulk moduli ichida bo'lmaganligi sababli, "
"``ref=\"base.model_res_users\"`` dan foydalanishingiz kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:244
msgid ""
"Your end result should look similar to the image in the **Goal** of this "
"section."
msgstr "Yakuniy natijangiz ushbu bo'limning **Maqsad** dagi rasmga o'xshash ko'rinishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:246
msgid "Remember to check that your reports match your data as expected!"
msgstr "Hisobotlaringiz ma'lumotlaringizga kutilganidek mos kelishini tekshirishni unutmang!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:249
msgid "Report Inheritance"
msgstr "Hisobot merosi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:253
msgid ""
"**Goal**: at the end of this section, we will inherit the property report"
" in the ``estate_account`` module."
msgstr "**Maqsad**: ushbu bo'lim oxirida ``estate_account`` modulida mulk hisobotini meros olamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst
msgid "An inherited report"
msgstr "Meros olingan hisobot"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:260
msgid ""
"Inheritance in QWeb uses the same ``xpath`` elements as :ref:`views "
"inheritance <reference/view_records/inheritance>`. A QWeb template refers"
" to its parent template in a different way though. It is even easier to "
"do by just adding the ``inherit_id`` attribute to the ``template`` "
"element and setting it equal to the *module.parent_template_id*."
msgstr ""
"QWeb da meros :ref:`ko'rinishlar merosi <reference/view_records/inheritance>` "
"dagi bir xil ``xpath`` elementlaridan foydalanadi. Biroq QWeb shabloni "
"ota shabloniga boshqa tarzda murojaat qiladi. Bu ``template`` elementiga "
"``inherit_id`` atributini qo'shish va uni *module.parent_template_id* ga "
"teng qilish orqali yanada osonroq amalga oshiriladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:264
msgid ""
"We didn't add any new fields to any of the estate models in "
"`estate_account`, but we can still add information to our existing "
"property report. For example, we know that any \"Sold\" properties will "
"already have an invoice created for them, so we can add this information "
"to our report."
msgstr ""
"Biz `estate_account` dagi mulk modellarining hech biriga yangi maydon "
"qo'shmadik, lekin mavjud mulk hisobotimizga ma'lumot qo'sha olamiz. "
"Masalan, biz \"Sotilgan\" mulklarda allaqachon ular uchun hisob-faktura "
"yaratilganligini bilamiz, shuning uchun bu ma'lumotni hisobotimizga "
"qo'sha olamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:268
msgid "Inherit a report."
msgstr "Hisobot meros oling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:270
msgid ""
"Extend the property report to include some information about the invoice."
" You can look at the **Goal** of this section for inspiration (i.e. print"
" a line when the property is Done, otherwise print nothing)."
msgstr ""
"Mulk hisobotini hisob-faktura haqida ba'zi ma'lumotlarni qo'shish uchun "
"kengaytiring. Ilhom olish uchun ushbu bo'limning **Maqsad** iga qaray "
"olasiz (ya'ni, mulk Tugallanganda qator chop eting, aks holda hech narsa "
"chop etmang)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:273
msgid "Again, remember to check that your reports match your data as expected!"
msgstr "Yana, hisobotlaringiz ma'lumotlaringizga kutilganidek mos kelishini tekshirishni unutmang!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:276
msgid "Additional Features"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha xususiyatlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:278
msgid ""
"All the following extra features are described further in the "
":ref:`reference/reports/report` documentation, including how to implement"
" each of them."
msgstr ""
"Quyidagi barcha qo'shimcha xususiyatlar :ref:`reference/reports/report` "
"hujjatlarida, shu jumladan ularning har birini qanday amalga oshirish "
"haqida batafsil tavsiflanган."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:284
msgid ""
"We all know Odoo is used in multiple languages thanks to automated and "
"manual translating. QWeb reports are no exception! Note that sometimes "
"the translations do not work properly if there are unnecessary spaces in "
"your template's text content, so try to avoid them when possible "
"(especially leading spaces)."
msgstr ""
"Biz barchamiz Odoo avtomatlashtirilgan va qo'lda tarjima tufayli bir "
"nechta tilda ishlatilishini bilamiz. QWeb hisobotlari ham istisno emas! "
"E'tibor bering, shabloningizning matn tarkibida keraksiz bo'shliqlar "
"bo'lsa, ba'zan tarjimalar to'g'ri ishlamaydi, shuning uchun iloji "
"boricha ulardan qochishga harakat qiling (ayniqsa boshidagi bo'shliqlar)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:291
msgid ""
"You probably are tired of hearing that QWeb creates HTML, but we're "
"saying it again! One of the neat features of reports being written in "
"QWeb is they can be viewed within the web browser. This can be useful if "
"you want to embed a hyperlink that leads to a specific report. Note that "
"the usual security checks will still apply to prevent unauthorized users "
"from accessing the reports."
msgstr ""
"Ehtimol siz QWebning HTML yaratishini eshitishdan charchagandirsiz, "
"lekin biz buni yana aytamiz! QWeb da yozilgan hisobotlarning ajoyib "
"xususiyatlaridan biri - ularni veb brauzerda ko'rish mumkin. Bu ma'lum "
"hisobotga olib boradigan giperhavolani joylashtirmoqchi bo'lsangiz "
"foydali bo'lishi mumkin. E'tibor bering, ruxsatsiz foydalanuvchilarning "
"hisobotlarga kirishiga yo'l qo'ymaslik uchun odatiy xavfsizlik tekshiruvlari "
"hali ham qo'llaniladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/pdf_reports.rst:299
msgid ""
"Odoo has a built-in barcode image creator that allows for barcodes to be "
"embedded in your reports. Check out the corresponding `code "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/web/controllers/main.py#L2044-L2046>`__"
" to see all the supported barcode types."
msgstr ""
"Odoo hisobotlaringizga shtrix kodlarni joylashtirishga imkon beradigan "
"o'rnatilgan shtrix kod rasm yaratuvchisiga ega. Qo'llab-quvvatlanadigan "
"barcha shtrix kod turlarini ko'rish uchun tegishli `kodga "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/0e12fa135882cd5095dbf15fe2f64231c6a84336/addons/web/controllers/main.py#L2044-L2046>`__ "
"qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:10
msgid ""
"So far we have mostly concerned ourselves with implementing useful "
"features. However in most business scenarios *security* quickly becomes a"
" concern: currently,"
msgstr ""
"Hozirgacha biz asosan foydali xususiyatlarni amalga oshirish bilan "
"shug'ullandik. Biroq ko'plab biznes stsenariylarida *xavfsizlik* tezda "
"muammoga aylanadi: hozirda,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:14
msgid ""
"Any employee (which is what ``group_user`` stands for) can create, read, "
"update or delete properties, property types, or property tags."
msgstr ""
"Har qanday xodim (``group_user`` nimani anglatadi) mulklarni, mulk "
"turlarini yoki mulk teglarini yaratishi, o'qishi, yangilashi yoki "
"o'chirishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:16
msgid ""
"If ``estate_account`` is installed then only agents allowed to interact "
"with invoicing can confirm sales as that's necessary to :ref:`create an "
"invoice <tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module/create>`."
msgstr ""
"Agar ``estate_account`` o'rnatilgan bo'lsa, faqat hisob-faktura bilan "
"ishlashga ruxsat berilgan agentlar :ref:`hisob-faktura yaratish "
"<tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module/create>` uchun zarur "
"bo'lganligi sababli sotishni tasdiqlashi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:20
msgid "However:"
msgstr "Biroq:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:22
msgid "We do not want third parties to be able to access properties directly."
msgstr "Biz uchinchi shaxslarning mulklarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri kira olishini xohlamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:23
msgid ""
"Not all our employees may be real-estate agents (e.g. administrative "
"personnel, property managers, ...), we don't want non-agents to see the "
"available properties."
msgstr ""
"Barcha xodimlarimiz ko'chmas mulk agentlari bo'lmasligi mumkin (masalan, "
"ma'muriy xodimlar, mulk menejerlari, ...), agentlar bo'lmaganlar mavjud "
"mulklarni ko'rishini xohlamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:26
msgid ""
"Real-estate agents don't need or get to decide what property types or "
"tags are *available*."
msgstr "Ko'chmas mulk agentlari qaysi mulk turlari yoki teglari *mavjud* ekanligini hal qilishlari shart yoki imkoni yo'q."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:28
msgid ""
"Real-estate agents can have *exclusive* properties, we do not want one "
"agent to be able to manage another's exclusives."
msgstr "Ko'chmas mulk agentlari *eksklyuziv* mulklarga ega bo'lishi mumkin, bir agentning boshqasining eksklyuzivlarini boshqara olishini xohlamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:30
msgid ""
"All real-estate agents should be able to confirm the sale of a property "
"they can manage, but we do not want them to be able to validate or mark "
"as paid any invoice in the system."
msgstr ""
"Barcha ko'chmas mulk agentlari boshqara oladigan mulk sotilishini "
"tasdiqlashi kerak, lekin biz ularning tizimdagi har qanday hisob-fakturani "
"tasdiqlash yoki to'langan deb belgilash imkoniga ega bo'lishini xohlamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:36
msgid "We may actually be fine with some or most of these for a small business."
msgstr "Biz kichik biznes uchun bularning ba'zilari yoki ko'pchiligi bilan yaxshi bo'lishimiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:38
msgid ""
"Because it's easier for users to disable unnecessary security rules than "
"it is to create them from nothing, it's better to err on the side of "
"caution and limit access: users can relax that access if necessary or "
"convenient."
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchilarga keraksiz xavfsizlik qoidalarini noldan yaratishdan ko'ra "
"o'chirib qo'yish osonroq bo'lganligi sababli, ehtiyot tomonida bo'lish va "
"kirishni cheklash yaxshiroq: foydalanuvchilar zarur yoki qulay bo'lsa "
"bu kirishni bo'shashtirishlari mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:43
msgid "Groups"
msgstr "Guruhlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:47
msgid ""
"The documentation related to this topic can be found in :ref:`the "
"security reference <reference/security>`."
msgstr "Bu mavzuga oid hujjatlarni :ref:`xavfsizlik ma'lumotnomasida <reference/security>` topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:50
msgid ""
":doc:`/contributing/development/coding_guidelines` document the format "
"and location of master data items."
msgstr ":doc:`/contributing/development/coding_guidelines` asosiy ma'lumot elementlarining formati va joylashuvini hujjatlashtiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:53
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:138
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:203
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:272
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:316
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:387
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:458
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme.rst:23
msgid "**Goal**"
msgstr "**Maqsad**"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:55
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:140
msgid "At the end of this section,"
msgstr "Ushbu bo'lim oxirida,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:57
msgid "We can make employees *real-estate agents* or *real-estate managers*."
msgstr "Biz xodimlarni *ko'chmas mulk agentlari* yoki *ko'chmas mulk menejerlari* qila olamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:58
msgid "The ``admin`` user is a real-estate manager."
msgstr "``admin`` foydalanuvchi ko'chmas mulk menejeri."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:59
msgid ""
"We have a new *real-estate agent* employee with no access to invoicing or"
" administration."
msgstr "Bizda hisob-faktura yoki ma'muriyatga kirish huquqi bo'lmagan yangi *ko'chmas mulk agenti* xodim bor."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:62
msgid ""
"It would not be practical to attach individual security rules to "
"employees any time we need a change so *groups* link security rules and "
"users. They correspond to roles that can be assigned to employees."
msgstr ""
"O'zgarish kerak bo'lganda xodimlarga alohida xavfsizlik qoidalarini "
"biriktirish amaliy bo'lmaydi, shuning uchun *guruhlar* xavfsizlik qoidalari "
"va foydalanuvchilarni bog'laydi. Ular xodimlarga tayinlanishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"rollarga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:66
msgid ""
"For most Odoo applications [#app]_ a good baseline is to have *user* and "
"*manager* (or administrator) roles: the manager can change the "
"configuration of the application and oversee the entirety of its use "
"while the user can well, use the application [#appuser]_."
msgstr ""
"Ko'plab Odoo ilovalari [#app]_ uchun yaxshi boshlang'ich holat - "
"*foydalanuvchi* va *menejer* (yoki administrator) rollariga ega bo'lish: "
"menejer ilovaning konfiguratsiyasini o'zgartirishi va uning to'liq "
"foydalanishini nazorat qilishi mumkin, foydalanuvchi esa ilovadan "
"foydalana oladi [#appuser]_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:71
msgid "This baseline seems sufficient for us:"
msgstr "Bu boshlang'ich holat bizga yetarli ko'rinadi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:73
msgid ""
"Real estate managers can configure the system (manage available types and"
" tags) as well as oversee every property in the pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Ko'chmas mulk menejerlari tizimni sozlash (mavjud turlar va teglarni "
"boshqarish) hamda quvurdagi har bir mulkni nazorat qilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:75
msgid ""
"Real estate agents can manage the properties under their care, or "
"properties which are not specifically under the care of any agent."
msgstr ""
"Ko'chmas mulk agentlari o'z qaramlari ostidagi mulklarni yoki hech qaysi "
"agentning maxsus qaramida bo'lmagan mulklarni boshqarishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:78
msgid ""
"In keeping with Odoo's data-driven nature, a group is no more than a "
"record of the ``res.groups`` model. They are normally part of a module's "
":doc:`master data <define_module_data>`, defined in one of the module's "
"data files."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ning ma'lumotga asoslangan tabiatiga muvofiq, guruh ``res.groups`` "
"modelining yozuvidan boshqa narsa emas. Ular odatda modulning "
":doc:`asosiy ma'lumotlari <define_module_data>` ning bir qismi bo'lib, "
"modulning ma'lumot fayllaridan birida aniqlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:82
msgid ""
"As simple example `can be found here "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/532c083cbbe0ee6e7a940e2bdc9c677bd56b62fa/addons/hr/security/hr_security.xml#L9-L14>`_."
msgstr ""
"Oddiy misol `bu yerda topish mumkin "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/532c083cbbe0ee6e7a940e2bdc9c677bd56b62fa/addons/hr/security/hr_security.xml#L9-L14>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:86
msgid ""
"Create the ``security.xml`` file in the appropriate folder and add it to "
"the ``__manifest__.py`` file."
msgstr "Tegishli papkada ``security.xml`` faylini yarating va uni ``__manifest__.py`` fayliga qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:88
msgid ""
"If not already, add a ``'category'`` field to your ``__manifest__.py`` "
"with value ``Real Estate/Brokerage``."
msgstr ""
"Agar hali bo'lmasa, ``__manifest__.py`` ga ``Real Estate/Brokerage`` "
"qiymati bilan ``'category'`` maydonini qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:90
msgid ""
"Add a record creating a group privilege with the id "
"``groups_privilege_real_estate``, the name \"Real Estate\" and the "
"category ``base.module_category_real_estate_brokerage``."
msgstr ""
"``groups_privilege_real_estate`` id si, \"Real Estate\" nomi va "
"``base.module_category_real_estate_brokerage`` kategoriyasi bilan guruh "
"imtiyozini yaratadigan yozuv qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:93
msgid ""
"Add a record creating a group with the id ``estate_group_user``, the name"
" \"Agent\" and the group privilege ``groups_privilege_real_estate``."
msgstr ""
"``estate_group_user`` id si, \"Agent\" nomi va "
"``groups_privilege_real_estate`` guruh imtiyozi bilan guruh yaratadigan "
"yozuv qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:96
msgid ""
"Below that, add a record creating a group with the id "
"``estate_group_manager``, the name \"Manager\" and the group privilege "
"``groups_privilege_real_estate``. The ``estate_group_manager`` group "
"needs to imply ``estate_group_user``."
msgstr ""
"Undan pastda, ``estate_group_manager`` id si, \"Manager\" nomi va "
"``groups_privilege_real_estate`` guruh imtiyozi bilan guruh yaratadigan "
"yozuv qo'shing. ``estate_group_manager`` guruhi ``estate_group_user`` ni "
"anglatishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:102
msgid ""
"Where does that **category** comes from ? It's a *module category*. Here "
"we used the category id ``base.module_category_real_estate_brokerage`` "
"which was automatically generated by Odoo based on the `category` set in "
"the ``__manifest__.py`` of the module. You can also find here the list of"
" `default module categories "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/71da80deb044852a2af6b111d695f94aad7803ac/odoo/addons/base/data/ir_module_category_data.xml>`_"
" provided by Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Bu **kategoriya** qayerdan keladi? Bu *modul kategoriyasi*. Bu yerda "
"biz modulning ``__manifest__.py`` da o'rnatilgan `category` asosida Odoo "
"tomonidan avtomatik yaratilgan ``base.module_category_real_estate_brokerage`` "
"kategoriya id sidan foydalandik. Shuningdek, bu yerda Odoo tomonidan "
"taqdim etilgan `standart modul kategoriyalari ro'yxatini "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/71da80deb044852a2af6b111d695f94aad7803ac/odoo/addons/base/data/ir_module_category_data.xml>`_ "
"topishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:111
msgid ""
"Since we modified data files, remember to restart Odoo and update the "
"module using ``-u estate``."
msgstr "Ma'lumot fayllarini o'zgartirganimiz sababli, Odoo ni qayta ishga tushirishni va ``-u estate`` yordamida modulni yangilashni esda tuting."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:114
msgid ""
"If you go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Manage Users` and open the "
"``admin`` user (\"Mitchell Admin\"), you should see a new section:"
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`Sozlamalar --> Foydalanuvchilarni boshqarish` ga "
"o'tsangiz va ``admin`` foydalanuvchisini (\"Mitchell Admin\") ochsangiz, "
"yangi bo'limni ko'rishingiz kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:119
msgid "Set the admin user to be a *Real Estate manager*."
msgstr "Admin foydalanuvchisini *Ko'chmas mulk menejeri* sifatida belgilang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:123
msgid ""
"Via the web interface, create a new user with only the \"real estate "
"agent\" access. The user should not have any Invoicing or Administration "
"access."
msgstr ""
"Veb interfeys orqali faqat \"ko'chmas mulk agenti\" kirishiga ega "
"yangi foydalanuvchi yarating. Foydalanuvchida Hisob-faktura yoki "
"Ma'muriyat kirishiga ega bo'lmasligi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:126
msgid ""
"Use a private tab or window to log in with the new user (remember to set "
"a password), as the real-estate agent you should only see the real estate"
" application, and possibly the Discuss (chat) application:"
msgstr ""
"Yangi foydalanuvchi bilan kirish uchun maxfiy yorliq yoki oynadan "
"foydalaning (parol o'rnatishni esda tuting), ko'chmas mulk agenti "
"sifatida faqat ko'chmas mulk ilovasini va ehtimol Muhokama (chat) "
"ilovasini ko'rishingiz kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:135
msgid ""
"The documentation related to this topic can be found at "
":ref:`reference/security/acl`."
msgstr "Bu mavzuga oid hujjatlarni :ref:`reference/security/acl` da topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:142
msgid ""
"Employees who are not at least real-estate agents will not see the real-"
"estate application."
msgstr "Kamida ko'chmas mulk agentlari bo'lmagan xodimlar ko'chmas mulk ilovasini ko'rmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:144
msgid "Real-estate agents will not be able to update the property types or tags."
msgstr "Ko'chmas mulk agentlari mulk turlarini yoki teglarini yangilay olmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:146
msgid ""
"Access rights were first introduced in "
":doc:`server_framework_101/04_securityintro`."
msgstr "Kirish huquqlari birinchi marta :doc:`server_framework_101/04_securityintro` da kiritilgan."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:148
msgid ""
"Access rights are a way to give users access to models *via* groups: "
"associate an access right to a group, then all users with that group will"
" have the access."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqlari - foydalanuvchilarga guruhlar *orqali* modellarga "
"kirish imkonini berish usuli: kirish huquqini guruhga bog'lang, keyin "
"o'sha guruhga ega barcha foydalanuvchilar kirishga ega bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:151
msgid ""
"For instance we don't want real-estate agents to be able to modify what "
"property types are available, so we would not link that access to the "
"\"user\" group."
msgstr ""
"Masalan, biz ko'chmas mulk agentlarining qaysi mulk turlari mavjudligini "
"o'zgartira olishini xohlamaymiz, shuning uchun bu kirishni \"foydalanuvchi\" "
"guruhiga bog'lamaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:154
msgid ""
"Access rights can only give access, they can't remove it: when access is "
"checked, the system looks to see if *any* access right associated with "
"the user (via any group) grants that access."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqlari faqat kirish berishi mumkin, ularni olib tashlash "
"mumkin emas: kirish tekshirilganda, tizim foydalanuvchi bilan bog'liq "
"*har qanday* kirish huquqi (har qanday guruh orqali) bu kirishni "
"berishini ko'radi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:159
msgid "read"
msgstr "o'qish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:159
msgid "update"
msgstr "yangilash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:161
msgid "A"
msgstr "A"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:161
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:162
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:163
msgid "X"
msgstr "X"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:162
msgid "B"
msgstr "B"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:163
msgid "C"
msgstr "C"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:166
msgid ""
"A user with the groups A and C will be able to do anything but delete the"
" object while one with B and C will be able to read and update it, but "
"not create or delete it."
msgstr ""
"A va C guruhlariga ega foydalanuvchi ob'ektni o'chirishdan tashqari "
"hamma narsani qila oladi, B va C guruhlariga ega foydalanuvchi esa "
"o'qish va yangilash, lekin yaratish yoki o'chirish imkoniga ega bo'lmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:171
msgid ""
"The group of an access right can be omitted, this means the ACL applies "
"to *every user*, this is a useful but risky fallback as depending on the "
"applications installed it can grant even non-users access to the model."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqining guruhi qoldirilishi mumkin, bu ACL *har bir "
"foydalanuvchi* ga qo'llanilishini anglatadi, bu foydali, lekin xavfli "
"qaytish - o'rnatilgan ilovalarga qarab u hatto foydalanuvchi bo'lmaganlarga "
"ham modelga kirish imkonini berishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:174
msgid ""
"If no access right applies to a user, they are not granted access "
"(default-deny)."
msgstr "Agar foydalanuvchiga hech qanday kirish huquqi qo'llanilmasa, ularga kirish berilmaydi (standart rad etish)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:176
msgid ""
"If a menu item points to a model to which a user doesn't have access and "
"has no submenus which the user can see, the menu will not be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Agar menyu elementi foydalanuvchi kira olmaydigan modelga ishora qilsa "
"va foydalanuvchi ko'ra oladigan quyi menyulari bo'lmasa, menyu "
"ko'rsatilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:179
msgid "Update the access rights file to:"
msgstr "Kirish huquqlari faylini yangilang:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:181
msgid "Give full access to all objects to your Real Estate Manager group."
msgstr "Ko'chmas mulk Menejeri guruhiga barcha ob'ektlarga to'liq kirish bering."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:182
msgid "Give agents (real estate users) only read access to types and tags."
msgstr "Agentlarga (ko'chmas mulk foydalanuvchilari) turlari va teglarga faqat o'qish kirishini bering."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:183
msgid "Give nobody the right to delete properties."
msgstr "Hech kimga mulklarni o'chirish huquqi bermang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:184
msgid ""
"Check that your agent user is not able to alter types or tags, or to "
"delete properties, but that they can otherwise create or update "
"properties."
msgstr ""
"Agent foydalanuvchingiz turlarni yoki teglarni o'zgartira olmasligini "
"yoki mulklarni o'chira olmasligini, lekin boshqa holatlarda mulklarni "
"yaratish yoki yangilash imkoniga ega ekanligini tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:190
msgid ""
"Remember to give different xids to your ``ir.model.access`` records "
"otherwise they will overwrite one another."
msgstr ""
"``ir.model.access`` yozuvlaringizga turli xid lar berishni esda tuting, "
"aks holda ular bir-birini qayta yozadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:193
msgid ""
"Since the \"demo\" user was not made a real-estate agent or manager, they"
" should not even be able to see the real-estate application. Use a "
"private tab or window to check for this (the \"demo\" user has the "
"password \"demo\")."
msgstr ""
"\"demo\" foydalanuvchisi ko'chmas mulk agenti yoki menejeri qilinmaganligi "
"sababli, ular ko'chmas mulk ilovasini ko'ra olmaydi. Buni tekshirish "
"uchun maxfiy yorliq yoki oynadan foydalaning (\"demo\" foydalanuvchisi "
"\"demo\" parolga ega)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:200
msgid ""
"The documentation related to this topic can be found at "
":ref:`reference/security/rules`."
msgstr "Bu mavzuga oid hujjatlarni :ref:`reference/security/rules` da topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:205
msgid ""
"At the end of this section, agents will not be able to see the properties"
" exclusive to their colleagues; but managers will still be able to see "
"everything."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu bo'lim oxirida agentlar hamkasblariga eksklyuziv mulklarni ko'ra "
"olmaydi; lekin menejerlar hali ham hamma narsani ko'ra oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:209
msgid ""
"Access rights can grant access to an entire model but often we need to be"
" more specific: while an agent can interact with properties in general we"
" may not want them to update or even see properties managed by one of "
"their colleagues."
msgstr ""
"Kirish huquqlari butun modelga kirish huquqini berishi mumkin, lekin "
"ko'pincha biz aniqroq bo'lishimiz kerak: agent umuman mulklar bilan "
"ishlashi mumkin bo'lsa ham, biz ularning hamkasblari boshqaradigan "
"mulklarni yangilash yoki hatto ko'rishini xohlamasligimiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:213
msgid ""
"Record *rules* provide that precision: they can grant or reject access to"
" individual records:"
msgstr "Yozuv *qoidalari* bu aniqlikni ta'minlaydi: ular individual yozuvlarga kirish huquqini berishi yoki rad etishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:229
msgid ""
"The :ref:`reference/orm/domains` is how access is managed: if the record "
"passes then access is granted, otherwise access is rejected."
msgstr ""
":ref:`reference/orm/domains` - kirish qanday boshqariladi: agar yozuv "
"o'tsa kirish beriladi, aks holda kirish rad etiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:234
msgid ""
"Because rules tends to be rather complex and not created in bulk, they're"
" usually created in XML rather than the CSV used for access rights."
msgstr ""
"Qoidalar juda murakkab bo'lishi va ommaviy yaratilmasligi sababli, ular "
"odatda kirish huquqlari uchun ishlatiladigan CSV o'rniga XML da yaratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:237
msgid "The rule above:"
msgstr "Yuqoridagi qoida:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:239
msgid ""
"Only applies to the \"create\", \"update\" (write) and \"delete\" "
"(unlink) operations: here we want every employee to be able to see other "
"users' records but only the author / assignee can update a record."
msgstr ""
"Faqat \"create\", \"update\" (write) va \"delete\" (unlink) operatsiyalariga "
"qo'llaniladi: bu yerda biz har bir xodimning boshqa foydalanuvchilar "
"yozuvlarini ko'ra olishini, lekin faqat muallif / tayinlangan kishi "
"yozuvni yangilashini xohlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:242
msgid ""
"Is :ref:`non-global <reference/security/rules/global>` so we can provide "
"an additional rule for e.g. managers."
msgstr ""
":ref:`global bo'lmagan <reference/security/rules/global>`, shuning uchun "
"biz masalan menejerlar uchun qo'shimcha qoida bera olamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:244
msgid ""
"Allows the operation if the current user (``user.id``) is set (e.g. "
"created, or is assigned) on the record, or if the record has no "
"associated user at all."
msgstr ""
"Agar joriy foydalanuvchi (``user.id``) yozuvda o'rnatilgan bo'lsa "
"(masalan, yaratilgan yoki tayinlangan) yoki yozuvda umuman bog'liq "
"foydalanuvchi bo'lmasa operatsiyaga ruxsat beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:249
msgid ""
"If no rule is defined or applies to a model and operation, then the "
"operation is allowed (*default-allow*), this can have odd effects if "
"access rights are not set up correctly (are too permissive)."
msgstr ""
"Agar model va operatsiya uchun hech qanday qoida aniqlanmagan yoki "
"qo'llanilmagan bo'lsa, operatsiyaga ruxsat beriladi (*default-allow*), "
"bu kirish huquqlari to'g'ri o'rnatilmagan bo'lsa (juda ruxsat beruvchi) "
"g'alati ta'sirlarga olib kelishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:255
msgid ""
"Define a rule which limits agents to only being able to see or modify "
"properties which have no salesperson, or for which they are the "
"salesperson."
msgstr ""
"Agentlarni faqat sotuvchisi bo'lmagan yoki o'zlari sotuvchi bo'lgan "
"mulklarni ko'rish yoki o'zgartirishga cheklaydigan qoida aniqlang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:258
msgid ""
"You may want to create a second real-estate agent user, or create a few "
"properties for which the salesperson is a manager or some other user."
msgstr ""
"Siz ikkinchi ko'chmas mulk agenti foydalanuvchisini yaratish yoki "
"sotuvchisi menejer yoki boshqa foydalanuvchi bo'lgan bir nechta mulk "
"yaratishni xohlashingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:261
msgid ""
"Verify that your real estate manager(s) can still see all properties. If "
"not, why not? Remember:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'chmas mulk menejer(lar)ingiz hali ham barcha mulklarni ko'ra "
"olishini tasdiqlang. Agar ko'ra olmasa, nima uchun? Esda tuting:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:264
msgid "The ``estate_group_manager`` group needs to imply ``estate_group_user``."
msgstr "``estate_group_manager`` guruhi ``estate_group_user`` ni anglatishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:267
msgid "Security Override"
msgstr "Xavfsizlikni bekor qilish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:270
msgid "Bypassing Security"
msgstr "Xavfsizlikni chetlab o'tish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:274
msgid ""
"At the end of this section, agents should be able to confirm property "
"sales without needing invoicing access."
msgstr "Ushbu bo'lim oxirida agentlar hisob-faktura kirishiga muhtoj bo'lmasdan mulk sotilishini tasdiqlashi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:277
msgid ""
"If you try to mark a property as \"sold\" as the real estate agent, you "
"should get an access error:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'chmas mulk agenti sifatida mulkni \"sotilgan\" deb belgilashga "
"urinib ko'rsangiz, kirish xatosini olishingiz kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:282
msgid ""
"This happens because ``estate_account`` tries to create an invoice during"
" the process, but creating an invoice requires the right to all invoice "
"management."
msgstr ""
"Bu ``estate_account`` jarayon davomida hisob-faktura yaratishga "
"urinayotganligi sababli sodir bo'ladi, lekin hisob-faktura yaratish "
"barcha hisob-faktura boshqaruviga huquq talab qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:285
msgid ""
"We want agents to be able to confirm a sale without them having full "
"invoicing access, which means we need to *bypass* the normal security "
"checks of Odoo in order to create an invoice *despite* the current user "
"not having the right to do so."
msgstr ""
"Biz agentlarning to'liq hisob-faktura kirishisiz sotishni tasdiqlash "
"imkoniga ega bo'lishini xohlaymiz, bu joriy foydalanuvchi bunga huquqqa "
"ega bo'lmasa *ham* hisob-faktura yaratish uchun Odoo ning normal "
"xavfsizlik tekshiruvlarini *chetlab o'tishimiz* kerakligini anglatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:290
msgid ""
"There are two main ways to bypass existing security checks in Odoo, "
"either wilfully or as a side-effect:"
msgstr "Odoo da mavjud xavfsizlik tekshiruvlarini chetlab o'tishning ikkita asosiy usuli mavjud, yo ixtiyoriy yoki yon ta'sir sifatida:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:293
msgid ""
"The ``sudo()`` method will create a new recordset in \"sudo mode\", this "
"ignores all access rights and record rules (although hard-coded group and"
" user checks may still apply)."
msgstr ""
"``sudo()`` metodi \"sudo rejimida\" yangi yozuvlar to'plamini yaratadi, "
"bu barcha kirish huquqlari va yozuv qoidalarini e'tiborsiz qoldiradi "
"(garchi qattiq kodlangan guruh va foydalanuvchi tekshiruvlari hali ham "
"qo'llanilishi mumkin)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:296
msgid ""
"Performing raw SQL queries will bypass access rights and record rules as "
"a side-effect of bypassing the ORM itself."
msgstr "Xom SQL so'rovlarini bajarish ORM ning o'zini chetlab o'tishning yon ta'siri sifatida kirish huquqlari va yozuv qoidalarini chetlab o'tadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:301
msgid ""
"Update ``estate_account`` to bypass access rights and rules when creating"
" the invoice."
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratishda kirish huquqlari va qoidalarini chetlab o'tish uchun ``estate_account`` ni yangilang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:306
msgid ""
"These features should generally be avoided, and only used with extreme "
"care, after having checked that the current user and operation should be "
"able to bypass normal access rights validation."
msgstr ""
"Bu xususiyatlar odatda qochilishi kerak va joriy foydalanuvchi va "
"operatsiya normal kirish huquqlari tekshiruvini chetlab o'ta olishini "
"tekshirgandan so'ng faqat haddan tashqari ehtiyot bilan ishlatilishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:310
msgid ""
"Operations performed in such modes should also rely on user input as "
"little as possible, and should validate it to the maximum extent they "
"can."
msgstr ""
"Bunday rejimlarda bajarilgan operatsiyalar foydalanuvchi kiritishiga "
"imkon qadar kam tayanishi va iloji boricha maksimal darajada tekshirishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:314
msgid "Programmatically checking security"
msgstr "Dasturiy ravishda xavfsizlikni tekshirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:318
msgid ""
"At the end of this section, the creation of the invoice should be "
"resilient to security issues regardless to changes to ``estate``."
msgstr "Ushbu bo'lim oxirida hisob-faktura yaratish ``estate`` ga o'zgartirishlardan qat'iy nazar xavfsizlik muammolariga bardoshli bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:321
msgid ""
"In Odoo, access rights and record rules are only checked *when performing"
" data access via the ORM* e.g. creating, reading, searching, writing, or "
"unlinking a record via ORM methods. Other methods do *not* necessarily "
"check against any sort of access rights."
msgstr ""
"Odoo da kirish huquqlari va yozuv qoidalari faqat *ORM orqali ma'lumotlarga "
"kirish amalga oshirilganda* tekshiriladi, masalan ORM metodlari orqali "
"yozuv yaratish, o'qish, qidirish, yozish yoki o'chirish. Boshqa metodlar "
"har qanday turdagi kirish huquqlariga nisbatan *tekshirmaydi*."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:326
msgid ""
"In the previous section, we bypassed the record rules when creating the "
"invoice in ``action_sold``. This bypass can be reached by any user "
"without any access right being checked:"
msgstr ""
"Oldingi bo'limda biz ``action_sold`` da hisob-faktura yaratishda yozuv "
"qoidalarini chetlab o'tdik. Bu chetlab o'tishga hech qanday kirish huquqi "
"tekshirilmasdan har qanday foydalanuvchi eta oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:330
msgid ""
"Add a print to ``action_sold`` in ``estate_account`` before the creation "
"of the invoice (as creating the invoice accesses the property, therefore "
"triggers an ACL check) e.g.::"
msgstr ""
"Hisob-faktura yaratishdan oldin ``estate_account`` da ``action_sold`` ga "
"print qo'shing (chunki hisob-faktura yaratish mulkka kiradi, shuning "
"uchun ACL tekshiruvini ishga tushiradi), masalan::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:336
msgid "You should see ``reached`` in your Odoo log, followed by an access error."
msgstr "Odoo jurnalingizda ``reached`` ni, so'ngra kirish xatosini ko'rishingiz kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:338
msgid ""
"Just because you're already in Python code does not mean any access right"
" or rule has or will be checked."
msgstr "Python kodida allaqachon bo'lishingiz har qanday kirish huquqi yoki qoidaning tekshirilgan yoki tekshirilishini anglatmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:341
msgid ""
"*Currently* the accesses are implicitly checked by accessing data on "
"``self`` as well as calling ``super()`` (which does the same and "
"*updates* ``self``), triggering access errors and cancelling the "
"transaction \"uncreating\" our invoice."
msgstr ""
"*Hozirda* kirishlar ``self`` dagi ma'lumotlarga kirish hamda ``super()`` "
"chaqiruvi orqali (bu ham bir xil narsani qiladi va ``self`` ni "
"*yangilaydi*) yashirin tekshiriladi, kirish xatolarini ishga tushiradi "
"va tranzaksiyani bekor qilib hisob-fakturamizni \"yaratilmagan\" qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:346
msgid ""
"*However* if this changes in the future, or we add side-effects to the "
"method (e.g. reporting the sale to a government agency), or bugs are "
"introduced in ``estate``, ... it would be possible for non-agents to "
"trigger operations they should not have access to."
msgstr ""
"*Biroq* bu kelajakda o'zgarsa, yoki metodga yon ta'sirlar qo'shsak "
"(masalan, sotishni davlat idorasiga xabar berish), yoki ``estate`` da "
"xatoliklar kiritilsa, ... agentlar bo'lmaganlarning kirish imkoniga "
"ega bo'lmasligi kerak bo'lgan operatsiyalarni ishga tushirishi mumkin bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:351
msgid ""
"Therefore when performing non-CRUD operations, or legitimately bypassing "
"the ORM or security, or when triggering other side-effects, it is "
"extremely important to perform *explicit security checks*."
msgstr ""
"Shuning uchun CRUD bo'lmagan operatsiyalarni bajarishda yoki ORM ni "
"yoki xavfsizlikni qonuniy chetlab o'tishda yoki boshqa yon ta'sirlarni "
"ishga tushirishda *aniq xavfsizlik tekshiruvlarini* bajarish juda muhim."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:355
msgid "Explicit security checks can be performed by:"
msgstr "Aniq xavfsizlik tekshiruvlarini quyidagi yo'llar bilan bajarish mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:357
msgid ""
"Checking who the current user is (``self.env.user``) and match them "
"against specific models or records."
msgstr ""
"Joriy foydalanuvchi kim ekanligini tekshirish (``self.env.user``) va "
"ularni ma'lum modellar yoki yozuvlarga solishtirish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:359
msgid ""
"Checking that the current user has specific groups hard-coded to allow or"
" deny an operation (``self.env.user.has_group``)."
msgstr ""
"Joriy foydalanuvchining operatsiyaga ruxsat berish yoki rad etish uchun "
"qattiq kodlangan ma'lum guruhlarga ega ekanligini tekshirish "
"(``self.env.user.has_group``)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:361
msgid ""
"Calling ``check_access(operations)`` on a recordset, this verifies that "
"the current user is allowed to perform the operation on *every* record of"
" the set. As a special case, when the recordset is empty, it verifies "
"that the current user has some access rights to perform the operation on "
"the model in general."
msgstr ""
"Yozuvlar to'plamida ``check_access(operations)`` ni chaqirish - bu "
"joriy foydalanuvchining to'plamning *har bir* yozuvida operatsiyani "
"bajarishga ruxsat berilganligini tekshiradi. Maxsus holat sifatida, "
"yozuvlar to'plami bo'sh bo'lganda, u joriy foydalanuvchining umuman "
"modelda operatsiyani bajarish uchun ba'zi kirish huquqlariga ega "
"ekanligini tekshiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:368
msgid ""
"Before creating the invoice, use ``check_access`` to ensure that the "
"current user can update the property the invoice is for."
msgstr ""
"Hisob-faktura yaratishdan oldin, joriy foydalanuvchi hisob-faktura "
"uchun bo'lgan mulkni yangilashini ta'minlash uchun ``check_access`` dan foydalaning."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:371
msgid "Re-run the bypass script, check that the error occurs before the print."
msgstr "Chetlab o'tish skriptini qayta ishga tushiring, xato printdan oldin sodir bo'lishini tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:376
msgid "Multi-company security"
msgstr "Ko'p kompaniyali xavfsizlik"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:380
msgid ""
":ref:`reference/howtos/company` for an overview of multi-company "
"facilities in general, and :ref:`multi-company security rules "
"<howto/company/security>` in particular."
msgstr ""
"Umuman ko'p kompaniyali imkoniyatlar uchun :ref:`reference/howtos/company`, "
"va xususan :ref:`ko'p kompaniyali xavfsizlik qoidalari "
"<howto/company/security>`."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:384
msgid ""
"Documentation on rules in general can, again, be found at "
":ref:`reference/security/rules`."
msgstr "Umuman qoidalar bo'yicha hujjatlarni yana :ref:`reference/security/rules` da topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:389
msgid ""
"At the end of this section, agents should only have access to properties "
"of their agency (or agencies)."
msgstr "Ushbu bo'lim oxirida agentlar faqat o'z agentligi (yoki agentliklari) mulklariga kirish huquqiga ega bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:392
msgid ""
"For one reason or another we might need to manage our real-estate "
"business as multiple companies e.g. we might have largely autonomous "
"agencies, a franchise setup, or multiple brands (possibly from having "
"acquired other real-estate businesses) which remain legally or "
"financially separate from one another."
msgstr ""
"Bir yoki boshqa sabab tufayli biz ko'chmas mulk biznesimizni bir nechta "
"kompaniya sifatida boshqarishimiz kerak bo'lishi mumkin, masalan biz "
"asosan avtonom agentliklarga, franchayzing tuzilishiga yoki bir-biridan "
"huquqiy yoki moliyaviy jihatdan alohida qoladigan bir nechta brend "
"(ehtimol boshqa ko'chmas mulk bizneslarini sotib olgan) ga ega bo'lishimiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:398
msgid ""
"Odoo can be used to manage multiple companies inside the same system, "
"however the actual handling is up to individual modules: Odoo itself "
"provides the tools to manage the issue of company-dependent fields and "
"*multi-company rules*, which is what we're going to concern ourselves "
"with."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bir xil tizimda bir nechta kompaniyani boshqarish uchun "
"ishlatilishi mumkin, biroq haqiqiy qayta ishlash individual modullarga "
"bog'liq: Odoo ning o'zi kompaniyaga bog'liq maydonlar va *ko'p "
"kompaniyali qoidalar* muammosini boshqarish uchun vositalarni taqdim "
"etadi, va biz shu bilan shug'ullanamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:403
msgid ""
"We want different agencies to be \"siloed\" from one another, with "
"properties belonging to a given agency and users (whether agents or "
"managers) only able to see properties linked to their agency."
msgstr ""
"Biz turli agentliklarni bir-biridan \"ajratilgan\" bo'lishini xohlaymiz, "
"mulklar ma'lum agentlikka tegishli bo'lib, foydalanuvchilar (agentlar "
"yoki menejerlar bo'lishidan qat'iy nazar) faqat o'z agentliklariga "
"bog'liq mulklarni ko'ra oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:407
msgid ""
"As before, because this is based on non-trivial records it's easier for a"
" user to relax rules than to tighten them so it makes sense to default to"
" a relatively stronger security model."
msgstr ""
"Avvalgidek, bu ahamiyatli bo'lmagan yozuvlarga asoslanganidan qo'llanuvchi "
"uchun qoidalarni bo'shatish ularni mahkamlashdan osonroq, shuning uchun "
"nisbatan kuchliroq xavfsizlik modelida standart bo'lish mantiqiy."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:411
msgid ""
"Multi-company rules are simply record rules based on the ``company_ids`` "
"or ``company_id`` fields:"
msgstr "Ko'p kompaniyali qoidalar - shunchaki ``company_ids`` yoki ``company_id`` maydonlariga asoslangan yozuv qoidalari:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:414
msgid "``company_ids`` is all the companies to which the current user has access"
msgstr "``company_ids`` - joriy foydalanuvchi kirish huquqiga ega bo'lgan barcha kompaniyalar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:415
msgid ""
"``company_id`` is the currently active company (the one the user is "
"currently working in / for)."
msgstr "``company_id`` - hozirda faol kompaniya (foydalanuvchi hozirda unda/u uchun ishlaydigan)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:418
msgid ""
"Multi-company rules will *usually* use the former i.e. check if the "
"record is associated with *one* of the companies the user has access to:"
msgstr ""
"Ko'p kompaniyali qoidalar *odatda* birinchisini ishlatadi, ya'ni "
"yozuv foydalanuvchi kirish huquqiga ega bo'lgan kompaniyalardan *biri* "
"bilan bog'liq ekanligini tekshiradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:434
msgid ""
"Multi-company rules are usually :ref:`global "
"<reference/security/rules/global>`, otherwise there is a high risk that "
"additional rules would allow bypassing the multi-company rules."
msgstr ""
"Ko'p kompaniyali qoidalar odatda :ref:`global "
"<reference/security/rules/global>`, aks holda qo'shimcha qoidalar ko'p "
"kompaniyali qoidalarni chetlab o'tishga ruxsat berish xavfi yuqori."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:440
msgid ""
"Add a ``company_id`` field to ``estate.property``, it should be required "
"(we don't want agency-less properties), and should default to the current"
" user's current company."
msgstr ""
"``estate.property`` ga ``company_id`` maydonini qo'shing, u talab "
"qilinadigan bo'lishi kerak (biz agentliksiz mulklarni xohlamaymiz), va "
"joriy foydalanuvchining joriy kompaniyasiga standart qilinishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:443
msgid "Create a new company, with a new estate agent in that company."
msgstr "O'sha kompaniyada yangi ko'chmas mulk agenti bilan yangi kompaniya yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:444
msgid "The manager should be a member of both companies."
msgstr "Menejer ikki kompaniyaning ham a'zosi bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:445
msgid "The old agent should only be a member of the old company."
msgstr "Eski agent faqat eski kompaniyaning a'zosi bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:446
msgid ""
"Create a few properties in each company (either use the company selector "
"as the manager or use the agents). Unset the default salesman to avoid "
"triggering *that* rule."
msgstr ""
"Har bir kompaniyada bir nechta mulk yarating (menejer sifatida kompaniya "
"tanlovchidan foydalaning yoki agentlardan foydalaning). *O'sha* qoidani "
"ishga tushirishdan saqlanish uchun standart sotuvchini o'chirib qo'ying."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:449
msgid ""
"All agents can see all companies, which is not desirable, add the record "
"rule restricting this behaviour."
msgstr ""
"Barcha agentlar barcha kompaniyalarni ko'ra oladi, bu maqsadga muvofiq "
"emas, bu xulq-atvorni cheklaydigan yozuv qoidasini qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:452
msgid "remember to ``--update`` your module when you change its model or data"
msgstr "model yoki ma'lumotini o'zgartirganingizda modulingizni ``--update`` qilishni esda tuting"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:456
msgid "Visibility != security"
msgstr "Ko'rinuvchanlik != xavfsizlik"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:460
msgid ""
"At the end of this section, real-estate agents should not see the "
"Settings menu of the real-estate application, but should still be able to"
" set the property type or tags."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu bo'lim oxirida ko'chmas mulk agentlari ko'chmas mulk ilovasining "
"Sozlamalar menyusini ko'rmasligi kerak, lekin hali ham mulk turini yoki "
"teglarini o'rnatish imkoniga ega bo'lishi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:464
msgid ""
"Specific Odoo models can be associated directly with groups (or "
"companies, or users). It is important to figure out whether this "
"association is a *security* or a *visibility* feature before using it:"
msgstr ""
"Muayyan Odoo modellari to'g'ridan-to'g'ri guruhlar (yoki kompaniyalar, "
"yoki foydalanuvchilar) bilan bog'lanishi mumkin. Uni ishlatishdan oldin "
"bu uyushma *xavfsizlik* yoki *ko'rinuvchanlik* xususiyati ekanligini "
"aniqlash muhim:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:468
msgid ""
"*Visibility* features mean a user can still access the model or record "
"otherwise, either through another part of the interface or by "
":doc:`performing operations remotely using RPC "
"<../reference/external_api>`, things might just not be visible in the web"
" interface in some contexts."
msgstr ""
"*Ko'rinuvchanlik* xususiyatlari foydalanuvchi modeli yoki yozuvga boshqa "
"yo'l bilan kirish imkoniga ega ekanligini anglatadi, yo interfeysning "
"boshqa qismi orqali yo "
":doc:`RPC yordamida masofadan turib operatsiyalarni bajarish "
"<../reference/external_api>` orqali, narsa ba'zi kontekstlarda veb "
"interfeysda ko'rinmasligi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:472
msgid ""
"*Security* features mean a user can not access records, fields or "
"operations."
msgstr "*Xavfsizlik* xususiyatlari foydalanuvchi yozuvlar, maydonlar yoki operatsiyalarga kirish imkoniga ega emasligini anglatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:474
msgid "Here are some examples:"
msgstr "Mana ba'zi misollar:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:476
msgid ""
"Groups on *model fields* (in Python) are a security feature, users "
"outside the group will not be able to retrieve the field, or even know it"
" exists."
msgstr ""
"*Model maydonlaridagi* (Python da) guruhlar xavfsizlik xususiyati bo'lib, "
"guruhdan tashqaridagi foydalanuvchilar maydonni ololmaydi yoki uning "
"mavjudligini ham bilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:479
msgid ""
"Example: in server actions, `only system users can see or update Python "
"code "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/7058e338a980268df1c502b8b2860bdd8be9f727/odoo/addons/base/models/ir_actions.py#L414-L417>`_."
msgstr ""
"Misol: server amallarida, `faqat tizim foydalanuvchilari Python kodini "
"ko'rishi yoki yangilashi mumkin "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/7058e338a980268df1c502b8b2860bdd8be9f727/odoo/addons/base/models/ir_actions.py#L414-L417>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:481
msgid ""
"Groups on *view elements* (in XML) are a visibility feature, users "
"outside the group will not be able to see the element or its content in "
"the form but they will otherwise be able to interact with the object "
"(including that field)."
msgstr ""
"*Ko'rinish elementlaridagi* (XML da) guruhlar ko'rinuvchanlik xususiyati "
"bo'lib, guruhdan tashqaridagi foydalanuvchilar formada elementni yoki "
"uning tarkibini ko'ra olmaydi, lekin boshqa holatda ob'ekt (shu maydon "
"bilan) bilan ishlash imkoniga ega bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:485
msgid ""
"Example: `only managers have an immediate filter to see their teams' "
"leaves "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/8e19904bcaff8300803a7b596c02ec45fcf36ae6/addons/hr_holidays/report/hr_leave_reports.xml#L16>`_."
msgstr ""
"Misol: `faqat menejerlar o'z jamoalari ta'tillarini ko'rish uchun "
"darhol filtrga ega "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/8e19904bcaff8300803a7b596c02ec45fcf36ae6/addons/hr_holidays/report/hr_leave_reports.xml#L16>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:487
msgid ""
"Groups on menus and actions are visibility features, the menu or action "
"will not be shown in the interface but that doesn't prevent directly "
"interacting with the underlying object."
msgstr ""
"Menyu va amallardagi guruhlar ko'rinuvchanlik xususiyatlari bo'lib, menyu "
"yoki amal interfeysda ko'rsatilmaydi, lekin bu asosiy ob'ekt bilan "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ishlashga to'sqinlik qilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:491
msgid ""
"Example: `only system administrators can see the elearning settings menu "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/ff828a3e0c5386dc54e6a46fd71de9272ef3b691/addons/website_slides/views/website_slides_menu_views.xml#L64-L69>`_."
msgstr ""
"Misol: `faqat tizim administratorlari elearning sozlamalari menyusini "
"ko'ra oladi "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/ff828a3e0c5386dc54e6a46fd71de9272ef3b691/addons/website_slides/views/website_slides_menu_views.xml#L64-L69>`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:496
msgid ""
"Real Estate agents can not add property types or tags, but can see their "
"options from the Property form view when creating it."
msgstr ""
"Ko'chmas mulk agentlari mulk turlari yoki teglarni qo'sha olmaydi, lekin "
"ularni yaratishda Mulk forma ko'rinishidan variantlarni ko'ra oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:499
msgid ""
"The Settings menu just adds noise to their interface, make it only "
"visible to managers."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamalar menyusi ularning interfeysini ortiqcha to'ldirib qo'yadi, "
"uni faqat menejerlar uchun ko'rinadigan qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:502
msgid ""
"Despite not having access to the Property Types and Property Tags menus "
"anymore, agents can still access the underlying objects since they can "
"still select tags or a type to set on their properties."
msgstr ""
"Mulk Turlari va Mulk Teglari menyulariga endi kirish imkoni bo'lmasa ham, "
"agentlar hali ham asosiy ob'ektlarga kira oladi, chunki ular hali ham "
"mulklarida teglar yoki turni tanlash imkoniga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:506
msgid ""
"An Odoo Application is a group of related modules covering a business "
"area or field, usually composed of a base module and a number of "
"expansions on that base to add optional or specific features, or link to "
"other business areas."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ilovasi - bu biznes sohasi yoki yo'nalishini qamrab oluvchi bog'liq "
"modullar guruhi bo'lib, odatda asosiy modul va ixtiyoriy yoki maxsus "
"xususiyatlar qo'shish yoki boshqa biznes sohalari bilan bog'lash uchun "
"ushbu asosga kengaytmalar to'plamidan iborat."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/restrict_data_access.rst:511
msgid ""
"For applications which would be used by most or every employees, the "
"\"application user\" role might be done away with and its abilities "
"granted to all employees directly e.g. generally all employees can submit"
" expenses or take time off."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pchilik yoki barcha xodimlar tomonidan ishlatiladigan ilovalar uchun "
"\"ilova foydalanuvchisi\" roli bekor qilinishi va uning imkoniyatlari "
"barcha xodimlarga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri berilishi mumkin, masalan, odatda "
"barcha xodimlar xarajatlarni topshirishi yoki ta'til olishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101.rst:13
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Server framework 101 tutorial! If you reached this page "
"that means you are interested in the development of your own Odoo module."
" It might also mean that you recently joined the Odoo company for a "
"rather technical position. In any case, your journey to the technical "
"side of Odoo starts here."
msgstr ""
"Server framework 101 darsligiga xush kelibsiz! Agar siz ushbu sahifaga "
"yetib kelgan bo'lsangiz, bu o'zingizning Odoo modulingizni ishlab "
"chiqishga qiziqasiz degani. Bu, shuningdek, yaqinda texnik lavozim uchun "
"Odoo kompaniyasiga qo'shilganingizni ham anglatishi mumkin. Har qanday "
"holda, Odoo ning texnik tomoniga sayohatingiz shu yerdan boshlanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101.rst:18
msgid ""
"The goal of this tutorial is for you to get an insight of the most "
"important parts of the Odoo development framework while developing your "
"own Odoo module to manage real estate assets. The chapters should be "
"followed in their given order since they cover the development of a new "
"Odoo application from scratch in an incremental way. In other words, each"
" chapter depends on the previous one."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu darslikning maqsadi - o'z ko'chmas mulk aktivlarini boshqarish "
"uchun Odoo modulini ishlab chiqarish jarayonida Odoo ishlab chiqish "
"framework ning eng muhim qismlarini tushunib olishdir. Boblar berilgan "
"tartibda ko'rib chiqilishi kerak, chunki ular bosqichma-bosqich tarzda "
"yangi Odoo ilovasini noldan yaratishni qamrab oladi. Boshqacha aytganda, "
"har bir bob avvalgisiga bog'liq."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101.rst:25
msgid ""
"Before going further, make sure you have prepared your development "
"environment with the :doc:`setup guide <setup_guide>`."
msgstr ""
"Davom etishdan oldin, :doc:`sozlash qo'llanmasi <setup_guide>` yordamida "
"ishlab chiqish muhitingizni tayyorlaganingizga ishonch hosil qiling."

