#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:5
msgid "Chapter 1: Architecture Overview"
msgstr "1-bob: Arxitekturaga umumiy ko'rinish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:8
msgid "Multitier application"
msgstr "Ko'p qatlamli ilova"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:10
msgid ""
"Odoo follows a `multitier architecture`_, meaning that the presentation, "
"the business logic and the data storage are separated. More specifically,"
" it uses a three-tier architecture (image from Wikipedia):"
msgstr ""
"Odoo `ko'p qatlamli arxitektura`_ ga amal qiladi, ya'ni taqdimot, "
"biznes mantiqi va ma'lumotlarni saqlash ajratilgan. Aniqroq aytganda, "
"u uch qatlamli arxitekturadan foydalanadi (rasm Vikipediyadan):"

msgid "Three-tier architecture"
msgstr "Uch qatlamli arxitektura"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:18
msgid ""
"The presentation tier is a combination of HTML5, JavaScript and CSS. The "
"logic tier is exclusively written in Python, while the data tier only "
"supports PostgreSQL as an RDBMS."
msgstr ""
"Taqdimot qatlami HTML5, JavaScript va CSS kombinatsiyasidan iborat. "
"Mantiq qatlami faqat Python da yozilgan, ma'lumotlar qatlami esa "
"faqat PostgreSQL ni RDBMS sifatida qo'llab-quvvatlaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:21
msgid ""
"Depending on the scope of your module, Odoo development can be done in "
"any of these tiers. Therefore, before going any further, it may be a good"
" idea to refresh your memory if you don't have an intermediate level in "
"these topics."
msgstr ""
"Modulingiz doirasiga qarab, Odoo ishlab chiqish ushbu qatlamlardan "
"istalganida amalga oshirilishi mumkin. Shuning uchun, ushbu mavzularda "
"o'rta darajada bilimga ega bo'lmasangiz, davom etishdan oldin "
"bilimlaringizni yangilash yaxshi fikr bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:25
msgid ""
"In order to go through this tutorial, you will need a very basic "
"knowledge of HTML and an intermediate level of Python. Advanced topics "
"will require more knowledge in the other subjects. There are plenty of "
"tutorials freely accessible, so we cannot recommend one over another "
"since it depends on your background."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu darslikni o'tish uchun HTML bo'yicha juda asosiy bilim va Python "
"bo'yicha o'rta daraja bilim kerak bo'ladi. Kengaytirilgan mavzular "
"boshqa fanlarda ko'proq bilimni talab qiladi. Erkin kirish imkoniyatiga "
"ega bo'lgan ko'plab darsliklar mavjud, shuning uchun birini boshqasiga "
"tavsiya qila olmaymiz, chunki bu sizning bilim bazangizga bog'liq."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:30
msgid "For reference this is the official `Python tutorial`_."
msgstr "Ma'lumot uchun bu rasmiy `Python darsligi`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:33
msgid ""
"Since version 15.0, Odoo is actively transitioning to using its own in-"
"house developed `OWL framework <https://odoo.github.io/owl/>`_ as part of"
" its presentation tier. The legacy JavaScript framework is still "
"supported but will be deprecated over time. This will be discussed "
"further in advanced topics."
msgstr ""
"15.0 versiyasidan beri, Odoo taqdimot qatlamining bir qismi sifatida "
"o'zining ichki ishlab chiqilgan `OWL framework <https://odoo.github.io/owl/>`_ "
"ga o'tishni faol amalga oshirmoqda. Eski JavaScript framework hali ham "
"qo'llab-quvvatlanadi, lekin vaqt o'tishi bilan eskirib qoladi. Bu "
"kengaytirilgan mavzularda batafsilroq muhokama qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:39
msgid "Odoo modules"
msgstr "Odoo modullari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:41
msgid ""
"Both server and client extensions are packaged as *modules* which are "
"optionally loaded in a *database*. A module is a collection of functions "
"and data that target a single purpose."
msgstr ""
"Hem server, ham mijoz kengaytmalari ixtiyoriy ravishda *ma'lumotlar "
"bazasiga* yuklanadigan *modullar* sifatida paketlanadi. Modul - bu "
"bitta maqsadga yo'naltirilgan funksiyalar va ma'lumotlar to'plami."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:45
msgid ""
"Odoo modules can either add brand new business logic to an Odoo system or"
" alter and extend existing business logic. One module can be created to "
"add your country's accounting rules to Odoo's generic accounting support,"
" while a different module can add support for real-time visualisation of "
"a bus fleet."
msgstr ""
"Odoo modullari Odoo tizimiga butunlay yangi biznes mantiqini qo'shishi "
"yoki mavjud biznes mantiqini o'zgartirishi va kengaytirishi mumkin. "
"Bir modul Odoo ning umumiy buxgalteriya qo'llab-quvvatlashiga o'z "
"mamlakatIngiz buxgalteriya qoidalarini qo'shish uchun yaratilishi mumkin, "
"boshqa modul esa avtobus parkini real vaqtda vizualizatsiya qilish "
"uchun qo'llab-quvvatlash qo'shishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:50
msgid "Everything in Odoo starts and ends with modules."
msgstr "Odoo dagi hamma narsa modullar bilan boshlanadi va tugaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:52
msgid ""
"Terminology: developers group their business features in Odoo *modules*. "
"The main user-facing modules are flagged and exposed as *Apps*, but a "
"majority of the modules aren't Apps. *Modules* may also be referred to as"
" *addons* and the directories where the Odoo server finds them form the "
"``addons_path``."
msgstr ""
"Terminologiya: ishlab chiquvchilar o'z biznes xususiyatlarini Odoo "
"*modullari* da guruhlaydi. Asosiy foydalanuvchiga yo'naltirilgan modullar "
"*Ilovalar* sifatida belgilanadi va ko'rsatiladi, lekin modullarning "
"ko'pchiligi Ilovalar emas. *Modullar* shuningdek *addons* deb ham "
"atalishi mumkin va Odoo serveri ularni topadigan kataloglar "
"``addons_path`` ni tashkil etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:60
msgid "An Odoo module **can** contain a number of elements:"
msgstr "Odoo moduli bir qancha elementlarni **o'z ichiga olishi** mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:65
msgid ":ref:`Business objects <reference/orm>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Biznes ob'ektlari <reference/orm>`"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:63
msgid ""
"A business object (e.g. an invoice) is declared as a Python class. The "
"fields defined in these classes are automatically mapped to database "
"columns thanks to the :abbr:`ORM (Object-Relational Mapping)` layer."
msgstr ""
"Biznes ob'ekti (masalan, hisob-faktura) Python klassi sifatida e'lon "
"qilinadi. Ushbu klasslar da aniqlangan maydonlar :abbr:`ORM "
"(Object-Relational Mapping)` qatlami tufayli ma'lumotlar bazasi "
"ustunlariga avtomatik ravishda ulanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:68
msgid ":doc:`Object views <../../reference/user_interface/view_architectures>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Ob'ekt ko'rinishlari <../../reference/user_interface/view_architectures>`"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:68
msgid "Define UI display"
msgstr "UI ko'rinishini aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:71
msgid "XML or CSV files declaring the model data:"
msgstr "Model ma'lumotlarini e'lon qiluvchi XML yoki CSV fayllar:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:73
msgid ""
":doc:`views <../../reference/user_interface/view_architectures>` or "
":ref:`reports <reference/reports>`,"
msgstr ""
":doc:`ko'rinishlar <../../reference/user_interface/view_architectures>` yoki "
":ref:`hisobotlar <reference/reports>`,"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:83
msgid "Images, CSS or JavaScript files used by the web interface or website"
msgstr "Veb-interfeys yoki veb-sayt tomonidan ishlatiladigan rasmlar, CSS yoki JavaScript fayllar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:85
msgid ""
"None of these elements are mandatory. Some modules may only add data "
"files (e.g. country-specific accounting configuration), while others may "
"only add business objects. During this training, we will create business "
"objects, object views and data files."
msgstr ""
"Bu elementlarning hech biri majburiy emas. Ba'zi modullar faqat ma'lumot "
"fayllarini qo'shishi mumkin (masalan, mamlakatga xos buxgalteriya "
"konfiguratsiyasi), boshqalari esa faqat biznes ob'ektlarini qo'shishi "
"mumkin. Ushbu o'quv mashg'ulotida biz biznes ob'ektlari, ob'ekt "
"ko'rinishlari va ma'lumot fayllarini yaratamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:98
msgid ""
"When an Odoo module includes business objects (i.e. Python files), they "
"are organized as a `Python package "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/tutorial/modules.html#packages>`_ with a "
"``__init__.py`` file. This file contains import instructions for various "
"Python files in the module."
msgstr ""
"Odoo moduli biznes ob'ektlarni (ya'ni Python fayllarni) o'z ichiga "
"olganda, ular ``__init__.py`` fayli bilan `Python paketi "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/tutorial/modules.html#packages>`_ sifatida "
"tashkil etiladi. Ushbu fayl modulning turli Python fayllarini import "
"qilish ko'rsatmalarini o'z ichiga oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:103
msgid "Here is a simplified module directory:"
msgstr "Mana soddalashtirilgan modul katalogi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:117
msgid "Odoo Editions"
msgstr "Odoo nashrlari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/01_architecture.rst:119
msgid ""
"Odoo is available in `two versions`_: Odoo Enterprise (licensed & shared "
"sources) and Odoo Community (open-source). In addition to services such "
"as support or upgrades, the Enterprise version provides extra "
"functionalities to Odoo. From a technical point-of-view, these "
"functionalities are simply new modules installed on top of the modules "
"provided by the Community version."
msgstr ""
"Odoo `ikki versiyada`_ mavjud: Odoo Enterprise (litsenziyalangan va "
"umumiy manbalar) va Odoo Community (ochiq manbali). Qo'llab-quvvatlash "
"yoki yangilanishlar kabi xizmatlardan tashqari, Enterprise versiyasi "
