#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:18
msgid ""
"In :doc:`04_securityintro`, we added data through a CSV file. The CSV "
"format is convenient when the data to load has a simple format. When the "
"format is more complex (e.g. load the structure of a view or an email "
"template), we use the XML format. For example, this `help field "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/09c59012bf80d2ccbafe21c39e604d6cfda72924/addons/crm/views/crm_lost_reason_views.xml#L61-L69>`__"
" contains HTML tags. While it would be possible to load such data through"
" a CSV file, it is more convenient to use an XML file."
msgstr ""
":doc:`04_securityintro` da biz CSV fayli orqali ma'lumot qo'shdik. "
"CSV formati yuklanadigan ma'lumotlar oddiy formatga ega bo'lganda qulay. "
"Format murakkabrok bo'lganda (masalan, ko'rinish yoki email shabloni "
"tuzilishini yuklash), biz XML formatidan foydalanamiz. Masalan, ushbu "
"`yordam maydoni "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/09c59012bf80d2ccbafe21c39e604d6cfda72924/addons/crm/views/crm_lost_reason_views.xml#L61-L69>`__ "
"HTML teglarini o'z ichiga oladi. Bunday ma'lumotlarni CSV fayli orqali "
"yuklash mumkin bo'lsa ham, XML faylidan foydalanish qulay."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:26
msgid ""
"The XML files must be added to the same folders as the CSV files and "
"defined similarly in the ``__manifest__.py``. The content of the data "
"files is also sequentially loaded when a module is installed or updated, "
"therefore all remarks made for CSV files hold true for XML files. When "
"the data is linked to views, we add them to the ``views`` folder."
msgstr ""
"XML fayllar CSV fayllar kabi papkalarga qo'shilishi va ``__manifest__.py`` "
"da o'xshash tarzda aniqlanishi kerak. Ma'lumot fayllarining tarkibi ham "
"modul o'rnatilganda yoki yangilanganida ketma-ket yuklanadi, shuning uchun "
"CSV fayllari uchun aytilgan barcha mulohazalar XML fayllar uchun ham "
"to'g'ri. Ma'lumotlar ko'rinishlar bilan bog'langan bo'lsa, biz ularni "
"``views`` papkasiga qo'shamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:31
msgid ""
"In this chapter, we will load our first action and menus through an XML "
"file. Actions and menus are standard records in the database."
