"Ushbu bobda biz XML fayli orqali birinchi amal va menyularimizni "
"yuklaymiz. Amallar va menyular ma'lumotlar bazasidagi standart yozuvlardir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:36
msgid ""
"When performance is important, the CSV format is preferred over the XML "
"format. This is the case in Odoo where loading a CSV file is faster than "
"loading an XML file."
msgstr ""
"Ishlash tezligi muhim bo'lganda, XML formati o'rniga CSV format afzal "
"ko'riladi. Odoo da CSV faylini yuklash XML faylini yuklashdan tezroq."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/05_firstui.rst:39
