"**Manba**: ushbu mavzuga oid hujjatlar :ref:`reference/orm/domains` da mavjud."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:203
msgid ""
"In Odoo, a domain encodes conditions on records: a domain is a list of "
"criteria used to select a subset of a model's records. Each criterion is "
"a triplet with a *field name*, an *operator* and a *value*. A record "
"satisfies a criterion if the specified field meets the condition of the "
"operator applied to the value."
msgstr ""
"Odoo da domen yozuvlardagi shartlarni kodlaydi: domen - bu model "
"yozuvlarining bir qismini tanlash uchun ishlatiladigan mezonlar ro'yxati. "
"Har bir mezon *maydon nomi*, *operator* va *qiymat* dan iborat uchlikdir. "
"Belgilangan maydon qiymatga qo'llangan operatorning shartini qondirsa, "
"yozuv mezonga mos keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:208
msgid ""
"For instance, when used on the *Product* model the following domain "
"selects all *services* with a unit price greater than *1000*::"
msgstr ""
"Masalan, *Mahsulot* modelida ishlatilganda quyidagi domen birlik narxi "
"*1000* dan katta barcha *xizmatlar* ni tanlaydi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:213
msgid ""
"By default criteria are combined with an implicit AND, meaning *every* "
"criterion needs to be satisfied for a record to match a domain. The "
"logical operators ``&`` (AND), ``|`` (OR) and ``!`` (NOT) can be used to "
"explicitly combine criteria. They are used in prefix position (the "
"operator is inserted before its arguments rather than between). For "
"instance, to select products 'which are services *OR* have a unit price "
"which is *NOT* between 1000 and 2000'::"
msgstr ""
"Standart bo'yicha mezonlar yashirin AND bilan birlashtiriladi, ya'ni "
"yozuv domenge mos kelishi uchun *har bir* mezon qondirilishi kerak. "
"Mezonlarni aniq birlashtirish uchun ``&`` (AND), ``|`` (OR) va ``!`` "
"(NOT) mantiqiy operatorlaridan foydalanish mumkin. Ular prefiks "
"pozitsiyada ishlatiladi (operator argumentlari orasida emas, balki "
"oldiga qo'yiladi). Masalan, 'xizmat bo'lgan *YOKI* birlik narxi 1000 "
"va 2000 o'rtasida *EMAS* bo'lgan' mahsulotlarni tanlash uchun::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/06_basicviews.rst:226
msgid ""
"XML does not allow ``<`` and ``&`` to be used inside XML elements. To "
"avoid parsing errors, entity references should be used: ``&lt;`` for "
"``<`` and ``&amp;`` for ``&``. Other entity references (``&gt;``, "
"``&apos;`` & ``&quot;``) are optional."
msgstr ""
"XML XML elementlari ichida ``<`` va ``&`` dan foydalanishga ruxsat bermaydi. "
"Tahlil xatolarini oldini olish uchun ob'ekt havolalaridan foydalanish kerak: "
"``<`` uchun ``&lt;`` va ``&`` uchun ``&amp;``. Boshqa ob'ekt havolalari "
"(``&gt;``, ``&apos;`` va ``&quot;``) ixtiyoriy."

