#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:131
msgid ""
"You might have noticed that computed fields are read-only by default. "
"This is expected since the user is not supposed to set a value."
msgstr ""
"Hisoblangan maydonlar standart bo'yicha faqat o'qish uchun ekanligini "
"sezgan bo'lishingiz mumkin. Bu kutilgan, chunki foydalanuvchi qiymat "
"o'rnatmasligi kerak."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:134
msgid ""
"In some cases, it might be useful to still be able to set a value "
"directly. In our real estate example, we can define a validity duration "
"for an offer and set a validity date. We would like to be able to set "
"either the duration or the date with one impacting the other."
msgstr ""
"Ba'zi hollarda hali ham to'g'ridan-to'g'ri qiymat o'rnatish imkoniyatiga "
"ega bo'lish foydali bo'lishi mumkin. Ko'chmas mulk misolimizda biz "
"taklif uchun amal qilish muddatini va yaroqlilik sanasini o'rnatishimiz "
"mumkin. Biz muddatni yoki sanani o'rnatish imkoniyatiga ega bo'lishni "
"xohlaymiz, biri ikkinchisiga ta'sir qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:138
msgid "To support this Odoo provides the ability to use an ``inverse`` function::"
msgstr ""
"Buni qo'llab-quvvatlash uchun Odoo ``inverse`` funksiyasidan foydalanish "
"imkoniyatini taqdim etadi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:157
msgid ""
"An example can be found `here "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/2ccf0bd0dcb2e232ee894f07f24fdc26c51835f7/addons/crm/models/crm_lead.py#L308-L317>`__."
msgstr ""
"Misol `bu yerda "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/2ccf0bd0dcb2e232ee894f07f24fdc26c51835f7/addons/crm/models/crm_lead.py#L308-L317>`__ "
"topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:160
msgid ""
"A compute method sets the field while an inverse method sets the field's "
"dependencies."
msgstr ""
"Hisoblash metodi maydonni o'rnatadi, teskari metod esa maydon "
"bog'liqliklarini o'rnatadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:163
msgid ""
"Note that the ``inverse`` method is called when saving the record, while "
"the ``compute`` method is called at each change of its dependencies."
msgstr ""
"``inverse`` metodi yozuv saqlanganida chaqirilishini, ``compute`` metodi "
"esa bog'liqliklarining har bir o'zgarishida chaqirilishini unutmang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:166
msgid "Compute a validity date for offers."
msgstr "Takliflar uchun yaroqlilik sanasini hisoblang."

