msgstr "``estate.property.offer`` modeliga quyidagi maydonlarni qo'shing:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:173
msgid "validity"
msgstr "yaroqlilik"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:173
msgid "7"
msgstr "7"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:174
msgid "date_deadline"
msgstr "date_deadline"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:177
msgid ""
"Where ``date_deadline`` is a computed field which is defined as the sum "
"of two fields from the offer: the ``create_date`` and the ``validity``. "
"Define an appropriate inverse function so that the user can set either "
"the date or the validity."
msgstr ""
"``date_deadline`` - bu taklifning ikki maydonining yig'indisi sifatida "
"aniqlangan hisoblangan maydon: ``create_date`` va ``validity``. "
"Foydalanuvchi sanani yoki yaroqlilikni o'rnatish imkoniga ega bo'lishi "
"uchun tegishli teskari funksiyani aniqlang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:181
msgid ""
"Tip: the ``create_date`` is only filled in when the record is created, "
"therefore you will need a fallback to prevent crashing at time of "
"creation."
msgstr ""
"Maslahat: ``create_date`` faqat yozuv yaratilganda to'ldiriladi, "
"shuning uchun yaratish vaqtida ishdan chiqishni oldini olish uchun "
"zaxira variant kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:184
msgid ""
"Add the fields in the form view and the list view as depicted on the "
