#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:187
#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:273
msgid "Additional Information"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha ma'lumot"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:189
msgid ""
"Computed fields are **not stored** in the database by default. Therefore "
"it is **not possible** to search on a computed field unless a ``search`` "
"method is defined. This topic is beyond the scope of this training, so we"
" won't cover it. An example can be found `here "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f011c9aacf3a3010c436d4e4f408cd9ae265de1b/addons/event/models/event_event.py#L188>`__."
msgstr ""
"Hisoblangan maydonlar standart bo'yicha ma'lumotlar bazasida **saqlanmaydi**. "
"Shuning uchun ``search`` metodi aniqlanmagan bo'lsa, hisoblangan maydonda "
"qidirish **mumkin emas**. Bu mavzu ushbu o'quv kursining doirasidan "
"tashqarida, shuning uchun biz uni qamrab olmaymiz. Misol `bu yerda "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f011c9aacf3a3010c436d4e4f408cd9ae265de1b/addons/event/models/event_event.py#L188>`__ "
"topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:194
msgid ""
"Another solution is to store the field with the ``store=True`` attribute."
" While this is usually convenient, pay attention to the potential "
"computation load added to your model. Lets re-use our example::"
msgstr ""
"Boshqa yechim - ``store=True`` atributi bilan maydonni saqlash. "
"Bu odatda qulay bo'lsa-da, modelingizga qo'shilgan potentsial hisoblash "
"yukiga e'tibor bering. Keling, misolimizni qayta ishlataylik::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:206
msgid ""
"Every time the partner ``name`` is changed, the ``description`` is "
"automatically recomputed for **all the records** referring to it! This "
"can quickly become prohibitive to recompute when millions of records need"
" recomputation."
msgstr ""
"Hamkor ``name`` i har safar o'zgartirilganda, ``description`` unga "
"murojaat qiluvchi **barcha yozuvlar** uchun avtomatik ravishda qayta "
"hisoblanadi! Millionlab yozuvlar qayta hisoblashni talab qilganda, bu "
"tezda taqiqlovchi tarzda katta bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:210
msgid ""
"It is also worth noting that a computed field can depend on another "
"computed field. The ORM is smart enough to correctly recompute all the "
"dependencies in the right order... but sometimes at the cost of degraded "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, hisoblangan maydon boshqa hisoblangan maydoniga bog'liq "
"bo'lishi mumkinligini ta'kidlash joiz. ORM barcha bog'liqliklarni "
"to'g'ri tartibda qayta hisoblashga yetarlicha aqlli... lekin ba'zida "
"ishlash samaradorligining pasayishi hisobiga."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:214
msgid ""
"In general performance must always be kept in mind when defining computed"
" fields. The more complex is your field to compute (e.g. with a lot of "
"dependencies or when a computed field depends on other computed fields), "
"the more time it will take to compute. Always take some time to evaluate "
"the cost of a computed field beforehand. Most of the time it is only when"
" your code reaches a production server that you realize it slows down a "
"whole process. Not cool :-("
msgstr ""
"Umuman olganda, hisoblangan maydonlarni aniqlashda ishlash samaradorligi "
"har doim yodda tutilishi kerak. Maydonni hisoblash qanchalik murakkab "
"bo'lsa (masalan, ko'p bog'liqliklar bilan yoki hisoblangan maydon boshqa "
"hisoblangan maydonlarga bog'liq bo'lsa), hisoblash shuncha ko'p vaqt "
"oladi. Hisoblangan maydonning narxini oldindan baholashga har doim biroz "
"vaqt ajrating. Ko'pincha faqat kod ishlab chiqarish serveriga yetgandagina "
"u butun jarayonni sekinlashtirayotganini anglaysiz. Yaxshi emas :-("

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/08_compute_onchange.rst:221
