#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:80
msgid ""
"By assigning ``type=\"object\"`` to our button, the Odoo framework will "
"execute a Python method with ``name=\"action_do_something\"`` on the "
"given model."
msgstr ""
"Tugmamizga ``type=\"object\"`` belgilash orqali Odoo freymvorki berilgan "
"model ustida ``name=\"action_do_something\"`` bilan Python metodini bajaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:83
msgid ""
"The first important detail to note is that our method name isn't prefixed"
" with an underscore (``_``). This makes our method a **public** method, "
"which can be called directly from the Odoo interface (through an RPC "
"call). Until now, all methods we created (compute, onchange) were called "
"internally, so we used **private** methods prefixed by an underscore. You"
" should always define your methods as private unless they need to be "
"called from the user interface."
msgstr ""
"E'tibor berilishi kerak bo'lgan birinchi muhim detal - metod nomimiz "
"pastki chiziq (``_``) bilan boshlanmaydi. Bu bizning metodimizni **ochiq** "
"metod qiladi, u Odoo interfeysidan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri (RPC chaqiruv orqali) "
"chaqirilishi mumkin. Hozirgacha yaratgan barcha metodlarimiz (compute, onchange) "
"ichki ravishda chaqirildi, shuning uchun biz pastki chiziq bilan boshlangan "
"**xususiy** metodlardan foydalandik. Agar foydalanuvchi interfeysidan "
"chaqirilishi shart bo'lmasa, metodlaringizni har doim xususiy deb belgilang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:89
msgid ""
"Also note that we loop on ``self``. Always assume that a method can be "
"called on multiple records; it's better for reusability."
msgstr ""
"Shuningdek, ``self`` ustida tsikl qilayotganimizga e'tibor bering. Metod "
"bir nechta yozuvda chaqirilishi mumkin deb har doim faraz qiling; bu "
"qayta foydalanish uchun yaxshiroqdir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/09_actions.rst:92
msgid ""
"Finally, a public method should always return something so that it can be"
" called through XML-RPC. When in doubt, just ``return True``."
msgstr ""
"Nihoyat, ochiq metod XML-RPC orqali chaqirilishi uchun har doim biror narsa "
"qaytarishi kerak. Shubhalanganingizda faqat ``return True`` deb yozing."

