#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:136
msgid "List Order"
msgstr "Ro'yxat tartibi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:138
msgid ""
"**Reference**: the documentation related to this section can be found in "
":ref:`reference/orm/models`."
msgstr ""
"**Ma'lumotnoma**: bu bo'lim bilan bog'liq hujjatlarni "
":ref:`reference/orm/models` da topish mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:143
msgid ""
"**Goal**: at the end of this section, all lists should display by default"
" in a deterministic order. Property types can be ordered manually."
msgstr ""
"**Maqsad**: bu bo'lim oxirida barcha ro'yxatlar standart bo'yicha "
"deterministik tartibda ko'rsatilishi kerak. Mulk turlarini qo'lda tartiblash mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:146
msgid ""
"During the previous exercises, we created several list views. However, at"
" no point did we specify which order the records had to be listed in by "
"default. This is a very important thing for many business cases. For "
"example, in our real estate module we would want to display the highest "
"offers on top of the list."
msgstr ""
"Oldingi mashqlarda biz bir nechta ro'yxat ko'rinishlari yaratdik. Biroq "
"hech qachon yozuvlar standart bo'yicha qaysi tartibda ro'yxatlanishi kerakligini "
"ko'rsatmadik. Bu ko'plab biznes hollari uchun juda muhim narsadir. Masalan, "
"ko'chmas mulk modulimizda ro'yxatning yuqori qismida eng yuqori takliflarni "
"ko'rsatishni xohlaymiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:154
msgid ""
"Odoo provides several ways to set a default order. The most common way is"
" to define the ``_order`` attribute directly in the model. This way, the "
"retrieved records will follow a deterministic order which will be "
"consistent in all views including when records are searched "
"programmatically. By default there is no order specified, therefore the "
"records will be retrieved in a non-deterministic order depending on "
"PostgreSQL."
msgstr ""
"Odoo standart tartibni o'rnatishning bir necha usullarini taqdim etadi. "
"Eng keng tarqalgan usul - bu modelda to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ``_order`` atributini "
"aniqlash. Shunday qilib, olingan yozuvlar barcha ko'rinishlarda, shu jumladan "
"yozuvlar dasturiy ravishda qidirilganda ham izchil bo'lgan deterministik "
"tartibga amal qiladi. Standart bo'yicha tartib ko'rsatilmagan, shuning uchun "
"yozuvlar PostgreSQL ga bog'liq bo'lmagan deterministik tartibda olinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:160
msgid ""
"The ``_order`` attribute takes a string containing a list of fields which"
" will be used for sorting. It will be converted to an order_by_ clause in"
" SQL. For example:"
msgstr ""
"``_order`` atributi saralash uchun ishlatiliadigan maydonlar ro'yxatini "
"o'z ichiga olgan satrni qabul qiladi. U SQL da order_by_ bandiga aylantiriladi. Masalan:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/11_sprinkles.rst:174
msgid ""
"Our records are ordered by descending ``id``, meaning the highest comes "
"first."
msgstr "Yozuvlarimiz ``id`` bo'yicha kamayish tartibida, ya'ni eng kattasi birinchi."

