" top of root views. These extension can both add and remove content from "
"their parent view."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud ko'rinishlarni joyida o'zgartirish o'rniga (ularni qayta yozish "
"orqali), Odoo bolalar 'kengaytma' ko'rinishlar ildiz ko'rinishlar ustiga "
"qo'llaniladigan ko'rinish merosini taqdim etadi. Bu kengaytmalar ota-ona "
"ko'rinishidan ham kontent qo'shishi, ham olib tashlashi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:182
msgid ""
"An extension view references its parent using the ``inherit_id`` field. "
"Instead of a single view, its ``arch`` field contains a number of "
"``xpath`` elements that select and alter the content of their parent "
"view:"
msgstr ""
"Kengaytma ko'rinish ``inherit_id`` maydoni yordamida ota-ona ko'rinishiga "
"murojaat qiladi. Bitta ko'rinish o'rniga uning ``arch`` maydoni ota-ona "
"ko'rinishining kontentini tanlaydigan va o'zgartiruvchi bir qator ``xpath`` "
"elementlarini o'z ichiga oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:208
msgid "appends ``xpath``'s body to the end of the matched element"
msgstr "``xpath`` tanasini mos kelgan element oxiriga qo'shadi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:217
msgid ""
"alters the attributes of the matched element using the special "
"``attribute`` elements in the ``xpath``'s body"
msgstr ""
"``xpath`` tanasidagi maxsus ``attribute`` elementlari yordamida mos "
"kelgan elementning atributlarini o'zgartiradi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:220
msgid ""
"When matching a single element, the ``position`` attribute can be set "
"directly on the element to be found. Both inheritances below have the "
"same result."
msgstr ""
"Bitta elementga mos kelganda, ``position`` atributi topilishi kerak bo'lgan "
"elementga to'g'ridan-to'g'ri o'rnatilishi mumkin. Quyidagi ikkala meros "
"ham bir xil natijaga ega."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:233
