"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/691d1f087040f1ec7066e485d19ce3662dfc6501/addons/gamification/views/res_users_views.xml#L5-L14>`__ topilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:243
