#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/12_inheritance.rst:246
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`next chapter <13_other_module>`, we will learn how to "
"interact with other modules."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Keyingi bobda <13_other_module>`, boshqa modullar bilan qanday "
"o'zaro ta'sir qilishni o'rganamiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:3
msgid "Chapter 13: Interact With Other Modules"
msgstr "13-bob: Boshqa modullar bilan o'zaro ta'sir"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`previous chapter <12_inheritance>`, we used inheritance to "
"modify the behavior of a module. In our real estate scenario, we would "
"like to go a step further and be able to generate invoices for our "
"customers. Odoo provides an Invoicing module, so it would be neat to "
"create an invoice directly from our real estate module, i.e. once a "
"property is set to 'Sold', an invoice is created in the Invoicing "
"application."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Oldingi bobda <12_inheritance>`, modul xatti-harakatini o'zgartirish "
"uchun merosdan foydalandik. Ko'chmas mulk stsenariyimizda bir qadam "
"oldinga qo'yib, mijozlarimiz uchun hisob-fakturalar yarata olishni "
"xohlaymiz. Odoo Hisob-faktura modulini taqdim etadi, shuning uchun "
"to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ko'chmas mulk modulimizdan hisob-faktura yaratish, "
"ya'ni mulk 'Sotilgan' ga o'rnatilganda Hisob-faktura ilovasida "
"hisob-faktura yaratish juda yaxshi bo'lar edi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:12
msgid "Concrete Example: Account Move"
msgstr "Aniq misol: Hisob harakati"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:18
msgid "A new module ``estate_account`` should be created"
msgstr "Yangi ``estate_account`` moduli yaratilishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:19
msgid "When a property is sold, an invoice should be issued for the buyer"
msgstr "Mulk sotilganda xaridor uchun hisob-faktura berilishi kerak"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst
msgid "Invoice creation"
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:25
msgid ""
"Any time we interact with another module, we need to keep in mind the "
"modularity. If we intend to sell our application to real estate agencies,"
" some may want the invoicing feature but others may not want it."
msgstr ""
"Boshqa modul bilan o'zaro ta'sir qilgan har safar modullilikni yodda "
"tutishimiz kerak. Agar ilovamizni ko'chmas mulk agentliklariga sotishni "
"mo'ljallasak, ba'zilari hisob-faktura funksiyasini xohlashi mumkin, "
"boshqalari esa xohlamasligi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:30
msgid "Link Module"
msgstr "Havola moduli"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:32
msgid ""
"The common approach for such use cases is to create a 'link' module. In "
"our case, the module would depend on ``estate`` and ``account`` and would"
" include the invoice creation logic of the estate property. This way the "
"real estate and the accounting modules can be installed independently. "
"When both are installed, the link module provides the new feature."
msgstr ""
"Bunday foydalanish holatlari uchun umumiy yondashuv 'havola' modulini "
"yaratishdir. Bizning holatimizda modul ``estate`` va ``account`` ga "
"bog'liq bo'ladi va ko'chmas mulkning hisob-faktura yaratish mantiqini "
"o'z ichiga oladi. Bu yo'l bilan ko'chmas mulk va buxgalteriya modullari "
"mustaqil ravishda o'rnatilishi mumkin. Ikkalasi ham o'rnatilganida, "
"havola moduli yangi funksiyani taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:37
msgid "Create a link module."
msgstr "Havola modulini yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:39
msgid ""
"Create the ``estate_account`` module, which depends on the ``estate`` and"
" ``account`` modules. For now, it will be an empty shell."
msgstr ""
"``estate`` va ``account`` modullariga bog'liq bo'lgan ``estate_account`` "
"modulini yarating. Hozircha u bo'sh qobiq bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:42
msgid ""
"Tip: you already did this at the :doc:`beginning of the tutorial "
"<02_newapp>`. The process is very similar."
msgstr ""
"Maslahat: siz buni allaqachon :doc:`darslikning boshida <02_newapp>` "
"qildingiz. Jarayon juda o'xshash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:46
msgid ""
"When the ``estate_account`` module appears in the list, go ahead and "
"install it! You'll notice that the Invoicing application is installed as "
"well. This is expected since your module depends on it. If you uninstall "
"the Invoicing application, your module will be uninstalled as well."
msgstr ""
"``estate_account`` moduli ro'yxatda paydo bo'lganda, uni o'rnating! "
"Hisob-faktura ilovasi ham o'rnatilganligini sezasiz. Bu kutilgan narsa, "
"chunki modulingiz unga bog'liq. Agar Hisob-faktura ilovasini o'rnatishni "
"bekor qilsangiz, modulingiz ham o'rnatishdan bekor qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:53
msgid "Invoice Creation"
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:55
msgid ""
"It's now time to generate the invoice. We want to add functionality to "
"the ``estate.property`` model, i.e. we want to add some extra logic for "
"when a property is sold. Does that sound familiar? If not, it's a good "
"idea to go back to the :doc:`previous chapter <12_inheritance>` since you"
" might have missed something ;-)"
msgstr ""
"Endi hisob-faktura yaratish vaqti keldi. ``estate.property`` modeliga "
"funksionallik qo'shmoqchimiz, ya'ni mulk sotilganda qo'shimcha mantiq "
"qo'shmoqchimiz. Bu tanishmi? Agar yo'q bo'lsa, :doc:`oldingi bobga "
"<12_inheritance>` qaytish yaxshi fikr, chunki biror narsani o'tkazib "
"yuborgan bo'lishingiz mumkin ;-)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:61
msgid ""
"As a first step, we need to extend the action called when pressing the "
":doc:`'Sold' button <09_actions>` on a property. To do so, we need to "
"create a :doc:`model inheritance <12_inheritance>` in the "
"`estate_account` module for the ``estate.property`` model. For now, the "
"overridden action will simply return the ``super`` call. Maybe an example"
" will make things clearer::"
msgstr ""
"Birinchi qadam sifatida mulk da :doc:`'Sotilgan' tugmasini <09_actions>` "
"bosganda chaqiriladigan amalni kengaytirishimiz kerak. Buning uchun "
"``estate.property`` modeli uchun `estate_account` modulida "
":doc:`model merosi <12_inheritance>` yaratishimiz kerak. Hozircha "
"bekor qilingan amal shunchaki ``super`` chaqiruvini qaytaradi. "
"Ehtimol misol narsalarni yanada aniq qiladi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:75
msgid ""
"A practical example can be found `here "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/event_sale/models/account_move.py#L7-L16>`__."
msgstr ""
"Amaliy misol `bu yerda "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/event_sale/models/account_move.py#L7-L16>`__ topilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:78
msgid "Add the first step of invoice creation."
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratishning birinchi bosqichini qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:80
msgid ""
"Create a ``estate_property.py`` file in the correct folder of the "
"``estate_account`` module."
msgstr "``estate_account`` modulining to'g'ri papkasida ``estate_property.py`` fayl yarating."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:81
msgid "``_inherit`` the ``estate.property`` model."
msgstr "``estate.property`` modelidan ``_inherit`` qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:82
msgid ""
"Override the ``action_sold`` method (you might have named it differently)"
" to return the ``super`` call."
msgstr ""
"``super`` chaqiruvini qaytarish uchun ``action_sold`` metodini "
"(boshqacha nomlagan bo'lishingiz mumkin) bekor qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:85
msgid ""
"Tip: to make sure it works, add a ``print`` or a debugger breakpoint in "
"the overridden method."
msgstr ""
"Maslahat: ishlayotganligiga ishonch hosil qilish uchun bekor qilingan "
"metodda ``print`` yoki disk raskadrovka to'xtash nuqtasini qo'shing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:87
msgid ""
"Is it working? If not, maybe check that all Python files are correctly "
"imported."
msgstr "Ishlayaptimi? Agar yo'q bo'lsa, barcha Python fayllar to'g'ri import qilinganligini tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:89
msgid ""
"If the override is working, we can move forward and create the invoice. "
"Unfortunately, there is no easy way to know how to create any given "
"object in Odoo. Most of the time, it is necessary to have a look at its "
"model to find the required fields and provide appropriate values."
msgstr ""
"Bekor qilish ishlayotgan bo'lsa, oldinga o'tib hisob-faktura yaratishimiz "
"mumkin. Afsuski, Odoo da berilgan ob'ektni qanday yaratishni bilishning "
"oson usuli yo'q. Ko'pincha zarur maydonlarni topish va tegishli qiymatlarni "
"taqdim etish uchun uning modeliga nazar tashlash zarur."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:93
msgid ""
"A good way to learn is to look at how other modules already do what you "
"want to do. For example, one of the basic flows of Sales is the creation "
"of an invoice from a sales order. This looks like a good starting point "
"since it does exactly what we want to do. Take some time to read and "
"understand the `_create_invoices "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/sale/models/sale.py#L610-L717>`__"
" method. When you are done crying because this simple task looks awfully "
"complex, we can move forward in the tutorial."
msgstr ""
"O'rganishning yaxshi usuli - boshqa modullar xohlagan narsangizni qanday "
"qilishini ko'rish. Masalan, Sotuv ning asosiy oqimlaridan biri sotish "
"buyurtmasidan hisob-faktura yaratishdir. Bu yaxshi boshlang'ich nuqta "
"bo'lib ko'rinadi, chunki u aynan biz xohlagan narsani qiladi. `_create_invoices "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/sale/models/sale.py#L610-L717>`__"
" metodini o'qish va tushunish uchun biroz vaqt ajrating. Bu oddiy vazifa "
"juda murakkab ko'ringani uchun yig'lab bo'lganingizdan so'ng, darslikda "
"oldinga o'tishimiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:100
msgid "To create an invoice, we need the following information:"
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratish uchun quyidagi ma'lumotlar kerak:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:102
msgid "a ``partner_id``: the customer"
msgstr "``partner_id``: mijoz"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:103
msgid ""
"a ``move_type``: it has several `possible values "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/account/models/account_move.py#L138-L147>`__"
msgstr ""
"``move_type``: uning bir nechta `mumkin bo'lgan qiymatlari "
"<https://github.com/odoo/odoo/blob/f1f48cdaab3dd7847e8546ad9887f24a9e2ed4c1/addons/account/models/account_move.py#L138-L147>`__ bor"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:104
msgid "a ``journal_id``: the accounting journal"
msgstr "``journal_id``: buxgalteriya jurnali"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:106
msgid "This is enough to create an empty invoice."
msgstr "Bu bo'sh hisob-faktura yaratish uchun yetarli."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/server_framework_101/13_other_module.rst:108
msgid "Add the second step of invoice creation."
msgstr "Hisob-faktura yaratishning ikkinchi bosqichini qo'shing."

