#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:137
msgid "Odoo JavaScript Module"
msgstr "Odoo JavaScript moduli"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:139
msgid ""
"Javascript doesn't have built-in modules. As a result variables defined "
"in different files are all mashed together and may conflict. This has "
"given rise to various module patterns used to build clean namespaces and "
"limit risks of naming conflicts."
msgstr ""
"Javascript-da o'rnatilgan modullar yo'q. Natijada turli fayllarda "
"aniqlangan o'zgaruvchilar hammasi birlashtiriladi va ziddiyat bo'lishi "
"mumkin. Bu nom ziddiyatlarining xavfini kamaytirish uchun toza nom fazolari "
"yaratish uchun ishlatiladigan turli modul naqshlarining paydo bo'lishiga "
"olib keldi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:144
msgid ""
"The Odoo framework uses one such pattern to define modules within web "
"addons, in order to both namespace code and correctly order its loading."
msgstr ""
"Odoo tizimi kodni nom fazosi va yuklanish tartibini to'g'ri belgilash uchun "
"veb qo'shimchalarda modullarni aniqlash uchun bunday naqshdan foydalanadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:147
msgid "``oepetstore/static/js/petstore.js`` contains a module declaration::"
msgstr "``oepetstore/static/js/petstore.js`` modul deklaratsiyasini o'z ichiga oladi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:153
msgid ""
"In Odoo web, modules are declared as functions set on the global ``odoo``"
" variable. The function's name must be the same as the addon (in this "
"case ``oepetstore``) so the framework can find it, and automatically "
"initialize it."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vebida modullar global ``odoo`` o'zgaruvchiga o'rnatilgan funksiyalar "
"sifatida e'lon qilinadi. Funksiyaning nomi qo'shimcha nomiga mos kelishi "
"kerak (bu holda ``oepetstore``) shunda tizim uni topib, avtomatik ravishda "
"ishga tushira oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:157
msgid ""
"When the web client loads your module it will call the root function and "
"provide two parameters:"
msgstr ""
"Veb mijoz modulingizni yuklaganida, u asosiy funksiyani chaqiradi va ikki "
"parametr beradi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:160
msgid ""
"the first parameter is the current instance of the Odoo web client, it "
"gives access to various capabilities defined by the Odoo (translations, "
"network services) as well as objects defined by the core or by other "
"modules."
msgstr ""
"birinchi parametr - bu Odoo veb mijozining joriy namunasi, u Odoo tomonidan "
"aniqlangan turli imkoniyatlarga (tarjimalar, tarmoq xizmatlari) hamda yadro "
"yoki boshqa modullar tomonidan aniqlangan ob'ektlarga kirish huquqini beradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:164
msgid ""
"the second parameter is your own local namespace automatically created by"
" the web client. Objects and variables which should be accessible from "
"outside your module (either because the Odoo web client needs to call "
"them or because others may want to customize them) should be set inside "
"that namespace."
msgstr ""
"ikkinchi parametr - bu veb mijoz tomonidan avtomatik yaratilgan o'zingizning "
"mahalliy nom fazosi. Modulingizdan tashqaridan kirish imkoniyati bo'lishi "
"kerak bo'lgan ob'ektlar va o'zgaruvchilar (chunki Odoo veb mijozi ularni "
"chaqirishi yoki boshqalar ularni sozlamoqchi bo'lishi mumkin) ushbu nom "
"fazosiga o'rnatilishi kerak."

