#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:282
msgid "Widgets Basics"
msgstr "Vidjetlar asoslari"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:284
msgid ""
"The Odoo web client bundles jQuery_ for easy DOM manipulation. It is "
"useful and provides a better API than standard `W3C DOM`_\\ [#dombugs]_, "
"but insufficient to structure complex applications leading to difficult "
"maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Odoo veb mijozi oson DOM manipulyatsiyasi uchun jQuery_ ni o'z ichiga oladi. "
"U foydali va standart `W3C DOM`_\\ [#dombugs]_ ga qaraganda yaxshiroq API "
"taqdim etadi, lekin murakkab ilovalarni tuzilmalash uchun etarli emas va "
"natijada qiyin texnik xizmat ko'rsatishga olib keladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:289
msgid ""
"Much like object-oriented desktop UI toolkits (e.g. Qt_, Cocoa_ or GTK_),"
" Odoo Web makes specific components responsible for sections of a page. "
"In Odoo web, the base for such components is the :class:`~odoo.Widget` "
"class, a component specialized in handling a page section and displaying "
"information for the user."
msgstr ""
"Ob'ektga yo'naltirilgan ish stoli UI vositalar to'plami (masalan, Qt_, "
"Cocoa_ yoki GTK_) kabi Odoo veb sahifa bo'limlarini mas'ul bo'lgan muayyan "
"komponentlardan foydalanadi. Odoo vebida bunday komponentlar uchun asos "
":class:`~odoo.Widget` sinfidir, bu sahifa bo'limini boshqarish va "
"foydalanuvchi uchun ma'lumot ko'rsatishga ixtisoslashgan komponent."

