"qo'shilganda avtomatik chaqiriladi. Uni ba'zi kontent ko'rsatish uchun "
"ishlatishimiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:339
msgid ""
"All widgets have a :attr:`~odoo.Widget.$el` which represents the section "
