"u yerga kiritilishi kerak. Standart bo'yicha, :attr:`~odoo.Widget.$el` "
"bo'sh ``<div>`` elementidir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:344
msgid ""
"A ``<div>`` element is usually invisible to the user if it has no content"
