#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:488
msgid "Destroying Widgets"
msgstr "Vidjetlarni o'chirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:490
msgid ""
"If you can display content to your users, you should also be able to "
"erase it. This is done via the :func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` method::"
msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchilaringizga kontent ko'rsata olsangiz, uni o'chirish ham "
"imkoniyatiga ega bo'lishingiz kerak. Bu :func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` metodi "
"orqali amalga oshiriladi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:495
msgid ""
"When a widget is destroyed it will first call "
":func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` on all its children. Then it erases itself "
"from the DOM. If you have set up permanent structures in "
":func:`~odoo.Widget.init` or :func:`~odoo.Widget.start` which must be "
"explicitly cleaned up (because the garbage collector will not handle "
"them), you can override :func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy`."
msgstr ""
"Vidjet o'chirilganda, avval barcha bolalarida :func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` "
"ni chaqiradi. Keyin o'zini DOM dan o'chiradi. Agar :func:`~odoo.Widget.init` "
"yoki :func:`~odoo.Widget.start` da aniq tozalanishi kerak bo'lgan doimiy "
"tuzilmalarni o'rnatgan bo'lsangiz (chunki axlat yig'uvchi ularni boshqarmaydi), "
":func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` ni bekor qilishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:503
msgid ""
"when overriding :func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy`, ``_super()`` *must always* "
"be called otherwise the widget and its children are not correctly cleaned"
" up leaving possible memory leaks and \"phantom events\", even if no "
"error is displayed"
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.Widget.destroy` ni bekor qilganda, hech qanday xato "
"ko'rsatilmasa ham ``_super()`` *har doim* chaqirilishi kerak, aks holda "
"vidjet va uning bolalari to'g'ri tozalanmaydi va potentsial xotira sizishi "
"hamda \"fantom hodisalar\"ga olib keladi"

