#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:520
msgid ""
"As many other environments, Odoo's solution is to use a `template "
"engine`_. Odoo's template engine is called :ref:`reference/qweb`."
msgstr ""
"Ko'plab boshqa muhitlar kabi, Odoo ning yechimi `shablon mexanizmi`_ dan "
"foydalanish. Odoo ning shablon mexanizmi :ref:`reference/qweb` deyiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:523
msgid ""
"QWeb is an XML-based templating language, similar to `Genshi "
"<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genshi_(templating_language)>`_, `Thymeleaf"
" <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymeleaf>`_ or `Facelets "
"<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Facelets>`_. It has the following "
"characteristics:"
msgstr ""
"QWeb - bu `Genshi <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genshi_(templating_language)>`_, "
"`Thymeleaf <http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thymeleaf>`_ yoki `Facelets "
"<http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Facelets>`_ ga o'xshash XML-asosli shablon "
"tili. Uning quyidagi xususiyatlari bor:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:529
msgid "It's implemented fully in JavaScript and rendered in the browser"
msgstr "U to'liq JavaScript-da amalga oshirilgan va brauzerda ko'rsatiladi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:530
msgid "Each template file (XML files) contains multiple templates"
msgstr "Har bir shablon fayli (XML fayllar) bir nechta shablonlarni o'z ichiga oladi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:531
msgid ""
"It has special support in Odoo Web's :class:`~odoo.Widget`, though it can"
" be used outside of Odoo's web client (and it's possible to use "
":class:`~odoo.Widget` without relying on QWeb)"
msgstr ""
"U Odoo vebining :class:`~odoo.Widget` da maxsus qo'llab-quvvatlashga ega, "
"garchi u Odoo veb mijozidan tashqarida ham ishlatilishi mumkin (va QWeb ga "
"tayanmasdan :class:`~odoo.Widget` dan foydalanish mumkin)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:536
msgid ""
"The rationale behind using QWeb instead of existing javascript template "
"engines is the extensibility of pre-existing (third-party) templates, "
"much like Odoo :doc:`views <../reference/user_interface/view_records>`."
msgstr ""
"Mavjud javascript shablon mexanizmlari o'rniga QWeb dan foydalanishning "
"asosi, oldindan mavjud (uchinchi tomon) shablonlarning kengaytirilishi, "
"Odoo :doc:`ko'rinishlari <../reference/user_interface/view_records>` kabi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:540
msgid ""
"Most javascript template engines are text-based which precludes easy "
"structural extensibility where an XML-based templating engine can be "
"generically altered using e.g. XPath or CSS and a tree-alteration DSL (or"
" even just XSLT). This flexibility and extensibility is a core "
"characteristic of Odoo, and losing it was considered unacceptable."
msgstr ""
"Ko'pgina javascript shablon mexanizmlari matn-asosli bo'lib, bu XML-asosli "
"shablon mexanizmi masalan XPath yoki CSS va daraxt-o'zgartirish DSL (yoki "
"hatto faqat XSLT) yordamida umumiy ravishda o'zgartirilishi mumkin bo'lgan "
"oson tuzilmaviy kengaytirish imkonini istisno qiladi. Bu moslashuvchanlik "
"va kengaytirilish Odoo ning asosiy xususiyati bo'lib, uni yo'qotish qabul "
"qilib bo'lmaydi deb hisoblangan."

