#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:656
msgid "Template Declaration"
msgstr "Shablon deklaratsiyasi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:658
msgid ""
"We've seen how to *render* QWeb templates, let's now see the syntax of "
"the templates themselves."
msgstr ""
"QWeb shablonlarini qanday *ko'rsatish* (render qilish)ni ko'rdik, endi "
"shablonlarning o'z sintaksisini ko'raylik."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:661
msgid ""
"A QWeb template is composed of regular XML mixed with QWeb *directives*. "
"A QWeb directive is declared with XML attributes starting with ``t-``."
msgstr ""
"QWeb shabloni QWeb *direktivlari* bilan aralashtirilgan oddiy XML dan iborat. "
"QWeb direktivi ``t-`` bilan boshlanadigan XML atributlari bilan e'lon qilinadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:664
msgid ""
"The most basic directive is ``t-name``, used to declare new templates in "
"a template file:"
msgstr ""
"Eng asosiy direktiva - bu ``t-name``, shablon faylida yangi shablonlarni "
"e'lon qilish uchun ishlatiladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:675
msgid ""
"``t-name`` takes the name of the template being defined, and declares "
"that it can be called using :func:`QWeb.render`. It can only be used at "
"the top-level of a template file."
msgstr ""
"``t-name`` aniqlanayotgan shablonning nomini oladi va u :func:`QWeb.render` "
"yordamida chaqirilishi mumkinligini e'lon qiladi. U faqat shablon faylining "
"yuqori darajasida ishlatilishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:680
msgid "Escaping"
msgstr "Ekranlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:682
msgid "The ``t-esc`` directive can be used to output text:"
msgstr "``t-esc`` direktivi matn chiqarish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:688
msgid ""
"It takes a Javascript expression which is evaluated, the result of the "
"expression is then HTML-escaped and inserted in the document. Since it's "
"an expression it's possible to provide just a variable name as above, or "
"a more complex expression like a computation:"
msgstr ""
"U baholangan Javascript ifodani oladi, ifoda natijasi HTML-ekranlangan va "
"hujjatga kiritiladi. Bu ifoda bo'lganligi sababli, yuqoridagi kabi faqat "
"o'zgaruvchi nomini yoki hisoblash kabi murakkabroq ifodani berish mumkin:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:697
msgid "or method calls:"
msgstr "yoki metod chaqiruvlari:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:704
msgid "Outputting HTML"
msgstr "HTML chiqarish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:706
msgid ""
"To inject HTML in the page being rendered, use ``t-raw``. Like ``t-esc`` "
"it takes an arbitrary Javascript expression as parameter, but it does not"
" perform an HTML-escape step."
msgstr ""
"Ko'rsatilayotgan sahifaga HTML qo'yish uchun ``t-raw`` dan foydalaning. "
"``t-esc`` kabi u ixtiyoriy Javascript ifodani parametr sifatida oladi, "
"lekin HTML-ekranlash qadamini amalga oshirmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:716
msgid ""
"``t-raw`` *must not* be used on any data which may contain non-escaped "
"user-provided content as this leads to `cross-site scripting`_ "
"vulnerabilities"
msgstr ""
"``t-raw`` ekranlanmagan foydalanuvchi tomonidan taqdim etilgan tarkibni "
"o'z ichiga olishi mumkin bo'lgan har qanday ma'lumotlar uchun *ishlatilmasligi "
"kerak* chunki bu `saytlar aro skript`_ zaifliklariga olib keladi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:723
msgid ""
"QWeb can have conditional blocks using ``t-if``. The directive takes an "
"arbitrary expression, if the expression is falsy (``false``, ``null``, "
"``0`` or an empty string) the whole block is suppressed, otherwise it is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"QWeb ``t-if`` yordamida shartli bloklar bo'lishi mumkin. Direktiva ixtiyoriy "
"ifodani oladi, agar ifoda yolg'on bo'lsa (``false``, ``null``, ``0`` yoki "
"bo'sh qator), butun blok bostiriladi, aks holda ko'rsatiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:740
msgid ""
"QWeb doesn't have an \"else\" structure, use a second ``t-if`` with the "
"original condition inverted. You may want to store the condition in a "
"local variable if it's a complex or expensive expression."
msgstr ""
"QWeb ning \"else\" tuzilmasi yo'q, asl shartning teskarisiga ega ikkinchi "
"``t-if`` dan foydalaning. Agar u murakkab yoki qimmatbaho ifoda bo'lsa, "
"shartni mahalliy o'zgaruvchida saqlamoqchi bo'lishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:745
msgid "Iteration"
msgstr "Takrorlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:747
msgid ""
"To iterate on a list, use ``t-foreach`` and ``t-as``. ``t-foreach`` takes"
" an expression returning a list to iterate on ``t-as`` takes a variable "
"name to bind to each item during iteration."
msgstr ""
"Ro'yxat ustida takrorlash uchun ``t-foreach`` va ``t-as`` dan foydalaning. "
"``t-foreach`` takrorlash uchun ro'yxat qaytaradigan ifodani oladi, ``t-as`` "
"esa takrorlash davomida har bir elementga bog'lash uchun o'zgaruvchi nomini "
"oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:761
msgid "``t-foreach`` can also be used with numbers and objects (dictionaries)"
msgstr "``t-foreach`` sonlar va ob'ektlar (lug'atlar) bilan ham ishlatilishi mumkin"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:765
msgid "Defining attributes"
msgstr "Atributlarni aniqlash"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:767
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"QWeb provides two related directives to define computed attributes: "
":samp:`t-att-{name}` and :samp:`t-attf-{name}`. In either case, *name* is"
