"tarjimani amalga oshiradigan ob'ektni qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1263
msgid ""
"It is used to define translatable terms before the translations system is"
" initialized, for class attributes for instance (as modules are loaded "
"before the user's language is configured and translations are "
"downloaded)."
msgstr ""
"U tarjimalar tizimi ishga tushirilguncha tarjima qilinadigan atamalarni "
"aniqlash uchun ishlatiladi, masalan sinf atributlari uchun (chunki modullar "
"foydalanuvchining tili sozlanishidan va tarjimalar yuklab olinishidan oldin "
"yuklanadi)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1268
msgid "Communication with the Odoo Server"
msgstr "Odoo serveri bilan aloqa"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1271
msgid "Contacting Models"
msgstr "Modellar bilan bog'lanish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1273
msgid ""
"Most operations with Odoo involve communicating with *models* "
"implementing business concern, these models will then (potentially) "
"interact with some storage engine (usually PostgreSQL_)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bilan aksariyat amallar biznes muammolarini amalga oshiradigan "
"*modellar* bilan muloqotni o'z ichiga oladi, bu modellar so'ngra (ehtimol) "
"ba'zi saqlash mexanizmi (odatda PostgreSQL_) bilan o'zaro ta'sir qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1277
msgid ""
"Although jQuery_ provides a `$.ajax`_ function for network interactions, "
"communicating with Odoo requires additional metadata whose setup before "
"every call would be verbose and error-prone. As a result, Odoo web "
"provides higher-level communication primitives."
msgstr ""
"jQuery_ tarmoq o'zaro ta'sirlari uchun `$.ajax`_ funksiyasini taqdim etsa "
"ham, Odoo bilan aloqa qilish har bir chaqiruvdan oldin o'rnatilishi batafsil "
"va xatoga moyil bo'lgan qo'shimcha metadata talab qiladi. Natijada, Odoo "
"veb yuqori darajadagi aloqa primitivlarini taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1282
