"This declares a model with two fields, and a method ``my_method()`` which"
" returns a literal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Bu ikkita maydon va so'zma-so'z lug'at qaytaradigan ``my_method()`` metodi "
"bilan model e'lon qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1300
msgid ""
"Here is a sample widget that calls ``my_method()`` and displays the "
"result::"
msgstr ""
"Mana ``my_method()`` ni chaqirib natijani ko'rsatadigan namuna vidjet::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1313
msgid ""
"The class used to call Odoo models is :class:`odoo.Model`. It is "
"instantiated with the Odoo model's name as first parameter "
"(``oepetstore.message_of_the_day`` here)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo modellarini chaqirish uchun ishlatiladigan sinf :class:`odoo.Model` dir. "
"U Odoo modelining nomi birinchi parametr sifatida (bu yerda "
"``oepetstore.message_of_the_day``) bilan yaratiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1317
msgid ""
":func:`~odoo.web.Model.call` can be used to call any (public) method of "
"an Odoo model. It takes the following positional arguments:"
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.web.Model.call` Odoo modelining har qanday (ommaviy) metodini "
"chaqirish uchun ishlatilishi mumkin. U quyidagi pozitsional argumentlarni "
"oladi:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1321
msgid "The name of the method to call, ``my_method`` here"
msgstr "Chaqiriladigan metod nomi, bu yerda ``my_method``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1337
msgid "``args``"
msgstr "``args``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1323
msgid ""
"an array of `positional arguments`_ to provide to the method. Because the"
" example has no positional argument to provide, the ``args`` parameter is"
" not provided."
msgstr ""
"metodga taqdim etish uchun `pozitsional argumentlar`_ massivi. Misol taqdim "
"etish uchun pozitsional argument yo'qligi sababli, ``args`` parametri "
"taqdim etilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1327
msgid "Here is an other example with positional arguments:"
msgstr "Mana pozitsional argumentlar bilan yana bir misol:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1351
msgid "``kwargs``"
msgstr "``kwargs``"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1340
msgid ""
"a mapping of `keyword arguments`_ to pass. The example provides a single "
"named argument ``context``."
msgstr ""
"uzatish uchun `kalit so'z argumentlari`_ xaritasi. Misol bitta nomlangan "
"argument ``context`` ni taqdim etadi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1353
msgid ""
":func:`~odoo.Widget.call` returns a deferred resolved with the value "
"returned by the model's method as first argument."
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.Widget.call` model metodining birinchi argument sifatida "
"qaytargan qiymati bilan hal qilingan kechiktirilganni qaytaradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1357
msgid "CompoundContext"
msgstr "CompoundContext"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1359
msgid ""
"The previous section used a ``context`` argument which was not explained "
"in the method call::"
msgstr ""
"Oldingi bo'lim metod chaqiruvida tushuntirilmagan ``context`` argumentidan "
"foydalangan::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1364
msgid ""
"The context is like a \"magic\" argument that the web client will always "
"give to the server when calling a method. The context is a dictionary "
"containing multiple keys. One of the most important key is the language "
"of the user, used by the server to translate all the messages of the "
"application. Another one is the time zone of the user, used to compute "
"correctly dates and times if Odoo is used by people in different "
"countries."
msgstr ""
"Kontekst metod chaqirilganda veb mijoz har doim serverga beradigan \"sehrli\" "
"argument kabidir. Kontekst bir nechta kalitlarni o'z ichiga olgan lug'atdir. "
"Eng muhim kalitlardan biri - bu ilovaning barcha xabarlarini tarjima qilish "
"uchun server tomonidan ishlatiladigan foydalanuvchi tili. Yana biri - bu "
"turli mamlakatlardagi odamlar Odoo dan foydalansa sana va vaqtlarni to'g'ri "
"hisoblash uchun ishlatiladigan foydalanuvchi vaqt mintaqasi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1371
msgid ""
"The ``argument`` is necessary in all methods, otherwise bad things could "
"happen (such as the application not being translated correctly). That's "
"why, when you call a model's method, you should always provide that "
"argument. The solution to achieve that is to use "
":class:`odoo.web.CompoundContext`."
msgstr ""
"``argument`` barcha metodlarda zarur, aks holda yomon narsalar yuz berishi "
"mumkin (masalan, ilova to'g'ri tarjima qilinmasligi). Shu sababli, model "
"metodini chaqirganda, siz har doim ushbu argumentni taqdim etishingiz kerak. "
"Buni amalga oshirish yechimi :class:`odoo.web.CompoundContext` dan "
"foydalanishdir."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1376
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext` is a class used to pass the user's "
"context (with language, time zone, etc...) to the server as well as "
"adding new keys to the context (some models' methods use arbitrary keys "
"added to the context). It is created by giving to its constructor any "
"number of dictionaries or other :class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext` "
"instances. It will merge all those contexts before sending them to the "
"server."
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext` foydalanuvchining kontekstini (til, vaqt "
"mintaqasi va hokazo) serverga uzatish va kontekstga yangi kalitlar qo'shish "
"uchun ishlatiladigan sinf (ba'zi modellar metodlari kontekstga qo'shilgan "
"ixtiyoriy kalitlardan foydalanadi). U konstruktoriga istalgan miqdordagi "
"lug'atlar yoki boshqa :class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext` namunalari "
"berilishi orqali yaratiladi. U barcha ushbu kontekstlarni serverga yuborishdan "
"oldin birlashtiradi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1394
msgid ""
"You can see the dictionary in the argument ``context`` contains some keys"
" that are related to the configuration of the current user in Odoo plus "
"the ``new_key`` key that was added when instantiating "
":class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext`."
msgstr ""
"``context`` argumentidagi lug'at Odoo dagi joriy foydalanuvchi "
"konfiguratsiyasi bilan bog'liq ba'zi kalitlar va :class:`~odoo.web.CompoundContext` "
"yaratilganda qo'shilgan ``new_key`` kalitini o'z ichiga olganini ko'rishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1400
msgid "Queries"
msgstr "So'rovlar"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1402
msgid ""
"While :func:`~odoo.Model.call` is sufficient for any interaction with "
"Odoo models, Odoo Web provides a helper for simpler and clearer querying "
"of models (fetching of records based on various conditions): "
":func:`~odoo.Model.query` which acts as a shortcut for the common "
"combination of :py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` and "
"::py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read`. It provides a clearer syntax to "
"search and read models::"
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.Model.call` Odoo modellari bilan har qanday o'zaro ta'sir uchun "
"etarli bo'lsa ham, Odoo veb modellarni soddaroq va ravshan so'rash (turli "
"shartlarga asoslangan yozuvlarni olish) uchun yordamchi taqdim etadi: "
":func:`~odoo.Model.query` bu :py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.search` va "
":py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` ning keng tarqalgan kombinatsiyasi uchun "
"yorliq sifatida ishlaydi. U modellarni qidirish va o'qish uchun ravshonroq "
"sintaksis taqdim etadi::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1417
msgid "versus::"
msgstr "va quyidagiga nisbatan::"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1427
msgid ""
":func:`~odoo.web.Model.query` takes an optional list of fields as "
"parameter (if no field is provided, all fields of the model are fetched)."
" It returns a :class:`odoo.web.Query` which can be further customized "
"before being executed"
msgstr ""
":func:`~odoo.web.Model.query` parametr sifatida ixtiyoriy maydonlar ro'yxatini "
"oladi (agar maydon taqdim etilmasa, modelning barcha maydonlari olinadi). U "
"bajarilishidan oldin yanada sozlanishi mumkin bo'lgan :class:`odoo.web.Query` "
"ni qaytaradi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1431
msgid ""
":class:`~odoo.web.Query` represents the query being built. It is "
"immutable, methods to customize the query actually return a modified "
"copy, so it's possible to use the original and the new version side-by-"
"side. See :class:`~odoo.web.Query` for its customization options."
msgstr ""
":class:`~odoo.web.Query` qurilayotgan so'rovni ifodalaydi. U o'zgarmas, "
"so'rovni sozlash metodlari aslida o'zgartirilgan nusxani qaytaradi, shuning "
"uchun asl va yangi versiyani yonma-yon ishlatish mumkin. Sozlash imkoniyatlari "
"uchun :class:`~odoo.web.Query` ga qarang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1436
msgid ""
"When the query is set up as desired, simply call "
":func:`~odoo.web.Query.all` to execute it and return a deferred to its "
"result. The result is the same as :py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read`'s, "
"an array of dictionaries where each dictionary is a requested record, "
"with each requested field a dictionary key."
msgstr ""
"So'rov kerakli tarzda o'rnatilgach, uni bajarish va natijaga kechiktirilganni "
"qaytarish uchun oddiygina :func:`~odoo.web.Query.all` ni chaqiring. Natija "
":py:meth:`~odoo.models.Model.read` ning natiijasi bilan bir xil, har bir "
"lug'at so'ralgan yozuv bo'lgan lug'atlar massivi, har bir so'ralgan maydon "
"lug'at kaliti bilan."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1443
