msgstr ""
"5 ta o'yinchoq ko'rsatadigan ``PetToysList`` vidjetini yarating (ularning "
"nomi va rasmlaridan foydalanib)."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1516
msgid ""
"The pet toys are not stored in a new model, instead they're stored in "
"``product.product`` using a special category *Pet Toys*. You can see the "
