"Oldindan yaratilgan o'yinchoqlarni ko'rish va yangilarini qo'shish uchun "
":menuselection:`Pet Store --> Pet Store --> Pet Toys` ga o'ting. Faqat uy "
"hayvoni o'yinchoqlarini tanlash uchun to'g'ri domenni yaratish uchun "
"``product.product`` ni o'rganishingiz kerak bo'lishi mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1523
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"In Odoo, images are generally stored in regular fields encoded as "
