"HTML base64 dan to'g'ridan-to'g'ri rasmlarni ko'rsatishni "
":samp:`<img src=\"data:{mime_type};base64,{base64_image_data}\"/>` bilan qo'llab-quvvatlaydi"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:1527
