msgstr ""
"``product.product`` ga kenglik va uzunlikni saqlaydigan ikkita maydon qo'shing, "
"so'ngra xaritada mahsulot kelib chiqishining kenglik va uzunligini ko'rsatadigan "
"yangi forma vidjetini yarating"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2192
msgid "To display the map, use Google Map's embedding:"
msgstr "Xaritani ko'rsatish uchun Google Xaritani joylashtirishdan foydalaning:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2199
msgid ""
"where ``XXX`` should be replaced by the latitude and ``YYY`` by the "
"longitude."
msgstr "bu yerda ``XXX`` kenglik va ``YYY`` uzunlik bilan almashtirilishi kerak."

