msgstr "Joriy koordinatani olish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2236
msgid ""
"Add a button resetting the product's coordinates to the location of the "
"user, you can get these coordinates using the `javascript geolocation "
"API`_."
msgstr ""
"Mahsulot koordinatalarini foydalanuvchi joylashuviga tiklash tugmasini "
"qo'shing, bu koordinatalarni `javascript geolokatsiya API`_ yordamida "
"olishingiz mumkin."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2240
msgid ""
"Now we would like to display an additional button to automatically set "
