msgstr ""
"Foydalanuvchi koordinatalarini olish uchun oson usul geolokatsiya JavaScript "
"API sidan foydalanish. `Uni qanday ishlatishni bilish uchun onlayn "
"hujjatlarga qarang`_."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2248
msgid ""
"Please also note that the user should not be able to click on that button"
