msgstr ""
"Forma ko'rinishi faqat o'qish rejimida bo'lganda foydalanuvchi ushbu tugmani "
"bosa olmasligi kerakligini ham e'tiboring. Shunday qilib, ushbu maxsus "
"vidjet har qanday maydon kabi ``effective_readonly`` xususiyatini to'g'ri "
"boshqarishi kerak. Buni amalga oshirishning bir usuli ``effective_readonly`` "
"true bo'lganda tugmani yo'q qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/web.rst:2299
msgid ""
"as a separate concept from instances. In many languages classes are full-"
