#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/05_dynamic_templates.rst:8
msgid "Adapt the shop template"
msgstr "Do'kon shablonini moslashtirish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/05_dynamic_templates.rst:10
msgid ""
"Now, let's adapt the dynamic sections of the website. As you may know, "
"some pages such as those for eCommerce are automatically generated. Pages"
" like the shop, product, and checkout are automatically generated when "
"the `website_sale` application is installed. These template pages pull "
"their displayed information from the backend."
msgstr ""
"Endi, veb-saytning dinamik bo'limlarini moslashtiramiz. Bilganingizdek, "
"eCommerce sahifalari kabi ba'zi sahifalar avtomatik tarzda yaratiladi. "
"Do'kon, mahsulot va to'lov sahifalari `website_sale` ilovasi o'rnatilganda "
"avtomatik tarzda yaratiladi. Bu shablon sahifalar ko'rsatilgan ma'lumotlarni "
"backend dan oladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/05_dynamic_templates.rst:15
msgid ""
"To modify these pages, we need to edit the standard Odoo template. This "
"can be done using SCSS, presets, and especially XPath. Locate the "
"standard Odoo template you want to modify and extend it using `XPath`. "
"Following the Airproof design, let's begin by modifying the shop view."
msgstr ""
"Bu sahifalarni o'zgartirish uchun standart Odoo shablonini tahrirlashimiz "
"kerak. Bu SCSS, oldindan sozlamalar va ayniqsa XPath yordamida amalga "
"oshirilishi mumkin. O'zgartirmoqchi bo'lgan standart Odoo shablonini toping "
"va uni `XPath` yordamida kengaytiring. Airproof dizayniga amal qilib, "
"do'kon ko'rinishini o'zgartirishdan boshlaylik."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/05_dynamic_templates.rst:19
msgid ""
"First, locate the standard template in Odoo : "
":menuselection:`website_sale --> templates.xml --> id=\"products\"`."
msgstr ""
"Avvalo, Odoo da standart shablonni toping : "
":menuselection:`website_sale --> templates.xml --> id=\"products\"`."

