msgid ""
"Find the solution in our Airproof example on `presets.xml "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/data/presets.xml>`_,"
" `website_sale_templates.xml "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/views/website_sale_templates.xml>`_"
" part *product page*, and `product_page.scss "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/static/src/scss/pages/product_page.scss>`_."
msgstr ""
"Yechimni Airproof misolimizdagi `presets.xml "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/data/presets.xml>`_, "
"`website_sale_templates.xml "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/views/website_sale_templates.xml>`_ "
"ning *mahsulot sahifasi* qismi va `product_page.scss "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/static/src/scss/pages/product_page.scss>`_ "
"da toping."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:3
msgid "Chapter 6 - Going live"
msgstr "6-bob - Jonli rejimga o'tish"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:10
msgid ""
"Congratulations! Your client has a beautifully designed homepage and "
"contact page, and the eCommerce is fully adapted to the Airproof design. "
"Amazing!"
msgstr ""
"Tabriklaymiz! Mijozingizning chiroyli bosh sahifasi va aloqa sahifasi bor, "
"eCommerce esa Airproof dizayniga to'liq moslashtirilgan. Ajoyib!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:13
msgid "Now, the client wants the website translated into French. To do so:"
msgstr "Endi mijoz veb-saytni fransuz tiliga tarjima qilishni istaydi. Buning uchun:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:15
msgid ""
"Add French to the website in the settings and enable the language "
"switcher in the header via presets."
msgstr ""
"Sozlamalarda veb-saytga fransuz tilini qo'shing va oldindan sozlamalar "
"orqali sarlavhada til almashtiruvchini yoqing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:17
msgid ""
"Then for the translation itself, you have two options. We shall therefore"
" test both:"
msgstr ""
"Keyin tarjimaning o'zi uchun ikki xil variant mavjud. Shuning uchun ikkalasini ham sinaymiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:19
msgid "Translate the content of the homepage carousel through the backend."
msgstr "Bosh sahifa carousel kontentini backend orqali tarjima qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:20
msgid "But for the menu, make the translations through the frontend."
msgstr "Lekin menyu uchun tarjimalarni frontend orqali amalga oshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:22
msgid ""
"Export the French :file:`.po` file for your Airproof module and place it "
"in the :file:`/i18n` translations folder."
msgstr ""
"Airproof modulingiz uchun fransuz :file:`.po` faylini eksport qiling va "
"uni :file:`/i18n` tarjimalar papkasiga joylashtiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:24
msgid ""
"If you would like, you can add more translations directly by editing the "
":file:`.po` file. (Using Poedit software, your code editor, or another "
"translation tool.)"
msgstr ""
"Xohlasangiz, :file:`.po` faylini tahrirlash orqali to'g'ridan-to'g'ri ko'proq "
"tarjimalar qo'shishingiz mumkin. (Poedit dasturi, kod muharriringiz yoki boshqa "
"tarjima vositasidan foydalaning.)"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:28
msgid ""
"See reference documentation on :ref:`website_themes/translations/backend`"
" and :ref:`website_themes/translations/frontend` translations, and how to"
" :ref:`website_themes/translations/export` them."
msgstr ""
":ref:`website_themes/translations/backend` va "
":ref:`website_themes/translations/frontend` tarjimalari hamda ularni "
":ref:`website_themes/translations/export` qilish haqida ma'lumot uchun qo'llanmani ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:33
msgid ""
"Be careful when using Poedit, as it doesn't handle tags with styles well "
"and generates an :file:`.mo` file."
msgstr ""
"Poedit dan foydalanishda ehtiyot bo'ling, chunki u stillar bilan teglarni "
"yaxshi ishlamaydi va :file:`.mo` fayl hosil qiladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:35
msgid ""
"To see the changes made directly via the :file:`.po` file, you will need "
"to manually import the file."
msgstr ""
":file:`.po` fayl orqali to'g'ridan-to'g'ri kiritilgan o'zgarishlarni ko'rish "
"uchun faylni qo'lda import qilishingiz kerak bo'ladi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:40
msgid ""
"Take a look at what the file `i18n/fr_BE.po "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/i18n/fr_BE.po>`_"
" of our Airproof example looks like."
msgstr ""
"Airproof misolimizdagi `i18n/fr_BE.po "
"<https://github.com/odoo/tutorials/blob/19.0/website_airproof/i18n/fr_BE.po>`_ "
"fayli qanday ko'rinishga ega ekanligini ko'rib chiqing."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:48
msgid ""
"Great job! The website is now completely finished and your module is "
"ready for installation in the client's SaaS database."
msgstr ""
"Ajoyib ish! Veb-sayt endi to'liq tayyor va modulingiz mijozning SaaS "
"ma'lumotlar bazasiga o'rnatishga tayyor."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:51
msgid "Just before that, test the import process on a new database."
msgstr "Undan oldin, yangi ma'lumotlar bazasida import jarayonini sinab ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:54
msgid ""
"See reference documentation on how to :doc:`deploy a module "
"</developer/howtos/website_themes/going_live>` on an Odoo SaaS database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo SaaS ma'lumotlar bazasiga :doc:`modul joylashtirish "
"</developer/howtos/website_themes/going_live>` haqida ma'lumot uchun qo'llanmani ko'ring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:58
msgid ""
"Ensure the `base_import_module` is installed on the database before the "
"module installation."
msgstr ""
"Modul o'rnatishdan oldin `base_import_module` ma'lumotlar bazasida "
"o'rnatilganligiga ishonch hosil qiling."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:59
msgid "Verify all required applications are installed."
msgstr "Barcha talab qilingan ilovalar o'rnatilganligini tekshiring."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:60
msgid "Skip the theme installation steps and start from scratch."
msgstr "Mavzu o'rnatish bosqichlarini o'tkazib yuboring va noldan boshlang."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:61
msgid ""
"Manually import translations after module installation, as they won't "
"apply automatically."
msgstr ""
"Modul o'rnatilgandan so'ng tarjimalarni qo'lda import qiling, chunki ular "
"avtomatik tarzda qo'llanilmaydi."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:64
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Xulosa"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:66
msgid ""
"Congratulations on completing the **Build a module for a website theme** "
"tutorial! You've successfully navigated through every stage, from setting"
" up your development environment to launching a fully customized Odoo "
"website theme."
msgstr ""
"**Veb-sayt mavzusi uchun modul qurish** darsligini muvaffaqiyatli yakunlaganingiz "
"bilan tabriklaymiz! Siz ishlab chiqish muhitini sozlashdan to to'liq "
"moslashtirilgan Odoo veb-sayt mavzusini ishga tushirishgacha bo'lgan har "
"bir bosqichni muvaffaqiyatli bosib o'tdingiz."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:70
msgid "Throughout this journey, you've mastered:"
msgstr "Bu sayohat davomida siz quyidagilarni mukammal o'zlashtirdingiz:"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:72
msgid ""
"✅ **Theme module creation** - setting up the structure, declaring Odoo "
"and Bootstrap variables."
msgstr ""
"✅ **Mavzu moduli yaratish** - tuzilmani sozlash, Odoo va Bootstrap "
"o'zgaruvchilarini e'lon qilish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:73
msgid ""
"✅ **Website building** - creating pages, adding media, and constructing "
"dynamic building blocks."
msgstr ""
"✅ **Veb-sayt qurish** - sahifalar yaratish, media qo'shish va dinamik "
"qurilish bloklari yaratish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:75
msgid ""
"✅ **Advanced customization** - implementing custom SCSS, JavaScript, "
"headers, footers, and unique design elements."
msgstr ""
"✅ **Kengaytirilgan sozlash** - maxsus SCSS, JavaScript, sarlavhalar, oyoq "
"qismlar va noyob dizayn elementlarini amalga oshirish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:77
msgid ""
"✅ **Visual enhancements** - designing background shapes, gradients, and "
"animations for an engaging user experience."
msgstr ""
"✅ **Vizual yaxshilanishlar** - jalb qiluvchi foydalanuvchi tajribasi uchun "
"fon shakllari, gradientlar va animatsiyalarni loyihalash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:79
msgid ""
"✅ **eCommerce optimization** - adapting shop and product templates for a "
"seamless shopping experience."
msgstr ""
"✅ **eCommerce optimallashtirish** - muammosiz xarid tajribasi uchun do'kon "
"va mahsulot shablonlarini moslashtirish."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:80
msgid ""
"✅ **Final preparations** - managing translations and ensuring a smooth "
"module import."
msgstr ""
"✅ **Yakuniy tayyorgarlik** - tarjimalarni boshqarish va silliq modul "
"importini ta'minlash."

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:83
msgid ""
"With these skills, you're now ready to design and develop professional, "
"fully customized website themes. Well done!"
msgstr ""
"Bu ko'nikmalar bilan siz endi professional, to'liq moslashtirilgan veb-sayt "
"mavzularini loyihalash va ishlab chiqishga tayyorsiz. Barakali bo'lsin!"

#: ../../content/developer/tutorials/website_theme/06_going_live.rst:84
msgid "We can't wait to see the amazing themes you'll create in the future."
msgstr "Kelajakda yaratadigan ajoyib mavzularingizni ko'rishni sabrsizlik bilan kutamiz."
